quran[5604]{c,v,t}:
  1,2,"El hamdu lillahi rabbil alemin"
  1,3,"Er rahmanir rahÄḟym"
  1,4,"Maliki yevmid din"
  1,5,"Iyyake naÂṀbudu ve iyyake nesteÄḟyn"
  1,6,"Ihdinas sÄḟratal mustekÄḟym"
  1,7,"SÄḟratallezine enÂṀamte aleyhim gayril magdubi aleyhim ve lad dallin"
  2,3,"EllezÄḟne yuÂṀminune bil gaybi ve yukÄḟymunas salate ve mimma razaknahum yunfikun"
  2,4,"Vellezine yuÂṀminune bi ma unzile ileyke ve ma unzile min kablik* ve bil ahÄḟrati hum yukÄḟnun"
  2,5,"Ulaike ala hudem mir rabbihim ve ulaike humul muflihun"
  2,6,"InnellezÄḟne keferu sevaun aleyhim e enzertehum em lem tunzirhum la yuÂṀminun"
  2,7,"Hatemallahu ala kulubihim ve ala semÂṀÄḟhim* ve ala ebsarihim gasaveh* ve lehum azabun azÄḟym"
  2,8,"Ve minen nasi mey yekulu amenna billahi ve bil yevmil ahÄḟri ve ma hum bi muÂṀminÄḟn"
  2,9,"Yuhadiunellahe vellezÄḟne amenu* ve ma yahdeune illa enfusehum ve ma yesÂṀurun"
  2,10,"FÄḟ kulubihim meradun fe zadehumullahu merada* ve lehum azabun elÄḟmum bi ma kanu yekzibun"
  2,11,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehum la tufsidu fil erdÄḟ kalu innema nahnu muslihun"
  2,12,"Ela innehum humul mufsidune ve lakil la lesÂṀurun"
  2,13,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehum aminu kema amenen nasu kalu e nuÂṀminu kema amenes sufehaÂṀ* ela innehum humus sufehau ve lakil la yaÂṀlemun"
  2,14,"Ve iza lekullezÄḟne amenu kalu amenna* ve iza halev ila seyatÄḟynihim kalu inna meakum innema nahnu mustehziun"
  2,15,"Allahu yestehziu bihim ve yemudduhum fÄḟ tugyanihim yaÂṀmehun"
  2,16,"UlaikellezÄḟnesteravud dalalete bil huda* fe ma rabihat ticaratuhum ve ma kanu muhtedÄḟn"
  2,17,"Meseluhum ke meselillezistevkade nara* fe lemma edaet ma havlehu zehebellahu bi nurihim ve terakehum fÄḟ zulumatil la yubsÄḟrun"
  2,18,"Summum bukmun umyun fe hum la yarciun"
  2,19,"Ev ke seyyibim mines semai fÄḟhi zulumatuv ve raÂṀduv ve bark* yecÂṀalune esabiahum fÄḟ azanihim mines savaÄḟkÄḟ hazeral mevt* vallahu muhÄḟytum bil kafirÄḟn"
  2,20,"Yekadul berku yahtafu ebsarahum* kullema edae lehum mesev fÄḟhi ve iza azleme aleyhim kamu* ve lev saellahu le zehebe bi semÂṀÄḟhim ve ebsarihim* innellahe ala kulli seyÂṀin kadiyr"
  2,21,"Ya eyyuhen nasuÂṀbudu rabbekumullezÄḟ halekakum vellezÄḟne min kablikum leallekum tettekun"
  2,22,"EllezÄḟ ceale lekumul erda firasev ves semae binaa* ve enzele mines semai maen fe ahrece bihÄḟ mines semerati rizkal lekum* fe la tecÂṀalu lillahi endadev ve entum taÂṀlemun"
  2,23,"Ve in kuntum fÄḟ raybim mimma nezzelna ala abdina feÂṀtu bi suratim mim mislih* vedÂṀu suhedaekum min dunillahi in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  2,24,"Fe illem tefÂṀalu ve len tefÂṀalu fettekun naralletÄḟ vekuduhen nasu vel hÄḟcarah* uÄḟddet lil kafirÄḟn"
  2,25,"Ve bessirillezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati enne lehum cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enhar* kullema ruziku minha min semeratir rizkan kalu hazellezÄḟ ruzÄḟkna min kablu ve utu bihÄḟ mutesabiha* ve lehum fÄḟha ezvacum mutahheratuv ve hum fÄḟha halidun"
  2,26,"Innellahe la yestahyÄḟ ey yadribe meselem ma beudaten fe ma fevkaha* fe emmellezÄḟne amenu fe yaÂṀlemune ennehul hakku mir rabbihim* ve emmellezÄḟne keferu fe yekulune maza eradellahu bi haza mesela* yudÄḟllu bihÄḟ kesÄḟrav ve yehdÄḟ bihÄḟ kesÄḟra* ve ma yudÄḟllu bihÄḟ illel fasikÄḟyn"
  2,27,"EllezÄḟne yenkudune ahdellahi mim baÂṀdi mÄḟsakÄḟh* ve yaktaune ma emerallahu bihÄḟ ey yusale ve yufsidune fil ard* ulaike humul hasirun"
  2,28,"Keyfe tekfurune billahi ve kuntum emvaten fe ahyakum* summe yumÄḟtukum summe yuhyÄḟkum summe ileyhi turceun"
  2,29,"HuvellezÄḟ haleka lekum ma fil erdÄḟ cemÄḟan summesteva iles semai fe sevvahunne sebÂṀa semavat* ve huve bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  2,30,"Ve iz kale rabbuke lil melaiketi innÄḟ caÄḟlun fil erdÄḟ halÄḟfeh* kalu e tecÂṀalu fÄḟha mey yufsidu fÄḟha ve yesfikud dimaÂṀ* ve nahnu nusebbihu bi hamdike ve nukaddisu lek* kale innÄḟ aÂṀlemu ma la taÂṀlemun"
  2,31,"Ve alleme ademel esmae kulleha summe aradahum alel melaiketi fe kale embiunÄḟ bi esmai haulai in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  2,32,"Kalu subhaneke la Äḟlme lena illa ma alemtena* inneke entel alÄḟmul hakÄḟm"
  2,33,"Kale ya ademu embiÂṀhum bi esmaihim* felemma embeehum bi esmaihim kale e lem ekul lekum innÄḟ aÂṀlemu gaybes semavati vel erdÄḟ ve aÂṀlemu ma tubdune ve ma kuntum tektumun"
  2,34,"Ve iz kulna lil melaiketiscudu li ademe fe secedu illa iblÄḟs* eba vestekbera ve kane minel kafirÄḟn"
  2,35,"Ve kulna ya ademuskun ente ve zevcukel cennete ve kula minha ragaden haysu siÂṀtuma* ve la takraba hazihis secerate fe tekuna minez zalimÄḟn"
  2,36,"Fe ezellehumes seytanu anha fe ahracehuma mimma kana fÄḟh* ve kulnehbitu baÂṀdukum li baÂṀdÄḟn aduvv* ve lekum fil erdÄḟ mustekarruv ve metaun ila hÄḟyn"
  2,37,"Fe telekka ademu mir rabbihÄḟ kelimatin fe tabe aleyh* innehu huvet tevvabur rahÄḟym"
  2,38,"Kulnehbitu minha cemÄḟa* fe imma yeÂṀtiyennekum minnÄḟ huden fe men tebia hudaye fe la havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  2,39,"VellezÄḟne keferu ve kezzebu bi ayatina ulaike ashabun nar* hum fÄḟha halidun"
  2,40,"Ya benÄḟ israÄḟlezkuru nÄḟÂṀmetiyelletÄḟ enÂṀamtu aleykum ve evfu bi ahdÄḟ ufi biahdikum ve iyyaye ferhebun"
  2,41,"Ve aminu bi ma enzeltu musaddikal li ma meakum ve la tekunu evvele kafirim bih* ve la testeru bi ayatÄḟ semenen kalilev ve iyaye fettekun"
  2,42,"Ve la telbisul hakka bil batÄḟlÄḟ ve tektumul hakka ve entum taÂṀlemun"
  2,43,"Ve ekÄḟymus salate ve atuz zekate verkeu mear rakiÄḟyn"
  2,44,"E teÂṀmurunen nase bil birri ve tensevne enfusekum ve entum tetlunel kitab* e fe la taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  2,45,"VesteÄḟynu bis sabri ves salah* ve inneha le keÄḟratun illa alel hasiÄḟyn"
  2,46,"EllezÄḟne yezunnune ennehum mulaku rabbihim ve ennehum ileyhi raciun"
  2,47,"Ya benÄḟ israÄḟlezkuru nÄḟÂṀmetiyelletÄḟ enÂṀamtu aleykum ve ennÄḟ faddaltukum alel alemÄḟn"
  2,48,"Vetteku yevmel la teczÄḟ nefsun an nefsin seyÂṀev ve la yukbelu minha sefaatuv ve la yuÂṀhazu minha adluv ve la hum yunsarun"
  2,49,"Ve iz necceynakum min ali firÂṀavneyesumunekum suel azabi yuzebbihune ebnaekum ve yestahyune nisaekum* ve fÄḟ zalikum belaum mir rabbikum azÄḟym"
  2,50,"Ve iz ferakna bikumul bahra fe enceynakum ve agrakna ale firÂṀavne ve entum tenzurun"
  2,51,"Veiz vaadna musa erbeÄḟyne leyleten summettehaztumul Äḟcle mim baÂṀdihÄḟ ve entum zalimun"
  2,52,"Summe afevna ankum mim baÂṀdi zalike leallekum teskurun"
  2,53,"Ve iz ateyna musel kitabe vel furkane leallekum teehtedun"
  2,54,"Ve iz kale musa li kavmihÄḟ ya kavmi innekum zalemtum enfusekum bittihazikumul Äḟcle fe tubu ila bariikum faktulu enfusekum* zalikum hayrul lekum Äḟnde bariikum* fe tabe aleykum* innehu huvet tevvabur rahÄḟym"
  2,55,"Ve iz kultum ya musa len nuÂṀmine leke hatta nerallahe cehraten fe ehazetkumus saÄḟkatu ve entum tenzurun"
  2,56,"Summe beasnakum mim baÂṀdi mevtikum leallekum teskurun"
  2,57,"Ve zallelna aleykumul gamame ve enzelna aleykumul menne ves selva* kulu min tayyibati ma razaknakum* ve ma zalemuna ve lakin kanu enfusehum yazlimun"
  2,58,"Ve iz kulnedhulu hazihil karyete fe kulu minha haysu siÂṀtum ragadev vedhulul babe succedev ve kulu hÄḟttatun nagfirlekum hatayakum* ve senezÄḟdul muhsinÄḟn"
  2,59,"Fe beddellezÄḟne zalemu kavlen gayrallezÄḟ kÄḟyle lehum fe enzelna alellezÄḟne zalemu riczem mines semai bi ma kanu yefsukun"
  2,60,"Ve izisteska musa li kavmihÄḟ fe kulnadrib bi asakel hacer* fenfecerat minhusneta asrate ayna* kad alime kullu unasim mesrabehum* kulu vesrabu mir rizkÄḟllahi ve la taÂṀsev fil erdÄḟ mufsidÄḟn"
  2,61,"Ve iz kultum ya musa len nasbira ala taamiv vahÄḟdin fedÂṀu lena rabbeke yuhric lena mimma tumbitul erdu mim bakliha ve kÄḟssaiha ve fumiha ve adesiha ve besaliha* kale e testebdilunellezÄḟ huv edna billezÄḟ huve hayr* ihbitu mÄḟsran fe inne lekum ma seeltum* ve duribet aleyhimuz zilletu vel meskenetu ve bau bi gadabim minellah* zalike bi ennehum kanu yekfurune bi ayatillahi ve yaktulunen nebiyyÄḟne bi gayril hakk* zalike bi ma asav ve kanu yaÂṀtedun"
  2,62,"InnellezÄḟne amenu vellezÄḟne hadu ven nesara ves sabiÄḟne min amene billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟri ve amile salihan fe lehum ecruhum Äḟnde rabbihim *ve la havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  2,63,"Ve iz ehazna mÄḟsakakum ve rafaÂṀna fevkakumut tur * huzu ma ateynakum bi kuvvetiv vezkuru ma fÄḟhi leallekum tettekun"
  2,64,"Summe tevelleytum mim baÂṀdi zalik *fe lev la fadlullahi aleykum ve rahmetuhu lekuntum minel hasirÄḟn"
  2,65,"Ve le kad alimtumullezÄḟnaÂṀtedev minkum fis sebti fe kulna lehum kunu kÄḟradeten hasiÄḟn"
  2,66,"Fe cealnaha nekalel li ma beyne yedeyha ve ma halfeha ve mevÂṀÄḟzatel lil muttekÄḟyn"
  2,67,"Ve iz kale musa li kavmihÄḟ innellahe yeÂṀmurukum en tezbehu bekarah *kalu etettehÄḟzuna huzuva *kale euzu billahi en ekune minel cahilÄḟn"
  2,68,"KaludÂṀu lena rabbeke yubeyyil lena ma hÄḟ *kale innehu yekulu inneha bekarutl la fariduv ve la bikr * avanum beyne zalik * fefÂṀalu ma tuÂṀmerun"
  2,69,"Kaludu lena rabbeke yubeyyil lena ma levnuha *kale innehu yekulu inneha bekaratun safrau fakÄḟul levnuha tesurrun nazÄḟrÄḟn"
  2,70,"KaludÂṀu lena rabbeke yubeyyil lena ma hiye innel bekara tesabehe aleyna* ve inna in saellahu le muhtedun"
  2,71,"Kale innehu yekulu inneha bekaratul la zelulun tusÄḟrul erda ve la teskÄḟl hars* musellemetul lasiyete fÄḟha* kalul ane ciÂṀte bil hakk* fe zebehuha ve ma kadu yefÂṀalun"
  2,72,"Ve iz kateltum nefsen feddaraÂṀtum fÄḟha* vallahu muhricum ma kuntum tektumun"
  2,73,"Fe kulnadribuhu bi baÂṀdÄḟha* kezalike yuhyillahul mevta ve yurÄḟkum ayatihÄḟ leallekum taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  2,74,"Summe kaset kulubukum mim baÂṀdi zalike fe hiye kel hÄḟcarati ev eseddu kasveh* ve inne minel hÄḟcarati lema yetefecceru minhul enhar* ve inne minha lema yessekkaku fe yahrucu minhul maÂṀ* ve inne minha lema yehbitu min hasyetillah* vemallahu bi gafilin amma taÂṀmelun"
  2,75,"E fetatmeune ey yuÂṀminu lekum ve kad kane ferÄḟkum minhum yesmeune kelamellahi summe yuharrifunehu mim baÂṀdi ma akaluhu ve hum yaÂṀlemun"
  2,76,"Ve iza lekullezÄḟne amenu kalu amenna* ve iza hala baÂṀduhum ila baÂṀdin kalu etuhaddisunehum bi ma fetehallahu aleykum li yuhaccukum bihÄḟ Äḟnde rabbikum* e fe la taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  2,77,"E ve la yaÂṀlemune ennellahe yaÂṀlemu ma yusirrune ve ma yuÂṀlinun"
  2,78,"Ve minhum ummiyyune la yaÂṀlemunel kitabe illa emaniyye ve in hum illa yezunnun"
  2,79,"Fe veylul lillezÄḟne yektubunel kitabe bi eydÄḟhim summe yekulunel kitabe bi eydÄḟhim summe yekulune haza min Äḟndillahi li yesteru bihÄḟ semenen kalÄḟla* fe veylul lehum mimma ketebet eydÄḟhim ve veylul lehum mimma yeksibun"
  2,80,"Ve kalu len temessenen naru illa eyyamem maÂṀdudeh* kul ettehaztum Äḟndellahi ahden fe ley yuhlifellahu ahdehu em tekulune alellahi ma la taÂṀlemun"
  2,81,"Bela men kesebe seyyietev ve ehatat bihÄḟ hatÄḟyÂṀetuhu fe ulaike ashabun nar* hum fÄḟha halidun"
  2,82,"VellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati ulaike ashabul cenneh* hum fÄḟha halidun"
  2,83,"Ve iz ehazna mÄḟsaka benÄḟ israÄḟle la taÂṀbudune illellahe ve bil valideyni Äḟhsanev ve izl kurba vel yetam vel mesakÄḟni ve kulu lin nasi husnev ve ekÄḟymus salate ve atuz zekah* summe tevelleytum ila kalÄḟlem minkum ve entum muÂṀridun"
  2,84,"Ve iz ehazna mÄḟsakakum la tesfikune dimaekum ve la tuhricune enfusekum min diyarikum summe akrartum ve entum teshedun"
  2,85,"Summe entum haulai taktulune enfusekum ve tuhricune ferÄḟkam minkum min diyarihim tezaherune aleyhim bil ismi vel udvan* ve iy yeÂṀtukum usara tufaduhum ve huve muharramun aleykum Äḟhracuhum* e fe tuÂṀminune bi ba7dÄḟl kitabi ve tekfurune bi baÂṀd* fe ma cezau mey yefÂṀalu zalike minkum illa hÄḟzyun fil hayatid dunya* ve yevmel kÄḟyameti yuraddune ila eseddil azab* vemallahu bi gafilin amma taÂṀmelun"
  2,86,"UlaikellezÄḟnesteravul hayated dunya bil ahÄḟrati fe la yuhaffefu anhumul azabu ve la hum yunsarun"
  2,87,"Ve le kad ateyna musel kitabe ve kaffeyna mim baÂṀdihÄḟ bir rusuli ve ateyna Äḟysebne meryemel beyyinati ve eyyednahu bi ruhÄḟl kudus* e fe kullema caekum rasulum bima la tehva enfusukumustekbartum* fe ferÄḟkan kezzebtum ve ferÄḟkan taktulun"
  2,88,"Ve kalu kulubuna gulf* bel leanehumullahu bi kufrihim fe kalÄḟlem ma yuÂṀminun"
  2,89,"Ve lemma caehum kitabum min Äḟndillahi musaddikul lima mealhum ve kanu min kablu yesteftihune alellezÄḟne keferu* fe lemma caehum ma arafu keferu bihÄḟ fe laÂṀnetullahi alel kafirÄḟn"
  2,90,"BiÂṀsemesterav bihÄḟ enfusehum ey yekfuru bi ma enzelellahu bagyen ey yunezzilellahu min fadlihÄḟ ala mey yesau min Äḟbadih* fe bau bi gadabin ala gadab* ve lil kafirÄḟne azabum muhÄḟn"
  2,91,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehum aminu bi ma enzelellahu kalu nuÂṀminu bima unzile aleyna ve yekfurune bi ma veraehu ve huvel hakku musaddikal lima meahum* kul fe lime taktulune embiyaellahi min kablu in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  2,92,"Ve le kad caekum musa bil beyyinati summettehaztumul Äḟcle mim baÂṀdihÄḟ ve entum zalimun"
  2,93,"Ve iz ehazna mÄḟsakakum ve rafaÂṀna fevkakumut tur* huzu ma ateynakum bi kuvvetiv vesmeu* kalu semÄḟÂṀna ve asayna ve usribu fÄḟ kulubihimul Äḟcle bi kufrihÄḟmv kul biÂṀsema yeÂṀmurukum bihÄḟ Äḟmanukum in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  2,94,"Kul in kanet lekumud darul ahÄḟratu indellahi halisatem min dunin nasi fe temennevul mevte in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  2,95,"Ve ley yetemennevhu ebedem bima kaddemet eydÄḟhim* vallahu alÄḟmum biz zalimÄḟn"
  2,96,"Ve le tecidennehum ahrasan nasi ala hayah* ve minellezÄḟne esraku yeveddu ehaduhum lev yuammeru elfe seneh* ve ma huve bi muzahzihÄḟhÄḟ minel azabi ey yuammer* vallahu besÄḟyrum bima yaÂṀmelun"
  2,97,"Kul men kane aduvvel licibrÄḟle fe innehu nezzelehu ala kalbike bi iznillahi musaddikal lima beyne yedeyhi ve hudev ve busra lil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  2,98,"Men kane aduvvel lillahi ve melaiketihÄḟ ve rusulihÄḟ ve cibrÄḟle ve mÄḟkale fe innellahe aduvvul lil kafirÄḟn"
  2,99,"Ve le kad enzelna ileyke ayatim beyyinat* ve ma yekfuru biha illel fasikun"
  2,100,"E ve kullema ahedu ahden nebezehu ferÄḟkum minhum* bel ekseruhum la yuÂṀminun"
  2,101,"Ve lemma caehum rasulum min Äḟndillahi musaddikul lima mealhum nebeze ferÄḟkum minellezÄḟne utul kitab* kitabellahi verae zuhurihim ke ennehum la yaÂṀlemun"
  2,102,"Vettebeu ma tetlus seyatÄḟynu ala mulki suleyman* ve ma kefera suleymanu ve lakinnes seyatÄḟyne keferu yuallimunen nasas sÄḟhra ve ma unzile alel melekeyni bi babile harute ve marut* ve ma yuallimani min ehadin hatta yekula innema nahnu fitnetun fe la tekfur* fe yeteallemune minhuma ma yuferrikune bihÄḟ beynel merÂṀi ve zevcih* ve ma hum bi darrÄḟne bihÄḟ min ehadin illa bi iznillah* ve yeteallemune ma yedurruhum ve la yenfeuhum* ve le kad alimu le menisterahu ma lehu fil ahÄḟrati min halakÄḟv ve le biÂṀse ma serav bihÄḟ enfusehum* lev kanu laÂṀlemun"
  2,103,"Ve lev ennehum amenu vettekav le mesubetum min Äḟndillahi hayr* lev kanu yaÂṀlemun"
  2,104,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tekulu raÄḟna ve kulunzurna vesmeu* ve lil kafirÄḟne azabun elÄḟm"
  2,105,"Ma yeveddullezÄḟne keferu min ehlil kitabi ve lel musrikÄḟne ey yunezzele aleykum min hayrim mir rabbikum* vallahu yehtessu bi rahmetihÄḟ mey yesaÂṀ* vallahu zul fadlil azÄḟym"
  2,106,"Ma nensah min ayetin ev nunsiha neÂṀti bi hayrim minha ev misliha* e lem taÂṀlem ennellahe ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  2,107,"E lem taÂṀlem ennellahe lehu mulkus semavati vel ard* ve ma lekum min dunillahi miv veliyyiv ve la nasÄḟyr"
  2,108,"Em turÄḟdune en tesÂṀelu rasulekum kema suile musa min kabl* ve mey yetebeddelil kufra bil Äḟmani fe kad dalle sevaes sbil"
  2,109,"Vedde kesÄḟrum min ehlil kitabi lev yeruddunekum mim baÂṀdi Äḟmanikum kuffara* hasedem min Äḟndi enfusihim mim baÂṀdi ma tebeyyene lehumul hakk* faÂṀfu vasfehu hatta yeÂṀtiyellahu bi emrih* innellahe ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  2,110,"Ve ekÄḟymus salate ve atuz zekah* ve ma tukaddimu li enfusikum min hayrin teciduhu Äḟndellah* innellahe bi ma taÂṀmelune besÄḟyr"
  2,111,"Ve kalu ley yedhulel cennete illa men kane huden ev nesar* tilke emaniyyuhum* kul hatu burhanekum in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  2,112,"Bela men esleme vechehu lillahi ve huve muhsinun fe lehu ecruhu Äḟnde rabbihÄḟ ve la havvfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  2,113,"Ve kaletil yehudu leysetin nesar ala seyÂṀiv ve kaletin nesara leysetil yehudu ala seyÂṀiv ve hum yetlunel kitab* kezalike kalellezÄḟne la yaÂṀlemune misle kavlihim* fallahu yahkumu beynehum yevmel kÄḟyameti fÄḟma kanu fÄḟhi yahtelifun"
  2,114,"Ve men azlemu mimmem menea mesacidellahi ey yuzkera fÄḟhesmuhu ve sea fÄḟ harabiha* ulaike ma kane lehum ey yedhuluha illa haifÄḟn* lehum fid dunya hÄḟzyuv ve lehum fil ahÄḟrati azabun azÄḟym"
  2,115,"Ve lillahil mesriku vel magribu fe eynema tuvellu fe semme vechullah* innallahe vasiun alÄḟm"
  2,116,"Ve kaluttehazellahu veleden subhaneh* bel lehu ma fis semavati vel ard* kullul lehu kanitun"
  2,117,"BedÄḟus semavati vel ard* ve iza kada emran fe innema yekulu lehu kun fe yekun"
  2,118,"Ve kalellezÄḟne la yaÂṀlemune lev la yukellimunellahu ev teÂṀtÄḟna ayeh* kezalike kalellezÄḟne min kablihim misle kavlihim* tesabehet kulubuhum* kad beyyennel ayati li kavmiy yukÄḟnun"
  2,119,"Inna erselnake bil hakkÄḟ besÄḟrav ve nezirav ve la tusÂṀelu an ashabil cehÄḟym"
  2,120,"Ve len terda ankel yehudu ve len nesara hatta tettebia milletehum* kul inne hudellahi huvel huda* ve leinittebaÂṀte ehvaehum baÂṀdellezÄḟ caeke minel Äḟlmi ma leke minallahi miv veliyyiv ve la nasÄḟyr"
  2,121,"EllezÄḟne ateynahumul kitabe yetlunehu hakka tilavetih* ulaike yuÂṀminune bih* ve mey yekfur bihÄḟ fe ulaike humul hasirun"
  2,122,"Ya benÄḟ israÄḟlezkuru nÄḟÂṀmetiyelletÄḟ enÂṀamtu aleykum ve ennÄḟ faddaltukum alel alemÄḟn"
  2,123,"Vetteku yevmel la teczÄḟ nefsun an nefsin seyÂṀev ve la yukbelu minha adluv ve la tenfeuha sefatuv ve la hum yunsarun"
  2,124,"Ve izibtela ibrahÄḟme rabbuhu bi kelimatin fe etemmehunn* kale innÄḟ caÄḟluke lin nasi imama* kale ve min zurriyyetÄḟ* kale la yenalu ahdiz zalimÄḟn"
  2,125,"Ve iz cealnel beyte mesabetel lin nasi ve emna* vettehÄḟzu mim mekami ibrahÄḟme musalla* ve ahidna ila ibrahÄḟme ve ismaÄḟyle en tahhira veytiye lit taifÄḟne vel akifÄḟne ver rukkeÄḟs sucud"
  2,126,"Ve iz kale ibrahÄḟmu rabbicÂṀal haza beleden aminev verzuk ehlehu mines semerati min amene minhum billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟr* kale ve men kefera fe umettiuhu kalÄḟlen summe adtarruhu ila azabin nar* ve biÂṀsel mesÄḟyr"
  2,127,"Ve iz yerfeu ibrahÄḟmul kavaÄḟde minel beyti ve ismaÄḟyl* rabbena tekabbel minna* inneke entes semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  2,128,"Rabbena vecÂṀalna muslimeyni leke ve min zurriyyetina ummetem muslimetel leke ve erina menasikena ve tub aleyna* inneke entet tevvabur rahÄḟym"
  2,129,"Rabbena vebÂṀas fÄḟhim rasulem minhum yetlu aleyhim ayatike ve yuallimuhumul kitabe vel hÄḟkmete ve yuzekkÄḟhim* inneke entel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  2,130,"Ve mey yergabu ammileti ibrahÄḟme illa men sefihe nefseh* ve le kadÄḟstafeynahu fid dunya* ve innehu fil ahÄḟrati le minas salihÄḟyn"
  2,131,"Iz kale lehu rabbuhu eslim kale eslemtu li rabbil alemÄḟn"
  2,132,"Ve vassa biha ibrahÄḟmu benÄḟhi ve yaÂṀkub* ya beniyye innellahestafa lekumud dÄḟne fe la temutunne illa ve entum muslimun"
  2,133,"Em kuntum suhedae iz hadara yaÂṀkubel mevtu iz kale li benÄḟhi ma taÂṀbudune mim baÂṀdÄḟ * kalu naÂṀbudu ilaheke ve ilahe abaike ibrahÄḟme ve ismaÄḟyle ve ishaka ilahev vahÄḟda* ve nahnu lehu muslimun"
  2,134,"Tilke ummetun kad halet* leha ma kesebet ve lekum ma kesebtum* ve la tusÂṀelune amma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  2,135,"Ve kalu kunu huden ev nesara tehtedu* kul bel millete ibrahÄḟme hanÄḟfa* ve ma kane minel musrikÄḟn"
  2,136,"Kulu amenna billahi ve ma unzile ileyna ve ma unzile ila ibrahÄḟme ve ismaÄḟyle ve ishaka ve yaÂṀkube vel esbatÄḟ ve ma utiye musa ve Äḟysa ve ma utiyen nebiyyune mir rabbihim* la nuferriku beyne ehadim minhum ve nahnu lehu muslimun"
  2,137,"Fe in amenu bi misli ma amentum bihÄḟ fe kadihtedev* ve in tevellev fe innema hum fÄḟ sikak* fe seyekfÄḟkehumullah* ve huves semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  2,138,"SÄḟbgatellah* ve men ahsenu minellahi sÄḟbgatev ve nahnu lehu abidun"
  2,139,"Kul etuhaccunena fillahi ve huve rabbuna ve rabbukum* ve lena amaluna ve lekum aÂṀmalukum* ve nahnu lehu muhlisun"
  2,140,"Em tekulune inne ibrahÄḟme ve ismaÄḟyle ve Äḟshaka ve yaÂṀkube vel esbata kanu huden ev nesara* kul e entum aÂṀlemu emillah* ve men azlemu mimmen keteme sehadeten Äḟndehu minellah* ve mallahu bi gafilin amma taÂṀmelun"
  2,141,"Tilke ummetun kad halet* leha ma kesebet ve lekum ma kesebtum* ve la tusÂṀelune amma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  2,142,"Se yekulus sufehau minen nasi ma vellahum an kÄḟbletihimulletÄḟ kanu aleyha* kul lillahil mesriku vel magrib* yehdÄḟ mey yesau ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  2,143,"Ve kezalike cealnakmum ummetev vesetal li tekunu suhedae alen nasi ve yekuner rasulu aleykum sehÄḟda* ve ma cealnel kÄḟbletelletÄḟ kunte aleyha illa li naÂṀleme mey yettebiur rasule mimmey yenkalibu ala akÄḟbeyh* ve in kanet le kebÄḟraten illa alellezÄḟne hedellah* ve ma kanellahu li yudÄḟyÂṀa Äḟmanekum* innellahe bin nasi le raufur rahÄḟym"
  2,144,"Kad nera tekallube vechike fis semai fe lenuvelliyenneke kÄḟbleten terdaha* fevelli vcheke satnal mescidil haram* ve haysu ma kuntum fevellu vucuhekum satrah* ve innellezÄḟne utul kitabe le yaÂṀlemune ennehul hakku mir rabbihim* vemallahu bi gafilin amma yaÂṀmelun"
  2,145,"Ve le in eteytellezÄḟne utul kitabe bi kulli ayetim ma tebiu kÄḟbletek* ve ma baÂṀduhum bi tabiÄḟn kÄḟblete baÂṀd* ve leinittebaÂṀte ehvaehum mim baÂṀdi ma caeke minel Äḟlmi inneke izel le minez zalimÄḟn"
  2,146,"EllezÄḟne ateynahumul kitabe yaÂṀrifunehu kema yaÂṀrifune ebnaehum* ve inne ferÄḟkam minhum le yektumunel hakka ve hum yaÂṀlemun"
  2,147,"Elhakku mir rabbike fe la tekunenne minel mumterÄḟn"
  2,148,"Ve li kulliv vichetun huve muvellÄḟha festebikul hayrat* eyne ma tekunu yeÂṀti bikumullahu cemÄḟa* innellahe ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  2,149,"Ve min haysu haracte fevelli vecheke satral mescidil haram* ve innehu lel hakku mir rabbik* ve mallahu bi gafilin amma taÂṀmelun"
  2,150,"Ve min haysu haracte fevelli vecheke satral mescidil haram* ve haysu ma kuntum fe vellu vucuhekum satrahu li ella yekune linnasi aleykum hucceh* ilellezÄḟne zalemu minhum fe la tahsevhum vahsevnÄḟ ve li utimme nÄḟÂṀmetÄḟ aleykum ve leallekum tehtedun"
  2,151,"Kema erselna fÄḟkum rasulem minkum yetlu aleykum ayatina ve yuzekkÄḟkum ve yuallimukumul kitabv vel hÄḟkmete ve yuallimukum ma lem tekunu taÂṀlemun"
  2,152,"FezkurunÄḟ ezkurkum veskuru lÄḟ ve la tekfurun"
  2,153,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenusteÄḟynu bis sabri ves salah* innellahe meas sabirÄḟn"
  2,154,"Ve la tekulu li mey yuktelu fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi emvat* bel ahyauv ve lakil la tesÂṀurun"
  2,155,"Ve le nebluvennekum bi seyÂṀim minel havfi vel cuÄḟ ve naksÄḟm minel emvali vel enfusi ves semerat* ve bessiris sabirÄḟn"
  2,156,"EllezÄḟne iza esabethum musÄḟybetun kalu inna lillahi ve inna ileyhi raciun"
  2,157,"Ulaike alayhim salevatum mir rabbihim ve rahmetuv ve ulaike humul muhtedun"
  2,158,"Innes safa vel mervete min seairillah* fe min haccel beyte evÄḟÂṀtemera fe la cunaha aleyhi ey yettavvefe bihima* ve men tetavvea hayran fe innellahe sakirun alÄḟym"
  2,159,"InnellezÄḟne yektumune ma enzelna minel beyyinati vel huda mim baÂṀdi ma beyyennahu lin nasi fil kitabi ulaike yelÂṀanuhumullahu ve yelÂṀanuhumul laÄḟnun"
  2,160,"IllellezÄḟne tabu ve aslehu ve beyyenu fe ulaike etubu aleyhim* ve enet tevvabur rahÄḟym"
  2,161,"InnellezÄḟne keferu ve matu ve hum kuffarun ulaike aleyhim laÂṀnetullahi vel melaiketi ven nasi ecmeÄḟyn"
  2,162,"HalidÄḟne fÄḟha* la yuhaffefu anhumul azabu ve la hum yunzarun"
  2,163,"Ve ilahukum ilahuv vahÄḟd* la ilahe illa huver rahmanur rahÄḟym"
  2,164,"Inne fÄḟ halkÄḟs semavati vel erdÄḟ vahtilafil leyli ven nehari vel fulkilletÄḟ tecrÄḟ fil bahri bima yenfeun nase ve ma enzelellahu mines semai mim main fe ahya bihil erda baÂṀde mevtiha ve besse fÄḟha min kulli dabbetiv ve tasrÄḟfir riyahÄḟ ves sehabil musahhari beynes semai vel erdÄḟ le ayatil li kavmiy yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  2,165,"Ve minen nasi mey yettehÄḟzu min dunillahi endadey yuhÄḟbbunehum ke hubbillah* vellezÄḟne amenu eseddu hubbel lillah* velev yerallezÄḟne zalemu iz yeravnel azabe ennel kuvvete lillahi cemÄḟav ve ennellahe sedÄḟdul azab"
  2,166,"Iz teberraellezÄḟnet tubiu minellezÄḟnettebeu ve raevul azabe ve tekattaat bihimul esbab"
  2,167,"Ve kalellezÄḟnet tebeu lev enne lena kerraten fe neteberrae minhum kema teberrau minna* kezalike yurÄḟhimullahu aÂṀmalehum haseratin aleyhim* ve ma hum bi haricÄḟne minen nar"
  2,168,"Ya eyyuhen nasu kulu mimma fil erdÄḟ halalen tayyibev ve la tettebiu hutuvatis seytan* innehu lekum aduvvum mubÄḟn"
  2,169,"Innema yeÂṀmurukum bis sui vel fahsai ve en tekulu alellahi ma la taÂṀlemun"
  2,170,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehumut tebiu ma enzellellahu kalu bel nettebiu ma elfeyna aleyhi abaena* e ve lev kane abauhum la yaÂṀkÄḟlune seyÂṀev ve la yehtedun"
  2,171,"Ve meselullezÄḟne keferu ke meselillezÄḟ yenÂṀÄḟku bi ma la yesmeu illa duaev ve nidaa* summum bukmun umyun fe hum la yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  2,172,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu kulu min tayyibati ma razaknakum veskuru lillahi in kuntum iyyahu taÂṀbudun"
  2,173,"Innema harrame aleykumul meytete ved deme ve lahmel hÄḟnzÄḟri ve ma uhille bihÄḟ li gayrillah* fe menidturra gayra bagÄḟv ve la adin fe la isme aleyh* innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  2,174,"InnellezÄḟne yektumune ma enzelellahu minel kitabi ve yesterune bihÄḟ semenen kalÄḟlen ulaike ma yeÂṀkulune fÄḟ butunihim illen nara ve la yukellimuhumullahu yevmel kÄḟyameti ve la yuzekkÄḟhim* ve lehum azabun eliym"
  2,175,"UlaikellezÄḟnesteravud dalalete bil huda vel azabe bil magfirah* fe ma asberahum alen nar"
  2,176,"Zalike bi ennellahe nezzelel kitabe bil hakk* ve innellezÄḟnahtelefu fil kitabi le fÄḟ sikakÄḟm beÄḟyd"
  2,177,"Leysel birra en tuvellu vucuhekum kÄḟbelel mesrikÄḟ vel magribi ve lakinnel birra men amene billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟri vel melaiketi vel kitabi ven nebiyyÄḟn* ve atel male ala hubbihÄḟ zevil kurba vel yetama vel mesakÄḟne vebnes sebÄḟli ves sailÄḟne ve fir rikab* ve ekames salate ve atez zekah* vel mufune bi ahdihim iza ahedu* ves sabirÄḟne fil beÂṀsai ved darrai ve hÄḟynel beÂṀs* ulaikellezÄḟne sadeku* ve ulaike humul muttekun"
  2,178,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu kutibe aleykumul kÄḟsasu fil katla* el hurru bil hurri vel abdu bil abdi vel unsa bil unsa* fe men ufiye lehu min ehÄḟyhi seyÂṀun fettibaum bil maÂṀrufi ve edaun ileyhi bi Äḟhsan* zalike tahfÄḟfum mir rabbikum ve rahmeh* fe menÄḟÂṀteda baÂṀde zalike fe lehu azabun eliym"
  2,179,"Ve lekum fil kÄḟsasÄḟ hayatuy ya ulil elbabi leallekum tettekun"
  2,180,"Kutibe aleykum iza hadara ehadekumul mevtu in terake hayra* elvasÄḟyyetu lil valideyni vel akrabÄḟne bil maÂṀruf* hakkan alel muttekÄḟyn"
  2,181,"Fe mem beddelehu baÂṀde ma semiahu fe innema ismuhu alellezÄḟne yubeddiluneh* innellahe semÄḟun aliym"
  2,182,"Fe men hafe mim musÄḟn cenefen ev ismen fe asleha beynehum fe la isme aleyh* innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  2,183,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu kutibe aleykumus sÄḟyamu kema kutibe alellezÄḟne min kablikum leallekum tettekun"
  2,184,"Eyyamem maÂṀdudat* fe men kane minkum merÄḟdan ev ala seferin fe Äḟddetum min eyyamin uhar* ve alellezÄḟne yutÄḟykunehu fidyetun taamu miskÄḟn* fe men tetavvea hayran fe huve hayrul leh* ve en tesumu hayrul lekum in kuntum taÂṀlemun"
  2,185,"Sehru ramedanellezÄḟ unzile fÄḟhil kurÂṀanu hudel lin nasi ve beyyinatim minel huda vel furkan* fe men sehide minkumus sehra felyesumh* ve em kane merÄḟdan ev ala seferin fe Äḟddetum min eyyamin uhar* yurÄḟdullahu bikuml yusra ve la yurÄḟdu bi kulum usr* ve li tukmilul Äḟddete ve li tukebbirullahe ala ma hedakum ve leallekum eskurun"
  2,186,"Ve iza seeleke ÄḟbadÄḟ annÄḟ fe innÄḟ karÄḟb* ucÄḟbu daÂṀveted daÄḟ iza deani felyestecÄḟbu lÄḟ vel yuÂṀminu bÄḟ leallehum yarsudun"
  2,187,"UhÄḟlle lekum leyletes sÄḟyamir rafesu ila nisaikum* hunne libasul lekum ve entum libasul lehunn* alimellahu ennekum kuntum tahtaune enfusekum fe tabe aleykum ve afa ankum* fel anebasiruhunne vevtegu ma ketebellahu lekum* ve kulu vesrabu hatta yetebeyyene lekumul huytul ebyadu minel haytÄḟl esvedi minel fecri summe etimmus sÄḟyame ilel leyl* ve la tubasiruhunne ve entum akifune fil mesacid* tilke hududullahi fe la takrabuha* kezalike yubeyyinullahu ayatihÄḟ lin nasi leallehum yettekun"
  2,188,"Ve la teÂṀkulu emvalekum beynekum bil batÄḟli ve tudlu biha ilel hukkami li teÂṀkulu ferÄḟkam min emvalin nasi bil ismi ve entum taÂṀlemun"
  2,189,"YesÂṀeluneke anil ehilleh* kul hiye mevakÄḟytu lin nasi velhacc* ve leysel birru bi en teÂṀtul buyute min zuhuriha ve lakinnel birra menitteka* veÂṀtul buyute min ebvabiha vettekullahe leallekum tuflihun"
  2,190,"Ve katilu fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahillizÄḟne yukatilunekum ve la taÂṀtedu* innellahe la yuhÄḟbbul mu7tedÄḟn"
  2,191,"Vaktuluhum haysu sekÄḟftumuhum ve ahricuhum min haysu ahracukum vel fitnetu eseddu minel katl* ve la tukatiluhum Äḟndel mescidil harami hatta yukatilukum fÄḟh* fe in katelukum faktuluhum* kezalike ceazul kafirÄḟn"
  2,192,"Fe inintehev fe innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  2,193,"Ve katiluhum hatta la tekune fitnetuv ve yekuned dÄḟnu lillah* fe inintehev fe la udvane illa alez zalimÄḟn"
  2,194,"Essehrul haramu bis sehril harami vel hurumatu kÄḟsas* fe menÄḟÂṀteda aleykum faÂṀtedu aleyhi bi misli maÂṀteda aleykum vettekullahe vaÂṀlemu ennellahe mealmuttekÄḟyn"
  2,195,"Ve enfiku fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi ve la tulku bi eydÄḟkum ilet tehluketi ve ahsinu* innellahe yuhÄḟbbul muhsinÄḟn"
  2,196,"Ve etimmul hacce vel umrate lillah* fe in uhsÄḟrtum femesteysera minel hedy* ve la tahliku ruusekum hatta yeblugal hedyu mehÄḟlleh* fe men kane minkum merÄḟdan ev bihÄḟ ezem mir raÂṀsihÄḟ fe fidyetum min sÄḟyamin ev sadekatin ev nusuk* fe iza emintum* fe men temettea bil umrati ilel hacci fe mesteysera minel hedy* fe mel lem yecid fe sÄḟyamu selaseti eyyamin fil hacci ve sebÂṀatin iza racaÂṀtum* tilke aseratun kamileh* zalike li mel lem yekun ehluhu hadÄḟril mescidil haram* vettekullahe vaÂṀlemu ennellahe sedÄḟdul Äḟkab"
  2,197,"Elhaccu eshurum maÂṀlumat* fe men ferada fÄḟhinnel hacce fe la rafese ve la fusuka ve la cidale fil hacc* ve ma tefÂṀalu min hayriy yaÂṀlemhullah* ve tezevvedu fe inne hayraz zadit takva vettekuni ya ulil elbab"
  2,198,"Leyse aleykum cunahun en tebtegu fadlem mir rabbikum* fe iza efadtum min arafatin fezkurullahe Äḟndel mesÂṀaril haram* vezkuruhu kema hedakum* ve in kuntum min kablihÄḟ le mined dallÄḟn"
  2,199,"Summe efÄḟdu min haysu efadan nasu vestagfirullah* innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  2,200,"Fe iza kadaytum menasikekum fezkurullahe ke zikrikum abekum ev esedde zikra* fe minen nasi mey yekulu rabbena atina fid dunya ve malehu fil ahÄḟrati min halak"
  2,201,"Ve minhum mey yekulu rabbena atine fid dunya hasenetev ve fil ahÄḟrati hasenetev ve kÄḟna azaben nar"
  2,202,"Ulaike lehum nasÄḟybum mimma kesebu* vallahu serÄḟul hÄḟsab"
  2,203,"Vezkurullahe fÄḟ eyyamim maÂṀdudat* fe men teaccele fÄḟ yevmeyni fe la isme aleyh* ve men teahhara fe la isme aleyh* limenitteka* vettekullahe vaÂṀlemu ennekum ileyhi tuhserun"
  2,204,"Ve minen nasi me yuÂṀcibuke kavluhu fil hayatid dunya ve yushidullahe ala ma fÄḟ kalbih* ve huve eleddul hÄḟsam"
  2,205,"Ve iza tevella sea fil erdÄḟ li yufside fÄḟha ve yuhlikel harse ven nesl* vallahu la yuhÄḟbbul fesad"
  2,206,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehuttekÄḟllahe ehazethul Äḟzzetu bil ismi fe hasbuhu cehennem* ve le biÂṀsel mihad"
  2,207,"Ve minen nasi mey yesrÄḟ nefsehubtigae merdatillah* vallahu raufum bil Äḟbad"
  2,208,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenudhulu fis silmi kaffeh* ve la tettebiu hutuvatus seytan* innehu lekum aduvvum mubiyn"
  2,209,"Fe in zeleltum mim baÂṀdi ma caetkumul beyyinatu faÂṀlemu ennellahe azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  2,210,"Hel yenzurune illa ey yeÂṀtiyehumullahu fÄḟ zulelim minel gamami vel melaiketu ve kudÄḟyel emr* ve ilellahi turceul umur"
  2,211,"Sel benÄḟ israÄḟle kem ateynahum min ayetim beyyineh* ve mey yubeddil nÄḟÂṀmetellahi mim baÂṀdi ma caethu fe innellahe sedÄḟdul Äḟkab"
  2,212,"Zuyyine lillezÄḟne keferul hayatud dunya ve yesharune minellezÄḟne amenu* vellezÄḟnettekav fevkahum yevmel kÄḟyameh* vallahu yerzuku mey yesau bi gayri hÄḟsab"
  2,213,"Kanen nasu ummetev vahÄḟdeten fe beasellahun nebiyyÄḟne mubessirÄḟne ve munzirÄḟne ve enzele mealhumul kitabe bil hakkÄḟ li yahkume beynen nasi fÄḟmahtelefu fÄḟh* ve mahtelefe fÄḟhi illellezÄḟne utuhu mim baÂṀdi ma caethumul beyyinatu bagyem beynehum* fe hedellahullezÄḟne amenu limahtelefu fÄḟhi minel hakkÄḟ bi iznih* vallahu yehdÄḟ mey yesau ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  2,214,"Em hasibtum en tedhulul cennete ve lemma yeÂṀtikum meselullezÄḟne halev min kablikum* messethumul beÂṀsau ved darrau ve zulzilu hatta yekuler rasulu vellezÄḟne amenu meahu meta nasrullah* ela inne nasrallahi karÄḟb"
  2,215,"YesÂṀeluneke maza yunfikun* kul ma enfaktum min hayrin fe lil valideyni vel akrabÄḟne vel yetama vel mesakÄḟni vebnis sebÄḟl* ve ma tefÂṀalu min hayrin fe innellahe bihÄḟ alÄḟm"
  2,216,"Kutibe aleykumul kÄḟtalu ve huve kurhul lekum* ve asa en tuhÄḟbbu seyÂṀev ve huve serrul lekum* vallahu yaÂṀlemu ve entum la taÂṀlemun"
  2,217,"YesÂṀeluneke anis sehril harami kÄḟtalin fÄḟh* kul kÄḟtalun fÄḟhi kebÄḟr* ve saddun an sebÄḟlillahi ve kufram bihÄḟ vel mescidil harami ve Äḟhracu ehlihÄḟ minhu ekberu Äḟndellah* vel fitnetu ekberu minel katl* ve la yezalune yukatilunekum hatta yeruddukum an dÄḟnikum inisteta* ve mey yertedid minkum an dÄḟnihÄḟ fe yemut ve huve kafirun fe ulaike habitat aÂṀmaluhum fid dunya vel ahÄḟrah* ve ulaike ashabun nar* hum fÄḟha halidun"
  2,218,"InnellezÄḟne amenu vellezÄḟne haceru ve cahedu fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi ulaike yercune rahmetellah* vallahu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  2,219,"YesÂṀeluneke anil hamri vel meysir* kul fÄḟhima imun kebÄḟruv ve menafiu lin nasi ve ismuhuma ekberu min nefÂṀÄḟhima* ve yesÂṀeluneke maza yunfikun* kulil afv kezalike yubeyyinullahu lekumul ayati leallekum tetefekkerun"
  2,220,"Fid dunya vel ahÄḟrah* ve yesÂṀeluneke anil yetama* kul Äḟslahul lehum hayr* ve in tuhalituhum fe Äḟhvanukum* vallahu yaÂṀlemul mufside minel muslÄḟh* ve lev saellahu le aÂṀnetekum* innellahe azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  2,221,"Ve la tenkihul musrikati hatta yuÂṀminn* ve le emetum muÂṀminetum hayrum mim musriketiv ve lev aÂṀcebetkum* ve la tunkihul musrikÄḟne hatta yuÂṀminu* ve le abdum muÂṀminun hayrum mim musrikiv ve lev aÂṀcebekum* ulaike yedÂṀune ilen nar* vallahu yedÂṀu ilel cenneti vel magfirati bi iznih* ve yubeyyinu ayatihÄḟ lin nasi leallehum yetezekkerun"
  2,222,"Ve yesÂṀeluneke anil mehÄḟyd* kul huve ezen faÂṀtezilun nisae fil mehÄḟydÄḟ ve la takrabuhunne hatta yathurn* fe iza tetahherne feÂṀtuhunne min haysu emerakumllah* innellahe yuhÄḟbbut tevvabÄḟne ve yuhÄḟbbul mutetahhirÄḟn"
  2,223,"Nisaukum harsul lemu feÂṀtu harsekum enna siÂṀtum ve kaddimu li enfusikum* vettekullahe vaÂṀlemu ennekum mulakuh* ve bessiril muÂṀminÄḟn"
  2,224,"Ve la tecÂṀalullahe urdatel li eymanikum en teberru ve tetteku ve tuslihu beynen nas* vallahu semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  2,225,"La yuahÄḟzukumullahu bil lagvi fÄḟ eymanikum ve lakiy yuahÄḟzukum bi ma kesebet kulubukum* vallahu gafurun halÄḟm"
  2,226,"LillezÄḟne yuÂṀlune min nisaihim terabbusu erbeati eshur* fe in fau fe innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  2,227,"Ve in azemut talaka fe innellahe semÄḟun aliym"
  2,228,"Vel mutallekatu yeterabbasne bi enfusihinne selasete kuruÂṀ* ve la yehÄḟllu lehunne ey yektmne ma halekallahu fÄḟ erhamihinne in kunne yuÂṀminne billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟr* ve buuletuhunne ehakku bi raddihinne fÄḟ zalike in eradu Äḟslaha* ve lehunne mislullezÄḟ aleyhinne bil ma7rufi ve lir ricali aleyhinne deraceh* vallahu azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  2,229,"Ettalaku merratani fe imsakum bi maÂṀrufin ev tesrÄḟhum bi ÄḟhsarÄḟ* ve la yehÄḟllu lekum en teÂṀhuzu mimma ateytumuhunne seyÂṀen illa ey yehafa ella yukÄḟyma hududellah* fe in hÄḟftum ella yukÄḟyma hududellahi fe la cunaha aleyhime fÄḟmeftedet bih* tilke hududullahi fe la ta7teduha* ve mey yeteadde hududellahi fe ulaike humuz zalimun"
  2,230,"Fe in tallekaha fe la tehÄḟllu lehu mim baÂṀdu hatta tenkÄḟha zevcen gayrah* fe in tallekaha fe la cunaha aleyhima ey yeteracea in zanna ey yukÄḟyma hududellah* ve tilke hududullahi yubeyyinuha li kavmiy yaÂṀlemun"
  2,231,"Ve iza tallaktumun nisae fe belagne ecelehunne fe emsikuhunne bi maÂṀrufin ev serrihuhunne bi maÂṀrufiv ve la tumsikuhunne dÄḟraran li taÂṀtedu* ve mey yefÂṀal zalike fe kad zaleme nefseh* ve la tettehÄḟzu ayatillahi huzuvev vezkuru nÄḟÂṀmetellahi aleykum ve ma enzele aleykum minel kitabi vel hÄḟkmeti yeÄḟzukum bih* vettekullahe vaÂṀlemu ennellahe bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟym"
  2,232,"Ve iza tallaktumun nisae fe belagne ecelehunne fe la taÂṀduluhunne ey yenkÄḟhne ezvacehunne iza teradav beynehum bil maÂṀruf* zalike yuazu bihÄḟ men kane minkum yuÂṀminu billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟr* zalikum ezka lekum ve ather* vallahu yaÂṀlemu ve entum la taÂṀlemun"
  2,233,"Vel validatu yurdÄḟÂṀne evladehunne havleyni kamileyni li men erade ey yutimmer radaah* ve alel mevludi lehu rizkuhunne ve kisvetuhunne bil maÂṀruf* la tukellefu nefsun illa vusÂṀaha* la tudarra validetum bi velediha ve la mevludul lehu bi veledihÄḟ ve alel varisi mislu zalik* fe in erada fisalen an teradÄḟm minhuma ve tesavurin fe la cunaha aleyhima * ve in eradtum en testerdÄḟu evladekum fe la cunaha aleykum iza sellemtum ma ateytum bih maÂṀruf* vettekullahe vaÂṀlemu ennellahe bi ma taÂṀmelune basÄḟyr"
  2,234,"VellezÄḟne yuteveffevne minkum ve yezerune ezvacey yeterabbasne bi enfusihinne erbeate eshuriv ve asra* fe iza belagne ecelehunne fe la cunaha aleykum fÄḟma fealne fÄḟ enfusihÄḟnne bil maÂṀruf* vallahu bi ma taÂṀmelune habÄḟr"
  2,235,"Ve la cunaha aleykum fÄḟma arradtum bihÄḟ min hÄḟtbetin nisai ev eknentum fÄḟ enfusikum* alimellahu ennekum se tezkurunehunne ve lakil la tuvaÄḟdulunne sirran illa en tekulu kavlem maÂṀrufa* ve la taÂṀzimu ukdetem nikahÄḟ hatta yeblugal kitabu eceleh* vaÂṀlemu ennellahe yaÂṀlemu ma fi enfusikum fahzeruh* vaÂṀlemu ennellahe gafurun halÄḟm"
  2,236,"La cunaha aleykum in talaktumun nisae ma lem temessuhunne ev tefridu lehunne ferÄḟdah* ve mettiuhunn* alel musiÄḟ kaderuhu ve alel muktiri kaderuh* metaam bil maÂṀruf* hakkan alel muhsinÄḟn"
  2,237,"Ve in tallaktumuhunne min kabli en temessuhunne ve kad feradtum lehunne ferÄḟdaten fe nÄḟsfu ma feradtum illa ey yaÂṀfune ev ya ÂṀfuvellezÄḟ bi yedihÄḟ ukdetun nikah* ve en taÂṀfu akrabu littakva* ve la tensevul fadle beynekum* innellahe bi ma taÂṀmelune basÄḟyr"
  2,238,"Hafizu ales salevati ves salatil vusta ve kumu lillahi kanitÄḟn"
  2,239,"Fe in hÄḟftum fe ricalen ev rukbana* fe iza emintum fezkurullahe ke ma allemekum ma lem tekunu taÂṀlemun"
  2,240,"VellezÄḟne yuteveffevne minkum ve yezerune ezvaca* vesÄḟyyetel li ezvacihim metaan ilel havli gayra Äḟhrac* fe in haracne fe la cunaha aleykum fÄḟ ma fealne fÄḟ enfusihinne mim maÂṀruf* vallahu aziyzun hakiym"
  2,241,"Ve lil mutallekati metaum bil maÂṀruf* hakkan alel muttekÄḟyn"
  2,242,"Kezalike yubeyyinullahu lekum ayatihÄḟ leallekum taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  2,243,"E lem tera ilellezÄḟne haracu min diyarihim ve hum ulufun hazeral mevti fe kale lehumullahu mutu summe ahyahum* innellahe le uz fadlin alen nasi ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yeskurun"
  2,244,"Ve katilu fÄḟ sebÄḟlillah vaÂṀlemu ennellahe semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  2,245,"MenzellezÄḟ yukridullahe kardan hasenen fe yudaÄḟfehu lehu adÂṀafen kesÄḟrah* vallahu yakbidu ve yebsut* ve ileyhi turceun"
  2,246,"E lem tera ilel melei mim benÄḟ israÄḟle mim baÂṀdi musa* iz kalu li nebiyyil lehumubÂṀas lena meliken nukatil fÄḟ sebÄḟlillah* kale hel aseytum in kutibe aleykumul kÄḟtalu ella tukatilu* kalu ve ma lena ella nukatile fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi ve kad uhricna min diyarina ve ebnaina* fe lemma kutibe aleyhimul kÄḟtalu tevellev illa kalÄḟlem minhum* vallahu alÄḟmum biz zalimÄḟn"
  2,247,"Ve kale lehum nebiyyuhum innellahe kad bease lekum talute melika* kalu enna yekunu lehul mulku aleyna ve nahnu ehakku bil mulki minhu ve lem yuÂṀte seatem minel mal* kale innellahestafahu aleykum ve zadehu betaten fil Äḟlmi vel cism* vallahu yuÂṀtÄḟ mulkehu mey yesaÂṀ* vallahu vasiun aliym"
  2,248,"Ve kale lehum nebiyyuhum inne ayete mulkihÄḟ ey yeÂṀtiyekumut tabutu fÄḟhi sekÄḟnetum mir rabbikum ve bekÄḟyyetum mimma terake alu musa ve alu harune tahmiluhul melaikeh* inne fÄḟ zalike le ayetel lekum in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  2,249,"Fe lemma fesale talutu bil cunudi kale innellahe mubtelÄḟkum bi neher* fe men seribe minhu fe leyse minnÄḟ* vemel lem yaÂṀamhu fe innehu minnÄḟ illa menÄḟgterafe gurfetem bi yedih* fe seribu minhu illa kalÄḟlem minhum* fe lemma cavezehu huve vellezÄḟne amenu meahu kalu la takate lenel yevme bi calute ve cunudih*kalellezÄḟne yezunnune ennehum mulakullahi kem min fietin kalÄḟletin galebet fieten kesÄḟratem bi iznillah* vallahu meas sabirÄḟn"
  2,250,"Ve lemma berazu li calute ve cunudihÄḟ kalu rabbena efrÄḟg aleyna sabrav ve sebbit akdamena vensurna alel kavmil kafirÄḟn"
  2,251,"Fe hezemuhum bi iznillahi ve katele davudu calute ve atahullahul mulke vel hÄḟkmete ve allemehu mimma yesaÂṀ* ve lev la defÂṀullahin nase baÂṀdahum bi baÂṀdÄḟl le fesedetil erdu ve lakinnellahe zu fadlin alel alemÄḟn"
  2,252,"Tilke ayatullahi netluha aleyke bil hakk* ve inneke le minel murselÄḟn"
  2,253,"Tilker rusulu faddalna baÂṀdahum ala baÂṀd* minhum men kellemellahe ve rafea baÂṀdahum deracat* ve ateyna Äḟysebne meryemel beyyinati ve eyyednahu bi ruhÄḟl kudus* ve lev saellahu maktetelellezÄḟne mim baÂṀdihim mim baÂṀdi ma caethumul beyyinatu ve lakinÄḟltelefu fe minhum men amene ve minhum men kefar* ve lev saellahu maktetelu ve lakinnellahe yefÂṀalu ma yurÄḟd"
  2,254,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu enfiku mimma rezaknakum min kabli ey yeÂṀtiye yevmul la beyÂṀun fÄḟhi ve la hulletuv ve la sefaah* vel kafirune humuz zalimun"
  2,255,"Allahu la ilahe illa huvel hayyul kayyum* la teÂṀhuzuhu sinetuv vela nevm* lehu ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard* men zellezÄḟ yesfeu Äḟndehu illa bi iznih* yaÂṀlemu ma beyne eydÄḟhim ve ma halfehum* ve la yuhÄḟytune bi seyÂṀim min ÄḟlmihÄḟ illa bi ma saÂṀ* vesia kursiyyuhus semavati vel ard* ve la yeuduhu hÄḟfzuhuma* ve huvel alÄḟyyul azÄḟym"
  2,256,"La ikrahe fid dÄḟni kad tebeyyener rusdu minel gayy* fe mey yekfur bit taguti ve yuÂṀmim billahi fe kadistemseke bil urvetil vuska lenfisame leha* vallahu semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  2,257,"Allahu veliyyullezÄḟne amenu yuhricuhum minez zulumati ilen nur* vellezÄḟne keferu evliyauhumut tagutu yuhricunehum minen nuri ilez zulumat* ulaike ashabun nar* hum fÄḟha halidun"
  2,258,"E lem tera ilellezÄḟ hacce ibrahÄḟme fÄḟ rabbihÄḟ en atahullahul mulk* iz kale ibrahÄḟmu rabbiyellezÄḟ yuhyÄḟ ve yumÄḟtu kel ene uhyÄḟ ve umÄḟt* kale ibrahÄḟmu fe innellahe yeÂṀtÄḟ bis semsi minel mesrikÄḟ feÂṀti biha minel magribi fe buhitellezÄḟ kefer* vallahu la yehdil kavmez zalimÄḟn"
  2,259,"Ev kellezÄḟ merra ala karyetiv ve hiye haviyetun ala urusiha* kale enna yuhyÄḟ hazihillahu baÂṀde mevtiha* fe ematehullahu miete amin summe beaseh* kale kem lebist* kale lebistu yevmen ev ba7oda yevm* kale bel lebiste miete amin fenzur ila taamike ve serabike lem yetesenneh* venzur ila hÄḟmarike ve li necÂṀaleke ayetel lin nasi venzur ilel Äḟzami keyfe nunsizuha summe neksuha lahma* fe lemma tebeyyene lehu kale aÂṀlemu ennellahe ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  2,260,"Ve iz kale ibrahÄḟmu rabbi erinÄḟ keyfe tuhyil mevta* kale e ve lem tuÂṀmin* kale bela ve lakil li yatmeinne kalbÄḟ* kale fe huz erbeatem minet tayri fe surhunne ileyke summecÂṀal ala kulli cebelim minhunne cuzÂṀen summedÂṀuhunne yeÂṀtÄḟneke saÂṀya* vaÂṀlem ennellahe azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  2,261,"MeselullezÄḟne yunfikune emvalehum fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi ke meseli habbetin embetet sebÂṀa senabihle fÄḟ kulli sumbuletim mietu habbeh* vallahu yudaÄḟfu li mey yesaÂṀ* vallahu vasiun alÄḟm"
  2,262,"EllezÄḟne yunfikune emvalehum fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi summe la yutbiune emvalehum fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi summe la yutbiune ma enfeku mennev ve la ezel lehum ecruhum Äḟnde rabbihim* ve la havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  2,263,"Kavlum maÂṀrufuv ve magfiratun hayrum min sadekatiy yetbeuha eza* vallahu ganiyyun halÄḟm"
  2,264,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tubtÄḟlu sadekatikum bil menni vel eza kellezÄḟ yunfiku malehu riaen nasi ve la yuÂṀminu billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟr* fe meseluhu ke meseli safvanin aleyhi turabun fe esabehu vabilun fe terakehu salda* la yakdirune ala seyÂṀim mimma kesebu* vallahu la yehdil kavmel kafirÄḟn"
  2,265,"Ve meselullezÄḟne yunfikune emvalehumub tigae merdatillahi ve tesbÄḟtem min enfusihim ke meseli cennetim bi rabvetin esabeha vabilun fe atet ukuleha dÄḟÂṀfeyn* fe il lem yusÄḟbha vabilun fe tall* vallahu bima taÂṀmelune basÄḟyr"
  2,266,"E yeveddu ehadukumen tekune lehu cennetum min nehÄḟyliv ve aÂṀnabin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu lehu fÄḟha min kullis semerati ve esabehul kiberu ve lehu zurriyyetun duafau fe esabeha ÄḟÂṀsarun fÄḟhi narin fahterakat* kezalike yubeyyinullahu lekumul ayati leallekum tetefekkerun"
  2,267,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu enfiku min tayyibati ma kesebtum ve mimma ahracna lekum minel ard* ve la teyemmemul habÄḟse minhu tunfikune ve lestum bi ahÄḟzÄḟhi illa en tugmidu fÄḟh* vaÂṀlemu ennellahe ganiyyun hamÄḟd"
  2,268,"Esseytanu yeÄḟdukumul fakra ve yeÂṀmurukum bil fahsaÂṀ* vallahu yeÄḟdukum magfiratem minhu ve fadla* vallahu vasiun alÄḟm"
  2,269,"YuÂṀtil hÄḟkmete mey yesaÂṀ* ve mey yuÂṀtel hÄḟkmete fe kad utiye hayran kesÄḟra* ve ma yezzekkeru illa ulul elbab"
  2,270,"Ve ma enfaktum min nefekatin ev nezertum min nezrin fe innellahe yaÂṀlemuh* ve ma liz zalimÄḟne min ensar"
  2,271,"In tubdus sadekati fe niÄḟmma hÄḟ* ve in tuhfuha ve tuÂṀtuhel fukarae fe huve hayrul lekum* ve yukeffiru ankum min seyyiatikum* vallahu bi ma taÂṀmelune habÄḟr"
  2,272,"Leyse aleyke hudahum ve lakinnellahe yehdÄḟ mey yesaÂṀ* ve ma tunfiku min hayrin fe li enfusikum* ve ma tunfikune illebtigae vechillah* ve ma tunfiku min hayriy yuveffe ilaykum ve entum la tuzlemun"
  2,273,"Lil fukaraillezÄḟne uhsÄḟru fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi la yestetÄḟyÂṀune darben fil erdÄḟ yahsebuhumul cahilu agniyae minet teaffuf* taÂṀrifuhum bi sÄḟmahum* la yesÂṀelunen nase ilhafa* ve ma tunfiku min hayrin fe innellahe bihÄḟ alÄḟm"
  2,274,"EllezÄḟne yunfikune emvalehum bil leyli ven nehari sirrav ve alaniyeten fe lehum ecruhum Äḟnde rabbihim* ve la havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  2,275,"EllezÄḟne yeÂṀkuluner riba la yekumune illa kema yekumullezÄḟ yetehabbetuhus seytanu minel mess* zalike bi ennehum kalu innemel beyÂṀu mislur riba* ve ehalellahul beyÂṀa ve harramer riba* fe min caehu mevÄḟzatum mir rabbihÄḟ fenteha fe lehu ma selef* ve emruhu ilellah* ve men ade fe ulaike ashabun nar* hum fÄḟha halidun"
  2,276,"Yemhakullahur riba ve yurbis sadekat* vallahu la yuhÄḟbbu kulle keffarin esÄḟm"
  2,277,"InnellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati ve ekamus salate ve atevuz zekate lehum ecruhum Äḟnde rabbihim* ve la havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  2,278,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenuttekullahe vezeru ma bekÄḟye miner riba in kunum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  2,279,"Fe il lem tefÂṀalu feÂṀzenu bi harbim minallahi ve rasulih* ve in tubtum fe lekum ruusu emvalikum* la tazlimune ve la tuzlemun"
  2,280,"Ve in kane zu usretin fe nezÄḟratun ila meyserah* ve en tesaddeku hayrul lekum in kuntum taÂṀlemun"
  2,281,"Vetteku yevmen turceune fÄḟhi ilellahi summe tuveffa kullu nefsim ma kesebet vehum la yuzlemun"
  2,282,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu iza tedayentum bi deynin ila ecelim musemmen fektubuh* vel yektub beynekum katibum bil adli ve la yeÂṀbe katibun ey yektube kema allemehullahu fel yektub* velyumlilillezÄḟ aleyhil hakku vel yettekÄḟllahe rabbehu ve la yebhas minhu seyÂṀa* fe in kanellezÄḟ aleyhil hakku sefÄḟhen ev daÄḟyfen ev la yestetÄḟyÂṀu eyyumille huve felyumlil hakku sefÄḟhen ev daÄḟyfen ev la yestetÄḟyÂṀu eyyumille huve felyumlil veliyyuhu bil adl* vesteshidu sehÄḟdeyni mir ricalikum* fe il lem yekuna raculeyni fe raculuv vemraetani mimmen terdavne mines suhedai en tedÄḟlle Äḟhdahuma fe tuzekkira Äḟldahumel uhra* ve la yeÂṀbes suhedau iza ma duu* ve la tesÂṀemu en tektubuhu sagÄḟyran ev kebÄḟran ila ecelih* zalikum aksetu Äḟndellahi ve akvemu lis sehadeti ve edna ella tertabu illa en tekune ticaraten hadÄḟraten tudÄḟruneha beynekum fe leyse aleykum cunahun ella tektubuha* ve sehidu iza tebayaÂṀtum* ve la yudarra katibuv ve la sehid* ve in tefÂṀalu fe innehu fusukum bikum* vettekullah* ve yuallimukumullah* vallahu bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  2,283,"Ve in kuntum ala seferiv ve lem tecidu katiben ferihanum makbudah* fe in emine baÂṀdukum baÂṀdan felyueddilleziÂṀtumine emanetehu velyettekÄḟllahe rabbeh* ve la tektumus sehadeh* ve mey yektumha fe innehu asimun kalbuh* vallahu bi ma taÂṀmelune alÄḟm"
  2,284,"Lillahi ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard* ve in tubdu ma fÄḟ enfusikum ev tuhfuhu yuhasibkum bihillah* fe yagfiru limey yesau ve yuazzibu mey yesaÂṀ* vallahu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  2,285,"Amener rasulu bi ma unzile ileyhi mir rabbihÄḟ vel muÂṀminun* kullun amene billahi ve melaiketihÄḟ ve kutubihÄḟ ve rusulih* la nuferriku beyne ehadim mir rusulih* ve kalu semÄḟÂṀna ve etaÂṀna gufraneke rabbena ve ileykel masÄḟyr"
  2,286,"La yukellifullahu nefsen illa vusÂṀaha* leha ma kesebet ve aleyha mektesebet* rabbena la tuahÄḟzna in nesÄḟna ev ahtaÂṀna* rabbena ve la tahmil aleyna Äḟsran kema hameltehu alellezÄḟne min kablina* rabbena ve la tuhammilna ma la takate lena bih* vaÂṀfu anna* vagfir lena* verhamna ente mevlane fensurna alel kavmil kafirÄḟn"
  3,4,"Min kablu hudel lin nasi ve enzelel furkan* innellezÄḟne keferu bi ayatillahi lehum azabun sedÄḟd* vallahu azÄḟzun zuntikam"
  3,5,"Innellahe la yahfa aleyhi seyÂṀum fil erdÄḟ ve la fis semaÂṀ"
  3,6,"HuvellezÄḟ yusavvirukum fil erhami keyfe yesaÂṀ* la ilahe illa huvel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  3,7,"HuvellezÄḟ enzele aleykel kitabe minhu ayatum muhkematun hunne ummul kitabi ve uharu mutesabihat* fe emmellezÄḟne fi kulubihim zeygun fe yettebiune ma tesabehe minhubtigael fitneti vebtigae teÂṀvÄḟlih* ve ma yaÂṀlemu teÂṀvÄḟlehu illellah* ver rasihune fil Äḟlmi yekulune amenna bihÄḟ kullum min Äḟndi rabbina* ve ma yezzekkeru illa ulul elbab"
  3,8,"Rabbena la tuzÄḟg kulubena baÂṀde iz hedeytena veheb lena mil ledunke rahmeh* inneke entel vehhab"
  3,9,"Rabbena inneke camiun nasi li yevmil la raybe fÄḟh* innellahe la yuhliful mÄḟad"
  3,10,"InnellezÄḟne keferu len tugniye anhum emvaluhum ve la evladuhum minellahi seyÂṀa* ve ulaike hum vekudun nar"
  3,11,"KedeÂṀbi ali firÂṀavne vellezÄḟne min kablihim* kezzebu bi ayatina fe ehazehumullahu bi zunubihim* vallahu sedÄḟdul Äḟkab"
  3,12,"Kul lillezÄḟne keferu setuglebune ve tuhserune ila cehennem* ve biÂṀsel mihad"
  3,13,"Kad kane lekum ayetun fÄḟ fieteynil tekata* fietun tukatilu fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi ve uhra kafiratuy yeravnehum misleyhim raÂṀyel ayn* vallahu yueyyidu bi nasrihÄḟ mey yesaÂṀ* inne fÄḟ zalike le Äḟbratel li ulil ebsar"
  3,14,"Zuyyine lin nasi hubbus sehevati minen nisai vel benÄḟne vel kanatÄḟyril mukantarati minez zehebi vel fiddati vel haylil musevvemeti vel enÂṀami vel hars* zalike metaul hayatid dunya* vallahu Äḟndehu husnul meab"
  3,15,"Kul e unebbiukum bi hayrim min zalikum* lillezÄḟnettekav Äḟnde rabbihim cennatun tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha ve ezvacum mutahheratuv ve rÄḟdvanum minellah* vallahu basÄḟyrum bil Äḟbad"
  3,16,"EllezÄḟne yekulune rabbena innena amenna fagfir lena zunubena vekÄḟna azaben nar"
  3,17,"EssabirÄḟne ves sadikÄḟyne vel kanitÄḟne vel munfikÄḟyne vel mustagfirÄḟne bil eshar"
  3,18,"SehÄḟdellahu ennehu la ilahe illa huve vel melaiketu ve ulul Äḟlmi kaimem bil kÄḟst* la ilahe illa huvel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  3,19,"Inned dÄḟne indellahil islam* ve mahtelefellezÄḟne utul kitabe illa mem baÂṀdi ma caehumul Äḟlmu bagyem beynehum* ve mey yekfur bi ayatillahi fe innellahe serÄḟul hÄḟsab"
  3,20,"Fe in haccuke fe kul eslemtu vechiye lillahi ve menittebean* ve kul lillezÄḟne utul kitabe vel ummiyyÄḟne e eslemtum* fe in eslemu fe kadihtedev* ve in tevellev fe innema aleykel belag* vallahu besÄḟyrum bil Äḟbad"
  3,21,"InnellezÄḟne yekfurune bi ayatillahi ve yaktulunen nebiyyÄḟne bi gayri hakkÄḟv ve yaktulunellezÄḟne yeÂṀmurune bil kÄḟstÄḟ minen nasi fe bessirhum bi azabin elÄḟm"
  3,22,"UlaikellezÄḟne habitat aÂṀmaluhum fid dunya vel ahÄḟrah* e ma lehum min nasÄḟrÄḟn"
  3,23,"E lem tera ilellezÄḟne utu nasÄḟybem minel kitabi yudÂṀavne ila kitabillahi li yahkume beynehum summe yetevella ferÄḟkum minhum ve hum muÂṀridun"
  3,24,"Zalike bi ennehum kalu len temessenen naru illa eyyamem maÂṀdudat* ve garrahum fÄḟ dÄḟnihim ma kanu yefterun"
  3,25,"Fe keyfe iza cemaÂṀnahum li yevmil la raybe fÄḟhi ve vuffiyet kullu nefsim ma kesebet ve hum la yuzlemun"
  3,26,"Kulillahumme malikel mulki tuÂṀtil mulke men tesau ve tenziul mulke mimmen tesaÂṀ* ve tuÄḟzzu men tesau ve tuzillu men tesaÂṀ* bi yedikel hayr* inneke ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  3,27,"Tulicul leyle fin nehari ve tulicun nehara fil leyl* ve tuhricul hayye minel meyyiti ve tuhricul meyyite minel hayy* ve terzuku men tesau bi gayri hÄḟsab"
  3,28,"La yettehÄḟzil muÂṀminunel kafirÄḟne evliyae min dunil muÂṀminÄḟn* ve mey yefÂṀal zalike fe leyse minallahi fÄḟ seyÂṀin illa en tetteku minhum tukah* ve yuhazzirukumullahu nefseh* ve ilellahil masÄḟyr"
  3,29,"Kul in tuhfu ma fÄḟ sudurikum ev tubduhu yaÂṀlemhullah* ve yaÂṀlemu ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard* vallahu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  3,30,"Yevme tecidu kullu nefsim ma amilet min hayrim muhdarav ve ma amilet min suÂṀ* teveddu lev enne beyneha ve beynehu emedem beÄḟyda* ve yuhazzirukumullahu nefseh* vallahu raufum bil Äḟbad"
  3,31,"Kul in kuntum tuhÄḟbbunellahe fettebiunÄḟ yuhbibkumullahu ve yagfir lekum zunubekum* vallahu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  3,32,"Kul etÄḟyÂṀullahe ver rasul* fe in tevellev fe innellahe le yuhÄḟbbul kafirÄḟn"
  3,33,"Innellahestafa ademe ve nuhav ve ale ibrahÄḟme ve ale Äḟmrane alel alemÄḟn"
  3,34,"Zurriyyetem baÂṀduha mim baÂṀd* vallahu semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  3,35,"Iz kaletimraetu Äḟmrane rabbi innÄḟ nezertu leke ma fÄḟ batnÄḟ muharranan fe tekabbel minnÄḟ* inneke entes semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  3,36,"Fe lemma vedaatha kalet rabbi innÄḟ vedaÂṀtuha unsa* vallahu aÂṀlemu bi ma vedaat* ve leysez zekeru kel unsa* ve innÄḟ semmeytuha meryeme ve innÄḟ uÄḟyzuha bike ve zurriyyeteha mines seytanir racÄḟm"
  3,37,"Fe tekabbeleha rabbuha bi kabulin haseniv ve embeteha nebaten hasenev ve keffeleha zekeriyya* kullema dehale aleyha zekeriyyel mÄḟhrabe vecede Äḟndeha rizka* kale ya meryemu enna leki haza* kalet huve min Äḟndillah* innellahe yerzuku mey yesau bi gayri hÄḟsab"
  3,38,"Hunalike dea zekeriyya rabbeh* kale rabbi heb lÄḟ mil ledunke zurriyyeten tayyibeh* inneke semÄḟud duaÂṀ"
  3,39,"Fe nadethul melaiketu ve huve kaimuy yusallÄḟ fil mÄḟhrabi ennellahe yubessiruke bi yahya musaddikam bi kelimetim minellahi ve seyyidev ve hasurav ve nebiyyem mines salihÄḟyn"
  3,40,"Kale rabbi enna yekunu lÄḟ gulamuv ve kad beleganiyel kiberu vemraetÄḟ akÄḟr* kale kezalikellahu yefÂṀalu ma yesaÂṀ"
  3,41,"Kale rabbicÂṀal lÄḟ ayeh* kale ayetuke ella tukellimen nase selasete eyyamin illa ramza* vezkur rabbeke kesÄḟrav ve sebbÄḟh bil asiyyi vel ibkar"
  3,42,"Ve iz kaletil melaiketu ya meryemu innellahestafaki ve tahheraki vastafaki ala nisail alemÄḟn"
  3,43,"Ya meryemuknutÄḟ li rabbiki vescudÄḟ verkeÄḟy mear rakiÄḟyn"
  3,44,"Zalike min embail gaybi nuhÄḟyhi ileyk* ve ma kunte ledeyhim iz yulkune aklamehum eyyuhum yekfulu meryeme ve ma kunte ledeyhim iz yahtesÄḟmun"
  3,45,"Iz kaletil melaiketu ya meryemu innellahe yubessiruki bi kelimetim minhum ismuhul mesÄḟhu Äḟysebnu meryeme vecÄḟhen fid dunya vel ahÄḟrati ve minel mukarrabÄḟn"
  3,46,"Ve yukellimun nase fil mehdi ve kehlev ve mines salihÄḟyn"
  3,47,"Kalet rabbi enna yekunu lÄḟ veleduv ve lem yemsesnÄḟ beser* kale kezalikillahu yahluku ma yesaÂṀ* iza kada emran fe innema yekulu lehu kun fe yekun"
  3,48,"Ve yuallimuhul kitabe vel hÄḟkmete vet tevrate vel incÄḟl"
  3,49,"Ve rasulen illa benÄḟ israÄḟle ennÄḟ kad ciÂṀtukum bi ayetim mir rabbikum ennÄḟ ahluku lekum minet tÄḟyni ke heyÂṀetit tayri fe enfuhu fÄḟhi fe yekunu tayram bi iznillah* ve ubriul ekmehe vel ebrasa ve uhyil mevta bi iznillah* ve unebbiukum bi ma teÂṀkulune ve ma teddehÄḟrune fÄḟ buyutikum* innefÄḟ zalike le ayetel lekum in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  3,50,"Ve musaddikal lima beyne yedeyye minet tevrati ve li uhÄḟlle lekum baÂṀdallezÄḟ hurrime aleykum ve ciÂṀtukum bi ayetim mir rabbikum fettekullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀun"
  3,51,"Innellahe rabbÄḟ ve rabbukum faÂṀbuduh* haza sÄḟratum mustekÄḟym"
  3,52,"Fe lemma ehasse Äḟysa minhumul kufra kale men ensarÄḟ ilellah* kalel havariyyune nahnu ensarullah* amenna billah* veshed bi enna muslimun"
  3,53,"Rabbena amenna bi ma enzelte vettebaÂṀner rasule fektubna meas sahidÄḟn"
  3,54,"Ve mekeru ve mekerallah* vallahu hayrul makirÄḟn"
  3,55,"Iz kalellahu ya Äḟysa innÄḟ muteveffÄḟke ve rafiuke ileyye ve mutahhiruke minellezÄḟne keferu ve caÄḟlullezÄḟnettebeuke fevkallezÄḟne keferu ila yevmil kÄḟyameh* summe ileyye merciukum fe ahkumu beynekum fÄḟma kuntum fÄḟhi tahtelifun"
  3,56,"Fe emmellezÄḟne keferu fe uazzibuhum azaben sedÄḟden fid dunya vel ahÄḟrah* ve ma lehum min nasÄḟriyn"
  3,57,"Ve emmellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati fe yuveffÄḟhim ucurahum* vallahu la yuhÄḟbbuz zalimÄḟn"
  3,58,"Zalike netluhu aleyke minel ayati vez zikril hakÄḟm"
  3,59,"Inne mesele Äḟysa Äḟndellahi ke meseli adem* halekahu min turabin summe kale lehu kun fe yekun"
  3,60,"Elhakku mir rabbike fe la tekum minel mumterÄḟn"
  3,61,"Fe me hacceke fÄḟhi mim baÂṀdi ma caeke minel Äḟlmi fe kul tealev nedÂṀu ebnaena ve ebnaekum ve nisaena ve nisaekum ve enfusena ve enfusekum summe nebtehil fe necÂṀal laÂṀnetellahi alel kazibÄḟn"
  3,62,"Inne haza lehuvel kasasul hakk* ve ma min ilahin illellah* ve innellahe le huvel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  3,63,"Fe in tevellev fe innellahe alÄḟmum bil mufsidÄḟn"
  3,64,"Kul ya ehlel kitabi tealev ila kelimetin sevaim beynena ve beynekum ella naÂṀbude ilellahe ve la nusrike bihÄḟ seyÂṀev ve la yettehÄḟze baÂṀduna baÂṀdan erbabem min dunillah* fe in tevellev fe kulushedu bi enna muslimun"
  3,65,"Ya ehlel kitabi lime tuhaccune fÄḟ ibrahÄḟme ve ma unziletit tevratu vel incÄḟlu illa mim baÂṀdih* e fela taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  3,66,"Ha entum haulai hacectum fima lekum bihÄḟ Äḟlmun fe lime tuhaccune fÄḟma leyse lekum bihÄḟ Äḟlm* vallahu yaÂṀlemu ve entum la taÂṀlemun"
  3,67,"Ma kane ibrahÄḟmu yehuddiyyev ve la nasraniyyev ve lakin kane hanÄḟfem muslima* ve ma kane minel musrikÄḟn"
  3,68,"Inne evlen nasi bi ibrahÄḟme lellezÄḟnettebeuhu ve hazen nebiyyu vellezÄḟne amenu* vallahu veliyyul muÂṀminÄḟn"
  3,69,"Veddet taifetum min ehlil kitabi lev yudÄḟllunekum* ve ma yudÄḟllune illa enfusehum ve ma yesÂṀurun"
  3,70,"Ya ehlel kitabi lime tekfurune bi ayatillahi ve entum teshedun"
  3,71,"Ye ehlel kitabi lime telbisunel hakka bil batÄḟli ve tektumunel hakka ve entum taÂṀlemun"
  3,72,"Ve kalet taifetum min ehlil kitabi aminu billezÄḟ unzile alellezÄḟne amenu vechen nehari vekfuru ahÄḟrahu leallehum yarciun"
  3,73,"Ve la tuÂṀminu illa li men tebia dÄḟnekum* kul innel huda hudellahi ey yuÂṀta ehadum misle ma utÄḟtum ev yuhaccukum Äḟnde rabbikum* kul innel fadle bi yedillah* yuÂṀtÄḟhi mey yesaÂṀ* vallahu vasiun alÄḟm"
  3,74,"Yahtessu bi rahmetihÄḟ mey yesaÂṀ* vallahu zul fadlil azÄḟym"
  3,75,"Ve min ehlil kitabi men inteÂṀmenhu bi kÄḟntariy yueddihÄḟ ileyk* ve minhum men in teÂṀmenhu bi dÄḟnaril la yueddihÄḟ ileyke illa ma dumte aleyhi kaima* zalike bi ennehum kalu leyse aleyna fil ummiyyÄḟne sebÄḟl* ve yekulune alellahil kezibe ve hum yaÂṀlemun"
  3,76,"Bela men evfa bi ahdihÄḟ vetteka fe innellahe yuhÄḟbbul muttekÄḟyn"
  3,77,"InnellezÄḟne yesterune bi ahdillahi ve eymanihim semenen kalÄḟlen ulaike la halak lehum fil ahÄḟrati ve la yukellimuhumullahu ve la yenzuru ileyhim yevmel kÄḟyameti ve la yuzekkÄḟhim* ve lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  3,78,"Ve inne minhum le ferÄḟtkay yelvune elsinetehum bil kitabi li tahsebuhu minel kitabi ve ma huve minel kitab* ve yekulune huve min Äḟndillahi ve ma huve min Äḟndillah* ve yekulune alellahil kezibe ve hum yaÂṀlemun"
  3,79,"Ma kane li beserin ey yuÂṀtiyehullahul kitabe vel hukme ven nubuvvete summe yekule lin nasi kun Äḟbadel lÄḟ min dunillahi ve lakin kunu rabbaniyyÄḟne bi ma kuntum tuallimunel kitabe ve bima kuntum tedrusun"
  3,80,"Ve la yeÂṀmurakum en tettehÄḟzul melaikete ve nebiyyÄḟne erbaba* e yeÂṀmurukum bil kufri baÂṀde iz entum muslimun"
  3,81,"Ve iz ehazellahu mÄḟsakan nebiyyÄḟne lema ateytukum min kitabiv ve hÄḟkmetin summe caekum rasulum musaddikul lima meakum le tuÂṀminunne bihÄḟ ve le tensurunneh* kale e akrartum ve ehaztum ala zalikum ÄḟsrÄḟ* kalu akrarna* kale feshedu ve ene meakum mines sahidÄḟn"
  3,82,"Fe men tevella baÂṀde zalike fe ulaike humul fasikun"
  3,83,"E fe gayra dÄḟnillahi yebgune ve lehu esleme men fis semavati vel erdÄḟ tavÂṀav ve kerhev ve ileyhi yurceun"
  3,84,"Kul amenna bilbillahi ve ma unzile aleyna ve ma unzile ala ibrahÄḟme ve ismaÄḟyle ve ishaka ve yaÂṀkube vel esbatÄḟ ve ma utiy musa ve Äḟysa ven nebiyyune mir rabbihim* la nuferriku beyne ehadim minhum ve nahnu lehu muslimun"
  3,85,"Ve mey yebtegÄḟ gayral islami dÄḟnen fe ley yukbele minh* ve huve fil ahÄḟrati minel hasirÄḟn"
  3,86,"Keyfe yehdillahu kavmen keferu baÂṀde Äḟmanihim ve sehidu enner rasule hakkuv ve caehumul beyyinat* vallahu la yehdil kavmez zalimÄḟn"
  3,87,"Ulaike cezauhum enne aleyhim laÂṀnetellahi vel melaiketi ven nasi ecmeÄḟyn"
  3,88,"HalidÄḟne fÄḟha* la yuhaffefu anhumul azabu ve la hum yunzarun"
  3,89,"IllellezÄḟne tabu mim baÂṀdi zalike ve aslehu fe innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  3,90,"InnellezÄḟne keferu baÂṀde Äḟmanihim summezdadu kufral len tukbele tevbetuhum* ve ulaike humud dallun"
  3,91,"InnellezÄḟne keferu ve matu ve hum kuffarun fe ley yukbele min ehadihim milÂṀul erdÄḟ zehebev ve levfteda bih* ulaike lehum azabun elÄḟmuv ve ma lehum min nasÄḟrÄḟn"
  3,92,"Len tenalul birra hatta tunfiku mimma tuhÄḟbbun* ve ma tunfiku min seyÂṀin fe innellahe bihÄḟ alÄḟm"
  3,93,"Kullut taami kane hÄḟllel li benÄḟ israÄḟle illa ma harrame israÄḟlu ala nefsihÄḟ min kabli en tunezzelet tevrah* kul feÂṀtu bit tevrati fetluha in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  3,94,"Fe meniftera alellahil kezibe mim baÂṀdi zalike fe ulaike humuz zalimun"
  3,95,"Kul sadekallahu fettebiu millete ibrahÄḟme hanÄḟfa* ve ma kane minel musrikÄḟn"
  3,96,"Inne evvele beytiv vudÄḟa linnasi lellezÄḟ bi bekkete mubarakev ve hudel lil alemÄḟn"
  3,97,"FÄḟhi ayatum beyyinatum mekamu ibrahÄḟm* ve men dehalehu kane amina* ve lillahi alen nasi hÄḟccul beyti menistetaa ileyhi sebÄḟla* ve men kefera fe innellahe ganiyyun anil alemÄḟn"
  3,98,"Kul ya ehlel kitabi lime tekfurune bi ayatillahi vallahu sehÄḟdun ala ma taÂṀmelun"
  3,99,"Kul ya ehlel kitabi lime tesuddune an sebÄḟlillahi men amene tebguneha Äḟvecev ve entum suhedaÂṀ* vemallahu bi gafilin amma taÂṀmelun"
  3,100,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu in tutÄḟyÂṀu ferÄḟkam minellezÄḟne utul kitabe yeruddukum baÂṀde Äḟmanikum kafirÄḟn"
  3,101,"Ve keyfe tekfurune ve entum tutla aleykum ayatullahi ve fÄḟkum rasuluh* ve mey yaÂṀtesÄḟm billahi fe kad hudiye ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  3,102,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenuttekullahe hakka tukatihÄḟ ve la temutunne illa ve entum muslimun"
  3,103,"VaÂṀtesumu bi hablillahi cemÄḟav ve la teferraku* vezkuru nÄḟÂṀmetellahi aleykum iz kuntum aÂṀdaen fe ellefe beyne kulubikum fe asbahtum bi nÄḟÂṀmetihÄḟ Äḟhvana* ve kuntum ala sefahufratim minen nari fe enkazekum minha* kezalike yubeyyinullahu le kum ayatihÄḟ leallekum tehtedun"
  3,104,"Veltekum minkum ummetuy yedÂṀune ilel hayri ve yeÂṀmurune bil maÂṀrufi ve yenhevne anil munker* ve ulaike humul muflihun"
  3,105,"Ve la tekunu kellezÄḟne teferraku vahtelefu mim baÂṀdi ma caehumul beyyinat* ve ulaike lehum azabun azÄḟym"
  3,106,"Yevme tebyaddu vucuhuv ve tesveddu vucuh* fe emmellezÄḟnesveddet vucuhuhum e kefartum baÂṀde Äḟmanikum fe zukul azabe bima kuntum tekfurun"
  3,107,"Ve emmellezÄḟnebyaddat vucuhuhum fe fÄḟ rahmetillah* hum fÄḟha halidun"
  3,108,"Tilke ayatullahi netluha aleyke bil hakk* vemallahu yurÄḟdu zulmel lil alemÄḟn"
  3,109,"Ve lillahi ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard* ve ilellahi turceul umur"
  3,110,"Kuntum hayra ummetin uhricet lin nasi teÂṀmurune bil maÂṀrufi ve tenhevne anil munkeri ve tuÂṀminune billah* ve lev amene ehlul kitabi le kane hayral lehum* minhumul muÂṀminune ve ekseruhumul fasikun"
  3,111,"Ley yedurrukum illa eza* ve iy yukatilukum yuvellukumul edbara summe la yunsarun"
  3,112,"Duribet aleyhimuz zilletu eyne ma sukÄḟfu illa bi hablim minellahi ve hablim minen nasi ve bau bi gadabim minellahi ve duribet aleyhimul meskeneh* zalike bi ennehum kanu yekfurune bi ayatillahi ve yaktulunel embiyae bi gayri hakk* zalike bi ma asav ve kanu yaÂṀtedun"
  3,113,"Leysu sevaa* min ehlil kitabi ummetun kaimetuy yetlune ayatillahi anael leyli ve hum yecudun"
  3,114,"YuÂṀminune billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟri ve yeÂṀmurune bil maÂṀrufi ve yenhevne anil munkeri ve yusariune fil hayrat* ve ulaike mines salihÄḟyn"
  3,115,"Ve ma yefÂṀalu min hayrin fe ley yukferuh* vallahu alÄḟmum bil muttekÄḟyn"
  3,116,"InnellezÄḟne keferu len tugniye anhum emvaluhum ve la evladuhum minellahi seyÂṀa* ve ulaike ashabun nar* hum fÄḟha halidun"
  3,117,"Meselu ma yunfikune fÄḟ hazihil hayatid dunya ke meseli rÄḟhÄḟn fÄḟha sÄḟrrun esebet harse kavmin zalemu enfusehum fe ehleketh* ve ma zalemehumullahu ve lakin enfusehum yazlimun"
  3,118,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tettehÄḟzu bitanetem min dunikum la yeÂṀlunekum habala* veddu ma anittum* kad bedetil bagdau min efvahihim ve ma tuhfÄḟ suduruhum ekber* kad beyyenna lekumul ayati in kuntum taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  3,119,"Ha entum ulai tuhÄḟbbunehum ve la yuhÄḟbbunekum ve tuÂṀminune bil kitabi kullih* ve iza lekukum kalu amenna ve iza halev addu aleykumul enamile minel gayz* kul mutu bi gayzÄḟkum* innellahe alÄḟmum bizatis sudur"
  3,120,"In temseskum hasenetun tesuÂṀhum* ve in tusÄḟbkum seyyietuy yefrahu biha* ve in tasbiru ve tetteku la yedurrukum keyduhum seyÂṀa* innellahe bi ma yaÂṀmelune muhÄḟyt"
  3,121,"Ve iz gadevte min ehlike tubevviul muÂṀminÄḟne mekaÄḟde lil kÄḟtal* vallahu semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  3,122,"Iz hemmet taifetani minkum en tefsela vallahu veliyyuhuma* ve alellahi fel yetevekkelil muÂṀminun"
  3,123,"Ve le kad nesarekumullahu bi bedriv ve entum ezilleh* fettekullahe leallekum teskurun"
  3,124,"Iz tekulu lil muÂṀminÄḟne eley yekfiyekum ey yumiddekum rabbukum bi selaseti alafim minel melaiketi munzelÄḟn"
  3,125,"Bela in tasbiru ve tetteku ve yeÂṀtukum min fevrihim haza yumdidkum rabbukum bi hamseti alafim minel melaiketi musevvimÄḟn"
  3,126,"Ve ma cealehullahu illa busra lekum ve li tatmeinne kulubukum bih* ve men nasru illa min Äḟndillahil azÄḟzil hakÄḟm"
  3,127,"Li yaktaa tarafem minellezÄḟne keferu ev yekbitehum fe yenkalibu haibÄḟn"
  3,128,"Leyse leke minel emri seyÂṀun ev yetube aleyhim ev yuazzibehum fe innehum zalimun"
  3,129,"Ve lillahi ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard* yagfiru li mey yesau ve yuazzibu mey yesaÂṀ* vallahu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  3,130,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la teÂṀkulur riba adÂṀafem mudaafetev vettekullahe leallekum tuflihun"
  3,131,"Vettekun naralletÄḟ uÄḟddet lil kafirÄḟn"
  3,132,"Ve etÄḟyÂṀullahe ver rasule leallekum turhamun"
  3,133,"Ve sariu ila magfiratim mir rabbikum ve cennetin arduhes semavatu vel erdu uÄḟddet lil muttekÄḟyn"
  3,134,"EllezÄḟne yunfikune fis serrai ved darrai vel kazÄḟmÄḟnel gayza vel afÄḟne anin nas* vallahu yuhÄḟbbul muhsinÄḟn"
  3,135,"VellezÄḟne iza fealu fahÄḟseten ev zalemu enfusehum zekerullahe festagferu li zunubihim* ve mey yagfiruz zunube illellah* ve lem yusÄḟrru ala ma fealu ve hum yaÂṀlemun"
  3,136,"Ulaike cezauhum magfiratum mir rabbihim ve cennatun tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha* ve nÄḟÂṀme ecrul amilÄḟn"
  3,137,"Kad halet mim kablikum sunenun fe sÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetul mukezzibÄḟn"
  3,138,"Haza beyanul linnasi ve hudev ve mevÂṀÄḟzatul lil muttekÄḟyn"
  3,139,"Ve la tehinu ve la tahzenu ve entumul aÂṀlevne in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  3,140,"Iy yemseskum karhun fe kad messel kavme karhum misluh* ve tilkel eyyamu nudaviluha beynen nas* ve li yaÂṀlemellahullezÄḟne amenu ve yettehÄḟze minkum suhedaÂṀ* vallahu la yuhÄḟbbuz zalimÄḟn"
  3,141,"Ve li yumehhÄḟsallahullezÄḟne amenu ve yemhakal kafirÄḟn"
  3,142,"Em hasibtum en tedhulul cennete ve lemma yaÂṀlemillahullezÄḟne cahedu minkum ve yaÂṀlemes sabirÄḟn"
  3,143,"Ve le kad kuntum temennevnel mevte min kabli en telkavhu fe kad raeytumuhu ve entum tenzurun"
  3,144,"Ve ma muhammedun illa rasul* kad halet min kablihir rusul* e fe im mate ev kutilenkalebtum ala aÂṀkabikum* ve mey yenkalib ala akÄḟbeyhi fe ley yedurrallahe seyÂṀa* ve seyeczillahus sakirÄḟn"
  3,145,"Ve ma kane li nefsin en temute illa bi iznillahi kitabem mueccela* ve mey yurid sevabed dunya nuÂṀtihÄḟ minha* ve mey yurid sevabel ahÄḟrati nuÂṀtihÄḟ minha* ve seneczis sakirÄḟn"
  3,146,"Ve keeyyim min nebiyyin katele meahu ribbiyyune kesÄḟr* fe ma vehenu li ma esabehum fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi ve ma daufu ve mestekanu* vallahu yuhÄḟbbus sabirÄḟn"
  3,147,"Ve ma kane kavlehum illa en kalu rabbenagfir lena zunubena ve israfena fÄḟ emrina ve sevvit akdamena vensurna alel kavmil kafirÄḟn"
  3,148,"Fe atahumullahu sevabed dunya ve husne sevabil ahÄḟrah* vallahu yuhÄḟbbul muhsinÄḟn"
  3,149,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu in tutÄḟyÂṀullezÄḟne keferu yeruddukum ala aÂṀkabikum fe tenkalibu hasirÄḟn"
  3,150,"Belillahu mevlakum* ve huve hayrum nasÄḟrÄḟn"
  3,151,"SenulkÄḟy fÄḟ kulubillezÄḟne keferur ruÂṀbe bi ma esraku billahi ma lem yunezzil bihÄḟ sultana* ve meÂṀvahumun nar* ve biÂṀse mesvez zalimÄḟn"
  3,152,"Ve le kad sadekakumullahu vaÂṀdehu iz tehussunehum bi iznih* hatta iza fesiytum ve tenazaÂṀtum fil emri ve asaytum mim baÂṀdi ma erakum ma tuhÄḟbbun* minkum mey yurÄḟdud dunya ve minkum mey yurÄḟdul ahÄḟrah* summe sarafekum anhum li yebteliyekum* ve le kad afa ankum* vallahu zu fadlin alel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  3,153,"Iz tusÂṀÄḟdune ve la telvune ala ehadiv ver rasulu yedÂṀukum fÄḟ uhrakum fe esabekum gammem bi gammil li keyla tahzenu ala ma fatekum ve la ma esabekum* vallahu habÄḟrum bima taÂṀmelun"
  3,154,"Summe enzele aleykum mim baÂṀdil gammi emeneten nuasey yagsa taifetem minkum ve taifetun kad ehemmethum enfusuhum yezunnune billahi gayral hakkÄḟ zannel cahiliyyeh* yekulune hel lena minel emri min seyÂṀ* kul innel emra kullehu lillah* yuhfune fÄḟ enfusihim ma la yubdune lek* yekulune lev kane lena minel emri seyÂṀum ma kutilna hahuna* kul lev kuntum fÄḟ buyutikum le berazellezÄḟne kutibe aleyhimul katlu ila medaciÄḟhim* ve li yebteliyellahu ma fÄḟ sudurikum ve li yumehhÄḟsa ma fÄḟ kulubikum* vallahu alÄḟmum bi zatis sudur"
  3,155,"InnellezÄḟne tevellev minkum yevmel tekal cemÂṀani innemestezellehumus seytanu bi baÂṀdÄḟ ma kesebu* ve le kad afallahu anhum* innellahe gafurunhalÄḟm"
  3,156,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tekunu kellezÄḟne keferu ve kalu li Äḟhvanihim iza daru fil erdÄḟ ev kanu guzzel lev kanu Äḟndena ma matu ve ma kutilu* li yecÂṀalellahu zalike hasraten fÄḟ kulubihim* vallahu yuhyÄḟ ve yumÄḟt* vallahu bi ma taÂṀmelune basÄḟyr"
  3,157,"Ve lein kutiltum fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi ev muttum le magfiratum minellahi ve rahmetun hayrum mimma yecmeun"
  3,158,"Ve leim muttum ev kutiltum le ilellahi tuhserun"
  3,159,"Fe bi ma rahmetim minellahi linte lehum* ve lev kunte fezzan galÄḟzal kalbi lenfeddu min havlike faÂṀfu anhum vestagfir lehum ve savirhum fil emr* fe iza azemte fe tevekkel alellah* innellahe yuhÄḟbbul mutevekkilÄḟn"
  3,160,"Iy yensurkumullahu fe la galibe lekum* ve iy yahzulkum fe min zellezÄḟ yensurukum mim baÂṀdih* ve alellahi felyetevekkelil muÂṀminun"
  3,161,"Ve ma kane li nebiyyin ey yegull* ve mey yaglul yeÂṀti bi ma galle yevmel kÄḟyameh* summe tuveffa kullu nefsim ma kesebet ve hum la yuzlemun"
  3,162,"E fe menittebea rÄḟdvanellahi ke mem bae bi sehatÄḟm minellahi ve meÂṀvahu cehennem* ve biÂṀsel mesÄḟyr"
  3,163,"Hum deracatun Äḟndellah* vallahu besÄḟyrum bi ma yaÂṀmelun"
  3,164,"Le kad mennellahu alel muÂṀminÄḟne iz bease fÄḟhim rasulem min enfusihim yetlu aleyhim ayatihÄḟ ve yuzekkÄḟhim ve yuallimuhumul kitabe vel hÄḟkmeh* ve in kanu min kablu le fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  3,165,"E ve lemma esabetkum musÄḟybetun kad esabtum misleyha kultum enna haza* kul huve min Äḟndi enfusikum* innellahe ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  3,166,"Ve ma esabekum yevmeltekal cemÂṀani fe bi iznillahi ve li yaÂṀlemel mu7minÄḟn"
  3,167,"Ve li yaÂṀlemellezÄḟne nefeku* ve kÄḟyle lehum tealev katilu fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi evidfeu* kalu lev naÂṀlemu kÄḟtalel lettebaÂṀnakum* hum lil kufri yevmeizin akrabu minhum lil Äḟman* yekulune bi efvahihim ma leyse fÄḟ kulubihim* vallahu aÂṀlemu bima yektumun"
  3,168,"EllezÄḟne kalu li Äḟhvanihim ve kaadu lev etauna ma kutilu* kul fedrau an enfusekumul mevte in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  3,169,"Ve la tahsebennellezÄḟne kutilu fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi emvate bel ahyaun Äḟnde rabbihim yurzekun"
  3,170,"FerihÄḟyne bi ma atahumullahu min fadlihÄḟ ve yestebsirune billezÄḟne lem yelhaku bihim min halfihÄḟm ella havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  3,171,"Yestebsirune bi nÄḟÂṀmetim minellahi ve fadliv ve ennellahe la yudÄḟyÂṀu ecral muÂṀminÄḟn"
  3,172,"EllezÄḟnestecabu lillahi ver rasuli mim baÂṀdi ma esabehumul karhu lillezÄḟne ahsenu minhum vettekav ecrun azÄḟym"
  3,173,"EllezÄḟne kale lehumun nasu innen nase kad cemeu lekum fahsevhum fe zadehum Äḟmana* ve kalu hasbunellahu ve nÄḟÂṀmel vekÄḟl"
  3,174,"Fenkalebu bi nÄḟÂṀmetim minellahi ve fadlil lem yemseshum suuv vettebeu rÄḟdvanellah* vallahu zu fadlin azÄḟym"
  3,175,"Innema zalikumus seytanu yuhavvifu evliyaehu fe la tehafuhum ve hafuni in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  3,176,"Ve la yahzunkellezÄḟne yusariune fil kufr* innehum ley yedurullahe seyÂṀa* yurÄḟdullahu ella yecÂṀale lehum hazzan fil ahÄḟrah* ve le hum azabun azÄḟym"
  3,177,"InnellezÄḟnesteravul kufra bil Äḟmani ley yedururlahe seyÂṀa* ve lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  3,178,"Ve la yahsebennelezÄḟne keferu ennema numlÄḟ lehum hayrul li enfusihimv innema numlÄḟ lehum li yezdadu isma* ve lehum azabum muhÄḟn"
  3,179,"Ma kanellahu li yezeral muÂṀminÄḟne ala ma entum aleyhi hatta yemÄḟzel habÄḟse minet tayyib* ve am kanellahu li yutliakum alel gaybi ve lakinnellahe yectebÄḟ mir rusulihÄḟ mey yesau fe aminu billahi ve rusulih* ve in tuÂṀminu ve tetteku fe le kum ecrun azÄḟym"
  3,180,"Ve la yahsebennellezÄḟne yebhalune bi ma atahumullahu min fadlihÄḟ huve hayral lehum* bel huve serrul lehum* seyutavvekune ma behÄḟlu bihÄḟ yevmel kÄḟyameh* ve lillah mÄḟrasus semavati vel ard* vallahu bi ma taÂṀmelune habÄḟr"
  3,181,"Le kad semiallahu kavlellezÄḟne kalu innellahe fekÄḟyruv ve nahnu agniyaÂṀ* senektubu ma kalu ve katlehumul embiyae bi gayri hakkÄḟv ve nekulu zuku azabel harÄḟyk"
  3,182,"Zalike bi ma kaddemet eydÄḟkum ve ennellahe leyse bi zallamil lil abÄḟd"
  3,183,"EllezÄḟne kalu innellahe ahide ileyna ella nuÂṀmine li rasulin hatta yeÂṀtiyena bi kurbanin teÂṀkuluhun nar* kul kad caekum rusulum min kablÄḟ bil beyyinati ve billezÄḟ kultum fe lime kateltumuhum in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  3,184,"Fe in kezzebuke fe kad kuzzibe rusulum min kablike cau bil beyyinati vez zuburi vel kitabil munÄḟr"
  3,185,"Kullu nefsin zaikatul mevt* ve innema tuveffevne ucurakum yevmel kÄḟyameh* fe men zuhziha anin nari ve udhÄḟlel cennete fe kad faz* ve mel hayatud dunya illa metaul gurur"
  3,186,"Le tublevunne fÄḟ emvalikum ve enfusikum ve le tesmeunne minellezÄḟne utul kitabe min kablikum ve minellezÄḟne esraku ezen kesira* ve in tasbiru ve tetteku fe inne zalike min azmil umur"
  3,187,"Ve iz ehazellahu mÄḟsakallezÄḟne utul kitabe le tubeyyinunnehu lin nasi ve la tektumuneh* fe nebezuhu verae zuhurihim vesterav bihÄḟ semenen kalÄḟla* fe biÂṀse ma yesterun"
  3,188,"La tahsebennellezÄḟne yefrahune bi ma etev ve yuhÄḟbbune ey yuhmedu bi ma lem yefÂṀalu fe la tahsebennehum bi mefazitem minel azab* ve lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  3,189,"Ve lillahi mulkus semavati vel ard* vallahu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  3,190,"Inne fÄḟ halkÄḟs semavati vel erdÄḟ vahtilafil leyli ven nehari le ayatil li ulil elbab"
  3,191,"EllezÄḟne yezkurunellahe kÄḟyamev ve kuudev ve ala cunubihim ve yetefekkerune fÄḟ halkÄḟs semavati vel ard* rabbena ma halakte haza batÄḟla* subhaneke fekÄḟna azaben nar"
  3,192,"Rabbena inneka men tudhÄḟlin nara fe kad ahzeyteh* ve ma liz zalimÄḟne min ensar"
  3,193,"Rabbena innena semÄḟÂṀna munadiyey yunadÄḟ lil Äḟmani en aminu bi rabbikum fe amenna* rabbena fagfir lena zunubena ve keffir anna seyyiatina ve teveffena meal ebrar"
  3,194,"Rabbena ve atina ma veadtena ala rusulike ve la tuhzina yevmel kÄḟyameh* inneke la tuhliful mÄḟad"
  3,195,"Festecabe lehum rabbuhum ennÄḟ la udÄḟyÂṀu amele amilim minkum min zekerin ev unsa* baÂṀdukum min baÂṀd* fellezÄḟne haceru ve uhricu min diyarihim ve uzu fÄḟ sebÄḟlÄḟ ve katelu ve kutilu le ukeffiranne anhum seyyiatihim ve le udhÄḟlennehum cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enhar* sevabem min Äḟndillah* vallahu Äḟndehu husnus sevab"
  3,196,"La yegurranneke tekallubullezÄḟne keferu fil bilad"
  3,197,"Metaun kalÄḟlun summe meÂṀvahum cehennem* ve biÂṀsel mihad"
  3,198,"LakinillezÄḟnettekav rabbehum lehum cennatun tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha nuzulem min Äḟndillah* ve ma Äḟndellahi hayrul lil ebrar"
  3,199,"Ve inne min ehlil kitabi le mey yuÂṀminu billahi ve ma unzile ileykum ve ma unzile ileyhim hasiÄḟyne lillahi la yesterune bi ayatillahi semenen kalÄḟla* ulaike lehum ecruhum Äḟnde rabbihim* innellahe serÄḟul hÄḟsab"
  3,200,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenusbiru ve sabiru ve rabitu vettekullahe leallekum tuflihun"
  4,5,"Ve la tuÂṀtus sufehae emvalekumulletÄḟ cealellahu lekum kÄḟyamev verzukuhum fÄḟha veksuhum ve kulu lehum kavlem maÂṀrufa"
  4,6,"Vebtelul yetama hatta iza belegun nikah fe in anestum minhum rusden fedfeu ileyhim emvalehum ve la teÂṀkuluha israfev ve bidaran ey yekberu ve men kane ganiyyen felyestaÂṀfif ve men kane fekÄḟyran felyeÂṀkul bil maÂṀruf fe iza defaÂṀtum ileyhim emvalehum fe eshidu aleyhim ve kefa billahi hasÄḟba"
  4,7,"Lir ricali nasÄḟybum mimma terakel validani vel akrabune ve lin nisai nasÄḟybum mimma terakel validani vel akrabune mimma kalle minhu evkesur nasÄḟybem mefruda"
  4,8,"Ve iza hadaral kÄḟsmete ulul kurba vel yetama vel mesakÄḟnu ferzukuhum minhu ve kulu lehum kavlem maÂṀrufa"
  4,9,"VelyahsellezÄḟne lev teraku min halfihim zurriyyeten dÄḟafen hafu aleyhim felyettekullahe velyekulu kavlen sedÄḟda"
  4,10,"InnellezÄḟne yeÂṀkulune emvalel yetama zulmen innema yeÂṀkulune fÄḟ butunihim nara ve seyaslevne seÄḟyra"
  4,11,"YusÄḟykumullahu fÄḟ evladikum lizzekeri mislu hazzÄḟl unseyeyn fe in kunne nisaen fevkasneteyni fe lehunne sulusa ma terakv ve in kanet vahÄḟdeten fe lene nÄḟsf ve li ebeveyhi li kulli vahÄḟdum minhumes sudusu mimma terake in kane lehu veled fe il lem yekul lehu veleduv ve verisehu ebevahu fe li ummihis sulus fe in kane lehu Äḟhvetun fe li ummihis sudus mim baÂṀdi vesÄḟyyetiy yusÄḟy biha ev deyn abaukum ve ebnaukum la tedrune eyyuhum akrabu lekum nefÂṀa ferÄḟdatem minellah innellahe kane alÄḟmen hakÄḟma"
  4,12,"Ve lekum nÄḟsfu ma terake ezvacukum il lem yekul lehunne veled fe in kane lehunne veledun fe lekumur rubuu mimma terakne mim baÂṀdi vesÄḟyyetiy yusÄḟyne biha ev deyn ve lehunner rubuu mimma teraktum il lem yekul lekum veled fe in kane lekum veledun fe lehunnes sumunu mimma teraktum mim ba7di vesÄḟyyetin tusune biha ev deyn ve in kane raculuy yurasu kelaleten evimraetuv ve lehu ehun ev uhtun fe li kulli vahÄḟdim minhumes sudus fe in kanu eksera min zalike fe hum surakau fis sulusi mim baÂṀdi vesÄḟyyetiy yusa biha ev deynin gayra mudarr vesÄḟyyetem minellah vellahu alÄḟmun halÄḟm"
  4,13,"Tilke hududullah ve mey yutÄḟÄḟllahe ve rasulehu yudhÄḟlhu cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟhav ve zalikel fevzul azÄḟym"
  4,14,"Ve mey yaÂṀsÄḟllahe ve rasulehu ve yeteadde hududehu yudhÄḟlhu naran haledn fÄḟha ve lehu azabum muhÄḟn"
  4,15,"VellatÄḟ yeÂṀtÄḟnel fahÄḟsete min nisaikum festeshidu aleyhinne erbeatem minkum fe in sehidu fe emsikuhunne fil buyuti hatta yeteveffahunnel mevtu ev yecÂṀalellahu lehunne sebÄḟla"
  4,16,"Vellezani yeÂṀtiyaniha minkum fe azuhuma fe in taba ve asleha fe aÂṀridu anhuma innellahe kane tevvaber rahÄḟyma"
  4,17,"Innemet tevbetu alellahi lillezÄḟne yaÂṀmelunes sue bi cehaletin summe yetubune min karÄḟbin fe ulaike yetubullahu aleyhim ve kanellahu alÄḟmen hakÄḟma"
  4,18,"Ve leysetit tevbetu lillezÄḟne yaÂṀmelunes seyyiat hatta iza hadara ehadehumul mevtu kale innÄḟ tubtul ane ve lellezÄḟne yemutune ve hum kuffar ulaike aÂṀtedna lehum azaben elÄḟma"
  4,19,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la yehÄḟllu lekum en terisun nisae kerha ve la taÂṀduluhunne li tezhebu bi baÂṀdÄḟ ma ateytumuhunne illa ey yeÂṀtÄḟne bi fahÄḟsetim mubeyyineh ve asiruhunne bil maÂṀruf fe in kerihtumuhunne fe asa en tekrahu sey7ev ve yecÂṀalellahu fÄḟhi hayran kesÄḟra"
  4,20,"Ve in eradtumustibdale zevcim mekane zevciv ve ateytum Äḟhdalunne kÄḟntaran fe la teÂṀhuzu minhu seyÂṀa e teÂṀhuzunehu buhtanev ve ismem mubÄḟna"
  4,21,"Ve keyfe teÂṀhuzunehu ve kad efda ba7dukum ila baÂṀdÄḟv ve ehazne minkum mÄḟsakan galÄḟza"
  4,22,"Ve la tenkihu ma nekeha abaukum minen nisai illa ma kad selefv innehu kane fahÄḟsetev ve makta ve sae sebÄḟla"
  4,23,"Hurrimet aleykum ummehatukum ve benatukum ve ehavatukum ve ammatukum ve halatukum ve benatul ehÄḟ ve benatul uhti ve ummehatukumullatÄḟ erdaÂṀnekum ve ehavatukum miner radaati ve ummehatu nisaikum ve rabaibukumullatÄḟ fÄḟ hucurikum min nisaikumullatÄḟ dehatum bihÄḟnne fe il lem tekunu dehaltum bihinne fe la cunaha aleykum ve halailu ebnaikumul lezÄḟne min aslabikum ve ne tecmeu beynel uhteyni illa ma kad selef innellahe kane gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  4,24,"Vel muhsanatu minen nisai illa ma meleket eymanukum kitabellahi aleykum ve uhÄḟlle lekum ma verae zalikum en tebtegu bi emvalikum muhsÄḟniyne gayra musafihÄḟyn femestemtaÂṀtum bihÄḟ minhunne fe atuhunne ucurahunne ferÄḟdah ve la cunaha aleykum fÄḟma teradaytum bihÄḟ mim baÂṀdil ferÄḟdah innellahe kane alÄḟmen hakÄḟma"
  4,25,"Ve mel lem yestetÄḟÂṀ minkum tavlen ey yenkihal muhsanatil muÂṀminati fe mim ma meleket eymaukum min feteyatikumul muÂṀminat vellahu aÂṀlemu bi Äḟmanikum baÂṀdukum mim baÂṀd fenkihuhunne bi izni ehlihinne ve atuhunne ucurahunne bil maÂṀrufi muhsanatin gayra musafihativ ve la muttehÄḟzati ahdan fe iza uhsÄḟnne fe in eteyne bi fahÄḟsetin fe aleyhinne nÄḟsfu ma alel muhsanati minel azab zalike li men hasiyel anete minkum ve en tasbiru harul lekum vellahu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  4,26,"YurÄḟdullahu li yubeyyine lekum ve yehdiyekum sunenellezÄḟne min kablikum ve yetube aleykum vellahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  4,27,"Vallahu yurÄḟdu ey yetube aleykum ve yurÄḟdullezÄḟne yettebiunes sehevati en temÄḟlu meylen azÄḟyma"
  4,28,"YurÄḟdullahu ey yuhaffife ankum ve hulikal insanu daÄḟyfa"
  4,29,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la teÂṀkulu emvalekum beynekum bil batÄḟli illa en tekune ticaraten an teradÄḟm minkum ve la taktulu enfusekum innellahe kane bikum rahÄḟyma"
  4,30,"Ve mey yefÂṀal zalike udvanev ve zulmen fe sevfe nuslÄḟhi nara ve kane zalike alellahi yesÄḟra"
  4,31,"In tectenibu kebaira ma tunhevne anhu nukeffir ankum seyyiatikum ve nudhÄḟlkum mudhalen kerÄḟma"
  4,32,"Ve la tetemennev ma faddalelelahu bihÄḟ baÂṀdakum ala baÂṀd lir ricali nasÄḟybum mimmektesebu ve lin nisai nasÄḟybum mimmektesebn vesÂṀelullahe min fadlih innellahe kane bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟma"
  4,33,"Ve li kullin cealna mevaliye mimma terakel validani vel akrabun vellezÄḟne akadet eymanukum fe atuhum nasÄḟybehum innellahe kane ala kulli seyÂṀin sehÄḟda"
  4,34,"Er ricalu kavvamune alen nisai bi ma faddalellahu baÂṀdahum ala baÂṀdÄḟv ve bi ma enfeku min emvalihim fes salihatu kanitatun hafizatul lil gaybi bi ma hafÄḟzallah vellatÄḟ tehafune nusuzehunne fe Äḟzuhunne vehcuruhunne fil medaciÄḟ vadribuhunn fe in etaÂṀnekum fe la tebgu aleyhinne sebÄḟla innellahe kane aliyyen kebÄḟra"
  4,35,"Ve in hÄḟftum sikaka beynihima febÂṀasu hakemem min ehlihÄḟ ve hakemem min ehliha iy yurÄḟda Äḟslahay yuveffikÄḟllahu beynehuma innellahe kane alÄḟmen habÄḟra"
  4,36,"VaÂṀbudullahe ve la tusriku bihÄḟ seyÂṀev ve bil valideyni Äḟhsanev ve bizil kurba vel yetama vel mesakÄḟni vel cari zil kurba vel caril cunubi ves sahÄḟbi vil cembi vebnis sebÄḟli ve ma meleket eymanukum innellahe la yuhÄḟbbu men kane muhtalen fehura"
  4,37,"EllezÄḟne yebhalune ve yeÂṀmurunen nase bil buhli ve yektumune ma atahumullahu min fadlih ve aÂṀtedna lil kafirÄḟne azabem muhÄḟna"
  4,38,"VellezÄḟne yunfikune emvalehum riaen nasi ve la yuÂṀminune billahi ve la bil yevmil ahÄḟr ve mey yekunis seytanu lehu karÄḟnen fe sae karÄḟna"
  4,39,"Ve maza aleyhim lev amenu billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟri ve enfeku mimma razekahumullah ve kanellahu bihim alÄḟma"
  4,40,"Innellahe la yazlimu miskale zerrah ve in teku hasenetey yudaÄḟfha ve yuÂṀti mil ledunhu ecran azÄḟyma"
  4,41,"Fe keyfe iza ciÂṀna min kulli ummetim bi sehÄḟdiv ve ciÂṀnabike ala haulai sehÄḟda"
  4,42,"Yevmeiziy yeveddullezÄḟne keferu ve asavur rasule lev tusevva bihimul ard ve la yuktumunellahe hadÄḟsa"
  4,43,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la takrabus salate ve entum sukara hatta taÂṀlemu ma tekulune ve la cunuben illa abirÄḟ sebÄḟlin hatta tagtesiluv ve in kuntum merda ev ala seferin ev cae ehadum minkum minel gaitÄḟ ev lamestumun nisae fe lem tecidu maen fe teyemmemu saÄḟyden tayyiben femsehu bi vucuhikum ve eydÄḟkum innellahe kane afuvven gafura"
  4,44,"E lem tera ilellezÄḟne utu nasÄḟybem minel kitabi yesteruned dalalete ve yurÄḟdune en tedÄḟllus sebÄḟl"
  4,45,"Vallahu a7lemu bi aÂṀdaikum ve kefa billahi veliyyev ve kefa billahi nasÄḟyra"
  4,46,"MinellezÄḟne hadu yuharrifunel kelime am mevadÄḟÄḟhÄḟ ve yekulune semÄḟÂṀna ve asayna vesmaÂṀ gayra musmeÄḟv ve raÄḟna leyyem bi elinetihim ve taÂṀnen fid dÄḟn ve lev ennehum kalu semÄḟÂṀna ve etaÂṀna vesmaÂṀ venzurna leane hayral lehum ve akveme ve lakil leanehumullahu bi kufrihim fe la yuÂṀminune illa kalÄḟla"
  4,47,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne utul kitabe aminu bi ma nezzelna musaddikal li ma meakum min kabli en natmise vucuhen fe neruddeha ala edbariha ev nelÂṀanehum ke ma leanna ashabes sebt ve kane emrullahi mefÂṀula"
  4,48,"Innellahe la yagfiru eyyusrake bihÄḟ ve yagfiru ma dune zalike li mey yesaÂṀ ve mey yusrik billahi fe kadiftera ismen azÄḟyma"
  4,49,"E lem tera ilellezÄḟne yuzekkune enfusehum belillahu yuzekkÄḟ mey yesau ve la yuzlemune fetÄḟla"
  4,50,"Unzur keyfe yefterune alellahul kezib ve kefa bihÄḟ ismem mubÄḟna"
  4,51,"E lem tera ilellezÄḟne utu nasÄḟybem minel kitabi yuÂṀminune bil cibti vet taguti ve yekulune lillizÄḟne keferu haulai ehda minellezÄḟne amenu sebÄḟla"
  4,52,"UlaikellezÄḟne leanehumullah ve mey yelÂṀanillahu fe len tecide lehu nesÄḟyra"
  4,53,"Em lehum nesÄḟybum minel mulki fe izel la yuÂṀtunen nase nekÄḟyra"
  4,54,"Em yahsudunen nase ala ma atahumullahu min fadlih fe kad ateyna ale ibrahÄḟmel kitabe vel hÄḟkmete ve ateynahum mulken azÄḟyma"
  4,55,"Fe minhum men amene bihÄḟ ve minhum men saddeanh ve kefa bi cehenneme seÄḟyra"
  4,56,"InnellezÄḟne keferu bi ayatina sevfe nuslÄḟhim nara kullema nedÄḟcet culuduhum beddelnahum culuden gayraha li yezukul azab innellahe kane azÄḟzen hakÄḟma"
  4,57,"Vellezine amenu ve amilus salihati senudhÄḟluhum cennatin tecri min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha ebeda lehum fÄḟha ezvacum mutuhheratuv ve nudhÄḟluhum zÄḟllen zalÄḟla"
  4,58,"Innellahe yeÂṀmurukum en tueddul emanati ila ehliha ve iza hakemtum beynen nasi en tahkumu bil adlv innellahe niÄḟmma yeÄḟzukum bih innellahe kane semÄḟam basÄḟyra"
  4,59,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu etÄḟyÂṀullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀur rasule ve ulil emri minkum fe in tenazeÂṀtum fÄḟ seyÂṀin fe rudduhu ilellahi ves rasuli in kuntum tuÂṀminune billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟrv zalike hayruv ve ahsenu teÂṀvÄḟla"
  4,60,"Elem tera ilellezÄḟne yezÂṀumune ennehum amenu bi ma unzile ileyke ve ma unzile min kablike yurÄḟdune ey yetehakemu ilet taguti ve kad umiru ey yekfuru bih ve yurÄḟdus seytanu ey yudÄḟllehum dalalem beÄḟyda"
  4,61,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehum tealev ila ma enzelellahu ve iler rasuli raeytel munafikÄḟyne yesuddune anke sududa"
  4,62,"Fe keyfe iza esabethum musÄḟybetum bi ma kaddemet eydÄḟhim summe cauke yahlifune billahi in eradna illa Äḟhsanev ve etvfÄḟka"
  4,63,"UlaikellezÄḟne yaÂṀlemullahu ma fÄḟ kulubihim fe aÂṀrÄḟd anhum veÄḟzhum ve kul lehum fÄḟ enfusihim kavlem belÄḟga"
  4,64,"Ve ma erselna mir rasulin illa li yutaa bi iznillah ve lev ennehum iz zalemu enfusehum cauke festagferullahe vestagfera lehumur rasulu le vecedullahe tevvaber rahÄḟyma"
  4,65,"Fe la ve rabbike la yuÂṀminune hatta yuhakkimuke fÄḟma secera beynehum summe la yecidu fÄḟ enfusihim haracem mimma kadayte ve yusellimu teslÄḟma"
  4,66,"Ve lev enna ketebna aleyhim enÄḟktulu enfusekum evÄḟhrucu min diyarikum ma fealuhu illa kalÄḟlum minhumv ve lev ennehum fealu ma yuazune bihÄḟ lekane hayran lehum ve esedde tesbita"
  4,67,"Ve izel le ateynahum mil ledunna ecran azÄḟyma"
  4,68,"Ve le hedeynahum sÄḟratam mustekÄḟyma"
  4,69,"Ve mey yutÄḟÄḟlahe ver rasule fe ulaike meallezÄḟne enÂṀamellahu alehim minen nebiyyÄḟne ves sÄḟddÄḟkÄḟyne ves suhedai ves salihÄḟyn ve hasune ulaike rafÄḟka"
  4,70,"Zalikel fadlu minellah ve kefa billahi alÄḟma"
  4,71,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu huzu hÄḟzrakum fenfiru subatin evinfiru cemÄḟa"
  4,72,"Ve inne minkum le mel leyubettÄḟenn fe in esabetkum musÄḟybetun kale kad enÂṀamellahu aleyye iz lem ekum meahum sehÄḟda"
  4,73,"Ve lein esabekum fadlum minellahi le yekulenne ke el lem tekum beynekum ve beynehu meveddetuy ya leytenÄḟ kuntu meahum fe efuze fevzen azÄḟyma"
  4,74,"Fel yukatil fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahillezÄḟne yesrunel hayated dunya bil ahÄḟrah ve mey yukatil fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi fe yuktel ev yaglib fe sevfe nuÂṀtÄḟhi ecran azÄḟyma"
  4,75,"Ve ma lekum la tukatilune fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi vel mustadÂṀafÄḟne miner ricali ven nisai vel vildanillezÄḟne yekulune rabbena ahricna min hazihil rayetiz zalimi ehluha vecÂṀal lena mil ledunke veliyya vecÂṀal lena mil ledunke nesÄḟyra"
  4,76,"EllezÄḟne amenu yukatilune fÄḟ sebÄḟlillah vellezÄḟne keferu yukatilune fÄḟ sebÄḟlit taguti fe katilu evliyaes seytan inne keydes seytani kane daÄḟyfa"
  4,77,"E lem tera ilellezÄḟne kÄḟyle lehum kuffu eydiyekum ve ekÄḟymus salet ve atuz zekah fe lemma kutibe aleyhimul kÄḟtalu iza ferÄḟkum minhum yahsevnen nase ke hasyetillahi ev esedde hasyeh ve kalu rabbena lime ketebte aleynel kÄḟtal lev la ehhartena ila ecelin karÄḟb kul metaud dunya kalÄḟl vel ahÄḟratu hayrul li menitteka ve la tuzlemune fetÄḟla"
  4,78,"Eyne ma tekunu yudrikumul mevtu ve lev kuntum fÄḟ burucim museyyedeh ve in tusÄḟbhum hasenetuy yekulu hazihÄḟ min Äḟndillah ve in tusÄḟbhum seyyetuy yekulu hazihÄḟ min Äḟndik kul kullum min Äḟndillah fe mali haulail kavmi la yekadune yefkahune hadÄḟsa"
  4,79,"Ma esabeke min hasenetin fe minellah ve ma esabeke min seyyietin fe min nefsik ve erselnake lin nasi rasula ve kefa billahi sehÄḟda"
  4,80,"Mey yutÄḟÄḟr rasule fe kad etaallah ve men tevella fe ma erselnake aleyhim hafÄḟyza"
  4,81,"Ve yekulune taatun fe iza berazu min Äḟndike beyyete taifetum minhum gayrallezÄḟ tekul vallahu yektubu ma yubeyyitun fe aÂṀrÄḟd anhum ve tevekkel alellah ve kefa billahi vekÄḟla"
  4,82,"E fe la yetedebberunel kurÂṀan ve lev kane min Äḟndi gayrullahi le vcedu fÄḟhÄḟhtilafen kesÄḟra"
  4,83,"Ve iza caehum emrum minel emni evil havfi ezau bih ve lev radduhu iler rasuli ve ila ulil emri minhum lealimehullezÄḟne yesmebitunehu minhum ve lev la fadlullahi aleykum ve rahmetuhu lettebaÂṀtumus seytane illa kalÄḟla"
  4,84,"Fe katil fÄḟ sebÄḟlillah la tukellefu illa nefseke ve harridÄḟl muÂṀminÄḟnv asellahu ey yekuffe beÂṀsellezÄḟne keferu vallahu esddu beÂṀsev ve eseddu tenkÄḟla"
  4,85,"Mey yesfaÂṀsefaaten hasenetey yekul lehu nesiybum minha ve mey yesfaÂṀsefaaten seyyietey yekul lehu kiflum minha ve kanellahu ala kulli seyÂṀim mukÄḟyta"
  4,86,"Ve iza huyyÄḟtum bi tehÄḟyyetin fe hayyu bi ahsene minha ev rudduha innellahe kane ala kulli seyÂṀin hasÄḟba"
  4,87,"Allahu la ilahe illa hu le yecmeannekum ila yevmil kÄḟyameti la raybe fÄḟh ve men asdeku minellahi hadÄḟsa"
  4,88,"Fe ma lekum fil munafikÄḟyne fieteyni vallahu erkesehum bi ma kesebu e turÄḟdune en tehdu men edallellah ve mey yudlilillahu fe len tecide lehu sebÄḟla"
  4,89,"Veddu lev tekfurune kema keferu fe tekunune sevaen fe la tettehÄḟzu minhum evliyae hatta yuhaciru fÄḟ sebÄḟlillah fe in tevellev fe huzuhum vaktuluhum haysu vecedtumuhum ve la tettehÄḟzu minhum veliyyev ve la nesÄḟyra"
  4,90,"IlillezÄḟne yesÄḟlune ila kavmim beynekum ve beynehum mÄḟsakun ev caukum hasÄḟrat suduruhum ey yukatilukum ev yukatilu kavmehum ve lev saellahu le selletahum aleykum fe le katelukum fe inÄḟÂṀtezelukum fe lem yukatilukum ve elkav ileykumus selem fe ma cealelahu lekum aleyhim sebÄḟla"
  4,91,"Setecidune aharÄḟne yurÄḟdune ey yeÂṀmenukum ev yeÂṀmenu kavmehum kullema ruddu ilel fitneti urkisu fÄḟha fe il lem yaÂṀtezilukum ve yulku ileykumus selem ve yekuffu eydiyehum fe huzuhum vaktuluhum haysu sekftumuhum ve ulaikum cealna lekum aleyhim sultanem mubÄḟna"
  4,92,"Ve ma kane li muÂṀminin ey yaktule muÂṀminen illa hataa ve men katele muÂṀmine hataen fe tahrÄḟru rakabetim muÂṀminetiv ve diyetum musellemetun ila ehlihÄḟ illa ey yessaddeku fe in kane min kavmin aduvvil lekum ve huve muÂṀminun fe tahrÄḟru rakabetim muÂṀmineh ve in kane mni kavmim beynekum ve beynehum mÄḟsakun fediyetum musellemetun ila ehlihÄḟ ve tahrÄḟru rakabetim muÂṀmineh fe mel lem yecid fe sÄḟyamu sehrayni mutetabiayni tevbetem minellah ve kanellahu alÄḟmen hakÄḟma"
  4,93,"Ve mey yaktul muÂṀminem muteammiden fe cezauhu cehnnemu haliden fÄḟha ve gadÄḟbellahu aleyhi ve leanehu ve eadde lehu azaben azÄḟyma"
  4,94,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu iza darabtum fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi fe tebeyyenu ve la tekulu li men elka ileykumus selame leste muÂṀmina tebtegune aradal hayatid dunya fe Äḟndellahi meganimu kesÄḟrah kezalike kuntum min kablu fe mennellahu aleykum fe tebeyyenu innellahe kane bi ma taÂṀmelune habÄḟra"
  4,95,"La yestevil kaÄḟdune minel muÂṀminÄḟne gayru ulid darari vel mucahidune fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi bi emvalihim ve enfusihim feddalellahul mucahidÄḟne bi emvalihim ve enfusihim alel kaÄḟdÄḟne deraceh ve kullev veadellahul husna ve feddalellahul mucahidÄḟne alel kaÄḟdÄḟne ecran azÄḟyma"
  4,96,"Deracatim minhu ve magfiratev ve rahmehv ve kanellahu gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  4,97,"InnellezÄḟne teveffahumul melaiketu zalimÄḟ enfusihim kalu fÄḟme kuntum kalu kunna mustadÂṀafÄḟne fil ard kalu e lem tekun erdullahi vasiaten fe tuhaciru fÄḟha fe ulaike meÂṀvahum cehennem ve saet mesÄḟyra"
  4,98,"Illel mustadÂṀafÄḟne miner ricali ven nisai vel vildani la yestetÄḟyÂṀune hÄḟyletev ve la yehtedune sebÄḟla"
  4,99,"Fe ulaike asellahu ey yaÂṀfuve anhum ve kanellahu afuvven gafura"
  4,100,"Ve mey yuhacir fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi yecid fil erdÄḟ muragamen kesÄḟrav veseah ve mey yahruc mim beytihÄḟ muhaciran ilellahi ve rasulihÄḟ summe yudrikhul mevtu fe ad vekaa ercuhu alellah ve kanellahu gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  4,101,"Ve iza darabtum fil erdÄḟ fe leyse aleykum cunahun en taksuru mines salah in hÄḟftum ey yeftinekumullezÄḟne keferu innel kafirune kanu lekum aduvvem mubÄḟna"
  4,102,"Ve iza kunte fÄḟhim fe ekamte lehumus salate feltekum taifetum minhum meake vel yeÂṀhuzu eslihatehumv fe iza secedu felyekunu miv veraikumv velteÂṀti taifetun uhra lem yusallu fel yusallu meake vel yeÂṀhuzu hÄḟzrahum ve eslihatehum veddellezÄḟne keferu lev tagfulune an eslihatikum ve emtiatikum fe yemÄḟlune aleykum meyletev vahÄḟdehv ve la cunuha aleykum in kane bi kum ezem mim metarin ev kuntum merda en tedau eslihatekum ve huzu hÄḟzrakumv innellahe eadde lil kafirÄḟne azabem muhÄḟna"
  4,103,"Fe iza kadaytumus salate fezkurullahe kÄḟyamev ve kuudev ve ala cunubikum fe izatmeÂṀnentum fe ekÄḟymus salah innes salate kanet alel muÂṀminÄḟne kitabem mevkuta"
  4,104,"Ve la tahinu fibtigail kavm in tekunu teÂṀlemune fe innehum yeÂṀlemune kema teÂṀlemune ve tercune minellahi mala yercun ve kanellahi alÄḟmen hakÄḟma"
  4,105,"Inna enzelna ileykel kitabe bil hakkÄḟ li tahkume beynen nasi bima erakellah ve la tekul lil hainÄḟne hasÄḟyma"
  4,106,"Vestagfirillah innellahe kane gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  4,107,"Ve la tucadil anillezÄḟne yahtanune enfusehumv innellahe la yuhÄḟbbu men kane havvanen esÄḟma"
  4,108,"Yestahfune minen nasi ve la yestahfune minellahi ve huve meahum iz yubeyyitune ma la yerda minel kavl ve kanellahu bi ma yaÂṀmelune muhÄḟyta"
  4,109,"Ha entum haulai cadeltum anhum fil hayatid dunya fe mey yucadilullahe anhum yevmel kÄḟyameti em mey yekunu aleyhim vekÄḟla"
  4,110,"Ve mey yaÂṀmel suen ev yazlim nefsehu summe yestagfirillahe yecidillahe gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  4,111,"Ve mey yeksib ismen fe innema yeksibuhu ala nefsih ve kanellahu alÄḟmen hakÄḟma"
  4,112,"Ve mey yeksib hatÄḟyÂṀeten ev ismen summe yermi bihÄḟ berÄḟen fe kadÄḟhtemele buhtanev ve ismem mubÄḟna"
  4,113,"Ve lev la fadlullahi aleyke ve rahmetuhu lehemmet taifetum minhum ey yudÄḟlluk ve ma yudÄḟllune illa enfusehum ve ma yedurruneke min seyÂṀ ve enzellellahu aleykel kitabe vel hÄḟkmete ve allemeke ma lem tekun taÂṀlemv ve kane fadlullahi aleyke azÄḟyma"
  4,114,"La hayra fÄḟ kesÄḟrim min necvahum illa men emera bi sadekatin ev maÂṀrufin ev ÄḟslahÄḟm beynen nas ve mey yefÂṀal zalikebtigae merdatillahi fe sevfe nuÂṀtÄḟhi ecran azÄḟyma"
  4,115,"Ve mey yusakÄḟkÄḟr rasule mim baÂṀdi ma tebeyyene lehul huda ve yettebÄḟÂṀ gayra sebÄḟlil muÂṀminÄḟne nuvellihÄḟ ma tevella ve nuslihÄḟ cehennem ve saet mesÄḟyra"
  4,116,"Innellahe la yagfiru ey yusrake bihÄḟ ve yagfiru ma dune zalike li mey yesaÂṀ ve mey yusrik billahi fe kad dalle dalalem beÄḟyda"
  4,117,"Iy yedÂṀune min dunihÄḟ illa inasa ve iy yadÂṀune illa seytanem merÄḟda"
  4,118,"leanehullah ve kale le ettehÄḟzenne min Äḟbadike nasÄḟybem mefruda"
  4,119,"Ve le udÄḟllennehum ve le umenniyennehum ve le amurrannehum fe le yubettikunne azanel enÂṀami ve le amurannehum fe le yugayyirunne halkallah ve mey yettehÄḟzis seytane veliyyem min dunillahi fe kad hasira husranem mubÄḟna"
  4,120,"YeÄḟduhum ve yumennÄḟhim ve ma yeÄḟduhumus seytanu illa gurura"
  4,121,"Ulaike meÂṀvahum cehennemu ve la yecidune"
  4,122,"VellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati senudhÄḟluhum cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha ebeda vaÂṀdellahi hakka ve men asdeku minellahi kÄḟyla"
  4,123,"Leyse bi emaniyyikum ve la emaniyyi ehlil kitab mey yaÂṀmel suey yucze bihÄḟ ve la yecid lehu min dunillahi veliyyev ve la nesÄḟyra"
  4,124,"Ve mey yaÂṀmel mines salihati min zekerin ev unsa ve huve muÂṀminun fe ulaike yedhulunel cennete ve la yuzlemune nekÄḟyra"
  4,125,"Ve men ahsenu dÄḟnem mimmen esleme vechehu lillahi ve huve muhsinuv vettebea millete ibrahÄḟme hanÄḟfa vetetehazellahu ibrahÄḟme halila"
  4,126,"Ve lillahi ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard ve kanellahu bi kulli seyÂṀim muhÄḟyta"
  4,127,"Ve yesteftuneke fin nisaÂṀ kulillahu yuftÄḟkum fÄḟhinne ve ma yutla aleykum fil kitabi fÄḟ yetamen nisaillatÄḟ la tuÂṀtunehunne ma kutibe lehunne ve tergabune en tenkihuhunne vel mustadÂṀafÄḟne minel vildani ve en tekumu lil yetama bil kÄḟst ve ma tefÂṀalu min hayrin fe inellahe kane bihÄḟ alÄḟma"
  4,128,"Ve inimraetun hafet mim baÂṀliha nusuzen ev ÄḟÂṀradan fe la cunaha aleyhima ey yusliha beynehuma sulha ves sulhu hayr ve uhdÄḟratil enfusus suhh ve in tuhsinu ve tetteku fe innellahe kane bi ma taÂṀmelune habÄḟra"
  4,129,"Ve len testetÄḟyÂṀu en taÂṀdilu beynen nisai ve lev harastum fe la temÄḟlu kullel meyli fe tezeruha kel mualekah ve in tuslihu ve tetteku fe innellahe kane gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  4,130,"Ve iy yeteferraka yugnillahu kullem min seatih ve kanellahu vasian hakÄḟma"
  4,131,"Ve lillahi ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard ve le kad vessaynellezÄḟne utul kitabe min kablikum ve iyyakum enittekullah ve in tekfuru fe inne lillahi ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard ve kanellahu ganiyyen hamÄḟda"
  4,132,"Ve lillahi ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard ve kefa billahi vekÄḟla"
  4,133,"Iy yeseÂṀ yuzhibkum eyyuhen nasu ve ye7ti bi aharÄḟn ve kanellahu ala zalike kadÄḟra"
  4,134,"Men kane yurÄḟdu sevabed dunya fe Äḟnellahi sevabud dunya vel ahÄḟrah ve kanellahu semÄḟam besÄḟyra"
  4,135,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu kunu kavvamÄḟne bil kÄḟstÄḟ suhedae lillahi ve lev ala enfusikum evil valideyni vel akrabÄḟn iy yekun ganiyyen ev fekÄḟyran fellahu evla bihima fe la tettebiul heva en taÂṀdilu ve in telvu ev tuÂṀridu fe innellahe kane bi ma taÂṀmelune habÄḟra"
  4,136,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu aminu billahi ve rasulihÄḟ vel kitabillezÄḟ nezzele ala rasulihÄḟ vel kitabillezÄḟ enzele min kabl ve me yekfur billahi ve melaiketihÄḟ ve kutubihÄḟ ve rusulihÄḟ vel yevmil ahÄḟri fe kad dalle dalalem beÄḟyda"
  4,137,"InnellezÄḟne amenu summe keferu summe amenu summe keferu summezdadu kufral lem yekunillahu li yagfira lehum ve la li yehdiyehum sebÄḟla"
  4,138,"Bessiril munafikÄḟyne bi enne lehum azaben elÄḟma"
  4,139,"EllezÄḟne yettehÄḟzunel kafirÄḟne evliyae min dunil muÂṀminÄḟn e yebtegune Äḟndehumul Äḟzzete fe innel Äḟzzete lillahi cemÄḟa"
  4,140,"Ve kad nezzele aleykum fil kitabi en iza semÄḟÂṀtum ayatillahi yukferu biha ve yustehzeu biha fe la takÂṀudu meahum hatta yehudu fÄḟ hadÄḟsin gayrihÄḟ innekum izem musluhum innellahe camiul munafikÄḟyne vel kafirÄḟne fÄḟ cehenneme cemÄḟa"
  4,141,"EllezÄḟne yeterabbesune bikum fe in kane lekum fethum minellahi kalu e lem nekum meakum ve in kane lil kafirÄḟne nasÄḟybun kalu elem nestahviz aleykum ve nemnaÂṀkum minel muÂṀminÄḟn fellahu yahkumu beynekum yevmel kÄḟyameh ve ley yecÂṀalellahu lil kafirÄḟne alel muÂṀminÄḟne sebÄḟla"
  4,142,"Innel munafikÄḟyne yuhadiunellahe ve huve hadÄḟuhum ve iza kamu iles salati kamu kusala yuraunen nase ve la yezkurunellahe illa kalÄḟla"
  4,143,"MuzebzebÄḟne beyne zalike la ila haulai ve la ila haulaÂṀ ve mey yudlilillahu fe len tecide lehu sebÄḟla"
  4,144,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tettehÄḟzul kafirÄḟne evliyae min dunil muÂṀminÄḟn e turÄḟdune en tecÂṀalu lillahi aleykum sultanem mubÄḟna"
  4,145,"Innel munafikÄḟyne fid derkil esfeli minen nar ve len tecide lehum nesÄḟyra"
  4,146,"IllellezÄḟne tabu ve aslehu vaÂṀtesamu billahi va ahlesu dÄḟnehum lillahi fe ulaike meal muÂṀminÄḟn ve sevfe yuÂṀtillahul muÂṀminÄḟne ecran azÄḟyma"
  4,147,"Ma yefÂṀalullahu bi azabikum in sekartum ve amentum ve kanellahu sakian alÄḟma"
  4,148,"La yuhÄḟbbullahul cehra bis sui minel kavli illa men zulim v kanellahu semÄḟan alÄḟma"
  4,149,"In tubdu hayran ev tuhfuhu ev taÂṀfu an suin fe innellahe kane afuvven kadÄḟra"
  4,150,"InnellezÄḟne yekfurune billah ive rusulihÄḟ ve yurÄḟdune ey yuferriku beynellahi ve rusulihÄḟ ve yekulune nuÂṀminu bi baÂṀdÄḟv ve nekfuru bi baÂṀdÄḟv ve yurÄḟdune ey yettehÄḟzu beyne zalike sebÄḟla"
  4,151,"Ulaike humul kafirune hakka ve aÂṀtedna lil kafirÄḟne azabem muhiyna"
  4,152,"VellezÄḟne amenu billahi ve rusulihÄḟ ve lem yuferriku beyne ehadim minhum ulaike sevfe yuÂṀtÄḟhim ucurahum ve kanellahu gafurar rahÄḟyam"
  4,153,"YesÂṀeluke ehlul ehlul kitabi en tunezzile aleyhim kitabem mines semai fe kad seelu musa ekbera min zalike fe kalu erinellah cehratem fe ehazethumus saÄḟkatu bi sulmihim summettehazul Äḟcle mim baÂṀdi ma caethumul beyyinatu fe afevna an zalik ve ateyna musa sultanem mubÄḟna"
  4,154,"Ve rafaÂṀna fevkahumut tura bi mÄḟsakÄḟhim ve kulna lehumudhulul babe sucedev ve kulna lehum la taÂṀdu fis sebti ve ehazna minhum mÄḟsakan galÄḟza"
  4,155,"Fe bima nakdÄḟhim mÄḟsakahum ve kufrihim bi ayatillahi ve katlihimul embiyae bi gayri hakkÄḟv ve kavlihim kulubuna gulf bel tabeallahu aleyha bi kufrihim fe la yuÂṀminune illa kalÄḟla"
  4,156,"Ve bi kufrihim ve kavlihim ala meryeme buhtanen azÄḟyam"
  4,157,"Ve kavlihim inna katelnel mesÄḟha Äḟysebne meryeme raulellah ve ma kateluhu ve ma salebuhu ve lakin subbihe lehum ve innellezÄḟnahtelefu fÄḟhi le fÄḟ sekkim minh ma lehum bihÄḟ min Äḟlmin illettibaaz zann ve ma kateluhu yekÄḟyna"
  4,158,"Ber rafeahullahu ileyh ve kanellahu azÄḟzen hakÄḟma"
  4,159,"Ve im min ehlil kitabi illa le yuÂṀminenne bihÄḟ kable mevtih ve yevmel kÄḟyameti yekunu aleyhim sehÄḟda"
  4,160,"Fe bi zulmim minellezÄḟne hadu harramna aleyhim tayyibatin uhÄḟllet lehum ve bi saddihim an sebÄḟlillahi kesÄḟra"
  4,161,"Ve ahzihimur riba ve kad nuhu anhu ve eklihim emvalen nasi bil baÂṀtÄḟl ve aÂṀtedna lil kafirÄḟne minhum azaben elÄḟma"
  4,162,"Lakinir rasihune fil Äḟlmi minhum vel muÂṀminune yuÂṀminune bi ma unzile ileyke ve ma unzile min kabileke vel mukÄḟymÄḟnes salate vel muÂṀtunez zekate vel muÂṀminune billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟr ulaike se nuÂṀtÄḟhim ecran azÄḟyma"
  4,163,"Inna evhayna ileyke kema evhayna ila nuhÄḟv ven nebiyyÄḟne mim baÂṀdih ve evhayna ila ibrahÄḟme ve ismaÄḟyle ve ishaka ve yaÂṀkube vel esbatÄḟ ve Äḟysa ve eyyube ve yunuse ve harune ve suleyman ve ateyna davude zebura"
  4,164,"Ve rusulen kad kasasnahum aleyke min kablu ve rusulel lem naksushum aleyk ve kellemellahu musa teklÄḟma"
  4,165,"Rusulem mubessirÄḟne ve munzirÄḟne li ella yekune lin nasi alellahi huccetum baÂṀder rusul ve kanellahu azÄḟzen hakÄḟma"
  4,166,"Lakinillahu yeshedu bi ma enzele ileyke enzelehu bi Äḟlmih vel melaiketu yeshedun ve kefa billahi sehÄḟda"
  4,167,"InnellezÄḟne keferu ve saddu an sebÄḟlillahi kad dallu dalalem beÄḟyda"
  4,168,"InnellezÄḟne keferu ve zalemu lem yekunillahu li yagfira lehum ve la li yehdiyehum tarÄḟka"
  4,169,"Illa tarika cehenneme halidÄḟne fÄḟha ebeda ve kane zalike alellahi yesÄḟra"
  4,170,"Ya eyyuhen nasu kad caekumur rasulu bil hakkÄḟ mir rabbikum fe aminu hayral lekum ve in tekfuru fe inne lillahi ma fis semavati vel ard ve kanellahu alÄḟmen hakÄḟma"
  4,171,"Ya ehlel kitabi la taglu fÄḟ dÄḟnikum ve la tekulu alellahi illel hakk innemel mesÄḟhu Äḟysebnu meryeme rasulullahi ve kelimetuh elkaha ila meryeme ve ruhum minhu fe aminu billahi ve rusulih ve la tekulu selaseh intehu hayral lekum innemellahu ilahuv vahÄḟd subhanehu ey yekune lehu veled lehu ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard ve kefa billahi vekÄḟla"
  4,172,"Ley yestenkifel mesÄḟhu ey yekune abdel lillahi ve lel melaiketul mukarrabun ve mey yestenkif an ÄḟbadetihÄḟ ve yestekbir fe seyahsuruhum ileyhi cemÄḟa"
  4,173,"Fe emmellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati fe yuveffÄḟhim ucurahum ve yezÄḟduhum min fadlih ve emmellezÄḟnestenkefu vestekberu fe yuazzibuhum azaben elÄḟmev ve la yecidune lehum min dunillahi veliyyev ve la nesÄḟyra"
  4,174,"Ya eyyuhen nasu kad caekum burhanum mir rabbikum ve enzelna ileykum nuram mubÄḟna"
  4,175,"Fe emmellezÄḟne amenu billahi vaÂṀtesamu bihÄḟ fe seyudhÄḟluhum fÄḟ rahmetim minhu ve fadliv ve yehdÄḟhim ileyhi sÄḟratam mustekÄḟyma"
  4,176,"Yesteftunek kulillahu yuftikum fil kelaleh inimruun heleke leyse lehu veleduv ve lehu uhtun fe leha nÄḟsfu ma terak ve huve yerisuha il lem yekul leha veled fe in kanetesneteyni fe lehumes sulusani mimma terak ve in kanu Äḟhveter ricalev ve nisaen fe lizzekeri mislu hazzÄḟl unseyeyen yubeyyinullahu lekum en tedÄḟllu vallahu bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  5,8,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu kunu kavvamÄḟne lillahi suhedae bil kÄḟstÄḟ ve la yecrimennekum seneanu kavmin ala ella taÂṀdilu ÄḟÂṀdilu huve akrabu lit takva vettekullah innellahe habÄḟrum bi ma taÂṀmelun"
  5,9,"VeadellahullezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati lehum magfiratuv ve ecrun azÄḟym"
  5,10,"VellezÄḟne keferu ve kezzebu bi ayatina ulaike ashabul cehÄḟym"
  5,11,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenuzkuru nÄḟÂṀmetellahi aleykum iz hemme kavmun ey yebsutu ileykum eydiyehum fe keffe eydiyehum anku vettekullah ve alellahi fel yetevekkelil muÂṀminun"
  5,12,"Ve le kad ehazellahu mÄḟsaka benÄḟ israÄḟl ve beasna minhumusney usera nekÄḟyba ve kalellahu innÄḟ meakum lein ekamtumus salate ve ateytumuz zekate ve amentum bi rusulÄḟ ve azzertumuhum ve akradtumullahe kardan hasenel le ukeffiranne ankum seyyiatikum ve le udhÄḟlennekum cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enhar fe men kefera baÂṀde zalike minkumfe kad dalle sevaes sebÄḟl"
  5,13,"Fe bima nakdÄḟhim mÄḟsakahum leannahum ve cealna kulubehum kasiyeh yuharrifunel kelime ammevadÄḟÄḟhÄḟ ve nesu hazzam mimma zukkiru bih ve la tezalu tettaliu ala hainetim minhum illa kalÄḟlem minhum faÂṀfu anhum vasfah innellahe yuhÄḟbbul muhsinÄḟn"
  5,14,"Ve minellezÄḟne kalu inna nesara ehazna mÄḟsakahum fe nesu hazzam mimma zukkiru bihÄḟ fe agrayna beynehumul adavete vel bagdae ila yevmil kÄḟyameh ve sevfe yunebbiuhumullahu bi ma kanu yasneun"
  5,15,"Ya ehlel kitabi kad caekum rasuluna yubeyyinu lekum kesÄḟram mimma kuntum tuhfune minel kitabi ve yaÂṀfu an kesÄḟr kad caekum minellahi nuruv ve kitabum mubÄḟn"
  5,16,"YehdÄḟ bilillahu menittebea rÄḟdvanehu subules selami ve yuhricuhum minez zulumati ilen nuri bi iznihÄḟ ve yehdÄḟhim ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  5,17,"Le kad keferallezÄḟne kalu innellahe huvel mesÄḟhunu meryem kul fe mey yemliku minellahi seyÂṀen in erade ey yuhlikel misÄḟhabne meryeme ve ummehu ve men fil erdÄḟ cemÄḟa ve lillahi mulkus semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ma beynehuma yahluku ma yesaÂṀ vallahu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  5,18,"Ve kaleltil yehudu ven nesara nahnu ebnaullahi ve ehÄḟbbauh kul fe lime yuazzibukum bi zunubikum bel entum beserum mimmen halak yagfiru li mey yesau ve yuazzibu mey yesaÂṀ ve lillahi mulkus semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ma beynehuma ve ileyhil mesÄḟyr"
  5,19,"Ya ehlel kitabi kad caekum rasuluna yubeyyinu lekum ala fetratim miner rusuli en tekulu ma caena mim besÄḟriv ve la nezÄḟrin fe kad caekum besÄḟruv venezÄḟr vallahu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  5,20,"Ve iz kale musa li kavmihÄḟ ya kavmizkuru nÄḟÂṀmetellahi aleykum iz ceale fÄḟkum embiyae ve ceallekum mulukev ve atakum ma lem yuÂṀti ehadem minel alemÄḟn"
  5,21,"Ya kavmidhulul erdal mukaddesetelletÄḟ ketebellahu lekum ve la terteddu ala edbarikum fe tenkalibu hasirÄḟn"
  5,22,"Kalu ya musa inne fÄḟha kavmen cebbarÄḟne ve inna len nedhuleha hatta yahrucu minha fe iy yahrucu minha fe inna dahÄḟlun"
  5,23,"Kale raculani minellezÄḟne yehafune enÂṀamellahu aleyhimedhulu aleyhimul bab fe iza dehaltumuhu fe innekum galibune ve alellahi fe tevekkelu in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  5,24,"Kalu ya musa inna len nedhuleha ebedem ma damu fÄḟha fezheb ente ve rabbuke fe katila inna hahuna kaÄḟdun"
  5,25,"Kale rabbi innÄḟ la emliku illa nefsÄḟ ve ehÄḟy fefruk beynena ve beynel kavmil fasikÄḟyn"
  5,26,"Kale fe inneha muharrametun aleyhim erbeÄḟyne seneh yetÄḟhune fil erdÄḟ fe la teÂṀse alel kavmil fasikÄḟyn"
  5,27,"Vetlu aleyhim nebeebney ademe bil hakk iz karraba kurbanen fe tukubbile min ehadihima ve lem yutekabbel minel ahar kale le aktulennek kale innema yetekabbelul lahu minel muttekÄḟyn"
  5,28,"Leim besatte ileyye yedeke li taktulenÄḟ ma ene bi basitÄḟy yediye ileyke li aktulek innÄḟ ehafullahe rabbel alemÄḟn"
  5,29,"InnÄḟ urÄḟdu en tebue bi ismÄḟ ve ismike fe tekune min ashabin nar ve zalike cezauz zalimÄḟn"
  5,30,"Fe tavveat lehu nefsuhu katle ehÄḟyhi fe katelehu fe asbeha minel hasirÄḟn"
  5,31,"Fe beasellahu gurabey yebhasu fil erdÄḟ li yuriyehu keyfe yuvarÄḟ sevÂṀete ehÄḟyh kale ya veyleta eaceztu en ekune misle hazel gurabi fe uvariye sevÂṀete ehÄḟy fe asbeha minen nadimÄḟn"
  5,32,"Min ecli zalike ketebna ala benÄḟ israÄḟle ennehu men katel nefsem bi gayri nefsin ev fesadin fil erdÄḟ fe keennema katelen nase cemÄḟa ve men ahyaha fe keennema ahyan nase cemÄḟa ve le kad caethum rusuluna bil beyyinati summe inne kesÄḟram minhum baÂṀde zalike fil erdÄḟ le musrifun"
  5,33,"Innema cezaullezÄḟne yuharribunellahe ve rasulehu ve yesÂṀavne fil erdÄḟ fesaden ey yukattelu ev yusallebu ev tukattaa eydÄḟhim ve erculuhum min hÄḟlafin ev yunfev minel ard zalike lehum hÄḟzyun fid dunya ve lehum fil ahÄḟrati azabun azÄḟym"
  5,34,"IllellezÄḟne tabu min kabli en takdiru aleyhim faÂṀlemu ennellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  5,35,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenuttekullahe vebtegu ileyhil vesÄḟlete ve cahidu fÄḟ sebÄḟlihÄḟ leallekum tuflihun"
  5,36,"InnellezÄḟne keferu lev enne lehum ma fil erdÄḟ cemÄḟav ve mislehu meahu li yeftedu bihÄḟ min azabi yevmil kÄḟyameti ma tukubbile minhum ve lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  5,37,"YurÄḟdune ey yahrucu minen nari ve ma hum bi haricÄḟne minha ve lehum azabum mukÄḟym"
  5,38,"Ves sariku ves sarikatu faktau eydiyehuma cezaem bima keseba nekalem minellah vallahu azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  5,39,"Fe men tabe mim baÂṀdi zulmihÄḟ ve asleha fe innellahe yetubu aleyh innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  5,40,"E lem taÂṀlem ennellahe lehu mulkus semavati vel erdÄḟ yuazzibu mey yesau ve yagfiru li mey yesaÂṀ vallahu ala kulli yesÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  5,41,"Ya eyyuher rasulu la yahzunkellezÄḟne yusariune fil kufri minellezÄḟne kalu amenna bi efvahihim ve lem tuÂṀmin kulubuhum ve minellezÄḟne hadu semmaune lil kezibi semmaune li kavmin aharÄḟne lem yeÂṀtuk yuharrifunel kelime mim baÂṀdi mevadÄḟÄḟh yekulune in utÄḟtum haza fe huzuhu ve il lem tuÂṀtevhu fahzeru ve mey yuridillahu fitnetehu fe len temlike lehu minellahi seyÂṀa ulaikellezÄḟne lem yuridillahu ey yutahhira kulubehum lehum fid dunya hÄḟzyuv ve lehum fil ahÄḟrati azabun azÄḟym"
  5,42,"Semmaune lil kesibi ekkalune lis suht fe in cauke fahkum beynehum ev aÂṀrÄḟd anhum ve in tuÂṀrÄḟd anhum fe ley yedurruke seyÂṀa ve in hakemte fahkum beynehum bil kÄḟst innellahe yuhÄḟbbul muksitÄḟyn"
  5,43,"Ve keyfe yuhakkimunee ve Äḟndehumut tevratu fÄḟha hukmullahi summe yetevellevne mim baÂṀdi zalik ve ma ulaike bil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  5,44,"Inna enzelnet tevrate fÄḟha hudev ve nur yahkumu bihen nebiyyunellezÄḟne eslemu lillezÄḟne hadu ver rabbaniyyune vel ahbaru bimestuhfizu min kitabillahi ve kanu aleyhi suhedaÂṀ fe la tahsevun nase vahsevni ve la testeru bi ayatÄḟ semenen kalÄḟla ve mel lem yahkum bi ma enzelellahu fe ulaike humul kafirun"
  5,45,"Ve ketebna aleyhim fÄḟha ennen nefse bin nefsi vel ayne bil ayni vel enfe bil enfi vel uzune bil uzuni ves sinne bis sinni vel curuha kÄḟsas fe men tesaddeka bihÄḟ fe huve keffaratul leh ve mel lem yahkum bima enzelellahu fe ulaike humuz zalimun"
  5,46,"Ve kaffeyna ala asarihim bi Äḟysebni meryeme musaddikal lima beyne yedeyhi minet tevrati ve ateynahul incÄḟle fÄḟhi hudev ve nuruv ve musaddikal lima beyne yedeyhi minet tevrati ve hudev ve mevÂṀÄḟzatel lil muttekÄḟyn"
  5,47,"Vel yahkum ehlul incÄḟli bima enzelellahu fÄḟh ve mel lem yahkum bima enzelellahu fe ulaike humul fasikun"
  5,48,"Ve enzelna ileykel kitabe bil hakkÄḟ musaddikal lima beyne yedeyhi minel kitabi ve muhayminen aleyhi fahkum beynehum bima enzelellahu ve la tettebÄḟÂṀ ehvaehum amma caeke minel hakk li kullin cealna minkum sirÂṀatev ve minhaca ve lev saellahu le cealekum ummetev vahÄḟdetev ve lakil li yebluvekum fÄḟ ma atakum festebikul hayrat ilellahi merciukum cemÄḟan fe yunebbiukum bi ma kuntum fÄḟhi tahtelifun"
  5,49,"Ve enÄḟhkum beynehum bi ma enzelellahu ve la tettebÄḟÂṀ ehvaehum vahzerhum ey yeftinuke ambaÂṀdÄḟ ma enzelellahu ileyk fe in tevellev faÂṀlem ennema yurÄḟdullahu ey yusÄḟybehum bi baÂṀdÄḟ zunubihim ve inne kesÄḟram minen nasi le fasikun"
  5,50,"E fe hukmel cahiliyyeti yebgun ve men ahsenu minellahi hukmel li kavmiy yukÄḟnun"
  5,51,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tettehÄḟzul yehude ven nesara evliyaÂṀ baÂṀduhum evliyau baÂṀd ve mey yetevellehum minkum fe innehu minhum innellahe la yehdil kavmez zalimÄḟn"
  5,52,"Fe terallezÄḟne fÄḟ kulubihim meraduy yusariune fÄḟhim yekulune nahsa en tusÄḟybena dairah fe asellahu ey yeÂṀtiye bil fethÄḟ ev emrim min ÄḟndihÄḟ fe yusbihu ala ma eserru fÄḟ enfusihim nadimÄḟn"
  5,53,"Ve yekulullezÄḟne amenu ehaulaillezÄḟne aksemu billahi cehde eymanihim innehum le meakum habitat aÂṀmaluhum fe asbehu hasirÄḟn"
  5,54,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu mey yertedde minkum an dÄḟnihÄḟ fe sevfe yeÂṀtillahu bi kavmiy yuhÄḟbbuhum ve yuhÄḟbbunehu ezilletin alel muÂṀminÄḟne e Äḟzzetin alel kafirÄḟne yucahidune fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi ve la yehafune levmete laim zalike fadlullahi yu7tÄḟhi mey yesaÂṀ vallahu vasiun alÄḟm"
  5,55,"Innema veliyyukumullahu ve rasuluhu vellezÄḟne amenullezÄḟne yukÄḟymunes salate ve yuÂṀtunez zekate ve hum rakiun"
  5,56,"Ve mey yetevellellahe ve rasulehu vellezÄḟne amenu fe inne hÄḟzbellahi humul galibun"
  5,57,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tettehÄḟzul lezÄḟnettehazu dÄḟnekum huzuvev ve leÄḟbem minellezÄḟne utul kitabe min kablikum vel kuffara evliyaÂṀ vettekullahe in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  5,58,"Ve iza nadeytum iles salatittehazuha huzuvev ve leÄḟba zalike bi ennehum kavmul la yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  5,59,"Kul ya ehlel kitabi hel tenkÄḟmune minna illa en amenna billahi ve ma unzile ileyna ve ma unzile min kablu ve enne ekserakum fasikun"
  5,60,"Kul hel unebbiukum bi serrim min zalike mesubeten Äḟndellah mel leanehullahu ve gadÄḟbe aleyhi ve ceale minhumul kÄḟradete vel hanazÄḟra ve abedet tagut ulaike serrum mekanev ve edallu an sevais sebÄḟl"
  5,61,"Ve iza caukum kalu amenna ve kad dehalu bil kufri ve hum kad haracu bih vallahu aÂṀlemu bi ma kanu yektumun"
  5,62,"Ve tera kesÄḟram minhum yusariune fil ismi vel udvani ve eklihimus suht le biÂṀse ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  5,63,"Lev la yenhahumur rabbaniyyune vel ahbaru an kavlihimul isme ve eklihimus suht le biÂṀse ma kanu yasneun"
  5,64,"Ve kaletil yehudu yedullahi magluleh gullet eydÄḟhim ve luÄḟnu bi ma kalu bel yedahu mebsutatani yunfiku keyfe yesaÂṀ ve le yezÄḟdenne kesÄḟram minhum ma unzile ileyke mir rabbike tugyanev ve kufra ve elkayna beynehumul adavete vel bagdae ila yevmil kÄḟyameh kullema evkadu naral lil harbi atfeehellahu ve yesÂṀavne fil erdÄḟ fesada vallahu la yuhÄḟbbul mufsidÄḟn"
  5,65,"Ve lev enne ehlel kitabi amenu vettekav le kefferna anhum seyyiatihim ve le edhalnahum cennatin neÄḟym"
  5,66,"Ve lev ennehum ekamut tevrate vel incÄḟle ve ma unzile ileyhim mir rabbihim le ekelu min fevkÄḟhim ve min tahti erculihim minhum ummetum muktesÄḟdeh ve kesÄḟrum minhum sae ma yaÂṀmelun"
  5,67,"Ya eyyuher rasulu bellÄḟg ma unzile ileyke mir rabbik ve il lem tefÂṀal fe ma bellagte risaleteh vallahu yaÂṀsÄḟmuke minen nas innellahe la yehdil kavmel kafirun"
  5,68,"Kul ya ehlel kitabi lestum alal seyÂṀin hatta tukÄḟymut tevrate vel incÄḟle ve ma unzile ileykum mir rabbikum ve le yezÄḟdenne kesÄḟram minhum ma unzile ileyke mir rabbike tugyanev ve kufra fe la teÂṀse alel kavmil kafirÄḟn"
  5,69,"InnellezÄḟne amenu vellezÄḟne hadu ves sabiune ven nesara men amene billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟri ve amile salihan fe la havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  5,70,"Le kad ehazna mÄḟsaka benÄḟ israÄḟle ve erselna ileyhim rusula kullema caehum rasulum bi ma la tehva enfusuhum ferÄḟkan kezzebu ve ferÄḟkay yaktulun"
  5,71,"Ve hasibu ella tekune fitnetun feamu ve sammu summe tabellahu aleyhim summe amu ve sammu kesÄḟrum minhum vallahu basÄḟyrum bima yaÂṀmelun"
  5,72,"Le kad keferallezÄḟne kalu innellahe huvel mesÄḟhubnu meryem ve kalel mesÄḟhu ya benÄḟ israÄḟlaÂṀbudullahe rabbÄḟ ve rabbekum innehu mey yusrik billahi fe kad harramellahu aleyhil cennete ve meÂṀvahun nar ve ma liz zalimÄḟne min ensar"
  5,73,"Le kad keferallezÄḟne kalu innellahe salisu selaseh ve ma min ilahin illa ilahuv vahÄḟd ve il lem yentehu amma yekulune le yemessennellezÄḟne keferu minhum azabun elÄḟm"
  5,74,"E fe la yetubune ilellahi ve yestagfiruneh vallahu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  5,75,"Mel mesÄḟhubnu meryeme illa rasul kad halet min kablihir rusul ve ummuhu sÄḟddÄḟkah kana yeÂṀkulanit taam unzur keyfe nubeyyinu lehumul ayati summenzur enna yuÂṀfekun"
  5,76,"Kul e taÂṀbudune min dunillahi ma la yemliku lekum darrav ve la nefÂṀa vallahu huves semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  5,77,"Kul ya ehlel kitabi la taglu fÄḟ dÄḟnikum gayral hakkÄḟ ve la tettebiu ehvae kavmin kad dallu min kablu ve edallu kesÄḟrav ve dallu an sevais sebÄḟl"
  5,78,"LuÄḟnellezÄḟne keferu mim benÄḟ israÄḟle ala lisani davude ve Äḟysebni meryem zalike bima asav ve kanu yaÂṀtedun"
  5,79,"Kanu la yetenahevne amunkerin fealuh lebiÂṀse ma kanu yefÂṀalun"
  5,80,"Tera kesÄḟram minhum yetevellevnellezÄḟne keferu le biÂṀse ma kaddemet lehum enfusuhum en sehÄḟtallahu aleyhim ve fil azabi hum halidun"
  5,81,"Ve lev kanu yuÂṀminune billahi vne nebiyyi ve ma unzile ileyhi mettehazuhum evliyae ve lakinne kesÄḟram minhum fasikun"
  5,82,"Le tecidenne esedden nasi adavetel lillezÄḟne amenul yehude vellezÄḟne esraku ve le tecidenne akrabehum meveddetel lillezÄḟne amenullezÄḟne kalu inna nesara zalike bi enne munhum kÄḟssÄḟsÄḟne ve ruhbanev ve ennehum la yestekbirun"
  5,83,"Ve iza semiu ma unzile iler rasuli tera aÂṀyunehum tefÄḟdu mined demÂṀÄḟ mimma arafu minel hakk yekulune rabbena amenna fektubna meas sahidÄḟn"
  5,84,"Ve ma lena la nuÂṀminu billahi ve ma caena minel hakkÄḟ ve natmeu ey yudhÄḟlena rabbuna meal kavmis salihÄḟyn"
  5,85,"Fe esabehumullahu bima kalu cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha ve zalike ceazul muhsinÄḟn"
  5,86,"VelelÄḟzne keferu ve kezzebu bi ayatina ulaike ashabul cehÄḟym"
  5,87,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tuharrimu tayyibati ma ehallellahu lekum ve la taÂṀtedu innellahe le yuhÄḟbbul muÂṀtedÄḟn"
  5,88,"Ve kulu mimma razekakumullahu halalen teyyibev vettekullahellezÄḟ entum bihÄḟ muÂṀminun"
  5,89,"La yuahÄḟzukumullahu billagvi fÄḟ eymanikum ve lakiy yuahÄḟzukum bima akkadtumul eyman fe keffaratuhu ÄḟtÂṀamu aserati mesakÄḟne min evsetÄḟ ma tutÂṀÄḟmune ehlÄḟkum evkisvetuhum ev tahrÄḟru rakabeh fe mel lem yecid fe sÄḟyamu selaseti eyyam zalike kefferatu eymanikum iza haleftum vahfezu eymanekum kezalike yubeyyinullahu lekum ayatihÄḟ leallekum teskurun"
  5,90,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu innemel hamru vel meysiru vel ensabu vel ezlamu ricsum min amelis seytani fectenibuhu leallekum tuflihun"
  5,91,"Innema yurÄḟdus seytanu ey yukÄḟa beynekumul adavete vel bagdae fil hamri vel meysiri ve yesuddekum an zikrillahi ve anis salah fe hel entum muntehun"
  5,92,"Ve etÄḟyÂṀullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀur rasule vahzeru fe in tevelleytum faÂṀlemu ennema ala rasulinel belagul mubÄḟn"
  5,93,"Leyse alellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati cunahun fÄḟma taÄḟmu iza mettekav ve amenu ve amilus salihati summettekav ve amenu summettekav ve ahsenu vallahu yuhabbul muhsinÄḟn"
  5,94,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu le yebluvenne kumulluhu bi seyÂṀim mines saydi tenaluhu eydÄḟkum ve rimahukum li yaÂṀlemellahu mey yehafuhu bil gayb fe menÄḟÂṀteda baÂṀde zalike fe lehu azabun elÄḟm"
  5,95,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la taktulus sayde ve entum hurram ve men katelehu minkum muteammiden fe ceazum mislu ma katele minen neami yahkumu bihÄḟ zeva adlim minkum hedyem baligal kaÂṀbeti ev keffaratun taamu mesakÄḟne ev adlu zalike sÄḟyamel li yezuka ve bale emrih afallahu amma selef ve men ade fe yentekÄḟmullahu minh vallahu azÄḟzun zuntikam"
  5,96,"UhÄḟlle lekum saydul bahri ve taamuhu metaal lekum ve lis seyyarah ve hurrime aleykum saydul birri ma duntum huruma vettekullahellezÄḟ ileyhi tuhserun"
  5,97,"Cealellahul kaÂṀbetel beyteh harame kÄḟyamel lin nasi ves sehral harame vel hedye vel kalaid zalike li taÂṀlemu ennellahe yaÂṀlemu ma fis semavati ve ma fil erdÄḟ ve ennellahe bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  5,98,"IÂṀlemu ennellahe sedÄḟdul Äḟkabi ve ennellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  5,99,"Ma aler rasuli illel belag vallahu ya7lemu ma tubdune ve ma tektumun"
  5,100,"Kul la yestevil habisu vet tayyibu ve lev aÂṀcebeke kesratul habÄḟs fettekullahe ya ulil elbabi leallekum tuflihun"
  5,101,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tesÂṀelu an esyae in tubde lekum tesuÂṀkum ve in tesÂṀelu anha hÄḟyne yunezzelul kurÂṀanu tubde lekum afallahu anha vallahu gafurun halÄḟm"
  5,102,"Kad seeleha kavmun min kablikum summe asbehu biha kafirÄḟn"
  5,103,"Ma cealellahu mim behÄḟyrativ ve la saibetiv ve la vesÄḟyletiv ve la hamiv ve lainnellezÄḟne keferu yefterune alellahil kezib ve ekseruhum la yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  5,104,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehum tealev ila ma enzelellahu ve iler rasuli kalu hasbuna ma vecedna aleyhi abaena e ve lev kane abauhum la yaÂṀlemune seyÂṀev ve la yehtedun"
  5,105,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu aleykum enfusekum la yedurrukum men dalle izehtedeytum ilellahi mirciukum cemÄḟan fe yunebbiukum bi ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  5,106,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu sehadetu beynikum iza hadara ehadekumul mevtu hÄḟynel vesÄḟyyetisnani zevaadlim minkum ev aharani min gayrikum in entum darabtum fil erdÄḟ fe esabetkum musÄḟybetul mevt tahbisunehuma mim baÂṀdis salati fe yuksimani billahi inirtebtum la nesterÄḟ bihÄḟ semenev ve lev kane za kurba ve la nektumu sehadetellahi inna izel le minel azimÄḟn"
  5,107,"Fe in usira ala ennehumestehakka ismen fe aharani yekumani mekamehuma minellezÄḟ nestehakka aleyhimul evleyani fe yuksimani billahi le sehadetuna ehakku min sehadetihima ve maÂṀtedeyna inna izel le minez zalimÄḟn"
  5,108,"Zalike edna ey yeÂṀtu bis sehadeti ala vechiha ev yehafu en turadde eymanum baÂṀde eymanihim vettekullahe vesmeu vallahu la yehdil kavmel fasikÄḟyn"
  5,109,"Yevme yecmeullahur rusule fe yekulu ma za ucibtum kalu la ilme lenav inneke ente allamul guyub"
  5,110,"Iz kalellahu ya iysebne meryemezkur nÄḟÂṀmetÄḟ aleyke ve ala validetik iza eyyedtuke bi ruhÄḟl kudusi tukellimun nase fil mehdi ve kehla ve iz alemtukel kitabe vel hÄḟkmete vet tevrate vel incÄḟl ve iz tahluku minet tÄḟyni ke heyÂṀetit tayri bi iznÄḟ fe tenfuhu fÄḟha fe tekunu tayram bi iznÄḟ ve tubriul ekmehe vel ebrasa bi iznÄḟ ve iz huricul mevta bi iznÄḟ ve iz kefeftu benÄḟ israÄḟle anke iz ciÂṀtehum bil beyyinati fe kalellezÄḟne keferu minhum in haza illa sÄḟhrum mubÄḟn"
  5,111,"Ve iz evhaytu ilel havariyyÄḟne en aminu bÄḟ ve bi rasulÄḟ kalu amenna veshed bi ennena muslimun"
  5,112,"Iz kalel havariyyune ya Äḟysebne meryeme hel yestetÄḟyÂṀu rabbuke ey yunezzile aleyna maidetem mines semaÂṀ kalettekullahe in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  5,113,"Kalu nurÄḟdu en neÂṀkule minha ve tatmeinne kulubuna ve naÂṀleme en kad sadaktena ve nekune aleyha mines sahidÄḟn"
  5,114,"Kale Äḟysebnu meryemellahumme rabbena enzil aleyna maidetem mines semai tekunu lena Äḟydel li evvelina ve ahÄḟrina ve ayetem mink verzukna ve ente hayrÄḟr razikÄḟyn"
  5,115,"Kalellahu innÄḟ munezziluha aleykum fe mey yekfur baÂṀdu minkum fe innÄḟ uazzibuhu azabel la uazzibuhu ehadem minel alemÄḟn"
  5,116,"Ve iz kalellahu ya iysebne meryeme e ente kulte lin nasittehÄḟzunÄḟ ve ummiye ilaheyni min dunillah kale subhaneke ma yekunu lÄḟ en ekÄḟle ma lesse lÄḟ bi hakk in kuntu kultuhu fe kad alimteh taÂṀlemu ma fÄḟ nefsÄḟ ve la aÂṀlemu ma fÄḟ nefsik inneke ente allamul guyub"
  5,117,"Me kultu lehum illa ma emartenÄḟ bihÄḟ enÄḟÂṀbudullahe rabbÄḟ ve rabbekum ve kuntu aleyhim sehÄḟdem ma dumtu fÄḟhim felemma teveffeytenÄḟ kunte enter rakÄḟybe aleyhim ve ente ala kulli seyÂṀin sehÄḟd"
  5,118,"In tuazzibhum fe innehum Äḟbaduk ve in tagfir lehum fe inneke entel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  5,119,"Kalellahu haza yevmu yenfeus sadikÄḟyne sÄḟdkuhum lehum cennatun tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha ebeda radÄḟyellahu anhum ve radu anh zalikel fevzul azÄḟym"
  5,120,"Lillahi mulkus semavati vel erdÄḟ va ma fÄḟhinn ve huve ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  6,8,"Ve kalu lev la unzile aleyhi melek ve lev enzelna melekel lekudÄḟyel emru summe la yunzarun"
  6,9,"Ve lev cealnahu melekel le cealnahu raculev ve lelebesna aleyhim ma yelbisun"
  6,10,"Ve le kadistuhzie bi rusulim min kablike fe haka billezÄḟne sehÄḟru minhum ma kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  6,11,"Kul sÄḟru fil erdÄḟ summenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetul mukezzibÄḟn"
  6,12,"Kul li mem ma fis semavati vel ard kul lillah ketebe ala nefsihir rahmeh le yecmeannekum ila yevmil kÄḟyameti la raybe fÄḟh ellezÄḟne hasiru enfusehum fe hum la yuÂṀminun"
  6,13,"Ve lehu ma sekene fil leyli ven nehar ve huves semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  6,14,"Kul e gayrallahi ettehÄḟu veliyyen fatÄḟris semavati vel erdÄḟ ve huve yutÂṀÄḟmu ve la yutÂṀam kul innÄḟ umirtu en ekune evvele men esleme ve la tekunenne minel musrikÄḟn"
  6,15,"Kul innÄḟ ehafu in asaytu rabbÄḟ azabe yevmin azÄḟym"
  6,16,"Mey yusraf anhu yevmeizin fe kad rahÄḟmeh ve zalikel fevzul mubÄḟn"
  6,17,"Ve iy yemseskellahu bi durrin fe la kasife lehu illa hu ve iy yemseske bi hayrin fe huve ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  6,18,"Ve huvel kahiru fevka Äḟbadih ve huvel hakÄḟmul habÄḟr"
  6,19,"Kul eyyu seyÂṀin ekberu sehadeh kulillahu sehÄḟdum beynÄḟ ve beynekum ve uhÄḟye ileyye hazel kurÂṀanu li unzirakum bihÄḟ ve mem belag e innekum le teshedune enne meallahi aliheten uhra kul la eshed kul innema huve ilahuv vahÄḟduv ve innenÄḟ berÄḟum mimma tusrikun"
  6,20,"EllezÄḟne ateynahumul kitabe yaÂṀrifunehu kema yaÂṀrifune ebnaehum ellezÄḟne hasiru enfusehum fe hum la yuÂṀminun"
  6,21,"Ve men azlemu kmimmeniftera alellahi keziben ev kezzebe bi ayatih innehu la yuflihuz zalimun"
  6,22,"Ve yevme nahsuruhum cemÄḟan summe nekulu lillezÄḟne esraku eyne surakaukumullezÄḟne kuntum tezÂṀumun"
  6,23,"Summe lem tekun fitnetuhum illa en kalu vallahi rabbina ma kunna musrikÄḟn"
  6,24,"Unzur keyfe kezebu ala enfusihim ve dalle anhum ma kanu yefterun"
  6,25,"Ve minhum mey yestemiu ileyk ve cealna ala kulubihim ekinneten ey yefkahuhu ve fÄḟ azanihim vakra ve iy yerav kulle ayetil la yuÂṀminu biha hatta iza cauke yucadiluneke yekulullezÄḟne keferu in haza illa esatÄḟyrul evvelÄḟn"
  6,26,"Ve hum yenhevne anhu ve yenÂṀevne anh ve iy yuhlikune illa enfusehum ve ma yesÂṀurun"
  6,27,"Ve lev tera iz vukÄḟfu alen nari fe kalu ya leytena nuraddu ve la nukezzibe bi ayati rabbina ve nekune minel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  6,28,"Bel bedalehum ma kanu yuhfune min kabl ve lev ruddu le adu lima nuhu anhu ve innehum le kazibun"
  6,29,"Ve kalu in hiye illa hayatuned dunya ve ma nahnu bi mebÂṀusÄḟn"
  6,30,"Ve lev tera iz vukÄḟfu ala rabbihim kale e leyse haza bil hakk kalu bela ve rabbina kale fe zukul azabe bima kuntum tekfurun"
  6,31,"Kad hasirallezÄḟne kezzebu bi likaillah hatta iza caethumus saatu bagteten kalu ya hasratena ala ma ferratna fÄḟha ve hum yahmilune evzarahum ala zuhurihim e la sae ma yezirun"
  6,32,"Ve mel hayatud dunya illa leÄḟbuv ve lehv ve leddarul ahÄḟratu hayrul lillezÄḟne yettekun e fe la taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  6,33,"Kad naÂṀlemu innehu le yahzunukellezÄḟ yekulune fe innehum la yukezzibuneke ve lakinnez zalimÄḟne bi ayatillahi yechadun"
  6,34,"Ve le kad kuzzibet rusulum min kablike fe saberu ala ma kuzzibu ve uzu hatta etahum nasruna ve la mubeddile li kelimatillah ve le kad caeke min nebeil murselÄḟn"
  6,35,"Ve in kane kebura aleyke ÄḟÂṀraduhum fe inistetaÂṀte en tebtegÄḟye nefekan fil erdÄḟ ev sullemen fis semai fe teÂṀtiyehum bi ayeh ve lev saellahu le cemeahum alel huda fe la tekunenne minel cahilÄḟn"
  6,36,"Innema yestecÄḟbullezÄḟne yesmeun vel mevta yebÂṀasuhumullahu summe ileyhi yurceun"
  6,37,"Ve kalu lev la nuzzile aleyhi ayetum mir rabbih kul innellahe kadirun ala ey yunezzile ayetev ve lakinne ekserahum la yaÂṀlemun"
  6,38,"Ve ma min dabbetin fil erdÄḟ ve la tairiy yetÄḟyru bi cenahayhi illa umemun emsalukum ma ferratna fil kitabi min seyÂṀin summe ila rabbihim yuhserun"
  6,39,"VellezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina summuv ve bukmun fiz zulumat mey yeseillahu yudlilh ve mey yeseÂṀyecÂṀalhu ala sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  6,40,"Kul eraeytekum in etakum azabullahi ev etetkumus saatu e gayrallahi tedÂṀun in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  6,41,"Bel iyyahu tedÂṀune fe yeksifu ma tedÂṀune ileyhi in sae ve tenzevne ma tusrikun"
  6,42,"Ve le kad erselna ila umemim min kablike fe ehaznahum bil beÂṀsai ved darrai leallehum yetedarraun"
  6,43,"Fe lev la iz caehum beÂṀsuna tedarrau ve lakin kaset kulubuhum ve zeyyene lehumus seytanu ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  6,44,"Felemma nesu ma zukkiru bihÄḟ fetahna aleyhim ebvabe kulli seyÂṀ hatta iza ferihu bima utu ehaznahum bagteten fe iza hum mublisun"
  6,45,"Fe kutÄḟa dabirul kavmillezÄḟne zalemu vel hamdu lillahi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  6,46,"Kul eraeytum in ehazellahu semÂṀakum ve ebsarakum ve hateme ala kulubikum men ilahun gayrullahi yeÂṀtÄḟkum bih unzur keyfe nusarriful ayati summe hum yasdifun"
  6,47,"Kul eraeytekum in etakum azabullahi bagteten ev cehraten hel yuhleku illel kavmuz zalimun"
  6,48,"Ve ma nursilul murselÄḟne illa mubessirÄḟne ve munzirÄḟn fe men amene ve asleha fe la havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  6,49,"VellezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina yemessuhumul azabu bi ma kanu yefukun"
  6,50,"Kul la ekulu lekum ÄḟndÄḟ hazainullahi ve la aÂṀlemul gaybe ve la ekulu lekum innÄḟ melek in ettebiu illa ma yuha ileyy kul hel yestevil aÂṀma vel besÄḟyr e fe la tetefekkerun"
  6,51,"Ve enzir bihillezÄḟne yehafune ey yuhseru ila rabbihim leyse lehum min dunihÄḟ veliyyuv ve la sefÄḟul leallehum yettekun"
  6,52,"Ve la tatrudillezÄḟne yedÂṀune rabbehum bil gadati vel asiyyi yurÄḟdune vecheh ma aleyke min hÄḟsabihim min seyÂṀiv ve ma min hÄḟsabike aleyhim min seyÂṀin fe tatrudehum fe tekune minez zalimÄḟn"
  6,53,"Ve kezalike fetenna baÂṀdahum bi baÂṀdÄḟl li yekulu e haulai mennellahu aleyhim mim beynina e leysellahu bi aÂṀleme bis sakirÄḟn"
  6,54,"Ve iza caekellezÄḟne yuÂṀminune bi ayatina fe kul selamun aleykum ketebe rabbukum ala nefsihir rahmete ennehu men amile minkum suem bi cehaletin summe tabe mim baÂṀdihÄḟ ve asleha fe ennehu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  6,55,"Ve kezalike nufessÄḟlul ayati ve li testebÄḟne sebÄḟlul mucrimÄḟn"
  6,56,"Kul innÄḟ nuhÄḟtu en aÂṀbudellezÄḟne tedÂṀune min dunillah kul la ettebiu ehvaekum kad daleltu izev ve ma ene minel muhtedÄḟn"
  6,57,"Kul innÄḟ ala beyyinetim mir rabbÄḟ ve kezzebtum bih ma ÄḟndÄḟ ma testaÂṀcilune bih inil hukmu illa lillah yekussul hakka ve huve hayrul fasÄḟlÄḟn"
  6,58,"Kul lev enne ÄḟndÄḟ ma testaÂṀcilune bihÄḟ le kudiyel emru beynÄḟ ve beynekum vallahu aÂṀlemu biz zalimÄḟn"
  6,59,"Ve Äḟndehu mefatihul gaybi la yaÂṀlemuha illa hu ve yaÂṀlemu ma fil berri vel bahr ve ma teskutu miv verakatin illa yaÂṀlemuha ve la habbetin fÄḟ zulumatil erdÄḟ ve la ratbiv ve la yavisin illa fÄḟ kitabim mubÄḟn"
  6,60,"Ve huvellezÄḟ yeteveffakum bil leyli ve yaÂṀlemu ma cerahtum bin nehari summe yebÂṀasukum fÄḟhi li yukda ecelum musemma summe ileyhi merciukum summe yunebbiukum bi ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  6,61,"Ve huvel kahiru fevka ÄḟbadihÄḟ ve yursilu aleykum hafezah hatta iza cae ehadekumul mevtu teveffethu rusuluna ve hum la yuferritun"
  6,62,"Summe ruddu ilellahi mevlahumul hakk e la lehul hukmu ve huve esraul hasibÄḟn"
  6,63,"Kul mey yuneccÄḟkum min zulumatil berri vel bahri tedÂṀunehu tedarruav ve hufyeh le in encana min hazihÄḟ le nekunenne mines sakirÄḟn"
  6,64,"Kulillahu yuneccÄḟkum minha ve min kulli kerbin summe entum tusrikun"
  6,65,"Kul huvel kadiru ala ey yebÂṀase aleykum azabem min fevkÄḟkum ev min tahti erculikum ev yelbisekum siyeav ve yuzÄḟka baÂṀdakum beÂṀse baÂṀd unzur keyfe nusarriful ayati leallehum yefkahun"
  6,66,"Ve kezzebe bihÄḟ kavmuke ve huvel hakk kul lestu aleykum bi vekÄḟl"
  6,67,"Li kulli nebeim mustekarruv ve sevfe taÂṀlemun"
  6,68,"Ve iza raeytellezÄḟne yehudune fÄḟ ayatina fe aÂṀrÄḟd anhum hatta yehudu fÄḟ hadÄḟsin gayrih ve imma yunsiyennekes seytanu fe la takÂṀud baÂṀdez zikra meal kavmiz zalimÄḟn"
  6,69,"Ve ma alellezÄḟne yettekune min hÄḟsabihim min seyÂṀiv ve lakin zikra leallehum yettekun"
  6,70,"Ve zerillezÄḟnettehazu dÄḟnehum leÄḟbev ve lehvev ve garrathumul hayatud dunya ve zekkir bihÄḟ en tubsele nefsum bima kesebet leyse leha min dunillahi veliyyuv ve la sefiyÂṀ ve in taÂṀdil kulle adlil la yuÂṀhaz minha ulaikellezÄḟne ubsilu bima kesebu lehum serabum min hamÄḟmiv ve azabun elÄḟmum bima kanu yekfurun"
  6,71,"Kul e nedÂṀu min dunillahi ma la yenfeuna ve la yedurruna ve nuraddu ala aÂṀkabina baÂṀde iz hedanellahu kellezistehvethus seyatÄḟynu fil erdÄḟ hayrane lehu ashabuy yedÂṀunehu ilel hudeÂṀtina kul inne hudellahi huvel huda ve umirna li nuslime li rabbil alemÄḟn"
  6,72,"Ve en ekÄḟymus salate vettekuh ve huvellezÄḟ ileyhi tuhserun"
  6,73,"Ve huvellezÄḟ halekas semavati vel erda bil hakk ve yevme yekulu kun fe yekun kavluhul hakk ve lehul mulku yevme yunfehu fis sur alimul gaybi ves sehadeh ve huvel hakÄḟmul habÄḟr"
  6,74,"Ve iz kale ibrahÄḟmu li ebÄḟhi azera etettehÄḟzu asnamen aliheh innÄḟ erake ve kavmeke fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  6,75,"Ve kezalike nurÄḟ ibrahÄḟme melekutes semavati vel erdÄḟ ve li yekune minel mukÄḟnÄḟn"
  6,76,"Felemma cenne aleyhil leylu raa kevkeba kale haza rabbÄḟ felemma efele kale la uhÄḟbbul afilÄḟn"
  6,77,"Felemma rael kamera bazigan kale haza rabbÄḟ felemma efele kale leil lem yehdinÄḟ rabbÄḟ le ekunenne minel kavmid dallÄḟn"
  6,78,"Felemma raes semse bazigaten kale haza rabbÄḟ haza ekber felemma efelet kale ya kavmi innÄḟ berÄḟum mimma tusrikun"
  6,79,"InnÄḟ veccehtu vechiye lillezÄḟ fetaras semavati vel erda hanÄḟfev ve ma ene minel musrimÄḟn"
  6,80,"Ve haccehu kavmuh kale e tuhaccunnÄḟ fillahi ve kad hedan ve la ehafu ma tusrikune bihÄḟ illa ey yesae rabbÄḟ seyÂṀa vesia rabbÄḟ kulle seyÂṀin Äḟlma e fe la tetezekkerun"
  6,81,"Ve keyfe ehafu ma esraktum ve la tehafune ennekum esraktum billahi ma lem yunezzil bihÄḟ aleykum sultana fe eyyul ferÄḟkayni ehakku bil emn in kuntum taÂṀlemun"
  6,82,"EllezÄḟne amenu ve lem yelbisu Äḟmanehum bi zulmin ulaike lehumul emnu ve hum muhtedun"
  6,83,"Ve tilke huccetuna ateynaha ibrahÄḟme ala kavmih nefeu deracatim men nesaÂṀ inne rabbeke hakÄḟmun alÄḟm"
  6,84,"Ve vehebna lehu ishaka ve yaÂṀkub kullen hedeyna ve nuhan hedeyna min kablu ve min zurriyyetihÄḟ davude ve suleymane ve eyyube ve yusufe ve musa ve harun ve kezalike neczil muhsinÄḟn"
  6,85,"Ve zekeriyya ve yahya ve Äḟysa ve ilyas kullum mines salihÄḟyn"
  6,86,"Ve ismaÄḟyle vel yesea ve yunuse ve luta ve kullen faddalna alel alemÄḟn"
  6,87,"Ve min abaihim ve zurriyyatihim ve Äḟhvanihim vectebeyna hum ve hedeynahum ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  6,88,"Zalike hudellahi yehdÄḟ bihÄḟ mey yesau min Äḟbadih ve lev esraku le habita anhum ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  6,89,"UlaikellezÄḟne ateynahumul kitabe vel hukme ven nubuvveh fe iy yekfur biha haulai fe kad vekkelna biha kavmel leysu biha bi kafirun"
  6,90,"UlaikellezÄḟne hedellahu fe bi hudahumuktedih kul la esÂṀelukum aleyhi ecra in huve illa zikra lil alemÄḟn"
  6,91,"Ve ma kaderullahe hakka kadrihÄḟ iz kalu ma enzelellahu ala beserim min seyÂṀ kul men enzelel kitabellezÄḟ cae bihÄḟ musa nurav ve hudel lin nasi tecÂṀalunehu karatÄḟyse tubduneha ve tuhfune kesÄḟra ve ullimtum ma lem taÂṀlemu entum ve la abaukum kulillahu summe zerhum fÄḟ havdÄḟhum yelÂṀabun"
  6,92,"Ve haza kitabun enzelnahu mubarakum musaddikullezÄḟ beyne yedeyhi ve li tunzira ummel kura ve men havleha vellezÄḟne yuÂṀminune bil ahÄḟrati yuÂṀminune bihÄḟ ve hum ala salatihim yuhafizun"
  6,93,"Ve men azlemu mimmeniftera alellahi keziben ev kale uhÄḟye ileyye ve lem yuha ileyhi seyÂṀuv ve men kale seanzilu misle ma enzelellah ve le v tera iziz zalimune fÄḟ gameratil mevti vel melaiketu basitu eydÄḟhim ahricu enfusekum elyevme tuczevne azabel huni bi ma kuntum tekulune alellahi gayral hakkÄḟ ve kuntum an ayatihÄḟ testekbirun"
  6,94,"Ve le kad ciÂṀtumuna furada kema halaknakum evvele merrativ ve teraktum ma havvelnakum verae zuhurikum ve ma nera meakum sufeaekumullezÄḟne zeamtum ennehum fÄḟkum surakaÂṀ le kad tekattaa beynekum ve dalle ankum ma kuntum tezÂṀumun"
  6,95,"Innellahe falikul habbi ven neva yuhricul hayye minel meyyiti ve muhricul meyyiti minel hayy zalikumullahu fe enna tuÂṀfekun"
  6,96,"Falikul Äḟsbah ve cealel leyle sekenev ves semse vel kamera husbana zalike takdÄḟrul azÄḟzil alÄḟm"
  6,97,"Ve huvellezÄḟ ceale lekumun nucume li tehtedu biha fÄḟ zulumatil berri vel bahr kad fassalnel ayati li kavmiy yaÂṀlemun"
  6,98,"Ve huvellezÄḟ enseekum min nefsiv vahÄḟdetin fe mustekarruv ve mustevdaÂṀ kad fassalnel ayati li kavmiy yefkahun"
  6,99,"Ve huvellezÄḟ enzele mines semai maa fe ahracna bihÄḟ nebate kulli seyÂṀin fe ahracna minhu hadÄḟran nuhricu minhu habbem muterakiba veminen nahli min talÂṀiha kÄḟnvanun daniyetuv ve cennatim min aÂṀnabiv vez zeytune ver rummane mustebihev ve gayra mutesabih unzuru ila semerihÄḟ iza esmera ve yenÂṀÄḟh inne fÄḟ zalikum le ayatil li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  6,100,"Ve cealu lillahi surakael cinne ve halekahum ve haraku lehu benÄḟne ve benatim bi gayri Äḟlm subhanehu ve teala amma yesÄḟfun"
  6,101,"BedrÄḟus semavati vel ard enna yekunu lehu veleduv ve lem tekul lehu sahÄḟbeh ve haleka kulle seyÂṀ ve huve bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  6,102,"Zalikumullahu rabbukum la ilahe illa hu haliku kulli seyÂṀin faÂṀbuduh ve huve ala kulli seyÂṀiv vekÄḟl"
  6,103,"La tudrikuhul ebsaru ve huve yudrikul ebsar ve huvel latÄḟyful habÄḟr"
  6,104,"Kad caekum besairu mir rabbikum fe men ebsara fe li nefsih ve men amiye fe aleyha ve ma ene aleykum bi hafÄḟyz"
  6,105,"Ve kezalike nusarriful ayati ve li yekulu deraste ve li nubeyyinehu li kavmiy yaÂṀlemun"
  6,106,"IttebÄḟÂṀ ma uhÄḟye ileyke mir rabbik la ilahe illa hu ve aÂṀrÄḟd anil musrikÄḟn"
  6,107,"Ve lev saellahu ma esraku ve ma cealnake aleyhim hafÄḟyza ve ma ente aleyhim bi vekÄḟl"
  6,108,"Ve la tesubbullezÄḟne yedÂṀune min dunillahi fe yesubbullahe advem bi gayri Äḟlm kezalike zeyyenna likulli ummetin amele0hum summe ila rabbihim merciuhum fe yunebbiuhum bi ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  6,109,"Ve askemu billahi cehde eymanihim le in caethum ayetul le yuÂṀminunne biha kul innemel ayatu Äḟndellahi ve ma yusÂṀÄḟrukum enneha iza caet la yuÂṀminun"
  6,110,"Ve nukallibu efÂṀidetehum ve ebsarahum kema lem yuÂṀminu bihÄḟ evvele merrativ ve nezeruhum fÄḟ tugyanihim yaÂṀmehun"
  6,111,"Ve lev ennena nezzelna ileyhimul melaikete ve kelemmehumul mevta ve haserna aleyhim kulle seyÂṀin kubulem ma kanu li yuÂṀminu illa ey yesaellahu ve lakinne ekserahum yechelun"
  6,112,"Ve kezalike cealna li kulli nebiyyin aduvven seyatÄḟynel insi vel cinni yuhÄḟy baÂṀduhum illa baÂṀdÄḟn zuhrufel kavli gurura ve lev sae rabbuke ma fealuhu fezerhum ve ma yefterun"
  6,113,"Ve li tesga ileyhi efÂṀidetullezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune bil ahÄḟrati ve li yerdavhu ve li yakterifu ma hum mukterifun"
  6,114,"E fe gayrallahi ebtegÄḟy hakamev ve huvellezÄḟ enzele ileykumul kitabe mufassala vellezÄḟne ateynahumul kitabe yaÂṀlemune ennehu munezzelum mir rabbike bil hakkÄḟ fe la tekunenne minel mumterÄḟn"
  6,115,"Ve temmet kelimetu rabbike sÄḟdkav ve adla la mubeddile li kelimatih ve huves semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  6,116,"Ve in tutÄḟÂṀeksera men fil erdÄḟ yudÄḟlluke an sebÄḟlillah iy yettebiune illez zanne ve in hum illa yahrusun"
  6,117,"Inne rabbeke huve aÂṀlemu mey yedÄḟllu an sebÄḟlil ve huve aÂṀlemu bil muhtedÄḟn"
  6,118,"Fe kulu mimma zukirasmullahi aleyhi in kuntum bi ayatihÄḟ muÂṀminÄḟn"
  6,119,"Ve malekum ella teÂṀkulu mimma zukirasmullahi aleyhi ve akd fassale lekum ma harrame aleykum illa madturirtum ileyh ve inne kesÄḟral le yudÄḟllune bi ehvaihim bi gayri Äḟlm inne rabbeke huve aÂṀlemu bil muÂṀtedÄḟn"
  6,120,"Ve zeru zahiral ismi ve batÄḟneh innellezÄḟne yeksibunel isme seyuczevne bima kanu yakterifun"
  6,121,"Ve la teÂṀkulu mimma lem yuzkerismullahi aleyhi ve innehu lefÄḟsk ve innes seyatÄḟyne le yuhune ila evliyaihim li yucadilukum ve in etaÂṀtumuhum innekum le musrikun"
  6,122,"E ve men kane meyten fe ahyeynahu ve cealna lehu nuray yemsÄḟ bihÄḟ fin nasi ke mem meseluhu fiz zulumati leyse bi haricim minha kezalike zuyyine lil kafirÄḟne ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  6,123,"Ve kezalike cealna fÄḟ kulli karyetin ekabira mucrimÄḟha li yemkuru fÄḟha ve ma yemkurune illa bi enfusihim ve ma yesÂṀurun"
  6,124,"Ve iza caethum ayetun kalu len nuÂṀmine hatta nuÂṀta misle ma utiye rusulullah Allahu aÂṀlemu haysu yecÂṀalu risaleteh seyusÄḟybullezÄḟne ecramu sagarun Äḟndellahi ve azabun sedÄḟdum bima kanu yemkurun"
  6,125,"Fe mey yuridillahu ey yehdiyehu yesrah sadrahu lil islam ve mey yurid ey yudÄḟlehu yecÂṀal sadrahu dayyikan haracen ke ennema yessaÂṀadu fis semaÂṀ kezalike yecÂṀalullahur ricse alellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminun"
  6,126,"Ve haza sÄḟratu rabbike mustekÄḟyma kad fessalnel ayati li kavmiy yezzekkerun"
  6,127,"Lehum darus selami Äḟnde rabbihim ve huve veliyyuhum bima kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  6,128,"Ve yevme yahsuruhum cemÄḟa ya maÂṀseral cinni kadisteksertum minel ins ve kale evliyauhum minel insi rabbenestemtea baÂṀduna bi baÂṀdÄḟv ve belagna ecelenellezÄḟ eccelte lena kalen naru mesvakum halidÄḟne fÄḟha illa ma saellah inne rabbeke hakÄḟmun alÄḟm"
  6,129,"Ve kezalike nuvellÄḟ baÂṀdaz zalimÄḟne baÂṀdam bima kanu yeksibun"
  6,130,"Ya maÂṀseral cinni vel insi e lem yeÂṀtikum rusulum minkum yekussune aleykum ayatÄḟ ve yunzirunekum likae yevmikum haza kalu sehidna ala enfusina ve garrathumul hayatud dunya ve sehÄḟdu ala enfusihim ennehum kanu kafirÄḟn"
  6,131,"Zalike el lem yekur rabbuke muhlikel kura bi zulmiv ve ehluha gafilun"
  6,132,"Ve li kullin deracatum mimma amilu ve ma rabbuke bi gafilin amma yaÂṀmelun"
  6,133,"Ve rabbukel ganiyyu zur rahmeh iy yesaÂṀ yuzhibkum ve yestahlif mim baÂṀdikum ma yesau kema enseekum min zurriyyeti kavmin aharÄḟn"
  6,134,"Innema tuadune leativ ve ma entum bi muÂṀcizÄḟn"
  6,135,"Kul ve kavmÄḟÂṀmelu ala mekanetikum innÄḟ amil fe sevfe taÂṀlemune men tekunu lehu akÄḟbetud dar innehu la yuflihuz zalimun"
  6,136,"Ve cealu lillahi mimma zerae minel harsi vel enÂṀami nesÄḟyben fe kalu haza lillahi bi zaÂṀmihim ve haza li surakaina fe ma kane li surakaihim fe la yesÄḟlu ilellah ve ma kane lillahi fe huve yesÄḟlu ila surakaihim sae ma yahkumun"
  6,137,"Ve kezalike zeyyene li kesÄḟrim minel musrikÄḟne katle evladihim surakauhum li yurduhum ve li yelbisu aleyhim dÄḟnehum ve lev saellahu ma fealuhu fezerhum ve ma yefterun"
  6,138,"Ve kalu hazihÄḟ enÂṀamuv ve harsun hÄḟcr la yatÂṀamuha illa men nesau bi zaÂṀmihim ve enÂṀamun hurrimet zuhuruha ve enÂṀamul la yezkurunesmellahi aleyheftiraen aleyh seyeczÄḟhim bima kanu yefterun"
  6,139,"Ve kalu ma fÄḟ butuni hazihil enÂṀami halisatul li zukurina ve muharramun ala ezvacina ve iy yekum meyteten fe hum fÄḟhi surakaÂṀ seyeczÄḟhim vasfehum innehu hakÄḟmun alÄḟm"
  6,140,"Kad hasirallezÄḟne katelu evladehum sefehem bi gayri Äḟlmiv ve harramu ma razekahumullahuftiraen alellah kad dallu ve ma kanu muhtedÄḟn"
  6,141,"Ve huvellezÄḟ ensee cennatim maÂṀrusativ ve gayra maÂṀrusativ ven nahle vez zerÂṀa muhtelifen ukuluhu vez zeytune ver rummane mutesabihev ve gayra mutesabih kulu min semerihÄḟ iza esmera ve atu hakkahu yevme hasadihÄḟ ve la tusrifu innehu la yuhÄḟbbul musrifÄḟn"
  6,142,"Ve minel enÂṀami hamuletev ve fersa kulu mimma razekakumullahu ve la tettebiu hutuvatis seytan innehu lekum aduvvum mubÄḟn"
  6,143,"Semaniyete ezvac mined daÂṀnisneyni ve minel maÂṀzisneyn kul azzekerayni harrame emil unseyeyn nebiunÄḟ bi Äḟlmin in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  6,144,"Ve minel ibilisneyni ve minel bekarisneyn kul azzekerayni harrame emil unseyeyni emmestemelet aleyhi erhamul unseyeyn em kuntum suhedae iz vessakumullahu bi haza fe men azlemu mimmeniftera alellahi kezibel li yudÄḟllen nase bi gayri Äḟlm innellahe la yehdil kavmez zalimÄḟn"
  6,145,"Kul la ecidu fÄḟ ma uhÄḟye ileyye muharramen ala taÄḟmiy yatÂṀamuhu illa ey yekune meyteten ev demem mesfuhan ev lahme hÄḟnzÄḟrin fe innehu ricsun ev fiskan uhille li gayrillahi bih fe menidturra gayra bagÄḟv ve la adin fe inne rabbeke gafurur rahÄḟym"
  6,146,"Ve alellezÄḟne hadu harramna kulle zÄḟ zufur ve minel bekari vel ganemi harramna aleyhim suhumehuma illa ma hamelet zuhuruhuma evil havaya ev mahteleta bi azm zalike cezeynahum bi bagyihim ve inna lesadikun"
  6,147,"Fe in kezzebuke fe kur rabbukum zu rahmetiv vasiah ve la yuraddu beÂṀsuhu anil kavmil mucrimÄḟn"
  6,148,"SeyekulullezÄḟne esraku lev saellahu ma esrakna ve la abauna ve la harramna min seyÂṀ kezalike kezzebellezÄḟne min kablihim hatta zaku beÂṀsena kul hel Äḟndekum min Äḟlmin fe tuhricuhu lena in tettebiune illez zanne ve in entum illa tahrusun"
  6,149,"Kul fe lillahil huccetul baligah fe lev sae le hedakum ecmeÄḟyn"
  6,150,"Kul helumme suhedaekumullezÄḟne yeshedune ennellahe harrame haza fe in sehidu fe la teshed meahum ve la tettebÄḟÂṀ ehvaellezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina vellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune bil ahÄḟrati ve hum bi rabbihim yaÂṀdilun"
  6,151,"Kul tealev etlu ma harrame rabbukum aleykum ella tusriku bihÄḟ seyÂṀa ve bil valideyni Äḟhsana ve la taktulu evladekum min imlak nahnu nerzukukum ve iyyahum ve la takrabul fevahÄḟse ma zahera minha ve ma betan ve la taktulun nefselletÄḟ harramellahu illa bil hakk zalikum vessakum bihÄḟ leallekum taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  6,152,"Ve la takrabu malel yetÄḟmi illa billetÄḟ hiya ahsenu hatta yebluga esuddeh ve evful keyle vel mizane bil kÄḟst la nukellifu nefsen illa vusÂṀaha ve iza kultum faÂṀdilu ve lev kane za kurba ve bi ahdillahi evfu zalikum vassakum bihÄḟ leallekum tezekkerun"
  6,153,"Ve enne haza zÄḟratÄḟy mustekÄḟymen fettebiuh ve la tettebius subule fe teferraka bikum an sebÄḟlih zalikum vassakum bihÄḟ leallekum tettekun"
  6,154,"Summe ateyna musel kitabe temamen alellezÄḟ ahsene ve tefsÄḟylel likulli seyÂṀiv ve hudev ve rahmetel leallehum bi likai rabbihim yuÂṀminun"
  6,155,"Ve haza kitabun enzelnahu mubarakun fettebiuhu vetteku leallekum turhamun"
  6,156,"En tekulu innema unzilel kitabu ala taifeteyni min kablina ve in kunna an dirasetihim legafilÄḟn"
  6,157,"Ev tekulu lev enna unzile aleynel kitabu le kunna ehda minhum fe kad caekum beyyinetum mir rabikum ve hudev ve rahmeh fe min azlemu mimmen kezzebe bi ayatillahi ve sadefe anha seneczillezÄḟne yasdifune an ayatina suel azabi bi ma kanu yasdifun"
  6,158,"Hel yenzurune illa en teÂṀtiyehumul melaiketu ev yeÂṀtiye rabbuke ev yeÂṀtiye baÂṀdu ayati rabbik yevme yeÂṀtÄḟ baÂṀdu ayati rabbike la yenfeu nefsen Äḟmanuha lem tekun amenet min kablu ev kesebet fÄḟ Äḟmaniha hayra kulintezÄḟru inna muntezÄḟrun"
  6,159,"InnellezÄḟne ferreku dÄḟnehum ve kanu siyeal leste minhum fÄḟ seyÂṀ innema emruhum ilellahi summe yunebbiuhum bima kanu yefÂṀalun"
  6,160,"Men cae bil haseneti fe lehu asru emsaliha ve men cae bis seyyieti fe la yucza illa misleha ve hum la yuzlemun"
  6,161,"Kul innenÄḟ hedanÄḟ rabbÄḟ ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym dÄḟnen kÄḟyemem millete ibrahÄḟme hanÄḟfa ve ma kane minel musrikÄḟn"
  6,162,"Kul inne salati ve nusukÄḟ ve mahyaye ve mematÄḟ lillahi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  6,163,"La serÄḟke leh ve bi zalike umirtu ve ene evvelul muslimÄḟn"
  6,164,"Kul e gayrallahi ebgÄḟy rabbev ve huve rabbu kulli seyÂṀ ve la teksibu kullu nefsin illa aleyha ve la teziru vaziratuv vizra uhra summe ila rabbikum merciukum fe yunebbiukum bima kuntum fÄḟhi tahtelifun"
  6,165,"Ve huvellezÄḟ cealekum halaifel erdÄḟ ve rafea baÂṀdakum fevka baÂṀdÄḟn deracatil li yebluvekum fÄḟ ma atakum inne rabbeke serÄḟul Äḟkabi ve innehu le gafurur rahÄḟym"
  7,8,"Vel veznu yevmeizinil hakk fe men sekulet mevazÄḟnuhu fe ulaike humul muflihun"
  7,9,"Ve men haffet mevazÄḟnuhu fe ulaikellezÄḟne hasiru enfusehum bima kanu bi ayatina yazlimun"
  7,10,"Ve le kad mekkennakum fil erdÄḟ ve cealna lekum fÄḟha meayis kalÄḟlem ma teskurÄḟn"
  7,11,"Ve le kad halaknakum summe savvernakum summe kulna lil melaiketiscudu li ademe fe secedu illa iblÄḟs lem yekum mines sacidÄḟn"
  7,12,"Kale ma meneake ella tescude iz emartuk kale ene hayrum minhhalaktenÄḟ min nariv ve halaktehu min tÄḟyn"
  7,13,"Kale fehbÄḟt minha fe ma yekunu leke en tetekebbera fÄḟha fahruc inneke mines sagÄḟrÄḟn"
  7,14,"Kale enzÄḟrnÄḟ ila yevmi yubÂṀasun"
  7,15,"Kale inneke minel munzarÄḟn"
  7,16,"Kale fe bima agveytenÄḟ le akÂṀudenne lehum sÄḟratakel mustekÄḟym"
  7,17,"Summe le atiyennehum mim beyni eydÄḟhim ve min halfihim ve an eymanihim ve an semailihim ve la tecidu ekserahum sakirÄḟn"
  7,18,"Kalehruc minha mezÂṀumem medhura le men tebiake minhum le emleenne cehenneme minkum ecmeÄḟyn"
  7,19,"Ve ya ademuskun ente ve zevcukel cennete fe kula min haysu siÂṀtuma ve la takraba hazihis secerate fe tekuna minez zalimÄḟn"
  7,20,"Fe vesvese lehumes seytanu li yubdiye lehuma mavuriye anhuma min sevÂṀatihima ve kale ma nehakuma rabbukuma an hazihis secerati illa en tekuna melekeyni ev tekuna minel halidÄḟn"
  7,21,"Ve kasemehuma innÄḟ lekuma le minen nasÄḟhÄḟyn"
  7,22,"Fe dellahuma bi gurur fe lemma zakas secerate bedet lehuma sevÂṀatuhuma ve tafika yahsifani aleyhima miv verakÄḟl cenneh ve nadahuma rabbuhuma e lem enhekuma an tilkuems secerati ve ekul lekuma innes seytane lekuma aduvvum mubÄḟn"
  7,23,"Kala rabbena zalemna enfusena ve il lem tagfir lena ve terhamna lenekunenne minel hasirÄḟn"
  7,24,"Kalehbitu baÂṀdukum li baÂṀdÄḟn aduvv ve lekum fil erdÄḟ mustekarruv ve metaun ila hÄḟyn"
  7,25,"Kale fÄḟha tahyevne ve fÄḟha temutune ve menha tuhracun"
  7,26,"Ya benÄḟ ademe kad enzelna aleykum libasey yuvarÄḟ sevÂṀatikum ve rÄḟsev ve libasut takva zalike hayr zalike min ayatillahi leallehum yezzekkerun"
  7,27,"Ya benÄḟ ademe la yeftinennekumus seytanu kema ahrace ebeveykum minel cenneti yenziu anhuma libasehuma li yuriyehuma sevÂṀatihima innehu yerakum huve ve kabÄḟluhu min haysu la teravnehum inna cealnes seyatÄḟyne evliyae lillezÄḟne la yuÂṀminun"
  7,28,"Ve iza fealu fahÄḟseten kalu vecedna aleyha abaena ballahu emerana biha kul innellahe la yeÂṀmuru bil fahsaÂṀ e tekulune alellahi ma la taÂṀlemun"
  7,29,"Kul emera rabbÄḟ bil kÄḟstÄḟ ve ekÄḟymu vucuhekum Äḟnde kulli mescidiv bedeekum teudun"
  7,30,"FerÄḟkan heda ve ferÄḟkan hakka aleyhimud dalaleh innehumut tehazus seyatÄḟyne evliyae min dunillahi ve yahsebune ennehum muhtedun"
  7,31,"Ya benÄḟ ademe huzu zÄḟnetekum Äḟnde kulli mescidiv ve kulu vesrabu ve la tusrifu innehu la yuhÄḟbbul musrifÄḟn"
  7,32,"Kul men harrame zÄḟnetellahilletÄḟ ahrace li ÄḟbadihÄḟ vet tayyibati miner rÄḟzk kul hiye lillezÄḟne amenu fil hayatid dunya halisatey yevmel kÄḟyameh kezalike nufassÄḟlul ayati li kavmiy yaÂṀlemun"
  7,33,"Kul innema harrame rabbiyel fevahÄḟse ma zahera minha ve ma betane vel isme vel bagye bi gayril hakkÄḟ ve en tusriku billahi ma lem yunezzil bihÄḟ sultanev ve en tekulu alellahi ma la taÂṀlemun"
  7,34,"Ve li kulli ummetin ecel fe iza cae ecluhum la yesteÂṀhÄḟrune saatev ve la yestakdimun"
  7,35,"Ya benÄḟ ademe imma yeÂṀtiyennekum rusulum minkum yekussune aleykum ayatÄḟ fe menitteka ve asleha fe la havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  7,36,"VellezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina vestekberu anha ulaike ashabun nar hum fÄḟha halidun"
  7,37,"Fe men azlemu mimmeniftera alellahi keziben ev kezzebe bi ayatih ulaike yenaluhum nesÄḟybuhum minel kitab hatta iza caethum rusuluna yeteveffevnehum kalu eyne ma kuntum tedÂṀune min dunillah kalu dallu anna ve sehidu ala enfusihim ennehum kanu kafirÄḟn"
  7,38,"Kaledhulu fÄḟ umemin kad halet min kablikum minel cinni vel insi fin nar kullema dehalet ummetul leanet uhteha hatta ized daraku fÄḟha cemÄḟan kalet uhrahum li ulahum rabbena haulai edalluna fe atihim azaben dÄḟÂṀfem minen nar kale li kullin dÄḟÂṀfuv ve lakil la taÂṀlemun"
  7,39,"Ve kalet ulahum li uhrahum fe ma kane lekum aleyna min fadlin fe zukul azabe bima kuntum teksibun"
  7,40,"InnellezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina vestekberu anha la tufettehu lehum ebvabus semai ve la yedhulunel cennete hatta yelicel cemelu fÄḟ semmil hÄḟyad ve kezalike neczil mucrimÄḟn"
  7,41,"Lehum min cehenneme mihaduv ve min fevkÄḟhum gavas ve kezalike necziz zalimÄḟn"
  7,42,"VellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati la nukellifu nefsen illa vusÂṀaha ulaike ashabul cenneh hum fÄḟha halidun"
  7,43,"Ve nezaÂṀna ma fÄḟ sudurihim min gÄḟllin tecrÄḟ min tahtihimul enhar ve kalul hamdu lillahillezÄḟ hedana li haza ve ma kunna li nehtediye lev la en hedanellah le kad caet rusulu rabbina bil hakk ve nudu en tilkumul cennetu uristumuha bima kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  7,44,"Ve nada ashabul cenneti ashaben nari en kad vecedna ma veadena rabbuna hakkan fe hel vecedtum ma veade rabbukum hakka kalu neam fe ezzene muezzinum beynehum el laÂṀnetullahi alez zalimÄḟn"
  7,45,"EllezÄḟne yesuddune an sebÄḟlillahi ve yebguneha Äḟveca ve hum bil ahÄḟrati kafirun"
  7,46,"Ve beynehuma hÄḟcab ve alel aÂṀrafi ricaluy yaÂṀrifune kullem bisÄḟmahum ve nadev ashabel cenneti en selamun aleykum lem yedhuluha ve hum yatmeun"
  7,47,"Ve iza surifet ebsaruhum tilkae ashabin nari kalu rabbena la tecÂṀalna meal kavmiz zalimÄḟn"
  7,48,"Ve nada ashabul aÂṀrafi ricaley yaÂṀrifunehum bisÄḟmahum kalu ma agna ankum cemÂṀukum ve ma kuntum testekbirun"
  7,49,"E haulaillezÄḟne aksemtum la yenaluhumullahu bi rahmeh udhulul cennete la havfun aleykum ve la entum tahzenun"
  7,50,"Ve nada ashabun nari ashabel cenneti en efÄḟdu aleyna minel mai ev mimma razekakumullah kalu innellahe harramehuma alel kafirÄḟn"
  7,51,"EllezÄḟnettehazu dÄḟnehum lehvev ve leÄḟbev ve garrathumul hayatud dunya fel yevme nensahum kema nesu likae yevmihim haza ve ma kanu bi ayatina yechadun"
  7,52,"Ve le kad ciÂṀnahum bi kitabin fassalnahu ala Äḟlmin hudev ve rahmetel li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  7,53,"Hel yenzurune illa teÂṀvÄḟleh yevme yeÂṀtÄḟ teÂṀvÄḟluhu yekulullezÄḟne nesuhu min kablu kad caet rusulu rabbina bil hakk fe hel lena min sufeae fe yesfeu lena ev nuraddu fe naÂṀmele gayrallezÄḟ kunna naÂṀmel kad hasiru enfusehum ve dalle anhum ma kanu yefterun"
  7,54,"Inne rabbekumullahullezÄḟ halekas semavati vel erda fÄḟ sitteti eyyamin summesteva alel arsi yugsil leylen nehara yatlubuhu hasÄḟsev ves semse vel kamera ven nucume musehharatim bi emrih ela lehul halku vel emr tebarakellahu rabbul alemÄḟn"
  7,55,"UdÂṀu rabbekum tedarruav ve hufyeh innehu la yuhÄḟbbul muÂṀtedÄḟn"
  7,56,"Ve la tufsidu fil erdÄḟ baÂṀde ÄḟslahÄḟha vedÂṀuhu havfev ve tamea inne rahmetellahi karÄḟbum minel muhsinÄḟn"
  7,57,"Ve huvellezÄḟ yursilur riyaha busram beyne yedey rahmetih hatta iza ekallet sehaben sikalen suknahu li beledim meyyitin fe enzelna bihil mae fe ahracna bihÄḟ min kullis semerat kezalike nuhricul mevta leallekum tezekkerun"
  7,58,"Vel beledut tayyibu yahrucu nebatuhu bi izni rabbih vellezÄḟ habuse la yahrucu illa nekida kezalike nusarriful ayati li kavmiy yeskurun"
  7,59,"Le kad erselna nuhan ila kavmihÄḟ fe kale ya kavmÄḟÂṀbudullahe ma lekum min ilahin gayruh innÄḟ ehafu aleykum azabe yevmin azÄḟym"
  7,60,"Kalel meleu min kavmihÄḟ inna li nerake fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  7,61,"Kale ya kavmi leyse bÄḟ dalaletuv ve lakinnÄḟ rasulum mir rabbil alamÄḟn"
  7,62,"Ubelligukum risalati rabbÄḟ ve ensahu lekum ve aÂṀlemu minellahi ma la taÂṀlemun"
  7,63,"E ve acibtum en caekum zikrum mir rabbikum ve li tetteku ve leallekum turhamun"
  7,64,"Fe kezzebuhu fe enceynahu vellezÄḟne meahu fil fulki ve agraknellezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina innehum kanu kavmen amÄḟn"
  7,65,"Ve ila adin ehahum huda kale ya kavmÄḟÂṀbudullahe malekum min ilahin gayruh e fe la tettekun"
  7,66,"Kalel meleullezÄḟne keferu min kavmihÄḟ inna le nerake fÄḟ sefahetiv ve inna le nesunnuke minel kazibÄḟn"
  7,67,"Kale ya kavmi leyse bÄḟ sefahetuv ve lakinnÄḟ rasulum mir rabbil alemÄḟn"
  7,68,"Ubelligukum risalati rabbÄḟ ve ene lekum nasÄḟhun emÄḟn"
  7,69,"E ve acibtum en caekum zikrum mir rabbikum ala raculim minkum li yunzirakum vezkuru iz cealekum hulefae mim baÂṀdi kavmi nuhÄḟv ve zadekum fil halkÄḟ bestah fezkuru alaellahi leallekum tuflihun"
  7,70,"Kalu eciÂṀtena li naÂṀbudellahe vahdehu ve nezera ma kane yaÂṀbudu abauna feÂṀtina bima teÄḟduna in kunte mines sadikÄḟyn"
  7,71,"Kale kad vekaa aleykum mir rabbikum ricsuv ve gadab e tucadilunenÄḟ fÄḟ esmain semmeytumuha entum ve abaukum ma nezzelellahu biha min sultan fentezÄḟru innÄḟ meakum minel muntezÄḟrÄḟn"
  7,72,"Fe enceynahu vellezÄḟne meahu bi rametim minna ve kataÂṀna dabirallezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina ve ma kanu muÂṀminÄḟn"
  7,73,"Ve ila semude ehahum saliha kale ya kavmiÂṀbudullahe malekum min ilahin gayruh kad caetkum beyyinetum mir rabbikum hazihÄḟ nakatullahi lekum ayeten fe zeruha teÂṀkul fÄḟ erdÄḟllahi ve la temessuha vi suin fe yeÂṀhuzekum azabun elÄḟm"
  7,74,"Vezkuru iz cealekum hulefae mim baÂṀdi adiv ve bevveekum fil erdÄḟ tettehÄḟzune min suhuliha kusurav ve tenhÄḟtunel cibale buyuta fezkuru alaellahi ve la taÂṀsev fil erdÄḟ mufsidÄḟn"
  7,75,"Kalel meleul lezÄḟnestekberu min kavmihÄḟ lillezÄḟnes tudÂṀÄḟfu li men amene minhum etaÂṀlemune enne saliham murselum mir rabbih kalu inna bima ursile bihÄḟ muÂṀminun"
  7,76,"KalellezÄḟnestekberu inna billezÄḟ amentum bihÄḟ kafirun"
  7,77,"Fe akarun nakate ve atev an emri rabbihim ve kalu ya salihuÂṀtina bima teÄḟduna in kunte minel murselÄḟn"
  7,78,"Fe ehazethumur racfetu fe asbehu fÄḟ darihim casimÄḟn"
  7,79,"Fe tevella anhum va kale ya kavmi le kad eblagtukum risalete rabbÄḟ ve nesahtu lekum ve lakil la tuhÄḟbbunen nasÄḟhÄḟyn"
  7,80,"Ve lutan iz kale li kavmihÄḟ eteÂṀtunel fahÄḟsete ma sebekakum biha min ehadim minel alemÄḟn"
  7,81,"Innekum le teÂṀtuner ricale sehvetem min dunin nisaÂṀ bel entum kavmum musrifun"
  7,82,"Ve ma kane cevabe kavmihÄḟ illa en kalu ahricuhum min karyetikum innehum unasuy yetetahherun"
  7,83,"Fe enceynahu ve ehlehu illemraetehu kanet minel gabirÄḟn"
  7,84,"Ve emtarna aleyhim metara fenzur keyfe kane akÄḟbetul mucrimÄḟn"
  7,85,"Ve ila medyene ehahum suayba kale ya kavmÄḟÂṀbudullahe malekum min ilahin gayruh kad caetkum beyyinetum mir rabbikum fe evful keyle vel mÄḟzane ve la tebhasun nase esyaehum ve la tufsidu fil erdÄḟ baÂṀde ÄḟslahÄḟha zalikum hayrul lekum in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  7,86,"Ve la takÂṀudu bi kulli sÄḟratÄḟn tuÄḟdune ve tesuddune an sebÄḟlillahi men amene bihÄḟ ve tebguneha Äḟveca vezkuru iz kuntum kalÄḟlen fe kesserakum venzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetul mufsidÄḟn"
  7,87,"Ve in kane taifetum minkum amenu billezÄḟ ursiltu bihÄḟ ve taifetul lem yuÂṀminu fasbiru hatta yahkumellahu beynena ve huve hayrul hakimÄḟn"
  7,88,"Kalel meleullezÄḟnestekberu min kavmihÄḟ le nuhricenneke ya suaybu vellezÄḟne amenu meake min karyetina ev leteudunne fÄḟ milletina kale e ve lev kunna karihÄḟn"
  7,89,"Kadifterayna alellahi keziben in udna fÄḟ milletikum baÂṀde iz neccanellahu minha ve ma yekunu lena en neude fÄḟha illa ey yesaellahu rabbuna vesia rabbuna kulle seyÂṀin Äḟlma alellahi tevekkelna rabbeneftah beynena ve beyne kavmina bil hakkÄḟ ve ente hayrul fatihÄḟyn"
  7,90,"Ve kalel meleullezÄḟne keferu min kavmihÄḟ le inittebaÂṀtum suayben innekum izel le hasirun"
  7,91,"Fe ehazethumur racfetu fe asbehu fÄḟ darihim casimÄḟn"
  7,92,"EllezÄḟne kezzebu suayben ke el lem yagnev fÄḟhellezÄḟne kezzebu suayben kanu humul hasirÄḟn"
  7,93,"Fe tevella anhum ve akle ya kavmi le kad eblagtukum risalati rabbÄḟ ve nesahtu lekum fe keyfe asa ala kavmin kafirÄḟn"
  7,94,"Ve ma erselna fÄḟ karyetim min nebiyyin illa ehazna ehleha bil beÂṀsai ved darrai leallehum yeddaraun"
  7,95,"Summe beddelna mekanes seyyietil hasenete hatta afev ve kalu kad messe abaenad darrau ves serrau fe ehaznahum bagtetev ve hum la yesÂṀurun"
  7,96,"Ve lev enne ehlel kura amenu vettekav le fetahna aleyhim berakatim mines semai vel erdÄḟ ve lakin kezzebu fe ehaznahum bima kanu yeksibun"
  7,97,"E fe emine ehlul kura ey yeÂṀtiyehum beÂṀsuna beyatev ve hum naimun"
  7,98,"E ve emine ehlul kura ey yeÂṀtiyehum beÂṀsuna duhav ve hum yelÂṀabun"
  7,99,"E fe eminu mekrallah fe la yeÂṀmenu mekrallahi illel kavmul hasirun"
  7,100,"E ve lem yehdi lillezÄḟne yerisunel erda mim baÂṀdi ehliha el lev nesau esabnahum bi zunubihim ve natbeu ala kulubihim fe hum la yesmeun"
  7,101,"Tilkel kura nekussu aleyke min embaiha ve le kad caethum rusuluhum bil beyyinat fe ma kanu li yuÂṀminu bima kezzebu min kabl kezalike yatbeullahu ala kulubil kafirÄḟn"
  7,102,"Ve ma vecedna li ekserihim min ahd ve ev vecedna ekserahum le fasikÄḟyn"
  7,103,"Summe beasna mim baÂṀdihim musa bi ayatina ila firÂṀavne ve meleihÄḟ fe zalemu biha fenzur keyfe kane akÄḟbetul mufsidÄḟn"
  7,104,"Ve kale musa ya firÂṀavnu innÄḟ rasulum mir rabbil alemÄḟn"
  7,105,"HakÄḟykun ala el la ekule alellahi illel hakk kad ciÂṀtumu bi beyyinetim mir rabbikum fe ersil meÄḟye benÄḟ israÄḟl"
  7,106,"Kale in kunte ciÂṀte bi ayetin feÂṀti biha in kunte mines sadikÄḟyn"
  7,107,"Fe elka asahu fe iza hiye suÂṀbanum mubÄḟn"
  7,108,"Ve nezea yedehu fe iza hiye beydau lin nazÄḟrÄḟn"
  7,109,"Kalel meleu min kavmi firÂṀavne inne haza le sahÄḟrun alÄḟm"
  7,110,"YurÄḟdu ey yuhricekum min erdÄḟkum fe maza teÂṀmurun"
  7,111,"Kalu ercih ve ehahu ve ersil fil medaini hasirÄḟn"
  7,112,"YeÂṀtuke bi kulli sahÄḟrin alÄḟm"
  7,113,"Ve caes seharatu firÂṀavne kalu inne lena le ecran in kunna nahnul galibÄḟn"
  7,114,"Kale neam ve innekum le minel mukarrabÄḟn"
  7,115,"Kalu ya musa imma en tulkÄḟye ve imma en nekune nahnul mulkÄḟy"
  7,116,"Kale elku fe lemma elkav seharu aÂṀyunen nasi vesterhebuhum ve cau bi sÄḟhrin azÄḟym"
  7,117,"Ve evhayna ila musa en elkÄḟ asak fe iza hiye telkafu ma yeÂṀfikÄḟn"
  7,118,"Fe vekaal hakku ve betale ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  7,119,"Fe gulibu hunalike venkalebu sagÄḟrÄḟn"
  7,120,"Ve ulkÄḟyes seharatu sacidÄḟn"
  7,121,"Kalu amenna bi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  7,122,"Rabbi musa ve harun"
  7,123,"Kale firÂṀavnu amentum bihÄḟ kable en azene lekum inne haza le mekrum mekertumuhu fil medÄḟneti li tuhricu minha ehleha fe sevfe taÂṀlemun"
  7,124,"Le ukattÄḟanne eydiyekum ve erculekum min hÄḟlafin summe le usallibennekum ecmeÄḟyn"
  7,125,"Kalu inna ila rabbina munkalibun"
  7,126,"Ve ma tenkÄḟmu minna illa en amenna bi ayati rabbina lemma caetna rabbena efrÄḟg aleyna sabrav ve teveffena muslimÄḟn"
  7,127,"Ve kalel meleu min kavmi firÂṀavne e etezru musa ve kavmehu li yufsidu fil erdÄḟ ve yezerake ve alihetek kale senukattilu ebnaehum ve nestahyÄḟ nisaehum ve inna fevkahum kahirun"
  7,128,"Kale musa li kavmihisteÄḟynu billahi vasbiru innel erda lillah yurisuha mey yesau min Äḟbadih vel akÄḟbetu lil muttekÄḟyn"
  7,129,"Kalu uzÄḟna min kabli en teÂṀtiyena ve mim baÂṀdi ma ciÂṀtena kale asa rabbukum ey yuhlike aduvvekum ve yestahlifekum fil erdÄḟ fe yenzura keyfe taÂṀmelun"
  7,130,"Ve le kad ehazna ale firÂṀavne bis sinÄḟne ve naksÄḟm mines semerati leallehum yezzekkerun"
  7,131,"Fe iza caethumul hasenetu kalu lena hazih ve in tusÄḟbhum seyyietuy yettayyeru bi musa ve mem meah e la innema tairuhum Äḟndellahi ve lakinne ekserahum la yaÂṀlemun"
  7,132,"Ve kalu mehma teÂṀtina bihÄḟ min ayetil li tesharana biha fe ma nahnu leke bi muÂṀminÄḟn"
  7,133,"Fe erselna aleyhimut tufane vel cerade vel kummele ved dafadia ved deme ayatim mufessalatin festekberu ve kanu kavmem mucrimÄḟn"
  7,134,"Ve lemma vekaa aleyhimur riczu kalu ya musedÂṀu lena rabbeke bima ahide Äḟndek le in kesefte annar ricze le nuÂṀminenne leke ve le nursilenne meake benÄḟ israÄḟl"
  7,135,"Felemma kesefna anhumur ricze ila ecelin hum baliguhu iza hum yenkusun"
  7,136,"Fentekamna minhum fe agraknahum fil yemmi bi ennehum kezzebu bi ayatina ve kanu anha gafilÄḟn"
  7,137,"Ve evrasnel kavmellezÄḟne kanu yustadÂṀafune mesarikal erdÄḟ ve megaribehelletÄḟ barakna fÄḟha ve temmet kelimetu rabbikel husna ala benÄḟ israÄḟle bima saberu ve demmerna ma kane yesneu firÂṀavnu ve kavmuhu ve ma kanu yaÂṀrisun"
  7,138,"Ve cavezna bi benÄḟ israilel bahra fe etev ala kavmiy yaÂṀkufune ala asnamil lehum kalu ya musecÂṀal lena ilahen kema lehum aliheh kale innekum kavmun techelun"
  7,139,"Inne haulai mutebberum ma hum fÄḟhi ve batÄḟlum ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  7,140,"Kale egayrallahi ebgÄḟykum ilahev ve huve feddalekum alel alemÄḟn"
  7,141,"Ve iz enceynakum min ali firÂṀavne yesumunekum suel azab yukattilune ebnaekum ve yestahyune nisaekum ve fÄḟ zalikum belaum mir rabbikum azÄḟym"
  7,142,"Ve vaadna musa selasÄḟne leyletev ve etmemnaha bi asrin fe temme mÄḟkatu rabbihÄḟ erbeÄḟyne leyleh ve kale musa li ehÄḟyhi harunahlufnÄḟ fÄḟ kavmÄḟ ve aslÄḟh ve la tettebÄḟÂṀ sebÄḟlel mufsidÄḟn"
  7,143,"Ve lemma cae musa li mÄḟkatina ve kelemehu rabbuhu kale rabbi erinÄḟ enzir ileyk kale len teranÄḟ ve lakininzur ilel cebeli fe inistekarra mekanehu fe sevfe teranÄḟ felemma tecella rabbuhu lil cebeli cealehu dekkev ve harra musa saÄḟka felemma efaka kale subhaneke tubtu ileyke ve ene evvelul muÂṀminÄḟn"
  7,144,"Kale ya musa innistafeytuke alen nasi bi risalatÄḟ ve bi kelamÄḟ fe huz ma ateytuke ve kum mines sakirÄḟn"
  7,145,"Ve ketebna lehufil elvahÄḟ min kulli seyÂṀim mevÂṀÄḟzatev ve tefsÄḟylel li kulli seyÂṀ fe huzha bi kuvvetiv veÂṀmur kavmeke yeÂṀhuzha bi ahseniha seurÄḟkum daral fasikÄḟyn"
  7,146,"Seasrifu an ayatiyellezÄḟne yetekebberune fil erdÄḟ bi gayril hakk ve iy yerav kulle ayetil la yuÂṀminu biha ve iy yerav sebÄḟler rusdi la yettehÄḟzuhu sebÄḟla ve iy yerav sebÄḟlel gayyi yettehÄḟzuhu sebÄḟla zalike bi ennehum kezzebu bi ayatina ve kanu anha gafilÄḟn"
  7,147,"VellezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina ve likail ahÄḟrati habitat aÂṀmaluhum hel yuczevne illa ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  7,148,"Vettehaze kavmu musa mim baÂṀdihÄḟ min huliyyihim Äḟclen cesedel lehu huvar e lem yerav ennehu la yukellimuhum ve la yehdÄḟhim sebÄḟla ittehazuhu ve kanu zalimÄḟn"
  7,149,"Ve lemma sukÄḟta fÄḟ eydÄḟhim ve raev ennehul kad dallu kalu leil lem yerhamna rabbuna ve yagfir lena lenekunenne minel hasirÄḟn"
  7,150,"Ve lemma racea musa ila kavmihÄḟ gadbane esifen kale biÂṀsema haleftumunÄḟ mim baÂṀdÄḟ e aciltum emra rabbikum ve elkal elvaha ve ehaze bi raÂṀsi ehÄḟyhi yecurruhu ileyh kalebne umme innel kavmestadÂṀafunÄḟ ve kadu yaktulunenÄḟ fe la tusmit biyel aÂṀdae ve la tecÂṀalnÄḟ meal kavmiz zalimÄḟn"
  7,151,"Kale rabbÄḟgfir lÄḟ ve li ehÄḟy ve edhÄḟlna fÄḟ rahmetike ve ente erhamur rahÄḟmÄḟn"
  7,152,"InnellezÄḟnet tehazul Äḟcle seyenaluhum gadabum mir rabbihim ve zilletun fil hayatid dunya ve kezalike neczil mufterÄḟn"
  7,153,"VellezÄḟne amilus seyyiati summe tabu mim baÂṀdiha ve amenu inne rabbeke mim baÂṀdiha le gafurur rahÄḟym"
  7,154,"Ve lemma sekete am musel gadabu ehazel elvah ve fÄḟ nushatiha hudev ve rahmetul lillezÄḟne hum li rabbihim yerhebun"
  7,155,"Vahtara musa kavmehu sebÂṀÄḟyne raculel li mÄḟkatina felemma ehazethumur racfetu kale rabbi lev siÂṀte ehlektehum min kablu ve iyyay e tuhlikuna bima feales sufehau minna in hiye illa fitnetuk tudÄḟllu biha men tesau ve tehdÄḟ men tesaÂṀ ente veliyyuna fagfir lena verhamna ve nete hayrul gafirÄḟn"
  7,156,"Vektub lena fÄḟ hazihid dunya hazenetev ve fil ahÄḟrati inna hudna ileyk kale azabÄḟ usÄḟybu bihÄḟ men esaÂṀ ve rahmetÄḟ vesiat kulle seyÂṀ fe seektubuha lillezÄḟne yettekune ve yuÂṀtunez zekate vellezÄḟne hum bi ayatina yuÂṀminun"
  7,157,"EllezÄḟne yettebiuner rasulen nebiyyel ummiyyellezÄḟ yecidune mektuben Äḟndehum fit tevrati vel incÄḟli yeÂṀmuruhum bil maÂṀrufi ve yenhahum anil munkeri ve yuhÄḟllu lehumut tayyibati ve yuharrimu aleyhimul habaise ve yedau anhum Äḟsrahum vel aglalelletÄḟ kanet aleyhim fellezÄḟne amenu bihÄḟ ve azzeruhu ve nesaruhu vetteveun nurallezÄḟ unzile meahu ulaike humul muflihun"
  7,158,"Kul ya eyyuhen nasu innÄḟ rasulullahi ileykum cemÄḟanillezÄḟ lehu mulkus semavati vel ard la ilahe illa huve yuhyÄḟ ve yumÄḟtu fe aminu billahi ve rasulihin nebiyyil ummiyyellezÄḟ yuÂṀminu billahi ve kelimetihÄḟ vettebiuhu leallekum tehtedun"
  7,159,"Ve min kavmi musa ummetuy yehdune bil hakkÄḟ ve bihÄḟ yaÂṀdilun"
  7,160,"Ve kattaÂṀnahumusnetey asrate esbatan umema ve evhayna ila musa izisteskahu kavmuhu enÄḟdrib bi asakel hacer fembeceset minhusneta asrate ayna kad alime kullu unasim mesrabehum ve zallelna aleyhimul gamame ve enzelna aleyhimul menne ves selva kulu min tayyibati ma razaknakum ve ma zalemuna ve lakin kanu enfusehum yazlimun"
  7,161,"Ve iz kÄḟyle lehumuskunu hazihil kayete ve kulu minha haysu siÂṀtum ve kulu hÄḟttatuv vedhulul babe succeden nagfirlekum hatÄḟyÂṀatikum senezÄḟdul muhsinÄḟn"
  7,162,"Fe beddelellezÄḟne zalemu minhum kavlen gayrallezÄḟ kÄḟyle lehum fe erselna aleyhim riczem mines semai bima kanu yazlimun"
  7,163,"VesÂṀelhum anil karyetilletÄḟ kanet hadÄḟratel bahr iz yaÂṀdune fis sebti iz teÂṀtÄḟhim hÄḟytanuhum yevme sevtihim surraav ve yevme la yesbitune la teÂṀtÄḟhim kezalike nebluhum bima kanu yefsukun"
  7,164,"Ve iz kalet ummetum minhum lime teÄḟzune kavmenillahu muhlikuhum ev muazzibuhum azaben sedÄḟda kalu maÂṀziraten illa rabbikum ve leallehum yettekun"
  7,165,"Felemma nesu ma zukkiru bihÄḟ enceynellezÄḟne yenhevne anis sui ve ehaznellezÄḟne zalemu bi azabim beÄḟsim bima kanu yefsukun"
  7,166,"Felemma atev amma nuhu anhu kulna lehum kunu kÄḟradetem hasiÄḟn"
  7,167,"Ve iz teezzene rabbuke le yebÂṀasenne aleyhim ila yevmil kÄḟyameti mey yesumuhum suel azab inne rabbeke le serÄḟul Äḟkab ve innehu le gafurur rahÄḟym"
  7,168,"Ve kattaÂṀnahum fil erdÄḟ umema minhumus salihune ve minhum dune zalike ve belevnahum bil hasenati ves seyyiati leallehum yarciun"
  7,169,"Fe halefe mim baÂṀdihim hayfuv verisul kitabe yeÂṀhuzune arada hazel edna ve yekulune se yugferulena ve iy yeÂṀtihim aradum misluhu yeÂṀhuzuh e lem yuÂṀhaz aleyhim mÄḟsakul kitabi el la yekulu alellahi illel hakka ve derasu ma fÄḟh ved darul ahÄḟratu hayrul lillezÄḟne yettekun e fela taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  7,170,"VellezÄḟne yumessikune bil kitabi ve ekamus salah inna la nudÄḟyÂṀu ecral muslihÄḟyn"
  7,171,"Ve iz netaknel cebel fevkahum keennehu zulletuv ve zannu ennehu vakÄḟum bihÄḟm huzu ma ateynakum bi kuvvetiv vezkuru ma fÄḟhi leallekum tettekun"
  7,172,"Ve iz ehaze rabbuke mim benÄḟ ademe min zuhurihim zurriyyetehum ve eshedehum ala enfusihim elestu bi rabbikum kalu bela sehidna en tekulu yevmel kÄḟyameti inna kunna an haza gafilÄḟn"
  7,173,"Ev tekulu innema esrake abauna min kablu ve kunna zurriyyetem mim baÂṀdihim e fetuhlikuna bima fealel mubtÄḟlun"
  7,174,"Ve kezalike nufessÄḟlul ayati ve leallehum yarciun"
  7,175,"Vetlu aleyhim nebeellezÄḟ ateynahu ayatina feneseleha minha fe etbeahus seytanu fe kane minel gavÄḟn"
  7,176,"Ve lev siÂṀna le rafaÂṀnahu biha ve lakinnehu ahlede ilel erdÄḟ vettebea hevah fe meseluhu ke meselil kelb in tahmil aleyhi yelhes ev tetrukhu yelhes zalike meselul kavmillezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina faksusÄḟl kasasa leallehum yetefekkerun"
  7,177,"Sae meselenil kavmullezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina ve enfusehum kanu yazlimun"
  7,178,"Mey yehdillahu fe huvel muhtedÄḟ ve mey yudlil fe ulaike humul hasirun"
  7,179,"Ve le kad zeraÂṀna li cehenneme kesÄḟram minel cinni vel insi lehum kulubul la yefkahune biha ve lehum aÂṀyunul la yubsÄḟrune biha ve lehum azanul la yesmeune biha ulaike kel enÂṀami bel hum edall ulaike humul gafilun"
  7,180,"Ve lillahil esmaul husna fedÂṀuhu biha ve zerullezÄḟne yulhÄḟdune fÄḟ esmail seyuczevne ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  7,181,"Ve mimmen halakna ummetuy yehdune bil hakku ve bihÄḟ yaÂṀdilun"
  7,182,"Vellezine kezzebu bi ayatina senestedricuhum min haysu la yaÂṀlemun"
  7,183,"Ve umlÄḟ lehum inne keydÄḟ metÄḟn"
  7,184,"E ve lem yetefekkeru ma bi sahÄḟbihim min cinneh in huve illa nezÄḟrum mubÄḟn"
  7,185,"E ve lem yenzuru fÄḟ melekutis semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ma halekallahu min seyÂṀiv ve en asa ey yekune kadÄḟkterabe eceluhum fe bi eyyi hadÄḟsim baÂṀdehu yuÂṀminun"
  7,186,"Mey yudlilillahu fe la hadiye leh ve yezeruhum fÄḟ tugyanihim yaÂṀmehun"
  7,187,"YesÂṀeluneke anis saati eyyane mursaha kul innema Äḟlmuha Äḟnde rabbÄḟ la yucellÄḟha lil vaktiha illa hu sekulet fis semavati vel ard la teÂṀtÄḟkum illa bagteh yesÂṀeluneke keenneke hafiyyun anha kul innema Äḟlmuha Äḟndellahi ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yaÂṀlemun"
  7,188,"Kul la emliku li nefsÄḟ nefÂṀav ve la darran illa ma saellah ve lev kuntu aÂṀlemul gaybe lesteksertu minel hayr ve ma messeniyes suu in ene illa nezÄḟruv ve besÄḟrul li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  7,189,"HuvellezÄḟ halekakum min nefsiv vahÄḟdetiv ve ceale minha zevceha li yeskune ileyha felemma tegassaha hamelet hamlen hafÄḟfen fe merrat bih felemma eskalet deavellahe rabbehuma lein ateytina salihal lenekunenne mines sakirÄḟn"
  7,190,"Felemma atahuma salihan ceala lehu surakae fÄḟma atahuma fe tealellahu amma yusrikun"
  7,191,"E yusrikune ma la yahluku seyÂṀev ve hum yuhlekun"
  7,192,"Ve la yestetuyÂṀune lehum nasra v ve la enfusehum yensurun"
  7,193,"Ve in tedÂṀuhum ilel huda la yettebiukum sevaun aleykum e deavtumuhum em entum samitun"
  7,194,"InnellezÄḟne tedÂṀune min dunillahi Äḟbadun emsalukum fedÂṀuhum felyestecÄḟbu lekum in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  7,195,"E lehum erculuy yemsune biha em lehum eydiy yebtÄḟsune biha em lehum aÂṀyunuy yubsÄḟrune biha em lehum azanuy yesmeune biha kulidÂṀu surakaekum summe kÄḟduni fela tunzÄḟrun"
  7,196,"Inne veliyyiyallahullezÄḟ nezzelel kitabe ve huve yetevelles salihÄḟyn"
  7,197,"VellezÄḟne tedÂṀune min dunihÄḟ la yestetÄḟyÂṀune nasrakum ve la enfusehum yensurun"
  7,198,"Ve in tedÂṀuhum ilel huda la yesmeu ve terahum yenzurune ileyke ve hum la yubsÄḟrun"
  7,199,"Huzil afve veÂṀmur bil urfi ve aÂṀrÄḟd anil cahilÄḟn"
  7,200,"Ve imma yenzeganneke mines seytani nezgun festeÄḟz billah innehu semiun alÄḟm"
  7,201,"InnellezÄḟnettekav iza messehum taifum mines seytani tezekkeru fe izahum mubsÄḟrun"
  7,202,"Ve Äḟhvanuhum yemuddunehum fil gayyi summe la yuksÄḟrun"
  7,203,"Ve iza lem teÂṀtihim bi ayatin kalu lev lectebeyteha kul innema ettebiu ma yuha ileyye mir rabbÄḟ haza besairu mir rabbikum ve hudev ve rahmetul li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  7,204,"Ve iza kuriel kurÂṀanu festemiu lehu ve ensÄḟtu leallekum turhamun"
  7,205,"Vezkur rabbeke fÄḟ nefsike tedardruav ve hÄḟyfetev ve dunel cehri minel gafilÄḟn"
  7,206,"InnellezÄḟne Äḟnde rabbike la yestekbirune an ÄḟbadetihÄḟ ve yusebbihune hu ve lehu yescudun"
  8,3,"EllezÄḟne yukÄḟymunes salate ve mimma razaknahum yunfikun"
  8,4,"Ulaike humul muÂṀminine hakka lehum deracatun Äḟnde rabbihim ve magfiratuv ve rizkun kerÄḟm"
  8,5,"Kema ahraceke rabbuke mim beytike bil hakkÄḟ ve inne ferÄḟkam minel muÂṀminÄḟne le karihun"
  8,6,"Yucadiluneke fil hakkÄḟ baÂṀde ma tebeyyene keennema yusakune ilel mevti ve hum yenzurun"
  8,7,"Ve iz yeÄḟdukumullahu Äḟhdet taifeteyni enneha lekum ve teveddune enne gayra zatis sevketi tekunu lekum ve yurÄḟdullahu ey yuhÄḟkkal hakka bi kelimatihÄḟ ve yaktaa dabiral kafirÄḟn"
  8,8,"Li yuhÄḟkkal hakka ve yubtÄḟlel batÄḟle ve lev kerihel mucrimun"
  8,9,"Iz testegÄḟysune rabbekum festecabe lekum ennÄḟ mumiddukum bi elfim minel melaiketi murdifÄḟn"
  8,10,"Ve ma cealehullahu illa busra ve li tatmeinne bihÄḟ kulubukum ve men nasru illa min Äḟndillah innellahe azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  8,11,"Iz yugassikumun nuase emenetem minhu ve yunessilu aleykum mines semai mael li yutahhirakum bihÄḟ ve yuzhibe ankum riczes seytani ve li yerbita ala kulubikum ve yusebbite bihil akdam"
  8,12,"Iz yuhÄḟy rabbuke ilel melaiketi ennÄḟ meakum fe sebbitullezÄḟne amenu seulkÄḟy fÄḟ kulubillezÄḟne keferur ruÂṀbe fadribu fevkal aÂṀnakÄḟ vadribu minhum kulle benan"
  8,13,"Zalike bi ennehum sakkullahe ve rasuleh ve mey yusakÄḟkÄḟllahe ve rasulehu fe innellahe sedÄḟdul Äḟkab"
  8,14,"Zalikum fe zukuhu ve enne lil kafirÄḟne azaben nar"
  8,15,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu iza lekÄḟytumullezÄḟne keferu zahfen fe la tuvelluhumul edbar"
  8,16,"Ve mey yuvellihim yevmeizin duburahu illa muteharrifel li kÄḟtalin ev mutehayyizen ila fietin fe kad bae bi gadabim minellahi ve meÂṀvahu cehennem ve biÂṀsel mesÄḟyr"
  8,17,"Fe lem taktuluhum ve lakinnellahe katelehum ve ma rameyte iz rameyte ve lakinnellahe rama ve li yubliyel muÂṀminÄḟne minhu belaen hasena innellahe semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  8,18,"Zalikum ve ennellahe muhinu keydil kafirÄḟn"
  8,19,"In testeftihu fekad caekumul feth ve in tentehu fe huve hayrul lekum ve in teudu neud ve len tugniye ankum fietukum seyÂṀev ve lev kesurat ve ennellahe meal muÂṀminÄḟn"
  8,20,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu etÄḟyÂṀullahe ve rasulehu vela tevellev anhu ve entum tesmeun"
  8,21,"Ve la tekunu kellezÄḟne kalu semÄḟÂṀna ve hum la yesmeun"
  8,22,"Inne serrad devabbi Äḟndellahis summul bukmullezÄḟne la yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  8,23,"Ve lev alimellahu fÄḟhim hayral le esmeahum ve lev esmeahum le tevellev ve hum muÂṀridun"
  8,24,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenustecÄḟbu lillahi v lir rasuli iza deakum lima yuhyÄḟkum vaÂṀlemu ennellahe yehulu beynel merÂṀi ve kalbihÄḟ ve ennehu ileyhi tuhserun"
  8,25,"Vetteku fitnetel la tusÄḟybennellezÄḟne zalemu minkum hassah vaÂṀlemu ennellahe sedÄḟdul Äḟkab"
  8,26,"Veskuru iz entum kalÄḟlum mustedÂṀafune fil erdÄḟ tehafune ey yetehattafekumun nasu fe avakum ve eyyedekum bi nasrihÄḟ ve razekakum minet tayyibati leallekum teskurun"
  8,27,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tehunullahe ver rasule ve tehunu emanatikum ve entum taÂṀlemun"
  8,28,"VaÂṀlemu ennema emvalukum ve evladukum fitnetuv ve ennellahe Äḟndehu ecrun azÄḟym"
  8,29,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu in tettekullahe yecÂṀal lekum furkanev ve yukeffir ankum seyyiatikum ve yagfir lekum vallahu zul fadlil azÄḟym"
  8,30,"Ve iz yemkuru bikellezÄḟne keferu li yusbituke ev yaktuluke ev yuhricuk ve yemkurune ve yemkurullah vallahu hayrul makirÄḟn"
  8,31,"Ve iza tutla alehim ayatuna kalu kad semÄḟÂṀna lev nesau le kulna misle haza in haza illa esatÄḟyrul evvelÄḟn"
  8,32,"Ve iz kalullahumme in kane haza huvel hakka min Äḟndike fe emtÄḟr aleyna hÄḟcaratem mines semai eviÂṀtina bi azabin elÄḟm"
  8,33,"Ve ma kanellahu li yuazzibehum ve ente fÄḟhim ve ma kanellahu muazzibehum ve hum yestagfirun"
  8,34,"Ve ma lehum ella yuazzibehumullahu ve hum yesuddune anil mescidil harami ve ma kanu evliyaeh in evliyauhu illel muttekune ve lakinne ekserahum la yaÂṀlemun"
  8,35,"Ve ma kane salatuhum Äḟndel beyti illa mukaev ve tasdiyeh fe zukul azabe bi ma kuntum tekfurun"
  8,36,"InnellezÄḟne keferu yunfikune emvalehum li yesuddu an sebÄḟlillah fe seyunfikuneha summe tekunu aleyhim hasraten summe yuglebun vellezÄḟne keferu ila cehenneme yuhserun"
  8,37,"Li yemizellahul habise minet tayyibi ve yecÂṀalel habÄḟse baÂṀdahu ala baÂṀdÄḟn fe yerkumehu cemÄḟan fe yecÂṀalehu fÄḟ cehennem ulaike humul hasirun"
  8,38,"Kul lillezÄḟne keferu iy yentehu yugfer lehum ma kad selef ve iy yeudu fe kad medat sunnetul evvelÄḟn"
  8,39,"Ve katiluhum hatta la tekune fitnetuv ve yekuned dÄḟnu kulluhu lillah fe inintehev fe innellahe bi ma yaÂṀmelune besÄḟyr"
  8,40,"Ve in tevellev faÂṀlemu ennellahe mevlakum nÄḟÂṀmel mevla ve nÄḟÂṀmen nesÄḟyr"
  8,41,"VaÂṀlemu ennema ganimtum min seyÂṀin fe enne lillahi humusehu ve lir rasuli ve lizil kurba vel yetama vel mesakÄḟni vebnis sebÄḟli in kuntum amentum billahi ve ma enzelna ala abdina yevmel furkani yevmel tekal cemÂṀan vallahu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  8,42,"Iz entum bil udvetid dunya ve hum bil udvetil kusva ver rakbu esfele minkum ve lev tevaadtum lahteleftum fil mÄḟadi ve lakil li yakdÄḟyellahu emran kane mefÂṀulel li yehlike men heleke am beyyinetiv ve yahya men hayye am beyyineh ve innellahe le semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  8,43,"Iz yurÄḟkehumullahu fÄḟ menamike kalÄḟla ve lev erakehum kesÄḟral le fesiltum ve le tenazaÂṀtum fil emri ve lainnellahe sellem innehu alÄḟmum bi zatis sudur"
  8,44,"Ve iz yurÄḟkumuhum izil tekaytum fÄḟ aÂṀyunikum kalÄḟlev ve yukallilukum fÄḟ aÂṀyunihim li yakdÄḟyellahu emran kane mefÂṀula ve ilellahi turceul umur"
  8,45,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu iza lekÄḟytum fieten fesbutu veskurullahe kesÄḟral leallekum tuflihun"
  8,46,"Ve etÄḟyÂṀullahe ve rasulehu ve la tenazeu fe tefselu ve tezhebe rÄḟhukum vasbiru innellahe meas sabirÄḟn"
  8,47,"Ve la tekunu kellezÄḟne haracu min diyarihim betarav ve riaen nasi ve yesuddune an sebÄḟlillah vallahu bi ma yaÂṀmelune muhÄḟyt"
  8,48,"Ve iz zeyyene lehumus seytanu aÂṀmalehum ve kale la galibe lekumul yevme minen nasi ve innÄḟ carul lekum felemma teraetil fietani nekesa ala akÄḟbeyhi ve kale innÄḟ berÄḟum minkum innÄḟ era ma la teravne innÄḟ ehafullah vallahu sedÄḟdul Äḟkab"
  8,49,"Iz yekulul munafikune vellezÄḟne fÄḟ kulubihim meradun garra haulai dÄḟnuhum ve mey yetevekkel alellahi fe innellahe azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  8,50,"Ve lev tera iz yeteveffellezÄḟne keferul melaiketu yadribune vucuhehum ve edbarahum ve zuku azabel harÄḟyk"
  8,51,"Zalike bima kaddemet eydÄḟkum ve ennellahe leysi bi zallamil lil abÄḟd"
  8,52,"KedeÂṀbi ali firÂṀavne vellezÄḟne min kablihim keferu bi ayatillahi fe ehazehumullahu bi zunubihim innellahe kaviyyun sedÄḟdul Äḟkab"
  8,53,"Zalike bi ennellahe lem yeku mugayyiran nÄḟÂṀmeten enÂṀameha ala kavmin hatta yugayyiru ma bi enfusihim ve ennellahe semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  8,54,"KedeÂṀbi ali firÂṀavne vellezÄḟne min kablihim kezzebu bi ayati rabbihim fe ehleknahum bi zunubihim ve agrakna ale firÂṀavn ve kullun kanu zalimÄḟn"
  8,55,"Inne serrad devabbi ÄḟndellahillezÄḟne keferu fehum la yuÂṀminun"
  8,56,"EllezÄḟne ahedte minhum summe yenkudune ahdehum fÄḟ kulli merrativ ve hum la yettekun"
  8,57,"Fe imma teskafennehum fil harbi fe serrid bihim men halfehum leallehum yezzekkerun"
  8,58,"Ve imma tehafenne min kavmin hÄḟyaneten fembiz ileyhim ala sevaÂṀ innellahe la yuhÄḟbbul hainÄḟn"
  8,59,"Ve la yahsebennellezÄḟne keferu sebeku innehum la yuÂṀcizun"
  8,60,"Ve eÄḟddu lehum mestetaÂṀtum min kuvvetiv ve mir ribatÄḟl hayli turhibune bihÄḟ aduvvellahi ve aduvvekum ve aharÄḟne min dunihim la taÂṀlemunehum allahu yaÂṀlemuhum ve ma tunfiku min seyÂṀin fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi yuveffe ileykum ve entum la tuzlemun"
  8,61,"Ve in cenehu lis selmi fecnah leha ve tevekkel alellah innehu huves semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  8,62,"Ve iy yurÄḟdu ey yahdeuke fe inne hasbekellah huvellezÄḟ eyyedeke bi nasrihÄḟ ve bil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  8,63,"Ve ellefe beyne kulubihim lev enfakte ma fil erdÄḟ cemÄḟam ma ellefte beyne kulubihim ve lakinnellahe ellefe beynehum innehu azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  8,64,"Ya eyyuhen nebiyyu hasbukellahu ve menittebeake minel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  8,65,"Ya eyyuhen nebiyyu harridÄḟl muÂṀminÄḟne alel kÄḟtal iy yekum minkum isrune sabirune yaglibu mieteyn ve iy yekum minkum mietuy yaglibu elfem minellezÄḟne keferu bi ennehum kavmul la yefkahun"
  8,66,"El ane haffefellahu ankum ve alime enne fÄḟkum daÂṀfa fe iy yekum minkum mietun sabiratuy yaglibu mieteyn ve iy yekum minkum elfuy yaglibu elfeyni bi iznillah vallahu meas sabirÄḟn"
  8,67,"Ma kane li nebiyyin ey yekune lehu esra hatta yushÄḟne fil ard turÄḟdune aradad dunya vallahu yurÄḟdul ahÄḟrah vallahu azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  8,68,"Lev la kitabum minellahi sebeka lemessekum fÄḟma ehaztum azabun azÄḟym"
  8,69,"Fe kulu mimma ganimtum halalen teyyibev vettekullah innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  8,70,"Ya eyyuhen nebiyyu kul limen fÄḟ eydÄḟkum minel esra iy yaÂṀlemillahu fÄḟ kulubikum hayray yuÂṀtikum hayram mimma uhÄḟze minkum ve yagfir lekum vallahu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  8,71,"Ve iy yurÄḟdu hÄḟyaneteke fe kad hanullahe min kablu fe emkene minhum vallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  8,72,"InnelezÄḟne amenu ve haceru ve cahedu bi emvalihim ve enfusihim fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi vellezÄḟne avev ve nesaru ulaike baÂṀduhum evliyau baÂṀd vellezÄḟne amenu ve lem yuhaciru ma lekum miv velayetihim min seyÂṀin hatta yuhaciru ve inistensarukum fid dÄḟni fe aleykumun nasru illa ala kavmim beynekum ve beynehum mÄḟsak vallahu bi ma taÂṀmelune besÄḟyr"
  8,73,"VellezÄḟne keferu baÂṀduhum evliyau baÂṀd illa tefÂṀaluhu tekun fitnetun fel erdÄḟ ve fesadun kebÄḟr"
  8,74,"VellezÄḟne amenu ve haceru ve cahedu fÄḟ sebilillahi vellezÄḟne avev ve nesaru ulaike humul muÂṀminune hakka lehum magfiratuv ve rizkun kerÄḟm"
  8,75,"VellezÄḟne amenu mim baÂṀdu ve haceru ve cahedu meakum fe ulaike minkum ve ulul erhami baÂṀduhum evla bi baÂṀdÄḟn fÄḟ kitabillah innellahe bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  9,6,"Ve in ehadum minel musrikÄḟnestecarake fe ecirhu hatta yesmea kelamellahi summe eblÄḟghu meÂṀmeneh zalik bi ennehum kavmul la yaÂṀlemun"
  9,7,"Keyfe yekunu lil musrikÄḟne ahdun Äḟndellahi ve Äḟnde rasulihÄḟ illellezÄḟne ahettum Äḟndel mescidil haram fe mestekamu lekum festekÄḟymu lehum innellahe yuhÄḟbbul mutekeyÄḟn"
  9,8,"Keyfe ve iy yazheru aleykum la yerkubu fikum illevve la zimmeh yurdunekum bi efvahihim ve teÂṀba kulubuhum ve ekseruhum fasikun"
  9,9,"Isterav ve ayatillahi semenen kalÄḟlen fe saddu an sebÄḟlih innehum sae ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  9,10,"La yerkubune fÄḟ muÂṀminÄḟn illev ve la zimmeh ve laike humul muÂṀtedun"
  9,11,"Fe in tabu ve ekamus salate ve atevuz zekate fe Äḟhvanukum fid dÄḟn ve nufassÄḟlul ayati le kavmiy yaÂṀlemun"
  9,12,"Ve in nekesu eymanehum mim baÂṀdi ahdihim ve taanu fÄḟ dÄḟnikum fe katilu eimmetel kufri innehum la eymane lehum leallehum yentehun"
  9,13,"Ela tukatilune kavmen nekesu eymanehum ve hemmu bi Äḟhracir rasuli ve hum bedeukum evvele merrah e tahsevnehum fellahu ehakku en tahsevhu in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  9,14,"Katiluhum yuazzibhumullahu bi eydÄḟkum ve yuhzihim ve yensurkum aleyhim ve yesfi sudura kavmim muÂṀminÄḟn"
  9,15,"Ve yuzhib gayza kulubihim ve yetubullahu ala mey yesaÂṀ vallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  9,16,"Em hasibtum en tutraku ve lemma yaÂṀlemillahullezÄḟne cahedu minkum ve lem yetehÄḟzu min dunillahi ve la rasulihÄḟ ve lel muÂṀminÄḟne velÄḟceh vallahu habÄḟrum bi ma taÂṀmelun"
  9,17,"Ma kane lil musrikÄḟne ey yaÂṀmuru mesacidellahi sahidÄḟne ala enfusihm bil kufr ulaike habitat aÂṀmaluhum ve fin nari hum halidun"
  9,18,"Innema yaÂṀmuru mesacidellahi men amene billahi vel yvmil ahÄḟri ve ekames salate ve atez zekate ve lem yahse illallahe fe asa ulaike ey yekunu minel muhtedÄḟn"
  9,19,"E cealtum sikayetel hacci ve Äḟmaratel mescidil harami ke men amen billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟri ve cahede fÄḟ sebÄḟlillah la yestevune Äḟndellah vallahu la yehdil kavmez zalimÄḟn"
  9,20,"EllezÄḟne amenu ve haceru ve cahdu fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi bi emvalihim ve enfusihim aÂṀzamu deracetem Äḟndellah ve ulaike humul faizun"
  9,21,"Yubessiruhum rabbuhum bi rahmetim minhu ve rÄḟdvaniv ve cennatil lehum fÄḟha neÄḟymum mukÄḟym"
  9,22,"HalidÄḟne fÄḟha ebeda innellahe Äḟndehu ecrun azÄḟym"
  9,23,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tettehÄḟzu abaekum ve Äḟhvanekum evliyae inistehabbul kkufra alel Äḟman ve mey yetevellehum minkum fe ulaike humuz zalimun"
  9,24,"Kul in kane abaukum ve ebnaukum ve Äḟhvanukum ve ezvacukum ve asÄḟratukum ve emvalu nÄḟkteraftumuha ve ticaratun tahsevne kesadeha ve mesakinu terdavneha ehabbe ileykum minallahi ve rasulihÄḟ ve cihadin fÄḟ sebÄḟlihÄḟ fe terabbesu hatta yeÂṀtiyallahu bi emrih vallahu la yehdil kavmel fasikÄḟyn"
  9,25,"Le kad nasarakumullahu fÄḟ mevatÄḟne kesÄḟrativ ve yevme hÄḟneynin iz aÂṀcebetkum kesratukum fe lem tugni ankum seyÂṀev ve dakat aleykumul erdu bi ma rahubet summe velleytum mudbirÄḟn"
  9,26,"Summe enezlellahu sekÄḟnetehu ala rasulihÄḟ ve alel muÂṀminÄḟne ve enzele cunudel lem teravha ve azzebellezÄḟne keferu ve zalike cezaul kafirÄḟn"
  9,27,"Summe yetubullahu min baÂṀdi zalike ala mey yesaÂṀ vallahu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  9,28,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu innemel musrikun necesun fe la yakrabul mescidel haram baÂṀde amihim haza ve in hÄḟftum ayleten fe sevfe yugnÄḟkumullahu min fadlihÄḟ in saÂṀ innellahe alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  9,29,"KatilullezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune billahi ve la bil yevmil ahÄḟri ve la yuhurrimune ma harremallahu ve rasuluhu ve la yedÄḟnune dÄḟnel hakkÄḟ minellezÄḟne utul kitube hatta yuÂṀtul cizyete ay yediv vehum sagÄḟrun"
  9,30,"Ve kaletil yehudu uzeyrunibnullahi ve kaletin nesaral mesÄḟhubnullah zalike kavluhum bi efvahaham yudahiune kavlellezÄḟne keferu min kabl katellehumullahu enna yuÂṀfekun"
  9,31,"Ittehazu ahbarahum ve ruhbanehum erbabem min dunillahi vel mesÄḟhabne meryem ve ma umiru illa li yaÂṀbudu ilahev vahÄḟda la ilahe illa hu subhanehu amma yusrikun"
  9,32,"YurÄḟdune ey yutfiu nurallahi bi efvahihim ve yeÂṀbellahu illa ey yutimme nurahu ve lev kerihel kafirun"
  9,33,"HuvellezÄḟ ersele rasulehu bil huda ve dÄḟnil hakkÄḟ li yuzhirahu aled dÄḟni kullihÄḟ ve lev kerihel musrikun"
  9,34,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu inne kesÄḟram minel ahbari ver ruhbani le yeÂṀkulune emvalen nasi bil batÄḟli ve yesuddune an sebÄḟlillah vellezÄḟne yeknizunez zehebe vel fiddate ve la yunfikuneha fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi fe bessirhum bi azabin elÄḟm"
  9,35,"Yevme yuhma aleyha fÄḟ nari cehenneme fe tukva biha cibahuhum ve cunubuhum ve zuhuruhum haza ma keneztum li enfusikum fe zuku ma kuntum teknizun"
  9,36,"Inne Äḟddes suhuri Äḟndellahisna asera sehran fÄḟ kitabillahi yevme halekas semavati vel erda miha erbeatum hurum zaliked dÄḟnul kayyimu fe la tazlimu fÄḟhinne enfusekum ve katilul musrikÄḟne kaffeten kema yukatilunekum kaffeh vaÂṀlemu ennallahe meal muttekÄḟyn"
  9,37,"Innemen nesÄḟu ziyadetun fil kufri yudallu bihillezÄḟne keferu yuhÄḟllunehu amev ve yuharrimunehu amel li yuvatÄḟu Äḟddete ma harramellahu fe yuhÄḟllu ma harremellah zuyyine lehum suu aÂṀmalihim vallahu la yehdil kavmel kafirÄḟn"
  9,38,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu ma lekum iza kÄḟyle lekumunfiru fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahis sakaltum ilel ard e radÄḟytum bil hayatid dunya minel ahÄḟrah fe ma metaul hayatid dunya minel ahÄḟrah fe ma metaul hayatid dunya fil ahÄḟrati illa kalÄḟl"
  9,39,"Illa tenfiru yuazzibkum azaben elÄḟmev ve yestebdil kavmen gayrakum ve la teduruhu seyÂṀa vallahu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  9,40,"Illa tensuruhu fe kad nesarahullahu iz ahracehullezÄḟne keferu saniyesneyni iz huma fil gayri iz yekul li sahÄḟbihÄḟ la tahzen innallahe meana fe enzelellahu sekÄḟnetehu aleyhi ve eyyedehu bi cunudil lem teravha ve ceale kelimetellezÄḟne keferus sufla ve kelimetullahi hiyel ulya vallahu azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  9,41,"Infiru hÄḟfafev ve sikalev ve cahidu bi emvalikum ve enfusikum fÄḟ sebÄḟlillah zalikum hayrul lekum in kuntum taÂṀlemun"
  9,42,"Lev kane aradan karÄḟbev ve seferan kasÄḟdel lettebeuke ve lakim beudet aleyhimus sukkah ve se yahlifune billahi levistetaÂṀna le haracna meakum yuhlikune enfusehum vallahu yaÂṀlemu innehum le kazibun"
  9,43,"Afallahu ank li me ezinte lehum hatta yetebeyyene lekellezÄḟne sadeku ve taÂṀlemel kazibÄḟn"
  9,44,"La yesteÂṀzinukellezÄḟne yuÂṀminune billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟri ey yucahidu bi emvalihim ve enfusihim vallahu alÄḟmum bil muttekÄḟyn"
  9,45,"Innema yesteÂṀzinukellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟri vertabet kulubuhum fe hum fÄḟ raybihim yeteraddedun"
  9,46,"Ve lev eradul huruce le eaddu lehu uddetev ve lakin kerihellahumbiasehum fe sebbetahum ve kÄḟylekÂṀudu meal kaÄḟdÄḟn"
  9,47,"Lev haracu fÄḟkum ma zadukum illa habalev ve le evdau hÄḟlalekum yebgunekumul fitneh ve fÄḟkum semmaune lehum vallahu alÄḟmum biz zalimÄḟn"
  9,48,"Lekadibtegavul fitnete min kablu ve kallebu lekel umura hatta cael hakku ve zahera emrullahi vehum karihun"
  9,49,"Ve minhum mey yekuluÂṀzel lÄḟ ve la teftinnÄḟ e la fil fitneti sekatu ve inne cehenneme le muhÄḟytatum bil kafirÄḟn"
  9,50,"In tusÄḟbke hasenetun tesuÂṀhum ve in tusÄḟbke musÄḟybetuy yekulu kad ehazna emrana min kablu ve yetevellev vehum ferihun"
  9,51,"Kul ley yusÄḟybena illa ma ketebellahu lena huve mevlana ve alellahi fel yetevekkelil muÂṀminun"
  9,52,"Kul hel terabbesune bina illa Äḟhdel husneyeyn ve nahnu neterabbesu bikum ey yusÄḟybekumullahu bi azabim min ÄḟndihÄḟ ev bi eydÄḟna fe terabbesu inna meakum muterabbisun"
  9,53,"Kul enfiku tavÂṀan ev kerhel len yutekabbele minkum innekum kuntum kavmen fasikÄḟyn"
  9,54,"Ve ma meneahum en tukbele minhum nefekatuhum illa ennehum keferu billahi ve bi rasulihÄḟ ve la yeÂṀtunes salate illa vehum kusala ve la yunfikune illa vehum karihun"
  9,55,"Fe la tuÂṀcibke emvaluhum ve la evladuhum innema yurÄḟdullahu li yuazzibehum biha fil hayatid dunya ve tezheka enfusuhm ve hum kafirun"
  9,56,"Ve yahlifune billahi innehum le minkum ve ma hum minkum ve lakinnehum kavmuy yefrakun"
  9,57,"Lev yecidune melceen ev megaratin ev muddehalel le vellev ileyhi vehum yecmehun"
  9,58,"Ve minhum mey yelmizuke fis sadekat fe in uÂṀtu minha radu ve il lem yuÂṀtav minha iza hum yeshatun"
  9,59,"Ve lev ennehum radu ma atahumlahu ve rasuluhu ve kalu hasbunallahu se yuÂṀtÄḟnellahu min fadlihÄḟ ye rasuluhu inna ilallahi ragÄḟbun"
  9,60,"Innemas sadekatu lil fukarai vel mesakÄḟni vel amilÄḟne aleyha vel muellefeti kulubuhum ve firrikabi vle garimÄḟne ve fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi vebnis sebÄḟl ferÄḟdatem minallah vallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  9,61,"Ve minhumullezÄḟne yuÂṀzunen nebiyye ve yekulune huve uzun kul uzunu hayril lekum yuÂṀminu billahi ve yuÂṀminu lil muÂṀminÄḟne ve rahmetul lillezÄḟne amenu minkum vellezÄḟne yuÂṀzune rasulellahi lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  9,62,"Yahlifune billahi lekum li yurdukum vallahu ve rasuluhu ehakku ey yurduhu in kanu muÂṀminÄḟn"
  9,63,"E lem yaÂṀlemu ennehu mey yuhadidillahe ve rasulehu fe enne lehu nara cehenneme haliden fÄḟha zalikel hÄḟzyul azÄḟym"
  9,64,"Yahzerul munafikune en tunezzele aleyhim suratun tunebbiuhum bi ma fÄḟ kulubihim kulistehziu innellahe muhricum ma tahzerun"
  9,65,"Ve lein seeltehum le yekulunne innema kunna nehudu ve nelÂṀab kul e billahi ve ayatihÄḟ ve rasulihÄḟ kuntum testehziun"
  9,66,"La taÂṀteziru kad kefartum baÂṀde Äḟmanikum in naÂṀfu an taifetim minkum nuazzib taifetem bi ennehum kanu mucrimÄḟn"
  9,67,"El munafikun vel munafikatu baÂṀduhum min baÂṀd yeÂṀmurune bil munkeri ve yenhevne anil maÂṀrufi ve yakbidune eydiyehum nesullahe fe nesiyehum innel munafikÄḟyne humul fasikun"
  9,68,"Veadellahul munafikÄḟyne vel munafikati vel kuffara nara cehenneme halidÄḟne fÄḟha hiye hasbuhum ve leanehumullah ve lehum azabum mukÄḟym"
  9,69,"KellezÄḟne min kablikum kanu esedde minkum kuvvetev ve eksera emvalev ve evlada festemteu bi halakÄḟhim festemtaÂṀtum bi halaÄḟkum kemestem teallazÄḟne min kablikum bi halakÄḟhum ve hudtum kellezÄḟ hadu ulaike habitat aÂṀmaluhum fid dunya vel ahÄḟrah ve ulaike humul hasirun"
  9,70,"E lem yeÂṀtihim nebullezÄḟne min kablihim kavmi nuhÄḟv ve adiv ve semude ve kavmi ibrahÄḟme ve ashabi medyene vel muÂṀtefikat etethum rusuluhum bil beyyinat fe ma kanellahu li yazlimehum ve lakin kanu enfusehum yazlimun"
  9,71,"Vel muÂṀminune vel muÂṀmiratu baÂṀduhum evliyau baÂṀd yeÂṀmurune bil maÂṀrufi ve yenhevne anil munkeri ve yukÄḟymunes salate ve yuÂṀtunez zekate ve yutÄḟyÂṀunellahe ve rasuleh ulaike se yerhamuhumullah innellaha azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  9,72,"Veadellahul muÂṀminÄḟne vel muÂṀminati cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha ve mesakine teyyibeten fÄḟ cennati adn ve rÄḟdvanum minallahi ekber zalike huvel fevzul azÄḟym"
  9,73,"Ya eyyuhen nebiyyu cahidil kuffara vel munafikÄḟyne vagluz aleyhim ve meÂṀvahum cehennem ve biÂṀsel mesÄḟyr"
  9,74,"Yahlifune billahi ma kalu ve le kad kalu kelimetel kufri ve keferu baÂṀde islamihim ve hemmu bi ma lem yenalu ve ma nekamu illa en agnahumullahu ve rasuluhu min fadlih fe iy yetubu yeku hayral lehum ve iy yetevellev yuazzibhumullahu azaben elÄḟmen fid dunya vel ahÄḟrah ve ma lehum fil erdÄḟ miv veliyyiv ve la nasÄḟyr"
  9,75,"Ve minhum men ahedellahe le in atana min fadlihÄḟ le nessaddekanne ve le nekunenne mines salihÄḟyn"
  9,76,"Felemma atahum min fadlihÄḟ behÄḟlu bihÄḟ ve tevellev ve hum muÂṀridun"
  9,77,"Fe aÂṀkabehum nifakan fÄḟ kulubihim ila yevmi yelkavnehu bi ma ahlefullahe ma veaduhu ve bi ma kanu yekzibun"
  9,78,"E lem yaÂṀlemu ennellahe yaÂṀlemu sirrahum ve necvahum ve ennellahe allamul guyub"
  9,79,"EllezÄḟne yelmizunel mutteavviÄḟyne minel muÂṀminÄḟne fis sadekati vellezÄḟne la yecidune illa cuhdehum fe yesharune minhum sehÄḟrallahu minhum ve lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  9,80,"Istagfir lehum ev la testagfir lehum in testagfir lehum sebÂṀÄḟyne merraten fe ley yagfirallahu lehum zalike bi ennehum keferu billahi ve rasulih vallahu la yehdil kavmel fasikÄḟyn"
  9,81,"Ferihal muhallefune bi makÂṀadihim hÄḟlafe rasulillahi ve kerehu ey yucahidu bi emvalihim ve enfusihim fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi ve kalu la tenfiru fil harr kul naru cehenneme esddu harra lev kanu yefkahun"
  9,82,"Fel yadhaku kalÄḟlev vel yebku kezÄḟra cezaem bi ma kanu yeksibun"
  9,83,"Fe ir raceakellahu ila taifetim minhum festeÂṀzenuke lil huruci fe kul len tahrucu meÄḟye ebedev ve len tukatilu meÄḟye aduvva innekum radÄḟytum bil kuudi evvele merratin fakÂṀudu meal halifÄḟn"
  9,84,"Ve la tusalli ala ehadim minhum mate ebedev ve la tekum ala kabrih innehum keferu billahi ve rasulihÄḟ ve matu ve hum fasikun"
  9,85,"Ve la tuÂṀcibke emvaluhum ve evladuhum innema yurÄḟdullahu ey yuazzibehum biha fid dunya ve tezheka enfusuhum ve hum kafirun"
  9,86,"Ve iza unzilet suratun en aminu billahi ve cahidu mea rasulihisteÂṀzeneke ulut tavli minhum ve kalu zerna nekum meal kaÄḟdÄḟn"
  9,87,"Radu bi ey yekunu meal havalifi ve tubia ala kulubihim fehum la yefkahun"
  9,88,"Lakinir rasulu vellezÄḟne amenu meahu cahedu bi emvalihim ve enfusihim ve ulaike lehumul hayratu ve ulaikehumul muflihun"
  9,89,"Eaddellahu lehum cennati tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha zalikel fevzul azÄḟym"
  9,90,"Ve cael muazzirune minel aÂṀrabi li yuÂṀzene lehum ve kaadellezÄḟne kezebullahe ve rasuleh se yusÄḟybullezÄḟne keferu minhum azabun elÄḟm"
  9,91,"Leyse aled duafai ve la alel merda ve la alellezÄḟne la yecidune me yunfikune haracun iza nesahu lillahi ve rasulih ma alel muhsinÄḟne min sebÄḟl vallahu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  9,92,"Ve la alellezÄḟne iza ma etevke li tahmilehum kulte la ecidu ma ahmilukum aleyhi tevellev ve aÂṀyunuhum tefÄḟdu mined demÂṀÄḟ hazenen ella yecidu ma yunfikun"
  9,93,"Innemes sebÄḟlu alellezÄḟne yesteÂṀzinuneke ve hum agniyaÂṀ radu bi ey yekunu meal havalifi ve tabeallahu ala kulubihim fehum la yaÂṀlemun"
  9,94,"YaÂṀtezirune ilykum iza racaÂṀtum ileyhim kul la taÂṀteziru len nuÂṀmine lekum kad nebbeenellahu min ahbarikum ve se yerallahu amelekum ve rasuluhu summe turaddune ila alimil gaybi ves sehadeti fe yunebbiukum bi ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  9,95,"Se yahlifune billahi lekum izenkalebtum ileyhim li tuÂṀridu anhum fe aÂṀridu anhum innehum ricsuv ve meÂṀvahum cehennem cezaem bi ma kanu yeksibun"
  9,96,"Yahlifune lekum li terdav anhum fe in terdav anhum fe innellahe la yerda anil kavmil fasikÄḟyn"
  9,97,"El aÂṀrabu eseddu kufrav ve nifakav ve ecderu ella yaÂṀlemu hudude ma enzelellahu ala rasulih vallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  9,98,"Ve minel aÂṀrabi mey yettehÄḟzu ma yunfiku magramev ve yeterabbesu bikumud devair aleyhim dairatus sevÂṀ vallahu semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  9,99,"Ve minel aÂṀrabi mey yuÂṀminu billahi vel yevmil ahÄḟri ve yettehÄḟzu ma yunfiku kurubatin Äḟndellahi ve salevatir rasul ela inneha kurbetul lehum se yudhÄḟluhumullahu fÄḟ rahmetih innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  9,100,"Ves sabikunel evvelune minel muhacirÄḟne vel ensari vellezÄḟnettebeuhum bi Äḟhsanir radÄḟyallahu anhum ve radu anhu ve eadde lehum cennatin tecrÄḟ tahtehel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha ebeda zalikel fevzul azÄḟym"
  9,101,"Ve mimmen havlekum minel aÂṀrabi munafikun ve min ehlil medÄḟneti meradu alen nifakÄḟ la taÂṀlemuhum nahnu naÂṀlemuhum se nuazzibuhum merrateyni summe yuraddune ila azabin azÄḟym"
  9,102,"Ve aharunaÂṀterafu bi zunubbihim haletu amelen salihav ve ahara seyyia asellahu ey yetube aleyhim innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  9,103,"Huz min emvalihim sadekaten tutahhiruhum ve tuzekkÄḟhim biha ve salli aleyhim inne salateke sekenul lehum vallahu semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  9,104,"E lem yaÂṀlemu ennellahe huve yakbelut tevbete an ÄḟbadihÄḟ ve yeÂṀhuzus sadekati ve ennellahe huvet tevvabur rahÄḟym"
  9,105,"Ve kulÄḟÂṀmelu fe se yerallahu amelekum ve rasuluhu vel muÂṀminun ve se turaddune ila alimil gaybi ves sehadeti fe yunebbiukum bi ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  9,106,"Ve aharune murcevne li emrillahi imma yuazzibuhum ve imma yetubu aleyhim vallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  9,107,"VellezÄḟnettehazu mesciden dÄḟrarav ve kufrav ve tefrÄḟkam beynel muÂṀminÄḟne ve irsadel li men habellahe ve rasulehu min kabl ve le yahlifunne in eradna illel husna vallahu yeshedu innehum le kazibun"
  9,108,"La tekum fÄḟhi ebeda le mescidun ussise alet takva min evveli yevmin ehakku en tekume fÄḟh fÄḟhi ricaluy yuhÄḟbbune ey yetetahheru vallahu yuhÄḟbbul muttahhirÄḟn"
  9,109,"E fe men essese bunyanehu ala katva minallahi ve rÄḟdvanin hayrun em men essese bunyanehu ala sefacurufin harin fenhara bihÄḟ fÄḟ nari cehennem vallahu la yehdil havmez zalimÄḟn"
  9,110,"La yezalu bunyanuhumlezÄḟ benev rÄḟbeten fÄḟ kulubihim illa en tekattaa kulubuhum yallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  9,111,"Innellahestera minel muÂṀminÄḟne enfushehum ve emvalehum bi enne lehumul cenneh yukatilune fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi fe yaktulune ve yuktelune vaÂṀden aleyhi hakkan fit tevrati vel incÄḟli vel kurÂṀan ve men evfa bi ahdihÄḟ festebsiru bi beyÂṀÄḟkumlezÄḟ bayÂṀtum bih ve zalike humvel fevzul azÄḟym"
  9,112,"Ettaibunel abidunel hamidunes saihuner rakiunes sacidunel amirune bil maÂṀrufi ven nahune anil mumkeri vel hafizune li hududillah ve bessiril muÂṀminÄḟn"
  9,113,"Ma kane lin nebiyyi vellezÄḟne amenu ey yestagfiru lil musrikÄḟne velev kanu ulÄḟ kurba mim baÂṀdi ma tebeyyene lehum ennehum ashabul cehÄḟym"
  9,114,"Ve ma kanestigfaru ibrahÄḟme li ebÄḟhi illa am mevÂṀÄḟdetiv veadeha iyyah felemma tebeyyene lehu ennehu aduvvul lilhahi teberrae minh inne ibrahÄḟme le evvahun halÄḟm"
  9,115,"Ve ma kanellahu li yudÄḟlle kavmem baÂṀde iz hedahum hatta yubeyyine lehum ma yettekun innellahe bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  9,116,"Innellahe lehu mulkus semavati vel ard yuhyÄḟ ve yumÄḟt ve ma lekum min dunillahi miv veliyyiv ve la nasÄḟyr"
  9,117,"Le kad tabellahu alen nebiyyi vel muhacirÄḟne vel ensarillezÄḟnettebeuhu fÄḟ saatil usrati mim baÂṀdi ma kade yezÄḟgu kulubu ferÄḟkÄḟm minhum summe tabe aleyhim innehu bihim raufur rahÄḟym"
  9,118,"Ve ales selasetillezÄḟne hulifu hatta iza dakat aleyhimul erdu bi ma rahubet ve dakat aleyhim enfusuhum ve zannu el la melcee minallahi illa ileyh summe tabe aleyhim li yetubu innellahe huvet tevvabur rahÄḟym"
  9,119,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenuttekullahe ve kunu meas sadikÄḟyn"
  9,120,"Ma kane li ehlil medÄḟneti ve men havlehum minel aÂṀrabi ey yetehallefu ar rasulillahi ve la yergabu bi enfusihim an nefsih zalike bi ennehum la yusÄḟybuhum zameuv ve la nesabu v ve la mahmesatun fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi ve la yetaune mevtÄḟey yegÄḟyzul kuffara ve la yenalune min aduvvin neylen illa kutibe lehum bihÄḟ amelun salÄḟh innellahe la yudÄḟyÂṀu ecral muhsinÄḟn"
  9,121,"Ve la yunfikune nefekaten sagÄḟyratev ve la kebÄḟratev ve la kebÄḟratev ve la yaktaune vadiyen illa kutibe lehum li yecziyehumullahu ahsene ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  9,122,"Ve ma kanel muÂṀminune li yenfiru kaffeh fe lev la nefera min kulli firkatim minhum taifetul li yetefekkahu fid dÄḟni ve li yunziru kavmehum iza raceu ileyhim leallehum yahzerun"
  9,123,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu katilullezÄḟne yalunekum minel kuffari vel yecidu fÄḟkum gÄḟlzah vaÂṀlemu ennallahe meal muttekÄḟyn"
  9,124,"Ve iza ma unzilet zuratun fe minhum mey yekulu eyyukum zadethu hazihÄḟ Äḟmana fe emmellezÄḟne amenu fe zadethum Äḟmanev vehum yestebsirun"
  9,125,"Ve emmellezÄḟne fÄḟ kulubihim meradnu fe zadethum ricsen ila ricsihim ve matu ve hum kafirun"
  9,126,"E ve la yeravne ennehum yuftenune fÄḟ kulli amim merraten ev merrateyni summe la yetubune ve la hum yezzekkerun"
  9,127,"Ve iza ma unzilet suratun nezara baÂṀduhum ila baÂṀd hel yerakum min ehadin summensarafu sarafellahu kulubehum bi ennehum kavmul la yefkahun"
  9,128,"Le kad caekum rasulum min enfusikum azÄḟzun aleyhi ma anittum harÄḟsun aleykum bil muÂṀminÄḟne raufur rahÄḟym"
  9,129,"Fe in tevellev fe kul hasbiyallahu la ilahe illa hu aleyhi tevekkeltu ve huve rabbul arsil azÄḟym"
  10,8,"Ulaike meÂṀvahumun naru bima kanu yeksibun"
  10,9,"InnellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati yehdÄḟhim rabbuhum bi Äḟmanihim tecrÄḟ min tahtihimul enharu fÄḟ cennatin neÄḟym"
  10,10,"DaÂṀvahum fÄḟha subhanekellahumme ve tehÄḟyyetuhum fÄḟha selam ve ahÄḟru daÂṀvahum enil hamdu lillahi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  10,11,"Ve lev yuaccilullahu lin nasis serratÄḟÂṀcalehum bil hayri le kudiye ileyhim eceluhum fe nezerullezÄḟne la yercune likaena fÄḟ tugyanihim yaÂṀmehun"
  10,12,"Ve iza messel insaned durru deanna li cembihÄḟ ev kaÄḟden ev kaima felemma kesefna anhu durrahu merra keel lem yedÂṀuna ila durrim messeh kezalike zuyyine lil musrifÄḟne ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  10,13,"Ve le kad ehleknel kurune min kabilkum lemma zalemu ve caethum rusuluhum bil beyyinati ve ma kanu li yuÂṀminu kezalike neczil kavmel mucrimÄḟn"
  10,14,"Summe cealnakum halaife fil erdÄḟ mim baÂṀdihim li nenzura keyfe taÂṀmelun"
  10,15,"Ve iza tutla aleyhim ayatuna beyyinatin kalellezÄḟne la yercune likaeneÂṀti bi kurÂṀanin gayri haza ev beddilh kul ma yekunu lÄḟ en ubeddilehu min tilkai nefsÄḟ in ettebiu illa ma yuha ileyy innÄḟ ehafu in asaytu rabbÄḟ azabe yevmin azÄḟym"
  10,16,"Kul lev saellahu ma televtuhu aleykum ve la edrakum bihÄḟ fe kad lebistu fÄḟkum umuram min kablih e fela taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  10,17,"Fe men azlemu mimmeniftera alellahi keziben ev kezzebe vi ayatih innehu la yuflihul mucrimun"
  10,18,"Ve yaÂṀbudune min dunillahi ma la yedurruhum ve la yenfeuhum ve yekulune haulai sufeauna Äḟndellah kul etunebbiunellahe bima la yaÂṀlemu fis semavati ve la fil ard subhanehu ve teala amma yasrikun"
  10,19,"Ve ma kanen nasu illa ummetev vahÄḟdeten fahtelefu ve lev la kelimetun sebekat mir rabbike le kudiye beynehum fÄḟma fÄḟhi yahtelifun"
  10,20,"Ve yekulune lev la unzile aleyhi ayetum mir rabbih fe kul innemel gaybu lillahi fentezÄḟru innÄḟ meakum minel muntezÄḟrÄḟn"
  10,21,"Ve iza ezaknen nase rahmetem mim baÂṀdi darrae messethum iza lehum merun fÄḟ ayatina kulillahu esrau mekra inne rusulena yektubune ma temkurun"
  10,22,"HuvellezÄḟ yuseyyirukum fil berri vel bahr hatta iza kuntum fil fulk ve cerayne bihim bi rÄḟyhÄḟn tayyibetiv ve ferihu biha caetha rÄḟhun asÄḟfuv ve caehumul mevcu min kulli mekaniv ve zannu ennehum uhÄḟyta bihim deavullahe muhlisÄḟyne lehud dÄḟn lein enceytena min hazihÄḟ le nekunenne mines sakirÄḟn"
  10,23,"Felemma encahum izahum yebgune fil erdÄḟ bi gayril hakk ya eyyuhennasu innema bagyukum ala enfusikum metaal hayatid dunya summe ileyna merciukum fe nunebbiukum bima kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  10,24,"Innema meselul hayatid dunya ke main enzelnahu mines semai fahteleta bihÄḟ nebatul erdÄḟ mimma yeÂṀkulun nasu vel enÂṀam hatta iza ehazetil erdu zuhrufeha vezzeyyenet ve zanne ehluha ennehum kadirune aleyha etaha emruna leylen ev neharan fe cealnaha hasÄḟyden ke el lem tagne bil ems kezalike nufessÄḟlul ayati li kavmiy yetefekkerun"
  10,25,"Vallahu yedÂṀu ila daris selam ve yehdÄḟ mey yesau ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  10,26,"LillezÄḟne ahsenul husna ve ziyadeh ve la yerheku vucuhehum kateruv ve la zilleh ulaike ashabul cenneh hum fÄḟha halidun"
  10,27,"VellezÄḟne kesebus seyyiati cezau seyyietim bi misliha ve terhekuhum zilleh ma lehum minellahi min asÄḟm keennema ugsiyet vucuhuhum kÄḟtaam minel leyli muslima ulaike ashabun nar hum fÄḟha halidun"
  10,28,"Ve yevme nahsuruhum cemÄḟan summe nekulu lillezÄḟne esraku mekanekum entum ve surakaukum fe zeyyelna beynehum ve kale surakauhum ma kuntum iyyana taÂṀbudun"
  10,29,"Fe kefa billahi sehÄḟdem beynena ve beynekum in kunna an Äḟbadetikum legafilÄḟn"
  10,30,"Hunalike teblu kullu nefsim ma eslefet ve ruddu ilellahi mevlahumul hakkÄḟ ve dalle anhum ma kanu yefterun"
  10,31,"Kul mey yerzukukum mines semai vel erdÄḟ emmey yemlikus semÂṀa vel ebsara ve mey yuhricul hayye minle miyyiti ve yuhricul meyyite minel hayyi ve mey yudebbirul emr fe seyekulunellah fe kul efela tettekun"
  10,32,"Fe zalikumullahu rabbukumulhakk fe maza ba7del hakkÄḟ illed dalal fe enna tusrafun"
  10,33,"Kezalike hakkat kelimetu rabbike alellezÄḟne feseku ennehum la yuÂṀminun"
  10,34,"Kul hel min surakaikum mey yebdeul halka summe yuÄḟyduh kulillahu yebdeul halku summe yuÄḟyduhu fe enna tuÂṀfekun"
  10,35,"Kul hel min surakaikum mey yehdÄḟ ilel hakk kulillahu yehdÄḟ lil hakk e fe mey yehdÄḟ ilel hakkÄḟ ehakku ey yuttebea emmel la yehiddÄḟ illa ey yuhda fe ma lekum keyfe tahkumun"
  10,36,"Ve ma yettebiu ekseruhum illa zanna innez zanne la yugnÄḟ minel hakkÄḟ seyÂṀa innellahe alÄḟmum bima yefÂṀalun"
  10,37,"Ve ma kane hazel kurÂṀanu ey yuftera min dunillahi ve lakin tasdÄḟkallezÄḟ beyne yedeyhi ve tefsÄḟylel kitabi la raybe fÄḟhi mir rabbil alemÄḟn"
  10,38,"Em yekulunefterah kul feÂṀtu bi suratim mislihÄḟ vedÂṀu menistetaÂṀtum min dunillahi in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  10,39,"Bel kezzebu bima lem yuhÄḟytu bi ÄḟlmihÄḟ ve lemma yeÂṀtihim teÂṀvÄḟluh kezalike kezzebellezÄḟne min kablihim fenzur keyfe kane akÄḟbetuz zalimÄḟn"
  10,40,"Ve minhum mey yuÂṀminu bihÄḟ ve minhum mel la yuÂṀminu bih ve rubbuke aÂṀlemu bil mufsidÄḟn"
  10,41,"Ve in kezzebuke fe kul lÄḟ amelÄḟ ve lekum amelukum entum berÄḟune mimma aÂṀmelu ve ene berÄḟum mimma taÂṀmelun"
  10,42,"Ve minhum mey yestemiune ileyk e fe ente tusmius summe ve lev kanu la yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  10,43,"Ve minhum mey yenzuru ileyk e fe ente tehdil umye ve lev kanu la yubsÄḟrun"
  10,44,"Innellahe la yazlimun nase seyÂṀev ve lakinnen nase enfusehum yazlimun"
  10,45,"Ve yevme yahsuruhum keel lem yelbesu illa saatem minen nehar iyetearafune beynehum kad hasirallezÄḟne kezzebu bi likaillahi ve ma kanu muhtedÄḟn"
  10,46,"Ve imma nuriyenneke baÂṀdallezÄḟ neÄḟduhum ev neteveffeyenneke fe ileyna merciuhum summellahu sehÄḟdun ala ma yefÂṀalun"
  10,47,"Ve likulli ummetir rasul fe iza cae rasuluhum kudiye beynehum bil kÄḟstÄḟ ve hum la yuzlemun"
  10,48,"Ve yekulune meta hazel vaÂṀdu in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  10,49,"Kul la emliku li nefsÄḟ darrav ve la nefÂṀan illa ma saellah likulli ummetinecel iza cae eceluhum fe la yesteÂṀhÄḟrune saatev ve la yestakdimun"
  10,50,"Kul eraeytum in etakum azabuhu beyaten ev neharam maza yestaÂṀcilu minhul mucrimun"
  10,51,"E summe iza ma vekaa amentum bih al ane ve kad kuntum bihÄḟ testaÂṀcilun"
  10,52,"Summe kÄḟyle lillezÄḟne zalemu zuku azabel huld hel tuczevne illa bima kuntum teksibun"
  10,53,"Ve yestembiuneke ehakkun hu kul Äḟ ve rabbÄḟ innehu lehakkuv ve ma entum bi muÂṀcizÄḟn"
  10,54,"Ve lev enne li kulli nefsin zalemet ma fil erdÄḟ leftedet bih ve eserrun nedamete lemma raevul azab ve kudiye beynehum bil kÄḟstÄḟ ve hum la yuzlemun"
  10,55,"E la inne lillahi ma fis semavati vel ard e la inne vaÂṀdellahi hakkuv ve lakinne ekserahum la yaÂṀlemun"
  10,56,"Huve yuhyÄḟ ve yumÄḟtu ve ileyhi turceun"
  10,57,"Ya eyyuhen nasu kad caetkum mevÂṀÄḟzatum mir rabbikum ve sifaul lima fis suduri ve hudev ve rahmetul lil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  10,58,"Kul bi fadlillahi ve bi rahmetihÄḟ fe bi zalike felyefrahu huve hayrum mimma yecmeun"
  10,59,"Kul e raeytum ma enzelellahu lekum mir rizkÄḟn fe cealtum minhu haramev ve halala kul allahu ezine lekum em alellahi tefterun"
  10,60,"Ve ma zannullezÄḟne yefterune alellahil kezibe yevmel kÄḟyameh innellahe lezu fadlin alen nasi ve lakinne ekserahum la yeskurun"
  10,61,"Ve ma tekunu fÄḟ seÂṀniv ve ma tetlu minhu min kurÂṀaniv ve la taÂṀmelune min amelin illa kunna aleykum suhuden iz tufÄḟdune fÄḟh ve ma yaÂṀzubu ar rabbike mim miskali zirratin fil erdÄḟ ve la fis semai ve la asgara min zalike ve la ekbera illa fÄḟ kitabim mubÄḟn"
  10,62,"E la inne evliyaellahi la havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  10,63,"EllezÄḟne amenu ve kanu yettekun"
  10,64,"Lehumul busra fil hayated dunya ve fil ahÄḟrah la tebdÄḟle li kelimatillah zalike huvel fevzul azÄḟym"
  10,65,"Ve la yahzunke kavluhum innel Äḟzzete lillahi cemÄḟa huves semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  10,66,"E la inne lillahi men fis semavati ve men fil ard ve ma yettebiullezÄḟne yedÂṀune min dunillahi surakaÂṀ iy yettebiune illez zanne ve in hum illa yahrusun"
  10,67,"HuvellezÄḟ ceale lekumul leyle li zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yesmeun"
  10,68,"Kaluttehazellahu veleden subhaneh huvel ganiyy lehu ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard in Äḟndekum min sultanim bi haza e tekulune alellahi ma la taÂṀlemun"
  10,69,"Kul innillezÄḟne yefterune alellahil kezibe la yuflihun"
  10,70,"Metaun fid dunya summe ileyna merciuhum summe nuzÄḟkuhumul azabes sedÄḟde bima kanu yekfurun"
  10,71,"Vetlu aleyhim nebee nuh iz kale li kavmihÄḟ ya kavmi in kane kebura aleykum mekamÄḟ ve tezkÄḟrÄḟÄḟ bi ayatillahi fe alellahi tevekkeltu fe ecmiu emrakum ve surakaekum summe la yekun emrukum ve surakaekum summe la yekun emrukum aleykum gummeten summakdu ileyye ve la tunzÄḟrun"
  10,72,"Fe in tevelleytum fe ma seeltukum mir ecrv in ecriye illa alellahi ve umirtu en ekune minel muslimÄḟn"
  10,73,"Fe kezzebuhu fe necceynahu ve min meahu fil fulki ve cealnahum halaife ve agraknellezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina fenzur keyfe kane akÄḟbetul munzerÄḟn"
  10,74,"Summe beasna mim baÂṀdihÄḟ rusulen ila kavmihim fe cauhum bil beyyinati fe ma kanu li yuÂṀminu bima kezzebu bihÄḟ min kabl kezalike natbeu ala kulubil muÂṀtedÄḟn"
  10,75,"Summe beasna mim baÂṀdihim musa ve harune ila firÂṀavne ve meleihÄḟ bi ayatina festekberu ve kanu kavmem mucrimÄḟn"
  10,76,"Fe lemma caehumul hakku min Äḟndina kalu inne haza le sÄḟhrum mubÄḟn"
  10,77,"Kale musa e tekulune lil hakkÄḟ lemma caekum e sÄḟhrun haza ve la yuflihus sahÄḟrun"
  10,78,"Kalu e ciÂṀtena li telfitena amma vecedna aleyhi abaena ve tekune lekumel kibriyau fil ard ve ma nahnu lekuma bi muÂṀminÄḟn"
  10,79,"Ve kale firÂṀavnuÂṀtunÄḟ bi kulli sahÄḟrin alÄḟm"
  10,80,"Felemma caes seharatu kale lehum musa elku ma entum mulkun"
  10,81,"Fe lemma elkav kale musa ma ciÂṀtum bihis sÄḟhr innellahe seyubtÄḟluh innellahe la yuslihu amelel mufsidÄḟn"
  10,82,"Ve yuhÄḟkkullahul hakka bi kelimatihÄḟ ve lev kerihel mucrimun"
  10,83,"Fe ma amene li musa illa zurriyyetum min kavmihÄḟ ala havfim min firÂṀavne ve meleihim ey yeftinehum ve inne firÂṀavne lealin fil ard ve innehu le minel musrifÄḟn"
  10,84,"Ve kale musa ya kavmi in kuntum amentum billahi fealleyhi tevekkelu in kuntum muslimÄḟn"
  10,85,"Fe kalu alellahi tevekkelna rabbena la tecÂṀalna fitnetel lil kavmiz zalimÄḟn"
  10,86,"Ve neccina bi rahmetike minel kavmil kafirun"
  10,87,"Ve evhayna ila musa ve ehÄḟyhi en tebevvea likavmikuma bi mÄḟsra buyutev vecÂṀalu buyutekum kÄḟbletev ve ekÄḟymus salah ve bessiril muÂṀminÄḟn"
  10,88,"Ve kale musa rabbena inneke ateyte firÂṀavne ve melehu zÄḟnetev ve emvalen fil hayetid dunya rabbena li yudÄḟllu an sebÄḟlik rabbenatmis ala emvalihim vesdud ala kulubihim fe la yuÂṀminu hatta yeravul azabel elÄḟm"
  10,89,"Kale kad ucÄḟbet daÂṀvetukuma festekÄḟyma ve la tettebianni sebÄḟlellezÄḟne la yaÂṀlemun"
  10,90,"Ve cavezna bi benÄḟ israilil bahra fe etbeahum firÂṀavnu ve cunuduhu bagyev ve adva hatta iza edrakehul garaku kale amentu ennehu la ilahe illezÄḟ amenet bihÄḟ benu israile ve ene minel muslimÄḟn"
  10,91,"Al ane ve kad asayte kablu ve kunte minel mufsidÄḟn"
  10,92,"Fel yevme nuneccÄḟke bi bedenike li tekune limen halfeke ayeh ve inne kesÄḟram minen nasi an ayatina le gafilun"
  10,93,"Ve le kad bevveÂṀna benÄḟ israÄḟle mubevvee sÄḟdkÄḟv ve razaknahum minet tayyibat femahtelefu hatta caehumul Äḟlm inne rabbeke yakdÄḟy beynehum yevmel kÄḟyameti fÄḟma kanu fÄḟhi yahtelifun"
  10,94,"Fe in kunte fÄḟ sekkim mimma enzelna ileyke fesÂṀelillezÄḟne yakraunel kitab min kablike le kad caekel hakku mir rabbike fe la tekununne minel mumterÄḟn"
  10,95,"Ve la tekunenne minellezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatillahi fe tekune minel hasirÄḟn"
  10,96,"InnellezÄḟne hakkat aleyhim kelimetu rabbike la yuÂṀminun"
  10,97,"Ve lev caethum kullu ayetin hatta yeravul azabel elÄḟm"
  10,98,"Fe lev la kanet karyetun amenet fe nefealna Äḟmanuha illa kavme yunus lemma amenu kesefna anhum azabel hÄḟzyi fil hayatid dunya ve mettaÂṀnahum ila hÄḟyn"
  10,99,"Ve lev sae rabbuke le amene men fil erdÄḟ kulluhum cemÄḟa e fe ente tukrihun nase hatta yekunu muÂṀminÄḟn"
  10,100,"Ve ma kane li nefsin en tuÂṀmine illa bi iznillah ve yecÂṀalur ricse alellezÄḟne la yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  10,101,"Kulinzuru maza fis semavati vel ard ve ma tugnil ayatu ven nuzuru an kavmil la yuÂṀminun"
  10,102,"Fe hel yentezÄḟrune illa misle eyyamillezÄḟne halev min kablihim kul fentezuru innÄḟ meakum minel muntezÄḟrÄḟn"
  10,103,"Summe nuneccÄḟ rusulena vellezÄḟne amenu kezalik hakkan aleyna nuncil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  10,104,"Kul ya eyyuhen nasu in kuntum fÄḟ sekkim min dÄḟnÄḟ fe la aÂṀbudullezÄḟne taÂṀbudune min dunillahi ve lakin aÂṀbudullahellezÄḟ yeteveffakum ve umirtu en ekune minel muÂṀminun"
  10,105,"Ve en ekÄḟm vecheke lid dÄḟni hanÄḟfa ve la tekunenne minel musrikÄḟn"
  10,106,"Ve la tedÂṀu min dunillahi ma la yenfeuke ve la yedurruk fe in fealte fe inneke izem minez zalimÄḟn"
  10,107,"Ve iy yemseskellahu bi durrin fe la kasife lehu illa hu ve iy yuridke bi hayrin fe la radde li fadlih yusÄḟybu bihÄḟ mey yesau min Äḟbadih ve huvel gafurur rahÄḟym"
  10,108,"Kul ya eyyuhen nasu kad caekumul hakku mir rabbikum fe menihteda fe innema yehtedÄḟ li nefsih ve men dalle fe innema yehtedÄḟ li nefsih ve men dalle fe innema yedÄḟllu aleyha ve ma ene aleykum bi vekÄḟl"
  10,109,"VettebÄḟÂṀma yuha ileyke vasbir hatta yahkumellah ve huve hayrul hakimÄḟn"
  11,8,"Ve le in ehharna anhumul azabe ila ummetim maÂṀdudetil le yekulunne ma yahbisuh e la yevme yeÂṀtÄḟhim leyse masrufen anhum ve haka bihim ma kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  11,9,"Ve lein ezaknel insane minna rahmeten summe nezaÂṀnaha minh innehu leyeusun kefur"
  11,10,"Ve lein ezaknahu naÂṀmae baÂṀde darrae messethu le yekulenne zehebes seyyiatu annÄḟ innehu le ferihun fe hur"
  11,11,"IllellezÄḟne saberu ve amilus salihat ulaike lehum magfiratuv ve ecrun kebÄḟr"
  11,12,"Fe lealleke tarikum baÂṀda ma yuha ileyke ve daikum bihÄḟ sadruke ey yekulu lev la unzile aleyhi kenzun ev cae meahu melek innema ente nezÄḟr vallahu ala kulli seyÂṀiv vekÄḟl"
  11,13,"Em yekulunefterah kul feÂṀtu bi asri suverim mislihÄḟ mufterayativ vedÂṀu menistetaÂṀtum min dunillahi in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  11,14,"Fe illem yestecÄḟbu lekum faÂṀlemu ennema unzile bi Äḟlmillahi ve el la ilahe illa hu fe hel entum muslimun"
  11,15,"Men kane yurÄḟdul hayated dunya ve zÄḟneteha nuveffi ileyhim aÂṀmalehum fÄḟha ve hum fÄḟha la yubhasun"
  11,16,"UlaikellezÄḟne leyse lehum fil ahÄḟrati illen nar ve habita ma saneu fÄḟha ve batÄḟlum ma kanu yaÂṀmÂṀlun"
  11,17,"E fe men kane ala beyyinetim mir rabbihÄḟ ve yetluhu sahidum minhu ve min kablihÄḟ kitabu musa imamev ve rahmeh ulaike yuÂṀminune bih ve mey yekfur bihÄḟ minel ahzabi fen naru mevÂṀÄḟduh fe la teku fÄḟ miryetim minhu innehul hakku mir rabbike ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yuÂṀminun"
  11,18,"Ve men azlemu mimmeniftera alellahi keziba ulaike yuÂṀradune ala rabbihim ve yekulul eshadu haulaillezÄḟne kezebu ala rabbihim e la laÂṀnetullahi alez zalimÄḟn"
  11,19,"EllezÄḟne yesuddune an sebÄḟlillahi ve yebguneha Äḟveca ve hum bil ahÄḟrati hum kafirun"
  11,20,"Ulaike lem yekunu muÂṀcizÄḟne fil erdÄḟ ve ma kane lehum min dunillahi min evliyaÂṀ yudaafu lehumul azabv ma kanu yestetÄḟyÂṀunes semÂṀa ve ma kanu yubsÄḟrun"
  11,21,"UlaikellezÄḟne hasiru enfusehum ve dalle anhum ma kanu yefterun"
  11,22,"La cerame ennehum fil ahÄḟrati humul ahserun"
  11,23,"InnellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati ve ahbetu ila rabbihim ulaike ashabul cenneh hum fÄḟha halidun"
  11,24,"Meselul ferÄḟkayni kel aÂṀma vel esammi vel baÄḟyri ves semiyÂṀ hel yesteviyani mesela e fe la tezekkerun"
  11,25,"Ve le kad erselna nuhan ila kamihÄḟ innÄḟ lekum nezÄḟrum mubÄḟn"
  11,26,"El la taÂṀbudu illellah innÄḟ ehafu aleykum azabe yevmin elÄḟm"
  11,27,"Fe kalel meleullezÄḟne keferu min kavmihÄḟ ma nerake illa beseram mislena ve ma neraket tebeake ilellezÄḟne hum eraziluna bediyer raÂṀy ve ma nera lekum aleyna min fadlim bel nezunukum kazibÄḟn"
  11,28,"Kale ya kavmi eraeytum in kuntu ala beyyinetim mir rabbÄḟ ve atanÄḟ rahmetem min ÄḟndihÄḟ fe ummiyet aleykum e nulzimukumuha ve entum leha karihun"
  11,29,"Ve ya kavmi la esÂṀelukum aleyhi mala in ecriye illa alellahi ve ma ene bi taridillezÄḟne amenu innehum mulaku rabbihim ve laninnÄḟ erakum kavmen techelun"
  11,30,"Ve ya kavmi mey yensurunÄḟ minellahi in taredtuhum e fela tezekkerun"
  11,31,"Ve la ekulu lekum ÄḟndÄḟ hazinullahi ve la aÂṀlemul gaybe ve la ekulu innÄḟ melekuv ve la ekulu lillezÄḟne tezderÄḟ aÂṀyunukum ley yuÂṀtiyehumullahu hayra allahu aÂṀlemu bima fÄḟ enfusihim innÄḟ izel le minez zalimÄḟn"
  11,32,"Kalu ya nuhu kad cadeltena fe ekserte cidalena feÂṀtina bima teÄḟduna in kunte mines sadikÄḟyn"
  11,33,"Kale innema yeÂṀtÄḟkum bihillahu in sae ve ma entum bi muÂṀcizÄḟn"
  11,34,"Ve la yenfeukum nushÄḟy in eradtu en ensaha lekum in kanellahu yurÄḟdu ey yugviyekum huve rabbukum ve ileyhi turceun"
  11,35,"Em yekulunefterah kul inifteraytuhu fe aleyye icramÄḟ ve ene birÄḟum mimma tucrimun"
  11,36,"Ve uhÄḟye ila nuhÄḟn ennehu ley yuÂṀmine min kavmike illa men kad amene fe la tebteis bima kanu yefÂṀalun"
  11,37,"VasneÄḟl fulke bi aÂṀyunina ve vahyina ve la tuhatÄḟbnÄḟ fillezÄḟne zalemu innehum mugrakun"
  11,38,"Ve yasneul fulke ve kullema merra aleyhi meleum min kavmihÄḟ sehÄḟru minh kale in tesharu minna fe inna nesharu minkum kema tesharun"
  11,39,"Fe sevfe taÂṀlemune mey yeÂṀtÄḟhi azabuy yuhzÄḟhi ve yehÄḟllu aleyhi azabum mukÄḟym"
  11,40,"Hatta iza cae emruna ve farat tennuru kulnahmil fÄḟha min kullin zevceynisneyni ve ehleke illa men sebeka aleyhil kavlu ve men amen ve ma amene meahu illa kalÄḟl"
  11,41,"Ve kalerkebu fÄḟha bismillahi mecraha ve mursaha inne rabbÄḟ le gafurur rahÄḟym"
  11,42,"Ve hiye tecrÄḟ bihim fÄḟ mevcin kel cibali ve nada nuhunibnehu ve kane fÄḟ maÂṀziliy ya buneyyerkem meana ve la tekum meal kafirÄḟn"
  11,43,"Kale seavÄḟ ila cebeliy yaÂṀsÄḟmunÄḟ minel maÂṀ kale la asÄḟmel yevme min emrillahi illa mer rahÄḟm ve hale beynehumel mevcu fe kane minel mugrakÄḟyn"
  11,44,"Ve kÄḟyle ya erdubleÄḟy maeki ve ya semau akliÄḟy ve gÄḟdal mau ve kudÄḟyel emru vestevet alel cudiyyi ve kÄḟyle buÂṀdel lil kavmiz zalimÄḟn"
  11,45,"Ve nada nuhur rabbehu fe kale rabbi innebnÄḟ min ehlÄḟ ve inne vaÂṀdekel hakku ve ente ahkemul hakimÄḟn"
  11,46,"Kale ya nuhu innehu leyse min ehlik innehu amelun gayru salihÄḟn fe la tesÂṀelni ma leyse leke bihÄḟ Äḟlm innÄḟ eÄḟzuke en ketune minel cahilÄḟn"
  11,47,"Kale rabbi innÄḟ euzu bike en esÂṀeleke ma leyse lÄḟ bihÄḟ Äḟlm ve illa tagfirlÄḟ ve terhamnÄḟ ekum minel hasirÄḟn"
  11,48,"KÄḟyle ya nuhuhbÄḟt bi selamim minna ve berakatin aleyke ve ala umemim mimmem meak ve umemun senumettiuhum summe yemessuhum minna azabun elÄḟm"
  11,49,"Tilke min embail gaybi nuhÄḟyha ileyk ma kunte taÂṀlemuhu ente ve la kavmuke min kabli haza fasbirv innel akÄḟbete lil muttekÄḟyn"
  11,50,"Ve ila adin ehahum huda kale ya kavmÄḟÂṀbudullahe ma lekum min ilahin gayruh in entum illa mufterun"
  11,51,"Ya kavmi la esÂṀelukum aleyhi ecra in ecriye illa alellezÄḟ fetaranÄḟ e fe la taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  11,52,"Ve ya kavmistagfiru rabbekum summe tubu ileyhi yursilis semae aleykum midrarav ve yezidkum kuvveten ila kuvvetikum ve la tetevellev mucrimÄḟn"
  11,53,"Kalu ya hudu ma ciÂṀtena bi beyyinetiv ve ma nahnu bi tarikÄḟ alihetina an kavlike ve ma nahnu leke bi muÂṀminÄḟn"
  11,54,"In nekulu illaÂṀterake baÂṀdu alilhetina bi suÂṀ kale innÄḟ ushidullahe veshedu ennÄḟ berÄḟum mimma tusrikun"
  11,55,"Min dunihÄḟ fekÄḟdunÄḟ cemÄḟan summe la tunzÄḟrun"
  11,56,"InnÄḟ tevekkeltu alellahi rabbÄḟ ve rabbikum ma min dabbetin illa huve ahÄḟzum binasÄḟyetiha inne rabbÄḟ ala sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  11,57,"Fe in tevellev fe kad eblagtukum ma ursiltu bihÄḟ ileykum ve yestahlifu rabbÄḟ kavmen gayrakum ve la tedurrunehu seyÂṀa inne rabbÄḟ ala kulli seyÂṀin hafÄḟyz"
  11,58,"Ve lemma cae emruna necceyna hudev vellezÄḟne amenu meahu bi rahmetim minna ve ncceynahum min azabin galÄḟyz"
  11,59,"Ve tilke adun cehadu bi ayati rabbihim ve asav rusulehu vettebeu emra kulli cebbarin anÄḟd"
  11,60,"Ve utbiu fÄḟ hazihid dunya laÂṀnetev ve yevmel kÄḟyameh e la inne aden keferu rabbehum e la buÂṀdel li adin kavmi hud"
  11,61,"Ve ila semude ehahum saliha kale ya kavmÄḟÂṀbudullahe malekum min ilahin gayruh huve enseekum minel erdÄḟ vestaÂṀmerakum fÄḟha festagfiruhu summe tubu ileyh inne rabbÄḟ karÄḟbum mucÄḟb"
  11,62,"Kalu ya salihu kad kunte fÄḟna mercuvven kable haza etenhana en naÂṀbude ma yaÂṀbudu abauna ve innena le fÄḟ sekkim mimma tedÂṀuna ileyhi murÄḟb"
  11,63,"Kale ya kavmi eraeytum in kuntu ala beyyinetim mir rabbÄḟ ve atanÄḟ minhu rahmetem fe mey yensurunÄḟ minellahi in asaytuhu fe ma tesÄḟdunenÄḟ gayra tahsÄḟr"
  11,64,"Ve ya kavmi hazihÄḟ nakatullahi lekum ayeten fezeruha teÂṀkul fÄḟ erdÄḟllahi ve la temessuha bi suin fe yeÂṀhuzekum azabun karÄḟb"
  11,65,"Fe akaruha fe kale metetteu fÄḟ darikum selasete eyyam zalike vaÂṀdun gayru mekzub"
  11,66,"Felemma cae emruna necceyna salihav vellezÄḟne amenu meahu bi rahmetim minna ve min hÄḟzyi yevmiiz inne rabbeke huvel kaviyyul azÄḟz"
  11,67,"Ve ehazellezÄḟne zalemus sayhatu fe asbehu fÄḟ diyarihim casimÄḟn"
  11,68,"Kel el lem yagnev fÄḟha e la inne semude keferu rabbehum e la buÂṀdel li semud"
  11,69,"Ve le kad cet rusuluna ibrahÄḟme bil busra kalu selama kale selamun fe ma lebise en cae bi Äḟclin hanÄḟz"
  11,70,"Felemma raa eydiyehum la tesÄḟlu ileyhi nekirahum ve evcese minhum hÄḟyfeh kalu la tehaf inna ursilna ila kavmi lut"
  11,71,"Vemraetuhu kaimetun fe dahÄḟket fe bessernaha bi ishaka ve miv verai ishaka yaÂṀkub"
  11,72,"Kalet ya veyleta e elidu ve ene acuzuv ve haza baÂṀli seyha inne haza le seyÂṀun acÄḟb"
  11,73,"Kalu e taÂṀcebÄḟne min emrillahi rahmetullahi ve berakatuhu aleykum ehlel beyv innehu hamÄḟdum mecÄḟd"
  11,74,"Femma zehebe an ibrahÄḟmer ravÂṀu ve caethul busra yucadiluna fÄḟ kavmi lut"
  11,75,"Inne ibrahÄḟme le halÄḟmun evvahum munÄḟb"
  11,76,"Ya ibrahÄḟmu aÂṀrÄḟd an haza innehu kad cae emru rabbik ve innehum atÄḟhum azabun gayru merdud"
  11,77,"Ve lemma caet rusuluna lutan sÄḟe bihim ve daka bihim zerÂṀav ve kale haza yevmun asÄḟyb"
  11,78,"Ve caehu kavmuhu yuhraune ileyhi ve min kablu kanu yaÂṀmelunes seyyiat kale ya kavmi haulai benatÄḟ hunne atheru lekum fettekullahe ve la tuhzuni fÄḟ dayfÄḟ e leyse minkum raculur rasÄḟd"
  11,79,"Kalu le kad alimte ma lena fÄḟ benatike min hakk ve inneke le taÂṀlemu ma nurÄḟd"
  11,80,"Kale lev enne lÄḟ bikum kuvveten ev avÄḟ ila ruknin sedÄḟd"
  11,81,"Kalu ya lutu inna rusulu rabbike ley yesÄḟlu ileyke fe esri bi ehlike bi kÄḟdÂṀÄḟm minel leyli ve la yeltefit minkum ehadun illemraetek innehu musÄḟybuha ma esabehum inne mevÂṀÄḟdehumus subh e leyses bi karÄḟb"
  11,82,"Felemma cae emruna cealna aliyeha safileha ve emtarna aleyha hÄḟcaratem min siccÄḟlim mendud"
  11,83,"Musevvemeten Äḟnde rabbik ve ma hiye minez zalimÄḟne bi beÄḟyd"
  11,84,"Ve ila medyene ehahum suayba kale ya kavmÄḟÂṀbudullahe malekum min ilahin gayruhv ve la tenkusul mikyale vel mÄḟzane innÄḟ erakum bi hayriv ve innÄḟ ehafu aleykum azabe yevmim muhÄḟyt"
  11,85,"Ve ya kavmi evful mikyale vel mÄḟzane bil kÄḟstÄḟ ve la tebhasun nase esyaehum ve la taÂṀsev fil erdÄḟ mufsidÄḟn"
  11,86,"BekÄḟyyetullahi hayrul lekum in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn ve ma ene aleykum bi hafÄḟyz"
  11,87,"Kalu ya suaybu e salatuke teÂṀmuruke en netruke ma yaÂṀbudu abauna ev en nefÂṀale fÄḟ emvalina ma nesaÂṀ inneke le entel halÄḟmur rasÄḟd"
  11,88,"Kale ya kavmi eraeytum in kuntu ala beyyinetim mir rabbÄḟ ve razekanÄḟ minhu rizkan hasena ve ma urÄḟdu en uhalifekum ila ma enhakum anh in urÄḟdu illel Äḟslaha mestetaÂṀt ve ma tevfÄḟkÄḟy illa billah aleyhi tevekkeltu ve ileyhi unÄḟb"
  11,89,"Ve ya kavmi la yecrimennekum sikakÄḟy ey yusÄḟybekum mislu ma esabe kavme nuhÄḟn ev kavme hudin ev kavme salÄḟh ve ma kavmu lutÄḟm minkum bi beÄḟyd"
  11,90,"Vestagfiru rabbekum summe tubu ileyh inne rabbÄḟ rahÄḟymuv vedud"
  11,91,"Kalu ya suaybu ma nefkahu kesÄḟram mimma tekulu ve inna le nerake fÄḟna daÄḟyfa ve lev la rahtuke le racemnake ve ma ente aleyna bi aziz"
  11,92,"Kale ya kami erahtÄḟy eazzu aleykum minellha vettehaztumuhu veaekum zÄḟhriyya inne rabbÄḟ bi ma taÂṀmelune muhÄḟyt"
  11,93,"Ve ya kavmÄḟÂṀmelu ala mekanetikum innÄḟ amil sevfe taÂṀlemune mey yeÂṀtÄḟhi azabuy yuhzÄḟhi ve men huve kazib vertekÄḟbu innÄḟ meakum rakÄḟyb"
  11,94,"Ve lemma cae emruna necceyna suaybev vellezÄḟne amenu meahu bi rahmetim minna ve ehazetillezÄḟne zalemus sayhatu fe asbehu fÄḟ diyarihim casimÄḟn"
  11,95,"Keel lem yagnev fÄḟha ela buÂṀdel li medyene kema beÄḟdet semud"
  11,96,"Ve le kad erselna musa bi ayatina ve sultanim mubÄḟn"
  11,97,"Ila firÂṀavne ve meleihÄḟ fettebeu emra firÂṀavn ve ma emru firÂṀavne bi rasÄḟd"
  11,98,"Yakdumu kavmehu yevmel kÄḟyameti fe evradehumun nar ve biÂṀsel virdul mevrud"
  11,99,"Ve utbiu fÄḟ hazihÄḟ laÂṀnetev ve yevmel kÄḟyameh biÂṀser rifdul merfud"
  11,100,"Zalike min embail kur nekussuhu aleyke minha kaimuv ve hasÄḟyd"
  11,101,"Ve ma zalemnahum ve lakin zalemu enfusehum fe ma agnet anhum alihetuhumulteÄḟ yedÂṀune min dunillahi min seyÂṀil lemma cae meru rabbik ve ma zaduhum gayra tetbÄḟb"
  11,102,"Ve kezalike ahzu rabbike iza ehazel kura ve hiye zalimeh inne ahzehu elimun sedÄḟd"
  11,103,"Inne fÄḟ zalike le ayetel li men hafe azabel ahÄḟrah zalike yevmim meshud"
  11,104,"Ve ma nuehhÄḟruhu illa li ecelim maÂṀdud"
  11,105,"Yevme yeÂṀti la tekellemu nefsun illa bi iznih fe minhum sekÄḟyyuv ve seÄḟyd"
  11,106,"Fe emmellezÄḟne seku fe fin nari lehum fÄḟha zefÄḟruv ve sehiyk"
  11,107,"HalidÄḟne fÄḟha madametis semavatu vel erdu illa ma sae rabbuk inne rabbeke feÂṀalul lima yurÄḟd"
  11,108,"Ve emmellezÄḟne suÄḟdu fe fil cenneti halidÄḟne fÄḟha madametis semavatu vel erdu illa ma sae rabbuk ataen gayra meczuz"
  11,109,"Fe la teku fÄḟ miryetim mimma yaÂṀbudu haulaÂṀ ma yaÂṀbudune illa kema yaÂṀbudu abauhum min kabl ve inna le muveffuhum nesÄḟybehum gayra menkus"
  11,110,"Ve le kad ateyna musel kitabe fahtulife fÄḟh ve lev la kelimetun sebekat mir rabbike le kudiye beynehum ve innehum le fÄḟ sekkim minhu murÄḟb"
  11,111,"Ve inne kulul lemma leyuveffiyennehum rabbuke aÂṀmalehum innehu bima yaÂṀmelune habÄḟr"
  11,112,"FestekÄḟm kema umirte ve men tabe meake ve la tatgav innehu bi ma taÂṀmelune besÄḟyr"
  11,113,"Ve la terkenu ilellezÄḟne zalemu fe temessekumun naru ve malekum min dunillahi min evliyae summe la tunsarun"
  11,114,"Ve ekÄḟmÄḟs salate tarafeyin nehari ve zulefem minel leylv innel hasenati yuzhibnes seyyiat zalike zikra liz zakirÄḟn"
  11,115,"Vasbir fe innellahe la yudÄḟyÂṀu ecral muhsinÄḟn"
  11,116,"Fe lev la kane minel kuruni min kablikum ulu bekÄḟyyetiy yenhevne anil fesadi fil erdÄḟ illa kalÄḟlem mimmen enceyna minhum vettebeallezÄḟne zalemu ma utrifu fÄḟhi ve kanu mucrimÄḟn"
  11,117,"Ve ma kane rubbuke li yuhlikel kura bi zulmiv ve ehluha muslihun"
  11,118,"Ve lev sae rabbuke le cealen nase ummetev vahÄḟdetev ve la yezalune muhtelifÄḟn"
  11,119,"Illa mer rahÄḟme rabbuk ve li zalike halekahum ve temmet kelimetu rabbike le emleenne cehenneme minel cinneti ve nasi ecmeÄḟyn"
  11,120,"Ve kullen nekussu aleyke mir embair rusuli ma nusebbitu bihÄḟ fuadek e caeke fÄḟ hazihil hakku ve emvÂṀÄḟzatu ve zikra lil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  11,121,"Ve kul lillezÄḟne la yuÂṀminunaÂṀmelu ala mekanetikum inna amilun"
  11,122,"VentezÄḟru inna muntezÄḟrun"
  11,123,"Ve lillahi gaybus semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ileyhi yurceul emru kulluhu faÂṀbudhu ve tevekkel aleyh ve ma rabbuke bi gafilin amma taÂṀmelun"
  12,8,"Iz kalu le yusufu ve ehuhu ehabbu ila ebÄḟna minna ve nahnu usbeh inne ebana le fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  12,9,"Uktulu yusufe evitrahuhu erday yahlu lekum vechu ebÄḟkum ve tekunu mim baÂṀdihÄḟ kavmen salihÄḟyn"
  12,10,"Kale kailum minhum la taktulu yusufe ve elkuhu fÄḟ gayabetil cubbi yeltekÄḟthu baÂṀdus seyyarati in kuntum faÄḟlÄḟn"
  12,11,"Kalu ya ebana ma leke la teÂṀmenna ala yusufe inna lehu lenasihun"
  12,12,"Ersilhu meana gadey yertaÂṀ ve yelÂṀab ve inna lehu lehafizun"
  12,13,"Kale innÄḟ le yahzununÄḟ en tezhebu bihÄḟ ve ehafu ey yeÂṀkulehuz ziÂṀbu ve entum anhu gafilun"
  12,14,"Kalu le in ekelehuz ziÂṀbu ve nahnu usbetun inna izel le hasirun"
  12,15,"Fe lemma zehebu bihÄḟ ve ecmeu ey yecÂṀaluhu fÄḟ gayabetil cubb ve evhayna ileyhi le tunebbiennehum bi emrihim haza ve hum la yesÂṀurun"
  12,16,"Ve cau ebahum Äḟsaey yebkun"
  12,17,"Kalu ya ebana inna zehebna nestebiku ve terakna yusufe Äḟnde metaÄḟna fe ekelehuz ziÂṀb ve ma ente bi muÂṀminil lena ve lev kunna sadikÄḟyn"
  12,18,"Ve cau ala kamÄḟsÄḟhÄḟ bi demin kezib kale bel sevvelet lekum enfusukum emra fe sabrun cemÄḟl vallahul musteanu ala ma tesÄḟfun"
  12,19,"Ve caet seyyaratun fe erselu varidehum fe edla delveh kale ya busra haza gulam ve eserruhu bidaah vallahu alÄḟmun bi ma yaÂṀmelun"
  12,20,"Ve seravhu bi semenim bahsin derahime maÂṀdudeh ve kanu fÄḟhi minez zahidÄḟn"
  12,21,"Ve kalellezisterahu mim mÄḟsra limraetihÄḟ ekrimÄḟ mesvahu asa ey yenfeana ev nettehÄḟzehu veleda ve kezalike mekkenna li yusufe fil erdÄḟ ve li nuallimehu min teÂṀvÄḟlil ehdÄḟs vallahu galibun ala emrihÄḟ ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yaÂṀlemun"
  12,22,"Ve lemma belega esuddehu ateynahu hukmev ve Äḟlma ve kezalike neczil muhsinÄḟn"
  12,23,"Ve ravedethulletÄḟ huve fÄḟ beytiha an nefsihÄḟ ve gallekatil ebvabe ve kalet heyte lek kale meazellahi innehu rabbÄḟ ahsene mesvay innehu la yuflihuz zalimun"
  12,24,"Ve le kad hemmet bihÄḟ ve hemme biha lev la er raa burhane rabbih kezalike li nasrife anhus sue vel fahsaÂṀ innehu min Äḟbadinel muhlesÄḟyn"
  12,25,"Vestebekal babe ve kaddet kamÄḟsahu min duburiv ve elfeya seyyideha ledel bab kalet ma ceazu men erade bi ehlike suen illa ey yuscene ev azabun elÄḟm"
  12,26,"Kale hiye ravedetnÄḟ an nefsÄḟ ve sehide sahidum min ehliha in kane kamÄḟsuhu kudde min kubulin fe sadekat ve huve minel kazibÄḟn"
  12,27,"Ve in kane kamÄḟsuhu kudde min duburin fe kezebet ve huve mines sadikÄḟyn"
  12,28,"Felemma raaa kamÄḟsahu kudde min duburin kale innehu min keydikunn inne keydekunne azÄḟym"
  12,29,"Yusufu aÂṀrÄḟd an haza vestagfirÄḟ li zembik inneki kunti minel hatÄḟÄḟn"
  12,30,"Ve kale nisvetun fil medÄḟnetimraetul azÄḟzi turavidu fetaha an nefsih kad segafeha hubba inna leneraha fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  12,31,"Felemma semiat bi mekrihinne erselet ileyhinne ve aÂṀtedet lehunne muttekeev ve atet kulla vahÄḟdetim minhunne sikkÄḟnev ve kaletÄḟhruc aleyhinn felemma raeynehu ekbernehu ve kattaÂṀne eydiyehunne ve kulne hase lillahi ma haza besera in haza illa melekun kerÄḟm"
  12,32,"Kalet fe zalikunnellezÄḟ lumtunnenÄḟ fÄḟh ve le kad ravedtuhu an nefsihÄḟ festaÂṀsam ve leil lem yefÂṀal ma amurruhu le yuscenenne ve leyekunem mines sagÄḟrÄḟn"
  12,33,"Kale rabbis sicnu ehabbu ileyye mimma yedÂṀunenÄḟ ileyh ve illa tasrif annÄḟ keydehunne asbu ileyhinne ve ekum minel cahilÄḟn"
  12,34,"Festecabe lehu rabbuhu fe sarafe anhu keydehunn innehu huves semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  12,35,"Summe beda lehum mim baÂṀdi ma raevul ayati le yescununnehu hatta hÄḟyn"
  12,36,"Ve dehale meahus sicne feteyan kale ehaduhuma innÄḟ eranÄḟ aÂṀsÄḟru hamra ve kalel aharu innÄḟ eranÄḟ ahmilu fevka raÂṀsÄḟ hubzen teÂṀkulut tayru minh nebbiÂṀna bi teÂṀvÄḟlih inna nerake minel muhsinÄḟn"
  12,37,"Kale la yeÂṀtikuma taamun turzekanihÄḟ illa nebbeÂṀtukuma bi teÂṀvÄḟlihÄḟ kable ey yeÂṀtiyekuma zalikuma mimma alemenÄḟ rabbÄḟ innÄḟ teraktu millete kavmil la yuÂṀminune billahi ve hum bil ahÄḟrati hum bil ahÄḟrati hum kafirun"
  12,38,"VettebaÂṀtu millete abai ibrahÄḟme ve ishaka ve yaÂṀkub ma kane lena en nusrike billahi min seyÂṀ zalike min fadlillahi aleyna ve alen nasi ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yeskurun"
  12,39,"Ya sahÄḟbeyis sicni e erbabum muteferrikune hayrun emillahul vahÄḟdul kahhar"
  12,40,"Ma taÂṀbudune min dunihÄḟ illa esmaen semmeytumuha entum ve abaukum ma enzelellahu biha min sultan inil hukmu illa lillah emera ella taÂṀbudu illa iyyah zaliked dÄḟnul kayyimu ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yaÂṀlemun"
  12,41,"Ya sahÄḟbeyis sicni emma ehadukuma fe yeskÄḟy rabbehu hamra ve emmel aharu fe yuslebu fe teÂṀkulut tayru mir raÂṀsih kudÄḟyel emrullezÄḟ fÄḟhi testeftiyan"
  12,42,"Ve kale lillezÄḟ zanne ennehu nacim minhumezkurnÄḟ Äḟnde rabbike fe ensahus seytanu zikra rabbihÄḟ fe lebise fis sicni bidÂṀa sinÄḟn"
  12,43,"Ve kalel meliku innÄḟ era sebÂṀa bekaratin simaniy yeÂṀkuluhunne sebÂṀun Äḟcafuv ve sebÂṀa sumbulatin hudriv ve uhara yabisat ya eyyuhel meleu eftunÄḟ fÄḟ ruÂṀyaye in kuntum lir ruÂṀya taÂṀburun"
  12,44,"Kalu adgasu ahlam ve ma nahnu bi teÂṀvÄḟlil ahlami bi alimÄḟn"
  12,45,"Ve kalellezÄḟ neca minhuma veddekera baÂṀde ummetin ene unebbiukum bi teÂṀvÄḟlihÄḟ fe ersilun"
  12,46,"Yusufu eyyuhes sÄḟddÄḟku eftina fÄḟ sebÂṀÄḟ bekaratin simaniy yeÂṀkulununne sebÂṀun Äḟcafuv ve sebÂṀÄḟ sumbulatin hudriv ve uhara yabisatil leallÄḟ erciu ilen nasi leallehum yaÂṀlemun"
  12,47,"Kale tezraune sebÂṀa sinÄḟne deeba fe ma hasadtum fezeruhu fÄḟ sumbulihÄḟ illa kalÄḟlem mimma teÂṀkulun"
  12,48,"Summe yeÂṀtÄḟ mim baÂṀdi zalike sebÂṀun sidaduy yeÂṀkulne ma kaddemtum lehunne illa kalÄḟlem mimma tuhsÄḟnun"
  12,49,"Summe yeÂṀtÄḟ mim baÂṀdi zalike amun fÄḟhi yugasun nasu ve fÄḟhi yaÂṀsÄḟrun"
  12,50,"Ve kalel melikuÂṀtunÄḟ bih fe lemma caehur rasulu kalercÄḟÂṀila rabbike fesÂṀelhu ma balun nisvetillatÄḟ kattaÂṀne eydiyehunn inne rabbÄḟ bi keydihinne alÄḟm"
  12,51,"Kale ma hatbukunne iz ravedtunne yusufe an nefsih kulne hase lillahi ma alimna aleyhi min suÂṀ kaletimraetul azÄḟzil ane hashasal hakku ene ravedtuhu an nefsihÄḟ ve innehu le mines sadikÄḟyn"
  12,52,"Zalike li yaÂṀleme ennÄḟ lem ehunhu bil gaybi ve ennellahe la yehdÄḟ keydel hainÄḟn"
  12,53,"Ve ma uberriu nefsÄḟ innen nefse le emmaratum bis sui illa ma rahÄḟme rabbÄḟ inne rabbÄḟ gafurur rahÄḟym"
  12,54,"Ve kalel melikuÂṀtunÄḟ bihÄḟ estahlÄḟshu li nefsÄḟ fe lemma kellemehu kale innekel yevme ledeyna mekÄḟnun emÄḟn"
  12,55,"KalecÂṀalnÄḟ ala hazainil ard innÄḟ hafÄḟyzun alÄḟm"
  12,56,"Ve kezalike mekkenna li yusufe fil ard yetebevveu minha haysu yesaÂṀ nusÄḟybu bi rahmetina men nesau ve la nudÄḟyÂṀu ecral muhsinÄḟn"
  12,57,"Ve le ecrul ahÄḟrati hayrul lillezÄḟne amenu ve kanu yettekun"
  12,58,"Ve cae Äḟhvetu yusufe fe dehalu aleyhi fe arafehum ve hum lehu munkirun"
  12,59,"Ve lemma cehhezehum bi cehazihim kaleÂṀtunÄḟ bi ehÄḟl lekum min ebÄḟkum ela teravne ennÄḟ ufil keyle ve ene hayrul munzilÄḟn"
  12,60,"Fe il lem teÂṀtunÄḟ bihÄḟ fe la keyle lekum ÄḟndÄḟ ve la takrabun"
  12,61,"Kalu senuravidu anhu ebahu ve inne le faÄḟlun"
  12,62,"Ve kaleli fityanihicÂṀalu bidaatehum fÄḟ rihalihim leallehum yaÂṀrifuneha izenkalebu ila ehlihim leallehum yarciun"
  12,63,"Fe lemma raceu ila ebÄḟhim kalu ya ebana munia minnel keylu fe ersil meana ehana nektel ve inna lehu lehafizun"
  12,64,"Kale hel amenukum aleyhi illa kema emintukum ala ehÄḟyhi min kabl fellahu hayrun hafizav ve huve erhamur rahÄḟmÄḟn"
  12,65,"Ve lemma fetehu metaahum vecedu bidaatehum ruddet ileyhim kalu ya ebana ma nebgÄḟy hazihÄḟ bidaatuna ruddet ileyna ve nemÄḟru ehlena ve nahfezu ehana ve nezdadu keyle beÄḟyr zalike keyluy yesÄḟr"
  12,66,"Kale len ursilehu meakum hatta tuÂṀtuni mevsikam minellahi leteÂṀtunnenÄḟ bihÄḟ illa ey yuhata bikum fe lemma atevhu mevsikahum kalellahu ala ma nekulu vekÄḟl"
  12,67,"Ve kale ya beniyye la tedhulu mim babiv vahÄḟdiv vedhulu min ebvabim muteferrikah ve ma ugnÄḟ ankum minellahi min seyÂṀ inil hukmu illa lillah aleyhi tevekkelt ve aleyhi fel yetevekkelil mutevekkilun"
  12,68,"Ve lemma dehalu min haysu emerahum ebuhum ma kane yugnÄḟ anhum minellahi min seyÂṀin illa laceten fÄḟ nefsi yaÂṀkube kadaha ve innehu le zu Äḟlmil lima allemnahu ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yaÂṀlemun"
  12,69,"Ve lemma dehalu ala yusufe ave ileyhi ehahu kale innÄḟ ene ehuke fe la tebteis bima kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  12,70,"Fe lemma cehhezehum bi cehazihim ceales sikayete fÄḟ rahli ehÄḟyhi summe ezzene muezzinun eyyetuhel Äḟyru innekum le sarikun"
  12,71,"Kalu ve akbelu aleyhim maza tefkÄḟdun"
  12,72,"Kalu nefkÄḟdu suvaal meliki ve li men cae bihÄḟ hÄḟmlu beÄḟyriv ve ene bihÄḟ zeÄḟym"
  12,73,"Kalu tellahi le kad alimtum ma ciÂṀna li nufside fil erdÄḟ ve ma kunna sarikÄḟyn"
  12,74,"Kalu fe ma cezauhu in kuntum kazibÄḟn"
  12,75,"Kalu cezauhu mev vucide fÄḟ rahlihÄḟ fe huve cezauh kezalike necziz zalimÄḟn"
  12,76,"Fe bedee bi evÂṀÄḟyetihim kable viai ehÄḟyhi summestahraceha min viai ehÄḟyh kezalike kidna li yusuf ma kane li yeÂṀhuze ehahu fÄḟ dÄḟnil melikÄḟ illa ey yesaellah nerfeu deracatim men nesaÂṀ ve fevka kulli zÄḟ Äḟlmin alÄḟm"
  12,77,"Kalu iy yesrÄḟk fe kad seraka ehul lehu min kabl fe eserraha yusufu fÄḟ nefsihÄḟ ve lem yubdiha lehum kale entum serrum mekana vallahu aÂṀlemu bima tesÄḟfun"
  12,78,"Kalu ya eyyuhel azÄḟzu inne lehu eben seyhan kebÄḟran fe huz ehadena mekaneh inna nerake minel muhsinÄḟn"
  12,79,"Kale meazellahi en neÂṀhuze illa mev vecedna metaana Äḟndehu inna izel le zalimun"
  12,80,"Fe lemmesteyÂṀesu minhu halesu neciyya kale kebÄḟruhum e lem taÂṀlemu enne ebakum kad ehaze aleykum mevsikam minellahi ve min kablu ma ferrattum fÄḟ yusuf fe len ebrahal erda hatta yeÂṀzene lÄḟ ebÄḟ ev yahkumellahu lÄḟ ve huve hayrul hakimÄḟn"
  12,81,"Irciu illa ebÄḟkum fe kulu ya ebana innebneke serak ve ma sehidna illa bima alimna ve ma kunna lilgaybi hafizÄḟyn"
  12,82,"VesÂṀelil karyetelletÄḟ kunna fÄḟha vel ÄḟyralletÄḟ akbelna fÄḟha ve inna lesadikun"
  12,83,"Kale bel sevvelet lekum enfusukum emra fe sabrun cemÄḟl asellahu ey yeÂṀtiyenÄḟ bihim cemÄḟa innehu huvel alÄḟmul hakÄḟm"
  12,84,"Ve tevella anhum ve kale ya esefa ala yusufe vebyaddat aynahu minel huzni fe huve kezÄḟym"
  12,85,"Kalu tellahi tefteu tezkuru yusufe hatta tekune haradan ev tekuru yusufe hatta tekune haradan ev tekune minel halikÄḟn"
  12,86,"Kale innema esku bessÄḟ ve huznÄḟ ilellahi ve aÂṀlemu minellahi ma la taÂṀlemun"
  12,87,"Ya beniyyezhebu fe tehassesu miy yusufe ve ehÄḟyhi ve la teyÂṀesu mir ravhÄḟllahi illel kavmul kafirun"
  12,88,"Fe lemma dehalu aleyhi kalu ya eyyuhel azÄḟzu messena ve ehlened durru ve ciÂṀna bi bidaatim muzcatin fe evfi lenel keyle ve tesaddak aleynav innellahe yeczil mutesaddikÄḟyn"
  12,89,"Kale hel alimtum ma fealtum bi yusufe ve ehÄḟyhi iz entum cahilun"
  12,90,"Kalu einneke le ente yusuf kale ene yusufu ve haza ehÄḟy kad mennellahu aleyna innehu mey yettekÄḟ ve yasbir fe innellahe la yudÄḟyÂṀu ecral muhsinÄḟn"
  12,91,"Kalu tellahi le kad aserakellahu aleyna ve in kunna le hatÄḟÄḟn"
  12,92,"Kale la tesrÄḟbe aleykumul yevm yagfirullahu lekum ve huve erhamur rahÄḟmÄḟn"
  12,93,"Izhebu bi kamÄḟsÄḟy haza fe elkuhu ala vechi ebÄḟ yeÂṀti besÄḟyra veÂṀtunÄḟ bi ehlikum ecmeÄḟyn"
  12,94,"Ve lemma fesaletil Äḟyru kale ebuhum innÄḟ le ecidu rÄḟha yusufe lev la en tufennidun"
  12,95,"Kalu tellahi inneke le fÄḟ dalalikel kadÄḟm"
  12,96,"Fe lemma en cael besÄḟru elkahu ala vechihÄḟ fertedde besÄḟyra kale elem ekul lekum innÄḟ aÂṀlemu minellahi ma la taÂṀlemun"
  12,97,"Kalu ya ebanestagfir lena zunubena inna kunna hatÄḟÄḟn"
  12,98,"Kale sevfe estagfiru lekum rabbÄḟ innehu huvel gafurur rahÄḟym"
  12,99,"Fe lemma dehalu ala yusufe ava ileyhi ebeveyhi ve kaledhulu mÄḟsra in saellahu aminÄḟn"
  12,100,"Ve rafea ebeveyhi alel arsi ve harru lehu succeda ve kale ya ebeti haza teÂṀvÄḟlu ruÂṀyaye min kablu kad cealeha ribbÄḟ hakka ve kad ahsene bÄḟ iz ahracenÄḟ mines sicni ve cae bikum minel bedvi mim baÂṀdi en nezegas seytanu beynÄḟ ve beyne ÄḟhvetÄḟ inne rabbÄḟ latÄḟyful lima yesaÂṀ innehu huvel alÄḟmul hakÄḟm"
  12,101,"Rabbi kad ateytenÄḟ minel mulki ve allemtenÄḟ min teÂṀvÄḟlil ehadÄḟs fatÄḟras semavati vel erdÄḟ ente veliyyÄḟ fid dunya vel ahÄḟrah teveffenÄḟ muslimev ve elhÄḟknÄḟ bis salihÄḟyn"
  12,102,"Zalike min embail gaybi nuhÄḟyhi ileyk ve ma kunte ledeyhim iz ecmeu emrahum ve hum yemkurun"
  12,103,"Ve ma ekserun nasi ve lev haraste bi muÂṀminÄḟn"
  12,104,"Ve ma tesÂṀeluhum aleyhi min ecr in huve illa zikrul lil alemÄḟn"
  12,105,"Ve keeyyim min ayetin fis semavati vel erdÄḟ yemurrune aleyha ve hum anhu muÂṀridun"
  12,106,"Ve ma yuÂṀminu ekseruhum billahi illa ve hum musrikun"
  12,107,"E fe eminu en teÂṀtiyehum gasiyetum min azabillahi ev teÂṀtiyehumus saatu bagtetev ve hum la yesÂṀurun"
  12,108,"Kul hazihÄḟ sebÄḟlÄḟ edÂṀu ilellahi ala besÄḟyratin ene ve menittebeanÄḟ ve subhanellahi ve ma ene minel musrikÄḟn"
  12,109,"Ve ma erselna min kablike illa ricalen nuhÄḟy ileyhim min ehlil kura e fe lem yesÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fe yenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetullezÄḟne min kablihim ve la darul ahÄḟrati hayrul lillezÄḟnettekav e fe la taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  12,110,"Hatta izesteyÂṀeser rusulu ve zannu ennehum kad kuzibu caehum nasruna fe nucciye men nesaÂṀ ve la yuraddu beÂṀsuna anil kavmil mucrimÄḟn"
  12,111,"Le kad kane fÄḟ kasasÄḟhum Äḟbratul li ulil elbab ma kane hadÄḟsey yuftera ve lakin tasdÄḟkallezÄḟ beyne yedeyhi ve tefsÄḟyle kulli seyÂṀiv ve hudev ve rahmetel li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  13,3,"Ve huvellezÄḟ meddel erda ve ceale fÄḟha ravasiye ve enhara ve min kullis semerati ceale fÄḟha zevceynisneyni yugsil leylen nehar inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yetefekkerun"
  13,4,"Ve fil erdÄḟ kÄḟtaum mutecaviratuv ve cennatum min aÂṀnabiv ve zerÂṀuv ve nehÄḟylun sÄḟnvanuv ve gayru sÄḟnvaniy yuska bi maiv vahÄḟdiv ve nufaddÄḟlu baÂṀdaha ala baÂṀdÄḟn fil ukul inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  13,5,"Ve in taÂṀceb fe acabun kavluhum e iza kunna turaben e inna le fÄḟ halkÄḟn cedÄḟd ulaikellezÄḟne keferu bi rabbihim ve ulaikel aglalu fÄḟ aÂṀnakÄḟhim ve ulaike ashabun nar hum fÄḟha halidun"
  13,6,"Ve yestaÂṀciluneke bis seyyieti kablel haseneti ve kad halet min kablihimul mesulat ve inne rabbeke lezu magfiratil linnasi ala zulmihim ve inne rabbeke le sedÄḟdul Äḟkab"
  13,7,"Ve yekulullezÄḟne keferu lev la unzile aleyhi ayetum mir rabbih innema ente munziruv ve likulli kavmin had"
  13,8,"Allahu yaÂṀlemu ma tahmilu kullu unsa ve ma tegÄḟydul erhamu ve ma tezdad ve kullu seyÂṀin Äḟndehu bi mÄḟkdar"
  13,9,"Alimul gaybi vas sehadetil kebÄḟrul muteal"
  13,10,"Sevaum minkum men eserral kavle ve men cehera bihÄḟ ve men huve mustahfim bil leyli ve saribum bin nehar"
  13,11,"Lehu muakkÄḟbatum mim beyni yedeyhi ve min halfihÄḟ yugayyiru ma bi kavmin hatta yugayyiru ma bi enfusihim ve iza eradellahu bi kavmin suen fe la meradde leh ve ma lehum min dunihÄḟ mev val"
  13,12,"HuvellezÄḟ yurÄḟkumul berka havfev ve tameav ve yanslus sehabes sikal"
  13,13,"Ve yusebbihur raÂṀdu bi hamdihÄḟ vel melaiketu min hÄḟyfetih ve yursilus savaÄḟka fe yusÄḟybu biha mey yesau ve hum yucadilune fillah ve huve sedÄḟdul mihal"
  13,14,"Lehu daÂṀvetul hakk vellezÄḟne yedÂṀune min dunihÄḟ la yestecÄḟbune lehum bi seyÂṀin illa ke basitÄḟ keffeyhi ilel mai li yebluga fahu ve ma huve bi baligÄḟh ve ma duaul kafirÄḟne illa fÄḟ dalal"
  13,15,"Ve lillahi yescudu men fis semavati vel ard tavÂṀav ve kerhev ve zÄḟlaluhum bil guduvvi vel asal"
  13,16,"Kul mer rabbus semavati vel erdÄḟ kulillah kul e fettehaztum min dunihÄḟ evliyae la yemlikune li enfusihim nefÂṀav ve la darra kul hel yestevil aÂṀma vel besÄḟyru em hel testeviz zulumanut ven nur em cealu lillahi surakae haleku ke halkÄḟhÄḟ fe tesabehel halku aleyhim kulillahu haliku kulli seyÂṀiv ve huvel vahÄḟdul kahhar"
  13,17,"Enzele mines semai maen fe salet evdiyetum bi kaderiha fahtemeles seylu zebeder rabiya ve mimma yukÄḟdune aleyhi fin naribtigae hÄḟlyetin ev metaÄḟn zebedum misluh kezalike yadribullahul hakka vel batÄḟl fe emmez zebedu fe yehebu cufaa ve emma ma yenfeun nase fe yemkusu fil ard kezalike yadribullahul emsal"
  13,18,"LillezÄḟnestecabu li rabbihimul husna vellezÄḟne lem yestecÄḟbu lehu lev enne lehum ma fil erdÄḟ cemÄḟav ve mislehu meahu leftedev bih ulaike lehum suul hÄḟsabi ve meÂṀvahum cehennem ve biÂṀsel mihad(15. Ayet secde ayetidir)"
  13,19,"E fe mey yaÂṀlemu ennema unzile ileyke mir rabbikel hakku ke men huve aÂṀma innema yetezekkeru ulul elbab"
  13,20,"EllezÄḟne yufune bi ahdillahi ve la yenkudunel mÄḟsak"
  13,21,"VellezÄḟne yesÄḟlune ma emerallahu bihÄḟ ey yusale ve yahsevne rabbehum ve yehafune suel hÄḟsab"
  13,22,"VellezÄḟne saberubtigae vechi rabbihim ve ekamus salate ve enfeku mimma razaknahum sirrav ve alaniyetev ve yedraune bil hasenetis seyyiete ulaike lehum ukbed dar"
  13,23,"Cennatu adniy yedhuluneha ve men saleha min abaihim ve ezvacihim ve zurriyyatihim vel melaiketu yedhulune aleyhim min kulli bab"
  13,24,"Selamun alaykum bima sabertum fe nÄḟÂṀme usbed dar"
  13,25,"VellezÄḟne yenkudune ahdellahi min baÂṀdi mÄḟsakÄḟhÄḟ ve yaktaune ma emarallahu bihÄḟ ey yusale ve yufidune fil erdÄḟ ulaike lehumul laÂṀnetu ve lehum suud dar"
  13,26,"Allahu yebsutur rizka li mey yesau ve yakdir ve ferihu bil hayatid dunya ve mel hayatud dunya fil ahÄḟrati illa metaÂṀ"
  13,27,"Ve yekulullezÄḟne keferu lev la unzile aleyhi ayetum mir rabbih kul innellahe yudÄḟllu mey yesau ve yehdÄḟ ileyhi men enab"
  13,28,"EllezÄḟne amenu ve tatmeinu kulubuhum bi zikrillah e la bi zikrillahi tatmeinul kulub"
  13,29,"EllezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati tuba lehum ve husnu meab"
  13,30,"Kezalike erselnake fÄḟ ummetin kad halet min kabliha umemul liltetluve aleyhimullezÄḟ evhayna ileyke ve hum yekfurune bir rahman kul huve rabbÄḟ la ilahe illa hu aleyhi tevekkeltu ve ileyhi metab"
  13,31,"Ve lev enne kurÂṀanen suyyirat bihil cibalu ev kuttÄḟat bihil erdu ev kullime bihil mevta bel lillahil emru cemÄḟa e fe lem yeyÂṀesillezÄḟne amenu el lev yesaullahu le heden nase cemÄḟa ve la yezalullezÄḟne keferu tusÄḟybuhum bi ma saneu kariatun ev tehullu karÄḟbem min darihim hatta yeÂṀtiye vaÂṀdullah innellahe la yuhliful mÄḟad"
  13,32,"Ve lekadistkuhzie bi rusulim min kabilek fe emleytu lillezÄḟne keferu summe ehaztuhum fe keyfe kane Äḟkab"
  13,33,"E fe men huve kaimun ala kulli nefsim bima kesebet ve cealu lillahi surakaÂṀ kul semmuhum em tunebbiunehu bima la yaÂṀlemu fil erdÄḟ em bi zahirim minel kavl bel zuyyine lillezÄḟne keferu mekruhum ve suddu anis sebÄḟl ve mey yudlilillahu fe ma lehu min had"
  13,34,"Lehum azabun fil hayatido dunya ve le azabul ahÄḟrati esaak ve ma lehum minellahi miv vak"
  13,35,"Meselul cennetilletÄḟ vuÄḟdel muttekun tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enhar ukuluha daimuv ve zÄḟlluha tilke ukbellezÄḟnettekav ve ukbel kafirÄḟnen nar"
  13,36,"VellezÄḟne ateynahumul kitabe yefrahune bima unzile ileyke ve minel ahzabi mey yunkiru baÂṀdah kul innema umirtu en aÂṀbudellahe ve la usrike bih ileyhi edÂṀu ve ileyhi meab"
  13,37,"Ve kezalike enzelnahu hukmen arabiyya ve leinittebaÂṀte ehvaehum baÂṀde ma caeke minel Äḟlmi ma leke minellahi miv veliyyiv ve la vak"
  13,38,"Ve le kad erselna rusulem min kablike ve cealna lehum ezvacev ve zurriyyeh ve ma kane li rasulin ey yeÂṀtiye bi ayetin illa bi iznillah li kulli ecelin kitab"
  13,39,"Yemhullahu ma yesau ve yusbit ve Äḟndehu ummul kitab"
  13,40,"Ve im ma nuriyenneke baÂṀdallezÄḟ neÄḟduhum ev neteveffeyenneke fe innema aleykel belagu ve aleynel hÄḟsab"
  13,41,"E ve lem yerav enna neÂṀtil erda nenkusuha min atrafiha vallahu yahkumu la muakkÄḟbe li hukmih ve huve serÄḟul hÄḟsab"
  13,42,"Ve kad mekerallezÄḟne min kablihim fe lillahil mekru cemÄḟa yaÂṀlemu ma teksibu kullu nefs ve seyaÂṀlemul kuffaru li men ukbed dar"
  13,43,"Ve yekulullezÄḟne keferu leste mursela kul kefa billahi sehÄḟdem beynÄḟ ve beynekum ve men Äḟndehu Äḟlmul kitab"
  14,5,"Ve le kad erselna musa bi ayatina en ahric kavmeke minez zulumati ilen nuri ve zekkirhum bi eyyamillah inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kulli sabbarin sekur"
  14,6,"Ve iz kale musa li kavmihizkuru nÄḟÂṀmetellahi aleykum iz encakum min ali firÂṀavne yesumunekum suel azabi ve yuzebbihune ebnaekum ve yestahyune nisaekum ve fÄḟ zalikum belaum mir rabbikum azÄḟym"
  14,7,"Ve iz teezzene rabbukum le in sekertum le ezÄḟdennekum ve le in kefertum inne azabÄḟ lesedÄḟd"
  14,8,"Ve kale musa in tekfuru entum ve men fil erdÄḟ cemÄḟan fe innellahe le ganiyyun hamÄḟd"
  14,9,"E lem yeÂṀtikum nebeullezÄḟne min kablikum kavmi nuhÄḟv ve adiv ve semude vellezÄḟne mim baÂṀdihim la yaÂṀlemuhum ilellah caethum rusuluhum bil beyyinati fe raddu eydiyehum fÄḟ efvahihim ve kalu inna kefarna bima ursiltum bihÄḟ ve inna le fÄḟ sekkim mimma tedÂṀunena ileyhi murÄḟb"
  14,10,"Kalet rusuluhum e fillahi sekkun fatÄḟris semavati vel ard yedÂṀukum li yagfira lekum min zunubikum ve yuehhÄḟrakum ila ecelim musemma kalu in entum illa beserum misluna turÄḟdune en tesudduna amma kane yaÂṀbudu abauna feÂṀtuna bi sultanim mubÄḟn"
  14,11,"Kalet lehum rusuluhum in nahnu illa beserum mislukum ve lakinnellahe yemunnu ala mey yesau min Äḟbadih ve ma kane lena en neÂṀtiyekum bi sultanin illa bi iznillah ve alellahi fel yetevekkelil muÂṀminun"
  14,12,"Ve ma lena ella netevekkele alellahi ve kad hedana subulena ve lenasbiranne ala ma azeytumuna ve alellahi fel yetevekkelil muteveklkilun"
  14,13,"Ve kalellezÄḟne keferu li rusulihim le nuhricennekum min erdÄḟna ev leteudunne fÄḟ milletina fe evha ileyhim rabbuhum le nuhlikennez zalimÄḟn"
  14,14,"Ve le nuskinennekumul erda mim baÂṀdihim zalike li men hafe mekamÄḟ ve hafe veÄḟyd"
  14,15,"Vesteftehu ve habe kullu cebbarin anÄḟd"
  14,16,"Miv veraihÄḟ cehennemu ve yuska mim main sadÄḟd"
  14,17,"Yetecerrauhu ve la yekadu yusÄḟguhu ve yeÂṀtÄḟhil mevtu min kulli mekaniv ve ma huve bi meyyit ve miv veraihÄḟ azabun galÄḟyz"
  14,18,"MeselullezÄḟne keferu bi rabbihim aÂṀmaluhum keramadinisteddet bihir rÄḟhu fÄḟ yevmin asÄḟf le yakdirune mimma kesebu ala seyÂṀ zalike huved dalalul beÄḟyd"
  14,19,"E lem tera ennellahe halekas semavati vel erda bil hakk iy yeseÂṀ yuzhibkum ve yeÂṀti bi halkÄḟn cedÄḟd"
  14,20,"Ve ma zalike alellahi bi azÄḟz"
  14,21,"Ve berazu lillahi cemÄḟan fe kaled duafau lillezÄḟnestekberu inna kunna lekum tebean fe hel entum mugnune anna min azabillahi min seyÂṀ kalu lev hedanellahu le hedeynakum sevaun aleyna ecezÄḟÂṀna em saberna ma lena mim mehÄḟys"
  14,22,"Ve kales seytanu lemma kudÄḟyel emru innellahe veadekum vaÂṀdel hakkÄḟ ve veadtukum fe ahleftukum ve ma kane liye aleykum min sultanin illa en deavtukum festecebtum lÄḟ fe la telumunÄḟ ve lumu enfusekum ma ene bi musrihÄḟkum ve ma entum ib musrihÄḟyy innÄḟ kefertu bima esraktumuni min kabl innez zalimÄḟne lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  14,23,"Ve udhÄḟlellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha bi izni rabbihim tehÄḟyyetuhum fÄḟha selam"
  14,24,"E lem tera keyfe darabellahu meselen kelimeten ttttayyibeten ke seceratin tayyibetin asluha sabituv ve ferÂṀuha fis semaÂṀ"
  14,25,"TuÂṀtÄḟ ukuleha kulle hÄḟynim bi izni rabbiha ve yadribullahul emsale lin nasi leallehum yetezekkerun"
  14,26,"Ve meselu kelimetin habÄḟsetin ke seceratin habÄḟsetinictusset min fevkÄḟl erdÄḟ ma leha min karar"
  14,27,"YusebbitullahullezÄḟne amenu bil kavlis sabiti fil hayatid dunya ve fil ahÄḟrah ve yudÄḟlullahuz zalimÄḟne ve yefÂṀalullahu ma yesaÂṀ"
  14,28,"E lem tera ilellezÄḟne beddelu nÄḟÂṀmetellahi kufrav ve ehallu kavmehum daral bevar"
  14,29,"Cehennem yaslevneha ve biÂṀsel karar"
  14,30,"Ve cealu lillahi endadel li yudÄḟllu an sebÄḟlih kul temetteu fe inne mesÄḟyrakum ilen nar"
  14,31,"Kul li ÄḟbadiyellezÄḟne amenu yukÄḟymus salate ve yunfiku mimma razaknahum sirrav ve alaniyetem min kabli ey yeÂṀtiye yevmul la beyÂṀun fÄḟhi ve la hÄḟlal"
  14,32,"AllahullezÄḟ halekas semavati vel erda ve enzele mines semai maen fe ahrace bihÄḟ mines semerati rizkal lekum ve sehhara lekumul fulke li tecriye fil bahri bi emrih ve sehhara lekumul enha"
  14,33,"Ve sehha lekumus semse vel kamera daibeyn ve sehhara lekumul leyle ven nehar"
  14,34,"Ve atakum min kulli ma seeltumuh ve in teudu nÄḟÂṀmetellahi la tuhsuha innel insane le zalumun keffar"
  14,35,"Ve iz kale ibrahÄḟmu rabbicÂṀal hazel belede aminev vecnubnÄḟ ve beniyye en naÂṀbudel asnam"
  14,36,"Rabbi innehunne adlelne kesÄḟram minen nas fe men tebianÄḟ fe innehu minnÄḟ ve men asanÄḟ fe inneke gafurur rahÄḟym"
  14,37,"Rabbena innÄḟ eskentu min zurriyyetÄḟ bi vadin gayri zÄḟ zerÂṀÄḟn Äḟnde beytikel muharrami rabbena li yukÄḟymus salate fecÂṀal efÂṀidetem minen nasi tehvÄḟ ileyhim verzukhum mines semerati leallehum yeskurun"
  14,38,"Rabbena inneke taÂṀlemu ma nuhfÄḟ ve ma nÄḟÂṀlin ve ma yahfa alellahi min seyÂṀin fil erdÄḟ ve la fis semaÂṀ"
  14,39,"Elhamdu lillahillezÄḟ vehebe lÄḟ alel kiberi ismaÄḟyle ve ishak inne rabbÄḟ le semÄḟud duaÂṀ"
  14,40,"RabbicÂṀalnÄḟ mukÄḟymes salati ve imn zurriyyetÄḟ rabbena ve tekabbel duaÂṀ"
  14,41,"Rabbenagfir lÄḟ ve li valideyye ve lil muÂṀminÄḟne yevme yekumul hÄḟsab"
  14,42,"Ve la tahsebennellahe gafilen amma yaÂṀmeluz zalimun innema yuehhÄḟruhum li yevmin teshasu fÄḟhil ebsar"
  14,43,"MuhtÄḟÄḟyne mukniÄḟy ruusihim la yerteddu ileyhim tarfuhum ve efÂṀidetuhum hevaÂṀ"
  14,44,"Ve enzirin nase yevme yeÂṀtÄḟhimul azabu fe yekulullezÄḟne zalemu rabbena ahhÄḟrna ila ecelin karÄḟbin nucib daÂṀveteke ve nettebiÄḟr rusul e ve lem tekunu aksemtum min kablu ma lekum min zeval"
  14,45,"Ve sekentum fÄḟ mesakinillezÄḟne zalemu enfusehum ve tebeyyene lekum keyfe fealna bihim ve darabna lekumul emsal"
  14,46,"Ve kad mekeru mekrahum ve Äḟndellahi mekruhum ve in kane mekruhum li tezule minhul cibal"
  14,47,"Fe la tahsebennellahe muhlife vaÂṀdihÄḟ rusuleh innellahe azÄḟzun zuntikam"
  14,48,"Yevme tubeddelul erdu gayral erdÄḟ ve semavatu ve berazu lillahil vahÄḟdil kahhar"
  14,49,"Ve teral mucrimÄḟne yevmeizim mukarranÄḟne fil asfad"
  14,50,"Serabiluhum min katÄḟraniv ve tagsa vucuhehumun nar"
  14,51,"Li yecziyellahu kulle nefsim ma kesebet innellahe serÄḟul hÄḟsab"
  14,52,"Haza belagul lin nasi ve li yunzeru bihÄḟ ve liyaÂṀlemu ennema huve ilahuv vahÄḟduv ve liyezzekkera ulul elbab"
  15,7,"Lev ma teÂṀtÄḟna bilmelaiketi in kunte mines sadikÄḟyn"
  15,8,"Ma nunezzilul melaikete illa bil hakkÄḟ ve ma kanu izem munzarin"
  15,9,"Inna nahnu nezzelnez zikra ve inna lehu le hafizun"
  15,10,"Ve le kad erselna min kablike siyeÄḟl evvelin"
  15,11,"Ve ma yeÂṀtÄḟhim mir rasulin illa kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  15,12,"Kezalike neslukuhu fÄḟ kulubil mucrimin"
  15,13,"La yuÂṀminune bihÄḟ ve kad halet sunnetul evvelin"
  15,14,"Ve lev fetahna aleyhim babem mines semai fe zallu fÄḟhi yaÂṀrucun"
  15,15,"Le kalu innema sukkirat ebsaruna bel nahnu kavmun meshurun"
  15,16,"Ve le kad cealna fis semai burucev ve zeyyennaha lin nazÄḟrÄḟn"
  15,17,"Ve hafÄḟznaha min kulli seytanir racÄḟm"
  15,18,"Illa menisterekas semÂṀa fe etbeahu sihabum mubÄḟn"
  15,19,"Vel erda medednaha ve elkayna fÄḟha ravasiye ve embetna fÄḟha min kulli seyÂṀim mevzun"
  15,20,"Ve cealna lekum fÄḟha meayise ve mel lestum lehu bi razikÄḟyn"
  15,21,"Ve im min seyÂṀin illa Äḟndena hazinuhu ve ma nunezziluhu illa bi kaderim maÂṀlum"
  15,22,"Ve erselner riyaha levakÄḟha fe enzelna mines semai maen fe eskaynakumuh ve ma entum lehu bi hazinÄḟn"
  15,23,"Ve inna le nahnu nuhyÄḟ ve numÄḟtu ve nahnul varisun"
  15,24,"Ve le kad alimnel mustakdimÄḟne minkum ve le kad alimnel musteÂṀhÄḟrÄḟn"
  15,25,"Ve inne rabbeke huve yahsuruhum innehu hakÄḟmun alÄḟm"
  15,26,"Ve le kad halaknel insane min salsalim min hameim mesnun"
  15,27,"Vel canne halaknahu min kablu min naris semum"
  15,28,"Ve iz kale rabbuke lil melaiketi innÄḟ halikum beseram min salsalim min hameim mesnun"
  15,29,"Fe iza sevveytuhu ve nefahtu fÄḟhi mir ruhÄḟy fekau lehu sacidÄḟn"
  15,30,"Fe secedel melaiketu kulluhum ecmeun"
  15,31,"Illa iblÄḟs eba ey yekune meas sacidÄḟn"
  15,32,"Kale ya iblÄḟsu ma leke ella tekune meas sacidÄḟn"
  15,33,"Kale lem ekul li escude li beserin halaktehu min salsalim min hameim mesnun"
  15,34,"Kale fahruc minha fe inneke racÄḟm"
  15,35,"Ve inne aleykel laÂṀnete ila yevmid dÄḟn"
  15,36,"Kale rabbi fe enzÄḟrnÄḟ ila yevmi yubÂṀasun"
  15,37,"Kale fe inneke minel munzarÄḟn"
  15,38,"Ila yevmil vaktil maÂṀlum"
  15,39,"Kale rabbi bima agveytenÄḟ le uzeyyinenne lehum fil erdÄḟ ve le ugviyennehum ecmeÄḟyn"
  15,40,"Illa Äḟbadeke minhumul muhlesÄḟyn"
  15,41,"Kale haza sÄḟratun aleyye mustekÄḟym"
  15,42,"Inne ÄḟbadÄḟ leyse leke aleyhim sultanun illa menittebeake minel gavÄḟn"
  15,43,"Ve inne cehenneme le mevÂṀÄḟduhum ecmeÄḟyn"
  15,44,"Leha sebÂṀatu ebvab likulli babim minhum cuzÂṀum maksum"
  15,45,"Innel muttekÄḟyne fÄḟ cennativ ve uyun"
  15,46,"Udhuluha bi selamin aminÄḟn"
  15,47,"Ve nezaÂṀna ma fÄḟ sudurihim min gÄḟllin Äḟhvanen ala sururim mutekabilÄḟn"
  15,48,"La yemessuhum fÄḟha nesabuv ve ma hum minha bi muhracÄḟn"
  15,49,"NebbiÂṀ ÄḟbadÄḟ ennÄḟ enel gafurur rahÄḟym"
  15,50,"Ve enne azabÄḟ huvel azabul elÄḟm"
  15,51,"Ve nebbiÂṀhum an dayfi ibrahÄḟm"
  15,52,"Iz dehalu aleyhi fe kalu selama kale inna minkum vecilun"
  15,53,"Kalu la tevcel inna nubessiruke bi gulamin alÄḟm"
  15,54,"Kale e bessertumunÄḟ ala em messeniyel kiberu fe bime tubessirun"
  15,55,"Kalu bessernake bil hakkÄḟ fe la tekum minel kanitÄḟyn"
  15,56,"Kale ve mey yaknetu mir rahmeti rabbihÄḟ illed dallun"
  15,57,"Kale fe ma hatbukum eyyuhel murselun"
  15,58,"Kalu inna ursilna ila kavmim mucrimÄḟn"
  15,59,"Illa ale lut inna le muneccuhum ecmeÄḟyn"
  15,60,"Illemraetehu kadderna inneha le minel gabirÄḟn"
  15,61,"Felemma cae ale lutnil murselun"
  15,62,"Kale innekum kavmumu munkerun"
  15,63,"Kalu bel ciÂṀnake bima kanu fÄḟhi yemterun"
  15,64,"Ve eteynake bil hakkÄḟ ve inna le sadikun"
  15,65,"Fe esri bi ehlike bi kÄḟtÂṀÄḟm minel leyli vettebÄḟÂṀ edbarahum ve la yeltefit minkum ehaduv vemdu haysu tuÂṀmerun"
  15,66,"Ve kadayna ileyhi zalikel emra enne dabira haulai maktuum musbihÄḟyn"
  15,67,"Ve cae ehlul medÄḟneti yestebsirun"
  15,68,"Kale inne haulai dayfÄḟ fe la tefdahun"
  15,69,"Vettekullahe ve la tuhzun"
  15,70,"Kalu e ve lem nenheke anil alemÄḟn"
  15,71,"Kale haulai benatÄḟ in kuntum faÄḟlÄḟn"
  15,72,"Le amruke innehum le fÄḟ sekratihim yaÂṀmehun"
  15,73,"Fe ehazethumus sayhatu musrikÄḟyn"
  15,74,"Fe cealna aliyeha safileha ve emtarna aleyhim hÄḟcaratem min siccÄḟl"
  15,75,"Inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil lil mutevessimÄḟn"
  15,76,"Ve inneha le bisebÄḟlim mukÄḟyn"
  15,77,"Inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatel lil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  15,78,"Ve in kane ashabul eyketi le zalimÄḟn"
  15,79,"Fentekamna minhum ve innehuma le bi imamim mubÄḟn"
  15,80,"Ve le kad kezzebe ashabul hÄḟcril murselÄḟn"
  15,81,"Ve ateynahum ayatina fe kanu anha muÂṀridÄḟyn"
  15,82,"Ve kanu yenhÄḟtune minel cibali buyuten aminÄḟn"
  15,83,"Fe ehazethumus sayhatu musbihÄḟyn"
  15,84,"Fe ma agna anhum ma kanu yeksibun"
  15,85,"Ve ma halaknes semavati vel erda ve ma beynehuma illa bil hakk ve innes saate le atiyetun fasfehÄḟs safhal cemÄḟl"
  15,86,"Inne rabbeke huvel hallakul alÄḟm"
  15,87,"Ve le kad ateynake sebÂṀam minel mesanÄḟ vel kurÂṀanel azÄḟym"
  15,88,"La temuddenne ayneyke ila ma mettaÂṀna bihÄḟ ezvacem minhum ve la tahzen aleyhim vahfÄḟd cenahake lil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  15,89,"Ve kul innÄḟ enen nezÄḟrul mubÄḟn"
  15,90,"Kema enzelna alel muktesimÄḟn"
  15,91,"EllezÄḟne cealul kurÂṀane ÄḟdÄḟyn"
  15,92,"Fe ve rabbike le nesÂṀelennehum ecmeÄḟyn"
  15,93,"Amma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  15,94,"FasdoaÂṀbima tuÂṀmeru ve aÂṀrÄḟd anil musrikÄḟn"
  15,95,"Inna kefeynakel mustehziÄḟn"
  15,96,"EllezÄḟne yecÂṀalune meallahi ilahen ahar fe sevfe yaÂṀlemun"
  15,97,"Ve le kad naÂṀlemu enneke yedÄḟyku sadruke bima yekulun"
  15,98,"Fe sebbÄḟh bi hamdi rabbike ve kum mines sacidÄḟn"
  15,99,"VeÂṀbud rabbeke hatta yeÂṀtiyekel yekÄḟyn"
  16,8,"Vel hayle vel bigale vel hamira li terkebuha ve zÄḟneh ve yahluku ma la taÂṀlemun"
  16,9,"Ve alellahi kasdus sebÄḟli ve minha cair ve lev sae le hedakum ecmeÄḟyn"
  16,10,"HuvellezÄḟ enzele mines semai mael lekum minhu serabuv ve minhu secerun fÄḟhi tusiymun"
  16,11,"Yumbitu lekum bihiz zerÂṀa vez zeytune ven nehÄḟyle ven aÂṀnabe ve min kullis semarat inne fÄḟ zalike le ayetel li kavmiy yetefekkerun"
  16,12,"Ve sehhara lekumul leyle ven nehara ves semse vel kaner ven nucumu musahharatum bi emrih inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  16,13,"Ve ma zerae lekum fil erdÄḟ muhtelifen elvanuh inne fÄḟ zalike le ayetel li kavmiy yezzekkerun"
  16,14,"Ve huvellezÄḟ sehharal bahra li teÂṀkulu minhu lahmen tariyyev ve testahricu minhu hÄḟlyeten telbesuneha ve teral fulke mevahÄḟra fÄḟhi ve li tebtegu min fadlihÄḟ ve leallekum teskurun"
  16,15,"Ve elka fil erdÄḟ ravasiye en temÄḟde bikum ve enharav ve subulel leallekum tehtedun"
  16,16,"Ve alamat ve bin necmi hum yehtedun"
  16,17,"E fe mey yahluku ke mel la yahluk e fe la tezekkerun"
  16,18,"Ve in teuddu nÄḟÂṀmetellahi la tuhsuha innellahe le gafurur rahÄḟym"
  16,19,"Vallahu yaÂṀlemu ma tusirrune ve ma tuÂṀlinun"
  16,20,"VellezÄḟne yedÂṀune min dunillahi la yahlukune seyÂṀev ve hum yuhlekun"
  16,21,"Emvatun gayru ahyaÂṀ ve ma yesÂṀurune eyyane yubÂṀasun"
  16,22,"Ilahukum ilahuv vahÄḟd fellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune bil ahÄḟrati kulubuhum munkiratuv ve hum mustekbirun"
  16,23,"La cerame ennellahe yaÂṀlemu ma yusirrune ve ma yuÂṀlinun innehu la yuhÄḟbbul mustekbirÄḟn"
  16,24,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehum maza enzele rabbukum kalu esatÄḟyrul evvelÄḟn"
  16,25,"Li yahmilu evzarahum kamiletey yevmel kÄḟyameti ve min evzarillezÄḟne yudÄḟllunehum bi gayri Äḟlm e la sae ma yezirun"
  16,26,"Kad mekarallezÄḟne min kablihim fe etellahu bunyanehum minel kavaÄḟdi fe harra aleyhimus sakfu min fevkÄḟhim ve etahumul azabu min haysu la yesÂṀurun"
  16,27,"Summe yevmel kÄḟyameti yuhzÄḟhum ve yekulu eyne surakaiyellezÄḟne kuntum tusakkune fÄḟhim kalellezÄḟne utul Äḟlme innel hÄḟzyel yevme ves sue lalel kafirÄḟn"
  16,28,"EllezÄḟne teteveffahumul melaiketu zalimÄḟ enfusihim fe elkavus seleme ma kunna naÂṀmelu min suÂṀ bela innellahe alÄḟmum bima kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  16,29,"Fedhulu ebvabe cehenneme halidÄḟne fÄḟha fe lebiÂṀse mesvel mutekebbirÄḟn"
  16,30,"Ve kÄḟyle lillezÄḟnettekav maza enzele rabbukum kalu hayra lillezÄḟne ahsenu fÄḟ hazihÄḟd dunya haseneh ve le darul ahÄḟrati hayr ve le nÄḟÂṀme darul muttekÄḟyn"
  16,31,"Cennatu adniy yedhuluneha tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu lehum fÄḟha ma yesaun kezalike yeczillahul muttekÄḟyn"
  16,32,"EllezÄḟne teteveffahumul melaiketu tayyibÄḟne yekulune selamun aleykumudhulul cennete bima kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  16,33,"Hel yenzurune illa en teÂṀtiyehumul melaiketu ev yeÂṀtiye emru rabbik kezalike fealellezÄḟne min kablihim ve ma zalemehumullahu ve lakin kanu enfusehum yazlimun"
  16,34,"Fe esabehum seyyiatu ma amilu ve haka bihim ma kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  16,35,"Ve kalellezÄḟne esraku lev saellahu ma abedna min dunihÄḟ min seyÂṀin nahnu ve la abauna ve la harramna min dunihÄḟ min seyÂṀ kezalike fealellezÄḟne min kablihim fe hel aler rusuli illel belagul mubÄḟn"
  16,36,"Ve le kad beasna fÄḟ kulli ummetir rasulen enÄḟÂṀbudullahe vectenibut tagut fe minhum men hedellahu ve minhum men hakkat aleyhid dalaleh fe sÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetul mukezzibÄḟn"
  16,37,"In tahrÄḟs ala hudahum fe innellahe la yehdÄḟ mey yudÄḟllu ve ma lehum min nasÄḟrÄḟn"
  16,38,"Ve aksemu billahi cehde eymanihim la yebÂṀasullahu mey yemut bela vaÂṀden aleyhi hakkav ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yaÂṀlemun"
  16,39,"Li yubeyyine lehumullezÄḟ yahtelifune fÄḟhi ve li yaÂṀlemellezÄḟne keferu ennehum kanu kazibÄḟn"
  16,40,"Innema kavluna li seyÂṀin iza eradnahu en nekule lehu kun fe yekun"
  16,41,"VellezÄḟne haceru fillahi mim baÂṀdi ma zulimu le nubevviennehum fid dunya haseneh ve le ecrul ahÄḟrati ekber lev kanu yaÂṀlemun"
  16,42,"EllezÄḟne saberu ve ala rabbihim yetevekkelun"
  16,43,"Ve ma erselna min kablike illa ricalen nuhÄḟy ileyhim fesÂṀelu ehlez zikri in kuntum la taÂṀlemun"
  16,44,"Bil beyyinati vez zubur ve enzelna ileykez zikra li tubeyyine linnasi ma nuzzile ileyhim ve leallehum yetefekkerun"
  16,45,"E fe eminellezÄḟne mekerus seyyiati ey yahsifellahu bihimul erda ev yeÂṀtiyehumul azabu min haysu la yasÂṀurun"
  16,46,"Ev yeÂṀhuzehum fÄḟ tekallubihim fe ma hum bi muÂṀcizÄḟn"
  16,47,"Ev yeÂṀhuzehum ala tehavvuf fe inne rabbekum le raufur rahÄḟym"
  16,48,"E ve lem yerav ila ma halekallahu min seyÂṀiy yetefeyyeu zÄḟlaluhu anil yemÄḟni ves semaili succedel lillahi ve hum dahÄḟrun"
  16,49,"Ve lillahi yescudu ma fis semavati ve ma fil erdÄḟ min dabbetiv vel melaiketue hum la yestekbirun"
  16,50,"Yehafune rabbehum min fevkÄḟhim ve yefÂṀalune ma yuÂṀmerun"
  16,51,"Ve kalellahu la tettehÄḟzu ilaheynisneyn innema huve ilahuv vahÄḟd fe iyyaye ferhebun"
  16,52,"Ve lehu ma fis semavati vel erdÄḟ ve lehud dÄḟnu vasÄḟba e fe gayrallahi tettekun"
  16,53,"Ve ma bukum min nÄḟÂṀmetin fe minellahi summe iza messekumud durru fe ileyhi tecÂṀerun"
  16,54,"Summe iza kesefed durra ankum iza ferÄḟkum minkum bi rabbihim yusrikun (49.ayet secde ayetedir)"
  16,55,"Li yekfuru bima ateynahum fe temetteu fe sevfe taÂṀlemun"
  16,56,"Ve yecÂṀalune li ma la ya7lemune nasÄḟybem mimma razaknahum tellahi le tusÂṀelunne amma kuntum tefterun"
  16,57,"Ve yecÂṀalune lillahil benati subhanehu ve lehum ma yestehun"
  16,58,"Ve iza bussira ehaduhum bil unsa zalle vechuhu musveddev ve huve kezÄḟym"
  16,59,"Yetevara minel kavmi min sui ma bussira bih e yumsikuhu ala hunin em yedussuhu fit turab e la sae ma yahkumun"
  16,60,"LillezÄḟne la yuÂṀminine bel ahÄḟrate meselus sevÂṀ ve lillahil meselul aÂṀla ve huvel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  16,61,"Ve lev yuahÄḟzullahun nase bi zulmihim ma terake aleyha min dabbetiv ve lakiy yuehhÄḟruhum ila ecelim musemma fe iza cae eceluhum la yesteÂṀhÄḟrune saatev ve la yestakdimun"
  16,62,"Ve yecÂṀalune lillahi ma yekrahune ve tesÄḟfu elsinetuhumul kezibe enne lehumul husna la cerame enne lehumun nara ve ennehum mufratun"
  16,63,"Tellahi le kad erselna ila umemim min kablike fe zeyyene lehumus seytanu aÂṀmalehum fe huve veliyyuhumul yevme ve lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  16,64,"Ve ma enzelna aleykel kitabe illa li tubeyyine lehumullezÄḟhtelefu fÄḟhi ve hudev ve rahmetel li kavmiy yuÂṀmininun"
  16,65,"Vallahu enzele mines semai maen fe ahya bihil erda baÂṀde mevtiha inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatel li kavmiy yesmeun"
  16,66,"Ve inne lekum fil enÂṀami le Äḟbrah nuskÄḟykum mimma fÄḟ butunihÄḟ mim beyni fersiv ve demil lebenen halisan saigal lis saribÄḟn"
  16,67,"Ve min semaratin nehÄḟyli vel aÂṀnabi tettehÄḟzune minhu sekerav ve rizkan hasena inne fÄḟ zalike le ayetel li kavmiy yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  16,68,"Ve evha rabbuke ilen nahli enittehÄḟzÄḟ minel cibali buyutev ve mines seceri ve mimma yaÂṀrisun"
  16,69,"Summe kulÄḟ min kulles semarati feslukÄḟ subule rabbiki zulula yahrucu mim butuniha serabum muhtelifun elvanuhu fÄḟhi sifaul linnas inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatel li kavmiy yetefekkerun"
  16,70,"Vallahu halekakum summe yeteveffakum ve minkum mey yuraddu ila erzelil umuri li keyla yaÂṀleme baÂṀde Äḟlmin seyÂṀa innellahe alÄḟmun kadÄḟr"
  16,71,"Vallahu faddale baÂṀdakum ala baÂṀdÄḟn fir rÄḟzk femellezÄḟne fuddÄḟlu bi raddÄḟ rizkÄḟhim ala ma meleket eymanuhum fe hum fÄḟhi sevaÂṀ ife bi nÄḟÂṀmetillahi yechadun"
  16,72,"Vallahu ceale lekum min enfusikum ezvacev ve ceale lekum min ezvacikum benÄḟne ve hafedetev ve razekakum minet tayyibat e fe bil batÄḟli yuÂṀminune ve bi nÄḟÂṀmetillahi hum yekfurun"
  16,73,"Ve yaÂṀbudune min dunillahi ma la yemliku lehum rizskam mines semavati vel erdÄḟ seyÂṀev ve la yestetÄḟyÂṀun"
  16,74,"Fe la tadribu lillahil emsal innellahe yaÂṀlemu ve entum la taÂṀlemun"
  16,75,"Darabellahu meselen abdem memlukel la yakdiru ala seyÂṀiv ve mer razaknahu minna zirkan hasenen fe huve yunfiku minhu sirrav ve cehra hel yestevun elhamdu lillah bel ekseruhum la yaÂṀlemun"
  16,76,"Ve darabellahu meseler raculeyni ehaduhuma ebkemu la yakdiru ala seyÂṀiv ve huve kellun ala mevlahu eynema yuveccihhu la yeÂṀti bi hayr hel yestevÄḟ huve ve mey yeÂṀmuru bil adli ve huve ala sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  16,77,"Ve lillahi gaybus semavati vel ard ve ma emrus saati illa ke lemhÄḟl besari ev huve akrab innellahe ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  16,78,"Vallahu ahracekum mim butuni ummehatikum la taÂṀlemune seyÂṀev ve ceale lekumus semÂṀa vel ebsara vel efÂṀidete leallekum teskurun"
  16,79,"E lem yerav ilet tayri musehharatin fÄḟ cevvis semaÂṀ ma yumsikuhunne illellah inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  16,80,"Vallahu ceale lekum min culudil enÂṀami buyuten testehÄḟffuneha yevme zaÂṀnikum ve yevme ikametikum ve min asvafiha ve evbariha ve esÂṀariha esasev ve metaan ila hÄḟyn"
  16,81,"Vallahu ceale lekum mimma haleka zÄḟlalev ve ceale lekum minel cibali eknanev ve ceale lekum serabiyle tekÄḟykumul harra ve serabiyle tekÄḟykum beÂṀsekum kezalike yutimmu nÄḟÂṀmetehu aleykum leallekum tuslimun"
  16,82,"Fe in tevellev fe innemu aleykel belagul mubÄḟn"
  16,83,"YaÂṀrifune nÄḟÂṀmetellahi summe yunkiruneha ve ekseruhumul kafirun"
  16,84,"Ve yevme nebÂṀasu min kulli ummetin sehÄḟden summe la yuÂṀzenu lillezÄḟne keferu ve la hum yustaÂṀtebun"
  16,85,"Ve iza raellezÄḟne zalemul azabe fe la yuhaffefu anhum ve la hum yunzarun"
  16,86,"Ve iza raellezÄḟne esraku surakaehum kalu rabbena haulai surakaunellezÄḟne kunna nedÂṀu min dunik fe elkav ileyhimul kavle innekum le kazibun"
  16,87,"Ve elkav ilellahi yevmeizinis seleme ve dalle anhum ma kanu yefterun"
  16,88,"EllezÄḟne keferu ve saddu an sebÄḟlillahi zidnahum azaben fevkal azabi bima kanu yufsidun"
  16,89,"Ve yevme nebÂṀazu fÄḟ kulli ummetin sehÄḟden ala haulaÂṀ ve nezzelna aleykel kitabe tibyanel likulli seyÂṀiv ve hudev ve rahmetev ve busra lil muslimÄḟn"
  16,90,"Innellahe yeÂṀmuru bil adli vel Äḟhsani ve Äḟtai zil kurba ve yenha anil fahsai vel munkeri vel bagy yeÄḟzukum leallekum tezekkerun"
  16,91,"Ve evfu bi ahdillahi iza ahettum ve la tenkudul eymane baÂṀde tevkÄḟdiha ve kad cealtumullahe aleykum kefÄḟla innellahe yaÂṀlemu ma tefÂṀalun"
  16,92,"Ve la tekunu kelletÄḟ nekadat gazleha mim baÂṀdi kuvvetin enkasa tettehÄḟzune eymanekum dehalem beynekum en tekune ummetun hiye erba min ummeh innema yeblukumullahu bih ve le yubeyyinenne lekum yevmel kÄḟyameti ma kuntum fÄḟhi tahtelifun"
  16,93,"Ve lev saellahu le ceallekum ummetev vahÄḟdetev ve lakiy yudÄḟllu mey yesau ve yehdoÄḟ mey yesaÂṀ ve le tusÂṀelunne amma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  16,94,"Ve la tettehÄḟzu eymanekum dehalem beynekum fe tezille kademum baÂṀde subutiha ve tezukus sue bima sadedtum an sebÄḟlillah ve lekum azabum azÄḟym"
  16,95,"Ve la testeru bi ahdillahi semenen kalÄḟla innema Äḟndellahi huve hayrul lekum in kuntum taÂṀlemun"
  16,96,"Ma Äḟndekum yenfedu ve ma Äḟndellahi bak ve le necziyennellezÄḟne saberu ecrahum bi ahseni ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  16,97,"Men amile saliham min zekerin ev unsa ve huve muÂṀminun fe le nuhyiyennehu hayaten tayyibeh ve la necziyennehum ecrahum bi ahseni ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  16,98,"Fe iza karaÂṀtel kurÂṀane festeÄḟz billahi mines seytanir racÄḟm"
  16,99,"Innehu leyse lehu sultanun alellezÄḟne amenu ve ala rabbihim yetevekkelun"
  16,100,"Innema sultanuhu alellezÄḟne yetevellevnehu vellezÄḟne hum bihÄḟ musrikun"
  16,101,"Ve iza beddelna ayetem mekane ayetiv vallahu aÂṀlemu bima yunezzilu kalu innema ente mufter bel ekseruhum la yaÂṀlemun"
  16,102,"Kul nezzelehu ruhul kudusi mir rabbike bil hakkÄḟ li yusebbitellezÄḟne amenu ve hudev ve busra lil muslimÄḟn"
  16,103,"Ve le kad naÂṀlemu ennehum yekulune innema yuallimuhu besar lisanullezÄḟ yulhÄḟdune ileyhi aÂṀcemiyyuv ve haza lisanun arabiyyum mubÄḟn"
  16,104,"InnellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune bi ayatillahi la yehdÄḟhimullahu ve lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  16,105,"Innema yefteril kezibellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune bi ayatillah ve ulaike humul kazibun"
  16,106,"Men kefera billahi mim baÂṀdi ÄḟmanihÄḟ illa men ukrihe ve kalbuhu mutmeinum bil Äḟmani ve lakim men seraha bil kufri sadran fe aleyhim gadabum minellah ve lehum azabun azÄḟym"
  16,107,"Zalike bi ennehumustehabbul hayated dunya alel ahÄḟratu ve ennellahe la yehdil kavmel kafirÄḟn"
  16,108,"UlaikellezÄḟne tabeallahu ala kulubihim ve semÂṀÄḟhim ve ebsarihim ve ulaike humul gafilun"
  16,109,"La cerame ennehum fil ahÄḟrati humul hasirun"
  16,110,"Summe inne rabbeke lillezÄḟne haceru mim baÂṀdi ma futinu summe cahedu ve saberu inne rabbeke mim baÂṀdiha le gafurur rahÄḟym"
  16,111,"Yevme teÂṀtÄḟ kullu nefsin tucadilu an nefsiha ve tuveffa kullu nefsim ma amilet ve hum la yuzlemun"
  16,112,"Ve darabellahu meselen karyeten kanet aminetem mutmeinnetey yeÂṀtÄḟha rizkuha ragadem min kulli mekanin fe keferat bi enÂṀumillahi fe ezakahallahu libasel cuÄḟ vel havfi bima kanu yasneun"
  16,113,"Ve le kad caehum rasulum minhum fe kezzebuhu fe ehazehumul azabu ve hum zalimun"
  16,114,"Fe kulu mimma razekakumullahu halalen tayyibev veskuru nÄḟÂṀmetellahi in kuntum iyyahu taÂṀbudun"
  16,115,"Innema harrama aleykumul meytete ved deme ve lahmel hÄḟnzÄḟri ve ma uhille li gayrillahi bih fe menidturra gayra bagÄḟv ve la adin fe innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  16,116,"Ve la tekulu lima tesÄḟfu elsinetukumul kezibe haza halaluv ve haza haramul li tefteru alellahil kezib innellezÄḟne yefterune alellahil kezibe la yuflihun"
  16,117,"Metaun kalÄḟluv ve lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  16,118,"Ve alellezÄḟne hadu harramna ma kasasna aleyke min kabl ve ma zalemnahum ve lakin kanu enfusehum yazlimun"
  16,119,"Summe inne rabbeke lillezÄḟne amilus sue bi cehaletin summe tabu mim baÂṀdi zalike ve aslehu inne rabbeke mim baÂṀdiha le gafurur rahÄḟym"
  16,120,"Inne ibrahÄḟme kane ummeten kanitel lillahi hanÄḟfa ve lem yeku minel musrikÄḟn"
  16,121,"Sakiral li enÂṀumih ictebahu ve hedahu ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  16,122,"Ve ateynahu fid dunya haseneh ve innehu fil ahÄḟrati le mines salihÄḟyn"
  16,123,"Summe evhayna ileyke enittebÄḟÂṀ millete ibrahÄḟme hanÄḟfa ve ma kane minel musrikÄḟn"
  16,124,"Innema cuÄḟles sebtu alellezÄḟnahtelefu fÄḟh ve inne rabbeke le yahkumu beynehum yevmel kÄḟyameti fÄḟma kanu fÄḟhi yahtelifun"
  16,125,"UdÂṀu ila sebÄḟli rabbike bil hÄḟkmeti vel mevÂṀÄḟzatil haseneti ve cadilhum billetÄḟ hiye ahsen inne rabbeke huve aÂṀlemu bi men dalle an sebÄḟlihÄḟ ve huve aÂṀlemu bil muhtedÄḟn"
  16,126,"Ve in akabtum fe akÄḟbu bi misli ma ukÄḟbtum bih ve lein sabertum le huve hayrul lissabirÄḟn"
  16,127,"Vasbir ve ma sabruke illa billahi ve la tahzen aleyhim ve la teku fÄḟ daykÄḟm mimma yemkurum"
  16,128,"Innellahe meallezÄḟnettekav vellezÄḟne hum muhsinun"
  17,8,"Asa rabbukum ey yerhamekum ve in udtum udna ve cealna cehenneme lil kafirÄḟne hasÄḟyra"
  17,9,"Inne hazel kurÂṀane yehdÄḟ lilletÄḟ hiye akvemu ve yubessirul muÂṀminÄḟnellezÄḟne yaÂṀmelunes salihati enne lehum ecran kebÄḟra"
  17,10,"Ve ennellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune bil ahÄḟrati aÂṀtedna lehum azaben elÄḟma"
  17,11,"Ve yedÂṀul insanu bis serri duaehu bil hayr ve kanel insanu acula"
  17,12,"Ve cealnel leyle ven nehara ayeteyni fe mehavna ayetel leyli ve cealna ayeten nehari mubsÄḟratel li tebtegu fadlem mir rabbikum ve li taÂṀlemu adedes sinÄḟne vel hÄḟsab ve kulle seyÂṀin fassalnahu tefsÄḟyla"
  17,13,"Ve kulle insanin elzemnahu tairahu fÄḟ unukÄḟh ve nuhricu lehu yevmel kÄḟyameti kitabey yelkahu mensura"
  17,14,"IkraÂṀ kitabek kefa bi nefsikel yevme aleyke hasÄḟba"
  17,15,"Menihteda fe innema yehtedÄḟ li nefsih ve men dalle fe innema yedÄḟllu aleyha ve la teziru vaziratuv vizra uhra ve ma kunna muazzibÄḟne hatt nebÂṀase rasula"
  17,16,"Ve iza eradna en nuhlike karyeten emarna mutrafÄḟha fe fesku fÄḟha fe hakka aleyhel kavlu fe demmernaha tedmÄḟra"
  17,17,"Ve kem ehlena minel kuruni mim baÂṀdi nuh ve kefa bi rabbike bi zunubi ÄḟbadihÄḟ habÄḟram besÄḟyra"
  17,18,"Men kane yurÄḟdul acilete accelna lehu fiha ma nesau li men nurÄḟdu summe cealna lehu cehennem yaslaha mezmumem medhura"
  17,19,"Ve men eradel ahÄḟrate ve sea leha saÂṀyeha ve huve muÂṀminun fe ulaike kane saÂṀyuhum meskura"
  17,20,"Kullen numiddu haulai ve haulai min atai rabbik ve ma kane atau rabbike mahzura"
  17,21,"Unzur keyfe faddalna baÂṀdahum ala baÂṀd ve lel ahÄḟratu ekberu deracativ ve ekberu tefdÄḟyla"
  17,22,"La tecÂṀal meallahi ilahen ahara fe takÂṀude mezmumem mahzula"
  17,23,"Ve kada rabbuke elle taÂṀbudu illa iyyahu ve bil valedeyni Äḟhsana imma yebluganne Äḟndekel kibera ehaduhuma ev kilahuma fe la tekul lehuma uffiv ve la tenher huma ve kul lehuma kavlen kerÄḟma"
  17,24,"VahfÄḟd lehuma cenahaz zulli miner rahmeti ve kur rabbirhamhuma kema rabbeyanÄḟ sagÄḟyra"
  17,25,"Rabbukum aÂṀlemu bima fÄḟ nufusikum in tekunu salihÄḟyne fe innehu kane lil evvabÄḟne gafura"
  17,26,"Ve ati zel kurba hakkahu vel miskÄḟne vebnes sebÄḟli ve la tubezzir tebzÄḟra"
  17,27,"Innel mubezzirÄḟne kanu Äḟhvanes seyatÄḟyn ve kanes seytanu li rabbihÄḟ kefura"
  17,28,"Ve imma tuÂṀridanne anhumubtigae rahmetim mir rabbike tercuha fe kul lehum kavlem meysura"
  17,29,"Ve la tecÂṀal yedek magluleten ila unukike ve la tebsutha kullel bestÄḟ fe takÂṀude melumem mahsura"
  17,30,"Inne rabbeke yebsutur riska li mey yesau ve yakdir innehu kane bi ÄḟbadihÄḟ habÄḟram besÄḟyra"
  17,31,"Ve la taktulu evladekum hasyete imlak nahnu nerzukuhum ve iyyakum inne katlehum kane hitÂṀen kebÄḟra"
  17,32,"Ve la takrabuz zina innehu kane fahÄḟseh ve sae sebÄḟla"
  17,33,"Ve la taktulun nefselletÄḟ harramellahu illa bil hakk ve men kutile mazlumen fe kad cealna li veliyyihÄḟ sultanen fe la yusrif fil katl innehu kane mensura"
  17,34,"Ve la takrabu malel yetÄḟmi illa billetÄḟ hiye ahsenu hatta yebluga esuddehu ve evfu bil ahd innel ahde kane mesÂṀula"
  17,35,"Ve evful keyle iza kiltum vesinu bil kÄḟstasil mustekÄḟym zalike hayruv ve hasenu teÂṀvÄḟla"
  17,36,"Ve la takfu ma leyse leke bihÄḟ Äḟlm innes semÂṀa vel besara vel fuade kullu ulaike kane anhu mesÂṀula"
  17,37,"Ve la temsi fil erdÄḟ merah inneka len tahrikal erda ve len teblugal cibale tula"
  17,38,"Kullu zalike kane seyyiuhu Äḟnde rabbike mekruha"
  17,39,"Zalike mimma evha ileyke rabbuke minel hÄḟkmeh ve la tecÂṀal meallahi ilahen ahara fe tulka fÄḟ cehenneme melumem medhura"
  17,40,"E fe asfakum rabbukum bil benÄḟne vettehaze minel melaiketi inasa inneku le tekulune kavlen azÄḟyma"
  17,41,"Ve le kad sarrafna fÄḟ hazel kurÂṀani li yezzekkeru ve ma yezÄḟduhum illa nufura"
  17,42,"Kul lev kane meahu alihetun kema yekulune izel lebtegav ila zil arsi sebÄḟla"
  17,43,"Subhanehu ve teala amma yekulune uluvven kebÄḟra"
  17,44,"Tusebbihu lehus semavatus sebÂṀu vel erdu ve men fÄḟhinn ve im min seyÂṀin illa yusebbihu bi hamdihÄḟ ve lakil la tefkahune tesbÄḟhahum innehu kane halimen gafura"
  17,45,"Ve iza karaÂṀtel kurÂṀane cealna beyneke ve beynellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune bil ahÄḟrati hÄḟcabem mestura"
  17,46,"Ve cealna ala kulubihim ekinneten ey yefkahuhu ve fÄḟ azanihim vakra ve iza zekerte rabbeke fil kurÂṀani vahdehu vellev ala edbarihim nufura"
  17,47,"Nahnu aÂṀlemu bima yestemiune bihÄḟ iz yestemiune ileyke ve iz hum necva iz yekuluz zalimune in tetteiune illa raculem meshura"
  17,48,"Unzur keyfe darabu lekel emsale fe dallu fela yestetfyÂṀune sebÄḟla"
  17,49,"Ve kalu e iza kunna Äḟzamev ve rufaten en inna le mebÂṀusune halkan cedÄḟda"
  17,50,"Kul kunu hÄḟcareten ev hadÄḟda"
  17,51,"Ev halkam mimma yekburu fÄḟ sudurikum fe seyekulune mey yuÄḟyduna kulillezÄḟ fetarakum evvele merrah feseyungÄḟdune ileyke ruusehum ve yekulune meta hu kul asa ey yekune karÄḟba"
  17,52,"Yevme yedÂṀukum fe testecÄḟbune bi hamdihÄḟ ve tezunnune il lebistum illa kalila"
  17,53,"Ve kul li ÄḟbadÄḟ yekululletÄḟ hiye ahsen innes seytane yenzegu beynehum innes seytane kane lil insani aduvvem mubÄḟna"
  17,54,"Rabbukum aÂṀlemu bilkum iy yeseÂṀ yerhamkum ev iy yeseÂṀ yuazzibkum ve ma erselnake aleyhim vekÄḟla"
  17,55,"Ve rabbuke aÂṀlemu bi men fis semavati vel ard ve le kad faddalna baÂṀdan nebiyyÄḟne ala baÂṀdÄḟv ve ateyna davude zebura"
  17,56,"KulidÂṀullezÄḟne zeamtaum min dunihÄḟ fe la yemlikune kesfed durri ankum ve la tahvÄḟla"
  17,57,"UlaikellezÄḟne yedÂṀune yebtegune illa rabbihimul vesÄḟlete eyyuhum akrabu ve yercune rahmetehu ve yehafune azabeh inne azabe rabbike kane mahzura"
  17,58,"Ve im min karyetin illa nahnu muhlikuha kable yevmil kÄḟyameti ev muazzibuha azaben sedÄḟda kane zalike fil kitabi mestura"
  17,59,"Ve ma meneana en nursile bil ayati illa en kezzebe bihel evvelun ve ateyna semuden nakate mubsÄḟraten fe zalemu biha ve ma nursilu bil ayati illa tahvÄḟfa"
  17,60,"Ve iz kulna leke inne rabbeke ehata bin nas ve ma cealner ruÂṀyelletÄḟ eraynake illa fitnetel linnasi ves seceratel melÂṀunete fil kurÂṀan ve nuhavvifuhum fe ma yezÄḟduhum illa tugyanen kebÄḟra"
  17,61,"Ve iz kulna lil melaiketiscudu li ademe fe secedu illa iblÄḟs kale e escudu li men halakte tÄḟyna"
  17,62,"Kale e raeyteke hazellezÄḟ kerramte aleyye le in ehherteni ila yevmil kÄḟyameti le ahtenikenne zurriyyetehu illa kalÄḟla"
  17,63,"Kalezheb fe men tebiake minhum fe inne cehenneme ceazukum cezaem mevfura"
  17,64,"Vestefziz menistetaÂṀte minhum bi savtike ve eclib aleyhim bi haylike ve racilike ve sarikhum fil emvali vel evladi veÄḟdhum ve ma yeÄḟduhumus seytanu illa gurura"
  17,65,"Inne ÄḟbadÄḟ leyse leke aleyhim sultan ve kefa bi rabbike vekÄḟla"
  17,66,"RabbukumullezÄḟ yuzcÄḟ lekumul fulke fil bahri li tebtegu min fadlih innehu kane bi kum rahÄḟyma"
  17,67,"Ve iza messekumud durru fil bahri dalle men tedÂṀune illa iyyah felemma neccakum ilel berri aÂṀradtum ve kanel insanu kefura"
  17,68,"E fe emintum ey yahsife bikum canibel berri ev yursile aleykum hasÄḟben summe la tecidu lekum vekÄḟla"
  17,69,"Em emintum ey yuÄḟydekim fÄḟhi taraten uhra fe yursile aleykum kasÄḟfem miner rÄḟhÄḟ fe yugrikakum bima kefartum summe la tecidu lekum aleyna bihÄḟ tebÄḟa"
  17,70,"Ve le kad kerramna benÄḟ ademe ve hamelnahum fil berri vel bahri ve razaknahum minet tayyibati ve faddalnahum ala kesÄḟrim mimmen halakna tefdÄḟyla"
  17,71,"Yevme nedÂṀu kulle unasim bi imamihim fe men utiye kitabehu bi yemÄḟnihÄḟ fe ulaike yakraune kitabehum ve la yuzlemune fetÄḟla"
  17,72,"Ve men kane fÄḟ hazihÄḟ aÂṀma fe huve fil ahÄḟrati aÂṀma ve edallu sebÄḟla"
  17,73,"Ve in kadu le yeftinuneke anillezÄḟ evhayna ileyke li tefteriye aleyna gayrahu ve izel lettehazuke halÄḟla"
  17,74,"Ve lev la en sebbetnake le kad kidte terkenu ileyhim seyÂṀen kalÄḟla"
  17,75,"Izel le ezaknake dÄḟÂṀfel hayati ve dÄḟÂṀfel memati summe la tecidu leke aleyna nesÄḟyra"
  17,76,"Ve in kadu leyestefizzuneke minel erdÄḟ li yuhricuke minha ve izel la yelbesune hÄḟlafeke illa kalÄḟla"
  17,77,"Sunnete men kad erselna kableke mir rusulina ve la tecidu li sunnetina tahvÄḟla"
  17,78,"EkÄḟmes salate li dulukus semsi ila gasekÄḟl leyli ve kurÂṀanel fecr inne kurÂṀanel fecri kane meshuda"
  17,79,"Ve minel leyli fe tehecced bihÄḟ nafiletel leke asa ey yebÂṀaseke rabbuke mekamem mahmuda"
  17,80,"Ve kur rabbi edhÄḟlnÄḟ mudhale sÄḟdkÄḟv ve ahricnÄḟ muhrace sÄḟdkÄḟv vecÂṀal lÄḟ mil ledunke sultanen nesÄḟyra"
  17,81,"Ve kul cael hakku ve zehekal batÄḟl innel batÄḟle kane zehuka"
  17,82,"Ve nunezzilu minel kurÂṀani ma huve sifauv ve rahmetul lil muÂṀminÄḟne ve la yezÄḟduz zalimÄḟne illa hasara"
  17,83,"Ve iza enÂṀamna alel insani aÂṀrada ve nea bi canibih ve iza messehus serru kane yeusa"
  17,84,"Kul kulluy yaÂṀmelu ala sakiletih fe rabbukum aÂṀlemu bi men huve ehda sebÄḟla"
  17,85,"Ve yesÂṀeluneke anir ruh kulir ruhu min emri rabbÄḟ ve ma utÄḟtum minel Äḟlmi illa kalÄḟla"
  17,86,"Ve lein siÂṀna le nezhebenne billezÄḟ evhayna ileyke summe la tecidu leke bihÄḟ aleyna vekÄḟla"
  17,87,"Illa rahmetem mir rabbik inne fadlehu kane aleyke kebÄḟra"
  17,88,"Kul leinictemeatil insu vel cinnu ala ey yeÂṀtu bi misli hazel kurÂṀani la yeÂṀtune bi mislihÄḟ ve lev kane baÂṀduhum li baÂṀdÄḟn zahÄḟra"
  17,89,"Ve le kad sarrafna lin nasi fÄḟ hazel kurÂṀani min kulli meselin fe eba ekserun nasi illa kufura"
  17,90,"Ve kalu len nuÂṀmine leke hatta tef cura lena minel erdÄḟ yembua"
  17,91,"Ev tekune leke cennetum min nehÄḟyliv ve Äḟnebin fe tufecciral enhara hÄḟlaleha tefcÄḟra"
  17,92,"Ev tuskÄḟtas semae kema zeamte aleyna kisefen ev teÂṀtiye billahi vel melaiketi kabÄḟla"
  17,93,"Ev yekune leke beytum min zuhrufin ev terka fis semaÂṀ min kulli meselin fe eba ekserun nasi illa kufura ve len nuÂṀmine li rukÄḟyyike hatta tunezzile aleyna kitaben nakrauh kul subhane rabbÄḟ hel kuntu illa beserar rasula"
  17,94,"Ve ma menean nase ey yuÂṀminu iz caehumul huda illa en kalu e beasellahu beserar rasula"
  17,95,"Kul lev kane fil erdÄḟ melaiketuy yemsune mutmeinnÄḟne le nezzelna aleyhim mines semai meleker rasula"
  17,96,"Kul kefa billahi sehÄḟdem beynÄḟ ve beynekum innehu kane bi ÄḟbadihÄḟ habÄḟram besÄḟyra"
  17,97,"Ve mey yehdillahu fe huvel muhted ve mey yudlil fe len tecide lehum evliyae min dunih ve nahsuruhum yevmel kÄḟyameti ala vucuhihim umyev ve bukmev ve summa meÂṀvahum cehennem kullema habet zidnahum seÄḟyra"
  17,98,"Zalike cezauhum bi ennehum keferu bi ayatina ve kalu e iza kunna Äḟzamev ve rufaten e inna le mebÂṀusune halkan cedÄḟda"
  17,99,"E ve lem yerav ennellahellezÄḟ halekas semavati vel erda kadirun ala ey yahluka mislehum ve ceale lehum ecelel la raybe fÄḟh fe ebez zalimune illa kufura"
  17,100,"Kul lev entum temlikune hazine rahmeti rabbÄḟ izel le emsektum hesyetel infak ve kanel insanu katura"
  17,101,"Ve le kad ateyna musa tisÂṀa ayatim beyyinatin fesÂṀel benÄḟ israÄḟle iz caehum fe kale lehu firÂṀavnu innÄḟ le ezunnuke ya musa meshura"
  17,102,"Kale le kad alimte ma enzele haulai illa rabbus semavati vel erdÄḟ besair ve innÄḟ le ezunnuke ya firÂṀavnu mesbura"
  17,103,"Fe erade ey yestefizzehum minel erdÄḟ fe agraknahu ve mem meahu cemÄḟa"
  17,104,"Ve kulna mim baÂṀdihÄḟ li benÄḟ israiyleskunul erda fe iza cae vaÂṀdul ahÄḟrati ciÂṀna bikum lefÄḟfa"
  17,105,"Ve bil hakkÄḟ enzelnahu ve ibl hakkÄḟ nezel ve ma erselnake illa mubessirav ve nezÄḟra"
  17,106,"Ve kurÂṀanen feraknahu li takraehu alen nasi ala muksiv ve nezzelnahu tenzÄḟla"
  17,107,"Kul aminu bihÄḟ ev la tuÂṀminu innellezÄḟne utul Äḟlem min kablihÄḟ iza yutla aleyhim yehÄḟrrune lil ezkani succeda"
  17,108,"Ve yekulune subhane rabbina in kane vaÂṀdu rabbina le mefÂṀula"
  17,109,"Ve yehÄḟrrune lil ezkani yebkune ve yezÄḟduhum husua"
  17,110,"KulidÂṀullahe evidÂṀur rahman eyyem ma tedÂṀu fe lehul esmaul husna ve la techer bi salatike ve la tuhafit biha vebtegÄḟ beyne zalike sebÄḟla"
  17,111,"Ve kulil hamdu lillahillezÄḟ lem yettehÄḟz veledev ve lem yekul lehu serÄḟkun fil mulki ve lem yekul lehu veliyyum minez zulli ve kebbirhu tekbÄḟra"
  18,8,"Ve inna le caÄḟlune ma aleyha saÄḟydem curuza"
  18,9,"Em hasibte enne ashabel kehfi ver rakÄḟymi kanu min ayatina aceba"
  18,10,"Iz evel fityetu ilel kehfi fe kalu rabbena atina mil ledunke rahmetev ve heyyiÂṀ lena min emrina raseda"
  18,11,"Fe darabna ala azanihim fil kehfi sinÄḟne adeda"
  18,12,"Summe beasnahum li naÂṀleme eyyul hÄḟzbeyni ahsa lima lebisu emeda"
  18,13,"Nahnu nekussu aleyke nebeehum bil hakk innehum fityetun amenu bi rabbihim ve zidnahum huda"
  18,14,"Ve rabatna ala kulubihim iz kamu fe kalu rabbuna rabbus semavati vel erdÄḟ len nedÂṀuve min dunihÄḟ ilahel le kad kulna izen setata"
  18,15,"Haulai kavmunettehazu min dunihÄḟ aliheh lev la yeÂṀtune aleyhim bi sultanim beyyin fe men azlemu mimmeniftera alellahi keziba"
  18,16,"Ve izÄḟÂṀtezeltumuhum ve ma yaÂṀbudune illallahe feÂṀvu ilel kehfi yensur lekum rabbukum mir rahmetihÄḟ ve yuheyyiÂṀ lekum min emrikum mirfeka"
  18,17,"Ve teras semse iza taleat tezaveru an kehfihim zatel yemÄḟni ve iza garabet takriduhum zates simali ve hum fÄḟ fecvetim minh zalike min ayatillah mey yehdillahu fe huvel muhted ve mey yudlil fe len tecide lehu veliyyem mursida"
  18,18,"Ve tahsebuhum eykazav ve hum rukuduv ve nukallibuhum zatel yemÄḟni ve zates simali ve kelbuhum basitun ziraayhi bil vesÄḟyd levit talaÂṀte aleyhim le velleyte minhum firarav ve le muliÂṀÂṀe minhum ruÂṀÂṀa"
  18,19,"Ve kezalike beasnahum li yetesaelu beynehum kale kailum minhum kem lebistum kalu lebisna yevmen ev baÂṀda yevm kalu rabbukum aÂṀlemu bi ma lebistum febÂṀasu ehadekum bi verikÄḟlum hazihÄḟ ilel medÄḟneti fel yenzur eyyuha ezka taamen fel yeÂṀtikum bi rizkÄḟm minhu vel yetelattaf ve la yusÂṀÄḟranne bikum ehada"
  18,20,"Innehum iy yazheru aleykum yercumukum ev yuÄḟydukum fÄḟ milletihim ve len tuflihu izen ebeda"
  18,21,"Ve kezalike aÂṀserna aleyhim li yaÂṀlemu enne vaÂṀdellahi hakkuv ve ennes saate la raybe fÄḟha iz yetenazeune beynehum emrahum fe kalubnu aleyhim bunyana rabbuhum aÂṀlemu bihim kalellezÄḟne galebu ala emrihim le nettehÄḟzenne aleyhim mescida"
  18,22,"Se yekulune selasetur rabiuhum kelbuhum ve yekulune hamsetun sadisuhum kelbuhum racmem bil gayb ve yekulune sebÂṀatuv ve saminuhum kelbuhum kur rabbÄḟ aÂṀlemu bi Äḟddetihim ma yaÂṀlemuhum illa kalÄḟlun fe la tumari fÄḟhim illa miraen zahirav ve la testefti fÄḟhim minhum ehada"
  18,23,"Ve la tekulenne li seyÂṀin innÄḟ faÄḟlun zalike gada"
  18,24,"Illa ey yesaellahu vezkur rabbeke iza nesÄḟte ve kul asa ey yehdiyeni rabbÄḟ li akrabe min haza raseda"
  18,25,"Ve lebisu fÄḟ kehfihim selase mietin sinÄḟne vazdadu tisÂṀa"
  18,26,"Kulillahu aÂṀlemu bima lebisu lehu gaybus semavati vel ard ebsÄḟr bihÄḟ ve esmÄḟÂṀ ma lehum min dunihÄḟ miv veliyyiv ve la yusriku fÄḟ hukmihÄḟ ehada"
  18,27,"Vetlu ma uhÄḟye ileyke min kitabi rabbik la mubeddile li kelimatihÄḟ ve len tecide min dunihÄḟ multehada"
  18,28,"Vasbir nefseke meallezÄḟne yedÂṀune rabbehum bil gadati vel asiyyi yurÄḟdune vechehu ve la taÂṀdu aynake anhum turÄḟdu zÄḟnetel hayatid dunya ve la tutÄḟÂṀ men agfelna kalbehu an zikrina vettebea hevahu ve kane emruhu furuta"
  18,29,"Ve kulil hakku mir rabbikum fe men sae fel yuÂṀmiv ve men sae fel yekfur inna aÂṀtedna liz zalimÄḟne naran ehata bihim suradikuha ve iy yestegÄḟysu yugasu bi mani kel muhli yesvil vucuh biÂṀses serab ve saet murtefeka"
  18,30,"InnellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati inna la nudÄḟyÂṀu ecra men ahsene amela"
  18,31,"Ulaike lehum cennatu adnin tecrÄḟ min tahtihimul enharu yuhallevne fÄḟha min esavira min zehebiiv ve yelbesune siyaben hudram min sundusiv ve istebrakÄḟm muttekiÄḟne fÄḟha alel eraik nÄḟÂṀmes sevab ve hasunet murtefeka"
  18,32,"Vadrib lehum meseler raculeyni min aÂṀnabiv ve hafefnahuma bi nahliv ve cealna beynehuma zerÂṀa"
  18,33,"Kiltel cenneteyni atet ukuleha ve lem tazlim minhu seyÂṀev ve feccerna hÄḟlalehuma nehara"
  18,34,"Ve kane lehu semer fe kale li sahÄḟbihÄḟ ve huve yuhaviruhu ene ekseru minke malev ve eazzu nefera"
  18,35,"Ve dehale cennetehu ve huve zalimul li nefsih kale ma ezunnu en tebÄḟde hazihÄḟ ebeda"
  18,36,"Ve ma ezunnus saate kaimetev ve leir rudidtu ila rabbÄḟ le ecidenne hayram minha munkaleba"
  18,37,"Kale lehu sahÄḟbuhu ve huve yuhavirruhu e keferte billezÄḟ halekake min turabin summe min nutfetin summe sevvake racula"
  18,38,"Lakinne huvellahu rabbÄḟ ve la usriku bi rabbÄḟ ehada"
  18,39,"Ve lev la iz dehalte cenneteke kulte ma saellahu la kuvvete illa billah in terani ene ekalle minke malev ve veleda"
  18,40,"Fe asa rabbÄḟ ey yuÂṀtiyeni hayram min cennetike ve yursile aleyha husbanem mines semai fe tusbiha saÄḟyden zeleka"
  18,41,"Ev yusbiha mauha gavran fe len testetÄḟyÂṀa lehu taleba"
  18,42,"Ve uhÄḟyta bi semerihÄḟ fe asbeha yukallibu keffeyhi ala ma enfeka fÄḟha ve hiye haviyetun ala urusiha ve yekulu ya leytenÄḟ lem usrik bi rabbÄḟ ehada"
  18,43,"Ve lem tekul lehu fietuy yensurunehu min dunillahi ve ma kane muntesÄḟra"
  18,44,"Hunalikel velayetu lillahil hakk huve hayrun sevabev ve hayrun Äḟkba"
  18,45,"Vadrib lehum meselel hayatid dunya ke main enzelnahu mines semai fahteleta bihÄḟ nebatul erdÄḟ fe asbeha hesÄḟmen tezruhur riyah ve kanellahu ala kulli seyÂṀim muktedira"
  18,46,"Elmalu vel benune zÄḟnetul hayatid dunya vel bakÄḟyatus salihatu hayrun Äḟnde rabbike sevabev ve hayrun emela"
  18,47,"Ve yevme nuseyyirul cibale ve teral erda barizetev ve hasernahum fe lem nugadir minhum ehada"
  18,48,"Ve uridu ala rabbike saffa le kad ciÂṀtumuna kema halaknakum evvele merratim bel zeamtum ellen necÂṀale lekum mevÂṀÄḟda"
  18,49,"Ve vudÄḟal kitabu fe teral mucrimÄḟne musfikÄḟyne mimma fÄḟhi ve yekulune ya veyletena mali hazel kitabi la yugadiru sagÄḟyratev ve la kebÄḟraten illa ahsaha ve vecedu ma amilu hadÄḟra ve la yazlimu rabbuke ehada"
  18,50,"Ve iz kulna lil melaiketiscudu li ademe fe secedu illa iblÄḟs kane minel cinni fe feseka an emri rabbih e fe tettehÄḟzunehu ve zuriyyetehu evliyae min dunÄḟ ve hum lekum aduvv biÂṀse liz zalimÄḟne bedela"
  18,51,"Ma eshedtuhum halkas semavati vel erdÄḟ ve la halka enfusihim ve ma kuntu muttehÄḟzel mudÄḟllÄḟne aduda"
  18,52,"Ve yevme yekulu nadu surakaiyellezÄḟne zeamtum fe deavhum fe lem yestecÄḟbu lehum ve cealna beynehum mevbika"
  18,53,"Verael mucrimunen nara fe zannu ennehum muvakÄḟuha ve lem yecidu anha masrifa"
  18,54,"Ve le kad sarrafna fÄḟ hazel kurÂṀani lin nasi min kulli mesel ve kanel insanu eksera seyÂṀin cedela"
  18,55,"Ve ma menean nase ey yuÂṀminu iz caehumul huda ve yestagfiru rabbehum illa en teÂṀtiyehum sunnetul evvelÄḟne ev yeÂṀtiyehumul azabu kubula"
  18,56,"Ve ma nursilul murselÄḟne illa mubessirÄḟne ve munzirÄḟn ve yucadilullezÄḟne keferu bil batÄḟli li yudhÄḟdu bihil hakka vettehazu ayatÄḟ ve ma unziru huzuva"
  18,57,"Ve men azlemu mimmen zukkira bi ayati rabbihÄḟ fe aÂṀrada anha ve nesiye ma kaddemet yedah inna cealna ala kulubihim ekinneten ey yefkahuhu ve fÄḟ azanihim vakra ve in tedÂṀuhum ilel huda fe ley yehtedu izen ebeda"
  18,58,"Ve rabbukel gafuru zur rahmeh lev yuahÄḟzuhum bi ma kesebu le accele lehumul azab bel lehum mevÂṀÄḟdul ley yecidu min dunihÄḟ mevÂṀila"
  18,59,"Ve tilkel kura ehleknahum lemma zalemu ve cealna li mehlikihim mevÂṀÄḟda"
  18,60,"Ve iz kale musa li fetahu la ebrahu hatta ebluga mecmeal bahrayni ev emdÄḟye hukuba"
  18,61,"Felemma belega mecmea beynihima nesiya hutehuma fettehaze zebÄḟlehu fil bahri seraba"
  18,62,"Felemma caveza kaleli fetahu atina gadaena le kad lekÄḟyna min seferina haza nesaba"
  18,63,"Kale eraeyte iz eveyna iles sahrati fe innÄḟ nesÄḟtul hute ve ma ensanÄḟhu illes seytanu en ezkurah vettehaze sebÄḟlehu fil bahri aceba"
  18,64,"Kale zalike ma kunna nebgÄḟ fertedda ala asarihima kasasa"
  18,65,"Fe veceda abdem min Äḟbadina ateynahu rahmetem min Äḟndina ve allemnahu mil ledunna Äḟlma"
  18,66,"Kale lehu musa hel ettebiuke ala en tuallimeni mimma ullimte rusda"
  18,67,"Kale inneke len testetÄḟyÂṀa meÄḟye sabra"
  18,68,"Ve keyfe tasbiru ala ma lem tuhÄḟt bihÄḟ hubra"
  18,69,"Kale setecidunÄḟ in saellahu sabirav ve la aÂṀsÄḟy leke emra"
  18,70,"Kale fe inittebaÂṀtenÄḟ fe la tesÂṀelnÄḟ an seyÂṀin hatta uhdise leke minhu zikra"
  18,71,"Fentaleka hatta iza rakiba fis sefÄḟneti harakaha kale eharakteha li tugrika ehleha le kad ciÂṀte seyÂṀen imra"
  18,72,"Kale e lem e kul inneke len testetÄḟyÂṀa meÄḟye sabra"
  18,73,"Kale la tuahÄḟznÄḟ bima nesÄḟtu ve la turhÄḟknÄḟ min emrÄḟ usra"
  18,74,"Fentaleka hatta iza lekÄḟya gulamen fe katellehu kale e katelte nefsen zekiyyetem bi gayri nefs le kad ciÂṀte seyÂṀen nukra"
  18,75,"Kale elem e kul leke inneke len testetÄḟyÂṀa meÄḟye sabra"
  18,76,"Kale in seeltuke an seyÂṀim baÂṀdeha fe la tusahÄḟbnÄḟ kad belagte mil ledunnÄḟ uzra"
  18,77,"Fentaleka hatta iza eteya ehle karyetinistetÂṀama ehleha fe ebev ey yudayyifuhuma fe veceda fÄḟha cidaray yurÄḟdu ey yenkadda fe ekameh kale lev siÂṀte lettehazte aleyhi ecra"
  18,78,"Kale haza firaku beynÄḟ ve beynik se unebbiuke bi teÂṀvÄḟli ma lem testetÄḟÂṀ aleyhi sabra"
  18,79,"Emmes sefÄḟnetu fe kanet li mesakÄḟne yaÂṀmelune fil bahri fe eradtu en eÄḟybeha ve kane veraehum melikuy yeÂṀhuzu kulle sefÄḟnetin gasba"
  18,80,"Ve emmel gulamu fekane ebevahu muÂṀmineyni fe hasÄḟna ey yurhikahuma tugyanev ve kufra"
  18,81,"Fe eradna ey yubdilehuma rabbuhuma hayram minhu zekatev ve akrabe ruhma"
  18,82,"Ve emmel cidaru fe kane li gulameyni yetÄḟmeyni fil medineti ve kane tahtehu kenzul lehuma ve kane ebuhuma saliha fe erade rabbuke ey yebluga esuddehuma ve yestahrica kenzehuma rahmetem mir rabbik ve ma fealtuhu an emrÄḟ zalike teÂṀvÄḟlu ma lem testÄḟÂṀ aleyhi sabra"
  18,83,"Ve yesÂṀeluneke an zil karneyn kul seetlu aleykum minhu zikra"
  18,84,"Inna mekkenna lehu fil erdÄḟ ve ateynahu min kulli seyÂṀin sebeba"
  18,85,"Fe etbea sebeba"
  18,86,"Hatta iza belaga magribes semsi vecedeha tagrubu fÄḟ aynin hamietiv ve vecede Äḟndeha kavma kulna yazel karneyni imma en tuazzibe ve imma en tettehÄḟze fÄḟhim husna"
  18,87,"Kale emma men zaleme fe sevfe nuazzibuhu summe yuraddu ila rabbihÄḟ fe yuazzibuhu azaben nukra"
  18,88,"Ve emma men amene ve amile salihan fe lehu cezaenil husna ve senekulu lehu min emrina yusra"
  18,89,"Summe etbea sebeba"
  18,90,"Hatta iza belaga matlias semsi vecedeha tatluu ala kavmil lem necÂṀal lehum min duniha sitra"
  18,91,"Kezalik ve kad ehatna bima ledeyhi hubra"
  18,92,"Summe etbea sebeba"
  18,93,"Hatta iza belaga beynes seddeyni vecede min dunihima kavmel la yekadune yefkahune kavla"
  18,94,"Kalu ya zel karneyni inne yeÂṀcuce ve meÂṀcuce mufsidune fil erdÄḟ fe hel necÂṀalu leke harcen ala en tecÂṀale beynena ve beynehum sedda"
  18,95,"Kale ma mekkennÄḟ fÄḟhi rabbÄḟ hayrun fe eÄḟynunÄḟ bi kuvvetin ecÂṀal beynekum ve beynehum redma"
  18,96,"Atuni zuberal hadÄḟd hatta iza sava beynes sadafeyni kalenfuhu hatta iza cealehu naran kale atunÄḟ ufrig aleyhi kÄḟdra"
  18,97,"Femestau ey yazheruhu ve mestetau lehu nakba"
  18,98,"Kale haza rahmetum mir rabbÄḟ fe iza cae vaÂṀdu rabbÄḟ cealehu dekkaÂṀ ve kane vaÂṀdu rabbÄḟ hakka"
  18,99,"Ve terakna baÂṀdahum yevmeiziy yemucu fÄḟ baÂṀdÄḟv ve nufiha fis suri fe cemaÂṀnahum cemÂṀa"
  18,100,"Ve aradna cehenneme yevmeizil lil kafirÄḟne arda"
  18,101,"EllezÄḟne kanet aÂṀyunuhum fÄḟ gÄḟtain an zikrÄḟ ve kanu la yestetÄḟyÂṀune semÂṀa"
  18,102,"E fe hasibellezÄḟne keferu ey yettehÄḟzu ÄḟbadÄḟ min dunÄḟ evliyaÂṀ inna aÂṀtedna cehenneme lil kafirÄḟnenuzula"
  18,103,"Kul hel nunebbiukum bil ahserÄḟne aÂṀmala"
  18,104,"EllezÄḟne dalle saÂṀyuhum fil hayatid dunya ve hum yahsebune ennehum yuhsinune sunÂṀa"
  18,105,"UlaikellezÄḟne keferu bi ayati rabbihim ve likaihÄḟ fe habitat aÂṀmaluhum fe la nukÄḟymu lehum yevmel kÄḟyameti vezna"
  18,106,"Zalike cezauhum cehennemu bima keferu vettehazu ayatÄḟ ve rusulÄḟ huzuve"
  18,107,"InnellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati kanet lehum cennatul firdevsi nuzula"
  18,108,"HalidÄḟne fÄḟha la yebgune anha hÄḟvela"
  18,109,"Kul lev kanel bahru midadel li kelimati rabbi le nefidel bahru kable en tenfede kelimatu rabbi ve lev ciÂṀna bi mislihÄḟ mededa"
  18,110,"Kul innema ene beserum mislukum yuha ileyye ennema ilahukum ilahuv vahÄḟd fe men kane yercu likae rabbihÄḟ felyaÂṀmel amelen salihav ve la yusrik bi Äḟbadeti rabbihÄḟ ehada"
  19,7,"Ya zekeriyya inna nubessiruke bi gulaminismuhu yahya lem necÂṀal lehu min kablu semiyya"
  19,8,"Kale rabbi enna yekunu lÄḟ gulamuv ve kanetimraeti akÄḟrav ve kad belagtu minel kiberi Äḟtiyya"
  19,9,"Kale kezalik kale rabbuke huve aleyye heyyinuv ve kad halaktuke min kablu ve lem teku seyÂṀa"
  19,10,"Kale rabbicÂṀal lÄḟ ayeh kale ayetuke ella tukellimen nase selase leyalin seviyya"
  19,11,"Fe harace ala kavmihÄḟ minel mÄḟhrabi fe evha ileyhim en sebbihu bukratev ve asiyya"
  19,12,"Ya yahya huzil kitabe bi kuvveh ve ateynahul hukme abiyya"
  19,13,"Ve hananem mil ledunna ve zekah ve kane tekÄḟyya"
  19,14,"Ve berram bi valideyhi ve lem yekun cebbaran asÄḟyya"
  19,15,"Ve selamun aleyhi yevme vulide ve yevme yemutu ve yevme yubÂṀasu hayya"
  19,16,"Vezkur fil kitabi meryem izintebezet min ehliha mekanen serkÄḟyya"
  19,17,"Fettehazet min dunihim hÄḟcaben fe erselna ileyha ruhana fe temessele leha besaren seviyya"
  19,18,"Kalet innÄḟ euzu bir rahmani minke in kunte tekÄḟyya"
  19,19,"Kale innema ene rasulu rabbiki li ehebe leki gulamen zekiyya"
  19,20,"Kalet enna yekunu li gulamuv ve lem yemsesnÄḟ beseruv ve lem eku begÄḟyya"
  19,21,"Kale kezalik kale rabbuki huve aleyye heyyin ve li necÂṀalehu ayetel linnasi ve rahmetem minna ve kane emram makdÄḟyya"
  19,22,"Fe hamelethu fentebezet bihÄḟ mekanen kasÄḟyya"
  19,23,"Fe ecaehel mehadu ila cizÂṀÄḟn nahleh kaletya leytenÄḟ mittu kable haza ve kuntu nesyem mensiyya"
  19,24,"Fe nadaha min tahtiha ella tahzenÄḟ kad ceale rabbuki tahteki seriyya"
  19,25,"Ve huzzÄḟ ileyki bi cizÂṀÄḟn nahleti tusakÄḟt aleyki rutaben ceniyya"
  19,26,"Fe kulÄḟ vesrabÄḟ ve karrÄḟ ayna fe imma terayinne minel beseri ehaden fe kulÄḟ innÄḟ nezertu lir rahmani savmen fe len ukellimel yevme insiyya"
  19,27,"Fe etet bihÄḟ kavmeha tahmiluh kalu ya meryemu le kad ciÂṀti seyÂṀen feryya"
  19,28,"Ya uhte harune ma kane ebukimrae sevÂṀiv ve ma kanet ummuki begÄḟyya"
  19,29,"Fe esarat ileyhi kalu keyfe nukelimu men kane fil mehdi sabiyya"
  19,30,"Kale innÄḟ abdullahi ataniyel kitabe ve cealenÄḟ nebiyya"
  19,31,"Ve cealenÄḟ mubaraken eyne ma kuntu ve evsanÄḟ bis salati vez zekati ma dumtu hayya"
  19,32,"Ve berram bi validetÄḟ ve lem yecÂṀalnÄḟ cebbaran sekÄḟyya"
  19,33,"Vesselamu aleyye yevme vulidtu ve yevme emutu ve yevme ubÂṀasu hayya"
  19,34,"Zalike Äḟysebnu meryem kavlel hakkÄḟllezÄḟ fÄḟhi yemterun"
  19,35,"Ma kane lillahi ey yettehÄḟze miv veledin subhaneh iza kada emran fe innema yekulu lehu kum fe yekun"
  19,36,"Ve innellahe rabbÄḟ ve rabbukum faÂṀbuduh haza sÄḟratum mustekÄḟym"
  19,37,"Fahtelefel ahzabu mim beynihim fe veylul lillezÄḟne keferu mim meshedi yevmin azÄḟym"
  19,38,"EsmÄḟÂṀbihim ve ebsÄḟr yevme yeÂṀtunena lakiniz zalimunel yevme fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  19,39,"Ve enzirhum yevmel hasrati iz kudÄḟyel emr ve hum fÄḟ gafletiv ve hum la yuÂṀminun"
  19,40,"Inna nahnu nerisul erda ve men aleyha ve ileyna yurceun"
  19,41,"Vezkur fil kitabi ibrahÄḟm innehu kane sÄḟddÄḟkan nebiyya"
  19,42,"Iz kale li ebÄḟhi ya ebeti lime taÂṀbudu ma la yesmeu ve la yubsÄḟru ve la yugnÄḟ anke seyÂṀa"
  19,43,"Ya ebeti innÄḟ kad caenÄḟ minel Äḟlmi ma lem yeÂṀtike fettebÄḟÂṀnÄḟ ehdike sÄḟratan seviyya"
  19,44,"Ya ebeti la taÂṀbudis seytan innes seytane kane lir rahmani asÄḟyya"
  19,45,"Ya ebeti ninÄḟ ehafu ey yemesseke azabum miner rahmani fe tekune lis seytani veliyya"
  19,46,"Kale eragÄḟbun ente an alihetÄḟ ya ibrahÄḟm leil lem tentehi le ercumenneke vehcurnÄḟ meliyya"
  19,47,"Kale selamun aleyk se estagfiru leke rabbÄḟ innehu kane bÄḟ hafiyya"
  19,48,"Ve aÂṀtezilukum ve ma tedÂṀune min dunillahi ve edÂṀu rabbÄḟ asa ella ekune bi duai rabbÄḟ sekÄḟyya"
  19,49,"FelemmaÂṀtezelehum ve ma yaÂṀbudune min dunillahi vehebna lehu ishaka ve yaÂṀkub ve kullen cealna nebiyya"
  19,50,"Ve vehebna lehum mir rahmetina ve cealna lehum lisane sÄḟdkÄḟn aliyya"
  19,51,"Vezkur fil kitabi musa innehu kane muhlesav ve kane rasulen nebiyya"
  19,52,"Ve nadeynahu min canibit turil eymeni ve karrabnahu neciyya"
  19,53,"Ve vehebna lehu mir rahmetina ehahu harune nebiyya"
  19,54,"Vezkur fil kitabi ismaÄḟyle innehu kane sadikal vaÂṀdi ve kane rasulen nebiyya"
  19,55,"Ve kane yeÂṀmuru ehlehu bis salati vez zekati ve kane Äḟnde rabbihÄḟ merdÄḟyya"
  19,56,"Vezkur fil kitabi idrÄḟse innehu kane sÄḟddÄḟkan nebiyya"
  19,57,"Ve rafaÂṀnahu mekanen aliyya"
  19,58,"UlaikellezÄḟne enÂṀamellahu aleyhim minen nebiyyÄḟne min zurriyyeti ademe ve mimmen hamelna mea nuhÄḟv ve min zurriyyeti ibrahÄḟme ve israÄḟle ve mimmen hedeyna vectebeyna iza tutla aleyhim ayatur rahmani harru succedev ve bukiyya"
  19,59,"Fe halefe mim baÂṀdihim halfun edaus salate yettebeus sehevati fe sevfe yelkavne gayya"
  19,60,"Illa men tabe ve amene ve amile salihan fe ulaike yedhulunel cennete ve la yuzlemune seyÂṀa"
  19,61,"Cennati adninilletÄḟ veader rahmanu Äḟbadehu bil gayb innehu kane vaÂṀduhu meÂṀtiyya"
  19,62,"La yesmeune fÄḟha bukratev ve asiyya"
  19,63,"Tilkel cennetulletÄḟ nurisu min Äḟbadina men kane tekÄḟyya"
  19,64,"Ve ma netezzelu illa bi emri rabbik lehu ma beyne eydÄḟna ve ma halfena ve ma beyne zalik ve ma kane rabbuke nesiyya (58. Ayet secde ayetidir)"
  19,65,"Rabbus semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ma beynehuma faÂṀbudhu vastabir li Äḟbadetih hel taÂṀlemu lehu semiyya"
  19,66,"Ve yekulul insanu e iza ma mittu le sevfe uhracu hayya"
  19,67,"E ve la yezkurul insanu enna halaknahu min kablu ve lem yeku seyÂṀa"
  19,68,"Fe ve rabbike le nahsurannehum ves seyatÄḟyne summe le nuhdÄḟrannehum havle cehenneme cisiyya"
  19,69,"Summe lenenzianne min kulli sÄḟatin eyyuhum eseddu aler rahmani Äḟtiyya"
  19,70,"Summe le nahnu aÂṀlemu billezÄḟne hum evla biha sÄḟliyya"
  19,71,"Ve im minkum illa variduha kane ala kabbike hatmem makdÄḟyya"
  19,72,"Summe nuneccillezÄḟnet tekav ve nezeruz zalimÄḟne fÄḟha cisiyya"
  19,73,"Ve iza tutla aleyhim ayatuna beyyinatin kalellezÄḟne keferu lillizÄḟne amenu eyyul ferÄḟkayni hayrum mekamev ve ahsenu nediyya"
  19,74,"Ve kem ehlekna kablehum min karnin hum ahsenu esasev ve riÂṀya"
  19,75,"Kul men kane fid dalaleti felyemdud lehur rahmanu medda hatta iza raev ma yuadune immel azabe ve immes saah fe seyaÂṀlemune men huve serrum mekanev ve adÂṀafu cunda"
  19,76,"Ve yezÄḟdullahullezÄḟnehtedev huda vel bakÄḟyatus salihatu hayrun Äḟnde rabbike sevabev ve hayrum meradda"
  19,77,"E fe raeytellezÄḟ kefera bi ayatina ve kale leuteyenne malev ve veleda"
  19,78,"Ettaleal gaybe emittehaze Äḟnder rahmani ahda"
  19,79,"Kella senektubu ma yekulu ve nemuddu lehu minel azabi medda"
  19,80,"Ve nerisuhu ma yekulu ve yeÂṀtÄḟna ferda"
  19,81,"Vettehazu min dunillahi alihetel li yekunu lehum Äḟzza"
  19,82,"Kella seyekfurune bi Äḟbadetihim ve yekunune aleyhim dÄḟdda"
  19,83,"E lem tera enna erselnes seyatÄḟyne alel kafirÄḟne teuzzuhum ezza"
  19,84,"Fe la taÂṀcel aleyhim innema neuddulehum adda"
  19,85,"Yevme nahsurul muttekÄḟyne iler rahmani vefda"
  19,86,"Ve nesukul mucrimÄḟne ila cehenneme virda"
  19,87,"La yemlikunes sefaate illa menttehaze Äḟnder rahmani ahda"
  19,88,"Ve kalittehazer rahmanu veleda"
  19,89,"Le kad ciÂṀtum seyÂṀen idda"
  19,90,"Tekadus semavatu yetefettarne minhu ve tensekkul erdu ve tehÄḟrrul cibalu hedda"
  19,91,"En deav lirrahmani veleda"
  19,92,"Ve ma yembegÄḟy lir rahmani ey yettehÄḟze veleda"
  19,93,"In kullu men fis semavate vel erdÄḟ illa atir rahmani abda"
  19,94,"Le kad ahsahum ve addehum adda"
  19,95,"Ve kulluhum atÄḟhi yevmel kÄḟyameti ferda"
  19,96,"InnellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati se yecÂṀalu lehumur rahmanu vudda"
  19,97,"Fe innema yessernahu bi lisanike li tubessira bihil muttekÄḟyne ve tunzira bihÄḟ kavmel ludda"
  19,98,"Ve kem ehlekna kablehum min karn hel tuhussu minhum min ehadin ev temeu lehum rikza"
  20,8,"Allahu la ilahe illa hu lehul esmaul husna"
  20,9,"Ve hel etake hadiysu musa"
  20,10,"Iz raa naran fe kale li ehlihimkusu innÄḟ anestu naral leallÄḟ atÄḟkum minha bi kabesin ev ecidu alen nari huda"
  20,11,"Felemma etaha nudiye ya musa"
  20,12,"InnÄḟ ene rabbuke fahlaÂṀ naÂṀleyk inneke bil vadil mukaddesi tuva"
  20,13,"Ve enahtertuke festemÄḟÂṀ lima yuha"
  20,14,"InnenÄḟ enallahu la ilahe illa ene faÂṀbudnÄḟ ve ekÄḟmÄḟs salate li zikrÄḟ"
  20,15,"Innes saate atiyetun ekadu uhfÄḟha li tucza kullu nefsim bi ma tesÂṀa"
  20,16,"Fe la yesuddenneke anha mel la yuÂṀminu biha vettebea hevahu fe terda"
  20,17,"Ve ma tilke bi yemÄḟnike ya musa"
  20,18,"Kale hiye asay etevekkeu aleyha ve ehussu biha ala ganemÄḟ ve liye fÄḟha mearibu uhra"
  20,19,"Kale elkÄḟha ya musa"
  20,20,"Fe elkaha fe iza hiye hayyetun tesÂṀa"
  20,21,"Kale huzha ve la tehaf se nuÄḟyduha sÄḟratehel ula"
  20,22,"Vadmun yedeke ila cenahÄḟke tahruc beydae min gayri suin ayeten uhra"
  20,23,"Li nuriyeke min ayatinel kubra"
  20,24,"Izheb ila firÂṀavne innehu taga"
  20,25,"Kale rabbisrah lÄḟ sadrÄḟ"
  20,26,"Ve yessir lÄḟ emrÄḟ"
  20,27,"Vahlul ukdetem mil lisanÄḟ"
  20,28,"Yefkahu kavlÄḟ"
  20,29,"VecÂṀal li vezÄḟram min ehlÄḟ"
  20,30,"Harune ehÄḟy"
  20,31,"Usdud bihÄḟ ezrÄḟ"
  20,32,"Ve esrikhu fÄḟ emrÄḟ"
  20,33,"Key nusebbihake kesÄḟra"
  20,34,"Ve nezkurake kesÄḟra"
  20,35,"Inneke kunte bina besÄḟyra"
  20,36,"Kale kad utiyte suÂṀleke ya musa"
  20,37,"Ve lekad menenna aleyke merraten uhra"
  20,38,"Iz evhayna ila ummike ma yuha"
  20,39,"EnÄḟkzi fÄḟhi fit tabuti fakzi fÄḟhi fil yemmi fel yulkÄḟhil yemnu bis sahÄḟli yeÂṀhuzhu aduvvul lÄḟ ve aduvvul leh ve elkaytu aleyke mehabbetem minnÄḟ ve li tusnea ala aynÄḟ"
  20,40,"Iz temsÄḟ uhtuke fe racaÂṀnake ila ummike key tekarra aynuha ve la tahzen ve katelte nefsen fe necceynake minel gammi ve fetennake futunen fe lebiste sinÄḟne fÄḟ ehli medyene summe ciÂṀte ala kaderiy ya musa"
  20,41,"VastanaÂṀtuke li nefsÄḟ"
  20,42,"Izheb ente ve ehuke bi ayatÄḟ ve la teniya fÄḟ zikrÄḟ"
  20,43,"Izheba ila firÂṀavne innehu taga"
  20,44,"Fe kula lehu kevlel leyyinel leallehu yetezekkeru ev yahsa"
  20,45,"Kala rabbena innena nehafu ey yefruta aleyna ev ey yatga"
  20,46,"Kale la tehafa innenÄḟ meakuma esmeu ve era"
  20,47,"FeÂṀtiyahu fe kula inna rasula rabbike fe ersel meana benÄḟ israÄḟle ve la tuazzibhum kad ciÂṀnake bi ayetim mir rabbik vesselamu ala menittebeal huda"
  20,48,"Inna kad uhÄḟye ileyna ennel azabe ala men kezzebe ve tevella"
  20,49,"Kale fe mer rabbukuma ya musa"
  20,50,"Kale rabbunellezÄḟ aÂṀta kulle seyÂṀin halkahu summe heda"
  20,51,"Kale fema balul kurunil ula"
  20,52,"Kale Äḟlmuha Äḟnde rabbÄḟ fÄḟ kitab la yedÄḟllu rabbÄḟ ve la yensa"
  20,53,"EllezÄḟ ceale lekumul erda mehdev ve selek lekum fÄḟha subulev ve enzele mines semai maa fe ahracna bihÄḟ ezvacem min nebatin setta"
  20,54,"Kulu verÂṀav enÂṀamekum inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li ulin nuha"
  20,55,"Minha halaknakum ve fÄḟha nuÄḟydukum ve minha nuhricukum taraten uhra"
  20,56,"Ve lekad eraynahu ayatina kulleha fe kezzebe ve eba"
  20,57,"Kale ecÂṀtena li tuhricena min erdÄḟna bi sÄḟhrike ya musa"
  20,58,"Fe le neÂṀtiyenneke bi sÄḟhrim mislihÄḟ fecÂṀal beynena ve belneke mevÂṀÄḟdel la nuhlifuhu nahnu ve la ente mekanen suva"
  20,59,"Kale mevÂṀÄḟdukum yevmuz zÄḟnet ve ey yuhseran nasu duha"
  20,60,"Fe tevella firÂṀavnu fe cemea keydehu summe eta"
  20,61,"Kale lehum musa veylekum la tefteru alellahi keziben fe yushÄḟtekum bi azab ve kad habe meniftera"
  20,62,"Fe tenazeu emrahum beynehum ve eserrun necva"
  20,63,"Kalu in hazani le sahÄḟrani yurÄḟdani ey yuhricakum min erdÄḟkum bi sÄḟhrihima ve yezheba bi tarÄḟkatikumul musla"
  20,64,"Fe ecmiu keydekum summeÂṀtu saffa ve kad eflehal yevme menistaÂṀla"
  20,65,"Kalu ya musa imma en tulkÄḟye ve imma en nekune evvele men elka"
  20,66,"Kale bel elku fe iza hÄḟbaluhum ve ÄḟsÄḟyyuhum yuhayyehu ileyhi min sÄḟhrihim enneha tesÂṀa"
  20,67,"Fe evcese fÄḟ nefsihÄḟ hÄḟyfetem musa"
  20,68,"Kulna la tehaf inneke entel aÂṀla"
  20,69,"Ve elkÄḟ ma fÄḟ yemÄḟnike telkaf ma saneu innema saneu keydu sahÄḟr ve la yuflihus sahÄḟru haysu eta"
  20,70,"Fe ulkÄḟyes seharatu succeden kalu amenna bi rabbi harune ve musa"
  20,71,"Kale amentum lehu kable en azene lekum innehu le kebÄḟrukumullezÄḟ allemekumus sÄḟhr fe le ukattÄḟanne eydiyekum ve erculekum min hÄḟlafiv ve le usallibennekum fÄḟ cuzuÄḟn nahli ve le taÂṀlemunne eyyuna eseddu azabev ve ebka"
  20,72,"Kalu len nuÂṀsirake ala ma caena minel beyyinati vellazÄḟ fetarana fakdÄḟ ma ente kad innema takdÄḟy hazihil hayated dunya"
  20,73,"Inna amenna bi rabbina li yagfira lena hatayana ve ma ekrahtena aleyhi mines sÄḟhr vallahu hayruv ve ebka"
  20,74,"Innehu mey yeÂṀti rabbehu murimen fe inne lehu cehennem la yemutu fÄḟha ve la yahya"
  20,75,"Ve mey yeÂṀtihÄḟ muÂṀminen kad amiles salihati fe ulaike lehumud deracatul ula"
  20,76,"Cennatu adnin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha ve zalyike cezau men tezekka"
  20,77,"Ve lekad evhayna ila musa en esri bi ÄḟbadÄḟ fadrib lehum tarÄḟkan fil bahri yebesa la tehafu derakev ve la tahsa"
  20,78,"Fe etbeahum firÂṀavnu bi cunudihÄḟ fe gasiyehum minel yemmi ma gasiyehum"
  20,79,"Ve edalle firÂṀavnu kavmehu ve ma heda"
  20,80,"Ya benÄḟ israÄḟle kad enceynakum min aduvvikum ve vaadnakum canibet turil eymene ve nezzelna aleykumul menne ves selva"
  20,81,"Kulu min tayyibati ma razaknnakum ve la tatgav fÄḟhi fe yehÄḟlle aleykum gadabÄḟ ve mey yahlil aleyhi gadabÄḟ fe kad heva"
  20,82,"Ve innÄḟ le gaffarul limen tabe ve amene ve amile salihan summehteda"
  20,83,"Ve am aÂṀcelek an kavmike ya musa"
  20,84,"Kale hum ulai ala eserÄḟ ve aciltu ileyke rabbi li terda"
  20,85,"Kale fe inna kad fetenna kavmeke mim baÂṀdike ve edallehumus samiriyy"
  20,86,"Fe racea musa ila kavmihÄḟ gadbane esifa kale ya kavmi elem yeÄḟdkum rabbukum vaÂṀden hasena e fe tale aleykumul ahdu em eradtum ey yehÄḟlle aleykum gadabum mir rabbikum fe ahleftum mevÂṀÄḟdÄḟ"
  20,87,"Kalu ma ahlefna mevÂṀÄḟdeke bi melkina velakinna hummilna evzaram min zÄḟnetil kavmi fe kazefnaha fe kezalike elkas samiriyy"
  20,88,"Fe ahrace lehum Äḟclen cesedel lehu huvarun fe kalu haza ilahukum ve ilahu musa fe nesiy"
  20,89,"E fe la yeravne ella yarciu ileyhim kavlev ve la yemliku lehum darrav ve la nefÂṀa"
  20,90,"Ve le kad kale lehum harunu min kablu ya kavmi innema futintum bih ve inne rabbekumur rahmanu fettebiuni ve etÄḟyÂṀu emrÄḟ"
  20,91,"Kalu len nebreha aleyhi akifÄḟne hatta yarcia ileyna musa"
  20,92,"Kale ya harunu ma meneake iz raeytehum dallu"
  20,93,"Ella tettebian e fe esayte emri"
  20,94,"Kale yebneumme la teÂṀhuz bi lÄḟhyetÄḟ ve la bi raÂṀsi innÄḟ hasÄḟtu en tekule ferrakte beyne benÄḟ israÄḟle ve lem terkub kavlÄḟ"
  20,95,"Kale fe ma hatbuke ya samiriyy"
  20,96,"Kale besurtu bi ma lem yebsuru bihÄḟ fe kabadtu kabdatem min eserir rasuli fe nebeztuha ve kezalike sevvelet lÄḟ nefsÄḟ"
  20,97,"Kale fezheb fe inne leke fil hayati en tekule la misase ve inne leke mevÂṀÄḟdel len tuhlefeh venzur ila ilahikellezÄḟ zalte aleyhi akifale nuharrÄḟkannehu summe le nensifennehu fil yemmi nesfa"
  20,98,"Innema ilahukumullahullezÄḟ la ilahe illa hu vesia kulle seyÂṀin Äḟlma"
  20,99,"Kezalike nekussu aleyke min embai ma kad sebak ve kad ateynake mil ledunna zikra"
  20,100,"Men aÂṀrada anhu fe innehu yahmilu yevmel kÄḟyameti vizra"
  20,101,"HalidÄḟne fÄḟh ve sae lehum yevmel kÄḟyameti hÄḟmla"
  20,102,"Yevme yunfehu fis suri ve nahsurul mucrimÄḟne yevmeizin zurka"
  20,103,"Yetehafetune beynehum il lebistum illa asra"
  20,104,"Nahnu aÂṀlemu bima yekulune iz yekulu emseluhum tarÄḟkaten il lebistum illa yevma"
  20,105,"Ve yesÂṀeluneke anil cibali fe kul yensifuha rabbÄḟ nesfa"
  20,106,"Fe yezeruha kaan safsafa"
  20,107,"La tera fÄḟha Äḟvecev ve la emta"
  20,108,"Yevmeiziy yettebiuned daÄḟye la Äḟvece leh ve haseatil asvatu lir rahmani fe la tesmeu illa hemsa"
  20,109,"Yevmeizil la tenfeus sefaatu illa men ezine lehur rahmanu ve radÄḟye lehu kavla"
  20,110,"YaÂṀlemu ma beyne eydÄḟhim ve ma halfehum ve la yuhÄḟytune bihÄḟ Äḟlma"
  20,111,"Ve anetil vucuhu lil hayyil kayyum ve kad habe men hamele zulma"
  20,112,"Ve mey yaÂṀmel mines salihuti ve huve muÂṀminun fe la yehafu zulmev ve la hadma"
  20,113,"Ve kezalike enzelnahu kurÂṀanen arabiyyev ve sarrafna fÄḟhi minel veÄḟydi leallehum yettekune ev yuhdisu lehum zikra"
  20,114,"Fe teallellahul melikul hakk ve la taÂṀcel bil kurÂṀani min kabli ey yukda ileyke vahyuhu ve kur rabbi zidnÄḟ Äḟlma"
  20,115,"Ve lekad ahÄḟdna ila ademe min kablu fe nesiye ve lem necid lehu azma"
  20,116,"Ve iz kulna lil melaiketiscudu li ademe fe secedu illa iblÄḟs eba"
  20,117,"Fe kulna ya ademu inne haza aduvvul leke ve li zevcike fe la yuhricennekuma minel cenneti fe teska"
  20,118,"Inne leke ella tecua fÄḟha ve la taÂṀra"
  20,119,"Ve enneke la tazmeu fÄḟha ve la tadha"
  20,120,"Fe vesvese ileyhis seytanu kale ya ademu hel edulluke ala seceratil huldi ve mulkil la yebla"
  20,121,"Fe ekela minha fe bedet lehuma sevÂṀatuhuma ve tafika yahsÄḟfani aleyhima miv verakÄḟl cenneti ve asa ademu rabbehu fe gava"
  20,122,"Summectebahu rabbuhu fe tabe aleyhi ve heda"
  20,123,"Kelehbita minha cemÄḟam baÂṀdukum li baÂṀdÄḟn aduvv fe imma yeÂṀtiyennekum minnÄḟ huden fe menittebea hudaye fe la yedÄḟllu ve la yeska"
  20,124,"Ve men aÂṀrada an zikrÄḟ fe innel lehu meÄḟyseten dankev ve nahsuruhu yevmel kÄḟyameti aÂṀma"
  20,125,"Kale rabbi lime hasertenÄḟ aÂṀma ve kad kuntu besÄḟyra"
  20,126,"Kale kezalike etetke ayatuna fe nesÄḟteha ve kezalikel yevme tunsa"
  20,127,"Ve kezalike neczÄḟ men esrafe ve lem yuÂṀmim bi ayati rabbih ve le azabul ahÄḟrati eseddu ve ebka"
  20,128,"E fe lem yehdi lehum kem ehleknu kablehum minel kuruni yemsune fÄḟ mesakinihim inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li ulin nuha"
  20,129,"Velev la kelimetun sebekat mir rabbike le kane lizamev ve ecelum musemma"
  20,130,"Fasbir ala ma yekulune ve sebbÄḟh bi hamdi rabbike kable tuluÄḟs semsi ve kable gurubiha ve min anail leyli fe sebbÄḟh ve atrafen nehari lealleke terda"
  20,131,"Ve la temuddenne aynelke ila ma mettaÂṀna bihÄḟ ezvacem minhum zehratel hayatid dunya li neftinehum fÄḟh ve rizku rabbike hayrun ve beka"
  20,132,"VeÂṀmur ehleke bis salati vastabir aleyha la nesÂṀeluke rizka nahnu nerzukuk vel akÄḟbetu lit takva"
  20,133,"Ve kalu lev la yeÂṀtiyna bi ayetim mir rabbih e ve lem teÂṀtihim beyyinetu ma fis suhufil ula"
  20,134,"Ve lev enna ehleknahum bi azabim min kablihÄḟ le kalu rabbena lev la erselte ileyna rasulen fe nettebia ayatike min kabli en nezille ve nahza"
  20,135,"Kul kullum muterabbisun fe terabbesu fe se taÂṀlemune men ashabus sÄḟratÄḟs seviyyi ve menihteda"
  21,8,"Ve ma cealnahum cesedel la yeÂṀkulunet taame ve ma kanu halidÄḟn"
  21,9,"Summe sadaknahumul va&ÂṀde fe enceynahum ve men nesau ve ehleknel musrifÄḟn"
  21,10,"Le kad enzelna ileykum kitkaben fÄḟhi zikrukum e fe la taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  21,11,"Ve kem kasamna min karyetin kanet zalimetev ve enseÂṀna baÂṀdeha kavmen aharÄḟn"
  21,12,"Felemma ehassu beÂṀsena izahum minha yerkudun"
  21,13,"La terkudu varciu ila ma utriftum fÄḟhi ve mesakinikum leallekum tusÂṀelun"
  21,14,"Kalu ya veylena inna kunna zalimin"
  21,15,"Fe ma zalet tilke daÂṀvahum hatta cealnahum hasÄḟyden haidÄḟn"
  21,16,"Ve ma halaknes semae vel erda ve ma beynehuma laÄḟbÄḟn"
  21,17,"Lev eradna en nettehÄḟze lehvel lettehaznahu mil ledunna in kunna faÄḟlÄḟn"
  21,18,"Bel nakzifu bil hakkÄḟ alel batÄḟli fe yedmeguhu fe iza huve zahÄḟk ve lekumul veylu mimma tesÄḟfun"
  21,19,"Ve lehu men fis semavati vel ard ve men Äḟndehu la yestekbirune an ÄḟbadetihÄḟ ve la yestahsirun"
  21,20,"Yusebbihunelleyle ven nehara la yefturun"
  21,21,"Emittehazu alihetem minel erdÄḟ hum yunsirun"
  21,22,"Lev kane fÄḟhima alihetun ilellahu lefesedeta fe subhanellahi rabbil arsi amma yasÄḟfun"
  21,23,"La yusÂṀelu amma yefÂṀalu ve hum yusÂṀelun"
  21,24,"Emittehazu min dunihÄḟ aliheh kul hatu burhanekumv haza zikru mem meÄḟye ve zikru men kablÄḟ bel ekseruhum la yaÂṀlemunel hakka fehum muÂṀridun"
  21,25,"Ve ma erselna min kablike mir rasulin illa nuhÄḟy ileyhi ennehu la ilahe illa ene faÂṀdudun"
  21,26,"Ve kaluttehazer rahmanu veleden subhaneh bel Äḟbadum mukramun"
  21,27,"La yesbikunehu bil kavli ve hum bi emrihÄḟ yaÂṀmelun"
  21,28,"YaÂṀlemu ma beyne eydÄḟhim ve ma halfehum ve la yesfeune illa li menirteda ve hum min hasyetihÄḟ musfikun"
  21,29,"Ve mey yekul minhum innÄḟ ilahum min dunihÄḟ fe zalike neczÄḟhi cehennem kezalike necziz zalimÄḟn"
  21,30,"E ve lem yerallezÄḟne keferu ennes semavati vel erda kaneta ratkan fe fetaknahuma ve cealna minel mai kulle seyÂṀin hayy e fe la yuÂṀminun"
  21,31,"Ve cealna fÄḟha ficacen subulel leallehum yehtedun"
  21,32,"Ve cealnes semae sakfem mahfusa ve hum an ayatiha muÂṀridun"
  21,33,"Ve huvellezÄḟ halekal leyle ven nehara ves semse vel kamer kullun fÄḟ felekiy yesbehun"
  21,34,"Ve ma cealna li beserim min kablikel huld efeim mitte fehumul halidun"
  21,35,"Kullu nefsin zaikatul mevt ve neblukum bis serri vel hayri fitneh ve ileyna turceun"
  21,36,"Ve iza raakellezÄḟne keferu iy yettehÄḟzuneke illa huzuva e hazellezÄḟ yezkuru alihetekum ve hum bi zikrir rahmani hum kafirun"
  21,37,"Hulikal insanu min acel se urÄḟkum ayatÄḟ fe la testaÂṀcilun"
  21,38,"Ve yekulune meta hazel vaÂṀdu in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  21,39,"Lev yaÂṀlemullezÄḟne keferu hÄḟyne la yekuffune av vucuhihimun nara ve la an zuhurihim ve la hum yunsarun"
  21,40,"Bel teÂṀtÄḟhim bagteten fe tebhetuhum fe la yestetÄḟyÂṀune raddeha ve la hum yunzarun"
  21,41,"Ve le kadistuhzie bi rusulim min kablike fe haka billezÄḟne sehÄḟru minhum ma kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  21,42,"Kul mey yekleukum bil leyli vne nehari miner rahmanv bel hum an zikri rabbihim muÂṀridun"
  21,43,"Em lehum alihetun metneuhum min dunina la yestetÄḟyÂṀune nasra enfusihim ve la hum minna yushabun"
  21,44,"Bel mettaÂṀna haulai ve abaehum hatta tale aleyhimul umur e fela yeravne enna neÂṀtil erda nenkusuha min atrafiha e fehumul galibun"
  21,45,"Kul innema unzirukum bil vahyi ve la yesmeus summud duae iza ma yunzerun"
  21,46,"Ve leim messethum nefhatum min azabi rabbike le yekulunne ya veylena inna kunna zalimÄḟn"
  21,47,"Ve nedaul mevazinel kÄḟsta li yevmil kÄḟyameti fe la tuzlemu nefsun seyÂṀa ve in kane miskale habbetim min hardelin eteyna biha ve kefa bina hasibÄḟn"
  21,48,"Ve le kad ateyna musa ve harunel furkane ve dÄḟyaev ve zikral lil muttekÄḟyn"
  21,49,"EllezÄḟne yahsevne rabbehum bil gaybi ve hum mines saati musfikun"
  21,50,"Ve haza zikrum mubarakun enzelnah e fe entum lehu munkirun"
  21,51,"Ve lekad ateyna ibrahÄḟme rusdehu min kablu ve kunna bihÄḟ alimÄḟn"
  21,52,"Iz kale li ebÄḟhi ve kavmihÄḟ ma hazihit teemasÄḟlulletÄḟ entum leha akifun"
  21,53,"Kau vecedna abaena leha abidÄḟn"
  21,54,"Kale le kad kuntum entum ve abaukum fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  21,55,"Kalu ecÂṀtena bil hakkÄḟ em ente minel laÄḟbÄḟn"
  21,56,"Kale ber rabbukum rabbus semavati vel erdÄḟllezÄḟ fetarahunne ve ene ala zalikum mines sahidÄḟn"
  21,57,"Ve tellahi le ekÄḟdenne asnamekum baÂṀde en tuvlelu mudbirÄḟn"
  21,58,"Fe cealehum cuzazen illa kebÄḟral lehum leallehum ileyhi yarciun"
  21,59,"Kalu men feale haza bi alihetina innehu le minez zalimÄḟn"
  21,60,"Kalu semÄḟÂṀna fetey yezkuruhum yukalu lehu ibrahÄḟm"
  21,61,"Kalu feÂṀtu bihÄḟ ala aÂṀyunin nasi leallehum yeshedun"
  21,62,"Kalu e ente fealte haza bialihetina ya ibrahÄḟm"
  21,63,"Kale bel fealehu kebiruhum haza fesÂṀeluhum in kanu yentÄḟkun"
  21,64,"Fe raceu ila enfusihim fe kalu innekum entumuz zalimun"
  21,65,"Summe nukisu ala ruusihim lekad alimte ma haulai yentÄḟkun"
  21,66,"Kale efetaÂṀbudune min dunillahi ma la yenfeukum seyÂṀev ve la yedurrukum"
  21,67,"Uffil lekum ve li ma taÂṀbudune min dunillah efela taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  21,68,"Kalu harrikuhu vensuru alihetekum in kuntum faÄḟlÄḟn"
  21,69,"Kulna ya naru kunÄḟ berdev ve selamen ala ibrahÄḟm"
  21,70,"Ve eradu bihÄḟ keyden fe cealnahumul ahserÄḟn"
  21,71,"Ve necceynahu ve lutan ilel erdÄḟlletÄḟ birakna fÄḟha lil alemÄḟn"
  21,72,"Ve vehebna lehu ishak ve yaÂṀkube nafileh ve kullen cealna salihÄḟyn"
  21,73,"Ve cealna hum eimmetey yehdune bi emrina ve evhayna ileyhim fÄḟÂṀlel hayrati ve ikames salati ve Äḟtaez zekah ve kanu lena abidÄḟn"
  21,74,"Ve lutan ateynahu hukmev ve Äḟlmev ve necceynahu minel karyetilletÄḟ kanet taÂṀmelul habis innehum kanu kavme sevÂṀin fasikÄḟyn"
  21,75,"Ve edhalnahu fÄḟ rahmetina innehu mines salihÄḟyn"
  21,76,"Ve nuhan iz nada min kablu festecebna lehu fenecceynahu ve ehlehu minel kerbil azÄḟym"
  21,77,"Ve nasarnahu minel kavmillezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina innehum kanu kavme sevÂṀin fe agraknahum ecmeyÄḟn"
  21,78,"Ve davude ve suleymane iz yahkumani fil harsi iz nefeset fÄḟhi ganemul kavm ve kunna li hukmihim sahidÄḟn"
  21,79,"Fe fehhemnaha suleyman ve kullen ateyna hukmev ve Äḟlmev ve sehharna mea davudel cibale yusebbÄḟhne vet tayr ve kunna faÄḟlÄḟn"
  21,80,"Ve allemnahu sanÂṀate lebusil lekum li tuhsÄḟnekum mim beÂṀsikum fe hel entum sakirun"
  21,81,"Ve li suleymaner rÄḟha asÄḟfeten tecrÄḟ bi emrihÄḟ ilel erdÄḟlletÄḟ barakna fÄḟha ve kunna bi kulli seyÂṀin alimÄḟn"
  21,82,"Ve mines seyatÄḟyni mey yegusune lehu ve yaÂṀmelune amelen dune zalik ve kunna lehum hafizÄḟyn"
  21,83,"Ve eyyube iz nada rabbehu ennÄḟ messeniyed durru ve ente erhamur rahÄḟmÄḟn"
  21,84,"Festecebna lehu fe kesefna ma bihÄḟ min durriv ve ateynahu ehlehu ve mislehum meahum rahmetem min Äḟndina ve zikra lil abidÄḟn"
  21,85,"Ve ismaÄḟyle ve idrÄḟse ve zel kifl kullum mines sabirÄḟn"
  21,86,"Ve edhalnahum fÄḟ rahmetina innehum mines salihÄḟyn"
  21,87,"Ve zen nuni iz zehebe mugadÄḟben fe zanne el len nakdira aleyhi fe nada fiz zulumati el la ilahe illa ente subhaneke innÄḟ kuntu minez zalimÄḟn"
  21,88,"Festecebna lehu ve necceynahu minel gamm ve kezalike nuncil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  21,89,"Ve zekeriyya iz nada rabbehu rabbi la tezernÄḟ fardev ve ente hayrul varisÄḟn"
  21,90,"Festecebna lehu ve vehebna lehu yahya ve aslahna lehu zevceh innehum kanu yusariune fil hayrati ve yedÂṀunena ragabev ve raheba ve kanu lena hasiÄḟyn"
  21,91,"VelletÄḟ ahsanet ferceha fe nefahna fÄḟha mir ruhÄḟna ve cealnaha vebneha ayetel lil alemÄḟn"
  21,92,"Inne hazihÄḟ ummetukum ummetev vahÄḟdetev ve ene rabbukum faÂṀbudun"
  21,93,"Ve tekattau emrahum beynehum kullun ileyna raciun"
  21,94,"Fe mey yaÂṀmel minas salihati ve huve muÂṀminun fe la kufrane li saÂṀyih ve inna lehu katibun"
  21,95,"Ve haramun ala karyetin ehleknaha ennahum la yarciun"
  21,96,"Hatta iza futihat yeÂṀcucu ve meÂṀcucu ve hum min kulli hadebiy yensilun"
  21,97,"Vakterabel vaÂṀdul hakku fe iza hiye sahÄḟsatun ebsarullezÄḟne keferu ya veylena kad kunna fÄḟ gafletim min haza bel kunna zalimÄḟn"
  21,98,"Innekum ve ma taÂṀbudune min dunillahi hasabu cehennem entum leha varidun"
  21,99,"Lev kane haulai alihetem ma veraduha ve kullun fÄḟha halidun"
  21,100,"Lehum fiha zefÄḟruv ve hum fÄḟha la yesmeun"
  21,101,"InnellezÄḟne sebekat lehum minel husna ulaike anha mubÂṀadun"
  21,102,"La yesmeune hasÄḟseha ve hum fÄḟ mestehet enfusuhum halidun"
  21,103,"La yahzunulumul fezeul ekberu ve tetelekkahumul melaikeh haza yevmukumullezÄḟ kuntum tuadun"
  21,104,"Yevme natvis semae ke tayyis sicililli lil kutub kema bedeÂṀna evvele halkÄḟn nuÄḟyduh vaÂṀden aleyna inna kunna faÄḟlÄḟn"
  21,105,"Ve le kad ketabna fiz zeburi mim baÂṀdiz zikri ennel erda yerisuha Äḟbadiyas salihun"
  21,106,"Inne fÄḟ haza le belagal li kavmil abidÄḟn"
  21,107,"Ve ma erselnake illa rahmetel lil alemÄḟn"
  21,108,"Kul innema yuha ileyye ennema ilahukum ilahuv vahÄḟd fe hel entum muslimun"
  21,109,"Fe in tevellev fe kul azentukum ala sevaÂṀ ve in edrÄḟ e karÄḟbun em beÄḟydum ma tuadun"
  21,110,"Innehu yaÂṀlemu ma tektumun"
  21,111,"Ve in edrÄḟ leallehu fitnetul lekum ve metaun ila hÄḟyn"
  21,112,"Kale rabbÄḟhkum bil hakk ve rabbuner rahmanul musteanu ala ma tesÄḟfu"
  22,8,"Ve minen nasi mey yucadilu fillahi bi gayri Äḟlmiv ve la hudev ve la kitabim munÄḟr"
  22,9,"Saniye ÄḟtfihÄḟ li yudÄḟlle an sebÄḟlillah lehu fid dunya hÄḟzyuv ve nuzÄḟkuhu yevmel kÄḟyameti azabel harÄḟyk"
  22,10,"Zalike bima kaddemet yedake ve ennellahe leyse bi zallamil lil abÄḟd"
  22,11,"Ve minen nasi mey yaÂṀbudullahe ala harf fe in esabehu hayrunÄḟtmeenne bih ve in esabethu fitnetuninkalebe ala vechihÄḟ hasirad dunya vel ahÄḟrah zalike huvel husranul mubÄḟn"
  22,12,"YedÂṀu min dunillahi ma la yedurruhu ve ma la yenfeuh zalike huved dalalul beÄḟyd"
  22,13,"YedÂṀu le men darruhu akrabu min nefÂṀÄḟh lebiÂṀsel mevla ve lebiÂṀsel asÄḟr"
  22,14,"Innellahe yudhÄḟlullezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enhar innellahe yefÂṀalu ma yurÄḟd"
  22,15,"Men kane yezunnu el ley yensurahullahu fid dunya vel ahÄḟrati felyemdud bi sebebin iles semai summelyaktaÂṀ felyenzur hel yuzhibenne keyduhu ma yegÄḟyz"
  22,16,"Ve kezalike enzelnahu ayatim beyyinativ ve ennellahe yehdÄḟ mey yurÄḟd"
  22,17,"InnellezÄḟne amenu vellezÄḟne hadu ves sabiÄḟne ve nesara vel mecuse vellezÄḟne esraku innellahe yefdÄḟlu beynehum yevmel kÄḟyameh innellahe ala kulli seyÂṀin sehÄḟd"
  22,18,"E lem tera ennellahe yescudu lehu men fÄḟs semavati ve men fil erdÄḟ ves semsu vel kameru ven nucumu vel cibalu ves seceru ved devabbu ve kesÄḟrum minen nas ve kesÄḟrun hakka aleyhil azab ve mey yuhinillahu fe ma lehu min mukrim innellahe yefÂṀalu ma yesaÂṀ"
  22,19,"Hazani hasmanÄḟhtesamu fÄḟ rabbihim fellezÄḟne keferu kuttÄḟat lehum siyabum min nar yusabbu min fekÄḟ ruusihimul hamÄḟm"
  22,20,"Yusheru bihÄḟ ma fÄḟ butunihim vel culud"
  22,21,"Ve lehum mekamiu min hadÄḟd"
  22,22,"Kullema eradu ey yahrucu minha min gammin uÄḟydu fÄḟha ve zuku azabel harÄḟyk"
  22,23,"Innellahe yudhÄḟlullezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu yuhallevne fÄḟha min esavira min zehebiv ve luÂṀlua ve libasuhum fÄḟha harÄḟr(18. Ayet secde ayetidir)"
  22,24,"Ve hudu ilet tayyibi minel kavli ve hudu ila sÄḟratÄḟl hamÄḟd"
  22,25,"InnellezÄḟne keferu ve yesuddune an sebÄḟlillahi vel mescidil haramillezÄḟ cealnahu lin nasi sevaenil akifu fÄḟhi vel bad ve mey yurid fÄḟhi bi ilhadim bi zulmin nuzÄḟkhu min azabin elÄḟm"
  22,26,"Ve iz bevveÂṀna li ibrahÄḟme mekanel beyti el la tusrk bÄḟ seyÂṀev ve tahhir beytiye littaifÄḟne vel kaimÄḟne ver rukkeÄḟs sucud"
  22,27,"Ve ezzin fin nasi bil hacci yeÂṀtuke ricalev ve ala kulli damiriy yeÂṀtÄḟne min kulli feccin amÄḟyk"
  22,28,"Li yeshedu menafia lehum ve yezkurusmellahi fÄḟ eyyamim maÂṀlumatin ala ma razekahum mim behÄḟmetil enÂṀam fe kulu minha ve atÂṀÄḟmul baisel fekÄḟyr"
  22,29,"Summelyakdu tefesehum velyufu nuzurahum velyettavvefu bil beytil atiyk"
  22,30,"Zalike ve mey yuazzÄḟm hurumatillahi fe huve hayrul lehu Äḟnda rabbih ve uhÄḟllet lekumul enÂṀamu illa ma yutla aleykum fectenibur ricse minel evsani vectenibu kavlez zur"
  22,31,"Hunefae lillahi gayra musrikÄḟne bih ve mey yusrik billahi fe keennema harra mines semai fe tahtafuhut tayru ev tehvÄḟ bihir rÄḟhu fÄḟ mekanin sehÄḟyk"
  22,32,"Zalike ve mey yuazzÄḟm seairallahi fe inneha min takvel kulub"
  22,33,"Lekum fÄḟha menafiu ila ecelim musemmen summe mehÄḟlluha ilel beytil atiyk"
  22,34,"Ve li kulli ummetin cealna mensekel li yezkurusmellahi ala ma razekahum mim behÄḟmetil enÂṀam fe ilahukum ilahuv vahÄḟdun fe lehu eslimu ve bessiril muhbitÄḟn"
  22,35,"EllezÄḟne iza zukirallahu vecilet kulubuhum ves sabirÄḟne ala ma esabehum vel mukÄḟymis salati ve memma razaknahum yunfikun"
  22,36,"Vel budne cealnaha lekum min seairillahi lekum fÄḟha hayrun fezkurusmellahi aleyha savaf fe iza vecebet cunubuha fe kulu minha ve atÂṀÄḟmul kania vel muÂṀterr kezalike sehharnaha lekum leallekum teskurun"
  22,37,"Ley yenalellahe luhumuha ve la dimauha ve lakiy yenaluhut takva minkum kezalike sehharaha lekum li tukebbirullahe ala ma hedakum ve bessiril muhsinÄḟn"
  22,38,"Innellahe yudafiu anillezÄḟne amenu innellahe la yuhÄḟbbu kulle havvanin kefur"
  22,39,"Uzine lillezÄḟne yukatelune bi ennehum zulimu ve innellahe ala nasrihim le kadÄḟr"
  22,40,"EllezÄḟne uhricu min diyarihim bi gayri hakkÄḟn illa ey yekulu rabbunellah ve lev la defÂṀullahin nase baÂṀdahum bi baÂṀdÄḟl lehuddimet savamiu ve biyeuv ve salevatuv ve mesacidu yuzkeru fÄḟhesmullahi kesÄḟra ve le yensurannellahu mey yensuruh innellahe le kaviyyun azÄḟz"
  22,41,"EllezÄḟne im mekkennahum fil erdÄḟ ekamus salate ve atevuz zekate ve emeru bil maÂṀrufi ve nehev anil munker ve lillahi akÄḟbetul umur"
  22,42,"Ve iy yukezzibuke fe kad kezzebet kablehum kavmu nuhÄḟv ve aduv ve semud"
  22,43,"Ve kavmu ibrahÄḟme ve kavmu lut"
  22,44,"Ve ashabu medyen ve kuzzibe misa fe emleytu lil kafirÄḟne summe ehaztuhum fe keyfe kane nekÄḟr"
  22,45,"Fe keeyyim min karyetin ehleknaha ve hiye zalimetun fe hiye haviyetun ala urusiha ve biÂṀrim muattaletiv ve kasrim mesÄḟd"
  22,46,"E fe lem yesÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fe tekune lehum kulubuy yaÂṀkÄḟlune biha ev azanuy yesmeune biha fe innehu la taÂṀmel ebsaru ve lakin taÂṀmel kulubulletÄḟ fis sudur"
  22,47,"Ve yestaÂṀciluneke bil azabi ve ley yuhlifellahu vaÂṀdeh ve inne yevmen Äḟnde rabbike ke elfi senetim mimma teuddun"
  22,48,"Ve keeyyim min karyetin emleytu leha ve hiye zalimetun summe ehaztuha ve ileyyel mesÄḟyr"
  22,49,"Kul ya eyyuhen nasu innema ene lekum nezÄḟrum mubÄḟn"
  22,50,"FellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati lehum magfiratuv ve rizkun kerÄḟm"
  22,51,"VellezÄḟne seav fÄḟ ayatina muacizÄḟne ulaike ashabul cehÄḟym"
  22,52,"Ve ma erselnamin kablike mir rasuliv ve la nebiyyin illa iza temenna elkas seytanu fÄḟ umniyyetih fe yensehullahu ma yulkÄḟs seytanu summe yuhkimullahu ayatih vallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  22,53,"Li yecÂṀale ma yulkÄḟs seytanu fitnetel lillezÄḟne fÄḟ kulubihim meraduv vel kasiyeti kulubuhum ve innez zalimÄḟne le fÄḟ sikakÄḟm beÄḟyd"
  22,54,"Ve li yaÂṀlemellezÄḟne utul Äḟlme ennehul hakku mir rabbike fe yuÂṀminu bihÄḟ fe tuhbite lehu kulubuhum ve innellahe le hadillezÄḟne amenu ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  22,55,"Ve la yezalullezÄḟne keferu fÄḟ miryetim minhu hatta teÂṀtiyehumus saatu bagteten ev yeÂṀtiyehum azabu yevmin akÄḟym"
  22,56,"Elmulku yevmeizil lillah yahkumu beynehum fellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati fÄḟ cennatin neÄḟym"
  22,57,"VellezÄḟne keferu ve kezzebu bi ayatina fe ulaike lehum azabum muhÄḟn"
  22,58,"VellezÄḟne haceru fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi summe kutilu ev matu le yerzukanne humullahu rizkan hasena ve innellahe lehuve hayrur razikÄḟyn"
  22,59,"Le yudhÄḟlennehum mudhaley yerdavneh ve innellahe leallÄḟmun halÄḟm"
  22,60,"Zalik ve men akaba bi misli ma ukÄḟbe bihÄḟ summe bugÄḟye aleyhi le yensirannehullah innellahe le afuvvun gafur"
  22,61,"Zalike bi ennellahe yulicul leyle fin nehari ve yulicun nehar fil leyli ve ennellahe semÄḟum besÄḟyr"
  22,62,"Zalike bi ennellahe huvel hakku ve enne ma yedÂṀune min dunihÄḟ huvel batÄḟlu ve ennellahe huvel aliyyul kebÄḟr"
  22,63,"E lem tera ennellahe enzele mines semai maen fe tusbihul erdu muhdarrahv innellahe latÄḟyfun habÄḟr"
  22,64,"Lehu ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard ve innellahe lehuvel ganiyyul hamÄḟd"
  22,65,"E lem tera ennellahe sehhara lekum ma fil erdÄḟ vel fulke tecrÄḟ fil bahri bi emrih ve yumsikus semae en tekaa alel erdÄḟ illa bi iznih innellahe bin nasi le raufur rahÄḟym"
  22,66,"Ve huvellezÄḟ ahyakum summe yumÄḟtukum summe yuhyÄḟkum innel insane le kefur"
  22,67,"Li kulli ummetin cealna menseken hum nasikuhu fe la yunaziunneke fil emri vedÂṀu ila rabbik inneke le ala hudem mustekÄḟym"
  22,68,"Ve in cadeluke fe kulillahu aÂṀlemu bima taÂṀmelun"
  22,69,"Allahu yahkumu beynekum yevmel kÄḟyameti fÄḟma kuntum fÄḟhi tahtelifun"
  22,70,"E lem taÂṀlem ennellahe yaÂṀlemu ma fis semai vel ard inne zalike fÄḟ kitab inne zalike alellahi yesÄḟr"
  22,71,"Ve yaÂṀbudune min dunillahi ma lem yunezzil bihÄḟ sultanev ve ma leyse lehum bihÄḟ Äḟlm ve ma liz zalimÄḟne min nesÄḟyr"
  22,72,"Ve iza tutla aleyhim ayatuna beyyinatin taÂṀrifu fÄḟ vucuhillezÄḟne keferul munker yekadune yestune billezÄḟne yetlune aleyhim ayatina kul efe unebbiukum biserrim min zalikum ennar veadehellahullezÄḟne keferu ve biÂṀsel mesÄḟyr"
  22,73,"Ya eyyuhen nasu duribe meselun festemiu leh innellezÄḟne tedÂṀune min dunillahi ley yahluku zubabev ve levictemu leh ve iy yeslubhumuz zubabu seyÂṀel la yestenkÄḟzuhu minh daufet talibu vel matlub"
  22,74,"Ma kaderullahe hakka kadrih innellahe fe kavviyyun azÄḟz"
  22,75,"Alluh yastafÄḟ minel melaiketi rusulev ve minen nas innellahe semÄḟum besÄḟyr"
  22,76,"YaÂṀlemu ma beyne eydÄḟhim ve ma halfehum ve ilellahi turceul umur"
  22,77,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenurkeu vescudu vaÂṀbudu rabbekum vefÂṀalul hayra leallekum tuflihun"
  22,78,"Ve cahidu fillahi hakka cihadil huvectebukum ve ma ceale aleykum fid dÄḟni min harac millete ebÄḟkum ibrahÄḟm huve semmakumul muslimÄḟne min kablu ve fÄḟ haza lÄḟ yekuner rasulu sehÄḟden aleykum ve ketunu suhedae alen nas fe ekÄḟymus salate ve atuz zekate vaÂṀtesÄḟmu billah huve mevlakum fe nÄḟÂṀmel mevla ve nÄḟÂṀmen nesÄḟyr"
  23,8,"VellezÄḟne hum li emanatihim ve ahdihim raun"
  23,9,"VellezÄḟne hum ala salevatihim yuhafizun"
  23,10,"Ulaike humul varisun"
  23,11,"EllezÄḟne yerisunel firdevs hum fÄḟha halidun"
  23,12,"Ve le kad halaknel insane min sulaletim min tÄḟyn"
  23,13,"Summe cealnahu nutfeten fÄḟ kararim mekÄḟn"
  23,14,"Summe halaknen nutfete alekaten fe halaknel alekate mudgaten fe halaknel mudgate Äḟzamen fe kesevnel Äḟzame lahmen summe enseÂṀnahu halkan ahar fe tebarakellahu ahsenul halikÄḟyn"
  23,15,"Summe innekum baÂṀde zalike le meyyitun"
  23,16,"Summe innekum yevmel kÄḟyameti tubÂṀasun"
  23,17,"Ve le kad halakna fevkakum sebÂṀa taraika ve ma kunna anil halkÄḟ gafilÄḟn"
  23,18,"Ve enzelna mines semai maem bi kaderin fe eskennahu fil erdÄḟ ve inna ala zehabim bihÄḟ le kadirun"
  23,19,"Fe enseÂṀna lekum bihÄḟ cennatim min nehÄḟyliv ve aÂṀnab lekum fÄḟha fevakihu kesÄḟratuv ve minha teÂṀkulun"
  23,20,"Ve seceraten tahrucu min turi seynae tembutu bid duhni ve sÄḟbgil lil akilÄḟn"
  23,21,"Ve inne lekum fil enÂṀami le Äḟbrah nuskÄḟykum mimma fÄḟ butuniha ve lekum fÄḟha menafiu kesÄḟratuv ve minha teÂṀkulun"
  23,22,"Ve aleyha ve alel fulki tuhmelun"
  23,23,"Ve le kad erselna nuhan ila kavmihÄḟ fe kale ya kavmÄḟÂṀbudullahe mal lekum min ilahin gayruh e fe la tettekun"
  23,24,"Fe kalel meleullezÄḟne keferu min kavmihÄḟ ma haza illa beserum mislukum yurÄḟdu ey yetefeddale aleykum ve lev saellahu le enzele melaikeh ma semÄḟÂṀna bi haza fÄḟ abainel evvelÄḟn"
  23,25,"In huve illa raculum bihÄḟ cinnetun fe terabbesu bihÄḟ hatta hÄḟyn"
  23,26,"Kale rabbinsurnÄḟ bima kezzebun"
  23,27,"Fe evhayna ileyhi enisnaÄḟl fulke bi aÂṀyunina ve vahyina fe iza cae emruna ve farat tennuru fesluk fÄḟha min kullin zevceynisneyni ve ehleke illa men sebeka aleyhil kavlu minhum ve la tuhatÄḟbnÄḟ fillezÄḟne zalemu innehum mugrakun"
  23,28,"Fe izesteveyte ente ve mem meake alel fulki fe kulil hamdu lillahillezÄḟ neccana minel kavmiz zalimÄḟn"
  23,29,"Ve kur rabbi enzilnÄḟ munzelem mubarakev ve ente hayrul munzilÄḟn"
  23,30,"Inne fÄḟ zalike le ayativ ve in kunna le mubtelÄḟn"
  23,31,"Summe enseÂṀna mim baÂṀdihim karnen aharÄḟn"
  23,32,"Fe erselna fÄḟhim rasulem minhum enÄḟÂṀbudullahe ma lekum min ilahin gayruh e fe la tettekun"
  23,33,"Ve kalel meleu min kavmihillezÄḟne keferu ve kezzebu bi likail ahÄḟrati ve etrafnahum fil hayatid dunya ma haza illa beserum mislukum yeÂṀkulu mimma teÂṀkulune minhu ve yesrabu mimma tesrabun"
  23,34,"Ve lein etaÂṀtum beseram mislekum innekum izel lehasirun"
  23,35,"E yeÄḟdukum ennekum iza mittum ve kuntum turabev ve Äḟzamen ennekum muhracun"
  23,36,"Heyhate heyhate lima tuadun"
  23,37,"In hiye illa hayatuned dunya nemutu ve nahya ve ma nahnu bi mebÂṀusÄḟn"
  23,38,"In huve illa raculuniftera alellahi kezibev ve ma nahnu lehu bi muÂṀminÄḟn"
  23,39,"Kale rabbinsurnÄḟ bima kezzebun"
  23,40,"Kale amma kalÄḟlil le yusbihunne nadimÄḟn"
  23,41,"Fe ehazethumus sayhatu bil hakkÄḟ fe cealnahum gussa fe buÂṀdel lil kavmiz zalimÄḟn"
  23,42,"Summe enseÂṀna mim baÂṀdihim kurunen aharÄḟn"
  23,43,"Ma tesbiku min ummetin eceleha ve ma yesteÂṀhÄḟrun"
  23,44,"Summe erselna rusulena tetra kullema cae ummeter rasuluha kezzebuhu fe etbaÂṀna baÂṀdahum baÂṀdav ve cealnahum ehadÄḟs fe buÂṀdel li kavmil la yuÂṀminun"
  23,45,"Summe erselna musa ve ehahu harune bi ayatina ve sultanim mubÄḟn"
  23,46,"Ila firÂṀavne ve meleihÄḟ festekberu ve kanu kavmen alÄḟn"
  23,47,"Fe kalu enuÂṀminu li beserayni mislina ve kavmuhuma lena abidun"
  23,48,"Fe kezzebuhuma fe kanu minel muhlekÄḟn"
  23,49,"Ve le kad ateyna musel kitabe leallehum yehtedun"
  23,50,"Ve cealnebne meryeme ve ummehu ayetev ve aveynahuma ila rabvetin zati karariv ve meÄḟyn"
  23,51,"Ya eyyuher rusulu kulu minet tayyibati vaÂṀmelu saliha innÄḟ bima taÂṀmelune alÄḟm"
  23,52,"Ve inne hazihÄḟ ummetukum ummetev vahÄḟdetev ve ene rabbukum fettekun"
  23,53,"Fetekkatau emrahum beynehum zubura kullu hÄḟzbim bima ledeyhim ferihun"
  23,54,"Fezerhum fÄḟ gamratihim hatta hÄḟyn"
  23,55,"E yahsebune ennema numidduhum bihÄḟ mim maliv ve benÄḟn"
  23,56,"Nusariu lehum fil hayrat bel la yesÂṀurun"
  23,57,"InnellezÄḟne hum min hasyeti rabbihim musfikun"
  23,58,"VellezÄḟne hum bi ayati rabbihim yuÂṀminun"
  23,59,"VellezÄḟne hum bi rabbihim la yusrikun"
  23,60,"VellezÄḟne yuÂṀtune ma atev ve kulubuhum veciletun ennehum ila rabbihim raciun"
  23,61,"Ulaike yusariune fil hayrati ve hum leha sabikun"
  23,62,"Ve la nukellifu nefsen illa vusÂṀaha ve ledeyna kitabuy yentÄḟku bil hakkÄḟ ve hum la yuzlemun"
  23,63,"Vel kulubuhum fÄḟ gamratim min haza ve lehum aÂṀmalum min duni zalike hum leha amilun"
  23,64,"Hatta iza ehazna mutrafÄḟhim bil azabi iza hum yecÂṀerun"
  23,65,"La tecÂṀerul yevme innekum minna la tunsarun"
  23,66,"Kad kanet ayatÄḟ tutla aleykum fe kuntum ala aÂṀkabikum tenkisun"
  23,67,"MustekbirÄḟne bihÄḟ samiran tehcurun"
  23,68,"E fe lem yeddebberul kavle em caehum ma lem yeÂṀti abaehumul evvelÄḟn"
  23,69,"Em lem yaÂṀrifu rasulehum fe hum lehu munkirun"
  23,70,"Em yekulune bihÄḟ cinneh bel caehum bil hakkÄḟ ve ekseruhum lil hakkÄḟ karihun"
  23,71,"Ve levittebeal hakku ehvaehum le fesedetis semavatu vel erdu ve men fÄḟhinn bel eteynahum bi zekrihim fe hum an zikrihim muÂṀridun"
  23,72,"Em tesÂṀeluhum harcen fe haracu rabbike hayruv ve huve hayrur razikÄḟyn"
  23,73,"Ve inneke le tedÂṀuhum ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  23,74,"Ve innellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune bil ahÄḟrati anis sÄḟratÄḟ lenakibun"
  23,75,"Ve lev rahÄḟmnahum ve kesefna ma bihim min durril leleccu fÄḟ tugyanihim yaÂṀmehun"
  23,76,"Ve le kad ehaznahum bil azabi fe mestekanu li rabbihim ve ma yetedarraun"
  23,77,"Hatta iza fetahna aleyhim baben za azabin sedÄḟdin iza hum fÄḟhi mublisun"
  23,78,"Ve huvellezÄḟ ensee lekumus semÂṀa vel ebsara vel efÂṀideh kalÄḟlem ma teskurun"
  23,79,"Ve huvellezÄḟ zeraekum fil erdÄḟ ve ileyhi tuhserun"
  23,80,"Ve huvellezÄḟ yuhyÄḟ ve yumiytu ve lehuhtilaful leyli ven nehar e fe la taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  23,81,"Bel kalu misle ma kalel evvelun"
  23,82,"Kalu e iza mitna ve kunna turabev ve Äḟzamen e inna le mebÂṀusun"
  23,83,"Le kad vuÄḟdna nahnu ve abauna haza min kablu in haza illa esatÄḟyrul evvelÄḟn"
  23,84,"Kul li menil erdu ve men fÄḟha in kuntum taÂṀlemun"
  23,85,"Seyekulune lillah kul efela tezekkerun"
  23,86,"Kul mer rabbus semavatis sebÂṀÄḟ ve rabbul arsil azÄḟym"
  23,87,"Seyekulune lillah kul e fe la tettekun"
  23,88,"Kul mem bi yedihÄḟ melekutu kulli seyÂṀiv ve huve yuciru ve la yucaru aleyhi in kuntum taÂṀlemun"
  23,89,"Seyekulune lillah kul fe enna tusharu"
  23,90,"Bel eteynuham bil hakkÄḟ ve innehum le kazibun"
  23,91,"Mettehazellahu miv velediv ve ma kane meahu min ilahin izel le zehebe kullu ilahum bima haleka ve leala baÂṀduhum ala baÂṀd subhanellahi amma yasÄḟfun"
  23,92,"Alimil gaybi ves sehadeti fe teala amma yusrikun"
  23,93,"Kur rabbi imma turiyennÄḟ ma yuadun"
  23,94,"Rabbi fe la tecÂṀalnÄḟ fil kavmiz zalimÄḟn"
  23,95,"Ve inna ala en nuriyeke ma neÄḟduhum lekadirun"
  23,96,"IdfaÂṀ billetÄḟ hiye ahsenus seyyieh nahnu aÂṀlemu bi ma yasÄḟfun"
  23,97,"Ve kur rabbi euzu bike min hemezatis seyatÄḟyn"
  23,98,"Ve euzu bike rabbi ey yahdurun"
  23,99,"Hatta iza cae ehadehumul mevtu kale rabbirciun"
  23,100,"LeallÄḟ aÂṀmelu salihan fÄḟma teraktu kella inneha kelimetun huve kailuha ve miv veraihim berzehun ila yevmi yubÂṀasun"
  23,101,"Fe iza nufiha fis suri fe la ensabe beynehum yevmeiziv ve la yetesaelun"
  23,102,"Fe men sekulet mevazinuhu fe ulaike humul muflihun"
  23,103,"Ve men haffet mevazÄḟnuhu fe ulaikellezÄḟne hasiru enfusehum fÄḟ cehenneme halidun"
  23,104,"Telfehu vucuhehumun naru ve hum fÄḟha kalihun"
  23,105,"E lem tekun ayatÄḟ tutla aleykum fe kuntum biha tukezzibun"
  23,106,"Kalu rabbena galebet aleyna sÄḟkvetuna ve kunna kavmen dallÄḟn"
  23,107,"Rabbena ahricna minha fe in udna fe inna zalimun"
  23,108,"Kalahseu fÄḟha ve la tukellimun"
  23,109,"Innehu kane ferÄḟkum min ÄḟbadÄḟ yekulune rabbena amenna fagfir lena varhamna ve ente hayrur rahÄḟmÄḟn"
  23,110,"Fettehaz tumuhum sÄḟhriyyen hatta ensevkum zikrÄḟ ve kuntum minhum tadhakun"
  23,111,"InnÄḟ cezeytuhumul yevme bima saberu ennehum humul faizun"
  23,112,"Kale kem lebistum fil erdÄḟ adede sinÄḟn"
  23,113,"Kalu lebisna yevmen ev baÂṀda yevmin fesÂṀelil addÄḟn"
  23,114,"Kale il lebistum illa kalÄḟlel lev ennekum kuntum taÂṀlemun"
  23,115,"E fe hasibtum ennema halaknakum abesev ve ennekum ileyna la turceun"
  23,116,"Fe teallellahul melikul hakk la ilahe illa hu rabbul arsil kerÄḟm"
  23,117,"Ve mey yedÂṀu meallahi ilahen ahara la burhane lehu bihÄḟ fe innema hÄḟsabuhu Äḟnde rabbih innehu la yuflihul kafirun"
  23,118,"Ve kur rabbÄḟgfir verham ve ente hayrur rahÄḟmÄḟn"
  24,7,"Vel hamisetu enne laÂṀnetellahi aleyhi in kane minel kazibÄḟn"
  24,8,"Ve yedrau anhel azabe en teshede erbea sehadatim billahi innehu le minel kazibÄḟn"
  24,9,"Vel hamisete enne gadabellahi aleyha in kane mines sadikÄḟyn"
  24,10,"Ve lev la fadlullahi aleykum ve rahmetuhu ve ennellahe tevvabun hakÄḟm"
  24,11,"InnellezÄḟne cau bil ifki usbetum minkum la tahsebuhu serral lekum bel huve hayrul lekum li kullimriim minhum mektesebe minel ism vellezÄḟ tevella kibrahu minhum lehu azabun azÄḟym"
  24,12,"Lev la iz semÄḟÂṀtumuhu zannel muÂṀminine vel muÂṀminatu bi egfusihim hayrav ve kalu haza ifkum mubÄḟn"
  24,13,"Lev la cau aleyhi bi erbeati suhedaÂṀ fe iz lem yeÂṀtu bis suhedai fe ulaike Äḟndellahi humul kazÄḟbun"
  24,14,"Ve lev fadlullahi aleykum ve rahmetuhu fid dunya vel ahÄḟrati ve messekum fÄḟ ma efadtum fÄḟhi azabun azÄḟym"
  24,15,"Iz telekkavnehu bi elsinetikum ve tekulune bi efvahikum ma leyse lekum bihÄḟ Äḟlmuv ve tahsebunehu heyyinev ve huve Äḟndellahi azÄḟym"
  24,16,"Ve lev la iz semÄḟÂṀtumuhu kultum ma yekunu lena en netekelleme bi haza subhaneke haza buhtanun azÄḟym"
  24,17,"YeÄḟzukumullahu en teudu li mislihÄḟ ebeden in kuntum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  24,18,"Ve yubeyyinullahu lekumul ayat vallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  24,19,"InnellezÄḟne yuhÄḟbbune en tesÄḟal fahÄḟsetu fillezÄḟne amenu lehum azabun elÄḟmun fÄḟd dunyu vel ahÄḟrah vallahu yaÂṀlemu ve entum la taÂṀlemun"
  24,20,"Ve lev la fadlulluhi aleykum ve rahmetuhu ve ennellahe raufur rahÄḟym"
  24,21,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tettebiu hutuvatis seytan ve mey yettebÄḟÂṀ hutuvatis seytani fe innehu yeÂṀmuru bil fahsai vel munker ve lev la fadlullahi aleykum ve rahmetuhu ma zeka minkum min ehadin ebedev ve laninnellahe yuzekkÄḟ mey yesaÂṀ vallahu semÄḟu alÄḟm"
  24,22,"Ve la yeÂṀteli ulul fadli minkum ves seati ey yuÂṀtu ulil kurba vel mesakÄḟne vel muhacirÄḟne fÄḟ sebÄḟlillahi vel yaÂṀfu velyasfehu e la tuhÄḟbbune ey yagfirallahu lekum vellahu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  24,23,"InnellezÄḟne yermunel muhsanatil gafilatil muÂṀminati luÄḟnu fid dunya vel ahÄḟrati ve lehum azabun azÄḟym"
  24,24,"Yevme teshedu aleyhim elsinetuhum ve eydÄḟhim ve erculuhum bima kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  24,25,"Yevmeiziy yuveffÄḟhimullahu dÄḟnehumul hakka ve yaÂṀlemune ennellahe huvel hakkul mubÄḟn"
  24,26,"Elhabisatu lil habÄḟsÄḟne vel habÄḟsune lil habisat vet tayyibatu lit tayyibÄḟne vet tayyibune lit tayyibat ulaike muberraune mimma yekulun lehim magfiratuv ve rizkun kerÄḟm"
  24,27,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la teodhulu buyuten gayru buyutikum hatta testeÂṀnisu ve tusellimu ala ehliha zalikum hayrul lekum leallekum tezekkerun"
  24,28,"Fe il lem tecidu fÄḟha ehaden fe la tedhuluha hatta yuÂṀzene lekum ve in kÄḟyle lekumurciu ferciu huve ezka lemum ve in kÄḟyle lekumurciu ferciu huve ezka lekum vlalahu bima taÂṀmelune alÄḟm"
  24,29,"Leyse aleykum cunahun en tedhulu buyuten gayra meskunetin fÄḟha metaul lekum vallahu yaÂṀlemu ma tubdune ve ma tektumun"
  24,30,"Kul lil muÂṀminÄḟne yeguddu min ebsarihim ve yahfezu furucehum zalike ezka lehum innellahe habÄḟrum bima yasneun"
  24,31,"Ve kul lil muÂṀminati yagdudne min ebsarihinne ve yahfazne furucehunne ve la yubdÄḟne zÄḟnetehunne illa ma zahera minha vle yadribne bi humurihinne ala cuyubihinne ve la yubdÄḟne zÄḟnetehunne illa li buuletihinne ev abaihinne ev abai buuletihinne ev ebaihinne ev ebnai buuletihnne ev Äḟhvanihinne ev benÄḟ Äḟhvanihinne ev benÄḟ ehavatihÄḟnne ev nisaihinne ev ma meleket eymanuhunne evit tabiÄḟyne gayri ulil irbeti miner ricali evit tÄḟflillezÄḟne lem yazheru ala avratin nisai ve la yadribne bi erculihunne li yuÂṀleme ma yuhfÄḟne min zÄḟnetihinn ve tubu ilellahi cemÄḟan eyyuhel muÂṀminune leallekum tuflihun"
  24,32,"Ve enkihul eyama minkum ves salihÄḟyne min Äḟbadikum ve imaikum iy yekun fukarae yugnihimullahu min fadlih vallahu vasiun alim"
  24,33,"Vel yestaÂṀfifillezÄḟne la yecidune nikahan hatta yugniyehumullahu min fadlih vellezÄḟne yebtegunel kitabe memma meleket eymanukum fe katibuhum in alimtum fÄḟhim hayrav ve atuhum mim malillahillezÄḟ atakum ve la tukrihu fetaytikum alel bigai in eradne tehassunel li tebtegu aradal hayatid dunya ve mey yukrihhunne fe innellahe mim baÂṀdi ikrahihinne gafurur rahÄḟym"
  24,34,"Ve le kad enzelna ileykum ayatim mubeyyinativ ve meselem minellezÄḟne halev min kablikum ve mevÂṀÄḟzatel lil tuttekÄḟyn"
  24,35,"Allahu nurus semavati vel ard meselu nurihÄḟ ke miskatin fÄḟha mÄḟsbah elmisbahu fÄḟ zucaceh ezzucacetu ke enneha kevkebun durriyyuy yukadu min seceratim mubaraketin zeytunetil la serkÄḟyyetiv ve la garbiyyetiy yekadu zeytuha yudÄḟyÂṀu ve lev lem temseshu nar nurun ala nur yehdillahu li nurihÄḟ mey yesaÂṀ ve yadribullahul emsale lin nas vallahu bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  24,36,"FÄḟ buyutin ezinellahu en turfea ve yuzkera fÄḟhesmuhu yusebbihu lehu fÄḟha bil guduvvi vel asal"
  24,37,"Ricalul la tulhÄḟhim ticaratuv ve la beyÂṀun an zikrillahi ve ikamis salit ve Äḟtaiz zekati yehafune yevmen tetekallebu fÄḟhil kulubu vel ebsar"
  24,38,"Li yecziyehumullahu ahsene ma amilu ve yezÄḟdehum min fadlih vallahu yerzuku mey yesau bi gayri hÄḟsab"
  24,39,"VellezÄḟne keferu aÂṀmaluhum keserabim bi kÄḟyÂṀatiy yahsebulhuz zamÂṀanu maa hatta iza caehu lem yecidhu seyÂṀev ve vecedellahe Äḟndehu feveffahu hÄḟsabeh vallahu serÄḟul hÄḟsab"
  24,40,"Ev ke zulumatin fÄḟ bahril lucciyyiy yagsahu mevcum min fevkÄḟhÄḟ mevcum min fevkÄḟhÄḟ sehab zulumatum baÂṀduha fevka baÂṀd iza ahrace yedehu lem yeked yeraha ve mel lem yecÂṀalillahu lehu nuran fe malehu min nur"
  24,41,"E lem tera ennellahe yusebbihu lehu men fis semavati vel erdÄḟ vet tayru saffat kullun kad alime salatehu ve tesbÄḟhah vallahu alÄḟmum bima yefÂṀalun"
  24,42,"Ve lillahi mulkus semavati vel ard ve ilellahil mesÄḟyr"
  24,43,"E lem tera ennellahe yuzcÄḟ sehaben summe yuellifu beynehu summe yecÂṀaluhu rukamen fe teral vedka yahrucu min hÄḟlalihv ve yunezzilu mines semai min cibalin fÄḟha mim beradin fe yusÄḟybu bihÄḟ mey yesau ve yasrifuhu ammey yesaÂṀ yekadu senaberkÄḟhÄḟ yezhebu bil ebsar"
  24,44,"Yukallibullahul leyle ven nehar inne fÄḟ zalike le Äḟbratel li ulil ebsar"
  24,45,"Vallahu haleku kulle dabbetim mim maÂṀ fe minhum mey yemsÄḟ ala batnih ve minhum mey yemsÄḟ ala ricleyn ve minhum mey yemsi ala erbaÂṀ yahlukullahu ma yesaÂṀ innellahe ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  24,46,"Le kad enzelna ayatim mubeyyinat vallahu yehdÄḟ mey yesau ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  24,47,"Ve yekulune amenna billahi ve bir rasuli ve etaÂṀna summe yetevella ferÄḟkum minhum mim baÂṀdi zalik ve ma ulaike bil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  24,48,"Ve iza duu ilellahi ve rasulihÄḟ li yahkume beynehum iza ferÄḟkum minhum muÂṀridun"
  24,49,"Ve iy yekul lehumul hakku yeÂṀtu ileyhi musÂṀÄḟnÄḟ"
  24,50,"E fÄḟ kulubihim meradn emrtabu em yehafune ey yehÄḟyfellahu aleyhim ve rasuluh bel ulaike humuz zalimun"
  24,51,"Innema kane kavlel muÂṀminÄḟne iza duu ilellahi ve rasulihÄḟ li yahkume beynehum ey yekulu semÄḟÂṀna ve eatÂṀna ve ulaike humul muflihun"
  24,52,"Ve mey yutÄḟÄḟllahe ve rasulehu ve yahsellahe ve yettakhi fe ulaike humul faizun"
  24,53,"Ve aksemu billahi cehde eymanihim lein emartehum le yahrucunn kulla tuksimu taatum maÂṀrufeh innellahe habÄḟrum bima taÂṀmelun"
  24,54,"Kul etÄḟyÂṀullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀur rasul fe in tevellev fe innema aleyhi ma hummile ve aleykum ma hummiltum ve in tutÄḟyÂṀuhu tehtedu ve ma aler rasuli illel belagul mubÄḟn"
  24,55,"VeadellahullezÄḟne amenu minkum ve amilus salihuti le yestahlifennehum fil erdÄḟ kemestahlefellezÄḟne min kablihim ve le yumukkinenne lehum dinehumul lezirteda lehum ve le yubeddilennehum mim baÂṀdi havfihim emna yaÂṀbudunenÄḟ la yusrikune ve seyÂṀa ve men kefera baÂṀde zalike fe ulaike humul fasikun"
  24,56,"Ve ekÄḟymus salate ve atuz zekate ve etÄḟyÂṀur rasule leallekum turhamun"
  24,57,"La tahsebennellezÄḟne keferu muÂṀcizÄḟne fil ard ve meÂṀvahumun nar ve le biÂṀsel mesÄḟyr"
  24,58,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu li yesteÂṀzinkumullezÄḟne meleket eymaukum vellezÄḟne lem yeblugul hulume minkum selase merratv min kabli salatil fecri ve hÄḟyne tedaune siyabekum minez zahÄḟrati ve mim baÂṀdi salatil ÄḟsaÂṀi selasu avratil lekum leyse aleykum ve la aleyhim cunahum baÂṀdehunn tavvafune aleykum baÂṀdukum ala baÂṀd kezalike yubeyyinullahu lekumul ayat vallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  24,59,"Ve iza belegal atfalu minkumul hulume fel yesteÂṀzinu kemesteÂṀzenellezÄḟne min kablihim kezalike yubeyyinullahu lekum ayatih vallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  24,60,"Vel kavaÄḟdu minen nisaillatÄḟ la yercune nikahan fe leyse aleyhinne cunahun ey yedaÂṀne siyabehunne gayra muteberricatim bi zÄḟneh ve ey yestaÂṀfifne hayrul lehunn vallahu semÄḟun alÄḟm"
  24,61,"Leyse alel aÂṀma haracuv ve la ala enfusikum en teÂṀkulu mim buyutikum ev buyuti abaikum ev buyuti umehatikum ev buyuti Äḟhvanikum ev buyuti ehavatikum ev buyuti aÂṀmamikum ev buyuti ammatikum ev buyuti ahvalikum ev buyuti halatikum ev ma melektum mefatihahu ev sadÄḟkÄḟkum leyse aleykum cunahun en teÂṀkulu cemÄḟan ev estata fe iza dehaltum buyuten fe sellimu ala enfusikum tehÄḟyyetem min Äḟndillahi mubaraketen tayyibeh kezalike yubeyyinullahu lekumul ayati leallekum taÂṀkÄḟlul"
  24,62,"Innemel muÂṀminunellezÄḟne amenu billahi ve rasulihÄḟ ve iza kanu meahu ala emrin camiÄḟl lem yezhebu hatta yesteÂṀzinuh innellezÄḟne yesteÂṀzinuneke ulaikellezÄḟne yuÂṀminune billahi ve rasulih fe izesteÂṀzenuke li baÂṀdÄḟ seÂṀnihim feÂṀzel li men siÂṀte minhum vestagfir lehumullah innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  24,63,"La tecÂṀalu duaer rasuli beynekum ke duai baÂṀdÄḟkum baÂṀda kad yaÂṀlemullahullezÄḟne yetesellelune minkum livaza fel yahzerillezÄḟne yuhalifune an emrihÄḟ en tusÄḟybehum fitnetun ev yusÄḟybehum azabun elÄḟm"
  24,64,"E la inne lillahi ma fis semavati vel ard kad yaÂṀlemu ma entum aleyh ve yevme yurceune ileyhi fe yunebbiuhum bi ma amilu vallahu bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  25,7,"Ve kalu mali hazer rasuli yeÂṀkulut taame ve yemsi fil esvak lev la unzile ileyhi melekun fe yekune meahu nezÄḟra"
  25,8,"Ev yulka ileyhi kenzun ev tekunu lehu cennetuy yeÂṀkulu minha ve kalez zalimune in tettebiune illa raculem meshura"
  25,9,"Unzur keyfe darabu lekel emsale fe dallu fe la yestetÄḟyÂṀune sebÄḟla"
  25,10,"TebarakellezÄḟ in sae ceale leke hayram min zalike cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu ve yecÂṀal leke kusura"
  25,11,"Bel kezzebu bis saati ve aÂṀtedna li men kezzebe bis saati seÄḟyra"
  25,12,"Iza raethum mim mekanim beÄḟydin semiu leha tegayyuzav ve zefÄḟra"
  25,13,"Ve iza ulku minha mekanen dayyikam mukarranÄḟne deav hunalike subura"
  25,14,"La tedÂṀul yevme suburav vahÄḟdev vedÂṀu suburan kesÄḟra"
  25,15,"Kul e zalike hayrun em cennetul huldilletÄḟ vuÄḟdel muttekun kanet lehum cezaev ve mesÄḟyra"
  25,16,"Lehum fÄḟha ma yesaune halidÄḟn kane ala rabbike vaÂṀdem mesÂṀula"
  25,17,"Ve yemve yahsuruhum ve ma yaÂṀbudune min dunillahi fe yekulu e entum adleltum ÄḟbadÄḟ haulai em hum dallus sebÄḟl"
  25,18,"Kalu subhaneke ma kane yembegÄḟy lena en nettehÄḟze min dunike min evliyae ve lakim mettaÂṀtehum ve abaehum hatta nesuz zikr ve kanu kavmen bura"
  25,19,"Fe kad kezzebukum bima tekulune fe ma testetÄḟyÂṀune sarfev ve la nasra ve mey yazlim minkum nuzÄḟkhu azaben kebÄḟra"
  25,20,"Ve ma erselna kableke minel murselÄḟne illa innehum le yeÂṀkulunet taame ve yemsune fil esvak ve cealna baÂṀdakum li baÂṀdÄḟn fitneh e tasbirun ve kane rabbuke besÄḟyra"
  25,21,"Ve kalellezÄḟne la yercune likaena lev la unzile aleynel melaiketu ev nera rabbena le kadistekberu fÄḟ enfusihim ve atev utuvven kebÄḟra"
  25,22,"Yevme yeravnel melaikete la busra yevmeizil lil mucrimÄḟne ve yekulune hÄḟcram mahcura"
  25,23,"Ve kadimna ila ma amilu min amelin fe cealnahu hebaem mensura"
  25,24,"Ashabul cenneti yemeizin hayrum mustekarrav ve ahsenu mekÄḟyla"
  25,25,"Ve yevme tesekkakus semau bil gamami ve nuzzilel melaiketu tenzÄḟla"
  25,26,"Elmulku yevmeizinil hakku lir rahman ve kane yevmen alel kafirÄḟne asÄḟra"
  25,27,"Ve yevme yeadduz zalimu ala yedeyhi yekulu ya leytenit tehaztu mear rasuli sebÄḟla"
  25,28,"Ya veyleta leytenÄḟ lem ettehÄḟz fulanen halÄḟla"
  25,29,"Le kad edallenÄḟ aniz zikri baÂṀde iz caenÄḟ ve kanes seytanu lil insani hazula"
  25,30,"Ve kaler rasulu ya rabbi inne kavmit tehazu hazel kurÂṀane mehcura"
  25,31,"Ve kezalike cealna li kulli nebiyyin aduvvem minel mucrimÄḟn ve kefa bi rabbike hadiyev ve nesÄḟyra"
  25,32,"Ve kalellezÄḟne keferu lev la nuzzile aleyhil kurÂṀanu cumletev vahÄḟdeh kezalike li nusebbite bihÄḟ fuadeke ve rattelnahu tertÄḟla"
  25,33,"Ve la yeÂṀtuneke bi meselin illa ciÂṀnake bil hakkÄḟ ve ahsene tefsÄḟra"
  25,34,"EllezÄḟne yuhserune ala vucuhihim ila cehenneme ulaike serrum mekanev ve edallu sebÄḟla"
  25,35,"Ve le kad ateyna musel kitabe ve cealna meahu ehahu harune vezÄḟra"
  25,36,"Fe kulnezheba ilel kavmillezÄḟne kezzebu bi ayatina fe demmernahum tedmÄḟra"
  25,37,"Ve kavme nuhÄḟl lemma kezzebur rusule agraknahum ve cealnahum lin nasi ayeh ve aÂṀtedna liz zalimÄḟne azaben elÄḟma"
  25,38,"Ve adev ve semude ve ashaber rassi ve kurunem beyne zalike kesÄḟra"
  25,39,"Ve kullen darabna lehul emsale ve kullen tebberna tetbÄḟra"
  25,40,"Ve le kad etev alel karyetilletÄḟ umtÄḟrat metaras seÂṀ e fe lem yekunu yeravneha bel kanu la yercune nusura"
  25,41,"Ve iza raevke iy yettehÄḟzuneke illa huzuva e hazellezÄḟ beasellahu rasula"
  25,42,"In kade le yudÄḟlluna an alihetina lev la en saberna aleyha ve sevfe yaÂṀlemune hÄḟyne yeravnel azabe men edallu sebÄḟla"
  25,43,"E raeyte menit tehaze ilahehu hevah e fe ente tekunu aleyhi vekÄḟla"
  25,44,"Em tahsebu enne ekserahum yesmeune ev yaÂṀkÄḟlun in hum illa kel enÂṀami bel hum edallu sebÄḟla"
  25,45,"E lem tera ila rabbike keyfe meddez zÄḟll ve lev sae le cealehu sakina summe cealnes semse aleyhi delÄḟla"
  25,46,"Summe kabadnahu ileyna kabday yesÄḟra"
  25,47,"Ve huvellezÄḟ ceale lekumul leyle libasev ven nevme subatev ve cealen nehar nusura"
  25,48,"Ve huvellezÄḟ erseler riyaha busram beyne yedey rahmetih ve enzelna menis semai maen tahura"
  25,49,"Li nuhyiye bihÄḟ beldetem meytev ve nuskÄḟyehu mimma halakna enÂṀamev ve enasiyye kesÄḟra"
  25,50,"Ve le kad sarrafnahu beynehum li yezzekkeru fe eba ekserun nasi illa kufura"
  25,51,"Ve lev siÂṀna le beasna fÄḟ kulli karyetin nezÄḟra"
  25,52,"Fe la tutÄḟÄḟl kafirÄḟne ve cahÄḟdhum bihÄḟ cihaden kebÄḟra"
  25,53,"Ve huvellezÄḟ meracel bahreyni haza azbun furatuv ve haza milhun ucac ve ceale beynehuma berzehav ve hÄḟcram mahcura"
  25,54,"Ve huvellezÄḟ haleka minel mai beseran fe cealehu nesebev ve sÄḟhra ve kane rabbuke kadÄḟra"
  25,55,"Ve yaÂṀbudune min dunillahi ma la yenfeuhum ve la yedurruhum ve kanel kafiru ala rabbihi zahÄḟra"
  25,56,"Ve ma erselnake illa mubessirav ve nezÄḟra"
  25,57,"Kul ma esÂṀelukum aleyhi min ecrin illa men sae ey yettehÄḟze ila rabbihÄḟ sebÄḟla"
  25,58,"Ve tevekkel alel hayyillezÄḟ la yemutu ve sebbÄḟh bi hamdih ve kefa bihÄḟ bi zunubi ÄḟbadihÄḟ habÄḟra"
  25,59,"EllezÄḟ halekas semavati vel erda ve ma beynehuma fÄḟ sitteti eyyamin summesteva alel arsir rahmanu fesÂṀel bihÄḟ habÄḟra"
  25,60,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehumuscudu lir rahmani kalu ve mer rahmanu e nescudu li ma teÂṀmuruna ve zadehum nufura"
  25,61,"TebarakellezÄḟ ceale fis semai burucev ve ceale fÄḟha siracev ve kameram munÄḟra"
  25,62,"Ve huvellezÄḟ cealel leyle ven nehara hÄḟlfetel li men erade ey yezzekkera ev erade sukura"
  25,63,"Ve Äḟbadur rahmanillezÄḟne yemsune alel erdÄḟ hevnev ve iza hatabehumul cahilune kalu selama"
  25,64,"VellezÄḟne yebÄḟtune li rabbihim succedev ve kÄḟyama"
  25,65,"VellezÄḟne yekulune rabbenasrif anna azabe cehenneme inne azabeha kane garam"
  25,66,"Inneha saet mustekarrav ve mukama"
  25,67,"VellezÄḟne iza enfeku lem yusrifu ve lem yakturu ve kane beyne zalike kavama (60. Ayet secde ayetidir)"
  25,68,"VellezÄḟne la yedÂṀune meallahi ilahen ahara ve la yaktulunen nefselletÄḟ harramellahu illa bil hakkÄḟ ve la yeznun ve mey yefÂṀal zalike yelka esama"
  25,69,"Yudaaf lehul azabu yevmel kÄḟyameti ve yahlud fÄḟhÄḟ muhana"
  25,70,"Illa men tabe ve amene ve amile amelen salihan fe ulaike yubeddilullahu seyyiatihim hasenat ve kanellahu gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  25,71,"Ve men tabe ve amile salihan fe innehu yetubu ilellahi metaba"
  25,72,"VellezÄḟne la yeshedunez zura ve iza merru bil lagvi merru kiram"
  25,73,"Vellezine iza zukkiru bi ayati rabbihim lem yehÄḟrru aleyha summev ve umyana"
  25,74,"VellezÄḟne yekulune rabbena heb lena min ezvacina va zurriyyatina kurrate aÂṀyuniv vecÂṀalna lil muttekÄḟyne imama"
  25,75,"Ulaike yuczevnel gurfete bi ma saberu ve yulekkavne fÄḟha tehÄḟyyetev ve selam"
  25,76,"HalidÄḟne fÄḟha hasunet mustekarrav ve mukama"
  25,77,"Kul ma yaÂṀbeu bi kum rabbÄḟ lev la duaukum fe kad kezzebtum fe sevfe yekunu lizama"
  26,8,"Inne fÄḟ zalike le ayeh ve ma kane ekseruhum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,9,"Ve inne rabbeke le huvel azÄḟzur rahÄḟym"
  26,10,"Ve iz nada rabbuke musa eniÂṀtil kavmez zalimÄḟn"
  26,11,"Kavme firÂṀavn e la yettekun"
  26,12,"Kale rabbi innÄḟ ehafu ey yukezzibun"
  26,13,"Ve yedÄḟyku sadrÄḟ ve la yentaliku lisanÄḟ fe ersil ila harun"
  26,14,"Ve le hum aleyye zembun fe ehafu ey yaktulun"
  26,15,"Kale kella fezheba bi ayatina inna meakum mustemiun"
  26,16,"FeÂṀtiya firÂṀavne fe kula inna rasulu rabbil alemÄḟn"
  26,17,"En ersil meana benÄḟ israiyl"
  26,18,"Kale e lem nurabbike fÄḟna velÄḟdev ve lebiste fÄḟna min umurike sinÄḟn"
  26,19,"Ve fealte faÂṀletekelletÄḟ fealte ve ente minel kafirÄḟn"
  26,20,"Kale fealtuha izev ve ene mined dallÄḟn"
  26,21,"Fe ferartu minkum lemma hÄḟftukum fe vehebe lÄḟ rabbÄḟ hukmev ve cealenÄḟ minel murselÄḟn"
  26,22,"Ve tilke nÄḟÂṀmetun temunnuha aleyye en abbedte benÄḟ israÄḟl"
  26,23,"Kale firÂṀavnu ve ma rabbul alemÄḟn"
  26,24,"Kale rabbus semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ma beynehuma inkuntum mukÄḟnÄḟn"
  26,25,"Kale li men havlehu ela testemiun"
  26,26,"Kale rabbukum ve rabbu abaikumul evvelÄḟn"
  26,27,"Kale inne rasulekumullezÄḟ ursile ileykum le mecnun"
