  26,29,"Kale leinittehazte ilahen gayrÄḟ le ecÂṀalenneke minel mescunÄḟn"
  26,30,"Kale e ve lev ciÂṀtuke bi seyÂṀim mubÄḟn"
  26,31,"Kale feÂṀti bihÄḟ in kunte mines sadikÄḟyn"
  26,32,"Fe elka asahu fe iza hiye suÂṀbanum mubÄḟn"
  26,33,"Ve nezea yedehu fe iza hiye beydau lin nazÄḟrÄḟn"
  26,34,"Kale lil melei havlehu inne haza lesahÄḟrun alÄḟm"
  26,35,"YurÄḟdu ey yuhricekum min erdÄḟkum bi sÄḟhrihÄḟ fe maza teÂṀmurun"
  26,36,"Kalu ercih ve ehahu vebÂṀas fil medaini hasirÄḟn"
  26,37,"YeÂṀtuke bi kulli sehharin alÄḟm"
