  26,39,"Ve kÄḟyle lin nasi hel entum muctemiun"
  26,40,"Leallena nettebius seharate in kanuhumul galibÄḟn"
  26,41,"Fe lemma caes seharatu kalu li firÂṀavne einne lena le ecran in kunna nahnul galibÄḟn"
  26,42,"Kale neam ve innekum izel le minel mukarrabÄḟn"
  26,43,"Kale lehum musa elku ma entum mulkun"
  26,44,"Fe elkav hÄḟbalehum ve ÄḟsÄḟyyehum ve kalu bi Äḟzzeti firÂṀavne inna le nahnul galibun"
