  26,46,"Fe ulkÄḟyes seharatu sacidÄḟn"
  26,47,"Kalu amenna bi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  26,48,"Rabbi musa ve harun"
  26,49,"Kale amentum lehu kable en azene lekum innehu le kebirukumullezÄḟ allemekumus sÄḟhr fe le sevfe taÂṀlemun le ukattÄḟanne eydiyekum ve erculekum min hÄḟlafiv ve la uzallibennekum ecmeÄḟyn"
  26,50,"Kalu la dayra inna ila rabbina munkalibun"
  26,51,"Inna natmeu ey yagfira lena rabbuna hatayana en kunna evvelel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,52,"Ve evhayna ila musa en esri bi ÄḟbadÄḟ innekum muttebeun"
  26,53,"Fe ersele firÂṀavnu fil medaini hasirÄḟn"
  26,54,"Inne haulai le sirzimetun kalÄḟlun"
  26,55,"Ve innehum lena le gaizun"
  26,56,"Ve inna le cemÄḟun hazirun"
  26,57,"Fe ahracnahum min cennativ ve uyun"
  26,58,"Ve kunuziv ve mekamin kerÄḟm"
  26,59,"Kezalik ve evrasnaha benÄḟ israÄḟl"
  26,60,"Fe etbeuhum musrikÄḟyn"
  26,61,"Felemma terael cemÂṀani kale ashabu musa inna le mudrakun"
  26,62,"Kale kella inne meÄḟye rabbÄḟ seyehdÄḟn"
  26,63,"Fe evhayna ila masa enÄḟdrib bi asakel bahr fenfeleka fe kane kullu firkÄḟn ket tavdil azÄḟym"
  26,64,"Ve ezlefna semmel aharÄḟn"
  26,65,"Ve enceyna musa ve mem meahu ecmeÄḟyn"
  26,66,"Summe agraknel aharÄḟn"
  26,67,"Inne fÄḟ zalike le ayeh ve ma kane ekseruhum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,68,"Ve inne rabbeke le huvel azÄḟzur rahÄḟym"
  26,69,"Vetlu aleyhim nebee ibrahÄḟm"
  26,70,"Iz kale li ebÄḟhi ve kavmihÄḟ ma taÂṀbudun"
