  26,72,"Kale hel yesmeunekum iz tedÂṀun"
  26,73,"Ev yenfeunekum ev yedurrun"
  26,74,"Kalu bel vecedna abaena kezalike yefÂṀalun"
  26,75,"Kale e feraeytum ma kuntum taÂṀbudun"
  26,76,"Entum ve abaukumul akdemun"
  26,77,"Fe innehum aduvvul lÄḟ illa rabbel alemÄḟn"
  26,78,"EllezÄḟ halekanÄḟ fe huve yehdÄḟn"
  26,79,"VellezÄḟ huve yutÂṀÄḟmunÄḟ ve yeskÄḟyn"
  26,80,"Ve iza merÄḟdtu fe huve yesfÄḟn"
  26,81,"VellezÄḟ yumÄḟtunÄḟ summe yuhyÄḟn"
  26,82,"VellezÄḟ atÂṀmeu ey yagfira lÄḟ hatÄḟyÂṀetÄḟ yevmeddÄḟn"
  26,83,"Rabbi heb lÄḟ hukmev ve elhÄḟknÄḟ bis salihÄḟyn"
  26,84,"VecÂṀal lÄḟ lisane sÄḟdkÄḟn fil ahÄḟrÄḟn"
