  26,86,"Vagfir li ebÄḟ innehu kane mined dallÄḟn"
  26,87,"Ve la tuhzinÄḟ yevme yubÂṀasun"
  26,88,"Yevme la yenfeu maluv ve la benun"
  26,89,"Illa men etellahe bi kalbin selim"
  26,90,"Ve uzlifetil cennetu lil muttekÄḟyn"
  26,91,"Ve burrizetil cehÄḟymu li gavÄḟn"
  26,92,"Ve kÄḟyle lehum eyne ma kuntum taÂṀbudun"
  26,93,"Min dunillah hel yensurunekum ev yentesÄḟrun"
  26,94,"Fe kubkibu fÄḟhahum vel gavun"
  26,95,"Ve cunudu iblÄḟse ecmeun"
  26,96,"Kalu ve hum fÄḟha yahtesÄḟmun"
  26,97,"Tellahi in kunna le fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  26,98,"Iz nusevvÄḟkum bi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  26,99,"Ve ma edalleha illel mucrimun"
  26,100,"Fe ma lena min safiÄḟyn"
  26,101,"Ve la sadÄḟkÄḟn hamÄḟm"
  26,102,"Fe lev enne lena kerraten fe nekune minel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,103,"Inne fÄḟ zalike le ayeh ve ma kane ekseruhum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,104,"Ve inne rabbeke le huvel azÄḟzur rahÄḟym"
  26,105,"Kezzebet kavmu nuhÄḟnil murselÄḟn"
  26,106,"Iz kale lehum ehuhum nuhun ela tettekun"
  26,107,"Inni lekum rasulun emÄḟn"
  26,108,"Fettekullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀun"
  26,109,"Ve ma esÂṀelukum aleyhi min ecr in ecriye illa ala rabbil alemÄḟn"
  26,110,"Fettekullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀun"
  26,111,"Kalu enuÂṀminu leke vettebeakel erzelun"
  26,112,"Kale vema ÄḟlmÄḟ bima kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  26,113,"In hÄḟsabuhum illa ala rabbÄḟ lev tesÂṀurun"
  26,114,"Ve ma ene bi taridil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,115,"In ene illa nezÄḟrum mubÄḟn"
  26,116,"Kalu le il lem tentehi ya nuhu le tekunenne minel mercumÄḟn"
  26,117,"Kale rabbi inne kavmÄḟ kezzebun"
  26,118,"Fettah beynÄḟ ve beynehum fethav ve neccinÄḟ ve mem meÄḟye minel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,119,"Fe enceynahu ve mem meahu fil fulkil meshun"
  26,120,"Summe agrakna baÂṀdul bakÄḟyn"
  26,121,"Inne fÄḟ zalik le ayeh ve ma kane ekseruhum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,122,"Ve inne rabbeke le huvel azÄḟzur rahÄḟym"
  26,123,"Kezzebet adunil murselÄḟn"
  26,124,"Iz kale lehum ehuhum hudun ela tettekun"
  26,125,"InnÄḟ lekum rasulun emÄḟn"
  26,126,"Fettekullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀun"
  26,127,"Ve ma esÂṀelukum aleyhi min ecr in ecriye illa ala rabbil alemÄḟn"
  26,128,"E tebnune bi kulli riyÂṀÄḟn ayeten taÂṀbesun"
  26,129,"Ve tettehÄḟzune mesanÄḟa leallekum tahludun"
  26,130,"Ve iza betastum betastum cebbarÄḟn"
  26,131,"Fettekullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀun"
  26,132,"VettekullezÄḟ emeddekum bima taÂṀlemun"
  26,133,"Emeddekum bi enÂṀamiv ve benÄḟn"
  26,134,"Ve cennativ ve uyun"
  26,135,"InnÄḟ ehafu aleykum azabe yevmin azÄḟym"
  26,136,"Kalu sevaun aleyna e veazte em lem tekum minel vaÄḟzÄḟyn"
  26,137,"In haza illa hulukul evvelÄḟn"
  26,138,"Ve ma nahnu bi muazzebÄḟn"
  26,139,"Fe kezzebuhu fe ehleknahum inne fÄḟ zalike le ayeh ve ma kane ekseruhum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,140,"Ve inne rabbeke le huvel azÄḟzur rahÄḟym"
  26,141,"Kezzebet semudul murselÄḟn"
  26,142,"Iz kale lehum ehuhum salihun ela tettekun"
  26,143,"InnÄḟ lekum rasulun emÄḟn"
  26,144,"Fettekullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀun"
  26,145,"Ve ma esÂṀelukum aleyhi men ecr in ecriye illa ala rabbil alemÄḟn"
  26,146,"E tutrakune fÄḟ ma hahuna aminÄḟn"
  26,147,"FÄḟ cennativ ve uyun"
  26,148,"Ve zuruÄḟv ve nahlin talÂṀuha hedÄḟym"
  26,149,"Ve tenhÄḟtune minel cibali buyuten farihÄḟn"
  26,150,"Fettekullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀun"
  26,151,"Ve la tutÄḟyÂṀu emral musrifÄḟn"
  26,152,"EllezÄḟne yufsidune fil erdÄḟ ve la yuslihun"
  26,153,"Kalu innema ente minel musahharÄḟn"
  26,154,"Ma ente illa beserum misluna feÂṀti bi ayetin in kunte mines sadikÄḟyn"
  26,155,"Kale hazihÄḟ nakatul leha sirbuv ve lekum sirbu yevmim maÂṀlum"
  26,156,"Ve la temessuha bi suin fe yeÂṀhuzekum azabu yevmin azÄḟym"
  26,157,"Fe akaruha fe asbehu nadimÄḟn"
  26,158,"Fe ehazehumul azab inne fÄḟ zalike le ayeh ve ma kane ekseruhum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,159,"Ve inne rabbeke le huvel azÄḟzur rahÄḟym"
  26,160,"Kezzebet kavmu lutÄḟnil murselun"
  26,161,"Iz kale lehum ehuhum lutun ela tettekun"
  26,162,"InnÄḟ lekum rasulun emÄḟn"
  26,163,"Fettekullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀun"
  26,164,"Ve esÂṀelukum aleyhi min ecr in ecriye illa ala rabbil alemÄḟn"
  26,165,"E teÂṀtunez zukrane minel alemÄḟn"
  26,166,"Ve tezerune ma haleka lekum rabbukum min ezvacikum bel entum kavmun adun"
  26,167,"Kalu leil lem tentehi ya lutu le tekunenne minel muhracÄḟn"
  26,168,"Kale innÄḟ li amelikum minel kalÄḟn"
  26,169,"Rabbi neccinÄḟ ve ehlÄḟ mimma yaÂṀmelun"
  26,170,"Fe necceynahu ve ehlehu ecmeÄḟyn"
  26,171,"Illa acuzen fil gabirÄḟn"
  26,172,"Summe demmernel aharÄḟn"
  26,173,"Ve emtarna aleyhim metara fe sae metarul munzerÄḟn"
  26,174,"Inne fÄḟ zalike le ayeh ve ma kane ekseruhum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,175,"Ve inne rabbeke le huvel azÄḟzur rahÄḟym"
  26,176,"Kezzebe ashabul eyketil murselÄḟn"
  26,177,"Iz kale lehum suaybun ela tettekun"
  26,178,"InnÄḟ lekum rasulun emÄḟn"
  26,179,"Fettekullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀun"
  26,180,"Ve ma esÂṀelukum aleyhi min ecr in ecriye illa ala rabbil alemÄḟn"
  26,181,"Evful keyle ve la tekunu minel muhsirÄḟn"
  26,182,"Vezinu bil kÄḟstasil mustekÄḟym"
  26,183,"Ve la tebhasun nase esyaehum ve la taÂṀsev fil erdÄḟ musidÄḟn"
  26,184,"VettekullezÄḟ halekakum vel cibilletel evvelÄḟn"
  26,185,"Kalu innema ente minel musahharÄḟn"
  26,186,"Ve ma ente illa beserum misluna ve in nezunnuke le minel kazibÄḟn"
  26,187,"Fe eskÄḟt aleyna kisefem mines semai in kunte mines sadikÄḟyn"
  26,188,"Kale rabbÄḟ aÂṀlemu bi ma taÂṀmelun"
  26,189,"Fe kezzebuhu fe ehazehum azabu yevmiz zulleh innehu kane azabe yevmin azÄḟym"
  26,190,"Inne fÄḟ zalike le ayeh ve ma kane ekseruhum muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,191,"Ve inne rabbeke le huvel azÄḟzur rahÄḟym"
  26,192,"Ve innehu le tenzÄḟlu rabbil alemÄḟn"
  26,193,"Nezele bihir ruhul emÄḟn"
  26,194,"Ala kalbike li tekune minel munzirÄḟn"
  26,195,"Bi lisanin arabiyyim mubÄḟn"
  26,196,"Ve innehu lefÄḟ zuburil evvelÄḟn"
  26,197,"E ve lem yekul lehum ayeten ey yaÂṀlemehu ulemau benÄḟ israÄḟl"
  26,198,"Ve lev nezzelnahu ala baÂṀdÄḟl aÂṀcemÄḟn"
  26,199,"Fe karaehu aleyhim ma kanu bihÄḟ muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,200,"Kezalike seleknahu fÄḟ kulubil mucrimÄḟn"
  26,201,"La yuÂṀminune bihÄḟ hatta yeravul azabel elÄḟm"
  26,202,"Fe yeÂṀtiyehum bagtetev ve hum la yesÂṀurun"
  26,203,"Fe yekul hel nahnu munzarun"
  26,204,"E fe bi azabina yestaÂṀcilun"
  26,205,"E feraeyte im mettaÂṀnahum sinÄḟn"
  26,206,"Summe caehum ma kun yuadun"
  26,207,"Ma agna anhum ma kanu yumetteun"
  26,208,"Ve ma ehlekna min karyetin illa leha munzirun"
  26,209,"Zikra ve ma kunna zalimÄḟn"
  26,210,"Ve ma tenezzelet bihis seyatÄḟyn"
  26,211,"Ve ma yembegÄḟy lehum ve ma yestetÄḟyÂṀun"
  26,212,"Innehum anis semÂṀÄḟ le maÂṀzulun"
  26,213,"Fe la tedÂṀu meallahi ilahen ahara fe tekune minel muazzebÄḟn"
  26,214,"Ve enzir asiratekel akrabÄḟn"
  26,215,"VahfÄḟd cenahake li menit tebeake minel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  26,216,"Fe in asavke fe kul innÄḟ berÄḟum mimma taÂṀmelun"
  26,217,"Ve tevekkel alel azÄḟzir rahÄḟym"
  26,218,"EllezÄḟ yerake hÄḟyne tekum"
  26,219,"Ve tekallubeke fis sacidÄḟn"
  26,220,"Innehu huves semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  26,221,"Hel unebbiukum ala men tenezzelus seyatÄḟyn"
  26,222,"Tenezzelu ala kulli effakin esÄḟm"
  26,223,"Yulkunes semÂṀa ve ekseruhum kazibun"
  26,224,"Ves suarau yettebiuhumul gavun"
  26,225,"E lem tera ennehum fÄḟ kulli vadiy yehÄḟmun"
  26,226,"Ve ennehum yekulune ma la yefÂṀalun"
  26,227,"IllellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati ve zekerullahe kesÄḟrav ventesaru mim baÂṀdi ma zulimu ve seyaÂṀlemullezÄḟne zalemu eyye munkalebiy yenkalibun"
  27,8,"Felemma caeha nudiye em burike men fin nari ve men havleha ve subhanellahi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  27,9,"Ya musa innehu enellahul azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  27,10,"Ve elkÄḟ asak felemma raaha tehtezzu ke enneha cannuv vella mudbirav ve lem yuakkÄḟb ya musa la tehaf innÄḟ la yehafu ledeyyel murselun"
  27,11,"Illa men zaleme summe beddele husnem baÂṀde suin fe innÄḟ gafurur rahÄḟym"
  27,12,"Ve edhÄḟl yedeke fÄḟ ceybike tahruc beydae min gayri suin fÄḟ tisÂṀÄḟ ayatin ila firÂṀavne ve kavmih innehum kanu kavmen fasikÄḟyn"
  27,13,"Felemma caethum ayatuna mubsÄḟraten kalu haza sÄḟhrum mubÄḟn"
  27,14,"Ve cehadu biha vesteykanetha enfusuhum zulmev ve uluvva fenzur keyfe kane akÄḟbetul mufsidÄḟn"
  27,15,"Ve le kad ateyna davede ve suleymane Äḟlma ve kalel hamdu lillahillezÄḟ faddalena ala kesÄḟrim min Äḟbadihil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  27,16,"Ve verise suleymanu davude ve kale ya eyyuhen nasu ullimna mentÄḟkat tayri ve utÄḟna min kulli seyÂṀ inne haza le huvel fadlul mubÄḟn"
  27,17,"Ve husira li suleymane cunuduhu minel cinni vel insi vet tayri fe hum yuzeun"
  27,18,"Hatta iza etev ala vadin nemli kalet nemletuy ya eyyuhen nemludhulu mesakinekum la yahtÄḟmennekum suleymanu ve cunuduhu ve hum la yesÂṀurun"
  27,19,"Fe tebesseme dahÄḟkem min kavliha ve kale rabbi evzÄḟÂṀnÄḟ en eskura nÄḟÂṀmetekelletÄḟ enÂṀamte aleyye ve ala valideyye ve en aÂṀmele salihan terdahu ve edhÄḟlnÄḟ bi rahmetike fÄḟ Äḟbadikes salihÄḟyn"
  27,20,"Ve tefekkadet tayra fe kale maliye le eral hudhude em kane minel gaibÄḟn"
  27,21,"Le uazzibennehu azaben sedÄḟden ev le ezbehannehu ev le yeÂṀtiyennÄḟ bi sultanim mubÄḟn"
  27,22,"Fe mekese gayra beÄḟydin fe kale ehattu bi ma lem tuhÄḟt bihÄḟ ve ciÂṀtuke min sebeim bi nebiy yekÄḟyn"
  27,23,"InnÄḟ vecedtumraeten temlikuhum ve utiyet min kulli seyÂṀiv ve leha arsun azÄḟym"
  27,24,"Vecedtuha ve kavmeha yescudune lis semsi min dunillahi ve zeyyene lehumus seytanu aÂṀmalehum fe saddehum anis sebÄḟli fehum la yehtedun"
  27,25,"Ella yescudu lillahillezÄḟ yuhricul habÂṀe fis semavati vel erdÄḟ ve yaÂṀlemu ma tuhfune ve ma tuÂṀlinun"
  27,26,"Allahu la ilahe illa huve rabbul arsil azÄḟym"
  27,27,"Kale senenzuru e sadakte em kunte minel kazibÄḟn"
  27,28,"Izheb bi kitabÄḟ haza fe elkÄḟh ileyhim summe tevelle anhum fenzur maza yarciun"
  27,29,"Kalet ya eyyuhel meleu innÄḟ ulkÄḟye ileyye kitabun kerÄḟm"
  27,30,"Innehu min suleymane ve innehu bismillahirrahmanirrahÄḟym"
  27,31,"Ella taÂṀlu aleyye veÂṀtunÄḟ muslimÄḟn"
  27,32,"Kalet ya eyyuhel meleu eftunÄḟ fÄḟ emrÄḟ ma kuntu katÄḟaten emrah hatta teshedun"
  27,33,"Kalu nahnu ulu kuvvetiv ve ulu beÂṀsin sedÄḟdiv vel emru ileyki fenzurÄḟ maza teÂṀmurÄḟn"
  27,34,"Kalet innel muluke iza dehalu karyeten efseduha ve cealu eÄḟzzete ehliha ezilleh ve kezalike yefalun"
  27,35,"Ve innÄḟ mursiletun ileyhim bi hedeyyetin fe nazÄḟratum bime yarciul murselun(25. Ayet secde ayetidir)"
  27,36,"Felemma cae suleymane kale etumidduneni bi malin fema ataniyellahu hayrum mimma atakum bel entum bi hediyyetikum tefrahun"
  27,37,"IrcÄḟÂṀileyhim fe leneÂṀtiyennehum bi cunudil la kÄḟbele lehum biha ve le nuhricennehum minha ezilletev ve hum sagÄḟrun"
  27,38,"Kale ya eyyuhel meleu eyyukum yeÂṀtÄḟnÄḟ bi arsiha kable ey yeÂṀtunÄḟ muslimÄḟn"
  27,39,"Kale ÄḟfrÄḟtum minel cinni ene atÄḟke bihÄḟ kable en tekume mim mekamik ve innÄḟ aleyhi le kaviyyun emÄḟn"
  27,40,"KalellezÄḟ Äḟndehu Äḟlmum minel kitabi ene atÄḟke bihÄḟ kable ey yertedde ileyke tarfuk felmma raahu mustekÄḟrran Äḟndehu kale haza min fadli rabbÄḟ li yebluvenÄḟ e eskuru em ekfur ve men sekera fe innema yeskuru li nefsih ve men kefera fe inne rabbÄḟ ganiyyun kerÄḟm"
  27,41,"Kale nekkiru leha arseha nenzur e tehtedÄḟ em tekunu minellezÄḟne la yehtedun"
  27,42,"Felemma caet kÄḟyle e hakeza arsuk kalet keennehu hu ve utÄḟnel Äḟlme min kabliha ve kunna muslimÄḟn"
  27,43,"Ve saddeha ma kanet taÂṀbudu min dunillah inneha kanet min kavmin kafirÄḟn"
  27,44,"KÄḟyle lehedhulis sarh felemma raethu hasibethu luccetev ve kesefet an sakayha kale innehu sarhum mumerradum min kavarÄḟr kalet rabbi innÄḟ zalemtu nefsÄḟ ve eslemtu mea suleymane lillahi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  27,45,"Ve le kad erselna ila semude ehahum salihan enÄḟÂṀbudullahe fe izahum ferÄḟkani yahtesÄḟmun"
  27,46,"Kale ya kavmi lime testaÂṀcilune bis seyyieti kablel haseneh lev la testagfirunellahe leallekum turhamun"
  27,47,"Kalut tayyerna bike ve bi mem meak kale tairukum Äḟndellahi bel entum kavmun tuftenun"
  27,48,"Ve kane fil medÄḟneti tisÂṀatu rahtÄḟy yufsidune fil erdÄḟ ve la yuslihun"
  27,49,"Kalu tekasemu billahi le nubeyyitennehu ve ehlehu summe le nekullenne li veliyyihÄḟ ma sehidna mehlike ehlihÄḟ ve inna le sadikÄḟn"
  27,50,"Ve mekeru mekrav ve mekerna mekrav ve hum la yesÂṀurun"
  27,51,"Fenzur keyfe kane akÄḟbetu mekrihim enna demmernahum ve kavmehum ecmeÄḟyn"
  27,52,"Fe tilke buyutuhum haviyetem bima zalemu inne fÄḟ zalike le ayetel li kavmiy yaÂṀlemun"
  27,53,"Ve enceynellezÄḟne amenu ve kanu yettekun"
  27,54,"Ve lutan iz kale li kavmihÄḟ eteÂṀtunel fahÄḟsete ve entum tubsÄḟrun"
  27,55,"E innekum le teÂṀtuner ricale sehvetem min dunin nisaÂṀ bel entum kavmun techelun"
  27,56,"Fe ma kane cevabe kavmihÄḟ illa en kalu ahricu ale lutÄḟm min karyetikum innehum unasuy yetetahherun"
  27,57,"Fe enceynahu ve ehlehu illemraetehu kaddernaha minel gabirÄḟn"
  27,58,"Ve emtarna aleyhim metara fe sae metarul munzerÄḟn"
  27,59,"Kulil humdu lillahi ve selamun ala ÄḟbadihillezÄḟnastafa allahu hayrun emma yusrikun"
  27,60,"Emmen halekas semavati vel erda ve enzele lekum mines semai maa fe embetna bihÄḟ hadaika zate behceh ma kane lekum en tumbitu seceraha e ilahum meallah bel hum kavmuy yaÂṀdilun"
  27,61,"Emmen ceallel erda kararav ve cealle hÄḟlaleha enharav ve ceale leha ravasiye ve ceale beynel bahrayni haciza e ilahum meallah bel ekseruhum la yaÂṀlemun"
  27,62,"Emmey yucÄḟbul mudtarra iza deahu ve yeksifus sue ve yecÂṀalukum hulefael ard e ilahum meallah kalÄḟlem ma tezekkerun"
  27,63,"Emmey yehdÄḟkum fÄḟ zulumatil berri vel bahri ve mey yursilur riyaha busram beyne yedey rahmetih e ilahum meallah tealellahu amma yusrikun"
  27,64,"Emmey yebdeul halka summe yuÄḟyduhu ve mey yerzukukum mines semai vel ard e ilahum meallah kul hatu burhanekum in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  27,65,"Kul la yaÂṀlemu men fis semavati vel erdÄḟl gaybe illellah ve ma yesÂṀurune eyyane yubÂṀasun"
  27,66,"Belid darake Äḟlmuhum fil ahÄḟrati bel hum fÄḟ sekkim minha bel hum minha amÄḟun"
  27,67,"Ve kalellezÄḟne keferu e iza kunna turabev ve abauna einna le muhracun"
  27,68,"Le kad vuÄḟdna haza nahnu ve abauna min kablu in haza illa esatÄḟyrul evvelÄḟn"
  27,69,"Kul sÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetul mucrimÄḟn"
  27,70,"Ve la tahzen aleyhim ve la tekun fÄḟ daykÄḟm mimma yemkurun"
  27,71,"Ve yekulune meta hazel vaÂṀdu in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  27,72,"Kul asa ey yekune radife lekum baÂṀdullezÄḟ testaÂṀcilun"
  27,73,"Ve inne rabbeke le zu fadlin alen nasi ve lakinne ekserahum la yeskurun"
  27,74,"Ve inne rabbeke le yaÂṀlemu ma tukinnu suduruhum ve ma yuÂṀlinun"
  27,75,"Ve ma min gaibetin fis semai vel erdÄḟ illa fÄḟ kitabim mubÄḟn"
  27,76,"Inne hazel kurÂṀane yekussu ala benÄḟ israÄḟle ekserallezÄḟ hum fÄḟhi yahtelifun"
  27,77,"Ve innehu lehudev ve rahmetul lil mu7minÄḟn"
  27,78,"Inne rabbeke yakdÄḟy beynehum bi hukmih ve huvel azÄḟzul alÄḟm"
  27,79,"Fe tevekkel alellah inneke alel hakkÄḟl mubÄḟn"
  27,80,"Inneke la tusmiul mevta ve la tusmius summed duae iza vellev mudbirÄḟn"
  27,81,"Ve ma ente bi hadil umyi an dalaletihim in tusmiu illa mey yuÂṀminu bi ayatina fe hum muslimun"
  27,82,"Ve iza vekaal kavlu aleyhim ahracna lehum dabbetem minel erdÄḟ tukellimuhum ennen nase kanu bi ayatina la yukÄḟnun"
  27,83,"Ve yevme nahsuru min kulli ummetin fevcem mimmey yukezzibu bi ayatina fehum yuzeun"
  27,84,"Hatta iza cau kale e kezzebtum bi ayatÄḟ ve lem tuhÄḟytu biha ilmen emma za kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  27,85,"Ve vekaal kavlu aleyhim bima zalemu fe hum la yentÄḟkun"
  27,86,"E lem yerav enna cealnel leyle li yeskunu fÄḟhi ven nehara mubsÄḟra inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  27,87,"Ve yevme yunfehu fis suri fe fezia men fis semavati ve men fil erdÄḟ illa men saellah ve kullun etevhu dahÄḟrÄḟn"
  27,88,"Ve teral cibale tahsebuha camidetev ve hiye temurru merras sehab sunÂṀallahillezÄḟ etkane kulle seyÂṀ innehu habÄḟrum bima tefalun"
  27,89,"Men cae bil haseneti fe lehu hayrum minha ve hum min fezeÄḟy yevmeizin aminÄḟn"
  27,90,"Ve men cae bis seyyieti fe kubbet vucuhuhum fin nar hel tuczevne ila ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  27,91,"Innema umirtu en aÂṀbude rabbe hazihil beldetillezÄḟ harrameha ve lehu kullu seyÂṀiv ve umirtu en ekune minel muslimÄḟn"
  27,92,"Ve en etluvel kurÂṀan fe menihteda fe innema yehtedÄḟ li nefsih ve men dalle fe kul innema ene minel munzirÄḟn"
  27,93,"Ve kulil hamdu lillahi seyurÄḟkum ayatihÄḟ fe taÂṀrifuneha ve ma rabbuke bi gafilin amma taÂṀmelun"
  28,8,"Feltekatahu alu firÂṀavne li yekune lehum aduvvev ve hazena inne firÂṀavne ve hamane ve cunudehuma kanu hatÄḟÄḟn"
  28,9,"Ve kaletimraetu firÂṀavne kurratu aynil lÄḟ ve lek la taktuluhu asa ey yenfeana ev nettehÄḟzehu veledev ve hum la yesÂṀurun"
  28,10,"Ve asbeha fuadu ummi musa fariga in kadet le tubdÄḟ bihÄḟ levla er rabatna ala kalbiha li tekune minel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  28,11,"Ve kalet li uhtihÄḟ kussÄḟhi fe besurat bihÄḟ an cunubiv ve hum la yesÂṀurun"
  28,12,"Ve harramna aleyhil meradÄḟa min kablu fe kalet hel edullukum ala ehli beytiy yekfulunehu lekum ve hum lehu nasÄḟhun"
  28,13,"Fe radednahu ila ummihÄḟ key tekarra aynuhaa ve la tahzene ve li taÂṀleme enne vaÂṀdellahi hakkuv ve lakinne ekserahum la yaÂṀlemun"
  28,14,"Ve lemma belega esuddehu vesteva ateynahu hukmev ve Äḟlma ve kezalike neczil muhsinÄḟn"
  28,15,"Ve dehalel medÄḟnete ala hÄḟyni gafletim min ehliha fe vecede fÄḟha raculeyni yaktetilani haza min sÄḟatihÄḟ ve haza min aduvvih festegasehullezÄḟ min sÄḟatihÄḟ alellezÄḟ min aduvvihÄḟ fe vekezehu musa fe kada aleyhi kale haza min amelis seytan innehu aduvvum mudÄḟllum mubÄḟn"
  28,16,"Kale rabbi innÄḟ zalemtu nefsÄḟ fagfirlÄḟ fe gafera leh innehu huvel gafurur rahÄḟym"
  28,17,"Kale rabbi bima enÂṀamte aleyye fe lem ekune zahÄḟral lil mucrimÄḟn"
  28,18,"Fe asbeha fil medÄḟneti haifey yeterakkabu fe izellezistensarahu bil emsi yestasrihuh kale lehu musa inneke le gaviyyum mubÄḟn"
  28,19,"Fe lemma en erade ey yebtÄḟse billezÄḟ huve aduvvul lehuma kale ya musa e turÄḟdu en taktulenÄḟ kema katelte nefsem bil emsi in turÄḟdu illa en tekune cebbara fil erdÄḟ ve ma turÄḟdu en tekune minel muslihÄḟyn"
  28,20,"Ve cae raculum min aksal medÄḟneti yesÂṀa kale ya musa innel melee yeÂṀtemirune bike li yaktuluke fahruc innÄḟ leke minen nasÄḟhÄḟyn"
  28,21,"Fe harace minha halifey yeterakkabu kale rabbi neccinÄḟ minel kavmiz zalimÄḟn"
  28,22,"Ve lemma teveccehe tilkae medyene kale asa rabbÄḟ ey yehdiyenÄḟ sevaes sebÄḟl"
  28,23,"Ve lemma verade mae medyene vecede aleyhi ummetem minen nasi yeskune ve veced min dunihimumraeteyni tezudan kel ma hatbukuma kaleta la neskÄḟy hatta yusdirar riau ve ebuna seyhun kebÄḟr"
  28,24,"Fe seka lehuma summe tevella ilez zÄḟlli fe kale rabbi ninÄḟ lima enzelte ileyye min hayrin fekÄḟyr"
  28,25,"Fe caethu Äḟhdahuma temsÄḟ alestÄḟhyain kalet inne ebÄḟ yedÂṀuke li yecziyeke ecra ma sekayte lena felemma caehu ve kassa aleyhil kasasa kale la tehaf necevte minel kavmiz zalimÄḟn"
  28,26,"Kalet ihdahuma ya ebetisteÂṀcirhu inne hayra menisteÂṀcertel kaviyyul emÄḟn"
  28,27,"Kale innÄḟ urÄḟdu en unkihake Äḟhdebneteyye hateyni ala en teÂṀcuranÄḟ semaniye hÄḟcec fe in etmente asran fe min Äḟndik ve ma urÄḟdu en esukka aleyk setecidunÄḟ in saellahu minas salihÄḟyn"
  28,28,"Kale zalike biynÄḟ ve beynek eyyemel eceleyni kadaytu fe la udvane aleyy vallahu ala ma nekulu vekÄḟl"
  28,29,"Felemma kada musel ecele ve sara bi ehlihÄḟ anese min canibit turi nasa kale li ehlihimkusu innÄḟ anestu naral leallÄḟ atÄḟkum minha bi haberin ev cezvetim minen nari leallekum tastalun"
  28,30,"Felemma etaha nudiye min satÄḟÄḟl vadil eymeni fil bukÂṀatil mubaraketi mines secerati ey ya musa innÄḟ enellahu rabbul alemÄḟn"
  28,31,"Ve en elkÄḟ asak felemma raaha tehtezzu keenneha cannuv vella mudbirav ve lem yuakkÄḟb ya musa akbil ve la teh0af inneke minel aminÄḟn"
  28,32,"Usluk yedeke fi ceybike tahruc beydae min gayri suÂṀiv vadmun ileyke cenahake miner rahbi fe zanike burhanani mir rabbike ila firÂṀavne ve meleih innehum kanu kavmen fasikÄḟyn"
  28,33,"Kale rabbi nnÄḟ kateltu minhum nefsen fe ehafu ey yaktulun"
  28,34,"Ve ehÄḟy harunu huve efsahu minnÄḟ lisaen fe ersilhu meÄḟye ridÂṀey yusaddikunÄḟ innÄḟ ehafu ey yukezzibun"
  28,35,"Kale senesuddu adudeke bi ehÄḟyke ve necÂṀalu lekuma sultanen fe la yesÄḟlune ileykuma bi ayatina entuma ve menit tebeakumel ggalibun"
  28,36,"Felemma caehum musa bi ayatina beyyinatin kalu ma haza illa sÄḟhrum mufterav ve ma semÄḟÂṀna bihaza fÄḟ abainel evvelÄḟn"
  28,37,"Ve kale musa rabbÄḟ aÂṀlemu bi men cae bil huda min ÄḟndihÄḟ ve men tekunu lehu akÄḟbetud dar innehu la yuflihuz zalimun"
  28,38,"Ve kale firÂṀavnu ya eyyuhel meleu ma alemtu lekum min ilahin gayrÄḟ Fe evkÄḟd lÄḟ ya hamanu alet tÄḟyni fecÂṀal lÄḟ sarhal leallÄḟ ettaliu ila ilahi musa ve inni le ezunnuhu minel kazibÄḟn"
  28,39,"Vestekbera huve ve cunuduhu fil erdÄḟ bi gayril hakkÄḟ ve zannu ennehum ileyna la yurceun"
  28,40,"Fe ahaznahu ve cunudehu fenebeznahum fil yemm fenzur keyfe kane akÄḟbetuz zalimÄḟn"
  28,41,"Ve cealnahum eimmetey yedÂṀune ilen nar ve yevmel kÄḟyameti la yunsarun"
  28,42,"Ve etbaÂṀnahum fÄḟ hazihid dunya laÂṀneh ve yevmel kÄḟyameti hum minel makbuhÄḟyn"
  28,43,"Ve le kad ateyna musel kitabe mim baÂṀdi ma ehleknel kurunel ula besaira lin nasi ve hudev ve rahmetel leallehum yetezekkerun"
  28,44,"Ve ma kunte bi canibil garbiyyi iz kadayna ila musel emra ve ma kunte mines sahidÄḟn"
  28,45,"Ve lakinna enseÂṀna kurunen fe tetavele aleyhimul umur ve ma kunte saviyen fÄḟ ehli medyene tetlu aleyhim ayatina ve lakinna kunna mursilÄḟn"
  28,46,"Ve ma kunte bi canibit turi iz nadeyna ve lakir rahmetem mir rabbike li tunzira kavmem ma etahum min nezÄḟrim min kablike leallehum yetezekkerun"
  28,47,"Ve lev la en tusiybehum musÄḟybetum bima kaddemet eydÄḟhim fe yekulu rabbena lev la erselte iyna rasulen fe nettebia yatike ve nekune minel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  28,48,"Felemma caehumul hakku min Äḟndina kalu levla utiye misle ma utiye musa e ve lem yekfuru bima utiye musa min kabl kalu sÄḟhrani tezahera ve kalu inna bi kullin kafirun"
  28,49,"Kul feÂṀtu bi kitabim min Äḟndillahi huve ehda minhuma etebÄḟÂṀhu in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  28,50,"Fe il lem yestecÄḟbu leke faÂṀlem ennema yettebiune ehvaehum ve men edallu mimmenittebea hevahu bi gayri hudem minellah innellahe la yehdil kavmez zalimÄḟn"
  28,51,"Ve le kad vessalna lehumul kavle leallehum yetezekkerun"
  28,52,"EllezÄḟne ateynahumul kitabe min kablihÄḟ hm bihÄḟ yuÂṀminun"
  28,53,"Ve iza yutla aleyhim kalu amenna bihÄḟ innehul hakku mir rabbina inna kunna min kablihÄḟ muslimÄḟn"
  28,54,"Ulaike yuÂṀtevne ecrahum merrateyni bima saberu ve yedraune bil hasenetis seyyiete ve mimma razaknahum yunfikun"
  28,55,"Ve iza semiullagve aÂṀadu anhu ve kalu lena aÂṀmaluna ve lekum aÂṀmalukum selamun aleykum la nebtegÄḟl cahilÄḟn"
  28,56,"Inneke la tehdÄḟ men ahbebte ve lakinnellahe yehdÄḟ mey yesaÂṀ ve huve aÂṀlemu bil muhtedÄḟn"
  28,57,"Ve kalu in netteblÄḟl huda meake nutehattaf min erdÄḟna e ve lem numekkil lehum haramen aminey yucba ileyhi semeratu kulli seyÂṀir rizkam mil ledunna ve lakinne ekserahum la ya7lemun"
  28,58,"Ve kem ehlekna min karyetim betÄḟrat meÄḟyseteha fe tilke mesakinuhum lem tuskem mim baÂṀdihim illa kalÄḟla kunna nahnul varisÄḟn"
  28,59,"Ve ma kane rabbuke muhlikel kura hatta yebÂṀase fÄḟ ummiha rasuley yetlu aleyhim ayatina ve ma kunna muhlikil kura illa ve ehluha zalimun"
  28,60,"Ve ma utÄḟtum min seyÂṀin fe metaul hayatid dunya ve zÄḟnetuha ve ma Äḟndellahi hayruv ve ebka e fe la taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  28,61,"E fe mev veadnahu vaÂṀden hasenen fe huve lakÄḟyhi ke mem mettaÂṀnahu metaal hayatid dunya summe huve yevmel kÄḟyameti minel muhdarÄḟn"
  28,62,"Ve yevme yunadÄḟhim fe yekulu eyne surakaiyellezÄḟne kuntum tezÂṀumun"
  28,63,"KalellezÄḟne hakka aleyhimul kavlu rabbena haulaillezÄḟne agveyna agveynahum kema gaveyna teberraÂṀna ileyke ma kanu iyyana yaÂṀbudun"
  28,64,"Ve kÄḟyledÂṀu surakaekum fe deavhum fe lem yestecÄḟbu lehum ve raevul azab lev ennehum kanu yehtedun"
  28,65,"Ve yevme yunadÄḟhim fe yekulu maza ecebtumul murselÄḟn"
  28,66,"Fe amiyet aleyhimul embau yevmeizin fe hum la yetesaelun"
  28,67,"Fe memma men tabe ve amene ve amile salihan fe asa ey yekune minel muflihÄḟyn"
  28,68,"Ve rabbuke yahluku ma yesau ve yahtar ma kane lehumul hÄḟyerah subhanellahi ve teala amma yusrikun"
  28,69,"Ve rabbuke yaÂṀlemu ma tukinnu suduruhum ve ma yuÂṀlinun"
  28,70,"Ve huvellahu la ilahe illa hu lehul hamdu fil ula vel ahÄḟrati ve lehul hukmu ve ileyhi turceun"
  28,71,"Kul eraeytum in cealellahu aleykumul leyle sermeden ila yevmil kÄḟyameti men ilahun gayrullahi yeÂṀtikum bi dÄḟyaÂṀ e fe la tesmeun"
  28,72,"Kul eraeytum incealellahu aleykumun nehara sermeden ila yevmil kÄḟyameti men ilahun gayrullahi yeÂṀtÄḟkum bi leylin teskunune fÄḟh e fe la tubsÄḟrun"
  28,73,"Ve mir rahmetihÄḟ ceale lekumul leyle ven nehara li teskunu fÄḟhi ve li tebtegu min fadlihÄḟ ve leallekum teskurun"
  28,74,"Ve yevme yunadÄḟhim fe yekulu eyne surakaiyellezÄḟne kuntum tezÂṀumun"
  28,75,"Ve nezaÂṀna minkulli ummetin sehÄḟden fe kulna hatu burhanekum fe alimu ennel hakka lillahi ve dalle anhum ma kanu yefterun"
  28,76,"Inne karune kane min kavmi masu fe bega aleyhim ve ateynahu minel kunuzi ma inne mefatihahu le tenuu bil usbeti ulil kuvveti iz kale lehu kavmuhu la tefrah innellahe la yuhÄḟbbul ferihÄḟyn"
  28,77,"VebtegÄḟ fÄḟma atakellahud daral ahÄḟrate ve la tense nesÄḟybeke mined dunya ve ahsin kema ahsenellahu ileyke ve la tebgÄḟl fesade fil ard innellahe la yuhÄḟbbul mufsidÄḟn"
  28,78,"Kale innema utÄḟtuhu ala Äḟlmin ÄḟndÄḟ e ve lem ya7lem ennellahe kad ehleke min kablihÄḟ minel kuruni men huve eseddu minhu kuvvetev ve ekseru cemÂṀa ve la yusÂṀelu an zunubihimul mucrimun"
  28,79,"Fe harace ala kamihÄḟ fÄḟ zÄḟnetih kalellezÄḟne yurÄḟdunel hayeted dunya ya leyte lena misle ma utiye karunu innehu lezu hazzÄḟn azÄḟym"
  28,80,"Ve kalellezÄḟne utul Äḟlme veylekum sevabullahi hayrul li men amene ve amile saliha ve la yulekkaha illes sabirun"
  28,81,"Fe hasefna bihÄḟ ve bidarihil erda fe ma kane lehu min fietiy yensurunehu min dunillahi ve ma kane minel muntesÄḟrÄḟn"
  28,82,"Ve asbehallezÄḟne temennev mekanehu bil emsi yekulune veyke ennellahe yebsutur rizka li mey yesau min ÄḟbadihÄḟ ve yakdir lev la em mennellahu aleyna le hasefe bina veykeennehu la yuflihul kafirun"
  28,83,"Tilked darul ahÄḟratu necÂṀaluha lillezÄḟne la yurÄḟdune uluvven fil erdÄḟ ve la fesada vel akÄḟbetu lil muttekÄḟyn"
  28,84,"Men cae bil haseneti fe lehu hayrum minha ve men cae bis seyyieti fe la yuczellezÄḟne amilus seyyiati illa ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  28,85,"InnellezÄḟ ferad aleykel kurÂṀane le radduke illa mead kur rabbÄḟ aÂṀlemu men cae bil huda ve men huve fÄḟ dalalum mubÄḟn"
  28,86,"Ve ma kunte tercu ey yulka ileykel kitabu illa rahmetem mir rabbike fe la tekunenne zahÄḟral lil kafirÄḟn"
  28,87,"Ve la yesuddunneke an ayatillahi baÂṀde iz unzilet ileyke vedÂṀu ila rabbike ve la tekunenne minel musrikÄḟn"
  28,88,"Ve la tedÂṀu meallahi ilahen ahar la ilahe illa huve kullu seyÂṀin halikun illa vecheh lehul hukmu ve ileyhi turceun"
  29,8,"Ve vassaynel insane bi valideyhi husna ve in cahedake li tusrike bÄḟ ma leyse leke bihÄḟ Äḟlmun fe la tutÄḟÂṀhuma ileyye merciukum fe unebbiukum bima kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  29,9,"VellezÄḟne amenu ve ameilus salihati le nudhÄḟlennehum fis salihÄḟyn"
  29,10,"Ve minen nasi mey yekulu amenna billahi fe iza uziye fillahi ceale fitneten nasi keazzabillah ve lein cae nasrum mir rabbike le yekulunne inna kunna meakum e ve leysellahu bi aÂṀleme bima fÄḟ suduril alemÄḟn"
  29,11,"Ve le yaÂṀlemennellahullezÄḟne amenu ve le yaÂṀlemennel munafikÄḟyn"
  29,12,"Ve kalellezÄḟne keferu lillezÄḟne amenut tebiu sebÄḟlena vel nahmil hatayakum ve ma hum bi hamilÄḟne min hatayahum min seyÂṀ innehum lekazibun"
  29,13,"Ve le yahmilunne eskalehum eskalem mea eskalihim ve leyusÂṀelunne yevmel kÄḟyameti amma kanu yefterun"
  29,14,"Ve le kad erselna nuhan ila kavmihÄḟ fe lebise fÄḟhim elfe senetin illa hamsÄḟne ama fe ehazehumut tufanu ve hum salimun"
  29,15,"Fe enceynahu ve ashabes sefÄḟneti ve cealnaha ayetel lil alemÄḟn"
  29,16,"Ve ibrahÄḟme iz kale li kavmihÄḟÂṀbudullahe vettekuh zalikum hayrul lekum in kuntum taÂṀlemun"
  29,17,"Innema taÂṀbudune min dunillahi evsanev ve tahlukune ifka innellezÄḟne taÂṀbudune min dunillahi la yemlikune lekum rizkan febtegu Äḟndellahir rizka vaÂṀbuduhu veskuru leh ileyhi turceun"
  29,18,"Ve in tukezzibu fe kad kezzebe umemum min kablikum ve ma aler rasuli illel belagul mubÄḟn"
  29,19,"E ve lem yerav keyfe yubdiullahul halka summe yuÄḟyduh inne zalike alellahi yesÄḟr"
  29,20,"Kul sÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fenzuru keyfe bedeel halka summellahu yunsiun nesÂṀetel ahÄḟrahinnellahe ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  29,21,"Yuazzibu mey yesau ve yerhamu mey yesaÂṀ ve ileyhi tuklebun"
  29,22,"Ve ma entum bi muÂṀcizÄḟne fil erdÄḟ ve la fis semai ve ma lekum min dunillahi miv veliyyiv ve la nasÄḟyr"
  29,23,"VellezÄḟne keferu bi ayatillahi ve likaihi ulaike yeisu mir rahmetÄḟ ve ulaike lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  29,24,"Fema kane cevabe kavmihÄḟ illa en kaluktuluhu ev harrikuhu fe necahullahu minen nar inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  29,25,"Ve kale innemet tehaztum min dunillahi evsanem meveddete beynikum fil hayatid dunya summe yevmel kÄḟyameti yekfuru baÂṀdukum bi baÂṀdÄḟv ve yelÂṀanu baÂṀdukum baÂṀdav ve meÂṀvakumun naru ve ma lekum min nasÄḟrÄḟn"
  29,26,"Fe amene lehu lut ve kale innÄḟ muhacirun ila rabbÄḟ innehu huvel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  29,27,"Ve vehebna lehu ishaka ve yaÂṀkube ve cealna fÄḟ zurriyyetihin nubuvvete vel kitabe ve ateynahu ecrahu fid dunya ve innehu fil ahÄḟrati le mines salihÄḟyn"
  29,28,"Ve lutan iz kale li kavmihÄḟ innekum le teÂṀtunel fahÄḟsete ma sebekakum biha min ehadim minel alemÄḟn"
  29,29,"E innekum le taÂṀtuner ricale ve taktaunes sebÄḟle ve teÂṀtune fÄḟ nadÄḟkumul munker fema kane cevabe kavmihÄḟ illa en kaluÂṀtina bi azabillahi in kunte mines sadikÄḟyn"
  29,30,"Kale rabbinsurnÄḟ alel kavmil mufsidÄḟn"
  29,31,"Ve lemma caet rusuluna ibrahÄḟme bil busra kalu inna muhliku elhi hazihil karyeh inne ehleha kanu zalimÄḟn"
  29,32,"Kale inne fÄḟha luta kalu nahnu aÂṀlemu bi men fÄḟha le nunecciyennehu ve ehlehu illemraetehu kanet minel gabirÄḟn"
  29,33,"Ve lemma en caet rusuluna lutan sÄḟe bihim ve daka bihim zerÂṀav ve kalu la tehaf ve la tahzen inna muneccuke ve ehleke illemraeteke kanet minel gabirÄḟn"
  29,34,"Inna munzilune ala ehli hazihil karyeti riczem mines semai bima kanu yefsukun"
  29,35,"Ve le kad terakna minha ayetem beyyinetel li kavmiy yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  29,36,"Ve ila medyene ehahum suayben fe kale ya kavmÄḟÂṀbudullahe vercul yevmel ahÄḟra ve la taÂṀsev fil erdÄḟ mufsidÄḟn"
  29,37,"Fe kezzebuhu fe ehazethumur racfetu fe asbehu fÄḟ darihim casimÄḟn"
  29,38,"Ve adev ve semude ve kad tebeyyene lekum mim mesakinihim ve zeyyene lehumus seytanu aÂṀmalehum fe saddehum anis sebÄḟli ve kanu mustebsÄḟrÄḟn"
  29,39,"Ve karune firÂṀavne ve hamane ve le kad caehum musa bil beyyinati festekberu fil erdÄḟ ve ma kanu sabikÄḟyn"
  29,40,"Fe kullen ehazna bi zembih fe minhum men erselna aleyhi hasÄḟba ve minhum men ehazethus sayhah ve minhum men hasefna bihil ard ve minhum men agrakna ve ma kanellahu li yazlimehum ve lhakin kanu enfusehum yazlimun"
  29,41,"MeselullezÄḟnet tehazu min dunillahi evliyae ke meselil ankebut ittehazet beyta ve inne evhenel buyuti le beytul ankebut lev kanu yaÂṀlemun"
  29,42,"Innallahe yaÂṀlemu ma yedÂṀune min dunihÄḟ min seyÂṀ ve huvel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  29,43,"Ve tilkel emsalu nadribuha lin nas ve ma yaÂṀkÄḟluha illel alimun"
  29,44,"Halekallahus semavati vel erda bil hakk inne fÄḟ zalike le ayetel lil muÂṀminÄḟn"
  29,45,"Utlu ma uhÄḟye ileyke minel kitabi ve ekÄḟmÄḟs salah innes salate tenha anil fahsai vel munker ve lezikrullahi ekber vallahu yaÂṀlemu ma tasneun"
  29,46,"Ve la tucadilu ehlel kitabi illa billetÄḟ hiye ahsenu illellezÄḟne zalemu minhum ve kulu amenna billezÄḟ unzile ileyna ve unzile ileykum ve ilahuna ve ilahukum vahÄḟduv ve nahnu lehu muslimun"
  29,47,"Ve kezalike enzelna ileykel kitab fellezÄḟne ateynahumul kitabe yuÂṀminune bih ve min haulai mey yuÂṀminu bih ve ma yechadu bi ayatina illel kafirun"
  29,48,"Ve ma kunte tetlu min kablihÄḟ min kitabiv ve la tehuttuhu bi yemÄḟnike izel lertabel mubtÄḟlun"
  29,49,"Bel huve ayatum beyyinatun fÄḟ sudurillezine utul Äḟlm ve ma yechadu bi ayatina illaz zalimun"
  29,50,"Ve kalu lev la unzile aleyhi ayatum mir rabbih kul innemel ayatu Äḟndellah ve innema ene nezÄḟrum mubÄḟn"
  29,51,"E ve lem yekfihim enna enzelna aleykel kitabe yutla aleyhim inne fÄḟ zalike le rahmetev ve zikra li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  29,52,"Kul kefa billahi beynÄḟ ve beynekum sehÄḟda yaÂṀlemu ma fis semavati vel ard vellezÄḟne amenu bil batÄḟli ve keferu billahi ulaike humul hasirun"
  29,53,"Ve yestaÂṀciluneke bil azab ve lev la ecelum musemmel la caehumul azab ve le yeÂṀtiyennehum bagtetev ve hum la yesÂṀurun"
  29,54,"YestaÂṀciluneke bil azab ve inne cehenneme le muhÄḟytatum bil kafirun"
  29,55,"Yevme yagsahumul azabu min fevkÄḟhim ve min tahti erculihim ve yekulu zuku ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  29,56,"Ya ÄḟbadiyellezÄḟne amenu inne erdÄḟy vasiatun fe iyyaye faÂṀbudun"
  29,57,"Kullu nefsin saikatul mevti summe ileyna turceun"
  29,58,"VellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati le nubevviennehum minel cenneti gurafen tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enharu halidÄḟne fÄḟha nÄḟÂṀme ecrul amilÄḟn"
  29,59,"EllezÄḟne saberu ve ala rabbihim yetevekkelun"
  29,60,"Ve keeyyim min dabbetil la tahmilu rizkahellahu yerzukuha ve iyyakum ve huves semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  29,61,"Ve lein seeltehum men halekas semavati vel erda ve sehharas semse vel kamera le yekulunnellah fe enna yuÂṀfekun"
  29,62,"Allahu yebsutur riska li mey yesau min ÄḟbadihÄḟ ve yakdiru lehv innellahe bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  29,63,"Ve lein seeltehum men nezzele mines semai maen fe ahya bihil erda mim baÂṀdi mevtiha le yekulunnellah kulil hamdu lillah bel ekseruhum la yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  29,64,"Ve ma hazihil hayatud dunya illa lehvuv ve leÄḟb ve inned darel ahÄḟrate le hiyel hayevan lev kanu yaÂṀlemun"
  29,65,"Fe iza rakibu fil fulki deavullahe muhlisÄḟyne lehud dÄḟn felemma neccahum ilel berri izahum yusrikun"
  29,66,"Li yekfuru bima ateynahum ve li yetemetteu fe sevfe yaÂṀlemun"
  29,67,"E ve lem yerav enna cealnu haramen aminev ve yutehattafun nasu min havlihim e fe bil batÄḟli yuÂṀminune ve bi nÄḟÂṀmetillahi yekfurun"
  29,68,"Ve men azlenu minmeniftera alellahi keziben ev kezzebe bil hakkÄḟ lemma caeh e leyse fÄḟ cehenneme mesvel lil kafirÄḟn"
  29,69,"VellezÄḟne cahedu fÄḟna le nehdiyennehum subulena ve innellahe le meal muhsinÄḟn"
  30,8,"E ve lem yetefekkeru fÄḟ enfusihim ma halekallahus semavati vel erda ve ma beynehuma illa bil hakkÄḟ ve ecelim musemma ve inne kesÄḟram minen nasi bi likai rabbihim le kafirun"
  30,9,"E ve lem yesÄḟru fil irdÄḟ fe yenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetullezÄḟne min kablihim kanu esedde minhum kuvvetev ve esarul erda ve ameruha eksera mimma ameruha ve caethum rusuluhum bil beyyinat kanu esedde minhum kuvvetev ve esarul erda ve ameruha eksera mimma ameruha ve caethum rusuluhum bil beyyinat fema kanellahu li yazlimehum ve lakin kanu enfusehum yazlimun"
  30,10,"Summe kane akÄḟbetellezÄḟne esaus sua en kezzebu bi ayatillahi ve kanu biha yestehziun"
  30,11,"Allahu yebdeul hakka summe yuÄḟyduhu summe ileyhi turceun"
  30,12,"Ve yevme tekumus saatu yublisul mucrimun"
  30,13,"Ve lem yekul lehum min surakaihim sufeau ve kanu bi surakaihim kafirÄḟn"
  30,14,"Ve yevme tekumus saatu yevmeiziy yeteferrakun"
  30,15,"Fe emmellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati fe hum fÄḟ ravdatiy yuhberun"
  30,16,"Ve emmellezÄḟne keferu ve kezzebu bi ayatina ve likail ahÄḟrati fe ulaike fil azabi muhdarun"
  30,17,"Fe subhanellahi hÄḟyne tubsune ve hÄḟyne tusbihun"
  30,18,"Ve lehul hamdu fis semavati vel erdÄḟ ve asiyyev ve hÄḟyne tuzhirun"
  30,19,"Yuhricul hayye minel meyyiti ve yuhricul meyyite minel hayyi ve yuhyil erda baÂṀde mevtiha ve kezalike tuhracun"
  30,20,"Ve min ayatihÄḟ en halekakum min turabin summe iza entum beserun tentesirun"
  30,21,"Ve min ayatihÄḟ en haleka lekum min enfusikum ezvacel li teskunu ileyha ve ceale beynekum meveddetev ve rahmeh inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yetefekkerun"
  30,22,"Ve min ayatihÄḟ halkus semavati vel erdÄḟ vahtilafu elsinetikum ve elvanikum inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil lil alimÄḟn"
  30,23,"Ve min ayatihÄḟ menamukum bil leyli ven nehari vebtigaukum min fadlih inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yesmeun"
  30,24,"Ve min ayatihÄḟ yurÄḟkumul berka havfev ve tameav ve yunezzilu mines semai maen fe yuhyÄḟ bihil erda baÂṀde mevtiha inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  30,25,"Ve min ayatihÄḟ en tekumes semau vel erdu bi emrih summe iza deakum daÂṀvetem minel erdÄḟ iza entum tahrucun"
  30,26,"Ve lehu men fis semavati vel ard kullul lehu kanitun"
  30,27,"Ve huvellezÄḟ yebdeul halka summe yuÄḟyduhu ve huve ehvenu aleyh ve lehul meselul aÂṀla fis semavati vel ard ve huvel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  30,28,"Darabe lekum meselem min enfusikum hel lekum mim ma meleket eymanukum min surakae fÄḟ ma razaknakum fe entum fÄḟhi sevaun tehafunehum ke hÄḟyfetikum enfusekum kezalike nufassÄḟlul ayati li kavmiy yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  30,29,"Belit tebeallezÄḟne zalemu ehvaehum bi gayri Äḟlm fe mey yehdÄḟ men edallellah ve ma lehum min nasÄḟrÄḟn"
  30,30,"Fe ekÄḟm vecheke lid dÄḟni hanÄḟfa fÄḟtratellahilletÄḟ fetaran nase aleyha la tebdÄḟle li halkÄḟllah zaliked dÄḟnul kayyimu ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yaÂṀlemun"
  30,31,"MunÄḟbÄḟne ileyhi vettekuhu ve ekÄḟymus salate ve la tekunu minel musrikÄḟn"
  30,32,"MinellezÄḟne ferraku dÄḟnehum ve kanu siyea kullu hÄḟzbim bima ledeyhim ferihun"
  30,33,"Ve iza messen nase durrun deav rabbehum munÄḟbÄḟne ileyhi summe iza ezakahum minhu rahmeten iza ferÄḟkum minhum bi rabbihim yusrikun"
  30,34,"Li yekfuru bima ateynahum fe temetteu fe sevfe taÂṀlemun"
  30,35,"Em enzelna aleyhim sultanen fe huve yetekellemu bima kanu bihÄḟ yusrikun"
  30,36,"Ve iza ezaknen nase rahmeten ferihu biha ve in tusÄḟbhum seyyietum bima kaddemet eydÄḟhim izahum yaknetun"
  30,37,"E ve lem yerav ennellahe yebsutur rizka li mey yesau ve yakdir inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  30,38,"Fe ati zel kurba hakkahu vel miskÄḟne vebnes sebÄḟl zalike hayrul lillezÄḟne yurÄḟdune vechellahi ve ulaike humul muflihun"
  30,39,"Ve ma ateytum mir ribel li yerbuve fÄḟ emvalin nasi fe la yerbu Äḟndellah ve ma ateytum min zekatin turÄḟdune vechellahi fe ulaike humul mudÂṀÄḟfun"
  30,40,"AllahullezÄḟ halekakum summe razekakum summe yumÄḟtukum summe yuhyÄḟkum hel min surakaikum mey yefalu min zalikum min seyÂṀ subhanelhu ve teala amma yusrikun"
  30,41,"Zaheral fesadu fil berri vel bahri bima kesebet eydin nasi li yuzikahum baÂṀdallezÄḟ amilu leallehum yarciun"
  30,42,"Kul sÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetullezÄḟne min kabl kane ekseruhum musrikÄḟn"
  30,43,"Fe ekÄḟm vecheke lid dÄḟnil kayyimi min kabli ey yeÂṀtiye yevmul la meradde lehu minellahi yevmeiziy yessaddeun"
  30,44,"Men kefera fealeyhi kufruh ve men amile salihan fe li enfusihim yemhedun"
  30,45,"Li yecziyellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati min fadlih innehu la yuhÄḟbbul kafirÄḟn"
  30,46,"Ve min ayatihÄḟ ey yursiler riyaha mubessirativ ve liyuzÄḟkakum mir rahmetihÄḟ ve litecriyel fulku bi emrihÄḟ ve li tebtegu min fadlihÄḟ ve leallekum teskurun"
  30,47,"Ve le kad erselna min kablike rusulen ila kavmihim fe cauhum bil beyyinati fentekamna minellezÄḟne ecramu ve kane hakkan aleyna nasrul muÂṀminÄḟn"
  30,48,"AllahullezÄḟ yursilur riyaha fe tusÄḟru sehaben fe yebsutuhu fis semai keyfe yesau ve yecÂṀaluhu kisefen feteral vedka yahrucu min hÄḟlalih fe iza esabe bihÄḟ mey yesau min ÄḟbadihÄḟ izahum yestebsirun"
  30,49,"Ve in kanu min kabli ey yunezzele aleyhim min kablihÄḟ le mublisÄḟn"
  30,50,"Fenzur ila asari rahmetillahi keyfe yuhyil erda baÂṀda mevtiha inne zalike le muhyil mevta ve huve ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  30,51,"Ve lein erselna rÄḟhan fe raevhu musferral lezallu mim baÂṀdihÄḟ yekfurun"
  30,52,"Fe inneke la tusmiul mevta ve la tusmius summed duae iza vellev mudbirÄḟn"
  30,53,"Ve ma ente bihadil umyi an dalaletihim in tusmiu illa mey yuÂṀminu bi ayatina fehum muslimun"
  30,54,"AllahullezÄḟ halekakum min daÂṀfin summe ceale mim baÂṀdi kuvvetin daÂṀfev ve seybeh yahluku ma yesaÂṀ ve huvel alÄḟmul kadÄḟr"
  30,55,"Ve yevme teumus saatu yuksimul mucrimune ma lebisu gayra saah kezalike kanu yuÂṀfekun"
  30,56,"Ve kalellezÄḟne utul Äḟlme vel Äḟmane le kad lebistum fÄḟ kitabillahi ila yevmil baÂṀsi fe haza yevmul baÂṀsi ve lakinnekum kuntum la taÂṀlemun"
  30,57,"Fe yevmeizil la yenfeullezÄḟne zalemu maÂṀziratuhum ve la hum yustaÂṀtebun"
  30,58,"Ve le kad darabna lin nasi fÄḟ hazel karÂṀani min kulli mesel ve lein ciÂṀtehum bi ayatil leyekulennellezÄḟne keferu in entum illa mubtÄḟlun"
  30,59,"Kezalike yatbeullahu ala kulubillezÄḟne la yaÂṀlemun"
  30,60,"Fasbir inne vaÂṀdellahi hakkuv ve la yestehÄḟffennekellezÄḟne la yukÄḟnun"
  31,6,"Ve minen nasi mey yesterÄḟ lehvel hadÄḟsi li yudÄḟlle an sebÄḟlillahi bi gayri Äḟlmiv ve yettehÄḟzeha huzuva ulaike lehum azabum muhÄḟn"
  31,7,"Ve iza tutla aleyhi ayatuna vella mustekbiran ke el lem yesmaÂṀha keenne fÄḟ uzuneyhi vakra fe bessirhu bi azabin elÄḟm"
  31,8,"InnellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati lehum cennatun neÄḟym"
  31,9,"HalidÄḟne fÄḟha vaÂṀdellahi hakka ve huvel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  31,10,"Halekas semavati bi gayri amedin teravneha ve elka fil erdÄḟ ravasiye en temÄḟde bikum ve besse fÄḟha min kulli dabbeh ve enzelna mines semai maen fe embetna fÄḟha min kulli zevcin kerÄḟm"
  31,11,"Haza halkullahi fe erunÄḟ maza halekallezÄḟne min dunih beliz zalimune fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  31,12,"Ve le kad ateyna lukmanel hÄḟkmete eniskur lillah ve mey yeskur fe innema yeskuru li nefsih ve men kefera fe innellahe gayniyyun hamÄḟd"
  31,13,"Ve iz kale lukmanu libnihÄḟ ve huve yeÄḟzuhu ya buneyye la tusrik billah innes sirke le zulmun azÄḟym"
  31,14,"Ve vessaynel insane bi valideyh hamelethu ummuhu vehnen ala vehniv ve fisaluhu fÄḟ ameyni eniskur lÄḟ ve li valideyk ileyyel mesÄḟyr"
  31,15,"Ve in cahedake ala en tusrike bÄḟ ma leyse leke bihÄḟ ilmun fe la tutÄḟÂṀhuma ve sahÄḟbhuma fid dunya maÂṀrufev vettebÄḟÂṀ sebÄḟle men enabe ileyy summe ileyye merciukum fe unebbiukum bima kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  31,16,"Ya buneyye inneha in teku miskale habbetim min hardelin fe tekun fÄḟ sahratin ev fis semavati ev fil erdÄḟ yeÂṀti bihellah innellahe latÄḟyfun habÄḟr"
  31,17,"Ya buneyye ekÄḟmÄḟs salate veÂṀmur bil maÂṀrufi venhe anil munkeri vasbir ala ma esabek inne zalike min azmil umur"
  31,18,"Ve la tusaÂṀÄḟr haddeke lin nasi ve la temsi fil erdÄḟ meraha innellahe la yuhÄḟbbu kulle muhtalin fehur"
  31,19,"VaksÄḟd fÄḟ mesyike vagdud min savtik inne emreral asvati le savtul hamÄḟr"
  31,20,"E lem terav ennellahe sehhara lekum ma fis semavati ve ma fil erdÄḟ ve esbega aleykum niamehu zahiratev ve batÄḟneh ve minen nasi mey yucadilu fillahi bi gayri Äḟlmiv ve la hudev ve la kitabim munÄḟr"
  31,21,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehumut tebiu ma enzellellahu kalu bel nettebiu ma vecedna aleyhi abaena e ve lev kanes seytanu yedÂṀuhum ila azabis seÄḟyr"
  31,22,"Ve mey yuslim vechehu ilellahi ve huve muhsinun fe kadistemseke bil urvetil vuska ve ilellahi akÄḟbetul umur"
  31,23,"Ve men kefera fe la yahzunke kufruh ileyna merciuhum fe nunebbiuhum bima amilu innellahe alÄḟmum bizatis sudur"
  31,24,"Numettiuhum kalÄḟlen summe nadtarruhum ila azabin galÄḟyz"
  31,25,"Ve lein seeltehum men halekas semavati vel erda le yekulunnellah kulil hamdu lillah bel ekseruhum la yaÂṀlemun"
  31,26,"Lillahi ma fis semavati vel ard innellahe huvel ganiyyul hamÄḟd"
  31,27,"Ve lev enne ma fil erdÄḟ min seceratin aklamuv vel bahru yemudduhu min baÂṀdihÄḟ sebÂṀatu ebhurim ma nefidet kelematullah innellahe azÄḟzun hakÄḟm"
  31,28,"Ma halkukum ve la baÂṀsukum illa ke nefsiv vahÄḟdeh innellahe semÄḟum basÄḟyr"
  31,29,"E lem tera ennellahe yulicul leyle fin nehari ve yulicun nehara fil leyli ve sehhares semsi vel kamera kulluy yecrÄḟ ila ecelim mussemmev ve ennellahe ve ma taÂṀmelune habÄḟr"
  31,30,"Zalike bi ennellahe huvel hakku ve enne ma yedÂṀ une min dunihil batÄḟlu ve ennellahe huvel aliyyul kebÄḟr"
  31,31,"E lem tera ennel fulke tecrÄḟ fil bahri bi nÄḟÂṀmetillahi li yuriyekum min ayatih inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kulli sabbarin sekur"
  31,32,"Ve iza gasiyehum mevcun kez zuleli deavullahe muhlisÄḟyne lehud dÄḟn felemma neccahum ilel berri fe minhum muktesÄḟd ve ma yechadu bi ayatina illa kullu hattarin kefur"
  31,33,"Ya eyyuhen nasutteku rabbekum vahsev yevmel la yezÄḟ validun av veledihÄḟ ve la meludun huve cazin av validihÄḟ seyÂṀa inne vaÂṀdellahi hakkun fe la tegurranekumul hayatud dunya ve la yegurranekum billahul garur"
  31,34,"Innellahe Äḟndehu Äḟlmus saahve yunezzilul gays ve yaÂṀlemu ma fil erham ve ma tedrÄḟ nefsum maza teksibu gada ve ma tedrÄḟ nefsum bi eyyi erdÄḟn temut innellahe alimun habÄḟr"
  32,4,"AllahullezÄḟ halekas semavati vel erda ve ma beynehuma fÄḟ sitteti eyyamin summesteva alel ars ma lekum min dunihÄḟ miv veliyyiv ve la sefiyÂṀ efela tetezekkerun"
  32,5,"Yudebbirul emra mines semai ilel erdÄḟ summe yaÂṀrucu ileyhi fÄḟ yevmin kane mÄḟkdaruhu elfe senetim mimma teuddun"
  32,6,"Zalike alimul gaybi ves sehadetil aziyzur rahÄḟym"
  32,7,"EllezÄḟ ahsene kulle seyÂṀin halekahu ve bedee halkal insani min tÄḟyn"
  32,8,"Summe ceal neslehu min sulaletim min maim mehiyn"
  32,9,"Summe sevvahu ve nefeha fiyhi mir ruhÄḟhÄḟ ve ceale lekumus semÂṀa vel ebsara vel efideh kaliylem ma teskurun"
  32,10,"Ve kalu e iza dalelna fil erdÄḟ e inna le fÄḟ halkÄḟn cediyd bel hum bi likai rabbihim kafirun"
  32,11,"Kul yeteveffakum melekul mevtillezÄḟ vukkile bikum summe ila rabbikum turceun"
  32,12,"Ve lev tera izil mucrimune nakisu ruusihim Äḟnde rabbihim rabbena ebsarna ve semÄḟÂṀna fercÄḟÂṀna naÂṀmel salihan inna mukÄḟnun"
  32,13,"Ve lev siÂṀna le ateyna kulle nefsin hudaha ve lakin hakkal kavlu minnÄḟ le emleenne cehenneme minel cinneti ven nasi ecmeÄḟyn"
  32,14,"Fe zuku bi ma nesiytum likae yevmikum haza inna nesiynakum ve zuku azabel huldi bi ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  32,15,"Innema yuÂṀminu bi ayatinellezine iza zukkiru biha harru succedev ve sebbehu bi hamdi rabbihim ve hum la yestekbirun"
  32,16,"Tetecafa cunubuhum anil medaciÄḟ yedÂṀune rabbehum havfev ve tameav ve mimma razaknahum yunfikun"
  32,17,"Fe la taÂṀlemu nefsum ma uhfiye lehum min kurrati aÂṀyun cezaem bi ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  32,18,"E femen kane muÂṀminen ke men kane fasika la yestevun"
  32,19,"Emmelleziyne amenu ve amilus salihati fe lehum cennatul meÂṀva nuzulem bi ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  32,20,"Ve emmellezÄḟne feseku fe meÂṀvahumun nar kullema eradu ey yahrucu minha uÄḟydu fiyha ve kÄḟyle lehum zuku azaben narillezÄḟ kuntum bihÄḟ tukezzibun(15. Ayet secde ayetidir)"
  32,21,"Ve le nuziykanehum minel azabil edna dunel azabil ekberi leallehum yarciun"
  32,22,"Ve men azlemu mimmem zukkira bi ayati rabbihÄḟ summe aÂṀrada anha inna minel mucrimiyne muntekÄḟmun"
  32,23,"Ve le kad ateyna musal kitabe fe la tekun fÄḟ miryetim mil likaihÄḟ ve cealnahu hudel li benÄḟ israiyl"
  32,24,"Ve cealna minhum elmmetey yehdune bi emrina lemma saberu ve kanu bi ayatina yukÄḟnun"
  32,25,"Inne rabbeke huve yafsÄḟlu beynehum yevmel kÄḟyameti fiyma kanu fÄḟhi yahtelifun"
  32,26,"E ve lem yehdi lehum kem ehlekna min kablihim minel kuruni yemsune fÄḟ mesakinihim inne fÄḟ zalike le ayat e fe la yesmeun"
  32,27,"E ve lem yerav enna nesukul mae ilel erdÄḟl curuzi fe nuhricu bihÄḟ zerÂṀan teÂṀkili mihu enÂṀamuhum ve enfusuhum e fe la yubsÄḟrun"
  32,28,"Ve yekulune meta hazal fethu in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  32,29,"Kul yevmel fethÄḟ la yenfeullezÄḟne keferu iymanuhum ve la hum yunzarun"
  32,30,"Fe aÂṀrÄḟd anhum ventezÄḟr innehum muntezÄḟrun"
  33,8,"Li yesÂṀeles sadikÄḟyne an sÄḟdkÄḟhim ve eadde lil kafirÄḟne azaben elÄḟma"
  33,9,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenuzkuru nÄḟÂṀmetellahi aleykum iz caetkum cunudun fe erselna aleyhim rÄḟhav ve cunudel lem teravha ve kanellahu bima taÂṀmelune besÄḟyra"
  33,10,"Iz caukum min fevkÄḟkum ve min esfele minkum ve iz zagatil ebsaru ve belegatil kulubul hanacira ve tezunnune billahiz zununa"
  33,11,"Hunalikebtuliyel muÂṀminune ve zulzilu zilzatlen sedÄḟda"
  33,12,"Ve iz yekulul munafikune vellezÄḟne fÄḟ kulubihim meradum ma veaddenellahu ve rasuluhu illa gurura"
  33,13,"Ve iz kalet taifetum minhum ya ehle yesribe la mukame lekum farciu ve yesteÂṀzinu ferÄḟkum minhumun nebiyye yekulune inne buyutena avratuv ve ma hiye bi avrah iy yurÄḟdune illa firara"
  33,14,"Ve lev duhÄḟlet aleyhim min aktariha summe suilul fitnete le atevha ve ma telebbesu biha illa yesÄḟra"
  33,15,"Ve le kad kanu ahedullahe min kablu la yuvellunel edbar ve kane ahdullahi mesÂṀula"
  33,16,"Kul ley yenfeakumul firaru in ferartum minel mevti evil katli ve izel la tumetteune illa kalÄḟla"
  33,17,"Kul men zellezÄḟ yaÂṀsÄḟmukum minellahi in erade bikum suen ev erade bikum rahmeh ve la yecidune lehum min dunillahi veliyyev ve la nesÄḟyra"
  33,18,"Kad yaÂṀlemullahul muavvikÄḟyne minkum ve kailÄḟne li Äḟhvanihim helumme ileyna ve la yeÂṀtunel beÂṀse illa kalila"
  33,19,"E sÄḟhhaten aleykum Fe iza cael havfu raeytehum yenzurune ileyke teduru aÂṀyunuhum kellezÄḟ yugsa aleyhi minel mevt fe iza zehebel havfu selekuhum bi elsinetin hÄḟdadin esÄḟhhaten alel hayr ulaike lem yuÂṀminu fe ahbetallahu aÂṀmalehum ve kane zalike alellahi yesÄḟra"
  33,20,"Yahsebunel ahzabe lem yezhebu ve iy yeÂṀtil ahzabu yeveddu lev ennehum badune fil aÂṀrabi yesÂṀelune an embaikum ve lev kanu fÄḟkum ma katelu illa kalÄḟla"
  33,21,"Le kad kane lekum fÄḟ rasulillahi usvetun hasenetul li men kane yercullahe vel yevmel haÄḟra ve zekerallahe kesÄḟra"
  33,22,"Ve lemma rael muÂṀminunel ahzabe kalu haza ma veadenellahu ve rasuluhu ve sadekallahu ve rasuluhu ve ma zadehum illa Äḟmanev ve teslÄḟma"
  33,23,"Minel muÂṀminÄḟne ricalun sadeku ma ahedullahe aleyh fe minhum men kada nahbehu ve minhum mey yentezÄḟru ve ma beddelu tebdÄḟla"
  33,24,"Li yecziyellahus sadikÄḟyne bi sÄḟdkÄḟhim ve yuazzibel munafikÄḟyne in sae ev yetube aleyhim innellahe kane gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  33,25,"Ve raddellahullezÄḟne keferu bi gayzÄḟhim lem yenalu hayra ve kefallahul muÂṀminÄḟnel kÄḟtal ve kanellahu kaviyyen azÄḟza"
  33,26,"Ve enzelellezÄḟne zaheruhum min ehlil kitabi min sayasÄḟyhim ve kazefe fÄḟ kulubihimur ruÂṀbe ferÄḟkan taktulune ve teÂṀsirune ferÄḟka"
  33,27,"Ve evrasekum erdahum ve diyarahum ve emvalehum ve erdal lem tetauha ve kanellahu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟra"
  33,28,"Ya eyyuhen nebiyyu kul li ezvacike in kuntunne turidnel hayated dunya ve zÄḟneteha fe tealeyne umettÄḟÂṀkunne ve userrÄḟhkunne serahan cemÄḟla"
  33,29,"Ve in kuntunne turidnellahe ve rasulehu ved daral ahÄḟrate fe innellahe eadde lil muhsinati minkunne ecran azÄḟyma"
  33,30,"Ya nisaen nebiyyi mey yeÂṀti minkunne bi fahÄḟsetim mubeyyinetiy yudaaf lehel azabu dÂṀfeyn ve kane zalike alellahi yesÄḟra"
  33,31,"Ve mey yaknut minkunne lillahi ve rasulihÄḟ ve taÂṀmel salihan nuÂṀtiha ecraha merrateyni ve aÂṀtedna leha rizkan kerÄḟma"
  33,32,"Ya nisaen nebiyyi lestunne ke ehadim minen nisai inittekaytunne fe la tahdaÂṀne bil kavli fe yatmeallezÄḟ fÄḟ kalbihÄḟ meraduv ve kulne kavlem maÂṀrufa"
  33,33,"Ve karne fÄḟ buyutikunne ve la teberracne teberrucel cahiliyyetil ula ve ekÄḟmmes salete ve atÄḟnez zekate ve etÄḟÂṀnellahe ve rasuleh innema yurÄḟdullahu li yuzhibe ankumur ricse ehlel beyti ve yutahhirakum tathÄḟra"
  33,34,"Vezkurne ma yutla fÄḟ buyutikunne min ayatillahi vel hÄḟkmeh innellahe kane latÄḟyfen habÄḟra"
  33,35,"Innel muslimÄḟne vel muslimati vel muÂṀminÄḟne vel muÂṀminati vel kanitÄḟne vel kanitati ves sadikÄḟyne ves sadikati ves sabirÄḟne ves sabirati vel hasiÄḟyne vel hasiati vel mutesaddikÄḟyne vel mutesaddikati ves saimÄḟne ves saimati vel hafizÄḟyne furucehum vel hafizate vez zakirÄḟnellahe kesÄḟrav vez zakirati eaddelahu lehum magfiratev ve ecran azÄḟyma"
  33,36,"Ve ma kane li muÂṀminiv ve la muÂṀminetin iza kadallahu ve rasuluhu emran ey yekune lehumul hÄḟyeratu min emrihim ve mey yaÂṀsÄḟllahe ve rasulehu fe kad dalle dalalem mubÄḟna"
  33,37,"Ve iz tekulu lillezÄḟ enÂṀamellahu aleyhi ve enÂṀamte aleyhi emsik aleyke zevceke vettekÄḟllahe ve tuhfÄḟ fÄḟ nefsike mellahu mubdÄḟhi ve tahsen nas vallahu ehakku en tahsah felemma kada zeydum minha vetaran zevvecnakeha li key la yekune alel muÂṀminÄḟne haracun fi ezvaci edÂṀÄḟyaihim iza kadav minhunne vetara ve kane emrullahi mefÂṀula"
  33,38,"Ma kane alen nebiyyi min haracin fÄḟma feradallahu leh sunnetellahi fillezÄḟne halev min kabl ve kane emrullahi kaderam makdura"
  33,39,"IllezÄḟne yubelligune risalatillahi ve yahsevnehu ve la yahsevne ehaden ilellah ve kefa billahi hasÄḟba"
  33,40,"Ma kane muhammedun eba ehadim mir ricalikum ve lakir rasulellahi ve hatemen nebiyyÄḟn ve kanellahu bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟma"
  33,41,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenuzkurullahe zikran kesÄḟra"
  33,42,"Ve sebbihuhu bukratev ve esÄḟyla"
  33,43,"HuvellezÄḟ yusallÄḟ aleykum ve melaiketuhu li yuhricekum minez zulumati ilen nur ve kane bil muÂṀminÄḟne rahÄḟyma"
  33,44,"TehÄḟyyetuhum yevme yelkavnehu selam ve eadde lehum ecran kerÄḟma"
  33,45,"Ya eyyuhen nebiyyu inna erselnake sahidev ve mubessirav ve nezÄḟra"
  33,46,"Ve daÄḟyen ilellahi bi iznihÄḟ ve siracem munÄḟra"
  33,47,"Ve bessiril muÂṀminÄḟne bi enne lehum minellahi fadlen kebÄḟra"
  33,48,"Ve la tutÄḟÄḟl kafirÄḟne vel munafikÄḟyne ve daÂṀ ezahum ve tevekkel alellah ve kefa billahi vekÄḟla"
  33,49,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu iza nekahtumul muÂṀminati summe tallaktumuhunne min kabli en temessuhunne femalekum aleyhinne min Äḟddetin taÂṀtedduneha fe mettiuhunne ve serrihuhunne serahan cemÄḟla"
  33,50,"Ya eyyuhen nebiyyu inna ahlelna leke ezvacekellatÄḟ ateyte ucurahunne ve ma meleket yemÄḟnuke memma efaellahu aleyke ve benati ammike ve benati ammatike ve benati halike ve benati halatikellatÄḟ hacerne meake vemraetem muÂṀmineten iv vehebet nefseha lin nebiyyi in eraden nebiyyu ey yestenkihaha halisatel leke min dunil muÂṀminÄḟn kad alimna ma feradna aleyhim fÄḟ ezvacihim ve ma meleket eymanuhum li keyla yekune aleyke harac ve kanellahu gafurrar rahÄḟyma"
  33,51,"TurcÄḟ men tesau minhunne ve tuÂṀvÄḟ ileyke men tesaÂṀ ve menibtegayte mimmen azelte fe la cunaha aleyk zalike edna en tekarra aÂṀyunuhunne ve la yahzenne ve yerdayne bima ateytehunne kulluhunn vallahu yaÂṀlemu ma fÄḟ kulubikum ve kanellahu alÄḟmen halÄḟma"
  33,52,"La yehÄḟllu leken nisau min baÂṀdu ve la en tebeddele bihinne min ezvaciv ve lev aÂṀcebeke husnuhunne illa ma meleket yemÄḟnuk ve kanellahu ala kulli seyÂṀir rakÄḟyba"
  33,53,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tedhulu buyuten nebiyyi illa ey yuÂṀzene lekum ila taamin gayra nazÄḟrÄḟne inahu ve lakin iza duÄḟytum fedhulu fe iza taÄḟmtum fentesiru ve la musteÂṀnisÄḟne li hadÄḟs inne zalikum kane yuÂṀzin nebiyye fe yestahyÄḟ minkum vallahu la yestahyÄḟ minel hakk ve iza seeltumuhunne metaan fesÂṀeluhunne miv verai hÄḟcab zalikum atheru li kulubikum ve kulubihinn ve ma kane lekum en tuÂṀzu rasullellahi ve la en tenkihu ezvacehu mim baÂṀdihÄḟ ebeda inne zalikum kane Äḟndellahi azÄḟyma"
  33,54,"In tubdu seyÂṀen ev tuhfuhu fe innellahe kane bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟma"
  33,55,"La cunaha aleyhinne fÄḟ abaihinne ve la ebnaihinne ve la Äḟhvanihinne ve la ebnai Äḟhvanihinne ve la ebnai ehavatihinne ve la nisaihinne ve la ma meleket eymanuhunn vettekÄḟynellah innellahe kane ala kulli seyÂṀin sehÄḟda"
  33,56,"Innellahe ve melaiketehu yusallune alen nebiyy ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu sallu aleyhi ve sellimu teslÄḟma"
  33,57,"InnellezÄḟne yuÂṀzunellahe ve rasulehu leanehumullahu fid dunya vel ahÄḟrati ve eadde lehum azabem muhÄḟna"
  33,58,"VellezÄḟne yuÂṀzunel muÂṀminÄḟne vel muÂṀminati bi gayri mektesebu fe kadÄḟhtemelu buhtanev ve ismem mubÄḟna"
  33,59,"Ya eyyuhen nebiyyu kul li ezvacike ve benatike ve nisail muÂṀminÄḟne yudnÄḟne aleyhinne min celabÄḟbihinn zalike edna ey yuÂṀrafne fe la yuÂṀzeyn ve kanellahu gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  33,60,"Le il lem yentehil munafikune vellezÄḟne fÄḟ kulubihim meraduv vel murcifune fil medÄḟneti le nugriyenneke bihim summe la yucaviruneke fÄḟha illa kalila"
  33,61,"MelÂṀunÄḟne eyne ma sukÄḟfu uhÄḟzu ve kuttilu taktila"
  33,62,"Sunnetellahi fillezÄḟne halev min kabl ve len tecide li sunnetillahi tebdÄḟla"
  33,63,"YesÂṀeluken nasu anis saah kul innema Äḟlmuha Äḟndellah ve ma yudrÄḟke lealles saat tekunu karÄḟba"
  33,64,"Innellahe leanel kafirÄḟne ve eadde lehum seÄḟyra"
  33,65,"HalidÄḟne fÄḟha ebeda la yecidune veliyyev ve la nesÄḟyra"
  33,66,"Yevme tukallebu vucuhuhum fin nari yekulune ya leytena etaÂṀnellahe ve etaÂṀner rasula"
  33,67,"Ve kalu rabbena inna etaÂṀna sadetena ve kuberaena fe edallunes sebÄḟla"
  33,68,"Rabbena atihim dÄḟÂṀfeyni minel azabi velÂṀanhum laÂṀnen kebÄḟra"
  33,69,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la tekunu kellezÄḟne azev musa fe berraehullahu mimma kalu ve kane Äḟndellahi vecÄḟha"
  33,70,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenuttekullahe ve kulu kavlen sedÄḟda"
  33,71,"YuslÄḟh lekum aÂṀmalekum ve yagfir lekum zunubekum ve mey yutÄḟÄḟllahe ve rasulehu fe kad faze fevzen azÄḟyma"
  33,72,"Inna aradnel emanete ales semavati vel erdÄḟ vel cibali fe ebeyne ey yahmilneha ve esfakne minha ve hamelehel insan innehu kane zalumen cehula"
  33,73,"Li yuazzibellahul munafikÄḟyne vel munafikati vel musrikÄḟne vel musrikati ve yetubellahu alel muÂṀminÄḟne vel muÂṀminat ve kanellahu gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  34,7,"Ve kalellezÄḟne keferu hel nedullukum ala raculiy yunebbiukum iza muzzÄḟktum kulle mumezzekÄḟn innekum lefÄḟ halkÄḟn cedÄḟd"
  34,8,"Eftera alellahi keziben em bihÄḟ cinneh belillezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune bil ahÄḟrati fil azabi ved dalalil beÄḟyd"
  34,9,"E fe lem yerav ila ma beyne eydÄḟhim ve ma halfehum mines semai vel ard in neseÂṀ nahsif bihimul erda ev nuskÄḟt aleyhim kisefem mines semaÂṀ inne fÄḟ zalike le ayetel li kulli abdim munÄḟb"
  34,10,"Ve le kad ateyna davude minna fadla ya cibalu evvibÄḟ meahu vet tayr ve elenna lehul hadÄḟd"
  34,11,"EnÄḟÂṀmel sabigativ ve kaddir fis serdi vaÂṀmelu saliha innÄḟ bima taÂṀmelune besÄḟyr"
  34,12,"Ve li suleymaner rÄḟha guduvvuha sehruv ve ravahuha sehr ve erselna lehu aynel kÄḟtr ve minel cinni mey yaÂṀmelu beyne yedeyhi bi izni rabbih ve mey yezig minhum an emrina nuzÄḟkhu min azabis seÄḟyr"
  34,13,"YaÂṀmelune lehu ma yesau mim meharÄḟbe ve temasÄḟle ve cifanin kel cevabi ve kudurir rasiyat ÄḟÂṀmelu ale davude sukra ve kalÄḟlum min Äḟbadiyes sekur"
  34,14,"Felemma kadayna aleyhil mevte ma dellehum ala mevtihÄḟ illa dabbetul erdÄḟ teÂṀkulu minseeteh Fe lemma harra tebeyyenetil cinnu el lev kanu yaÂṀlemunel gaybe ma lebisu fil azabil muhÄḟn"
  34,15,"Le kad kane li sebein fÄḟ meskenihim ayeh cennetani ay yemÄḟniv ve simal kulu mir rizkÄḟ rabbikum vsekuru leh beldetun tayyibetuv ve rabbun gafur"
  34,16,"Fe aÂṀradu fe erselna aleyhim seylel arimi ve beddelnahum bi cenneteyhim cenneteyni zevatey ukulin hamtÄḟv ve esliv ve seyÂṀim min sidrin kalÄḟl"
  34,17,"Zalike cezeynahum bima keferu ve hel nucazÄḟ illel kefur"
  34,18,"Ve cealna beynehum ve beynel kuralletÄḟ barakna fÄḟha kuran zahiratev ve kadderna fÄḟhes seyr sÄḟru fÄḟha leyaliye ve eyyamen aminÄḟn"
  34,19,"Fe kalu rabbena baÄḟd beyne esfarina ve zalemu enfusehum fe cealnahum ehadÄḟse ve mezzaknahum kulle mumezzak inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kulli sabbarin sekur"
  34,20,"Ve le kad saddeka aleyhim iblÄḟsu zannehu fettebeuhu illa ferÄḟkam minel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  34,21,"Ve ma kane lehu aleyhim min sultanin illa li naÂṀleme mey yuÂṀminu bil ahÄḟrati mimmen huve minha fÄḟ sekk ve rabbuke ala kulli seyÂṀin hafÄḟyz"
  34,22,"KulidÂṀullezÄḟne zeamtum min dunillah la yemlikune miskale zerratin fis semavati ve la fil erdÄḟ ve ma lehum fÄḟhima min sirkiv ve ma lehu minhum min zahÄḟr"
  34,23,"Ve la tenfeus sefaatu Äḟndehu illa li men ezine leh hatta iza fuzzia an kulubihim kalu ma za kale rabbukum kalul hakk ve huvel aliyyul kebÄḟr"
  34,24,"Kul mey yerzukukum mines semavati vel ard kulillahu ve inna ev iyyakum leala huden ev fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  34,25,"Kul la tusÂṀelune amma ecramna ve la nusÂṀelu amma taÂṀmelun"
  34,26,"Kul yecmeu beynena rabbuna summe yeftehu beynena bil hakk ve huvel fettahul alÄḟm"
  34,27,"Kul eruniyellezÄḟne elhaktum bihÄḟ surakae kella bel huvellahul azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  34,28,"Ve ma erselnake illa kaffetel lin nasi besÄḟrav ve nezÄḟrav ve lakÄḟnne ekseran nasi la yaÂṀlemun"
  34,29,"Ve yekulune meta hazel vaÂṀdu in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  34,30,"Kul lekum mÄḟadu yevmel la testeÂṀhÄḟrune anhu saatev ve la testakdimun"
  34,31,"Ve kalellezÄḟne keferu len nuÂṀmine bi hazel kurÂṀani ve la billezÄḟ beyne yedeyh ve lev tera iziz zalimune mevkufune Äḟnde rabbihim yarciu baÂṀduhum ila baÂṀdÄḟnil kavl yekulullezÄḟnestudÂṀÄḟfu lillezÄḟ nestekberu lev la entum lekunna muÂṀminÄḟn"
  34,32,"KalellezÄḟnestekberu lillezÄḟnestudÂṀÄḟfu e nahnu sadednakum anil huda baÂṀde iz caekum bel kuntum mucrimÄḟn"
  34,33,"Ve kalellesÄḟnestudÂṀÄḟfu lillesÄḟnestekberu bel mekrul leyli ven nehari iz teÂṀmurunena en nekfura billahi ve necÂṀale lehu endada ve eserrun nedamete lemma raevul azab ve cealnel aglale fÄḟ aÂṀnakÄḟllezÄḟne keferu hel yuczevne illa ma kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  34,34,"Ve ma erselna fÄḟ karyetim min nezÄḟrin illa kale mutrafuha inna bima ursiltum bihÄḟ kafirun"
  34,35,"Ve kalu nahnu ekseru emvalev ve evladev ve ma nahnu bi muazzebÄḟn"
  34,36,"Kul inne rabbÄḟ yebsutur rizka li mey yesau ve yakdiru ve lakinne ekseran nasi la ya7lemun"
  34,37,"Ve ma emvalukum ve la evladukum billetÄḟ tukarribukum Äḟndena zulfa illa men amene ve amile salihan fe ulaike lehum cezaud dÄḟÂṀfi bima amilu ve hum fil gurufati aminun"
  34,38,"VellezÄḟne yesÂṀavne fÄḟ ayatina muacizÄḟne ulaike fil azabi muhdarun"
  34,39,"Kul innne rabbÄḟ yebtutur rizka li mey yesau min ÄḟbadihÄḟ ve yakdiru leh ve ma enfaktum min seyÂṀin fe huve yuhlifuh ve huve hayrur razikÄḟyn"
  34,40,"Ve yevme yahsuruhum cemÄḟan summe yekulu lil melaiketi e haulai iyyakum kanu yaÂṀbudun"
  34,41,"Kalu subhhaneke ente veliyyuna min dunihim bel kanu yaÂṀbudunel cinn ekseruhum bihim muÂṀminun"
  34,42,"Fel yevme la yemliku baÂṀdukum li baÂṀdÄḟn nefav ve la darra ve nekulu lillezÄḟne zalemu zuku azaben narilletÄḟ kuntum biha tukezzibun"
  34,43,"Ve iza tutla aleyhim ayatuna beyyinatin kalu ma haza illa raculuy yurÄḟdu ey yesuddekum amma kane yaÂṀbudu abaukum ve kalu ma haza illa ifkum muftera ve kalellezÄḟne keferu lil hakkÄḟ lemma caehum in haza illa sÄḟhrum mubÄḟn"
  34,44,"Ve ma ateynahum min kutubiy yedrusuneha ve ma erselna ileyhim kableke min nezÄḟr"
  34,45,"Ve kezzebellezÄḟne min kablihim ve ma belegu mÄḟÂṀsara ma ateynahum fe kezzebu rusuli fe keyfe kane nekÄḟr"
  34,46,"Kul innema eÄḟzukum bi vahÄḟdeh en tekumu lillahi mesna ve furaa summe tetefekkeru ma bi sahÄḟbikum min cinneh in huve illa nezÄḟrul lekum beyne yedey azabin sedÄḟd"
  34,47,"Kul ma seeltukum min ecrin fe huve lekum in ecriye illa alellah ve huve ala kulli seyÂṀin sehÄḟd"
  34,48,"Kul inne rabbÄḟ yakzifu bil hakk allamul guyub"
  34,49,"Kul cael hakku ve ma yubdiul batÄḟlu ve ma yuÄḟyd"
  34,50,"Kul in daleltu fe innema edÄḟllu ala nefsÄḟ ve inihtedeytu fe bima yuhÄḟy ileyye rabbÄḟ innehu semÄḟun karÄḟb"
  34,51,"Ve lev tera iz feziu fe la fevte ve uhÄḟzu mim mekanin karÄḟb"
  34,52,"Ve kalu amenna bih ve enna lehumut tenavusu mim mekanim beÄḟyd"
  34,53,"Ve kad keferu bihÄḟ min kabl ve yakzifune bil gaybi mim mekanim beÄḟyd"
  34,54,"Ve hÄḟyle beynehum ve beyne ma yestehune kema fuÄḟle bi esyaÄḟhim min kabl innehum kanu fÄḟ sekkim murÄḟb"
  35,6,"Innes seytane lekum aduvvun fettehÄḟzuhu aduvva innema yedÂṀu hÄḟzbehu li yekunu min ashabis seÄḟyr"
  35,7,"EllezÄḟne keferu lehum azabun sedÄḟd vellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati lehum magfiratuv ve ecrun kebÄḟr"
  35,8,"E fe men zuyyine lehu suu amelihÄḟ fe raahu hasena fe innellahe yudÄḟllu mey yesau ve yehdÄḟ mey yesau fe la tezheb nefsuke aleyhim haserat innellahe alÄḟmum bima yasneun"
  35,9,"VallahullezÄḟ erseler riyaha fe tusÄḟru sehaben fe suknahu ila beledum meyyitin fe ahyeyna bihil erda baÂṀde mevtiha kezaliken nusur"
  35,10,"Men kane yurÄḟdul Äḟzzete fe lillahil Äḟzzetu cemÄḟa ileyhi yasÂṀadul kelimut tayyibu vel amelus salihu yerfeuh vellezÄḟne yemkurunes seyyiati lehum azabun sedÄḟd ve mekru ulaike huve yebur"
  35,11,"Vallahu halekakum min turabin summe min nutfetin summe cealekum ezvaca ve ma tahmilu min unsa ve la tedau illa bi Äḟlmih ve ma tahmilu min unsa la tedau illa bi Äḟlmih ve ma yuammeru min muammeriv ve la yunkasu min umurihÄḟ illa fÄḟ kitab inne zalike alellahi yesÄḟr"
  35,12,"Ve ma yestevil bahrani haza azbun furatun saigun serabuhu ve haza milhun ucacve min kullin teÂṀkulune lahmen tariyyev ve testahricune hÄḟlyeten telbesuneha ve teral fulke fÄḟhi mevahÄḟra li tebtegu min fadlihÄḟ ve leallekum teskurun"
  35,13,"Yulicul leyle fin nehari ve yulicun nehar fil leyli ve sehhares semse vel kamera kulluy yecrÄḟ li ecelim musemma zalikumullahu rabbukum lehul mulk vellezÄḟne tedÂṀune min dunihÄḟ ma yemlikune min kÄḟtmÄḟr"
  35,14,"In tedÂṀuhum la yesmeu duaekum ve lev semiu mestecabu lekum ve yevmel kÄḟyameti yekfurune bi sirkikum ve la yunebbiuke mislu habÄḟr"
  35,15,"Ya eyyuhen nasu entumul fukarau ilellah vallahu huvel ganiyyul hamÄḟd"
  35,16,"Iy yeseÂṀ yuzhibkum ve yeÂṀti bi halkÄḟn cedÄḟd"
  35,17,"Ve ma zalike alellahi bi azÄḟz"
  35,18,"Ve la teziru vaziratuv vizra uhra ve in tedÂṀu muskaletun ila hÄḟmliha la yuhmel minhu seyÂṀuv ve lev kane za kurba innema tunzirullezÄḟne yahsevne rabbehum bil gaybi ve ekamus salah ve men tezekka fe innema yetezekka li nefsih ve ilellahil mesÄḟyr"
  35,19,"Ve ma yesteil aÂṀma vel besÄḟyr"
  35,20,"Ve lez zulumatu ve len nur"
  35,21,"Ve lez zÄḟllu ve lel harur"
  35,22,"Ve ma yestevil ahyau ve lel emvat innellahe yusmiu mey yesaÂṀ ve ma ente bi musmiÄḟm men fil kubur"
  35,23,"In ente illa nezÄḟr"
  35,24,"Inna erselnake bil hakkÄḟ besÄḟrav ve nesÄḟra ve im min ummetin illa hala fÄḟha nezÄḟr"
  35,25,"Ve iy yukezzibuke fe kad kezzebellezÄḟne min kablihim caethum rusuluhum bil kitabil munÄḟr"
  35,26,"Summe ehaztullezÄḟne keferu fe keyfe kane nekÄḟr"
  35,27,"E lem tera ennellahe enzele mines semai maa fe ahracna bihÄḟ semeratim muhtelifen elvanuha ve minel cibali cudedum bÄḟduv ve humrum muhtelifun elvanuha ve garabÄḟbu sud"
  35,28,"Ve minen nasi ved devabbi vel enÂṀami muhtelifun elvanuhu kezalik innema yahsellahe min Äḟbadihil ulemaÂṀ innellahe azÄḟzun gafur"
  35,29,"InnellezÄḟne yetlune kitabellahi ve ekamus salete ve enfeku mimma razaknahum sirrav va alaniyetey yercune ticaratel len tebur"
  35,30,"Li yuveffiyehum ucurahum ve yezÄḟdehum min fadlih innehu gafurun sekur"
  35,31,"VellezÄḟ evhayna ileyke minel kitabi huvel hakku musaddikal lima beyne yedeyh innellahe bi ÄḟbadihÄḟ le habÄḟrum besÄḟyr"
  35,32,"Summe evrasnel kitabellezÄḟnestafeyna min Äḟbadina fe minhum zalimul li nefsih ve minhum muktesÄḟdve minhum sabikum bil hayrati bi iznillah zalike huvel fadlul kebÄḟr"
  35,33,"Cennatu adniy yedhuluneha yuhallevne fiha min esavira min zehebiv ve luÂṀlua ve libasuhum fÄḟha harir"
  35,34,"Ve kalul hamdu lillahillezÄḟ ezhebe annel hazÄḟn inne rabbena le gafurun sekur"
  35,35,"EllezÄḟ ehallena daral mukameti min fadlih la yemessuna fÄḟha nesabuv ve la yemessuna fÄḟha lugub"
  35,36,"VellezÄḟne keferu lehum naru cehennem la yukda aleyhim fe yemutu ve la yuhaffefu anhum min azabiha kezalike neczÄḟ kulle kefur"
  35,37,"Ve hum yastarihune fÄḟha rabbena ahricna naÂṀmel salihan gayrallezÄḟ kunna naÂṀmel e ve lem nuammirkum ma yetezekkeru fÄḟhi men tezekkera ve caekumun nezÄḟr fe zuku fe ma liz zalimÄḟne min nesÄḟyr"
  35,38,"Innellahe alimu gaybis semavati vel ard innehu alÄḟmum bi zatus sudur"
  35,39,"HuvellezÄḟ cealekum halaife fil ard fe men kefera fe aleyhi kufruh ve la yezÄḟdul kafirÄḟne rufruhum Äḟnde rabbihim illa makta ve la yezÄḟdul kafirÄḟne kufruhum illa hasara"
  35,40,"Kul eraeytum surakaekumullezÄḟne tedÂṀune min dunillah erunÄḟ maza haleku minel erdÄḟ em lehum sirkun fis semavat em ateynahum kitaben fehum ala beyyinetim minh bel iy yeÄḟduz zalimune baÂṀduhum baÂṀdan illa gurura"
  35,41,"Innellahe yumsikus semavati vel erda en tezula ve lein zaleta in emsekehuma min ehadim mim baÂṀdih innehu kane halÄḟmen gafura"
  35,42,"Ve aksemu billahi cehde eymanihim lein caehum nezÄḟrul le yekununne ehda min Äḟhdel umem felemma caehum nezÄḟrum mazadehum illa nufura"
  35,43,"Istikbaran fil erdÄḟ ve mekras seyyiÂṀ ve la yehÄḟykul mekrus seyyiu illa bi ehlih fe hel yenzurune illa sunnetel evvelÄḟn fe len tecide li sunnetillahi tebdÄḟla ve len tecide li sunnetillahi tahvÄḟla"
  35,44,"E ve lem yesÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fe yenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetullezÄḟne min kablihim ve kanu esedde minhum kuvveh ve ma kanellahu li yuÂṀcizehu min seyÂṀin fis semavati ve la fil ard innehu kane alimen kadÄḟraw"
  35,45,"Ve lev yuahÄḟzullahun nase bima kesebu ma terake ala zahriha min dabbetiv ve lakiy yuahhÄḟruhum ila ecelim musemma fe iza cae eceluhum fe innellahe kane bi ÄḟbadihÄḟ besÄḟyra"
  36,7,"Le kad hakkal kavlu ala ekserihim fehum la yuÂṀminun"
  36,8,"Inna cealna fÄḟ aÂṀnakÄḟhim aglalen fe hiye ilel ezkani fehum mukmehun"
  36,9,"Ve cealna mim beyni eydihim seddev ve min halfihim sedden fe agseynahum fehum la yubsÄḟrun"
  36,10,"Ve sevaun aleyhim e enzertehum em lem tunzirhum la yuÂṀminun"
  36,11,"Innema tunziru menittebeaz zikra ve hasiyer rahmane bil gayb fe bessirhu bi magfirativ ve ecrin kerÄḟm"
  36,12,"Inna nahnu nuhyil mevta ve nektubu ma kaddemu ve asarahum ve kulle seyÂṀin ahsaynahu fÄḟ imamim mubiyn"
  36,13,"Vadrib lehum meselen ashabel karyeh iz caehel murselun"
  36,14,"Iz erselna ileyhimusneyni fe kezzebuhuma fe azzezna bi salisin fe kalu inna ileykum murselun"
  36,15,"Kalu ma entum illa beserum misluna ve ma enzeler rahmanu min seyÂṀin in entum illa tekzibun"
  36,16,"Kalu rabbuna yaÂṀlemu inna ileykum le murselun"
  36,17,"Ve ma aleyna illel belagul mubÄḟn"
  36,18,"Kalu inna tetayyarna bikum leil lem tentehu le nercumennekum ve le yemessennekum minna azabun eliym"
  36,19,"Kalu tairukum meakum ein zukkirtum bel entum kavmum musrifun"
  36,20,"Ve cae min aksal medÄḟneti raculuy yesÂṀa kale ya kavmittebiul murseliyn"
  36,21,"Ittebiu mel la yesÂṀelukum ecrav vehum muhtedun"
  36,22,"Ve ma liye la aÂṀbudullezÄḟ fetaranÄḟ ve ileyhi turceun"
  36,23,"E ettehÄḟzu min dunihÄḟ aliheten iy yuridnir rahmanu bi durril la tugni annÄḟ sefaatuhum seyÂṀev ve la yunkÄḟzun"
  36,24,"InnÄḟ izel le fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  36,25,"InnÄḟ amentu bi rabbikum fesmeun"
  36,26,"KÄḟyledhulil cenneh kale ya leyte kavmÄḟ yaÂṀlemun"
  36,27,"Bima gafera lÄḟ rabbÄḟ ve cealenÄḟ minel mukramiyn"
  36,28,"Ve ma enzelna ala kavmihÄḟ mim baÂṀdihÄḟ min cundim mines semai ve ma kunna munziliyn"
  36,29,"In kanet illa sayhatev vahÄḟdeten fe iza hum hamidun"
  36,30,"Ya hasraten alel Äḟbad ma yetiyhim mir rasulin illa kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  36,31,"Elem yerav kem ehlekna kablehum minel kuruni ennehum ileyhim la yarciun"
  36,32,"Ve in kullul lemma cemiyÂṀul ledeyna muhdarun"
  36,33,"Ve ayetul lehumul erdul meyteh ahyeynaha ve ahracna minha habben feminhu yeÂṀkulun"
  36,34,"Ve cealna fiyha cennatim min nahÄḟyliv ve aÂṀnabiv ve feccerna fiyha minel uyun"
  36,35,"Li yeÂṀkulu min semerihÄḟ ve ma amilethu eydiyhim efela yeskurun"
  36,36,"SubhanellezÄḟ halekal ezvace kulleha mimma tumbitul erdu ve min enfusihim ve mimma la yaÂṀlemun"
  36,37,"Ve ayetul lehumul leyl neslehu minhun nehara fe iza hum muslimun"
  36,38,"Ves semsu tecrÄḟ li mustekarril leha zalike takdiyrul aziyzil aliym"
  36,39,"Vel kamera kaddernahu menazile hatta ade kel urcunil kadiym"
  36,40,"Lessemsu yembegÄḟy leha en tudrikel kamera velel leylu sabikun nehar ve kullun fÄḟ felekiy yesbehun"
  36,41,"Ve ayetul lehum enna hamelna zurriyyetehum fil fulkil meshun"
  36,42,"Ve halakna lehum mim mislihÄḟ ma yarkebun"
  36,43,"Ve in neseÂṀ nugrÄḟkkum fela sariyha lehum velahum yunkazun"
  36,44,"Illa rahmetem minna ve metaan ila hÄḟyn"
  36,45,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehumutteku ma beyne eydÄḟkum ve ma halfekum leallekum turhamun"
  36,46,"Ve ma teÂṀtiyhim min ayetim min ayati rabbihim illa kanu anha muÂṀridÄḟyn"
  36,47,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehum enfiku mimma razekakumullahu kalelleziyne keferu lilleziyne amenu e nutÂṀÄḟmu mel lev yesaullahu atÂṀamehu in entum illa fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  36,48,"Ve yekulune meta hazel vaÂṀdu in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  36,49,"Ma yenzurune illa sayhatev vahÄḟdeten teÂṀhuzuhum vehum yehÄḟssÄḟmun"
  36,50,"Fela yestetÄḟyÂṀune tevsÄḟyetev ve la ila ehlihim yarciun"
  36,51,"Ve nufiha fis suri fe iza hum minel ecdasi ila rabbihim yensilun"
  36,52,"Kalu ya veylena mem beasena mim merkadina haza ma veader rahmanu ve sadekal murselun"
  36,53,"In kanet illa sayhatev vahÄḟdeten feiza hum cemiyÂṀul ledeyna muhdarun"
  36,54,"Fel yevme la tuzlemu nefsun seyÂṀev vela tuczevne illa ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  36,55,"Inne ashabel cennetil yevme fÄḟ sugulin fakihun"
  36,56,"Hum ve ezvacuhum fÄḟ zÄḟlalÄḟn alel eraiki muttekiun"
  36,57,"Lehum fiyha fakihetuv ve lehum ma yeddeun"
  36,58,"Selamun kavlem mir rabbir rahÄḟym"
  36,59,"Vemtazul yevme eyyuhel mucrimun"
  36,60,"Elem aÂṀhed ileykum ya benÄḟ ademe el la taÂṀbudus seytan innehu lekum aduvvum mubiyn"
  36,61,"Ve enÄḟÂṀbuduni haza sÄḟratum mustekÄḟym"
  36,62,"Ve lekad edalle minkum cibillen kesiyra efelem tekunu taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  36,63,"HazihÄḟ cehennemulletÄḟ kuntum tuadun"
  36,64,"Islevhel yevme bima kuntum tekfurun"
  36,65,"El yevme nahtimu ala efvahihim ve tukellimuna eydÄḟhim ve teshedu erculuhum bima kanu yeksibun"
  36,66,"Velev nesau letamesna ala aÂṀyunihim festebekus sÄḟrata fe enna yubsÄḟrun"
  36,67,"Velev nesau le mesahnahum ala mekanetihim femestetau mudiyyev ve la yarciun"
  36,68,"Ve men nuammirhu nunekkishu fil halk efela yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  36,69,"Ve ma alemnahus sÄḟÂṀra ve ma yembegÄḟy leh in huve illa zikruv ve kurÂṀanum mubiyn"
  36,70,"Li yunzira men kane hayyave ve yehÄḟkkal kavlu alel kafirÄḟn"
  36,71,"E ve lem yerav enna halakna lehum mimma amilet eydÄḟna enÂṀamen fehum leha malikun"
  36,72,"Ve zellelnaha lehum fe minha rakubuhum ve minha yeÂṀkulun"
  36,73,"Ve lehum fiyha menafiu ve mesarib efela yeskurun"
  36,74,"Vettehazu min dunillahi alihetel leallehum yunsarun"
  36,75,"La yestetÄḟyÂṀune nasrahum vehum lehum cundum muhdarun"
  36,76,"Fela yahzunke kavluhum inna naÂṀlemu ma yusirrune ve ma yuÂṀlinun"
  36,77,"Evelem yeral insanu enna halaknahu min nutfetin fe iza huve hasÄḟymun mubÄḟn"
  36,78,"Ve darabe lena meselev ve nesiye halkah kale mey yuhyil Äḟzame ve hiye ramÄḟm"
  36,79,"Kul yuhyÄḟhellezÄḟ enseeha evvele merrah ve huve bi kulli halkÄḟn alÄḟm"
  36,80,"EllezÄḟ ceale lekum mines seceril ahdari naran fe iza entum minhu tukÄḟdun"
  36,81,"EveleysellezÄḟ halekas semavati vel erda bi kadirin ala ey yahluka mislehum bela ve huvel hallakul alÄḟm"
  36,82,"Innema emruhu iza erade seyÂṀen ey yekule lehu kun fe yekun"
  36,83,"Fe subhanellezÄḟ bi yedihÄḟ melekutu kulli seyÂṀiv ve ileyhi turceun"
  37,8,"La yessemmeune ilel meleil aÂṀla ve yukzefune min kulli canib"
  37,9,"Duhurav ve lehum azabuv vasÄḟb"
  37,10,"Illa men hatfel hatfete fe etbeahu sihabun sakÄḟb"
  37,11,"Festeftihim ehum esddu halkan em men halakna inna halaknahum min tÄḟynil lazib"
  37,12,"Bel acibte ve yesharun"
  37,13,"Ve iza zukkiru la yezkurun"
  37,14,"Ve iza raev ayetey yesteshÄḟrun"
  37,15,"Ve kalu in haza illa sÄḟhrum mubÄḟn"
  37,16,"E iza mitna ve kunna turabev ve Äḟzamen e inna le mebÂṀusun"
