  37,19,"Fe innema hiye zecratuv vahÄḟdetun fe izahum yenzurun"
  37,20,"Ve kalu ya veylena haza yevmud dÄḟn"
  37,21,"Haza yevmul faslillezÄḟ kuntum bihÄḟ tukezzibun"
  37,22,"UhsurullezÄḟne zalemu ve ezvacehum ve ma kanu yaÂṀbudun"
  37,23,"Min dunillahi fehduhum ila sÄḟratÄḟl cehÄḟym"
  37,24,"Ve kÄḟfuhum innehum mesÂṀulun"
  37,25,"Me lekum la tenasarun"
  37,26,"Bel humul yevme musteslimun"
  37,27,"Ve akbele baÂṀduhum ala baÂṀdÄḟy yetesaelun"
  37,28,"Kalu innekum kuntum teÂṀtunena anil yemÄḟn"
  37,29,"Kalu bel lem tekunu muÂṀminÄḟn"
  37,30,"Ve ma kane lena aleykum min sultan bel kuntum kavmen tagÄḟyn"
  37,31,"Fe hakka aleyna kavlu rabbina inna le zaikun"
  37,32,"Fe agveynakum inna kunna gavÄḟn"
  37,33,"Fe innehum yevmeizin fil azabi musterikun"
  37,34,"Inna kezalike nefÂṀalu bil mucrimÄḟn"
  37,35,"Innehum kanu iza kÄḟyle lehum la ilahe illellahu yestekbirun"
  37,36,"Ve yekulune e inna letariku alihetina li saÄḟrim mecnun"
  37,37,"Bel cae bil hakkÄḟ ve saddekal murselÄḟn"
  37,38,"Innekum lezaikul azabil elÄḟm"
  37,39,"Ve ma tuczevne illa ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  37,40,"Illa Äḟbadellahil muhlesÄḟyn"
  37,41,"Ulaike lehum rizkum maÂṀlum"
  37,42,"Fevakih ve hum mukramun"
  37,43,"FÄḟ cennatin neÄḟym"
  37,44,"Ala sururim mutekabilÄḟn"
  37,45,"Yutafu alyhim bi keÂṀsim mim meÄḟyn"
  37,46,"Beydae lezzetil lissaribÄḟn"
  37,47,"La fÄḟha gavluv ve la hum anha yunzefun"
  37,48,"Ve Äḟndehum kasÄḟratut tarfi Äḟyn"
  37,49,"Ke ennehunne beydum meknun"
  37,50,"Fe akbele baÂṀduhum ala baÂṀdÄḟy yetesaelun"
  37,51,"Kle kailum minhum innÄḟ kane lÄḟ karÄḟn"
  37,52,"Yekulu e inneke le minel musaddikÄḟyn"
  37,53,"E iza mitna ve kunna turabev ve Äḟzamen e inna le medÄḟnun"
  37,54,"Kale hel entum muttaliun"
  37,55,"Fattalea fe raahu fÄḟ sevail cehÄḟym"
  37,56,"Kale tellahi in kidte le turdÄḟn"
  37,57,"Ve lev la nÄḟÂṀmetu rabbÄḟ lekuntu minel muhdarÄḟn"
  37,58,"E fe ma nahnu bi meyyitÄḟn"
  37,59,"Illa mevtetenel ula ve ma nahnu bi muazzebÄḟn"
  37,60,"Inne haza le huvel fevzul azÄḟym"
  37,61,"Li misli haza felyaÂṀmelil amilun"
  37,62,"E zalike hayrun nuzulen em seceratuzc zekkum"
  37,63,"Inna cealnaha fitnetel liz zalimÄḟn"
  37,64,"Inneha seceratun tahrucu fÄḟ aslil cehÄḟym"
  37,65,"TalÂṀuha ke ennehu ruusus seyatÄḟyn"
  37,66,"Fe innehum le akilune minha fe maliune minhel butun"
  37,67,"Summe inne lehum aleyha le sevbem min hamum"
  37,68,"Summe inne merciahum le ilel cehÄḟym"
  37,69,"Innehum elfev abaehum dallÄḟn"
  37,70,"Fe hum ala asarihim yuhraun"
  37,71,"Ve le kad dalhle kablehum ekserul evvelÄḟn"
  37,72,"Ve le kad erselna fÄḟhim munzirÄḟn"
  37,73,"Fenzur keyfe kane akÄḟbetul munzerÄḟn"
  37,74,"Illa Äḟbadellahil muhlesÄḟyn"
  37,75,"Ve le kad nadana nuhun fe le nÄḟÂṀmel muccÄḟbun"
  37,76,"Ve necceynahu ve ehlehu minel kerbil azÄḟym"
  37,77,"Ve cealna zurriyyetehu humul bakÄḟyn"
  37,78,"Ve terakna aleyhi fil ahÄḟrÄḟn"
  37,79,"Selamun ala nuhÄḟn fil alemÄḟn"
  37,80,"Inna kezalike neczil muhsinÄḟn"
  37,81,"Innehu min Äḟbadinel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  37,82,"Summe agraknel aharÄḟn"
  37,83,"Ve inne min sÄḟatihÄḟ le ibrahÄḟm"
  37,84,"Iz cae rabbehu bi kalbin selÄḟm"
  37,85,"Iz kale li ebÄḟhi ve kavmihÄḟ maza taÂṀbudun"
  37,86,"E ifken aliheten dunellahi turÄḟdun"
  37,87,"Fe ma zannukum bi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  37,88,"Fe nezara nazraten fin nucum"
  37,89,"Fe kale innÄḟ sekÄḟym"
  37,90,"Fe tevellev anhu mudbirÄḟn"
  37,91,"Feraga ila alihetihim fe kale e ela teÂṀkulun"
  37,92,"Ma lekum la tentÄḟkun"
  37,93,"Feraga aleyhim darbem bil yemÄḟn"
  37,94,"Fe akbelu ileyhi yeziffun"
  37,95,"Kale e taÂṀbudune ma tenhÄḟtun"
  37,96,"Vallahu halekkkakum ve ma taÂṀmelun"
  37,97,"Kalubnu lehu bunyanen fe elkuhu fil cehÄḟym"
  37,98,"Fe eradu bihÄḟ keyden fe cealnahumul esfelÄḟn"
  37,99,"Ve kale innÄḟ zahibun ila rabbÄḟ seyehdÄḟn"
  37,100,"Rabbi heb lÄḟ mines salihÄḟyn"
  37,101,"Fe bessernahu bi gulamin halÄḟm"
  37,102,"Felemma belega meahus saÂṀye kale ya buneyye innÄḟ era fil menami ennÄḟ ezbehuke fenzur maza tera kale ya ebetifÂṀal ma tuÂṀmeru setecidunÄḟ in saellahu mines sabirÄḟn"
  37,103,"Felemma eslema ve tellehu lil cebÄḟn"
  37,104,"Ve nadeynahu ey ya ibrahÄḟm"
  37,105,"Kad saddakter ruÂṀya inna kezalike neczil muhsinÄḟn"
  37,106,"Inne haza le huvel belaul mubÄḟn"
  37,107,"Ve fedeynahu bi zibhÄḟn azÄḟym"
  37,108,"Ve terakna aleyhi fil ahÄḟrÄḟn"
  37,109,"Selamun ala ibrahÄḟm"
  37,110,"Kezalike neczil muhsinÄḟn"
  37,111,"Innehu min Äḟbadinel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  37,112,"Ve bessernahu bi ishaka nebiyyem mines salihÄḟyn"
  37,113,"Ve barakna aleyhi ve ala ishak ve min zurriyyetihima muhsinuv ve zalimul li nefsihÄḟ mubÄḟn"
  37,114,"Ve le kad menenna ala musa ve haun"
  37,115,"Ve necceynahuma va kavmehuma minel kerbil azÄḟym"
  37,116,"Ve nasarnahum fe kanu humul galibÄḟn"
  37,117,"Ve ateynahumel kitabel mustebÄḟn"
  37,118,"Ve hedeynahumes sÄḟratal mustekÄḟym"
  37,119,"Ve terakna aleyhima fil ahÄḟrÄḟn"
  37,120,"Selamun ala musa ve harun"
  37,121,"Inna kezalik enczil muhsinÄḟn"
  37,122,"Innehuma min Äḟbadinel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  37,123,"Ve inne ilyase le minel murselÄḟn"
  37,124,"Iz kale li kavmihÄḟ ela tettekun"
  37,125,"E tedÂṀune baÂṀlev ve tezerune ahsenel halikÄḟyn"
  37,126,"Allahe rabbekum ve rabbe abaikumul evvelÄḟn"
  37,127,"Fe kezzebuhu fe innehum le muhdarun"
  37,128,"Illa Äḟbadellahil muhlesÄḟyn"
  37,129,"Ve terakna aleyhi fil ahÄḟrÄḟn"
  37,130,"Selamun ala ilyasÄḟn"
  37,131,"Inna kezalike neczil muhsinÄḟn"
  37,132,"Innehu min Äḟbadinel muÂṀminÄḟn"
  37,133,"Ve inne lutal le minel murselÄḟn"
  37,134,"Iz necceynahu ve ehlehu ecmeÄḟyn"
  37,135,"Illa acuzen fil gabirÄḟn"
  37,136,"Summe demmernel aharÄḟn"
  37,137,"Ve innekum le temurrune aleyhim musbihÄḟyn"
  37,138,"Ve bil leyl e fe la taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  37,139,"Ve inne yunuse le minel murselÄḟn"
  37,140,"Iz ebeka ilel fulkil meshun"
  37,141,"Fe saheme fe kane minel mudhadÄḟyn"
  37,142,"Feltekamehul hutu ve huve mulÄḟm"
  37,143,"Fe lev la ennehu kane minel musebbihÄḟyn"
  37,144,"Le lebise fÄḟ batnihÄḟ ila yevmi yubÂṀasun"
  37,145,"Fe nebeznahu bil arai ve huve sekÄḟym"
  37,146,"Ve embenta aleyhi seceratem miy yaktÄḟyn"
  37,147,"Ve erselnahu ila mieti elfin ev yezÄḟdun"
  37,148,"Fe amenu fe mettaÂṀnahum ila hÄḟyn"
  37,149,"Festeftihim e li rabbikel benatu ve lehumul benun"
  37,150,"Em halaknel melaiket inasev ve hum sahidun"
  37,151,"E la innehum min ifkihim le yekulun"
  37,152,"Veledellahu ve innehum le kazibun"
  37,153,"Astafel benati alel benÄḟn"
  37,154,"Ma lekum keyfe tahkumun"
  37,155,"E fe la tezekkerun"
  37,156,"Em lekum sultanum mubÄḟn"
  37,157,"FeÂṀtu bi kitabikum in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  37,158,"Ve cealu beynehu ve beynel cinneti neseba ve le kad alimetil cinnetu innehum le muhdarun"
  37,159,"Subhanellahi amma yesÄḟun"
  37,160,"Illa Äḟbadellahil muhlesÄḟyn"
  37,161,"Fe innekum ve ma taÂṀbudun"
  37,162,"Ma entum aleyhi bi fatinÄḟn"
  37,163,"Illa men huve salil cehÄḟym"
  37,164,"Ve ma minna illa lehu mekamum maÂṀlum"
  37,165,"Ve inna le nahnus saffun"
  37,166,"Ve inna le nahnul musebbihun"
  37,167,"Ve in kanu le yekulun"
  37,168,"Lev enne Äḟndena zikram minel evvelin"
  37,169,"Lekunna Äḟbadellahil muhlesÄḟyn"
  37,170,"Fe keferu bih fe sevfe yaÂṀlemun"
  37,171,"Ve le kad sebekat kelimetuna li Äḟbadinel murselÄḟn"
  37,172,"Innehum le humul mensurun"
  37,173,"Ve inne cundena lehumul galibun"
  37,174,"Fe tevelle anhum hatta hÄḟyn"
  37,175,"Ve ebsÄḟrhum fe sevfe yubsÄḟrun"
  37,176,"E fe biazabina yestaÂṀcilun"
  37,177,"Fe iza nezele bi sahatihim fe sae sabahul munzerÄḟn"
  37,178,"Ve tevelle anhum hatta hÄḟyn"
  37,179,"Ve ebsÄḟr fe sevfe yubsÄḟrun"
  37,180,"Subhane rabbike rabbil Äḟzzeti amma yesfun"
  37,181,"Ve selamun alel murselÄḟn"
  37,182,"Vel hamdu lillahi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  38,6,"Ventalekal melau minhum enimsu vasbiru ala alihetikum inne haza le seyÂṀuy yurad"
  38,7,"Ma semÄḟÂṀna bihaza fil milletil ahÄḟrah in haza illahtilak"
  38,8,"E unzile aliyhiz zikru mim beynina bel hum fÄḟ sekkim min zikrÄḟ bel lemma yezuku azab"
  38,9,"Em Äḟndehum hazinu rahmeti rabbikel azÄḟzil vehhab"
  38,10,"Em lehum mulkus semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ma beynehuma feyerteku fil esbab"
  38,11,"Cundum ma hunalike menzumum minel ahzab"
  38,12,"Kezzebet kablehum kavmu nuhÄḟv ve aduv ve firÂṀavnu zul evtad"
  38,13,"Ve semudu ve kavmu lutÄḟv ve ashabul eykeh ulaikel ahzab"
  38,14,"In kullun illa kezzeber rusule fe hakka Äḟkab"
  38,15,"Ve ma yenzuru haulai illa sayhatev vahÄḟdetem ma leha min fevak"
  38,16,"Ve kalu rabbena accil lena kÄḟttana kable yevmil hÄḟsab"
  38,17,"Isbir ala ma yekulune veskur abdena davude zel eyd innehu evvab"
  38,18,"Inna sehharnel cibale meahu yusebbÄḟhne bil asiyyi vel israk"
  38,19,"Vettayra mahsurah kullul lehu evvab"
  38,20,"Ve sededna mulehu ve ateynahul hÄḟkmete ve faslel hÄḟtab"
  38,21,"Ve hel etake nebeul hasm iz tesevverul mÄḟhrab"
  38,22,"Iz dehalu ala davude fe fezia minhum kalu la tehaf hasmani bega baÂṀduna ala baÂṀdÄḟn fahkum beynena bil hakkÄḟ ve la tustÄḟt vehdina ila sevais sÄḟrat"
  38,23,"Inne haza ehÄḟy lehu tisÂṀuv ve tisÂṀune naÂṀcetev ve liye naÂṀcetuv vahÄḟdetun fe kale ekfilnÄḟha ve azzenÄḟ fil hÄḟtab"
  38,24,"Kale le kad zalemeke bi suali naÂṀcetike ila niacih ve inne kesÄḟram minel huletai le yebgÄḟy baÂṀduhum ala baÂṀdÄḟn ilellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati ve kalÄḟlum ma hum ve zanne davudu ennema fetennahu festagfera rabbehu ve harra rakiav ve enab"
  38,25,"Fe gaferna lehu zalik ve inne lehu Äḟndena le zulfa ve husne meab"
  38,26,"Ya davudu inna cealnake hhalÄḟfeten fil erdÄḟ fahkum beynen nasi bil hakkÄḟ ve la tettebiÄḟl heva fe yudÄḟlleke an sebÄḟlillah innellezÄḟne yedÄḟllune an sebÄḟlillahi lehum azabun sedÄḟdum bima nesu yevmel hÄḟsab (24. Ayet secde ayetidir)"
  38,27,"Ve ma halaknes semae vel erda ve ma beynehuma batÄḟla zalike zannullezÄḟne keferu fe veylul lillezine keferu minen nar"
  38,28,"Em necÂṀalullezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati kel mufsidÄḟne fil erdÄḟ em necÂṀalul muttekÄḟyne kel fuccar"
  38,29,"Kitabun enzelnahu ileyke mubarakul li yeddebberu ayatihÄḟ ve li yetezekkera ulul elbab"
  38,30,"Ve vehebna li davude suleyman nÄḟÂṀmel abdinnehu evvab"
  38,31,"Iz urida aleyhi bil asiyyis safinatul ciyad"
  38,32,"Fe kale innÄḟ ahbebtu hubbel hayri an zikri rabbÄḟ hatta tevarat bil hÄḟcab"
  38,33,"Rudduha aleyy fe tafika mesham bis sukÄḟ vel aÂṀnak"
  38,34,"Ve le kad fetenna suleymane ve elkayna ala kursiyyihÄḟ ceseden summe enab"
  38,35,"Kale rabbÄḟgfir lÄḟ veheb li mulkel la yembegÄḟy li ehadim mim baÂṀdi inneke entel vehhab"
  38,36,"Fe sehharna lehur rÄḟha tecrÄḟ bi emrihÄḟ ruhaen haysu esab"
  38,37,"Ves seyatÄḟyne kullu bennaiv ve gavvas"
  38,38,"Ve aharÄḟne mukarranÄḟne fil asfad"
  38,39,"Haza atauna femnun ev emsik bi gayri hÄḟsab"
  38,40,"Ve inne lehu Äḟndena le zulfa ve husne meab"
  38,41,"Vezkur abdena eyyub iz nada rabbehu ennÄḟ messeniyes seytanu bi nusbiv ve azab"
  38,42,"Urkud bi riclik haza mugteselum bariduv ve serab"
  38,43,"Ve vehebna lehu ehlehu ve mislehum meahum rahmetem minna ve zikra li ulil elbab"
  38,44,"Ve huz biyedike dÄḟgsen fadrib bihu ve la tahnes inna vecednahu sabira nÄḟÂṀ mel abd innehu evvab"
  38,45,"Vezkur Äḟbadena ibrahÄḟme ve ishaka ve yaÂṀkube ulil eydÄḟ ve ebsar"
  38,46,"Inna ahlasnahum bi halisatin zikrad dar"
  38,47,"Ve innehum Äḟndena le minel mustefeynel ahyar"
  38,48,"Vezkur ismaÄḟyle vel yesea ve zel kifl ve kullum minel ahyar"
  38,49,"Haza zikr ve inne lil muttekÄḟyne le husne meab"
  38,50,"Cennati adnim mufettehatel lehumul ebvab"
  38,51,"MuttekiÄḟne fÄḟha yedÂṀune fÄḟha bi fakihetin kesÄḟrativ ve serab"
  38,52,"Ve Äḟndehum kasÄḟratut turfi etrab"
  38,53,"Haza ma tuadune li yevmil hÄḟsab"
  38,54,"Inne haza le rizkuna ma lehu min nefad"
  38,55,"Haza ve inne lit tagÄḟyne le serra meab"
  38,56,"Cehennem yaslevneha fe biÂṀsel mihad"
  38,57,"Haza fel yezukuhu hamÄḟmuv ve gassak"
  38,58,"Ve aharu min seklihÄḟ ezvac"
  38,59,"Haza fevcum muktehÄḟmum meakum la merhabem bihim innehum salun nar"
  38,60,"Kalu bel entum la merhabem bikum entum kaddemtumuhu lena fe biÂṀsel karar"
  38,61,"Kalu rabbena men kaddeme lena haza fezidhu azaben dÄḟÂṀfen fin nar"
  38,62,"Ve kalu ma lena la nera ricalen kunna neudduhum minel esrar"
  38,63,"Ettehaznahum sÄḟhriyyen em zagat anhumul ebsar"
  38,64,"Inne zalike le hakkun tehasumu ehlin nar"
  38,65,"Kul innema ene munziruv ve ma min ilahin illellahul vahÄḟdul kahhar"
  38,66,"Rabbus semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ma beynehumel azÄḟzul gaffar"
  38,67,"Kul huve nebun azÄḟym"
  38,68,"Entum anhu muÂṀridun"
  38,69,"Ma kane liye min Äḟlmin bil meleil aÂṀla iz yahtesÄḟmun"
  38,70,"Iy yuha ileyye illa ennema ene nezÄḟrum mubÄḟn"
  38,71,"Iz kale rabbuke lil melaiketi innÄḟ halikum beseram min tÄḟyn"
  38,72,"Fe iza sevveytuhu ve nefahtu fÄḟhi mir ruhÄḟy fekau lehu sacidÄḟn"
  38,73,"Fe secedel melaiketu kulluhum ecmeun"
  38,74,"Illa iblÄḟs istekbera ve kane minel kafirÄḟn"
  38,75,"Kale ya iblÄḟsu ma meneake en tescude li ma halaktu bi yedeyy estekberte em kunte minel alÄḟn"
  38,76,"Kale ene hayrum minh halaktenÄḟ min nariv ve halaktehu min tÄḟyn"
  38,77,"Kale fahruc minha fe inneke racÄḟm"
  38,78,"Ve inne aleyke laÂṀnetÄḟ ila yevmid dÄḟn"
  38,79,"Kale rabbi fe enzÄḟrni ila yevmi yubÂṀasun"
  38,80,"Kale fe inneke minel munzarÄḟn"
  38,81,"Ila yevmil vaktil maÂṀmum"
  38,82,"Kale fe bi Äḟzzetike le ugviyennehum ecmeÄḟyn"
  38,83,"Illa Äḟbadeke minhumul muhlesÄḟyn"
  38,84,"Kale fel hakku vel hakka ekul"
  38,85,"Le emleenne cehenneme minke ve mimmen tebiake minhum ecmeÄḟyn"
  38,86,"Kul ma esÂṀelukum aleyhi min ecriv ve ma enen minel mutekellifÄḟn"
  38,87,"In huve illa zikrul lil alemÄḟn"
  38,88,"Ve le taÂṀlemunne nebeehu baÂṀde hÄḟyn"
  39,8,"Ve iza messel insane durrun dea rabbehu munÄḟben ileyhi summe iza havvelehu nÄḟÂṀmetem minhu nesiye ma kane yedÂṀu ileyhi min kabul ve ceale lillahi endadel li yudÄḟlle an sebÄḟlih kul temettaÂṀ bi kufrike kalÄḟlen inneke min ashabin nar"
  39,9,"Emmen huve kanitun anael leyli sacidev ve kaimey yahzerul ahÄḟrate ve yercu rahmete rabbih kul hel yestevillezÄḟne yaÂṀlemune vellezÄḟne la yaÂṀlemun innema yetezekkeru ulul elbab"
  39,10,"Kul ya ÄḟbadillezÄḟne amenutteku rabbekum lillezÄḟne ahsenu fÄḟ hazihid dunya haseneh ve erdullahi vasiah innema yuveffes sabirune ecrahum bi gayri hÄḟsab"
  39,11,"Kul innÄḟ umirtu en aÂṀbudellahe muhlisal lehud dÄḟn"
  39,12,"Ve umirtu li en ekune evvelel muslimÄḟn"
  39,13,"Kul innÄḟ ehafu in asaytu rabbÄḟ azabe yevmin azÄḟym"
  39,14,"Kulillahe aÂṀbudu muhlisal lehu dÄḟnÄḟ"
  39,15,"FÂṀbudu ma siÂṀtum min dunih kul innel hasirÄḟnellezÄḟne hasiru enfusehum ve ehlihim yevmel kÄḟyameh e la zalike huvel husranul mubÄḟn"
  39,16,"Lehum min fevkÄḟhim zulelum minen nari ve imn tahtihim zulel zalike yuhavvifullahu bihÄḟ Äḟbadeh ya Äḟbadi fettekun"
  39,17,"VellezÄḟnectenebut tagute ey yaÂṀbuduha ve enabu ilillahi lehumul busra fe bessir Äḟbad"
  39,18,"EllezÄḟne yestemiunel kavle feyettebiune ahseneh ulaikellezÄḟne hedahumullahu ve ulaike hum ulul elbab"
  39,19,"E fe men hakka aleyhi kelimetul azab e fe ente tunkÄḟzu men fin nar"
  39,20,"LakinillezÄḟnettekav rabbehum lehum gurafum min fevkÄḟha gurafum mebniyyetun tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enhar vaÂṀdellah la yuhlifullahul mÄḟad"
  39,21,"E lem tera ennellahe enzele mines semai maen fe selekehu yenabÄḟa fil erdÄḟ summe yuhricu bihÄḟ zerÂṀam muhtelifen elvanuhu summe yehÄḟcu fe terahu musferran summe yecÂṀaluhu hutama inne fÄḟ zalike le zikra li ulil elbab"
  39,22,"E fe men serahallahu sadrahu lil islami fe huve ala murim mir rabbih fe veylul lil kasÄḟyeti kulubuhum min zikrillah ulaike fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  39,23,"Allahu nezzele ahsenel hadÄḟsi kitabem mutesebihem mesaniye takseÄḟrru minhu cculudullezÄḟne yahsevne rabbehum summe telÄḟnu culuduhum ve kulubuhum ila zikrillah zalike hudellahi yehdÄḟ bihÄḟ mey yesaÂṀ ve mey yudlilillahu fe ma lehu min had"
  39,24,"E fe mey yettekÄḟy bi vechihÄḟ suel azabi yevmel kÄḟyameh ve kÄḟyle liz zalimÄḟne zuku ma kuntum teksibun"
  39,25,"KezzebellezÄḟne min kablihim fe etehumul azabu min hayus la yesÂṀurun"
  39,26,"Fe ezakahumullahul hÄḟzye fil hayatid dunya ve leazabul ahÄḟrati ekber lev kanu yaÂṀlemun"
  39,27,"Ve le kad darabna lin nasi fÄḟ hazel kurÂṀani min kulli meselil leallehum yetesekkerun"
  39,28,"KurÂṀanen arabiyyen gayra zÄḟ Äḟvecil leallehum yettekun"
  39,29,"Darabellahu meseler raculen fÄḟhi surakau mutesakisune ve raculen selemel li racul hel yesteviyani mesela elhamdu lillah bel ekseruhum la yaÂṀlemun"
  39,30,"Inneke meyyituv ve innehum meyyitun"
  39,31,"Summe innekum yevmel kÄḟyameti Äḟnde rabbikum tahtesÄḟmun"
  39,32,"Fe men azlemu mimmen kezebe alellahi ve kezzebe bis sÄḟdkÄḟ iz caeh e leyse fÄḟ cehenneme mesvel lil kafirÄḟn"
  39,33,"VellezÄḟ cae bis sÄḟdkÄḟ ve saddeka bihÄḟ ulaike humul muttekun"
  39,34,"Lehum ma yesaune Äḟnde rabbihim zalike cezalu muhsinÄḟn"
  39,35,"Li yukeffirallahu anhum esveellezÄḟ amilu ve yecziyehum ecrahum bi ahsenillezÄḟ kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  39,36,"E leysellahu bi kafin abdeh ve yuhavvifuneke billezÄḟne min dunih ve mey yudlilillahu fema lehu min had"
  39,37,"Ve mey yehdillahu fema lehu mim mudÄḟll e leysellahu bi azÄḟzin zintikam"
  39,38,"Ve lein seeltehum men halekas semavati vel erda le yekulunnellah kul eferaeytum ma tedÂṀune min dunillahi in eradeniyellahu bi durrin hel hunne kasifatu durrihÄḟ ev eradenÄḟ bi rahmetin hel hunne mumsikatu rahmetih kul hasbiyellah aleyhi yetevekkelul mutevekkilun"
  39,39,"Kul ya kavmÄḟÂṀmelu ala mekanetikum innÄḟ amil fe sevfe taÂṀlemun"
  39,40,"Mey yeÂṀtÄḟhi azabuy yuhzÄḟhi ve yehÄḟllu aleyhi azabum mukÄḟym"
  39,41,"Inna enzelna aleykel kitabe lin nasi bil hakk fe menihteda fe li nefsih ve men dalle fe innema yedÄḟllu aleyha ve ma ente aleyhim bi vekÄḟl"
  39,42,"Allahu yeteveffel enfuse hÄḟyne mevtiha velletÄḟ lem temut fÄḟ menamiha fe yumsikulletÄḟ kada aleyhel mevte ve yursilul uhra ila ecelim musemma inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yetefekkerun"
  39,43,"Emittehazu min dunillahi sufeaÂṀ kul e ve lev kanu la yemlikune seyÂṀev ve la yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  39,44,"Kul lillahis sefaatu cemÄḟa lehu mulkus semavati vel ard summe ileyhi turceun"
  39,45,"Ve iza zukirallahu vahdehusmeezzet kulubullezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune bil ahÄḟrah ve iza zukirallezÄḟne min dunihÄḟ izahum yestebsirun"
  39,46,"Kulillahumme fatÄḟras semavati vel erdÄḟ alimel gaybi ves sehadeti ente tahkumu beyne Äḟbadike fÄḟma kanu fÄḟhi yahtelifun"
  39,47,"Ve lev enne lillezÄḟne zalemu ma fil erdÄḟ cemÄḟav ve mislehu meahu leftedev bihÄḟ min suil azabi yevmel kÄḟyameh ve beda lehum minellahi ma lem yekunu yahtesibun"
  39,48,"Ve beda lehum seyyiatu ma kesebu ve haka bihim ma kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  39,49,"Fe iza messel insane durrun deana summe iza havvelnahu nÄḟÂṀmetem minna kale innema utÄḟtuhu ala Äḟlm bel hiye fitnetuv ve lakinne ekserahum la yaÂṀlemun"
  39,50,"Kad kalehellezÄḟne min kablihim fe ma agna anhum ma kanu yeksibun"
  39,51,"Fe esabehum seyyiatu ma kesebu vellezÄḟne zalemu min haulai seyusÄḟybuhum seyyiatu ma kesebu ve mahum bi muÂṀcizÄḟn"
  39,52,"E ve lem yaÂṀlemu ennellahe yebsutur rizka li mey yesau ve yakdir onne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yuÂṀminun"
  39,53,"Kul ya ÄḟbadiyellezÄḟne esrafu ala enfusihim la taknetu mir rahmetillah innellahe yagfiruz zunube cemÄḟa innehu huvel gafurur rahÄḟym"
  39,54,"Ve enÄḟbu ila rabbikum ve eslimu lehu min kabli ey yetiyekumul azabu summe la tunsarun"
  39,55,"Vettebiu ahsene ma unzile ileykum mir rabbikum min kabli ey yeÂṀtiyekumul azabu bagtetev ve entum la tesÂṀurun"
  39,56,"En tekule nefsuy ya hasrata ala ma ferrattu fÄḟ cembillahi ve in kuntu le mines sahÄḟrÄḟn"
  39,57,"Ev tekule lev ennellahe hedani lekuntu minel muttekÄḟyn"
  39,58,"Ev tekule hÄḟyne teral azabe lev enne lÄḟ kerraten fe ekune minel muhsinÄḟn"
  39,59,"Bela kad caetke ayatÄḟ fe kezzebte biha vestekberte ve kunte minel kafirÄḟn"
  39,60,"Ve yevmel kÄḟyameti terallezÄḟne kezebu alellahi vucuhuhum musveddeh e leyse fÄḟ cehenneme mesvel lil mutekebbirÄḟn"
  39,61,"Ve yuneccillahullezÄḟnettekav bi mefazetihim la yemessuhumus suu ve la hum yahzenun"
  39,62,"Allahu haliku kulli seyÂṀiv ve huve ala kulli seyÂṀiv vekÄḟl"
  39,63,"Lehu mekalÄḟdus semavati vel ard vellezÄḟne keferu bi ayatillahi ulaike humul hasirun"
  39,64,"Kul e fe gayrallahi teÂṀmurunnÄḟ aÂṀbudu eyyuhel cahilun"
  39,65,"Ve le kad uhÄḟye ileyke ve ilellezÄḟne min kablik lein esrakte le yahbetanne ameluke ve le tekunenne minel hasirÄḟn"
  39,66,"Belillahe faÂṀbud ve kum mines sakirÄḟn"
  39,67,"Ve ma kaderullahe hakka kadrihÄḟ vel erdu cemÄḟan kabdatuhu yevmel kÄḟyameti ves semavatu matviyyatum bi yemÄḟnih subhunehu ve teala amma yusrikun"
  39,68,"Ve nufiha fis suri fe saÄḟka men fis semavati ve men fil erdÄḟ illa men saellah summe nufiha fÄḟhi uhra fe izahum kÄḟyamuy yenzurun"
  39,69,"Ve esrakatil erdu bi nuri rabbiha ve vudÄḟal kitabu ve cÄḟe bin nebiyyÄḟne ves suhedai ve kudiye beynehum bil hakkÄḟ ve hum la yuzlemun"
  39,70,"Ve vuffiyet kullu nefsim ma amilet ve huve aÂṀlemu bima yefÂṀalun"
  39,71,"VesÄḟkallezÄḟne keferu ila cehenneme zumera hatta iza cauha futihat ebvabuha ve kale lehum hazenetuha e lem yeÂṀtikum rusulum minkum yetlune aleykum ayati rabbikum ve yunzirunekum likae yemikum haza kalu bela velakin hakkat kelimetul azabi alel kafirÄḟn"
  39,72,"KÄḟyledhulu ebvabe cehenneme halidÄḟne fÄḟha fe biÂṀse mesvel mutekebbirÄḟn"
  39,73,"VesÄḟkallezÄḟnet tekav rabbehum ilel cenneti zumera hatta iza cauha ve futihat ebvabuha ve kale lehum hazenetuha selamun aleykum tÄḟbtum fedhuluha halidÄḟn"
  39,74,"Ve kalul hamdu lillahillezÄḟ sadekana vaÂṀdehu ve evrasenel erda netebevveu minel cenneti hayus nesaÂṀ fe nÄḟÂṀme ecrul amilÄḟn"
  39,75,"Ve teral melaikete haffÄḟne min havlil arsi yusebbihune bi hamdi rabbihim ve kudÄḟye beynehum bil hakkÄḟ ve kÄḟylel hamdu lillahi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  40,8,"Rabbena ve edhÄḟlhum cennati adninilletÄḟ veadtehum ve men salehu min abaihim ve ezvacihim ve zurriyyatihim inneke entel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  40,9,"VekÄḟhimus seyyiat ve men tekÄḟs seyyiati yevmeizin fe kad rahÄḟmteh ve zalike huvel fevzul azÄḟym"
  40,10,"InnellezÄḟne keferu yunadevne le maktullahi ekberu mim maktikum enfusekum iz tudÂṀavne ilel imani fe tekfurun"
  40,11,"Kalu rabbena emettenesneteyni ve ahyeytenesneteyni faÂṀterafna bi zunubina fe hel ila hurucim min sebÄḟl"
  40,12,"Zalikum bi ennehu iza duÄḟyellahu vahdehu kefartum ve iy yusruk bihÄḟ tuÂṀminu fel hukmu lillahul aliyyil kebÄḟr"
  40,13,"HuvellezÄḟ yurÄḟkum ayatihÄḟ ve yunezzilu lekum mines semai rizka ve ma yetezekkeru illa mey yunÄḟb"
  40,14,"FedÂṀullahe mhlisÄḟyne lehud dÄḟne ve lev kerihel kafirun"
  40,15,"RafÄḟud deracati zul ars yulkÄḟr ruha min emrihÄḟ ala mey yesau min ÄḟbadihÄḟ li yunzira yevmet telak"
  40,16,"Yevme hum barizun la yahfa alellahi minhum seyÂṀ li menil mulkul yevm lillahil vahÄḟdil kahhar"
  40,17,"Elyevme tucza kullu mefsim bima kesebet La zulmel yevm innellahe serÄḟul hÄḟsab"
  40,18,"Ve enzihum yevmel azifeti izil kulubu ledel hanaciri kazÄḟmÄḟn ma liz zalimÄḟne min hamÄḟmiv ve la sefÄḟÄḟy yutaÂṀ"
  40,19,"YaÂṀlemu hainetel aÂṀyuni ve ma tuhfis sudur"
  40,20,"Vallahu yakdÄḟy bil hakk vellezÄḟne yedÂṀune min dunihÄḟ la yakdune bi seyÂṀ innellahe huves semÄḟul besÄḟyr"
  40,21,"E ve lem yesÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fe yenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetullezÄḟne kanu min kablihim kanu hum esedde minhum kuvvetev ve asaran fil erdÄḟ fe ehazehumullahu bi zunubihim ve ma kane lehum minellahi miv vak"
  40,22,"Zalike bi ennehum kanet teÂṀtÄḟhim rusuluhum bil beyyinati fe keferu fe ehazehumullah innehu kaviyyun sedÄḟdul Äḟkab"
  40,23,"Ve le kad erselna musa bi ayatina ve sultanim mubÄḟn"
  40,24,"Ila firÂṀavne ve hamane ve karune fe kalu sahÄḟrun kezzab"
  40,25,"Fe lemma caehum bil hakkÄḟ min Äḟndina kaluktulu ebnaellezÄḟne amenu meahu vestahyu nisaehum ve ma keydul kafirÄḟne illa fÄḟ dalal"
  40,26,"Ve kale firÂṀavnu zerunÄḟ aktul musa vel yedÂṀu rabbeh innÄḟ ehafu ey yubeddile dÄḟnekum ev ey yuzhira fil erdÄḟl fesad"
  40,27,"Ve kale musa innÄḟ ustu bi rabbÄḟ ve rabbikum min kulli mutekebbiril la yuÂṀminu bi yevmil hÄḟsab"
  40,28,"Ve kale raculum muÂṀminum min ali firÂṀavne yektumu Äḟmanehu etaktulune raculen ey yekule rabbiyellahu ve kad caekum bil beyyinati mir rabbikum ve iy yeku sadikay yusÄḟbkum baÂṀdullezÄḟ yeÄḟdukum innellahe la yehdÄḟ men huve musrifun kezzab"
  40,29,"Ya kavmi lekumul mulkul yevme zahirÄḟne fil erdÄḟ fe mey yensuruna mim beÂṀsillahi in caena kale firÂṀavnu ma urÄḟkum illa ma era ve ma ehdÄḟkum illa sebÄḟler rasad"
  40,30,"Ve kalellezÄḟ amene ya kavmi innÄḟ ehafu aleykum misle yevmil ahzab"
  40,31,"Misle deÂṀbi kavmi nuhÄḟv ve adiv ve semude vellezÄḟne mim baÂṀdihim ve mellahu yurÄḟdu zulmel lil Äḟbad"
  40,32,"Ve ya kavmi innÄḟ ehafu aleykum yevmet tenad"
  40,33,"Yevme tuvellune mudbirÄḟn ma lekum minellahi min asÄḟm ve mey yudlilillahu fe ma lehu min had"
  40,34,"Ve le kad caekum yusufu min kablu bil beyyinati fe ma ziltum fÄḟ sekkim mimma caekum bih hatta iza heleke kultum ley yebÂṀasellahu mim baÂṀdihÄḟ rasula kezalike yudÄḟllullahu men huve musrifum murtab"
  40,35,"EllezÄḟne yucadilune fi ayatillahi bi gayri sultanin etahum kebura makten Äḟndellahi ve ÄḟndellezÄḟne amenu kezalike yatbeullahu ala kulli kalbi mutekebbirin cebbar"
  40,36,"Ve kale firÂṀavnu ya hamanubni lÄḟ sarhal le allÄḟ eblugul esbab"
  40,37,"Esbabes semavati fe attalia ila ilahi musa ve innÄḟ le ezunnuhu kaziba ve kezalike zuyyine li firÂṀavne suu amelihÄḟ ve sudde anis sebÄḟl ve ma keydu firÂṀavne illa fÄḟ tebab"
  40,38,"Ve kalellezÄḟ amene ya kavmit tebiuni ehdikum sebÄḟler rasad"
  40,39,"Ya kavmi innema hazihil hayatud dunya metaÂṀuv ve innel ahÄḟrate hiye darul karar"
  40,40,"Men amile seyyieten fe la yucza illa misleha ve men amile salihum min zekerin ev unsa ve huve muÂṀminun fe ulaike yedhulunel cennete yurzekune fÄḟha bi gayri hÄḟsab"
  40,41,"Ve ya kavmi malÄḟ edÂṀukum ilen necati ve tedÂṀunenÄḟ ilen nar"
  40,42,"TedÂṀunenÄḟ li ekfura billahi ve usrike bihÄḟ ma leyse lÄḟ bihÄḟ Äḟlmuv ve ene edÂṀukum ilel azÄḟzil gaffar"
  40,43,"La cerame ennema tedÂṀunenÄḟ ileyhi leyse lehu daÂṀvetun fid dunya ve la fil ahÄḟrati ve enne meraddena ilellahi ve ennel musrifÄḟne hum ashabun nar"
  40,44,"Fe setezkurune ma ekulu lekum ve ufevvidu emrÄḟ ilellah innellahe basÄḟyrum bil Äḟbad"
  40,45,"Fe vekahullahu seyyiati ma mekeru ve haka bi ali firÂṀavne suul azab"
  40,46,"Ennaru yuÂṀradune aleyha guduvvev ve asiyya ve yevme tekumus saatu edhÄḟlu ale firÂṀavne eseddel azab"
  40,47,"Ve iz yetehaccune fin nari fe yekulud duafau lillezÄḟnestekberu inna kunnu lekum tebean fe hel entum mugnune anna nasÄḟybem minen nar"
  40,48,"KalellezÄḟ nestekberu inna kullun fÄḟha innellahe kad hakeme beynel Äḟbad"
  40,49,"Ve kalellezÄḟne fin nari li hazeneti cehennemedÂṀu rabbekum yuhaffif anna yevmem minel azab"
  40,50,"Kalu eve lem teku teÂṀtÄḟkum rusulukum bil beyyinat kalu bela kalu fedÂṀ ve ma duaul kafirÄḟne illa fÄḟ dalal"
  40,51,"Inna henensuru rusulena vellezÄḟne amenu fil hayatid dunya ve yevme yekulul eshad"
  40,52,"Yevme la yenfeuz zalimÄḟne maÂṀziratuhum ve lehumul laÂṀnetu ve hehum suud dar"
  40,53,"Ve le kad ateyna musel huda ve evrasna benÄḟ israilel kitab"
  40,54,"Hudev ve zikra li ulil elbab"
  40,55,"Fasbir inne vaÂṀdellahi hakkuv vestagfir li zembike ve sebbÄḟh bi hamdi rabbike bil asiyyi vel ibkar"
  40,56,"InnellezÄḟne yucadilune fÄḟ ayatillahi bi gayri sultanin etahum in fÄḟ sudurihim illa kibrum ma hum bi baligÄḟyh festeÄḟz billah innehu huves semÄḟul besÄḟyr"
  40,57,"Le halkus semavati vel erdÄḟ ekberu min halkÄḟn nasi ve lakinne ekserannasi la yaÂṀlemun"
  40,58,"Ve ma yestevil aÂṀma vel besÄḟyru vellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati ve lel musiÂṀ kalÄḟlem ma tetezekkerun"
  40,59,"Innes saate le atiyetul la raybe fÄḟha ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yuÂṀminun"
  40,60,"Ve kale rabbukumudÂṀunÄḟ estecib lekum innellezÄḟne yestekbirune an ÄḟbatetÄḟ seyedhulune cehenneme dahÄḟrÄḟn"
  40,61,"AllahullezÄḟ ceale lekumul leyle li teskunu fÄḟhi ven nehara mubsÄḟra innellahe le zu fadlin alen nasi ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yeskurun"
  40,62,"Zalikumullahu rabbukum haliku kulli seyÂṀ la ilahe illa huve fe enna tuÂṀfekun"
  40,63,"Kezalike yuÂṀfekullezÄḟne kanu bi ayatillahi yechadun"
  40,64,"AllahullezÄḟ ceale lekumul erda kararav ves semae binaev ve savverakum fe ahsene suverakum ve razekakum minet tayyibat zalikumullahu rabbukam fe tebarakellahu rabbul alemÄḟn"
  40,65,"Huvel hayyu la ilahe illa huve fedÂṀuhu muhlisÄḟyne lehud dÄḟn elhamdu lillahi rabbil alemÄḟn"
  40,66,"Kul innÄḟ nuhÄḟtu en aÂṀbudellezÄḟne tedÂṀune min dunillahi lemma caeniyel beyyinatu mir rabbÄḟ ve umirtu en uslime li rabbil alemÄḟn"
  40,67,"HuvellezÄḟ halekakum min turabin summe min nutfetin summe min alekatin summe yuhricukum tÄḟflen summe li teblugu esuddekum summe li tekunu suyuha ve minkum mey yuteveffa min kablu ve li teblugu ecelem musemmev ve leallekum taÂṀkÄḟlun"
  40,68,"HuvellezÄḟ yuhyi ve yumÄḟt fe iza kada emran fe innema yekulu lehu kun fe yekun"
  40,69,"E lem tera ilellezÄḟne yucadilune fÄḟ ayatillah enna yusrafun"
  40,70,"EllezÄḟne kezzebu bil kitabi ve bima erselna bihÄḟ rusulena fe sevfe yaÂṀlemun"
  40,71,"Izil aglalu fÄḟ aÂṀnakÄḟhim ves selasil yushabun"
  40,72,"Fil hamÄḟmi summe fin nari yuscerun"
  40,73,"Summe kÄḟyle lehum eyne ma kuntum tusrikun"
  40,74,"Min dunillah kalu dallu anna bel lem nekun nedÂṀu min kablu seyÂṀa kezalike yudÄḟllullahul kafirÄḟn"
  40,75,"Zalikum bima kuntum tefrahune fil erdÄḟ bi gayril hakkÄḟ ve bima kuntum temrahun"
  40,76,"Udhulu ebvabe cehenneme halidÄḟne fÄḟha fe biÂṀse mesvel mutekebbirÄḟn"
  40,77,"Fasbir inne vaÂṀdellahi hakk fe imma nuriyenneke baÂṀdallezÄḟ neÄḟduhum ev neteveffeyenneke fe ileyna yurceun"
  40,78,"Ve le kad erselna rusulem min kablike minhum men kasasna aleyke ve minhum mel lem naksus aleyk ve ma kane li rasulin ey yeÂṀtiye bi ayetin illa bi iznillah fe iza cae emrallahi kudiye bil hakkÄḟ ve hasira hunalikel mubtÄḟlun"
  40,79,"AllahullezÄḟ ceale lekumul enÂṀame li terkebu minha ve minha teÂṀkulun"
  40,80,"Ve lekum fiha menafiu ve li teblugu aleyha haceten fÄḟ sudurikum ve aleyha ve alel fulki tuhmelun"
  40,81,"Ve yurÄḟkum ayatihÄḟ fe eyye ayatillahi tunkirun"
  40,82,"E fe lem yesÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fe yenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetullezÄḟne min kablihim kanu eksera minhum ve esedde kuvvetev ve asaran fil erdÄḟ fe ma agna anhum ma kanu yeksibun"
  40,83,"Felemma caethum rusuluhum bil beyyinati ferihu bima Äḟndehum minel Äḟlmi ve haka biham ma kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  40,84,"Felemma raev beÂṀsena kalu amenna billahi vahdehu ve kefarna bima kunna bihÄḟ musrikÄḟn"
  40,85,"Fe lem yeku yenfeuhum Äḟmanuhum lemma raev beÂṀsena sunnetellahiletÄḟ kad halet fÄḟ Äḟbadih ve hasira hunalikel kafirun"
  41,7,"EllezÄḟne la yuÂṀtunez zekate ve hum bil ahÄḟrati hum kafirun"
  41,8,"InnellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati lehum ecrun gayru memnun"
  41,9,"Kul e innekum le tekfurune billezÄḟ halekal erda fÄḟ yevmeyni ve tecÂṀalune lehu endada zalike rabbul alemÄḟn"
  41,10,"Ve ceale fÄḟha ravasiye min fevkÄḟha ve barake fÄḟha ve kaddera fÄḟha akvateha fÄḟ erbeati eyyam sevael lis sailÄḟn"
  41,11,"Summesteva iles semai ve hiye duhanun fe kale leha ve lil erdÄḟÂṀtiya tavÂṀan ev kerha kaleta eteyna taiÄḟyn"
  41,12,"Fe kadahunne sebÂṀa semavatin fÄḟ yevmeyni ve evha fÄḟ kulli semain emraha ve zeyyennes semaed dunya bi mesabÄḟha ve hÄḟfza zalike takdÄḟrul azÄḟzil alÄḟm"
  41,13,"Fe in aÂṀradu fe kul enzertukum saÄḟkatem misle saÄḟkati adiv ve semud"
  41,14,"Iz caethumur rusulu mim beyni iydÄḟhim ve min halfihim ella taÂṀbudu illellah kalu lev sae rabbuna le enzele melaiketen fe inna bima ursiltum bihÄḟ kafirun"
  41,15,"Fe emma adun festekberu fil erdÄḟ bi gayril hakkÄḟ ve kalu men eseddu minna kuvveh e ve lem yerav ennellahellezÄḟ halekahum huve eseddu minhum kuvveh kanu bi ayatina yechadun"
  41,16,"Fe erselna aleyhim rÄḟhan sarsaran fÄḟ eyyamin nehÄḟsatil li nuzÄḟkahum azabel hÄḟzyi fil hayatid dunya ve leazabul ahÄḟrati ahza ve hum la yunsarun"
  41,17,"Ve emma semudu fe hedeynahum saÄḟkatul azabil huni bima kanu yeksibun"
  41,18,"Ve necceynellezÄḟne amenu ve kanu yettekun"
  41,19,"Ve yevme yuhseru aÂṀdaullahi ilen nari fe hum yuzeun"
  41,20,"Hatta iza ma cauha sehide aleyhim semÂṀuhum ve ebsaruhum ve culuduhum bima kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  41,21,"Ve kalu li cuhudihim lime sehidtum aleyna kalu entaknellahullezÄḟ entaka kulle seyÂṀiv ve huve halekakum evvele merrativ ve ileyhi turceun"
  41,22,"Ve ma kuntum testetirune ey yeshede aleykum semÂṀukum ve la ebsarukum ve la culudukum ve lakin zanentum ennellahe la yaÂṀlemu kesÄḟram mimma taÂṀmelun"
  41,23,"Ve zalikum zannukumullezÄḟ zanentum bi rabbikum erdakum fe asbahtum minel hasirÄḟn"
  41,24,"Fe iy yasbiru fen naru mesvel lehum ve iy yestaÂṀtibu femahum minel muÂṀtebÄḟn"
  41,25,"Ve kayyadna lehum kuranae fezeyyenu lehum ma beyne eydÄḟhim ve ma halfehum ve hakka aleyhimul kavlu fÄḟ umemin kad halet min kablihim minel cinni vel ins innehum kanu hasirÄḟn"
  41,26,"Ve kalellezÄḟne keferu la tesmeu li hazel kurÂṀani velgav fÄḟhi leallekum taglibun"
  41,27,"Fe lenuzÄḟkannellezÄḟne keferu azaben sedÄḟdev ve lenecziyennehum esveellezÄḟ kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  41,28,"Zalike ceazu aÂṀdaillahin nar lehum fÄḟha darul huld cezaem bima kanu bi ayatina yechadun"
  41,29,"Ve kalellezÄḟne keferu rabbena erinellezeyni edallana minel cinni vel insi necÂṀalhuma tahte akdamina li yekuna minel esfelÄḟn"
  41,30,"InnellezÄḟne kalu rabbunellahu summestekamu tetenezzelu aleyhimul melaiketu ella tehafu ve la tehzenu ve ebsiru bil cennetilletÄḟ kuntum tuadun"
  41,31,"Nahnu evliyaukum fil hayatid dunya ve fil ahÄḟrah ve lekum fÄḟha ma testehÄḟ enfusukum ve lekum fÄḟha ma teddeun"
  41,32,"Nuzulem min gafurir rahÄḟym"
  41,33,"Ve men ahsenu kavlem mimmen dea ilellahi ve amile salihav ve kale innenÄḟ minel muslimÄḟn"
  41,34,"Ve la testevil hasenetu ve les seyyieh idfaÂṀ billetÄḟ hiye ahsenu fe izellezÄḟ beyneke ve beynehu adavetun keennehu veliyyun hamÄḟm"
  41,35,"Ve ma yulekkaha illellezÄḟne saberu ve ma yulekkaha illa zu hazzÄḟn azÄḟym"
  41,36,"Ve imma yenzeganneke mines seytani nezgun festeÄḟz billah innehu huves semÄḟul alÄḟm"
  41,37,"Ve min ayatihil leylu ven neharu ves semsu vel kamer la tescudu lis semsi ve la lil kameri vescudu lillahillezÄḟ halekahunne in kuntum iyyahu taÂṀbudun"
  41,38,"Fe inistekberu fellezÄḟne Äḟnde rabbike yusebbihune lehu bil leyli ven nehari ve hum la yesÂṀemun (37. Ayet secde ayetidir)"
  41,39,"Ve min ayatihÄḟ enneke teral erda hasiaten fe iza enzelna aleyhel maehtezzet ve rabet innellezÄḟ ahyaha le muhyil mevta innehu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  41,40,"InnellezÄḟne yulhÄḟdune fÄḟ ayatina la yahfevne aleyna e fe mey yulka fin nari hayrun em mey yeÂṀti aminey yevmel kÄḟyameh ÄḟÂṀmelu ma siÂṀtum innehu bima taÂṀmelune basÄḟyr"
  41,41,"InnellezÄḟne keferu biz zikri lemma caehum ve innehu le kitabun azÄḟz"
  41,42,"La yeÂṀtÄḟhil batÄḟlu mim beyni yedeyhi ve la min halfih tenzÄḟlum min hakÄḟmin hamÄḟd"
  41,43,"Ma yukalu leke illa ma kad kÄḟyle lir rusuli min kablik inne rabbeke lezu magfirativ ve zu Äḟkabin elim"
  41,44,"Ve lev cealnahu kurÂṀanen aÂṀcemiyyuv ve arabiyy kul huve lillezÄḟne amenu hudev ve sifaÂṀ vellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune fÄḟ azanihim vakruv ve huve aleyhim ama ulaike yunadevne mim mekanim beÄḟyd"
  41,45,"Ve le kad ateyna musel kitabe fahtulife fÄḟh ve lev la kelimetun sebekat mir rabbike le kudÄḟye beynehum ve innehum lefÄḟ sekkim minhu murÄḟb"
  41,46,"Men amile salihan fe li nefsihÄḟ ve men esae fe aleyha ve ma rabbuke bi zallamil lil abÄḟd"
  41,47,"Ileyhi yuraddu Äḟlmus saah ve ma tahrucu min semeratum min ekmamiha ve ma tahmilu min unsa ve la tedau illa biÄḟlmih ve yevme yunadÄḟhim eyne surakaÄḟ kalu azennake ma minna min sehÄḟd"
  41,48,"Ve dalle anhum ma kanu yedÂṀune min kablu ve zannu ma lehum mim mehÄḟys"
  41,49,"La yesÂṀemul insanu min duail hayri ve im messehus serru fe yeusun kanut"
  41,50,"Ve lein ezaknahu rahmetem minna mim baÂṀdi darrae messethu le yekulenne haza lÄḟ ve ma ezunnus saate kaimetev ve heir rucÄḟÂṀtu ila rabbi inne lÄḟ Äḟndehu lel husna fe le munebbiennellezÄḟne keferu bima amilu ve le nuzÄḟkannehum min azibn galÄḟyz"
  41,51,"Ve iza enÂṀamna alel insani aÂṀrada ve nea bicanibih ve iza messehus serru fe zu duain arÄḟyd"
  41,52,"Kul eraeytum in kane min Äḟndillahi summe kefertum bihÄḟ men edallu mimmen huve fÄḟ sikakÄḟm beÄḟyd"
  41,53,"SenurÄḟhim ayatina fil afakÄḟ ve fÄḟ enfusihum hatta yetebeyyene lehum ennehul hakk e ve lem yekfi bi rabbike ennehu ala kulli seyÂṀin sehÄḟd"
  41,54,"E la innehum fÄḟ miryetim mil likai rabbihim e la innehu bi kulli seyÂṀim muhÄḟyt"
  42,7,"Ve kezalike evhayna ileyke kurÂṀanen arabiyyel li tunzira ummel kura ve men havleha ve tunzira yevmel cemÂṀÄḟ la raybe fÄḟl ferÄḟkun fil cenneti ve ferÄḟkun fis seÄḟyr"
  42,8,"Ve lev saellahu le cealehum ummetev vahÄḟdetev ve lakiy yudhÄḟlu mey yesau fÄḟ rahmetih vezzalimune ma lehum miv veliyyiv ve la nesÄḟyr"
  42,9,"Emittehazu min dunihÄḟ evliyaÂṀ fellahu huvel veliyyu ve huve yuhyil mevta ve huve ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  42,10,"Ve mahteleftum fÄḟhi min seyÂṀin fe hukmuhu ilellah zalikumullahu rabbÄḟ aleyhi tevekkeltu ve ileyhi unÄḟb"
  42,11,"FatÄḟrus semavati vel ard ceale lekum min enfusikum ezvacev ve minel enÂṀami ezvaca yezraukum fÄḟh leyse ke mislihÄḟ seyÂṀ ve huves semÄḟul besÄḟyr"
  42,12,"Lehu mekalÄḟdus semavati vel ard yebsutur riska li mey yesau ve yakdir innehu bikulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  42,13,"Seraa lekum mined dÄḟni ma vessa bihÄḟ nuhav vellezÄḟ evhayna ileyke ve ma vessayna bihÄḟ ibrahÄḟme ve musa ve Äḟysa en ekÄḟymud dÄḟne ve la teteferraku fÄḟh kebura alel musrikÄḟne ma tedÂṀuhum ileyh allahu yectebÄḟ ileyhi mey yesau ve yehdÄḟ ileyhi mey yunÄḟb"
  42,14,"Ve ma teferraku illa mim baÂṀdi ma caehumul Äḟlmu bagyem beynehum ve lev la kelimetun sebkat mir rabbike ila ecelim musemmel le kudiye beynehum ve lev la kelimetun sebekat mir rabbike ila ecelim musemmel le kudÄḟye beynehum ve innellezÄḟne urisul kitabe mim baÂṀdihim lefÄḟ sekkim minhu murÄḟb"
  42,15,"Fe li zalike fedÂṀu vestekÄḟm kema umirt ve la tettebÄḟÂṀ ehvaehum ve kul amentu bima enzelellahu min kitab ve umirtu li aÂṀdile beynekum allahu rabbuna ve rabbukum lena aÂṀmaluna ve lekum aÂṀmalukum la huccete beynena ve beynekum allahu yecmeu beynena ve ileyhil mesÄḟyr"
  42,16,"VellezÄḟne yuhaccune fillahi mim baÂṀdi mestucÄḟbe lehu huccetuhum dahÄḟdatun Äḟnde rabbihim ve aleyhim gadabuv ve lehum azabun sedÄḟd"
  42,17,"AllahullezÄḟ enzelel kitabe bil hakkÄḟ vel mÄḟzan ve ma yudrÄḟke lealles saate karÄḟb"
  42,18,"YestaÂṀcilu bihellezÄḟne la yuÂṀminune biha vellezÄḟne amenu musfikune minha ve yaÂṀlemune ennehel hakk e la innellezÄḟne yumarune fis saati lefÄḟ dalalim beÄḟyd"
  42,19,"Allahu latÄḟyfum bi ÄḟbadihÄḟ yerzuku mey yesaÂṀ ve huvel kaviyyul azÄḟz"
  42,20,"Men kane yurÄḟdu harsel ahÄḟrati nezid lehu fÄḟ harsih ve men kane yurÄḟdu harsed dunya nuÂṀtihÄḟ minha ve ma lehu fil ahÄḟrati min nesÄḟyb"
  42,21,"Em lehum surakau serau lehum mined dÄḟni ma lem yeÂṀzem bihillah ve lev la kelimetul fasli le kudÄḟye beynehum ve innez zalimÄḟne lehum azabun elÄḟm"
  42,22,"Teraz zalimÄḟne musfikÄḟyne mimma kesebu ve huve vakÄḟum bihim vellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati fÄḟ ravdatil cennat lehum ma yesaune Äḟnde rabbihim zalike huvel fadlull kebÄḟr"
  42,23,"ZalikellezÄḟ yubbessirullahu ÄḟbadehullezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihat kul la esÂṀelukum aleyhi ecran illel mevededdete fil kurba ve mey yakterif haseneten nezid lehu fÄḟha husna innellahe gafurun sekur"
  42,24,"Em yekuluneftera alellahi keziba fe iy yeseillahu yahtim ala kalbik ve yemhullahul batÄḟle ve yuhÄḟkkul hakka bi kelimatih innehu alÄḟmum bizatis sudur"
  42,25,"Ve huvellezÄḟ yakbelut tevbete an ÄḟbadihÄḟ ve yaÂṀfu anis seyyiati ve yaÂṀlemu ma tefalun"
  42,26,"Ve yestecÄḟbullezÄḟne amenu ve amilu salihati ve yezÄḟduhum min fadlih vel kafirune lehum azabun sedÄḟd"
  42,27,"Ve lev besetallahur rizka li ÄḟbadihÄḟ le begav fil erdÄḟ ve lakiy yunezzilu bi kaderim ma yesaÂṀ innehu bi ÄḟbadihÄḟ habÄḟrum besÄḟyr"
  42,28,"Ve huvellezÄḟ yunezzilul gayse mim baÂṀdi ma kanetu ve yensuru rahmeteh ve huvel veliyyul hamÄḟd"
  42,29,"Ve min ayatihÄḟ halkus semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ma besse fÄḟhima min dabbeh ve huve ala cemÂṀÄḟhim iza yesau kadÄḟr"
  42,30,"Ve ma esabekum mim musÄḟybetin fe bima kesebet eydÄḟkum ve yaÂṀfu an kesÄḟr"
  42,31,"Ve ma entum bi muÂṀcizÄḟne fil ard ve ma lekum min dunillahi miv veliyyiv ve la nasÄḟyr"
  42,32,"Ve min ayatihil cevari fil bahri kel aÂṀlam"
  42,33,"Iy yeseÂṀyuskinir rÄḟha fe yazlelne ravakide ala zahril inne fÄḟ zalike le ayatil li kulli sabbarin sekur"
  42,34,"Ev yubÄḟkhunne bima kesebu ve yaÂṀfu an kesÄḟr"
  42,35,"Ve yaÂṀlemellezÄḟne yucadilune fÄḟ ayatina ma lehum mim mehÄḟys"
  42,36,"Fe ma utÄḟtum min seyÂṀin fe metaul hayatid odunya ve ma Äḟndellahi hayruv ve ebka lillezÄḟe amenu ve ala rabbihim yetevekkelun"
  42,37,"VellezÄḟne yectenibune kebairal ismi vel fevahÄḟse ve iza ma gadÄḟbu hum yagfirun"
  42,38,"VellezÄḟnestecabu li rabbihim ve ekamus salate ve emruhum sura beynehum ve mimma razaknahum yunfikun"
  42,39,"Vellezine iza esabehumul bagyu hum yentesÄḟrun"
  42,40,"Ve cezau seyyietin seyyietum misluha fe men afa ve asleha fe ecruhu alellah innehu la yuhÄḟbbuz zalimÄḟn"
  42,41,"Ve lemenintesara baÂṀde zulmihÄḟ fe ulaike ma aleyhim min sebÄḟl"
  42,42,"Innemes sebÄḟlu alellezÄḟne yazlimunen nase ve yebgune fil erdÄḟ bi gayril hakk ulaike lehum azabÄḟun elÄḟm"
  42,43,"Ve le men sabera ve gafera inne zalike le min azmil umur"
  42,44,"Ve mey yudlililahu fe ma lehu miv veliyyim mim baÂṀdih ve teraz zalimÄḟne lemma raevul azabe yekulune hel ila meraddim min sebÄḟl"
  42,45,"Ve terahum yuÂṀradune aleyha hasiÄḟyne minez zulli yenzurune min tarfin hafiyy ve kalellezÄḟne amenu innel hasirÄḟnellezÄḟne hasiru enfusehum ve ehlÄḟhim yevmel kÄḟyameh e la innez zalimÄḟne fÄḟ azabim mukÄḟym"
  42,46,"Ve ma kane lehum min evliyae yensurunehum min dunillah ve mey yudlilillahu fe ma lehu min sebÄḟl"
  42,47,"IstecÄḟbu li rabbikum min kabli ey yeÂṀtiye yevmul la meradde lehu minellah ma lekum mim melceiy yevmeiziv ve ma lekum min nekÄḟr"
  42,48,"Fe in aÂṀradu fema erselnake aleyhim hafÄḟza in aleyke illel belag ve inna iza ezaknel insane minna rahmetenk feriha biha ve in tusÄḟbhum seyyietum bima kaddemet eydÄḟhim fe innel insane kefur"
  42,49,"Lillahi mulkus semavati vel ard yahluku ma yesaÂṀ yehebu li mey yesau inasev ve yehebu li mey yesauz zukur"
  42,50,"Ev yuzevvicuhum zukranev ve inasa ve yecÂṀalu mey yesau akÄḟyma innehu alÄḟmun kadÄḟr"
  42,51,"Ve ma kane li beserin ey yukellimehullahu illa vahyen ev miv verai hÄḟcabin ev yurile rasulen fe yuhÄḟye bi iznihÄḟ ma yesaÂṀ innehu aliyyun hakÄḟm"
  42,52,"Ve kezalike evhayna ileyke ruham min emrina ma kunte tedrÄḟ mel kitabu ve lel Äḟmanu ve lakin cealnahu nuran nehdÄḟ bihÄḟ men nesau min Äḟbadina ve inneke le tehdÄḟ ila sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  42,53,"SÄḟratÄḟllahÄḟllezÄḟ lehu ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard e la ilellahi tesÄḟyrul umur"
  43,7,"Ve ma yetÂṀtÄḟhim min nebiyyin illa kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  43,8,"Fe ehlekna esedde minhum batsev ve meda meselul evvelÄḟn"
  43,9,"Ve lein seeltehum men halekas semavati vel erda le yekulunne halekahunnel azÄḟzul alÄḟm"
  43,10,"EllezÄḟ ceale lekumul erda mehdev ve veale lekum fÄḟha subulel leallekum tehtedun"
  43,11,"VellezÄḟ nezzele mines semai maem bi kader fe ensarna bihÄḟ beldetem meyta kezalike tuhracun"
  43,12,"VellezÄḟ halekal ezvace kulleha ve ceale lekum minel fulki vel enÂṀami ma terkebun"
  43,13,"Li testevu ala zuhurihÄḟ summe tezkuru nÄḟÂṀmete rabbikum izesteveytum aleyhi ve tekulu subhanellezÄḟ sehhara lena haza ve ma kunna lehu mukrinÄḟn"
  43,14,"Ve inna ila rabbina le munkalibun"
  43,15,"Ve cealu lehu min ÄḟbadihÄḟ cuzÂṀa innel insane le kefurum mubÄḟn"
  43,16,"Emittehaze memma yahluku benativ ve asfakum bil benÄḟn"
  43,17,"Ve iza bussira ehaduhum bima darabe lir rahmani meselen zalle vechuhu musveddev ve huze kezÄḟym"
  43,18,"E ve mey yunesseu fil hÄḟlyeti ve huve fil hÄḟsami gayrumubÄḟn"
  43,19,"Ve cealul melaiketellezÄḟne hum Äḟbadur rahmani inasa e sehidu halkahum setuktebu sehadetuhum ve yusÂṀelun"
  43,20,"Ve kalu lev saer rahmanu ma abednahum ma lehum bi zalike min Äḟlmin in hum illa yahrusun"
  43,21,"Em ateynahum kitabem min kablihÄḟ fe hum bihÄḟ mustemsikun"
  43,22,"Bel kalu inna vecedna abaena ala ummetiv ve inna ala asarihim muhtedun"
  43,23,"Ve kezalike ma erselna min kablike fÄḟ karyetim min nezÄḟrin illa kale mutrafuha inna vecedna abaena ala ummetiv ve inna ala asarihim muktedun"
  43,24,"Kale e ve lev ciÂṀtukum bi ehda mimma vecedtum aleyhi abaekum kalu inna bima ursiltum bihÄḟ kafirun"
  43,25,"Fentekamna mihum fenzur keyfe kane akÄḟbetul mukezzibÄḟn"
  43,26,"Ve iz kale ibrahÄḟmu li ebÄḟhi ve kavmihÄḟ innenÄḟ beraum mimma taÂṀbudun"
  43,27,"IllellezÄḟ fetaranÄḟ fe innehu seyehdÄḟn"
  43,28,"Ve cealeha kelimetem bakÄḟyeten fÄḟ akÄḟbihÄḟ leallehum yarciun"
  43,29,"Vel mettaÂṀtu haulai ve abaehum hatta caehumul hakku ve rasulum mubÄḟn"
  43,30,"Ve lemma caehumul hakku kalu haza sÄḟhruv ve inna bihÄḟ kafirun"
  43,31,"Ve kalu lev la nuzzile hazel kurÂṀanu ala raculim minel karyeteyni azÄḟym"
  43,32,"E hum yaksimune rahmete rabbik nahnu kasemna beynahum meÄḟysetehum fil hayatid dunya ve rafaÂṀna baÂṀdahum fevka baÂṀdÄḟn deracatil li yettehÄḟze baÂṀduhum baÂṀdan suhriyya ve rahmetu rabbike hayrum mimma yecmeun"
  43,33,"Ve lev la ey yekunen nasu ummetev vahÄḟdetel le cealna li mey yekfuru bir rahmani li buyutihim sukufem min fiddativ ve mearice aleyha yazherun"
  43,34,"Ve li buyutihim ebvabev ve sururan aleyha yettekiun"
  43,35,"Ve zuhrufa ve in kullu zalike lemma metaul haytiod dunya vel ahÄḟratu Äḟnde rabbike lil muttekÄḟyn"
  43,36,"Ve mey yaÂṀsu an zikrir rahmani nukayyÄḟd lehu seytanen fe huve lehu karÄḟn"
  43,37,"Ve innehum le yesuddunehum anis sebÄḟli ve yahsebune ennehum anis sebÄḟli ve yahsebune ennehum muhtedun"
  43,38,"Hatta iza caena kale ya leyte beynÄḟ ve beyneke buÂṀdel mesrikayni fe biÂṀsel karÄḟn"
  43,39,"Ve ley yenfeakumul yevme iz zalemtum ennekum fil azabe musterikun"
  43,40,"E fe ente tusmius summe ev tehdil umye ve men kane fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  43,41,"Fe imma nezhebenne bike fe inna minhum muntekÄḟmun"
  43,42,"Ev nuriyenne kellezÄḟ veadnahum fe inna aleyhim muktedoirun"
  43,43,"Festemsik billezÄḟ uhÄḟye ileyk inneke ala sÄḟratÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  43,44,"Ve innehu lezikrul leke ve li kavmik ve sevfe tusÂṀelun"
  43,45,"VesÂṀel men erselna min kablike mir rusulina e cealna min dunir rahmani alihetey yuÂṀbedun"
  43,46,"Ve le kad erselna musa bi ayatina ila firÂṀavne ve meleihÄḟ fe kale inni rasulu rabbil alemÄḟn"
  43,47,"Felemma caehum bi ayatina iza hum minha yadhakun"
  43,48,"Ve ma nurÄḟhim min ayetin illa hiye ekberu min uhtiha ve ehaznahum bil azabi leallehum yarciun"
  43,49,"Ve kalu ya eyyuhes sahÄḟrudÂṀu lena rabbeke bima ahide Äḟndeke innena le muhtedun"
  43,50,"Felemma kesefna anhumul azabe izahum yenkusun"
  43,51,"Ve nada firÂṀavnu fÄḟ kamihÄḟ kale ya kavmi e leyse lÄḟ mulku mÄḟsra ve hazihil enharu tecrÄḟ min tahtÄḟ e fe la tubsÄḟrun"
  43,52,"Em ene hayrum min hazellezÄḟ huve mehÄḟnuv ve la yekadu yubÄḟn"
  43,53,"Fe lev la ulkÄḟye aleyhi esviratum min zehebin ev cae meahul melaiketu mukterinÄḟn"
  43,54,"Festehaffe kavmehu fe etauh innehum kanu kavmen fasikÄḟyn"
  43,55,"Felemma asefununtekamna minhum fe agraknahum ecmeÄḟyn"
  43,56,"Fe cealnahum selefev ve meselel lil ahÄḟrÄḟn"
  43,57,"Ve lemma duribebnu meryeme meselen iza kavmuke minhu yesÄḟddun"
  43,58,"Ve kalu e alihetuna hayrun em hu ma darabuhu leke illa cedela bel hum kavmun hasÄḟmun"
  43,59,"In huve illa abdun enÂṀamna aleyhi ve cealnahu meselel li benÄḟ israÄḟl"
  43,60,"Ve lev nesau le cealna minkum melaiketen fil erdÄḟ yahlufun"
  43,61,"Ve innehu le Äḟlmul lissaati fe la temterunne biha vettebiun haza sÄḟratum mustekÄḟym"
  43,62,"Ve la yesudodennekumus seytan innehu lekum aduvvun mubÄḟn"
  43,63,"Ve lemma cae Äḟysa bil beyyinati kale kad ciÂṀtukum bil hÄḟkmeti ve li ubeyyine lekum baÂṀdallezÄḟ tahtelifune fÄḟh fettekullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀun"
  43,64,"Innellahe huve rabbÄḟ ve rabbukum faÂṀbuduh haza sÄḟratum mustekÄḟym"
  43,65,"Fahtelefel ahzabu mim beynihim fe veylul lillezÄḟne zalemu min azabi yevmin elÄḟm"
  43,66,"Hel yenzurune illes saate en teÂṀtiyehum bagtetev ve hum la yesÂṀurun"
  43,67,"El ehÄḟllau yevmeizim baÂṀduhum li baÂṀdÄḟn aduvvun illel muttekÄḟyn"
  43,68,"Ya Äḟbadi la havfun aleykumul yevme ve la entum tanzenun"
  43,69,"EllezÄḟne amenu bi ayatina ve kanu muslimÄḟn"
  43,70,"Udhulul cennete entum ve ezvacukum tuhberun"
  43,71,"Yutafu aleyhim bi sÄḟhafim min zehebiv ve ekvab ve fÄḟha ma testehÄḟhil enfusu ve telezzul aÂṀyun ve entum fÄḟha halidun"
  43,72,"Ve tilkel cennetulletÄḟ uristumuha bima kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  43,73,"Lekum fiha fakihetun kesÄḟratum miha teÂṀkulun"
  43,74,"Innel mucrimÄḟne fÄḟ azabi cehenneme halidun"
  43,75,"La yufetteru anhum ve hum fÄḟhi mublisun"
  43,76,"Ve ma zalemnahum ve lakin kanu humuz zalimÄḟn"
  43,77,"Ve nadev ya maliku li yakdÄḟ aleyna rabbuk kale innekum makisun"
  43,78,"Lekad ciÂṀnakum bil hakkÄḟ ve lakinne ekserakum lil hakkÄḟ karihun"
  43,79,"Em ebramu emran fe inna mubrimun"
  43,80,"Em yahsebune enna la nesmeu sirrahum ve necvahum bela ve rusuluna ledeyhum yektubun"
  43,81,"Kul in kane lirrahmani veledun fe ene evvelul abidÄḟn"
  43,82,"Subhune rabbis semavati vel erdÄḟ rabbil arsi amma yesÄḟfun"
  43,83,"Fezerhum yahudu ve yelÂṀabu hatta yulaku yevmehumullezÄḟ yuadun"
  43,84,"Ve huvellezÄḟ fis semai ilahuv ve fil erdÄḟ ilah ve huvel hakÄḟmul alÄḟm"
  43,85,"Ve tebarakellezÄḟ lehu mulkus semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ma beynehuma ve Äḟndehu Äḟlmus saah ve ileyhi turceun"
  43,86,"Ve la yemlikullezÄḟne yedÂṀune min dunihis sefaate illa men sehide bil hakkÄḟ ve hum yaÂṀlemun"
  43,87,"Ve lein seeltehum men halekahum le yekulunnellahu fe enna yuÂṀfekun"
  43,88,"Ve kÄḟylihÄḟ ya rabbi inne haulai kavmul la yuÂṀminun"
  43,89,"Fasfah anhum ve kul selam fe sevfe yaÂṀlemun"
  44,6,"Rahmeten mir rabbik innehu huves semiyÂṀul aliym"
  44,7,"Rabbis semavati vel erdÄḟ ve ma beynehuma in kuntum mukÄḟniyn"
  44,8,"La ilahe illa huve yuhyÄḟ ve yumiyt rabbukum ve rabbu abaikumul evveliyn"
  44,9,"Bel hum fÄḟ sekkiy yelÂṀabun"
  44,10,"FertekÄḟb yevme teÂṀtis semau bi duhanim mubiyn"
  44,11,"Yagsen nas haza azabun eliym"
  44,12,"Rabbeneksif annel azabe inna muÂṀminun"
  44,13,"Enna lehumuz zikra ve kad caehum rasulum mubiyn"
  44,14,"Summe tevellev anhu ve kalu muallemum mecnun"
  44,15,"Inna kasiful azib kaliylen innekum aidun"
  44,16,"Yevme nebtÄḟsul batsetel kubra inna muntekÄḟmun"
  44,17,"Ve le kad fetenna kablehum kavme firÂṀavne ve caehum rasulun keriym"
  44,18,"En eddu ileyye Äḟbadellah inni lekum rasulun emiyn"
  44,19,"Ve el la taÂṀlu alellah innÄḟ atÄḟkum bi sultanim mubiyn"
  44,20,"Ve innÄḟ uztu bi rabbÄḟ ve rabbikum en tercumun"
  44,21,"Ve il lem tuÂṀminu lÄḟ faÂṀtezilun"
  44,22,"Fe dea rabbehu enne haulai kavmum mucrimun"
  44,23,"Fe esri bi ÄḟbadÄḟ leylen innekum muttebeun"
  44,24,"Vetrukil bahra rahva innehum cundum mugrakun"
  44,25,"Kem teraku min cennativ ve uyun"
  44,26,"Ve zuruÄḟv ve mekamin keriym"
  44,27,"Ve naÂṀmetin kanu fiyha fakihiyn"
  44,28,"Kezalike ve evrasnaha kavmen ahariyn"
  44,29,"Fema beket aleyhimus semau vel erdu vema kanu munzariyn"
  44,30,"Ve le kad necceyna benÄḟ israiyle minel azabil muhiyn"
  44,31,"Min firÂṀavn innehu kane aliyem minel musrifiyn"
  44,32,"Ve lekadÄḟhternahum ala Äḟlmin alel alemiyn"
  44,33,"Ve ateynahum minel ayati ma fÄḟhi belaum mubiyn"
  44,34,"Inne haulai le yekulun"
  44,35,"In hiye illa mevtetunel ula ve ma nahnu bi munseriyn"
  44,36,"FeÂṀtu bi abaina in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  44,37,"E hum hayrun em kamu tubbeÄḟv vellezÄḟne min kablihim ehleknahum innehum kanu mucrimiyn"
  44,38,"Ve ma halaknes semavati vel erda ve ma beynehuma laÄḟbiyn"
  44,39,"Ma halaknahuma illa bil hakkÄḟ ve lakinne ekserahum la yaÂṀlemun"
  44,40,"Inne yevmel fasli mÄḟkatuhum ecmeÄḟyn"
  44,41,"Yevme la yugni mevlen ammevlen seyÂṀev ve la hum yunsarun"
  44,42,"Illa mer rahÄḟmellah innehu huvel aziyzur rahÄḟym"
  44,43,"Inne seceratez zekkum"
  44,44,"Taamul esiym"
  44,45,"Kel muhl yaglÄḟ fil butun"
  44,46,"Ke galyil hamiym"
  44,47,"Huzuhu faÂṀtiluhu ila sevail cehÄḟym"
  44,48,"Summe subbu fevka raÂṀsihÄḟ min azabil hamiym"
  44,49,"Zuk inneke entel aziyzul keriym"
  44,50,"Inne haza ma kuntum bihÄḟ temterun"
  44,51,"Innel muttekÄḟyne fÄḟ mekamin emiyn"
  44,52,"Fi cennativ ve uyun"
  44,53,"Yelbesune min sundusiv ve istebrakÄḟm mutekabiliyn"
  44,54,"Kezali ve zevvecnahum bi hurin Äḟyn"
  44,55,"YedÂṀune fiha bi kulli fakihetin aminiyn"
  44,56,"La yezukune fiyhel mevte illel mevtetel ula ve vekahum azabel cehÄḟym"
  44,57,"Fadlem mir rabbik zalike huvel fevzul azÄḟym"
  44,58,"Fe innema yessernahu bi lisanike leallehum yetezekkerun"
  44,59,"FertekÄḟb innehum mirtek"
  45,6,"Tilke ayatullahi netluha aleyke bil hakk fe bi eyyi hadÄḟsim baÂṀdellahi ve ayatihÄḟ yuÂṀminun"
  45,7,"Veylul li kulli effakin esÄḟm"
  45,8,"Yesmeu ayatillahi tutla aleyhi summe yusÄḟrru mustekbiran ke el lem yesmaÂṀha fe bessirhu bi azabin elÄḟm"
  45,9,"Ve iza alime min ayatina seyÂṀenittehazeha huzuva ulaike lehum azabum muhÄḟn"
  45,10,"Miv veraihim cehennem ve la yugnÄḟ anhum ma kesebu seyÂṀev ve la mettehazu min dunillahi evliyaÂṀ ve lehum azabun azÄḟym"
  45,11,"Haza huda vellezÄḟne keferu bi ayati rabbihim lehum azabum mir riczin elÄḟm"
  45,12,"Allahullezi sehhara lekumul bahra li tecriyel fulku fÄḟhi bi emrihÄḟ ve li tebtegu min fadlihÄḟ ve leallekum teskurun"
  45,13,"Ve sehhara lekum ma fis semavati ve ma fil erdÄḟ cemÄḟam minh inne fi zalike le ayatil li kavmiy yetefekkerun"
  45,14,"Kul lillezÄḟne amenu yagfiru lillezÄḟne la yercune eyyamellahi li yecziye kavmem bima kanu yeksibun"
  45,15,"Men amile salihan fe linefsih ve men esae fe aleyha summe ila rabbikum turceun"
  45,16,"Ve le kad ateyna benÄḟ israÄḟlel kitabe vel hukme ven nubuvvete ve razaknahum minet tayyibati ve faddalnahum alel alemÄḟn"
  45,17,"Ve ateynahum beyyinatim minel emr femahtelefu illa mim baÂṀdi ma caehumul Äḟlmu bagyem beynehum inne rabbeke yakdÄḟy beynehum yevmel kÄḟyameti fÄḟma kanu fÄḟhi yahtelifun"
  45,18,"Summe cealnake ala sarÄḟatim minel emri fettebÄḟÂṀha ve la tettebÄḟÂṀ ehvaellezÄḟne la yaÂṀlemun"
  45,19,"Innehum ley yugnu anke minellahi seyÂṀa ve innez zalimÄḟne baÂṀduhum evliyau baÂṀd vallahu veliyyul muttekÄḟyn"
  45,20,"Haza besairu lin nasi ve hudev ve rahmetul li kavmiy yukÄḟnun"
  45,21,"Em hasibel lezÄḟnecterahus seyyiati en necÂṀalehum kellezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati sevaem mahyahum ve mematuhum sae ma yahkumun"
  45,22,"Ve halekallahus semavati vel erda bil hakkÄḟ ve li tucza kullu nefsim bima kesebet ve hum la yuzlemun"
  45,23,"Feraeyte menittehaze ilahehu hevahu ve edallehullahu ala Äḟlmiv ve hateme ala semÂṀÄḟhÄḟ ve kalbihÄḟ ve ceale ala besarihÄḟ gÄḟsaveh fe mey yehdÄḟhi mim baÂṀdillah e fe la tezekkerun"
  45,24,"Ve kalu ma hiye illa hayatuned dunya nemutu ve nahya ve ma yuhlikuna illed dehr ve ma lehum bi zalike min Äḟlm in hum illa yezunun"
  45,25,"Ve iza tutla aleyhim ayatuna beyyinatim ma kane huccetehum illa en kaluÂṀtu bi abaina in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  45,26,"Kullillahu yuhyÄḟkum summe yumÄḟtukum summe yecmeukum ila yevmil kÄḟyameti la raybe fÄḟhi ve lakinne ekseran nasi la yaÂṀlemun"
  45,27,"Ve lillahi mulkus semavati vel ard ve yevme tekumus saatu yevmeiziy yahserul mubtÄḟlun"
  45,28,"Ve tera kulle ummetin casiyeten kullu ummetin tudÂṀa ila kitabiha elyevme tuczevne ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  45,29,"Haza kitabuna yentÄḟku aleykum bil hakk inna kunna nestensihu ma kuntum taÂṀmelun"
  45,30,"Fe emmelzÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati fe yudhÄḟluhum rabbuhum fÄḟ rametih zalike huvel fevzul mubÄḟn"
  45,31,"Ve emmellezÄḟne keferu e fe lem tekun ayatÄḟ tutla aleykum festekbertum ve kuntum kavmen mucrimÄḟn"
  45,32,"Ve iza kÄḟyle inne vaÂṀdellahi hakkuv ves saatu la raybe fÄḟha kultum ma nedrÄḟ mes saatu in nezunnu illa zannev ve ma nahnu bi musteykÄḟnÄḟn"
  45,33,"Ve beda lehum seyyiatu ma amilu ve haka bihim ma kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  45,34,"Ve kÄḟylel yevme nensakum kema nesÄḟtum likae yevmikum haza ve meÂṀvakumun naru ve ma lekum min nasÄḟrÄḟn"
  45,35,"Zalikum bi ennekumuttehaztum ayatÄḟllahi huzuvev ve garratkumul hayatud dunya felyevme la yuhracune minha ve la hum yustaÂṀtebun"
  45,36,"Fe lillahil hamdu rabbis semavati ve rabbil erdÄḟ rabbil alemÄḟn"
  45,37,"Ve lehul kibriyau fis semavati vel erdÄḟ ve huvel azÄḟzul hakÄḟm"
  46,7,"Ve iza tutla aleyhim ayatuna beyyinatin kalellezÄḟne keferu lil hakkÄḟ lemma caehum haza sÄḟhrum mubÄḟn"
  46,8,"Em yekulunefterah kul inifteraytuhu fe la temlikune lÄḟ minellahi seyÂṀa huve aÂṀlemu bima tufÄḟdune fih kefa bihÄḟ sehÄḟdem beynÄḟ ve beynekum ve huvel gafurur rahÄḟym"
  46,9,"Kul ma kuntu bidÂṀam miner rusuli ve ma edrÄḟ ma yufahu bÄḟ ve la bikum in ettebiu illa ma yuha ileyye ve ma ene ila nezÄḟrum mubÄḟn"
  46,10,"Kul eraeytum in kane min Äḟndillahi ve kefartum bihÄḟ ve sehide sahidum mim benÄḟ israÄḟle ala mislihÄḟ fe amene vestekbertum innellahe la yehdil kavmez zalimÄḟn"
  46,11,"Ve kalellezÄḟne keferu lillezÄḟne amenu lev kane hayram ma sebekuna ileyh ve iz lem yehtedu bihÄḟ fe seyekulune haza ifkun kadÄḟm"
  46,12,"Ve min kablihÄḟ kitabu musa imamev ve rahmeh ve haza kitabum musaddikul lisanen arabiyyel li yunzirallezÄḟne zalemu ve busra lil muhsinÄḟn"
  46,13,"InnellezÄḟne kalu rabbunellahu summestekamu fe la havfun aleyhim ve la hum yahzenun"
  46,14,"Ulaike ashabul cenneti halidÄḟne fÄḟha cezaem bima kanu yaÂṀmelun"
  46,15,"Ve vessaynel insane bi valideyhi Äḟhsana hamelethu ummuhu kurhev ve vedaathu kurha ve hamluhu ve fisaluhu selasune sehra hatta iza belega esuddehu ve belga erbeÄḟyne seneten kale rabbi evzÄḟÂṀnÄḟ en eskura nÄḟÂṀmetekelletÄḟ enÂṀamte aleyye ve ala valedeyye ve en aÂṀmele salihan terdahu ve aslÄḟh lÄḟ fÄḟ zurriyyetÄḟ innÄḟ tubtu ileyke ve innÄḟ minel muslimÄḟn"
  46,16,"UlaikellezÄḟne netekabbelu anhum ahsene ma amilu ve netecavezu an seyyiatihim fÄḟ ashabil cenneh vaÂṀdes sÄḟdkÄḟllezÄḟ kanu yuadun"
  46,17,"VellezÄḟ kale li valideyhi uffil lekuma e teÄḟdaninÄḟ en uhrace ve kad haletil kurunu min kablÄḟ ve huma yestegÄḟysanillahe veyleke amin inne vaÂṀdellahi hakk fe yekulu ma haza illa esatÄḟyrul evvelÄḟn"
  46,18,"UlaikellezÄḟne hakka aleyhimul kavlu fÄḟ umemin kad halet min kablihim minel cinni vel ins innehum kanu hasirÄḟn"
  46,19,"Ve li kullin derecatun mimma amilu ve li yuveffiyetuh eaÂṀ malehum ve hum la yuzlamu"
  46,20,"Ve yevme yuÂṀradullezÄḟne keferu alen nar ezhebtum tayyibatikum fÄḟ hayatikumud dunya vestemtaÂṀÂṀum biha fel yevme tuczevne azabel huni bima kuntum testekbirune fil erdÄḟ bi gayril hakkÄḟ ve bima kuntum tefsukun"
  46,21,"Vezkur eha ad iz enzera kavmehu bil ahkafi ve kad haletin nuzuru mim beyni yedeyhi ve min halfihÄḟ ella taÂṀbudu illellah innÄḟ ehafu aleykum azabe yevmin azÄḟym"
  46,22,"Kalu eciÂṀtena li teÂṀfikena an alihetina feÂṀtina bima teÄḟduna in kunte mines sadikÄḟyn"
  46,23,"Kale innemel ilmu Äḟndellahi ve ubelligukum ma ursiltu bihÄḟ ve lakinnÄḟ erakum kavmen techelun"
  46,24,"Felemma raevhu aridam mustakbile evdiyetihim kalu haza aridum muntÄḟruna bel huve mestaÂṀceltum bih rÄḟhun fÄḟha azabun elÄḟm"
  46,25,"Tudemmiru kulle seyÂṀim bi emri rabbiha fe asbehu la yura illa mesakinuhum kezalike neczil kavmel mucrimÄḟn"
  46,26,"Ve le kad mekkennahum fÄḟma im mekkennakum fÄḟhi ve cealna lehum semÂṀav ve ebzarav ve efideten fe ma agna anhum semÂṀuhum ve la ebsaruhum ve la efidetuhum min seyÂṀin iz kanu yechadune bi ayatillahi ve haka bihim ma kanu bihÄḟ yestehziun"
  46,27,"Ve le kad ehlekna ma havlekum minel kura ve sarrafnel ayati leallehum yarciun"
  46,28,"Fe lev la nesarahumlezÄḟnettehazu min dunillahi kurbanen aliheh bel dallu anhum ve zalike ifkuhum ve ma kanu yefterun"
  46,29,"Ve iz sarafna ileyke neferam minel cinni yestemiunel kurÂṀan felemma hadaruhu kalu ensÄḟtu felemma kudÄḟye vellev ila kavmihim munzirÄḟn"
  46,30,"Kalu ya kevmena inna semÄḟÂṀna kitaben unzile min baÂṀdi musa musaddikal lima beyne yedeyhi yehdÄḟ ilel hakkÄḟ ve ila tarÄḟkÄḟm mustekÄḟym"
  46,31,"Ya kavmena ecÄḟbu daÄḟyellahi ve aminu bihÄḟ yagfir lekum min zunubikum ve yucirkum min azabin elÄḟm"
  46,32,"Ve mel la yucib daÄḟyellahi fe leyse bi buÂṀcizin fil erdÄḟ ve leyse lehu min dunihÄḟ evliyaÂṀ ulaike fÄḟ dalalim mubÄḟn"
  46,33,"E ve lem yerav ennellahellezÄḟ halekas semavati vel erda ve lem yaÂṀye bi halkÄḟhinne bi kadirin ala ey yuhyiyel mevta bela innehu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟr"
  46,34,"Ve yevme yuÂṀradullezÄḟne keferu alen nar leyse haza bil hakk kalu bela ve rabbinakale fe zukul azabe bi ma kuntum tekfurun"
  46,35,"Fasbir kema sabera ulul azmi miner rusuli ve la testaÂṀcil lehum ke ennehum yevme yeravne ma yuadune lem yelbesu illa saatem min nehar belag fe hel yuhleku illel kavmul fasikun"
  47,5,"Se yehdÄḟhim ve yuslihu balehum"
  47,6,"Ve yudhÄḟluhumul cennete arrafeha lehum"
  47,7,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu in tensurullahe yensurkum ve yusebbit akdamekum"
  47,8,"VellezÄḟne keferu fe taÂṀsel lehum ve edalle aÂṀmalehum"
  47,9,"Zalike bi ennehum kerihu ma enzelellahu fe ahbeta aÂṀmalehum"
  47,10,"E fe lem yesÄḟru fil erdÄḟ fe yenzuru keyfe kane akÄḟbetullezÄḟne min kablihim demmerallahu aleyhim ve lil kafirÄḟne emsaluha"
  47,11,"Zalike bi ennellahe mevlellezÄḟne amenu ve ennel kafirÄḟne la mevla lehum"
  47,12,"Innellahe yudhÄḟlullezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enhar vellezÄḟne keferu yetemetteune ve yeÂṀkulune kema teÂṀkulul enÂṀamu ven naru mesvel lehum"
  47,13,"Ve keeyyum min karyetin hiye eseddu kuvvetem min karyetikelletÄḟ ahracetk ehleknahum fe la nasÄḟra lehum"
  47,14,"E fe men kane ala beyyinetim mir rabbihÄḟ ke men zuyyine lehu suu amelihÄḟ vettebeu ehvaehum"
  47,15,"Meselul cennetilletÄḟ vuÄḟdel muttekun FÄḟha enharum mim main gayri asin ve enharum mil lebenil lem yetegayyer taÂṀmuh ve enharum min hamril lezetil lis saribÄḟn ve enharum min aselim musaffa ve lehum fÄḟha min kullis semerati ve magfiratum mir rabbihim ke men huve halidun fin nari ve suku maen hamÄḟmen fe kattaa emÂṀaehum"
  47,16,"Ve minhum mey yestemiu ileyk hatta iza harecu min Äḟndike kalu lillezÄḟne utul Äḟlme maza kale anifen ulaikellezÄḟne tabeallahu ala kulubihim vettebeu ehvaehum"
  47,17,"VellezÄḟnehtedev zadehum hudev ve atahum takvahum"
  47,18,"Fe hel yenzurune illes saate en teÂṀtiyehum bagteh fe kad cae esratuha fe enna lehum iza caethum zikrahum"
  47,19,"FaÂṀlem ennehu la ilahe illellahu vestagfir li zembike ve lil muÂṀminÄḟne vel muÂṀminat vallahu yaÂṀlemu mutekallebekum ve mesvakum"
  47,20,"Ve yekulullezÄḟne amenu lev la nuzzilet surah fe iza unzilet suratum muhkemetuv ve zukira fÄḟhel kÄḟtalu raeytellezÄḟne fÄḟ kulubihim meraduy yenzurune ileyke nazaral magsiyyi aleyhi minel mevti fe evla lehum"
  47,21,"Taatuv ve kavlum maÂṀrufun fe iza azemel emru fe lev sadekullahe le kane hayral lehum"
  47,22,"Fe hel aseytum in tevelletum en tufsidu fil erdÄḟ ve tukattÄḟu erhamekum"
  47,23,"UlaikellezÄḟne leanehumullahu fe esammehum ve aÂṀma ebsarahum"
  47,24,"E fe la yetedebberunel kurÂṀane em ala kulubin akfaluha"
  47,25,"InnellezÄḟner teddu ala edbarihim min baÂṀdi ma tebeyyene lehumul hudes seytanu sevvele lehum ve emla lehum"
  47,26,"Zalike bi ennehum kalu lillezÄḟne kerihu ma nezzelellahu senutÄḟyÂṀukum fÄḟ baÂṀdÄḟl emr vallahu yaÂṀlemu israrahum"
  47,27,"Fe keyfe iza teveffethumul melaiketu yadribune vucuhehum ve edbarahum"
  47,28,"Zalike bi ennehumuttebeu ma eshatallahe ve kerihu rÄḟdvanehu fe ahbeta aÂṀmalehum"
  47,29,"Em hasibellezÄḟne fÄḟ kulubihim meradun el ley yuhricellahu adganehum"
  47,30,"Ve lev nesau le eraynakehum fe learaftehum bisÄḟmahum ve le taÂṀrifennehum fÄḟ lahnil kavl vallahu yaÂṀlemu aÂṀmalekum"
  47,31,"Ve le nebluvennekum hatta naÂṀlemel mucahidÄḟne minkum vessabirÄḟne ve nebluve ahbarakum"
  47,32,"InnellezÄḟne keferu ve saddu an sebÄḟlillahi ve sakkur rasule mim baÂṀdi ma tebeyyene lehumul huda ley yedurrullahe seyÂṀa ve seyuhbitu aÂṀmalehum"
  47,33,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu etÄḟyÂṀullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀur rasule ve la tubtÄḟlu aÂṀmalekum"
  47,34,"InnellezÄḟne keferu ve saddu an sebÄḟlallahi summe matu ve hum kuffarun fe ley yagfirallahu lehum"
  47,35,"Fe la tehinu ve tedÂṀu ilis selmi ve entumul aÂṀlevne vallahu meakum ve ley yetirakum aÂṀmalekum"
  47,36,"Innemel hayatud dunya leÄḟbuv ve lehv ve in tuÂṀminu ve tetteku yuÂṀtikum ucurakum ve la yesÂṀelkum emvalekum"
  47,37,"Iy yesÂṀelkumuha fe yuhfikum tebhalu ve yuhric adganekum"
  47,38,"Ha entum haulai tudÂṀavne li tunfiku fÄḟ sebÄḟlillah fe minkum mey yebhal vallahul ganiyyu ve entumul fukaraÂṀ ve in tetevellev yestebdil kavmen gayrakum summe la yekunu emsalekum"
  48,6,"Ve yuazzibel munafikÄḟyne vel munafikati vel musrikÄḟne vel musrikatiz zannÄḟne billahi zannez sevÂṀ aleyhim dairatus sevÂṀ ve gadÄḟbellahu aleyhim ve leanehum ve eadde lehum cehennem ve saet masÄḟyra"
  48,7,"Ve lillahi cunudus semavati vel ard ve kanellahu azÄḟzen hakÄḟma"
  48,8,"Inna erselnake sahidev ve mubessirav ve nezÄḟra"
  48,9,"Li tuÂṀminu billahi ve rasulihi ve tuazziruhu ve tuvekkiruh ve tusebbihuhu bukreten ve ezÄḟyla"
  48,10,"InnellezÄḟne yubayiuneke innema yubayiunellah yedullahi fevka eydÄḟhim fe men nekese fe innema yenkusu ala nefsih ve men evfa bi ma ahede aleyhullahe fe se yuÂṀtÄḟhi ecran azÄḟyma"
  48,11,"Se yekulu lekel muhallefune minel aÂṀrabi segaletna emvaluna ve ehluna festagfir lena yekulune bi elsinetihim ma leyse fi kulubihim Kul fe mey yemliku lekum minellahi seyÂṀen in erade bikum darran ev erade bikum nefa bel kanellahu bima taÂṀmelune habÄḟra"
  48,12,"Bel zanentum el ley yenkaliber rasulu vel muÂṀminune ila ehlÄḟhim ebedev ve zuyyine zalike fÄḟ kulubikum ve zanentum zannes sevÂṀ ve kuntum kavmen bura"
  48,13,"Ve mel lem yu mim billahi ve rasulihÄḟ fe inna aÂṀtedna lil kafirÄḟne seÄḟyra"
  48,14,"Ve lillahi mulkus semavati vel ard yagfiru li mey yesau ve yuazzibu mey yesaÂṀ ve kanellahu gafurar rahÄḟyma"
  48,15,"Se yekulul muhallefune izen talaktum ila meganime li teÂṀhuzuha zeruna nettebÄḟÂṀkum yurÄḟdune ey yubeddilu kelamellah kul len tettebiuna kezalikum kalellahu min kabl fe se yekulune bel tahsudunena bel kanu la yefkahune illa kalÄḟla"
  48,16,"Kul lil muhallefÄḟne minel aÂṀrabi se tudÂṀavne ila kavmin ulÄḟ beÂṀsin sedÄḟdin tukatilunehum ev yuslimun fe in tutÄḟyÂṀu yuÂṀtikumullahu ecran hasena ve in tetevellev kema tevelleytum min kablu yuazzibkum azaben elÄḟma"
  48,17,"Leyse alel aÂṀma haracuv ve la alel aÂṀraci haracuv ve la alel meriydÄḟ harac ve mey yutÄḟÄḟlahe ve rasulehu yudhÄḟlhu cennatin tecrÄḟ min tahtihel enhar ve mey yetevelle yuazzibhu azaben elÄḟma"
  48,18,"Le kad radÄḟyallahu anil muÂṀminÄḟne iz yubayiuneke tahtes secerati fe alime ma fÄḟ kulubihim fe enzeles sekÄḟnete aleyhim ve esabehum fethan karÄḟba"
  48,19,"Ve meganime kesiraten yeÂhuzuneha ve kanallahu aziyzen hakiym"
  48,20,"Ve adekumullahu meganime kesiraten teÂṀhuzuneha fe accele lekum hazihÄḟ ve keffe eydiyen nasi ankum ve li tekune ayetel lil muÂṀminÄḟne ve yehdiyekum sÄḟratam mustekÄḟyma"
  48,21,"Ve uhra lem takdiru aleyha kad ehatallahu biha ve kanellahu ala kulli seyÂṀin kadÄḟra"
  48,22,"Ve lev katelekumullezÄḟne keferu le vellevul edbara summe la yecidune veliyyev ve la nesÄḟyra"
  48,23,"SunnetellahilletÄḟ kad halet min kabl Ve len tecide li sunnetillahi tebdÄḟla"
  48,24,"Ve huvellezÄḟ keffe eydiyehum ankum ve eydiyekum anhum bi batni mekkete mim baÂṀdi en azferakum aleyhim ve kanellahu bi ma taÂṀmelune basÄḟyra"
  48,25,"HumullezÄḟne keferu ve saddukum anil mescidil harami vel hedye maÂṀkufen ey yebluga mehÄḟlleh ve lev la ricalum muÂṀminune ve nisaum muÂṀminatul lem taÂṀlemuhum en tetauhum fe tusÄḟybekum minhum mearratum bi gayri Äḟlm li yudhÄḟlellahu fÄḟ rahmetihÄḟ mey yesaÂṀ lev tezeyyelu le azzebnellezÄḟne keferu minhum azaben elÄḟma"
  48,26,"Iz cealellezÄḟne keferu fi kulubihimul hamiyyete hameyyetel cahiliyyeti fe enzelellahu sekÄḟnetehu ala rasulihi ve alel muÂṀminÄḟne ve elzemehum kelimetet takva ve kanu ehakka biha ve ehleha ve kanellahu bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟma"
  48,27,"Le kad sadekallahu rasulehur ruÂṀya bil hakk le tedhulunnel mescidel harame in saellahu aminÄḟne muhallikÄḟyne ruusekum ve mukassÄḟriyne la tehafun fe alime ma lem taÂṀlemu fe ceale min duni zalike fethan karÄḟba"
  48,28,"HuvellezÄḟ ersele rasulehu bil huda ve dÄḟnil hakkÄḟ li yuzhirahu aled dÄḟni kullih Ve kefa billahi sehÄḟda"
  48,29,"Muhammedur rasulullah vellezÄḟne meahu esiddau alel kuffari ruhamau beynehum terahum rukkean succedey yebtegune fadlem minellahi ve rÄḟdvana sÄḟmahum fÄḟ vucuhihim min eseris sucud zalike meseluhum fit tevrati ve meseluhum fil incÄḟl ke zerÂṀÄḟn ahrace satÂṀehu fe azerahu festagleza festeva ala sukÄḟhÄḟ yuÂṀcibuz zurraa li yegÄḟyza bihimul kuffar veadellahullezÄḟne amenu ve amilus salihati minhum magfiratev ve ecran azÄḟyma"
  49,4,"InnellezÄḟne yunaduneke miv verail hucurati ekseruhum la yaÂṀkÄḟlun"
  49,5,"Ve lev ennehum saberu hatta tahruce ileyhim le kane hayral lehum vallahu gafurur rahÄḟym"
  49,6,"Ya eyyuhellezine amenu in caekum fazikum bi nebein fe tebeyyenu en tusÄḟybu kavmem bi cehaletin fe tusbihu ala ma fealtum nadimÄḟn"
  49,7,"VaÂṀlemu enne fÄḟkum rasulellah lev yutÄḟyÂṀukum fÄḟ kesÄḟrim minel emri le anittum ve lakÄḟnnellahe habbebe ileykumul Äḟmane ve zeyyenehu fÄḟ kulubikum ve kerrahe ileykumul kufra vel fusuka vel Äḟsyan ulaike humur rasidun"
  49,8,"Fadlem minellahi ve nÄḟÂṀmeh vallahu alÄḟmun hakÄḟm"
  49,9,"Ve in taifetani minel muÂṀminÄḟnaktetelu fe aslihu beynehuma fe im begat Äḟhdaluma alel uhra fe katiluletÄḟ tebgÄḟy hatta tefÄḟe ila emrillah fe in faet fe aslihu beynehuma bil adli ve aksitu innellahe yuhÄḟbbul muksitÄḟyn"
  49,10,"Innemel muÂṀminune Äḟhvetun fe aslihu beyne ehaveykum vettekullahe leallekum turhamun"
  49,11,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenu la yeshar kavmun min kavmin asa ey yekunu hayram minhum ve la nisaum min nisain asa ey yekunne hayram minhunn ve la telmizu enfusekum ve la tenabezu bil elkab biÂṀsel ismul fusuku baÂṀdel iman ve mel lem yetub fe ulaike humuz zalimun"
  49,12,"Ya eyyuhellezÄḟne amenutenibu kesÄḟram minez zanni inne baÂṀdaz zanni ismuv ve la tecessesu ve la yagteb baÂṀdukum baÂṀda e yuhÄḟbbu ehadukum ey yeÂṀkule lahme ehÄḟyhi meyten fe kerihtumuh vettekullah innellahe tevvabur rahÄḟym"
  49,13,"Ya eyyuhen nasu inna halaknakum min zekeriv ve unsa ve cealnakum suubev ve kabaile li tearafu inne ekramekum Äḟndellahi etkakum innellahe alÄḟmun habÄḟr"
  49,14,"Kaletil aÂṀrabu amenna kul lem tuÂṀminu ve lakin kulu eslemna ve lemma yedhulil imanu fi kulubikum ve in tutÄḟyÂṀulahe ve rasulehu la yelitkum min aÂṀmalikum seyÂṀa innellahe gafurur rahÄḟym"
  49,15,"Innemel muÂṀminunellezÄḟne amenu billahi ve rasulihÄḟ summe lem yertabu ve cahedu bi emvalihim ve enfusihim fÄḟ sebÄḟlillah ulaike humus sadikun"
  49,16,"Kul etuallimunellahe bi dÄḟnikum vallahu yaÂṀlemu ma fis semavati ve ma fil ard vallahu bi kulli seyÂṀin alÄḟm"
  49,17,"Yemunnune aleyke en eslemu kul la temunnu aleyye islamekum belillahu yemunnu aleykum en hedakum lil Äḟmani in kuntum sadikÄḟyn"
  49,18,"Innellahe yaÂṀlemu gaybes semavati vel ard vallahu basÄḟyrum bima taÂṀmelun"
  50,5,"Bel kezzebu bil hakkÄḟ lemma caehum fe hum fi emrim meric"
  50,6,"E fe lem yenzuru iles semai fevkahum keyfe beneynaha ve zeyyennaha ve ma leha min furuc"
  50,7,"Vel erda medednaha ve elkayna fiha ravasiye ve embetna fiha min kulli zevcim behic"
  50,8,"TebsÄḟratev ve zikra li kulli abdim munib"
  50,9,"Ve nezzelna mines semai maem mubaraken fe embetna bihi cennativ ve habbel hasÄḟyd"
  50,10,"Ven nahle basikatil leha talÂṀun nedÄḟyd"
  50,11,"Rizkal lil Äḟbadi ve ahyeyna bihi beldetem meyta kezalikel huruc"
  50,12,"Kezzebet kablehum kavmu nuhÄḟv ve ashabur rassi ve semud"
  50,13,"Ve aduv ve firÂṀavnu ve Äḟhvanu lut"
  50,14,"Ve ashahub eyketi ve kavmu tubba kulun kezzeber rusule fe hakka veÄḟyd"
  50,15,"E fe ayÄḟna bil halkÄḟl evvel bel hum fi lebsim min halkÄḟn cedid"
  50,16,"Ve le kad halaknel insane ve naÂṀlemu ma tuvesvisu bihi nefsuh ve nahnu akrabu ileyhi min hablil verid"
  50,17,"Iz yetelekkal mutelekkÄḟyani anil yemini ve anis simali kaÄḟyd"
  50,18,"Ma yelfizu min kavlin illa ledeyhi rakÄḟybun atid"
  50,19,"Ve caet sekratul mevti bil hakk zalike ma kunte minhu tehÄḟyd"
  50,20,"Ve nufiha fis sur zalike yevmul veÄḟyd"
  50,21,"Ve caet kullu nefsim meaha saikuv ve sehid"
  50,22,"Le kad kunte fi gafletim min haza fe kesefna anke gÄḟtaeke fe besarukel yevme hadid"
  50,23,"Ve kale karinuhu haza ma ledeyye atid"
  50,24,"ElkÄḟya gÄḟ cehenneme kulle keffarin anid"
  50,25,"MennaÄḟl lil hayri muÂṀteim murib"
  50,26,"Ellezi ceale meallahi ilahen ahar fe elkiyahu fil azabis sedid"
  50,27,"Kale karinuhu rabbena ma atgaytuhu ve lakin kane fi dalalim beÄḟyd"
  50,28,"Kale la tahtesÄḟmu ledeyye ve kad kaddemtu ileykum bil veÄḟyd"
  50,29,"Ma yubeddelul kavlu ledeyye ve ma enen bi zallamil lil abid"
  50,30,"Yevme nekulu li cehenneme helimteleÂṀti ve tekulu hel mim mezid"
  50,31,"Ve uzlifetil cennetu lil muttekÄḟyne gayra beÄḟyd"
  50,32,"Haza ma tuadune li kulli evvabin hafÄḟyz"
  50,33,"Men hasiyer rahmane bil gaybi ve cae bi kalbim munib"
  50,34,"Udhuluha bi selam zalike yevmul hulud"
  50,35,"Lehum ma yesaune fiha ve ledeyna mezid"
  50,36,"Ve kem ehlekna kablehum min karnin hum eseddu minhum batsen fe nekkabu fil bilad hel mim mehÄḟys"
  50,37,"Inne fi zalike le zikra li men kane lehu kalbun ev elkas semÂṀa ve huve sehid"
  50,38,"Ve le kad halaknes semavati vel erda ve ma beynehuma fi sitteti eyyamiv ve ma messena mil lugub"
  50,39,"Fasbr ala ma yekulune ve sebbÄḟh bi hamdi rabbike kable tuluÄḟs semsi ve kablel gurub"
  50,40,"Ve minel leyli fe sebbÄḟhhu ve edbaras sucud"
  50,41,"VestemÄḟÂṀyevme yunadil munadi mim mekanin karib"
  50,42,"Yevme yesmeunes sayhate bil hakk zalike yevmul huruc"
  50,43,"Inna nahnu nuhyi ve numitu ve ileynel mesÄḟyr"
  50,44,"Yevme tesekkalul erdu anhum siraa zalike hasrun aleyna yesir"
  50,45,"Nahnu aÂṀlemu bi ma yekulune ve ma ente aleyhim bi cebbarin fe zekkir bil kurÂṀani mey yehafu veÄḟyd"
  51,7,"Ves semai zatil hubuk"
  51,8,"Innekum le fi kavlim muhtelif"
  51,9,"YuÂṀfeku anhu men ufik"
  51,10,"Kutilel harrasun"
  51,11,"Ellezine hum fi gamratin sahun"
  51,12,"YesÂṀelune eyyane yevmud din"
  51,13,"Yevme hum alen nari yuftenun"
  51,14,"Zuku fitnetekum hazellezi kuntum bihi testaÂṀcilun"
  51,15,"Innel muttekÄḟyne fi cennativ ve uyun"
  51,16,"AhÄḟzÄḟne ma atahum rabbuhum innehum kanu kable zalike muhsinin"
  51,17,"Kanu kalilem minel leyli ma yehceun"
  51,18,"Ve bil eshari hum yestagfirun"
  51,19,"Ve fi emvalihim hakkul lis saili vel mahrum"
  51,20,"Ve fil erdÄḟ ayatul lil mukÄḟnin"
  51,21,"Ve fi enfusikum e fe la tubrÄḟrun"
  51,22,"Ve fis semai rizkukum ve ma tuadun"
  51,23,"Fe ve rabbis semai vel erdÄḟ innehu lehakkum misle ma ennekum tentÄḟkun"
  51,24,"Hel etake hadisu dayfi ibrahimel mukramin"
  51,25,"Iz dehalu aleyhi fe kalu selama kale selam kavmum munkerun"
  51,26,"Feraga ila ehlihi fe cae bi Äḟclin semin"
  51,27,"Fe karrabehu ileyhim kale e la teÂṀkulun"
  51,28,"Fe evcese minhum hÄḟyfeh kalu la tehaf ve besseruhu bi gulamin alim"
  51,29,"Fe akbeletimraetuhu fi sarratin fe sakket vecheha ve kalet acuzun akÄḟym"
  51,30,"Kalu kezaliki kale rabbuk innehu huvel hakimul alim"
  51,31,"Kale fema hatbukum eyyuhel murselun"
  51,32,"Kalu inna ursilna ila kavmim mucrimin"
  51,33,"Li nursile aleyhim hÄḟcaratem min tÄḟyn"
  51,34,"Musevvemeten Äḟnde rabbike lil musrifin"
  51,35,"Fe ahracna men kane fiha minel muÂṀminin"
  51,36,"Fe ma vecedna fiha gayra beytim minel muslimin"
  51,37,"Ve terakna fiha ayetel lillezine yehafunel azabel elim"
  51,38,"Ve fi musa iz erselnahu ila firÂṀavne bi sultanim mubin"
  51,39,"Fe tevella bi ruknihi ve kale sahÄḟrun ev mecnun"
  51,40,"Fe ehaznahu ve cunudehu fe nebeznahum fil yemmi ve huve mulim"
  51,41,"Ve fi adin iz erselna aleyhimur rihal akÄḟym"
  51,42,"Ma tezeru min seyÂṀin etet aleyhi illa cealethu kir ramim"
  51,43,"Ve fi semude iz kÄḟyle lehum temetteu hatta hÄḟyn"
  51,44,"Fe atev an emri rabbihim fe ehazethumus saÄḟkatu ve hum yenzurun"
  51,45,"Femestetau min kÄḟyamiv ve ma kanu muntesÄḟrÄḟn"
  51,46,"Ve kavme nuhÄḟm min kabl innehum kanu kavmen fasikÄḟyn"
  51,47,"Ves semae beneynaha bi eydiv ve inna le musiun"
  51,48,"Vel erda ferasnaha fe nÄḟÂṀmel mahidun"
  51,49,"Ve min kulli seyÂṀin halakna zevceyni leallekum tezekkerun"
  51,50,"Fe firru ilallah inni lekum minhu nezirum mubin"
  51,51,"Ve la tecÂṀalu meallahi ilahen ahar inni lekum minhu nezirum mubin"
  51,52,"Kezalike ma etellezine min kablihim mir rasulin illa kalu sahÄḟrun ev mecnun"
  51,53,"E tevasav bih bel hum kavmun tagun"
  51,54,"Fe tevelle anhum fe ma ente bi melun"
  51,55,"Ve zekkir fe innez zikra tenfeul muÂṀminin"
  51,56,"Ve ma halaktul cinne vel inse illa li yaÂṀbudun"
