  56,90,"Ve emma in kane min ashabilyemiyni"
  56,91,"Feselamun leke min ashabilyemiyni"
  56,92,"Ve emma in kane minelmukezzibiyneddalliyne"
  56,93,"Fenuzulun min hamiymin"
  56,94,"Ve tasliyetu cahÄḟymin"
  56,95,"Inne haza lehuve hakkulyakÄḟyni"
  56,96,"Fesebbih bismi rabbikelÂṀazÄḟymi"
  57,6,"Yuliculleyle fiynnehari ve yulicunnehare fiylleyli ve huve ÂṀaleymun bizatissuduri"
  57,7,"Aminu billahi ve resulihi ve enfiku mimma ceÂṀalekum mustahlefiyne fiyhi felleziyne amenu minkum ve enfeku lehum ecrun kebiyrun"
  57,8,"Ve ma lekum la tuÂṀminune billahi verresulu yedÂṀukum lituÂṀminu birabbikum ve kad ehaze miysakakum in kuntum muÂṀminiyne"
  57,9,"Huvelleziy yunezzilu ÂṀala ÂṀabdihi ayiten beyyinatin liyuhricekum minezzilimati ilennuri ve innallahe bikum lereufun rahÄḟymun"
  57,10,"Ve malekum ella tunfiku fiy sebiylellahi ve lillahi miyrasussemavati velÂṀardÄḟ la yesteviy minkum men enfeka min kablilfethÄḟ ve katele ulaike aÂṀzamu dereceten minelleziyne enfeku min baÂṀdu ve katelu ve kullen veÂṀadallahulhusna vallahu bima taÂṀmelune habiyrun"
  57,11,"Men zelleziy yukridullahe kardan hasenen feyudaÂṀÄḟfehu lehu ve lehu ecrun keriymun"
  57,12,"Yevme terelmuÂṀminiyne velmuÂṀminati yesÂṀa nuruhum beyne eydiyhim ve bieymanihim busrakumulyevme cennatun tecriy min tahtihelÂṀenharu haliduyne fiyha zalike huvelfevzulÂṀazÄḟymu"
  57,13,"Yevme yekululmunafikune velmunafikatu lilleziyne amenunzurna naktebis min nurikum kÄḟylerciÂṀu veraekum feltemisu nuren feduribe beynehum bisurin lehu babun batÄḟnuhu fiyhirrahmetu ve zahiruhu min kÄḟbelihulÂṀazabu"
  57,14,"Yunadunehum elem nekun meÂṀakum kalu bela ve lakinnekum fetentum enfusekum ve terabbastum vertebtum ve garretkumulÂṀemaniyyu hatta cae emrullahi ve garrekum billahilgaruru"
  57,15,"Felyevme la yuÂṀhazu minkum fidyetun ve la minelleziyne keferu meÂṀvakumunnaru hiye mevlakum ve biÂṀselmesÄḟyru"
  57,16,"Elem yeÂṀni lilleziyne amenu en tahseÂṀa kulubuhum lizikrillahi ve ma nezele minelhakkÄḟ vela yekunu kelleziyne utulkitabe min kablu fetale ÂṀaleyhimulÂṀemedu fekaset kulubuhum ve kesiyrun minhum fasikune"
  57,17,"IÂṀlemu ennallahe yuhyiylÂṀarda baÂṀde mevtiha kado beyyenna lekumulÂṀayati leÂṀallekum taÂṀkÄḟlune"
  57,18,"InnelmusaddikÄḟyne velmusaddikati ve akredullahe kardan hasenen yudaÂṀafu lehum ve lehum ecrun keruymun"
  57,19,"Velleziyne amenu billahi ve rusulihi ulaik humussÄḟddiykune vessuhedauÂṀÄḟnde rabbihim lehum ecruhum ve nuruhum velleziyne keferu ve kezzebu biayatina ulaik ashabulcahÄḟymi"
  57,20,"IÂṀlemu ennemelhayatuddnuya leÂṀÄḟbun ve lehvun ve ziynetun ve tefahurun beynekum ve ziynetun ve tefahurun biynekum ve tekasurun fiylÂṀemvali velÂṀevladi kemeseli gaysin aÂṀcebelkuffare nebatuhu summe yekunu hutamen ve fiylÂṀahÄḟreti ÂṀazabun seduydun ve magfiretun minallahi ve rÄḟdvanun ve melhayatuddunya illa metaÂṀulgururi"
  57,21,"Sabiku ila magfiretin min rabbikum ve cennetin ÂṀarduha keÂṀardissemai velÂṀardÄḟ uÂṀÄḟddet lilleziyne amenu billahi ve rusulihi zalike fadlullahi yuÂṀtiyhi men yesaÂṀu vallahu zulfadlilÂṀazÄḟymi"
  57,22,"Ma esabe min musÄḟybetin fiylÂṀardÄḟ ve la fiy enfusikum illa fiy kitabin min kabli en nebreeha inne zalike ÂṀalellahi yesiyrun"
  57,23,"Likeyla teÂṀsev ÂṀala ma fatekum ve la tefrahu bima atakum vallahu la yuhÄḟbbu kulle muhtalin fehurin"
  57,24,"Elleziyne yebhalune ve yeÂṀmurunennase bilbuhli ve men yetevelle feinnallahe huvelganiyyulhamiydu"
  57,25,"Lekad erselna rusulena bilbeyyinati ve enzelna meÂṀahumulkitabe velmiyzane liyekumennasu bilkÄḟstÄḟ ve enzelnelhadiyde fiyhi beÂṀsun sediydun ve menafiÂṀu linnasi ve liyaÂṀlemallahu men yensuruhu ve rusulehu bilgaybi innallahe kaviyyun ÂṀaziyzun"
  57,26,"Ve lekad erselna nuhan ve ibrahiyme ve ceÂṀalna fiy zurriyyetihimennubuvvete velkitabe feminhum muhtedin ve kesiyrun minhum fasikune"
  57,27,"Summe kaffeyna ÂṀala asarihim birusulina ve kaffeyna biÂṀÄḟysebni meryeme ve ateynahulÂṀinciyle ve ceÂṀalna fiy kulubilleziynettebeÂṀuhu reÂṀfeten ve ramheten ve rehbaniyyetenibtedeÂṀuha ma ketebnaha ÂṀaleyhim illebtigae rÄḟdvanillahi fema reÂṀavha hakka riÂṀayetiha feateynelleziyne amenu minhum ecrehum ve kesiyrun minhum fasikune"
  57,28,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenuttekullahe ve aminu biresulihi yuÂṀtikum kifleyni min rahmetihi ve yecÂṀal lekum nuren temsune bihi ve yagfir lekum vallahu gafurun rahÄḟymun"
  57,29,"Liella yaÂṀleme ehlulkitabi ella yakdirune ÂṀala seyÂṀin min fadlillahi ve ennelfadle biyedillahi yuÂṀtÂṀyhi men yesaÂṀuÂṀvallahu zulfadlilÂṀazÄḟymi"
  58,5,"Innelleziyne yuhaddunallahe ve resulehu kubitu kema kubitelleziyne min kablihim ve kad enzelna ayatin beyyinatin v uhumullahu cemiyÂṀan feyunebbiuhum bima ÂṀamilu ahsahullahu ve nesuhu e lilkafiriyne ÂṀazabun muhiynun"
  58,6,"Yevme yebÂṀas vallahu ÂṀala kulli seyÂṀin sehiydun"
  58,7,"Elem tere ennallahe yaÂṀlemu ma fiyssemavati ve ma fiylÂṀardÄḟ ma yekunu min necva selasetin illa huve rabiÂṀuhum ve la hamsetin illa huve sadisuhum ve la edna min zalike ve la eksere illa huve meÂṀahum iyne ma kanu summe yunebbiuhum bima ÂṀamilu yevmelkÄḟyameti innallahe bikulli seyÂṀin ÂṀaliymun"
  58,8,"Elem tere ilelleziyne nuhu ÂṀaninnecva summe yeÂṀudune lima nuhu ÂṀanhu ve yetenacevne bilÂṀismi velÂṀudvani ve maÂṀsÄḟyetirresuli ve iza cauke hayyevke bima lem yuhayyike bilillahu ve yekulune fiy enfusihim lev la yuÂṀazzibunallahu bima nekulu hasbuhum cehennemu yaslevneha febi;ÂṀselmasÄḟyru"
  58,9,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu iza tenaceytum fela tetenacev bilÂṀismi velÂṀudvani ve maÂṀsÄḟyetirresuli ve tenacev bilbirri vettakva vettekullahelleziy ileyhi tuhserune"
  58,10,"Innemennecva minesseytani liyahzunelleziyne amenu ve leyse bidarrihim seyÂṀen illa biiznillahi ve ÂṀalellahi felyetevekkelilmuÂṀminune"
  58,11,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu iza kÄḟyle lekum tefessehu fiylmecalisi fefsehu yefsehÄḟllahu lekum ve iza kÄḟylensuzu fensuzu yerfeÂṀÄḟllahulleziyne amenu minkum velleziyne utulÂṀÄḟlme derecatin vallahu bima taÂṀmelune habiyrun.ÂṀ"
  58,12,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu iza naceytumurresule fekaddimu beyne yedey necvakum sadekaten zalike hayrun lekum ve atheru fein lem tecidu feinnallahe gafurun rahÄḟymun"
  58,13,"Eesfaktum en tukaddimu beyne yedey necvakum sadekatin feiz lem tefÂṀalu ve taballahu ÂṀaleykum feekÄḟymussalate ve atuzzekate ve etÄḟyÂṀallahe ve resulehu vallahu habiyrun bima taÂṀmelune"
  58,14,"Elem tere ilelleziyne tevellev kavmen gadÄḟballahu ÂṀaleyhim ma hum minkum ve la minhum ve yahlifune ÂṀalelkezibi ve hum yaÂṀlemune"
  58,15,"EÂṀaddallahu lehum ÂṀazaben sediyden innehum sae ma lanu yaÂṀmelune"
  58,16,"Ittehazu eymanehum cunneten fesaddu ÂṀan sebiylillahi felehum ÂṀazabun muhiynun"
  58,17,"Len tugniye ÂṀanhum emvaluhum ve la evladuhum minallahi seyÂṀen ulaik ashabunnari hum fiyha halidune"
  58,18,"Yevme yebÂṀasuhumullahu cemiyÂṀan feyahlifune lehu kema yahlifune lekum ve yahsebune ennehum ÂṀala seyÂṀin ela innehum humulkazibune"
  58,19,"Istahvese ÂṀaleyhimusseytanu feensahum zikrallahi ulaike hÄḟzbusseytani ela inne hÄḟzbesseytani humulhasirune"
  58,20,"Innelleziyne yuhaddunallahe ve resulehu ulaike fiylÂṀezelliyne"
  58,21,"Ketaballahu leaglibenne ene ve rusuliy innallahe kaviyyun ÂṀaziyzun"
  58,22,"La tecidu kavmen yuÂṀminune billahi velyevmilÂṀahÄḟri yuvaddune men haddallahe ve resulehu ve lev kanu abaehum ev ebnaehum ev Äḟhvanehum ev ÂṀasiyretehum ulaike ketebe fiy kulubihimulÂṀiymane ve eyyedehum biruhÄḟn minhu ve yudhÄḟluhum cennatin tecriy min tahtihelÂṀenharu halidiyne fiyha radÄḟyallahu ÂṀanhum ve radu ÂṀanhu ulaike hÄḟzbullahi ela inne hÄḟzballahi humulmuflihune"
  59,6,"Ve ma efaalahu ÂṀala resulihi minhum fema evceftum ÂṀaleyhi min haylin ve la rikabin ve lakinnallahe yusellitu rusulehu ÂṀala men yesaÂṀu vallahu ÂṀala kulli seyÂṀin kadiyrun"
  59,7,"Ma efaallahu ÂṀala resulihi min ehlilkura felillahi ve lirresuli ve liziylkurba velyetama velmesakiyni vebnissebiyli key la yekune duleten beynelÂṀagniyai minkum ve ma atakumurresulu fehuzuhu ve ma nehakum ÂṀanhu fentehu vettekullahe innallahe sediydulÂṀÄḟkabi"
  59,8,"Lelfukarailmuhaciriyn-elleziyne uhricu min diyarihim ve emvalihim yebtegune fadlen minallahi ve rÄḟdvanen ve yensurunallahe ve resulehu ulaike humussadikune"
  59,9,"Velleziyne tebevveuddare velÂṀiymane min kablihim yuhÄḟbbune men hacere ileyhim ve la yecidune fiy sudurihim haceten mimma utu ve yuÂṀsirune ÂṀala enfusihim ve lev kane bihim hasasatun ve men yuka suhha nefsihi feulaike humulmuflihune"
  59,10,"Velleziyne cau min baÂṀdihim yekulune rabbenagfir lena ve liÄḟhvaninelleziyne sebekuna bilÂṀiymani ve la tecÂṀal fiy kulubina gullen lilleziyne amenu rabbena inneke raufun rahÄḟymun"
  59,11,"Elem tere ilelleziyne nafeku yekulune liÄḟhvanihimulleziyne keferu min ehlilkitabi lein uhrictum lenahrucenne meÂṀakum ve la nutÄḟyÂṀu fiykum ehaden ebeden ve in kutiltum lenensurennekum vallahu yeshedu innehum lekazibune"
  59,12,"Lein uhricu la yahrucune meÂṀahum ve lein kutilu la yensurunehum ve lein nesaruhum leyuvellunelÂṀedbare summe la yunsarune"
  59,13,"Leentum eseddu rehbeten fiy sudurihim minallahi zalike biennehum kavmun la yefkahune"
  59,14,"La yukatilunekum cemiyÂṀan illa iy kuran muhassenetin ev min verai cudurin beÂṀsuhum beynehum sediydun tahsebuhum cemiyÂṀan ve kulubuhum setta zalike biennehum kavmun la yaÂṀkÄḟlune"
  59,15,"Kemeselilleziyne min kablihim kariyben zaku vebule emrihim ve lehum ÂṀazabun eliymun"
  59,16,"Kemeselisseytani iz kale lilÂṀinsanikfur felemma kefere kale inniy beriyÂṀun minke inniy ehafullahe rabbelÂṀalemiyne"
  59,17,"Fekane ÂṀakÄḟbetehuma ennehuma fiynari halideyni fiyha ve zalike cezauzzalimiyne"
  59,18,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenuttekullahe veltenzur nefsun ma kaddemet ligadin vettekullahe innallahe habiyrun bima taÂṀmelune"
  59,19,"Ve la tekunu kelleziyne nesullahe feensahum enfusehum ulaike humulfasikune"
  59,20,"La yesteviy ashabunnari ve ashabulcenneti ashabulcenneti humulfaizune"
  59,21,"Lev enzelna hazelkurÂṀane ÂṀala cebelin lereeytehu hasiÂṀan mutesaddi ÂṀan min hasyetillahi ve tilkelÂṀemsalu nadribuha linnasi leÂṀallehum yetefekkerune"
  59,22,"Huvallahulleziy la ilahe illa huve ÂṀalimulgaybi vessehadeti huverrahmanurrahÄḟymu"
  59,23,"Huvallahulleziy la ilahe illa huve elmelikulkuddususselamul muÂṀminul muheyminul ÂṀaziyzul cebbarul mutekebbiru subhanallahi ÂṀamma yusrikune"
  59,24,"Huvallahul halikul - bariy-ulmusavviru lehumÂṀesma ulhusna yusebbihu lehu ma fiyssemavati velÂṀardÄḟ. Ve huvelÂṀaziyzulhakiymu"
  60,7,"ÂṀAsallahu en yecÂṀale beynekum ve beynelleziyne ÂṀadeytum minhum meveddeten vallahu kadiyrun vallahu gafurun rahÄḟymun"
  60,8,"La yenhakumullahu ÂṀanilleziyne lem yukatilukum fiyddiyni ve lem yuhricukum min diyarikum en teberruhum ve tuksitu ileyhim innallahe yuhÄḟbbulmuksitÄḟyne"
  60,9,"Innema yenhakumullahu ÂṀanilleziyne katelukum fiydiyni ve ahrecukum min duyarikum ve zaheru ÂṀala Äḟhracikum en tevellevhum ve men yetevellehum feulaike humuzzalimune"
  60,10,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu iza caekumulmuÂṀminatu muha ciratin femtehÄḟnuhunne allahu aÂṀlemu biiymanihinne fein ÂṀalimtumuhunne muÂṀminatin fela terciÂṀuhunne ilelkuffari la hunne hÄḟllun lehum ve la hum yehÄḟllune lehunne ve atuhum ma enfeku ve la cunaha ÂṀaleykum en tenkÄḟhuhunne iza ateytumuhunne ucurehunne ve la tumsiku biÂṀÄḟsamilkevafiri vesÂṀelu ma enfaktum velyes&elu ma enfeku zalikum hukmullahi yahkumu beynekum vallahu ÂṀaliymun hakuymun"
  60,11,"Ve in fatekum seyÂṀun min ezvacikum ilelkuffari feÂṀakabtum featulleziyne zehebet ezvacuhum misle ma enfeku vettekullahelleziy entum bihi muÂṀminune"
  60,12,"Ya eyyuhennebiyyu iza caekelmuÂṀminatu yubayÄḟÂṀneke ala en la yusrikne billahi seyÂṀen ve la yesrÄḟkne ve la yezniyne ve la yaktulne evladehunne ve la yetÂṀtiyne bibuhtanin yefteriynehu beyne eydiyhinne ve erculihinne ve la yaÂṀsÄḟyneke fiy maÂṀrufin febayÄḟÂṀhunne vestagfir lehunnallahe innallahe gafurun rahÄḟymun"
  60,13,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu la tetevellev kavmen gadÄḟballahu ÂṀaleyhim kad yesiu minelÂṀahÄḟreti kema yeiselkuffaru min ashabilkuburi"
  61,6,"Ve iz kale ÂṀÄḟysebnu meryeme ya beniy israiyle inniy resulullahi ileykum musaddikan lima beyne yedeyye minettevrati ve mubessiren biresulin yeÂṀtiy min baÂṀdiy-ismuhu ahmedu felemma caehum bilbeyyinati kalu haza sÄḟhrun mubiynun"
  61,7,"Ve men azlenu mimmeniftera ÂṀalellahilkezibe ve huve yudÂṀa ilelÂṀislami vallahu la yehdiylkavmezzalimiyne"
  61,8,"Yuriydune liyutfiu nurallahi biefvahihim vallahu mutimmu nurihi velev kerihelkafirune"
  61,9,"Huvelleziy ersele resulehu bilhuda ve diynilhakkÄḟ liyuzhirehu ÂṀaleddiyni kullihi velev kerihelmusrikune"
  61,10,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu hel edullukum ÂṀala ticaretin tunciykum min ÂṀazabin eliymin"
  61,11,"TuÂṀminune billahi ve resulihi ve tucahidune fiy sebiylillahi biemvalikum ve enfusikum zalikum hayrun lekum in kuntum taÂṀlemune"
  61,12,"Yagfir lekum zunubekum ve yudhÄḟlkum cennatin tecriy min tahtihelÂṀenharu ve mesakine tayyibeten fiy cennati ÂṀadnin zalikelfevzulÂṀazÄḟymu"
  61,13,"Ve uhra tuhÄḟbbuneha nasrun minallahi ve fethun kariybun ve bessirilmuÂṀminiyne"
  61,14,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu kunu ensarallahi kema kale ÂṀÄḟysebnu meryeme lilhavariyyiyne men ensariy ilellahi kalelhavariyyune nahnu ensarullahi feamenet taifetun min benuy israiyle ve keferet taifetun feeyyednelleziyne amenu ÂṀala ÂṀaduvyihim feasbehu zahiriyne"
  62,5,"Meselulleziyne hummiluttevrate summe lem yahmiluha kemeselilhÄḟmari yahmilu esfaren biÂṀse meselulkavmilleziyne kezzebu biayatillahi vallahu la yehdiylkavmezzalimiyne"
  62,6,"Kul ya eyyuhelleziyne hadu in zeÂṀamtum ennekum evliyau lillahi min duninnasi fetemennevulmevte in kuntum sadikÄḟyne"
  62,7,"Ve la yetemennevnehu ebeden bima kaddemet eydiyhim vallahu ÂṀaliymun bizzalimiyne"
  62,8,"Kul innelmevtelleziy tefirrune minhu feinnehu mulakÄḟykum summe tureddune ila ÂṀalimilgaybi vessehadeti feyunebiiukum bima kuntum taÂṀmelune"
  62,9,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu iza nudiye lissalati min yevmilcumuÂṀati fesÂṀav ila zikrillahi ve zerulbeyÂṀa zalikum hayrun lekum in kuntum taÂṀlemune"
  62,10,"Feiza kudÄḟyetissalatu fentesiru fiylÂṀardÄḟ vebtegu min fadlillahi vezkurullahe kesiyren leÂṀallekum tuflihune"
  62,11,"Ve iza reev ticareten ev lehveninfaddu ileyha ve terekuke kaimen kul ma ÂṀÄḟndallahi hayrun millehvi ve minetticareti vallahu hayrurrazikÄḟyne"
  63,4,"Ve iza reeytehum tuÂṀcibuke ecsamuhum ve in yekulu tesmaÂṀ likavlihim keennehum husubun musennedetun yahsebune kulle sayhatin ÂṀaleyhim humulÂṀaduvvu fahzerhum katelehumullahu enna yuÂṀfekune"
  63,5,"Ve iza kÄḟyle lehum teÂṀalev yestagfir lekum resulullahi levvev ruusehum ve reeytehum yesuddune ve hum mustekbirune"
  63,6,"Sevun ÂṀaleyhim estagferte lehum em lem testagfir lehum len yagfirallahu lehum innallahe la yehdiylkavmelfasikÄḟyne"
  63,7,"Humulleziyne yekulune la tunfiku ÂṀala men ÂṀÄḟnde resulillahi hatta yenfaddu ve lillahi hazainussemavati velÂṀardÄḟ ve lakinnelmunafikÄḟyne la yefkahune"
  63,8,"Yekulune lein recaÂṀna ilelmediyneti leyuhricennelÂṀeÂṀazzu minhelÂṀezelle ve lillahilÂṀÄḟzzetu ve liresulihi ve lilmuÂṀminiyne ve lakinnelmunafikÄḟyne la yaÂṀlemune"
  63,9,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu la tulhikum emvalukum ve la evladukum ÂṀan zikrillahi ve men yefÂṀal zalike feulaike humulhasirune"
  63,10,"Ve enfiku mimma rezaknakum min kabli en yeÂṀtiye ehadekumulmevtu feyekule rabbi lev la ahharteniy ila ecelin kariybin feassaddeka ve ekun minessalihÄḟyne"
  63,11,"Ve len yuahhÄḟrallahu nefsen iza cae eceluha vallahu habiyrun bima taÂṀmelune"
  64,7,"ZeÂṀamelleziyne keferu en len yubÂṀasu kul bela ve rabbiy letubÂṀasunne summe letunebbeunne bima ÂṀamiltum ve zalike ÂṀalellahi yesiyrun"
  64,8,"Feaminu billahi ve resulihi vennurilleziy enzelna vallahu bima taÂṀmelune habiyrun"
  64,9,"Yevme yecmeÂṀukum liyevmicemÂṀÄḟ zalike yevmuttegabuni ve men yuÂṀmin billahi ve yaÂṀmel salihan yukeffir ÂṀanhu seyyiatihi ve yudhÄḟlhu cennatin tecriy min tahtihelÂṀenharu halidiyne fiyha ebeden zalikelfevzulÂṀazÄḟymu"
  64,10,"Velleziyne keferu ve kezzebu biayatina ulaike ashabunnari halidiyne fiyha ve biÂṀselmasÄḟyru"
  64,11,"Ma esabe min musÄḟybetin illa biiznillahi ve men yuÂṀmin billahi yehdi kalbehu vallahu bikulli seyÂṀin ÂṀaliymun"
  64,12,"Ve etÄḟyÂṀullahe ve etÄḟyÂṀurresule fein tevelleytum feinnema ÂṀala resulinelbelagulmubiynu"
  64,13,"Allahu la ilahe illa huve ve ÂṀalellahi felyetevekkelilmuÂṀminune"
  64,14,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu inne min ezvacikum ve evladikum ÂṀaduvven lekum fahzeruhum ve in taÂṀfu ve tasfehu ve tagfiru feinnallahe gafurun rahÄḟymun"
  64,15,"Ennema emvalukum ve evladukum fitnetun vallahu ÂṀÄḟndehu ecrun ÂṀazÄḟymun"
  64,16,"Fettekullahe mestetaÂṀtum vesmeÂṀu ve etiyÂṀu ve enfiku hayren lienfusikum ve men yuka suhha nefsihi feulaike humulmufluhune"
  64,17,"In tukridullahe kardan hasenen yudaÂṀÄḟfhu lekum ve yagfir lekum vallahu sekurin haliymun"
  64,18,"ÂṀAlimulgaybi vessehadetilÂṀaziyzulhakiymu"
  65,6,"Eskinuhunne min haysu sekentum min vucdikum ve la tudarruhunne litudayyiku ÂṀaleyhinne ve in kunne ulati hamlin feenfiku ÂṀaleyhinne hatta yedaÂṀne hamlehunne fein erdaÂṀne lekum featuhunne ucurehunne veÂṀtemiru beynekum bimaÂṀrufin ve in teÂṀasertum feseturdÄḟÂṀu lehu uhra"
  65,7,"LiyunfÄḟk zu seÂṀa tin min seÂṀatihi ve men kudire ÂṀaleyhi rizkuhu felyunfÄḟk mimma atahÄḟllahu la yukellifullahu nefsen illa ma ataha seyecÂṀalullahu baÂṀde ÂṀusrin yusren"
  65,8,"Ve keeyyin min karyetin ÂṀatet ÂṀan emri rabbiha ve rusulihi fehasebnaha hÄḟsaben sediyden ve ÂṀazzebnaha ÂṀazaben nukren"
  65,9,"Fezakat vebale emriha ve kane ÂṀakÄḟbetu emriha husren"
  65,10,"EÂṀaddallahu lehum ÂṀazaben sediyden fettekullahe ya ulilÂṀelbabi ellizyne amenu kad enzelallahu ileykum zikren"
  65,11,"Resulen yetlu ÂṀaleykum ayatillahi mubeyyinatin liyuhricelleziyne amenu ve ÂṀamilussalihati minezzulumati ilennuri ve men yuÂṀmin billahi ve yaÂṀmel salihan yudhÄḟlhu cennatin tecriy min tahtihelÂṀenharu halidiyne fiyha ebeden kad ahsenallahu lehu rizkan"
  65,12,"Allahulleziy haleka sebÂṀa semavatin ve minelÂṀardÄḟ mislehunne yetenezzelulÂṀemru beynehunne litaÂṀlemu ennallahe ala kulli seyÂṀin kadirun ve ennalahe kad ehata bikulli seyÂṀin ÂṀÄḟlmen"
  66,7,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne keferu la taÂṀtezirulyevme innema tuczevne ma kuntum taÂṀmelune"
  66,8,"Ya eyyuhelleziyne amenu tubu ilellahi tevbeten nesuhan asa rabbukum en yukeffire ÂṀankum seyyiatikum ve yudhÄḟlekum cennatin tecriy min tahtihelÂṀenharu yevme la yuhzillahunnebiyye velleziyne amenu meÂṀahu nuruhum yesÂṀa beyne eydiyhim ve bieymanihim yekulune rabbena etmin lena nurena vagfir lena inneke ÂṀala kulli seyÂṀin kadiyrun"
  66,9,"Ya eyyuhennebiyyu cahidilkuffare velmunafikÄḟyne vagluz ÂṀaleyhim ve meÂṀvahum cehennemu ve biÂṀselmasÄḟyru"
  66,10,"Dareballahu meselen lilleziyne keferumreete nuhÄḟn vemreete lutin kaneta tahte ÂṀabdeyni min ÂṀÄḟbadina salihayni fehanetahuma felem yugniya ÂṀanhuma minallahi seyÂṀen ve kÄḟyledhulennare meÂṀaddahiliyne"
  66,11,"Ve da reballahu meselen lilleziyne amenumreete firÂṀavne iz kalet rabbibni liy ÂṀÄḟndeke beyten fiylcenneti ve necciniy min firÂṀavne ve ÂṀamelihi ve necciniy minelkavmizzalimiyne"
  66,12,"Ve meryemebte ÂṀÄḟmranelletiy ahsanet ferceha fenefahna fiyhi min ruhÄḟna ve saddekat bikelimati rabbiha ve kutubihi ve kanet minelkanitÄḟyne"
  67,6,"Ve lilleziyne keferu birabbihim ÂṀazabu cehenneme ve biÂṀselmasÄḟyru"
  67,7,"Iza ulku fiyha semiÂṀu leha sehiykan ve hiye tefuru"
  67,8,"Tekadu temeyyezu minelgayzÄḟ kullema ulkÄḟye fiyha fevcun seelehum hazenetuha elem yetÂṀkum neziyrun"
  67,9,"Kalu bela kad caena neziyrun fekezzebna ve kulna ma nezzelellahu min seyÂṀin in entum illa fiy dalalin kebiyrin"
  67,10,"Ve kalu lev kunna nesmeÂṀu ev naÂṀkÄḟlu ma kunna fiy ashabisseÂṀÄḟyri"
  67,11,"FaÂṀterefÂṀu bizenbihim fesuhkan liashabisseÂṀÄḟyri"
  67,12,"Innelleziyne yahsevne rabbehum bilgaybi lehum magfiretun ve ecrun kebiyrun"
  67,13,"Ve esirru kavlekum evicheru bihi innehu ÂṀaliymun bizatissuduri"
  67,14,"Ela yaÂṀlemu men haleka ve huvelletÄḟyfulhabiyru"
  67,15,"Huvelleziy ceÂṀale lekumulÂṀarda zelulen femsu fiy menakibiha ve kulu min rizkÄḟhi ve ileyhinnusuru"
  67,16,"Eemintum men fiyssemai en yahsife bikumulÂṀarda feiza hiye temuru"
  67,17,"Em emintum men fiyssemai en yursile ÂṀaleykum hasÄḟben fesetaÂṀlemune keyfe neziyri"
  67,18,"Ve lekad kezzebilleziyne min kablihim fekeyfe kane nekiyri"
  67,19,"Evelem yerev ilettayri fevkahum saffatin ve yakbÄḟdne ma yumsikuhunne illerrahmanu innehu bikulli seyÂṀin basÄḟyrun"
  67,20,"Emmen hazelleziy huve cundun lekum yansurukum min dunirrahmani inilkafirune illa fiy gururin"
  67,21,"Emmen hazelleziy yerzukukum in emseke rizkahu bel leccu fiy ÂṀutuvvin ve nufurin"
  67,22,"Efemen yemsiy mukibben ÂṀala vechihi ehda emmen yemsiy seviyyen ÂṀala sÄḟratÄḟn mustekÄḟymin"
  67,23,"Kul huvelleziy enseekum ve ceÂṀale lekumussemÂṀa velÂṀebsare velÂṀefÂṀidete kaliylen ma teskurune"
  67,24,"Kul huvelleziy zereekum fiylÂṀardÄḟ ve ileyhi tuhserune"
  67,25,"Ve yekulune meta hazelvaÂṀdu in kuntum sadikÄḟyne"
  67,26,"Kul innemelÂṀÄḟlmu ÂṀÄḟndallahi ve innema ene neziyrun mubiynun"
  67,27,"Felemma reevhu zulfeten siy-et vucuhulleziyne keferu ve kÄḟyle hazelleziy kuntum bihi teddeÂṀune"
  67,28,"Kul ereeytum in ehlekeniyallahu ve men meÂṀÄḟye ev rahÄḟmena femen yuciyrulkafiriyne min ÂṀazabin eliymin"
  67,29,"Kul huverrahmanu amenna bihi ve ÂṀaleyhi tevekkelna fesetaÂṀlemune men huve fiy dalalin mubiynin"
  67,30,"Kul ereeytum in asbeha maukum gavren femen yeÂṀtiykum bimain meÂṀÄḟynin"
  68,5,"FesetubsÄḟru ve yubsÄḟrune"
  68,6,"Bieyyikumulmeftunu"
  68,7,"Inne rabbeke huve aÂṀlemu bimen dalleÂṀan sebiylihi ve huve aÂṀlemu bilmuhtediyne"
  68,8,"Fela tutÄḟÂṀÄḟlmukezzibiyne"
  68,9,"Veddu lev tudhinu feyudhinune"
  68,10,"Ve la tutÄḟÂṀ kulle hallafin mehiyni"
  68,11,"Hemmazin messain binemiymin"
  68,12,"MennaÂṀÄḟn lilhayri muÂṀtedin esiymin"
  68,13,"ÂṀutullin baÂṀde zalike zeniymen"
  68,14,"En kane za malin ve beniyne"
  68,15,"Iza tutla ÂṀaleyhi ayatuna kale esatÄḟyrulevveliyne"
  68,16,"Senesimuhu ÂṀalelhurtumi"
  68,17,"Inna belevnahum kema belevna ashabelcenneti iz aksemu leyasri munneha musbihÄḟyne"
  68,18,"Ve la yestesnune"
  68,19,"Fetafe ÂṀaleyha taifun min rabbike ve hum naimune"
  68,20,"Feasbehat kessariymi"
  68,21,"Fetenadev musbihÄḟyne"
  68,22,"Enigdu ÂṀala harsikum in kuntum sarimiyne"
  68,23,"Fentaleku ve hum yetehafetune"
  68,24,"En la yedhulennehelyevme ÂṀaleykum miskiynun"
  68,25,"Ve gadev ÂṀala hardin kadiriyne"
  68,26,"Felemma reevha kalu inna ledallune"
  68,27,"Bel nahnu mahrumune"
  68,28,"Kale evsetuhum elem ekul lekum levha tusebbihune"
  68,29,"Kalu subhane rabbina inna kunna zalimiyne"
  68,30,"Feakbele baÂṀduhum ÂṀala baÂṀdÄḟn yetelavemune"
  68,31,"Kalu ya veylena inna kunna tagÄḟyne"
  68,32,"ÂṀasa rabbuna en yubdilena hayren minha inna ila rabbina ragÄḟbune"
  68,33,"KezalikelÂṀazabu ve leÂṀazabulÂṀahÄḟreti ekberu lev kanu yaÂṀlemune"
  68,34,"Inne lilmuttekÄḟyne ÂṀÄḟnde rabbihim cennatin neÂṀÄḟymi"
  68,35,"EfenecÂṀalulmuslimiyne kelmucrimiyne"
  68,36,"Ma lekum keyfe tahkumune"
  68,37,"Emlekum kitabun fiyhi tedrusune"
  68,38,"Inne lekum fiyhu lema tehayyerune"
  68,39,"Em lekum eymanun ÂṀaleyna baligatun ila yevmilkÄḟyameti inne lekum lema tahkumune"
  68,40,"Selhum eyyuhum bizalike zeÂṀÄḟymun"
  68,41,"Emlehum surekaÂṀu felyeÂṀtu bisurekaihim in kanu sadikÄḟyne"
  68,42,"Yevme yuksefu ÂṀan sakÄḟn ve yudÂṀavne ilessucudi fela yestetÄḟyÂṀune"
  68,43,"HasiÂṀaten ebsaruhum terhekuhum zillefun ve kad kanu yudÂṀavne ilessucudi ve lum salimune"
  68,44,"Fezerniy ve men yukezzibu bihazelhadiysi senestedricuhum min haysu la yaÂṀlemune"
  68,45,"Ve umliy lehum inne keydiy metiynun"
  68,46,"Em tesÂṀeluhum ecren fehum min magremin muskalune"
  68,47,"Em ÂṀÄḟndehumulgaybu fehum yektubune"
  68,48,"Fasbir lihukmi rabbike ve la tekun kesahÄḟbilhuti iz nada ve huve mekzumun"
  68,49,"Levla en tedarekehu nÄḟÂṀmetun min rabbihi lenubize bilÂṀarai ve huve mezmumun"
  68,50,"Fectebahu rabbuhu feceÂṀalehu minessalihÄḟyne"
  68,51,"Ve in yekadulleziyne keferu leyuzlikuneke biebsarihim lemma semiÂṀuzzikre ve yekulune innehu lemecnunun"
  68,52,"Ve ma huve illa zikrun lilÂṀalemiyne"
  69,7,"Sahhareha ÂṀaleyhim sebÂṀa leyalin ve semaniyete eyyamin husumen feterelkavme fiyha sarÂṀa keennehum aÂṀcazu nahlin haviyetin"
  69,8,"Fehel tera hehum min bakÄḟyetin"
  69,9,"Ve cae firÂṀavnu ve men kablehu velmuÂṀtefikatu bilhatÄḟeti"
  69,10,"FeÂṀasav resule rabbihim feehazehum ahzeten rabiyeten"
  69,11,"Inna lemma tagalmau hamelnakum fiylcariyeti"
  69,12,"LinecÂṀaleha lekum tezkireten ve teÂṀÄḟyeha uzunun vaÂṀÄḟyetun"
  69,13,"Feiza nufiha fiysuri nefhatun vahÄḟdetun"
  69,14,"Ve humiletilÂṀardu velcibalu fedukketa dekketen vahÄḟdeten"
  69,15,"Feyevmeizin vekaÂṀatilvakÄḟÂṀatu"
  69,16,"VensakkatissemaÂṀu fehiye yevmeizin vahiyetun"
  69,17,"Velmeleku ÂṀala ercaiha ve yahmilu ÂṀarse rabbike fevkahum yevmeizin semaniyetun"
  69,18,"Yevmeizin tuÂṀradune la tahfa minkum hafiyetun"
  69,19,"Feemma men utiye kitabehu bi yemiynihi feyekulu haumuÂṀkrau kitabiyeh"
  69,20,"Inniy zanentu enniy mulakÄḟn hÄḟsabiyeh"
  69,21,"Fehuve fiy ÂṀÄḟysetin radÄḟyetin"
  69,22,"Fiy cennetin ÂṀaliyetin"
  69,23,"Kutufuha daniyetun"
  69,24,"Kulu vesrebu heniyen bima esleftum fiylÂṀeyyamilhaliyeti"
  69,25,"Ve emma men utiye kitabehu bisimalihi feyekulu ya leyteniy lem ute kitabiyeh"
  69,26,"Ve lem edri ma hÄḟsabiyeh"
  69,27,"Ya leyteha kanetilkadÄḟyete"
  69,28,"Ma agna ÂṀanniy maliyeh"
  69,29,"Heleke ÂṀanniy sultaniyeh"
  69,30,"Huzuhu fegulluhu"
  69,31,"Summel cehÄḟyme salluhu"
  69,32,"Summe fiy silsi letin zerÂṀuha sebÂṀune ziraÂṀan feslukuhu"
  69,33,"Innehu kane la yuÂṀminu billahilÂṀa zÄḟymi"
  69,34,"Ve la yehuddu ÂṀala taÂṀamil miskiyni"
  69,35,"Feleyse lehulyevme hahuna hamiymun"
  69,36,"Ve la taÂṀamun illa min gÄḟsliynin"
  69,37,"La yeÂṀkuluhu illelhatÄḟune"
  69,38,"Fela uksimu bima tubsÄḟrune"
  69,39,"Ve ma la tubsÄḟrune"
  69,40,"Innehu lekavlu resulin keriymin"
  69,41,"Ve ma huve bikavli saÂṀÄḟrin kaliylen ma tuÂṀminune"
  69,42,"Ve la bilkavli kahinin kaliylen ma tezekkerune"
  69,43,"Tenziylun min rabbilÂṀalemiyne"
  69,44,"Velev tekavvele ÂṀaleyna baÂṀdalÂṀekaviyli"
  69,45,"Leehazna minhu bilyemiyni"
  69,46,"Summe lekataÂṀna minhulvetiyne"
  69,47,"Fema minkum min ehadin ÂṀanhu haciziyne"
  69,48,"Ve innehu letezkiretun lilmuttekÄḟyne"
  69,49,"Ve inna lenaÂṀlemu enne minkum mukezzibiyne"
  69,50,"Ve innehu lehasretun ÂṀalelkafiriyne"
  69,51,"Ve innehu lehakkulyakÄḟyni"
  69,52,"Fesebbih bismi rabbikelÂṀazÄḟymi"
  70,8,"Yevme tekunussemaÂṀu kelmuhli"
  70,9,"Ve tekunulcibalu kelÂṀÄḟhni"
  70,10,"Ve la yesÂṀelu hamiymun hamiymen"
  70,11,"Yubassarunehum yeveddulmucrimu lev yeftediy min ÂṀazabi yevmeizin bibeniyhi"
  70,12,"Ve sahÄḟbetihi ve ehÄḟyhi"
  70,13,"Ve fasÄḟyletihilletiy tuÂṀviyhi"
  70,14,"Ve men fiylÂṀardÄḟ cemiyÂṀan summe yunciyhi"
  70,15,"Kella inneha leza"
  70,16,"NezzaÂṀaten lisseva"
  70,17,"TedÂṀu men edbere ve tevella"
  70,18,"Ve cemaÂṀa feevÂṀa"
  70,19,"InnelÂṀinsane hulika heluÂṀan"
  70,20,"Iza messehusserru cezuÂṀan"
  70,21,"Ve iza messehulhayru menuÂṀan"
  70,22,"Illelmusalliyne"
  70,23,"Elleziynehum ÂṀala salatihim daimune"
  70,24,"Velleziyne fiy emvalihim hakkun maÂṀlumun"
  70,25,"Lissaili velmahrumi"
  70,26,"Velleziyne yusaddikune biyevmiddiyni"
  70,27,"Velleziyne hum min ÂṀazabi rabbihim musrikune"
  70,28,"Inne ÂṀazabe rabbihim gayru meÂṀmunin"
  70,29,"Velleziyne hum lifurucihim hafizune"
  70,30,"Illa ÂṀala ezvacihim ev ma meleket eymanuhum feinnehum gayru melumiyne"
  70,31,"Femenibtega verae zalike feulaike humulÂṀadune"
  70,32,"Velleziyne hum liemanatihim ve ÂṀahdihim raÂṀune"
  70,33,"Velleziyne hum bisehadatihim kaimune"
  70,34,"Velleziyne hum ÂṀala salatihim yuhafizune"
  70,35,"Ulaike fiy cennatin mukremune"
  70,36,"Femalilleziyne keferu kÄḟbeleke muhtÄḟÂṀÄḟyne"
  70,37,"Anilyemiyni ve ÂṀanissimali ÂṀÄḟziyne"
  70,38,"EyatmeÂṀu kullumriin minhum en yudhale cennete naÂṀÄḟymin"
  70,39,"Kella inna halaknahum mimma yaÂṀlemune"
  70,40,"Fela uksimu birabbilmesarikÄḟ velmegaribi inna likadirune"
  70,41,"Ala en nubeddile hayren minhum ve ma nahnu bimesbukÄḟyne"
  70,42,"Fezerhum yehudu ve yelÂṀadune"
  70,43,"Yevme yahrucune minelÂṀecdasi siraÂṀan keennehum ila nusubin yufidune"
  70,44,"HasiÂṀaten ebsaruhum terhekuhum zilletun zalikelyevmulleziy kanu yuÂṀadune"
  71,8,"Summe iniy deÂṀavtuhum ciharen"
  71,9,"Summe inniy aÂṀlentu lehum ve esrertu lehum israren"
  71,10,"Fekultustagfiru rabbekum innehu kane gaffaren"
  71,11,"Yursilissemae ÂṀaleykum midraren"
  71,12,"Ve yumdidkum biemvalin ve beniyne ve yecÂṀal lekum cennatin ve yecÂṀal lekum enharen"
  71,13,"Malekum la tercune lillahi vekaren"
  71,14,"Ve kad halekakum atvaren"
  71,15,"Elem terev keyfe halekallahu sebÂṀa semavetin tÄḟbakan"
  71,16,"Ve ceÂṀalelkamere fiyhinne nuren ve ceÂṀalessemse siracen"
  71,17,"Vallahu enbetekum minelÂṀardÄḟ nebaten"
  71,18,"Summe yuÂṀÄḟydukum fiyha ve yuhricukum Äḟhracen"
  71,19,"Vallahu ceÂṀalelekumul(arda bisatan)"
  71,20,"Litesluku minha subulen ficacen"
  71,21,"Kale nuhun rabbi innehum ÂṀasavniy vettebeÂṀu men lem yezidhu maluhu ve veleduhu illa hasaren"
  71,22,"Ve mekeru mekren kubbaren"
  71,23,"Ve kalu la tezerune alihetekum ve la tezerunne vedden ve la suvaÂṀan ve la yeguse ve yeÂṀuka ve naren"
  71,24,"Ve kad edallu kesiyren ve la tezidizzalimiyne illa dalalen"
  71,25,"Minma hatiyatihim ugriku feudhÄḟhu naren felem yecidu lehum min dunillahi ensaren"
  71,26,"Ve kale nuhun rabbiy la tezer ÂṀalelÂṀardÄḟ minelkafiriyne deyyaren"
  71,27,"Inneke in tezerhum yuodÄḟllu ÂṀÄḟbadeke ve la yehidu illa faciren keffaren"
  71,28,"Rabbigfirliy ve livalideyye ve limen de hale beytiye muÂṀminen ve lilmuÂṀminiyne velmuÂṀminati ve la tezidizzalimiyne illa tebaren"
  72,8,"Ve enna lemesnessemae fevecednaha muliet haresen sediyden ve suhuben"
  72,9,"Ve enna kunna nakÂṀudu minha mekaÂṀÄḟde lissemÂṀÄḟ femen yestemiÂṀÄḟlÂṀane yecid lehu sihahaben resaden"
  72,10,"Ve enna la nedriy eserrun uriyde bimen fiylÂṀardÄḟ em erade bihim rabbuhum reseden"
  72,11,"Ve enna minnessalihune ve minna dune zalike kunna taraika kÄḟdeden"
  72,12,"Ve enna zanenna en len nuÂṀcizallahe fiylÂṀardÄḟ ve len nuÂṀcizehu hereben"
  72,13,"Ve enna lema semiÂṀnelhuda amenna bihi femen yuÂṀmin birabbihi fela yehafu bahsen ve la rehekan"
  72,14,"Ve enna minnelmuslimune ve minnelkasitune femen esleme feulaike teharrev reseden"
  72,15,"Ve emmelkasitune fekanu licehenneme hataben"
  72,16,"Ve en levistekamu ÂṀalettariykati leeskaynahum maen gadekan"
  72,17,"Lineftinehum fiyhi ve men yuÂṀrÄḟd ÂṀan zikri rabbihi yeslukhu ÂṀazaben saÂṀaden"
  72,18,"Ve ennelmesacide lillahi fela tedÂṀu maÂṀallahi ehaden"
  72,19,"Ve ennehu lemma kame ÂṀabdullahi yedÂṀuhu kadu yekunune ÂṀaleyhi libeden"
  72,20,"Kul innema edÂṀu rabbiy ve la usriku bihi ehaden"
  72,21,"Kul inniy la emliku lekum darran ve la reseden"
  72,22,"Kul inniy len yuciyreniy minallahi ehadun ve len ecide min dunihi multehaden"
  72,23,"Illa belagan minallahi ve risalatihi ve men yaÂṀsÄḟllahe ve resulehu feinne lehu nare cehenneme halidiyne fiyha ebeden"
  72,24,"Hatta iza reev ma yuÂṀadune feseyaÂṀlemune men edÂṀafu nasÄḟren ve ekallu ÂṀadeden"
  72,25,"Kul in edriy ekariybun ma tuÂṀadune em yecÂṀalu lehu rabbiy emeden"
  72,26,"ÂṀAlmulgaybi fela yuzhiru ÂṀala gaybihi ehaden"
  72,27,"Illa menirteda min resulin feinnehu yesluku min beyni yedeyhi ve min halfihi resaden"
  72,28,"LiyaÂṀleme en kad eblegu risalati rabbihim ve ehata bima lediyhim ve ahsa kulle seyÂṀin ÂṀadeden"
  73,7,"Inne leke fiynnehari sebhan taviylen"
  73,8,"Vezkurisme rabbike ve tebettel ileyhi tebtiylen"
  73,9,"RabbulmesrikÄḟ velmagribi la ilahe illa huve fettehÄḟzhu vekiylen"
  73,10,"Vasbir ÂṀala ma yekulune vehcurhum hecren cemiylen"
  73,11,"Ve zerniy velmukezzibiyne uliynnaÂṀmeti ve mehhilhum kaliylen"
  73,12,"Inne ledeyna enkalen ve cahÄḟymen"
  73,13,"Ve taÂṀamen za gussatin ve ÂṀazaben eliymen"
  73,14,"Yevme tercufulÂṀardu velcibalu ve kanetilcibalu kesiyben mehiylen"
  73,15,"Inna erselna ileykum resulen sahiden ÂṀaleykum kema erselna ila firÂṀavne resulen"
  73,16,"FeÂṀasa firÂṀavnurresule feehaznahu ahzen vebiylen"
  73,17,"Fekeyfe tettekune in kefertum yevmen yecÂṀalulvildane siyben"
  73,18,"Essemau munfetÄḟrun bihi kane vaÂṀduhu mefÂṀulen"
  73,19,"Inne hazihi tezkiretun femen saettehaze ila rabbihi sebiylen"
  73,20,"Inne rabbeke yaÂṀlemu enneke tekumu edna min suluseyilleyli ve nÄḟsfehu ve sulusehu ve taifetun minelleziyne meÂṀake vallahu yukaddirulleyle vennehare ÂṀalime en len tuhsuhu fetabe ÂṀaleykum fakreu ma teyessere minelkurÂṀani ÂṀalime en seyekunu minkum merda ve aharune yadribune fiylÂṀardÄḟ yebtegune min fadlillahi ve aharune yukatilune fiy sebiylillahi fakreu ma teyessere minhu ve ekÄḟymussalate ve atuzzekate ve akridullahe kardan hasenen ve ma tukaddimu lienfusikum min hayrin teciduhu ÂṀÄḟndallahi huve hayren ve aÂṀzame ecren vestagfirullahe innallahe gafurun rahÄḟymun"
  74,7,"Ve lirabbike fasbir"
