  74,30,"ÂṀAleyha tisÂṀate ÂṀasere"
  74,31,"Ve ma ceÂṀalna ashabennari illa melaiketen ve ma ceÂṀalna ÂṀÄḟddetehum illa fitneten lilleziyne keferu liyesteykÄḟnelleziyne utulkitabe ve yezdadelleziyne amenu iymanen ve la yertabelleziyne utulkitabe velmuÂṀminune ve liyekulelleziyne fiy kulubihim meredun velkafirune maza eradallahu bihaza meselen kezalike yudillullahu men yesaÂṀu ve ma yaÂṀlemu cunude rabbike illa huve ve ma hiye illa zikra lilbeseri"
